Don't wait any longer, start exploring your creativity and indulge in the joy of coloring with our Sugar Skull Coloring Pages game. Click the "play" button now and let the fun begin!71:T5d7,Pixel Peak is an exciting 2D platformer game where players take control of a red-hatted character who must constantly jump upward to overcome various obstacles and reach the top of the level. The game features a pixelated art style that harkens back to classic games of the 80s and 90s, adding a nostalgic touch to the gameplay.
In Pixel Peak, players must navigate through a series of increasingly challenging levels, each filled with unique obstacles such as moving platforms, enemies, and other hazards. Along the way, players can collect power-ups and bonuses that will help them reach new heights and overcome the challenges they face.
One of the standout features of Pixel Peak is its simple, yet addictive gameplay. The controls are easy to learn, with players only needing to jump and maneuver left or right as they climb ever higher. The game also features a high level of replayability, with players able to replay levels in order to achieve higher scores and earn new achievements.
Pixel Peak is a game that is suitable for players of all ages, offering a fun and challenging experience that will keep players coming back for more. With its charming pixel art style, addictive gameplay, and challenging levels, Pixel Peak is a platformer game that is sure to provide hours of entertainment for players of all skill levels.
Overall, Pixel Peak is a fantastic addition to the platformer genre, offering a fun and engaging gameplay experience that is sure to delight players of all ages.72:T45b,In this pseudo-historical game set in the wars of 19th century Europe, you need to achieve global dominance on an isometric map using your skills as a strategist. Ira is distinguished by a humorous approach, where funny majorettes act as soldiers. A turn-based strategy that contains elements of diplomacy, economy, managing your armies (hiring, creating an army, building units, replenishing, moving, attacking the enemy). Armies move along the cells of the isometric map. A game for one player against the computer. There are 8 factions in the game, each with its own characteristics in terms of the strength of certain types of troops, the cost of hiring, the location of cells. The original system of battles, in which not only the number and strength of troops play an important role, but also their timely location, on which the order of attack and the associated advantages depend. There are 4 military companies in which you need to go through the presented factions in turn, achieving in each victory-full dominance on the map for a certain number of moves, except for the last global map of pseudo-Europe.73:T40b,BapBap.gg is a spectacular multiplayer battle royale with cartoon-style graphics. You will be able to play with many different heroes, with unique gameplay and skills. Choose your favorite character and get rdy to battle in the heart of an arena whose playing surface will shrink over time. Use your skills to eliminate your opponents and try to be the last surviving player to win the game. Easy to learn but difficult to master, BapBap offers gameplay rich in possibilities and an infinite progression curve. Learn to master each hero and know every corner of the map to gain the advantage over your enemies. You will also be able to obtain equipment to increase your power and steal equipment from defeated enemies. Inspired by games such as Battlerite Royale, BapBap is simple and intuitive to play, we have fun from the first game!

BapBap.gg features:
- An intense and competitive battle royale mode
- 10 different Heroes, each with unique skills
- A ranking of the best online players
- You can play in team, up to three players74:T51a,Les monstres ont grimpé dans les toilettes! Aidez et sauvez wensday des monstres dans les toilettes. Sauvez Wensday et ses amis: Steve maincraft, Rainbow Friends, Naruto-ils veulent tous aussi échapper aux monstres dans les toilettes! Wensday est là!

Les monstres sont sortis à la chasse et interfèrent avec wensday! 👾

Règles pour le mode Dessin:
- tracez une ligne du personnage aux toilettes; ✍️
- évitez les collisions avec des objets différents 🚧 sinon le personnage n'atteindra pas les toilettes et éclatera; 💥
- essayez de ne pas traverser les lignes des personnages ensemble 🙅 ♀ ️ sinon ils vont se battre;
- aidez vos personnages préférés et wensday à se rendre aux toilettes à temps pour éviter les confusions.

Règles pour jouer à la Corde🪢:
- aidez le personnage à se rendre aux toilettes; 💨
- - prenez la corde d'un bord et transférez-la à l'autre; 📍
- évitez les épines et les épines pour ne pas éclater ⚙️ 📌

Règles pour les Toilettes 🔥 :
- gagnez des pièces dans les niveaux; 💰
- ouvrez les objets dans les chambres et les meubler; 🦑
- après avoir meublé toute la pièce, vous obtiendrez une musique unique, caractéristique de chaque pièce! 🎶

PS. et n'oubliez pas les peaux, il y en a beaucoup dans le magasin!75:Tf48,Jouez et profitez du jeu classique Bubble Shooter ™ Puzzle dans une version puzzle super amusante!

Faites éclater des bulles dans des milliers de niveaux impressionnants dans ce jeu de puzzle gratuit et addictif. Profitez du jeu de puzzle le plus excitant conçu pour garder votre cerveau vif et actif ! Jouez maintenant et découvrez de nombreux défis amusants et des bonus incroyables qui rendent ce jeu de bulles unique en son genre ! Amusez-vous et commencez à tirer des BULLES dès aujourd'hui !

Jouez partout, n'importe où et autant que vous le souhaitez - aucune connexion Internet n'est requise. Partagez le plaisir de faire éclater le ballon avec votre famille et vos amis et voyez qui peut atteindre le meilleur score. Il n'y a pas de durée de vie ou de limite de temps, vous pouvez donc jouer autant que vous le souhaitez !
Écrasez tous les ballons pour vider le plateau et gagner des pièces !

Fan de jeux d'arcade en ligne ? Vous cherchez une façon amusante d'exercer votre cerveau? Essayez ce jeu de bulles relaxant, profitez de tous les puzzles gratuits, créez de puissants combos et GAGNEZ GROS !


Caractéristiques du puzzle Bubble Shooter :
- Mode de jeu classique et addictif.
- Beaucoup d'énigmes et de défis amusants.
- Des milliers de niveaux impressionnants.
- Échange de bulles gratuit ! Appuyez simplement sur votre bulle pour changer sa couleur.
- Boost puissant pour vous aider à faire exploser les balles et à résoudre des énigmes.
- Un jeu gratuit et amusant qui vous divertira pendant des heures !
💣🔥 Boostez votre expérience avec des bonus impressionnants !
Chargez-vous avec des boosts et des power-ups incroyables qui vous aideront à parcourir les niveaux et à vous frayer un chemin à travers les défis difficiles.
* Lâchez 10 ballons en un seul coup pour obtenir une bombe qui éliminera les bulles environnantes.
* Pop 7 balles d'affilée pour obtenir une boule de feu qui coupera à travers une passe.

Bubble Shooter Puzzle est entièrement gratuit et parfait pour jouer et s'amuser à tous les âges. Téléchargez maintenant depuis le Play Store et rejoignez l'aventure amusante du puzzle !


Comment jouer:
* Appuyez sur l'écran pour faire glisser la visée laser et soulevez-la pour faire exploser des bulles.
* Associez 3 balles colorées pour briser le combo et gagner des pièces.
* Relevez le défi avec des milliers de niveaux passionnants.
* Planifiez vos mouvements de chemin et essayez de terminer un niveau avec moins de mouvements pour obtenir un score plus élevé.
* Frappez et faites exploser toutes les bulles et gagnez des cadeaux gratuits !
* Atteignez des scores élevés et essayez d'obtenir trois étoiles à chaque niveau.
* Débloquez de puissants boosters qui vous aideront à franchir les obstacles sur votre chemin.
* Effacez toutes les boules colorées du tableau pour passer au niveau de puzzle génial suivant !
* Terminez les missions pour découvrir de nouveaux défis passionnants.
* Appuyez sur pour changer la couleur de votre bulle, l'échange de bulles est entièrement gratuit.
* Jouez en ligne ou hors ligne - aucune connexion wifi n'est nécessaire.

Mettez vos compétences en logique et en stratégie à l'épreuve ! Améliorez vos compétences de correspondance et profitez d'un gameplay fluide. Entraînez votre cerveau et vos doigts et relevez tous les défis. Résolvez toutes les énigmes et casse-tête et frayez-vous un chemin vers une victoire écrasante !

Téléchargez pour jouer à votre nouveau jeu de puzzle Bubble Shooter ™ préféré uniquement si vous AIMEZ les défis amusants et passionnants.

ÉCLATEZ DES BULLES ET RÉSOLVEZ DES PUZZLES !
C'est une expérience classique d'éclatement de bulles à ne pas manquer !

Avertissement:
Ce jeu est super divertissant et extrêmement addictif!

Tous les droits de Bubble Shooter™ appartiennent à Ilyon Dynamics Ltd.76:T4a2,In Inner Sphere Assassin, you play as a highly trained assassin on a mission to infiltrate a heavily guarded facility and eliminate the target at the center of its inner sphere. Your goal is to navigate through a labyrinth of obstacles and enemy defenses, using stealth, precision, and agility to avoid detection and take out your targets with deadly efficiency.  
  
As you progress through each level, you'll encounter increasingly complex obstacles and enemies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. You'll need to use your wits and cunning to outsmart your enemies, taking advantage of their blind spots and using the environment to your advantage.  
  
To succeed in Inner Sphere Assassin, you'll need to master a variety of skills, including stealth, combat, and strategy. You'll need to stay focused and make split-second decisions as you navigate through the facility, taking out guards, hacking security systems, and avoiding traps and alarms.  
  
With its immersive gameplay, challenging levels, and intuitive controls, Inner Sphere Assassin is the ultimate test of your stealth and assassination skills. Are you ready to take on the challenge? Play now and find out!0:["bfnL36Zy_Z4EAZ-qZH5Ps",[[["",{"children":["__PAGE__",{}]},"$undefined","$undefined",true],["",{"children":["__PAGE__",{},[["$L1",[["$","$L2",null,{}],["$","$L3",null,{"slot":"1111111111","format":"horizontal"}],["$","$4",null,{"fallback":["$","div",null,{"className":"page_loading__4WMny","children":"Chargement..."}],"children":["$","$L5",null,{"games":[{"id":"36DO1","slug":"body-drop-3d","title":"Body Drop 3D","description":"The game will delight you with a realistic simulation of the body falling! Its advantage is not only physics, but also the realistic behavior of the character, his animations, nice graphics and many levels!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36DO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/body-drop-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":46072,"rating":4.9,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GS7CA","slug":"slope-racing-3d","title":"Slope Racing 3D","description":"Welcome to Slope Racing 3D!  It is a 3D running game with perfect controls, breath-taking speeds, and an addictive gameplay. \nHow far can you go without reaching the floor? Try Slope Racing 3D, the more you play the game, the easier it is and the more enjoyable it is. Our goal in the game is to make the ball roll without falling on the surface of the inclined buildings.. Get ready for serious speed boost as you fall downhill the never-ending surface. Play Slope Racing 3D!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GS7CA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slope-racing-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":45437,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7MS9M","slug":"moto-x3m-spooky-land","title":"Moto X3M: Spooky Land","description":"Drive your motorbike through Halloween-themed tracks filled with obstacles and stunt opportunities. Get your bike through the trials quickly to earn more points!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7MS9M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moto-x3m-spooky-land/embed?sid=1","plays":45358,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P11VR","slug":"lol-surprise-insta-party-divas","title":"LOL Surprise Insta Party Divas","description":"Welcome to the LOL Surprise Insta Party Divas. LOL girls heard about the surprise Insta party. They planned to try some new trends. But they need some hands to be perfect. Browse the girl’s wardrobe for perfect outfits and costumes. Before that pick some cute makeover for the girls. Play and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P11VR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lol-surprise-insta-party-divas/embed?sid=1","plays":45247,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"35LBE","slug":"basketball-stars","title":"Basketball Stars","description":"Basketball Stars is a 2-player basketball game. In this game, you can play with your favorite team and play with basketball legends. In this game, you can either play with friends in 2-player mode or solo in single-player mode.\nShow off your basketball skills and see if you can score a three-pointer or slam home an impressive dunk! You can play as many different legendary teams and try out both your defensive and offensive skills.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/35LBE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":44852,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20XI2","slug":"drunken-boxing-2","title":"Drunken Boxing 2","description":"New game is live for boxing lovers! Drunken Boxing 2 offers a new gaming experience with renewed animations, effects and 3D graphics. Try to control the Drunken Boxers and throw quick punches at your opponent but watch out for your Energy Bar! If you run out of energy, it will take a while for you to recover. Make forward and backward moves, throw quick punches and win the match!\n\nDrunken Boxing game has 1P and 2P modes. The first to reach a score of 5 in the game wins the match!\n\nGame Controls:\nPLAYER 1: \"ARROW KEYS\"\nPLAYER 2: \"W,A,S,D\"","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20XI2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drunken-boxing-2/embed?sid=1","plays":44844,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NG7TT","slug":"among-at-easter","title":"Among at Easter","description":"Play online or over local WiFi with 4-10 players as you attempt to prep your spaceship for departure, but beware as one will be an impostor bent on killing everyone!\n\nCrewmates can win by completing all tasks or discovering and voting the impostor off the ship.\n\nThe Impostor can use sabotage to cause chaos, making for easier kills and better alibis.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NG7TT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/among-at-easter/embed?sid=1","plays":44740,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40434","slug":"magikmon","title":"Magikmon","description":"Magikmon is an awesome RPG game in which you must capture different types of monsters. The magical world you live in is packed full with weird and wonderful monsters. You can use them to battle! Enjoy it!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40434/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magikmon/embed?sid=1","plays":44728,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O2NNU","slug":"battle-simluator-counter-stickman","title":"Battle Simluator - Counter Stickman","description":"The stickmen must strike at the terror enemy stickmen in this Battle Simulator\n\nThe stickmen terror forces must be stopped with a tactical strike! You are the battle commander of the counter terrorist stickman (CTS) forces.\n\n▶TABS simulator - style gameplay\n▶3D stickmen, levels and gun models\n▶Help win the stickman war.. on terror!\n▶Accurate stickman tactics\n\nSounds: Freesound.org\nMusic_cornandbeans_generic_techno","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O2NNU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-stickman/embed?sid=1","plays":44705,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L6TL9","slug":"fractal-combat-x","title":"Fractal Combat X","description":"FCX is an HTML5 action-packed flight combat game, sporting top notch 3D graphics, WebGL and a progressively intense gameplay!\n\nMAIN FEATURES\n- Exciting, fast-paced arcade flight combat action\n- Top notch 3D graphics\n- Unique gorgeous fractal landscapes\n- Dozens of missions in Story mode\n- New missions every day!\n- Epic sound tracks\n- Arcade and Simulator modes\n- Cross-device","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L6TL9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fractal-combat-x/embed?sid=1","plays":44699,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EYN60","slug":"funny-throat-surgery","title":"Funny Throat Surgery","description":"Having a throat sore? Let the doctor see you! Cure the diseases on you gums, destroy all bacteries, and remove the infected amandels. Get some cute and funny dress up at the end of your journey to the doctor. It's important to be healthy and stylish!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EYN60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-throat-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":44452,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N6AV","slug":"vangers-hd","title":"Vangers HD","description":"Mind-altering sandbox game that can be described as a racing role-playing adventure game with a complicated storyline. You’ll find a unique atmosphere, complete freedom and lots of gameplay hours to figure out what’s the game is all about.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","classics","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N6AV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vangers/embed?sid=1","plays":44151,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40450","slug":"alpha-guns","title":"Alpha Guns","description":"Alpha Guns a 2D side scroller shooter with classic gameplay and unique mechanics. Play as a soldier from the Elite Force!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40450/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alpha-guns/embed?sid=1","plays":44074,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20048","slug":"foot-chinko","title":"Foot Chinko","description":"Défiez vos adversaires dans le tournoi de football le plus célèbre au monde. Serez-vous assez doué pour rafler toutes les récompenses des 90 niveaux du jeu ? Assez brave pour vous confronter au gardien de but surnommé le \"gardien du diable\" ? Nous verrons!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20048/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/foot-chinko/embed?sid=1","plays":44071,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TM7A","slug":"football-masters","title":"Football Masters","description":"Football Masters Euro 2020 is a fun soccer game.  In this game, you can play as your favorite team and compete against other teams in challenging football matches; solo or together with your friends. Show your best ball kicking moves! \n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TM7A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-masters/embed?sid=1","plays":43950,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DDY8C","slug":"red-and-blue-stickman-huggy","title":"Red and Blue Stickman Huggy","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of two very cute brothers, namely blue and red stickman? Brothers red and blue need to get the key and reach the door. Be two people and get them to the door with your friend. reach the door and pass it to the new level. You will face multiple challenges but reach the door. \n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys                  \n*Double Jump available                  \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DDY8C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-blue-stickman-huggy/embed?sid=1","plays":43901,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54418","slug":"pixel-on-titan","title":"Pixel on Titan","description":"The titans is coming and attacking the city, you need to save the civilians in the city by killing all the titans in this beautiful pixel art game based on manga or anime attack on titan (AoT).\n\n*This game will be updated periodically\n\nMove Left = A   Move Right = D  Attack = F  Jump to Certain Direction = Left Mouse Click","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54418/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-on-titan/embed?sid=1","plays":43891,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PVPRV","slug":"red-impostor-vs-crew","title":"Red Impostor vs. Crew","description":"Red Imposter vs. Crew is a fun and engaging Action game. Your mission is simple: Execute all living crewmates in the spaceship. Let no one survive.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PVPRV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-impostor-vs-crew/embed?sid=1","plays":43859,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40214","slug":"cut-the-rope-2","title":"Cut the Rope 2","description":"Cut the Rope 2 reprend les éléments qui ont fait le succès du premier volet, tout en ajoutant de nouveaux défis et des obstacles inattendus pour le plus grand bonheur des millions de fans aux quatre coins du globe ! Vous avez aimé Cut the Rope ? Vous allez adorer Cut the Rope 2!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40214/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cut-the-rope-2/embed?sid=1","plays":43854,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40344","slug":"bomber-friends","title":"Bomber Friends","description":"Fais exploser tes amis et remporte le match en étant le dernier survivant! Ramasse les bonus pour obtenir des bombes toujours plus puissantes! Utilise les bombes explosives pour souffler tes amis à travers toute la carte!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40344/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bomber-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":43821,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L81O9","slug":"poly-art","title":"Poly Art","description":"Des dizaines d'animaux, de plantes, de véhicules, de fleurs et plus encore. Voilà ce qui vous attend dans cette œuvre d'art absolument fantastique et relaxante. Assemblez de belles images à partir de fragments et complétez tous les segments du jeu.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L81O9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poly-art/embed?sid=1","plays":43804,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40263","slug":"1941-frozen-front","title":"1941 Frozen Front","description":"Menez les forces allemandes lors de la poussée vers l'Est ou défendez la mère patrie du côté soviétique. Choisissez la bonne tactique de guerre et gagnez vos galons en commandant de manière ingénieuse dans FROZEN FRONT ! Découvrez des batailles de la seconde guerre mondiale époustouflantes dans la toute nouvelle simulation militaire et STRATÉGIQUE de HandyGames™!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40263/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/1941-frozen-front/embed?sid=1","plays":43751,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40071","slug":"cut-the-rope","title":"Cut The Rope","description":"Vous avez reçu un mystérieux paquet, et le petit monstre à l’intérieur n’a envie que d’une chose… de BONBONS ! Collectez les étoiles dorées, découvrez les prix cachés et débloquez de nouveaux niveaux dans ce jeu addictif acclamé par la critique et au moteur physique réaliste!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40071/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cut-the-rope/embed?sid=1","plays":43711,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GC2MR","slug":"my-sugar-factory","title":"My Sugar Factory","description":"My Sugar Factory is a turn-based game about managing a sugar factory. Start with one sugar cane bush and earn millions! Buy a factory and open a laboratory to improve the sugar cane variety.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GC2MR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-sugar-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":43707,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40337","slug":"cut-the-rope-experiments","title":"Cut the Rope Experiments","description":"Le petit monstre vert Om Nom est de retour et il est plus affamé que jamais! Faites équipe avec le Professeur, un savant un peu fou (mais pas voyou!) résolu à étudier le goût prononcé de Om Nom pour les bonbons à l'aide d'expérimentations en tout genre. Dévoiler les prix cachés et déverrouiller de nouveaux niveaux! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40337/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cut-the-rope-experiments/embed?sid=1","plays":43703,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"35L6I","slug":"flip-goal","title":"Flip Goal","description":"Aim the ball to hit the goal! Time your kick perfectly without touching any other soccer players. Pick up your favourite team!\n\nAs you progress, you’ll collect coins to upgrade your soccer stadium and get new soccer balls!\n\nWin the soccer tournament, collect keys and open chests for more coins!\n\nBecome the world champion! With easy controls, Flip Goal gives you a whole new level of soccer experience.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/35L6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flip-goal/embed?sid=1","plays":43677,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ADHH2","slug":"dash-masters","title":"Dash Masters","description":"Les règles sont simples. Touchez l'écran pour sauter tous azimuts et faites glisser votre doigt vers le haut pour exécuter un Rush.\n\nIl y a 20 ans, les extraterrestres ont attaqué. Des milliards d'innocents ont péri.\n\nQuelques-uns d'entre nous sont parvenus à échapper in extremis à ce massacre systématique ! Nous nous sommes alors cachés et avons tout mis en œuvre pour créer la seule et unique arme qui nous permettrait de libérer la Terre et d'anéantir cette race d'aliens artificiels que nous avons surnommée les Robots.\n\nÉquipé de l'exo-armure C-31, vous tenterez l'impossible : infiltrer les tours offensives des extraterrestres et les démolir. Utilisez vos propulseurs pour détruire les Robots gardiens et frayez-vous un chemin à travers les défenses ennemies.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ADHH2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dash-masters/embed?sid=1","plays":43653,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T02T0","slug":"tower-crush","title":"Tower Crush","description":"Tower Crush is an epic indie game where you build 1 tower, up to 6 floors, load them with weapons, upgrade, evolve and defeat your opponents in fantastic battles. A combination of action and strategy!\n\nDon't fear, you’ll collect Machine Guns, Cannons, Flame Guns, Bomb Launchers, Shockwaves, Rocket Launchers, Lasers, Teslas, Ice Cannons and Mighty Plasma Cannons to help defend your tower. Unleash the most devastating special powers upon your enemies in this Combat Game.","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T02T0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-crush/embed?sid=1","plays":43583,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LNI17","slug":"lol-surprise-fresh-spring-look","title":"LOL Surprise Fresh Spring Look","description":"Welcome to the LOL Surprise Fresh Spring Look.  LOL Suprise Girls have some plans for welcoming their favorite season spring. They already filled their cupboard with new spring fashion. But they have a dilemma is to choose the best outfits. Browse the wardrobe and pick the suitable outfits for each one.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LNI17/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lol-surprise-fresh-spring-look/embed?sid=1","plays":43559,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"871A2","slug":"swipy-basketball","title":"Swipy Basketball","description":"Swipy Basketball is the new basketball game you can play on any device! Swipe the balls towards the hoop and reach an higher score.\nCollect stars to unlock new skins. Improve your skills and become the master of Swipy Basketball!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/871A2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swipy-basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":43556,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0730R","slug":"superbike-hero","title":"Superbike Hero","description":"Compete across Europe and the Middle East as you race in the Superbike Series. Boost between opponents, hang-on around tight corners, collect coins and upgrade your superbike for the next race. Are you the Superbike Hero?","category":"Course","tags":["sports","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0730R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superbike-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":43556,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G7625","slug":"god-of-light","title":"God of Light","description":"nstallez-vous confortablement et immergez-vous corps et âme au cœur du monde de God of Light, un jeu lumineux qui va en faire voir de toutes les couleurs à votre matière grise ! \nAvec son extraordinaire gameplay qui met l’accent sur l’exploration, ses visuels splendides et sa bande-son génialissime signée UNKLE (le géant de la musique électronique), ce titre fait exploser les fondations du puzzle-game et repousse les lois de la physique vidéoludique pour offrir une expérience purement et simplement hors-norme !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G7625/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/god-of-light/embed?sid=1","plays":43526,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"037S6","slug":"rabbit-samurai-2","title":"Rabbit Samurai 2","description":"Throw the rope and swing around to find all little bees and bring them back home.   ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/037S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rabbit-samurai-2/embed?sid=1","plays":43483,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9I093","slug":"helix-blitz","title":"Helix Blitz","description":"Helix Blitz, the ultimate arcade game where you need to move the ball of paint down the helixes! Try to avoid the helixes and enter the cool Blitz mode!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9I093/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/helix-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":43460,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B34R1","slug":"drag-racing-club","title":"Drag Racing Club","description":"Entrez dans le monde passionnant des courses de dragsters dans ce jeu unique. Commencez comme outsider inconnu et frayez-vous un chemin jusqu'au sommet. Prouvez à tout le monde que vous êtes le meilleur pilote de la ville. Pour y parvenir, vous devrez acheter ou gagner les superbes voitures de vos adversaires. Ensuite tunez-les pour en faire des bolides puissants. En piste !\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B34R1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drag-racing-club/embed?sid=1","plays":43416,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"45TBR","slug":"babel-tower","title":"Babel Tower","description":"You are building the Tower of Babel, that will reach to the sky!\nYou have a team of professionals: miners, masons, crafters, lumberjacks, builders, who will help you achieve success in this incremental idle game.\n\nNew fun machines are unlocked with every tower floor.\n\nThe game was made by Airapport and expands our idle games universe. \n\nControls\nPress-and-hold on the screen to mine stone, transfer stone to processing, speed up bricks creation, chop trees, and perform other activities.\n\nSell part of your resources at the Market to gain money for upgrades. At certain upgrade level the building works by itself, you will be spectating and having fun.\n\nRestarting your tower building gives you Golden Bricks, which boost your tap power, production and increase market prices.\n\nIf you are away you are earning time bonus, which can be used to speed up game processes.\n\nBuy special artifacts to boost your progress even further.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/45TBR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/babel-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":43366,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ERSEI","slug":"supermarket-expert-idle","title":"Supermarket Expert Idle","description":"A new Supermarket idle adventure is now beginning with the experts of this job. You have just opened a new supermarket in your town and you should manage there. There are lots of customers visiting your supermarket daily. You can earn good money and you can open new departments inside your supermarket. More departments mean more income. Don't forget to do your upgrades within the upgrade menu. You can buy helpers and do your work faster. Let the Supermarket Expert Idle adventure begin!\n\nHow to play?\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\" or \"W,A,S,D\" or \"MOUSE\" and \"LEFT-CLICK\"\n\nPick products from the places where they grow up or are produced and place them inside their departments and check out customers on the counter and earn money.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ERSEI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/supermarket-expert-idle/embed?sid=1","plays":43328,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40307","slug":"basket-champs","title":"Basket Champs","description":"Basket Champs is the brand new game from the developer of Foot Chinko. Select your basketball team and play in World Championship.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40307/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basket-champs/embed?sid=1","plays":43327,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IIAOR","slug":"funny-shooter-destroy-all-enemies","title":"Funny Shooter - Destroy all enemies","description":"Choose your weapon from the 18 available. Protect yourself from the invasion of enemies. Enemies differ in size and ability. Avoid enemy grenades and pitchforks. Dodge blows from clubs, axes, and chainsaws. Destroy enemies with a grenade launcher and a bazooka. Shoot them with machine guns and pistols. Destroy them all !!!       \n       \nFeatures:       \n- beautiful graphics       \n- a variety of weapons       \n- addictive gameplay       \n- driving music and great sound effects","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IIAOR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-shooter-destroy-all-enemies/embed?sid=1","plays":43321,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4B1SB","slug":"skyblock","title":"Skyblock","description":"Minecraft - SkyBlock Description Skyblock is a popular challenge, where the player starts the game in a small island in the void, including a tree and often a chest, which contains items you couldn't get without it. WASD or arrows Mouse or Touch","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4B1SB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skyblock/embed?sid=1","plays":43290,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40415","slug":"stock-car-hero","title":"Stock Car Hero","description":"Compete across North America as you race in the Stock Car Series. Dodge traffic, boost around banked corners, collect coins and upgrade your car for the next race. Are you the Stock Car Hero the world needs?","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40415/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stock-car-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":43256,"rating":4.8,"featured":true,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6A631","slug":"mr-santa-run-2","title":"Mr Santa Run 2","description":"mr santa run 2 is a html5 arcade game, run and avoid enemy, collect star to earn score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6A631/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-santa-run-2/embed?sid=1","plays":43249,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40422","slug":"street-ball-jam","title":"Street Ball Jam","description":"A one-touch basketball arcade game with an endless gameplay. Unlock all balls, earn crystals to open extra courts and enjoy Street Ball Jam!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40422/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/street-ball-jam/embed?sid=1","plays":43245,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TC86D","slug":"castel-war-3d","title":"Castel War 3D","description":"Defeat the opponent by collecting the balls and make troops. \n\nLet’s join the epic fight 3d simulator, fight like the strongest army clash in the town to defend your castle fight from the extreme fighting and crazy enemies. It is your duty to claim your legacy as a big hero warrior, assemble your epic clash army troops, get them ready for 3d battle view and destroy the enemy stick army of and become the master of the 3d battle view. Defend your gang clash castle fight as a big battle hero of your town.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TC86D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/castel-war-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":43215,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C4LMG","slug":"ultimate-flying-car","title":"Ultimate Flying Car","description":"Do you want to take fast rides and flights on the long streets of the city? Ultimate Flying Car game invites you to realistic flying car simulator experience. Explore the sky with stylish flying cars, or unlock new cars by participating in races. You can play all of these game modes either 1 player or 2 player.\n\nPlayer 1:\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\"\nNOS: \"SHIFT  \"\nLook back: \"T\"\nFix car's position: \"R\"\nHandbrake: \"SPACE\"\n\nPlayer 2:\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\"\nNOS: \"M\"\nLook back: \"L\"\nFix car's position: \"U\"\nHandbrake: \"K\"","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C4LMG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ultimate-flying-car/embed?sid=1","plays":43173,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40407","slug":"bouncy-dunk","title":"Bouncy Dunk","description":"Get ready, shoot, score and WIN: Bouncy Dunk will make your excitement grow! Test your skills by winning all the challenges and unlock special basketballs to grow your power and style! Become a Bouncy Champion NOW!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40407/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncy-dunk/embed?sid=1","plays":43064,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20049","slug":"metal-animals","title":"Metal Animals","description":"Appelez les Metal Animals à la rescousse! Prenez le contrôle d'une escouade de petits animaux à fourrure aussi mignons que déterminés et défendez votre Tank face à l'ennemi!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20049/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/metal-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":43020,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40272","slug":"dark-lands","title":"Dark Lands","description":"Frayez-vous un chemin au travers de hordes de squelettes, de trolls et affrontez les terribles scorpions et minotaures. Améliorez votre héros pour venir à bout du monde aventure et survivre au mode infini. Courez pour votre survie!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40272/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dark-lands/embed?sid=1","plays":43014,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40405","slug":"foot-chinko-world-cup","title":"Foot Chinko World Cup","description":"Foot Chinko World Cup features a different take on soccer games with a unique blend of pachinko and pinball. As fun as soccer can get!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40405/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/foot-chinko-world-cup/embed?sid=1","plays":43006,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23ES5","slug":"deadswitch-3","title":"Deadswitch 3","description":"Deadswitch 3 is a fast-paced 2D multiplayer shooter with plenty of game modes, maps, and weapons!","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23ES5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deadswitch-3/embed?sid=1","plays":42926,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6O6G5","slug":"monster-go","title":"Monster Go","description":"Les Pokémonstres ne sont heureux qu'à deux ! Reliez-les à de l'énergie pour les activer. Amusez-vous avec ce jeu de casse-têtes simple mais addictif. N'oubliez pas de remplir le plateau de jeu de courant pour rendre les Pokémonstres heureux et gagner 3 étoiles. Les flux d'énergie ne peuvent ni se croiser ni se chevaucher.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6O6G5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-go/embed?sid=1","plays":42925,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20067","slug":"penalty-shooters","title":"Penalty Shooters","description":"2 joueurs, un ballon et un but - la guerre des penalty peut commencer ! Résisterez-vous à la pression des milliers de supporters pour gagner la coupe de ce jeu de foot hyper excitant ? Choisissez parmi 32 équipes et devenez le plus grand champion de tous les temps!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20067/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-shooters/embed?sid=1","plays":42906,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8MSVS","slug":"masquerades-vs-impostors","title":"Masquerades vs Impostors","description":"The man in the red and blue mask needs to escape from the spaceship? you must help them. watch out, only red colored impostors with red masks can kill. Likewise with the blue mask. Anyone can kill their own color. watch out for zombies, kill them too.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  \n*double jump available  \n*jump on it to kill!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8MSVS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/masquerades-vs-impostors/embed?sid=1","plays":42884,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UR833","slug":"drunken-duel","title":"Drunken Duel","description":"\nDrunken Duel is an entertaining western game with physics-based one-button control that can be played as two people and one person. In the game, two drunk rag dolls duel. You can hit the chance serial target by firing randomly, but you can lose by playing this way. It is possible to take more professional shots by mastering the physics of the game after a few games. The sounds and visual effects in the game make the game more fun.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UR833/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drunken-duel/embed?sid=1","plays":42875,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S4271","slug":"push-noob","title":"Push Noob","description":"Push Noob - is an amazing simulator game about a dancing Noob and his fall. Join the earning of diamonds for pumping Noob and opening new locations.\nThrow snowballs at Noob and get diamonds for his collisions! Unlock new levels and skins! Compete in the amount of diamonds earned!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S4271/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/push-noob/embed?sid=1","plays":42874,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZB7M7","slug":"special-strike-zombies","title":"Special Strike Zombies","description":"You are special forces soldier and your mission is to use big arsenal of weapons to shoot hordes of zombies and mercenaries, choose suitable weapon for each wave of enemies in order to survive and successfully complete each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZB7M7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/special-strike-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":42872,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40232","slug":"little-alchemy","title":"Little Alchemy","description":"Libérez votre pouvoir créatif! Commencez avec les quatre éléments de base et utilisez-les pour trouver des dinosaures, des licornes et des vaisseaux spatiaux!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40232/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-alchemy/embed?sid=1","plays":42794,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40376","slug":"cut-the-rope-magic","title":"Cut the Rope: Magic","description":"Rejoins la dernière aventure d'Om Nom et transforme ce charmant petit monstre par magie pour l'aider à récupérer ses bonbons volés par un sorcier magique! Un incident magique a accidentellement téléporté Om Nom vers un monde mystique rempli d'énigmes complexes pour des joueurs de tous les âges. Sauras-tu utiliser les nouvelles compétences d'Om Nom pour déjouer les ruses et pièges d'un sorcier maléfique?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40376/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cut-the-rope-magic/embed?sid=1","plays":42790,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3MA1","slug":"geometrical-dash","title":"Geometrical Dash","description":"Contrôlez un carré et arrivez à la fin, c'est tout ! Mais ce n'est pas aussi facile. Les niveaux que vous traverserez sont des labyrinthes de pixels conçus pour tester vos réflexes. La seule chose que vous devez faire, c'est sauter, sauter, et sauter encore au son de la musique ! Alors plongez dans ce jeu et goûtez au rythme de ce jeu délicat !\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3MA1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometrical-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":42754,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51E00","slug":"king-rugni-tower-defense","title":"King Rugni Tower Defense","description":"A classic Tower Defense game with lots of enemies and territories to conquer. Join King Rügni on his epic adventure against hordes of elementals.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51E00/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-rugni-tower-conquest/embed?sid=1","plays":42639,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6B1I8","slug":"baby-hazel-bed-time","title":"Baby Hazel Bed Time","description":"Stars are twinkling in the sky and night seems beautiful in moonlight. Baby Hazel is now ready to go to bed but before that she needs to brush her teeth and take a shower. Help Hazel in carrying her bedtime activities. Make a bed for her and pamper the little girl by telling her interesting stories. If bad dream scares Hazel, pamper her with kisses and playing lullabies.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6B1I8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-bed-time/embed?sid=1","plays":42607,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SM1PS","slug":"master-chess-multiplayer","title":"Master Chess Multiplayer","description":"\"Use the most effective strategies to defeat the computer or real players from all over the world in this classic game for all time.\n\nThe goal of the game is to capture your opponent's king. This is done by moving the pieces on the board.\n\nWho will be the first to say \"\"Checkmate\"\".\n\nTo make a move, click on the shape and drag it to the desired position.\"","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SM1PS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/master-chess-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":42575,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9DK7H","slug":"stacky-dash-nail","title":"Stacky Dash Nail","description":"Nail Stack is an hyper casual arcade game available on the web. This game focuses on stacking fingernails. The longer the nails, the bigger the reward for each level. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9DK7H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stacky-dash-nail/embed?sid=1","plays":42561,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SL86T","slug":"basketball-master","title":"Basketball Master","description":"Un défi pour les vrais joueurs de basket et de streetball ! Sautez avec le ballon et faites un panier dans le délai imparti. Obtenez le meilleur score et collectez des pièces. Débloquez tous les ballons et lieux. Essayez 2 modes de jeu. Il vous faudra un timing précis, viser juste et un peu de chance.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SL86T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-masters/embed?sid=1","plays":42553,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6S1Y8","slug":"funny-rescue-pet","title":"Funny Rescue Pet","description":"Lica and Purry had an accident! Lica's house is on fire, and Purry is soak wet when she played inside the wall. How can it happen? Rescue them immediately and also give them some makeover!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6S1Y8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-rescue-pet/embed?sid=1","plays":42537,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"27115","slug":"bois-d-arc-bow-shooting","title":"Bois d'Arc: Bow Shooting","description":"Défendez votre château contre des forces obscures qui tentent de violer inimaginables ses puissants murs. Choisir l'un des trois royaumes arc de tir de héros dans ce jeu de tir arc super addictif et bourré d'action. Bois D'Arc déjà a déjà été joué par des millions sur les nombreux sites de jeu différents. Par conséquent VascoGames est fier de vous présenter la version complète mobile de ce jeu de tir à l'arc, choisissez votre héros et prendre les forces de mal sur la tête!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/27115/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bois-d-arc/embed?sid=1","plays":42530,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"24A7L","slug":"kobadoo-flags","title":"Kobadoo Flags","description":"Kobadoo Flags is a browser game that trains your brain by memorizing flags of the World in the right order.\n\nWhen you play Kobadoo Flags you are actively using your working memory. Several scientific studies suggest that training of working memory has beneficial effects and can increase your cognitive functions.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/24A7L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kobadoo-flags/embed?sid=1","plays":42512,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R628C","slug":"halloween-horror-massacre","title":"Halloween Horror Massacre","description":"Halloween approche à grands pas, tout comme les nuits d'hiver froides et effrayantes ! Les horribles monstres ont aussi froid la nuit, alors ils doivent ajouter du bois à la chaudière. En plus de couper des têtes, ils doivent couper du bois ! Mais attention, leurs branches sont aussi dirigées vers vous ! Coupez autant de bûches que possible de l'arbre tout en évitant les branches qui approchent ! Changez de position pour éviter le danger. Avez-vous ce qu'il faut pour gagner la médaille d'or ?\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R628C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-horror-massacre/embed?sid=1","plays":42504,"rating":4.8,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K41PS","slug":"killer-escape-huggy","title":"Killer Escape Huggy","description":"you are a murderer! And you have to kill all your teammates kill them all. Hunt down all your teammates and unleash the killer emotion inside the blue huggy. Only you can see the karambit in your hand, don't forget they're all dead secretly, hide, come out and kill the killer Huggy!  \n\nHow to Play?\nUse Arrow keys to move.  \nMobile control available.  \nKill all your teammates.  \nKill everyone before time runs out.  \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K41PS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/killer-escape-huggy/embed?sid=1","plays":42487,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G32O2","slug":"red-impostor-guys","title":"Red Impostor Guys","description":"Red impostor guys Welcome to the Game World!\nFinish dozens of courses and collect crowns. Be the winner of the day! Buy the costumes and your image has been changed. Race with 10-40 people, be the winner of the race! Join the world of Fall Days. Race with different costumes on different maps! Make the Difference.\n10 Maps\n20 Uniform Costumes\nA completely different mechanic is waiting for you!\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + ZQSD + Arrow Keys And Mobile Touch Controls","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G32O2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-mpostor-guys/embed?sid=1","plays":42486,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"999D9","slug":"death-run","title":"Death Run","description":"This game is an adventure game. You have thousands of lives in your hands. The game is full of various agencies. As the controller of the agency, you can repel all people and avoid passing.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/999D9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/death-run/embed?sid=1","plays":42437,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3N322","slug":"night-city-racing","title":"Night City Racing","description":"Night City has been prepared for the night races with this great car simulator game! It is time to challenge your opponents and prove to them you are the most skillful driver of all time. The best side of this adventure is to be played in both single player and in two player game modes. You can pick between various cars and you can customize these cars in the shop and you can have great moments while flying or while racing or while driving for free. Let the super Night City adventure begin!\n\nHow to play? \n\nIf playing single:\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\" or \"ARROW KEYS\"\nNOS: \"L-SHIFT\" or \"R-SHIFT\"\nRestart car position: \"R\"\nLook back: \"T\"\nChange camera view: \"C\"\n\nIf playing two player:\nPlayer 1:\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\"\nNOS: \"M\"\nRestart car position: \"O\"\nLook back: \"P\"\nChange camera view: \"K\"\n\nPlayer 2:\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\"\nNOS: \"L-SHIFT\"\nRestart car position: \"R\"\nLook back: \"T\"\nChange camera view: \"C\"","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3N322/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/night-city-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":42397,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7PE6N","slug":"hunters-and-props","title":"Hunters and Props","description":"Hunt or be hunted in this fun first-person shooter game! Pretend that you are one of the props or play as the hunter in Hunter and Props!\n\nHunter and Props is a first-person multiplayer shooter game where the team is divided into two: the hunter, and the props. Playing as the hunter is quite easy, your goal is to shoot other players that are pretending to be the props and should not miss. Playing as one of the props is a bit tricky as you have to be both patient and cunning with your disguise. Remember the saying that the \"best way to hide a tree is in the forest\" and keep your disguise perfect. Good luck and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7PE6N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hunters-and-props/embed?sid=1","plays":42377,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9T02R","slug":"smart-looter","title":"Smart Looter","description":"Be quick and sneaky and grab tons of loots! Watch out for the patrols and become the king of thieves!\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9T02R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smart-looter/embed?sid=1","plays":42348,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CD7KS","slug":"red-stickman-vs-monster-school","title":"Red Stickman vs Monster School","description":"Stickman vs Monster School - is a perfect game for the lovers of Red And Blue Stickman Adventure! The Stick Adventure is an addictive platform fighting game, where you have to control characters. Participate in the Monster School challenge together with the Red Stickman.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CD7KS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-stickman-vs-monster-school/embed?sid=1","plays":42338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TOD6","slug":"wounded-winter-a-lakota-story","title":"Wounded Winter A Lakota Story","description":"\n\nAbout\nWounded Winter: A Lakota Story is a free action / shooter western game with a beautiful low poly graphic.\nStory\nThe hero of the story is called Akecheta, who is a Lakota(Native American). The Akecheta tribe is attacked and its people are killed while he is hunting. The attackers also took Akecheta's wife with them. Akecheta embarks on a perilous journey to bring his wife back and avenge the murderers of his tribe.\nFeatures:\n\n    Beautiful low poly style graphic\n    Strong native American protagonist\n    Fun and exciting action/shooter gameplay\n    Easy to pick up and play\n    For fans of western and action games\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TOD6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wounded-winter-a-lakota-story/embed?sid=1","plays":42332,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40621","slug":"10-blocks","title":"10 Blocks","description":"10 Blocks puzzle game is addicting brain tester game play. You need to place the given blocks on grid, while trying to fill up with grid rowscolumns blocks will disappear when are filled up horizontally or vertically. Always plan for next move because some blocks are not easy to fit in. You can use GRAVITY BUTTON once. Use it if you feeling stuck.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40621/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/10x10/embed?sid=1","plays":42309,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40442","slug":"angry-gran","title":"Angry Gran","description":"Play the game that began the Angry Gran series and take to the streets and whack those punk neighbors! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40442/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angry-gran/embed?sid=1","plays":42292,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57RZE","slug":"baby-hazel-backyard-party","title":"Baby Hazel Backyard Party","description":"Baby Hazel was busy watching her favorite TV show, suddenly she got an idea of backyard party. She will be hosting the party first time, so she needs your help in decorating the venue and making all other necessary arrangements for the gathering. Play the game to help Hazel in organizing the party and also make sure guests are served properly.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57RZE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-backyard-party/embed?sid=1","plays":42254,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C494N","slug":"russian-car-drift-3d","title":"Russian Car Drift 3D","description":"Russian Car Drift 3D is an HTML5 3D driving game that challenges you to get rid of the snow in each level using nothing but your crazy Russian vehicle. To do so, just skid & drift non-stop. The more you drift, the better! Drift in an old or new Russian car!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C494N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-car-drift-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":42244,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33","slug":"zombie-can-t-jump","title":"Zombie Can't Jump","description":"Préparez-vous à l'invasion des zombies! Prenez vos armes, votre kit de construction et ne laissez pas les zombies vous mettre K.O! Organisez votre défense: TNT, pieux ou encore nids de mitrailleuses, récupérez de nouvelles armes surpuissantes et libérez votre fureur pour survivre!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-cant-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":42239,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2R2U6","slug":"draw-save-puzzle","title":"Draw Save Puzzle","description":"Le modèle de jeu Draw Save Puzzle est un modèle de projet complet qui est un jeu de puzzle 2D.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2R2U6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/draw-save-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":42225,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TOC58","slug":"tic-tac-toe-mania","title":"Tic Tac Toe Mania","description":"Tic Tac Toe Mania est un excellent moyen de passer votre temps. Arrêtez de gaspiller du papier et sauvez les arbres. Jouez à Tic Tac Toe Mania sur votre appareil et profitez de nombreuses heures de divertissement seul ou avec vos amis.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TOC58/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tic-tac-toe-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":42187,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40334","slug":"grand-prix-hero","title":"Grand Prix Hero","description":"Compete across multiple continents as you race in the Grand Prix Series. Dodge traffic, boost at high speeds, collect coins and upgrade your car for the next race. Are you the Grand Prix Hero?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40334/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-prix-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":42179,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40417","slug":"boss-level-pumpkin-madness","title":"Boss Level - Pumpkin Madness","description":"Enjoy this Halloween version of the Boss Level Shootout original game. Billy boy fell into a retro game console and is now fighting the boss!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40417/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boss-level-pumpkin-madness/embed?sid=1","plays":42145,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"562TT","slug":"battboy-adventure","title":"Battboy Adventure","description":"“Battboy Adventure” is a platform game, where the hero must overcome all the levels by dodging the thorns and eliminating the villains (killer clowns). Collect all the stars to complete the game 100%. The graphics are colorful, cartoonized and beautiful. Altogether, there are 08 levels that increase the difficulty as the player goes through each one.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/562TT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battboy-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":42131,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I29FM","slug":"flamit","title":"Flamit","description":"Light all the torches as fast as you can in this engaging platform.\nBut do it fast, because a your flame won't last forever!\nFeaturing:\n- 30 one-screen levels full of funny obstacles\n- 2 Different game mode\n- spikes\n- ice enemies\n- more spikes\n- snow\n- A lot of torches\n\nControls\nTouch the screen controls or use arrow keys to move the Player\n\n- 30 one-screen levels full of funny obstacles\n- 2 Different game mode\n- spikes\n- ice enemies\n- more spikes\n- snow\n- A lot of torches","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I29FM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flamit/embed?sid=1","plays":42110,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3E79E","slug":"robo-butcher","title":"Robo-Butcher","description":"A human outpost was attacked by an army of robots out of control, but it's not over yet! The human resistance has an\nultimate weapon to counteract the advance of the crazy robots: the Robo-butcher, a robot made with the sole purpose of protecting humans from other robots.\n\nFeatures:\n\nLots and lots of enemies\nPower-ups\nPerma-uprgrades\nDouble-jump \nOld-style pre-rendered graphics\nRobots\nFantastic BGM by Nosebreed\n\n\n\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3E79E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robo-butcher/embed?sid=1","plays":42090,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S4N5N","slug":"piano-tiles-game","title":"Piano Tiles Game","description":"Get the best score on Piano Tiles!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S4N5N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/piano-tiles/embed?sid=1","plays":42086,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6D87D","slug":"dd-blocky","title":"DD Blocky","description":"Blocky is a fun and addictive puzzle game that you can match the blocks with drag & drop on the puzzle board. Play this game and strengthen your mind. game shapes are like the tetris shapes.\n\nFEATURES:\nAge Rating: 8 and Up\nResponsibility: Portrait\nGame Mode: Single-Player\nControls: Mouse / Touch","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6D87D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dd-blocky/embed?sid=1","plays":42029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40124","slug":"baby-bear","title":"Baby Bear","description":"Maman ours et papa ours sont très excités à l'idée d'avoir un petit ourson à la maison. Mais comme c'est leur tout premier bébé, ils sont un peu stressés et ont besoin d'être aidés dans leur rôle de parents. Saurez-vous être leur guide?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40124/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-bear/embed?sid=1","plays":42028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20054","slug":"fruit-blaster","title":"Fruit Blaster","description":"Soyez rapide et précis ! C'est tout ce que vous avez besoin de savoir pour exceller dans \"Fruit Blaster\"! Touchez ou cliquez pour couper les fruits, et enchainez les \"slice\" pour débloquer des combos et exploser les high scores! Devenez un véritable ninja!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20054/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-blaster/embed?sid=1","plays":42022,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2NP74","slug":"super-chains","title":"Super Chains","description":"Super Chains a fun puzzle game.\nTo capture and use them, create long links of chain blocks by simply touching an adjoining block that is one number higher, lower, or of the same value.\nPowerful mythical creatures are hidden in this super numbers puzzle game! Get powerful Heroes to help you in your task!\nCan you be the EPIC champion??\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2NP74/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-chains/embed?sid=1","plays":42009,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40095","slug":"pigeon-bomber","title":"Pigeon Bomber","description":"Jack le pigeon a peur des gens. La peur mène à la colère. La colère mène à la haine. Et la haine mène aus fientes! Jack survole la ville et son but est de déféquer sur tout et tout le monde!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40095/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pigeon-bomber/embed?sid=1","plays":42002,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S5498","slug":"kobadoo-shapes","title":"Kobadoo Shapes","description":"Kobadoo Shapes is a browser game that trains your brain by memorizing coloured geometric shapes in the right order.\n\nWhen you play Kobadoo Shapes you are actively using your working memory. Several scientific studies suggest that training of working memory has beneficial effects and can increase your cognitive functions.\n\nFull version: https://www.kobadoo.com","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S5498/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kobadoo-shapes/embed?sid=1","plays":41996,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40274","slug":"badland","title":"Badland","description":"BADLAND est un jeu primé d'aventure-action à défilement horizontal qui se déroule dans une magnifique forêt luxuriante, remplie de drôles d'habitants, de fleurs et d'arbres. Bien que la forêt ait l'air de sortir tout droit d'un conte de fées, l'atmosphère semble vraiment très étrange... Vous contrôlez l'un des habitants de la forêt pour découvrir ce qui s'y passe. Tout au long de votre périple, vous découvrirez tout un tas de pièges et d'obstacles plus ingénieux les uns que les autres.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40274/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/badland/embed?sid=1","plays":41993,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A6167","slug":"squid-race","title":"Squid Race","description":"Squid Raceis a squid game specially designed to be fully-featured sugar game. Survive race, Carve dalgona honeycomb cookie, cross glass bridge and tug of war\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A6167/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-race/embed?sid=1","plays":41987,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5R16","slug":"face-breaker","title":"Face Breaker","description":"Face Breaker is an enjoyable puzzle game where you are a paddle\nDestroy all the blocks using your happy paddle to hit your square-face-ball, like in a weird tennis match!\nHit and destroy all the blocks as soon as you can.\nAfter any bounce the ball gains speed, making it harder and harder to intercept it!\nIf the ball falls on the bottom you lose!\nBeat all the 45 engaging levels if you can!\nYou will face (not pan intended) a lot of difficult challenges! Prepare yourself!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5R16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/face-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":41944,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3K1I6","slug":"ski-king-2022","title":"Ski King 2022","description":"La saison de ski commence, alors venez skier dans ce jeu aux commandes intuitives et simples. Dévalez la pente, récupérez des pièces, améliorez vos compétences et devenez le roi du ski. Pouvez-vous échapper à l'avalanche aussi ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3K1I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ski-king-2022/embed?sid=1","plays":41938,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78608","slug":"tiny-tomb","title":"Tiny Tomb","description":"C'est le type de jeu qui va te transporter :\n\nQuatre mondes éthérés magnifiquement rendus flottent aux confins de l'univers. Pour sauver tes amis, tu devras tous les visiter... en veillant à souvent nourrir un monstre goinfre au tempérament difficile !\n\n(Au cours de ton périple, essaie également de comprendre ce qui contrarie tant Birdman...)\n\nTiny Tomb propose un univers rogue-like avec notamment :\n- une histoire loufoque avec des personnages sympathiques et décalés.\n- un voxel-art classique et touchant\n- des animations en stop-motion\n- Des tombes en perpétuelle évolution\n- Plus de 25 objets à collecter\n- 4 mondes tout droit sortis d'un rêve et n'attendant qu'une chose : que tu les explores\n\nL'amusement t'attend dans ce jeu dynamique et facile à prendre en main. Idéal pour de longues sessions de jeu ou des parties éclair !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78608/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-tomb/embed?sid=1","plays":41936,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36515","slug":"chess-2d","title":"Chess 2D","description":"Play Chess in 2D mode against the computer.\n\nChess 2D assist with all possible Chess moves, with a green indication for a valid move, with a blue indicator for En Passant and Castling, a yellow indicator indicating a move that is not allowed because the Chess piece, King is in danger if the move were to be valid, and a red indication of the Chess piece, King when in danger.\n\nThe space or square once selecting a Chess piece will lit up accordingly, and give a clear indication like real life robotic colours, green means go, orange means warning and red means danger.","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36515/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chess-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":41935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"48I3D","slug":"mixed-world-weekend","title":"Mixed World Weekend","description":"Welcome to Mixed World, the cheerful platform puzzle game! Use your funny friends’ special skills to nudge all monsters off the platforms!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/48I3D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mixed-world-weekend/embed?sid=1","plays":41929,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0OMID","slug":"zombie-road","title":"Zombie Road","description":"Un monde post-apocalyptique dangereux plein de zombies où seuls les conducteurs les plus courageux et les plus expérimentés tentent de survivre en affrontant d'innombrables armées des morts-vivants. Un jeu de course palpitant. Le plaisir de conduire et d'exterminer des zombies.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0OMID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-road/embed?sid=1","plays":41924,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40444","slug":"princess-hair-spa-salon","title":"Princess Hair Spa Salon","description":"Princess Hair Salon, Makeovers & Hair Spa Salon for brides, teenage girls, stars and celebrities. Hundreds of hair style, makeup, clothes, and accessories to choose from! Let's play the Hair Salon . To be a barber and design various hairstyles for your customer. Share your Princess with friends and family! Unlock more ways to dress up your Prom Princess, there’s no limit!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40444/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-hair-spa-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":41914,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IINV6","slug":"evo-city-driving","title":"EVO City Driving","description":"EVO City Driving features realistic graphics and big variety of super cars to drive across the evo city, drive as fast as you can and try to explore every road in town.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IINV6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evo-city-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":41903,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91E6S","slug":"knife-smash","title":"Knife Smash","description":"Vous aimez lancer des trucs ? Comme des couteaux sur des cibles mouvantes ? Alors voici le défi ultime pour vous ! Synchronisez vos coups, visez bien et devenez le maître du couteau ! Pouvez-vous terminer tous les niveaux ? Un gameplay très simple mais qui est difficile à maîtriser ! Pourrez-vous collectionner tous les couteaux ridicules ?\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91E6S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knife-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":41900,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F006A","slug":"baby-hazel-fun-time","title":"Baby Hazel Fun Time","description":"Baby Hazel enjoyed a nightlong sleep with sweet dreams. She woke up happily this morning and ready to enjoy her day. Help her in getting fresh and then feed her with lukewarm water. Make her fun hours more playful by offering toys of her choice. Enjoy having fun with Hazel and keep her happy by fulfilling all her needs.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F006A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-fun-time/embed?sid=1","plays":41891,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CEIG5","slug":"cake-shop-cafe-pastries-waffles-cooking-game","title":"Cake Shop Cafe Pastries & Waffles cooking Game","description":"$6","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CEIG5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cake-shop-cafe-pastries-waffles-cooking-game/embed?sid=1","plays":41882,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40420","slug":"icy-purple-head-2","title":"Icy Purple Head 2","description":"Icy slides , Purple sticks. Touch anywhere to become icy, try to reach the postage box to finish the level and void dangerous spikes and electricity!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40420/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/icy-purple-head/embed?sid=1","plays":41879,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B8IW8","slug":"rope-bowing-puzzle","title":"Rope Bowing Puzzle","description":"Rope Bowing Puzzle is an interesting and addictive puzzle game. It looks easy enough, but you also have to concentration and dodge some obstacles that will make it difficult for you.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B8IW8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rope-bowing-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41863,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3NM56","slug":"green-and-blue-cuteman","title":"Green and Blue Cuteman","description":"In the green and blue cuteman game played for two, you are two players as green and blue and you must reach the flag by passing through obstacles and defeating the enemies. reach the flag pass the level!\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Arrow keys & Mobile Touch Control \nPause \"P\"","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3NM56/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/green-and-blue-cuteman/embed?sid=1","plays":41857,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GG5EC","slug":"penalty-challenge","title":"Penalty Challenge","description":"\"Penalty Challenge Multiplayer is a Sport Game.\n\nSelect between 32 different teams your favorite one.\n\nYou have 5 attempts to pass the goalie and other 5 to save your opponent’s kicks!\n\nIt’s all in your hands and feet!\n\nTwo Game Modes:\n\n - Play against the computer in tournament mode!\n\n - Challenge a friend playing online multiplayer!\"","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GG5EC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":41848,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA444","slug":"baby-hazel-annual-day","title":"Baby Hazel Annual Day","description":"Wow! Annual Day is organized at Baby Hazel's preschool. Baby Hazel has decided to dress up in clown outfits. First of all assist Hazel and mom in purchasing the required costume and accessories. Then dress her in clown costumes and apply attractive makeup shades to her. Finally, on Annual Day help Hazel and friends to perform onstage without getting nervous. Enjoy celebrating Annual Day with Baby Hazel and friends!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA444/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-annual-day/embed?sid=1","plays":41828,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T016E","slug":"tiger-run","title":"Tiger Run","description":"Very exciting and interesting tiger parkour game, as fun as subway parkour","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T016E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiger-run/embed?sid=1","plays":41816,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76D97","slug":"squidgames-3d","title":"Squidgames 3D","description":"Here is the Squid Game!\nYou will be playing Red Light, Green Light.\n\nYou are allowed to move forward when ‘it’ shouts out, ‘Green Light’, stop when ‘it’ shouts, ‘Red Light’.\nIf your movement is detected afterwards, you will be eliminated.\nLet me repeat the rule.\nYou are allowed to move forward when ‘it’ shouts out, ‘Green Light’, stop when ‘it’ shouts, ‘Red Light’.\nThose players who cross the finish line without being eliminated within the playtime will pass this round.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76D97/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squidgame-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":41812,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AM511","slug":"amaze-escape","title":"Amaze Escape","description":"Un jeu hyper-décontracté passionnant de logique et d'ingéniosité. Le joueur doit résoudre un puzzle simple et sortir de prison.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AM511/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amaze-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":41810,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P0721","slug":"canjump","title":"Canjump","description":"Canjump is a game in which you can only jump, but you have to do it at the right time.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P0721/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/canjump/embed?sid=1","plays":41785,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2EM1B","slug":"noob-vs-zombie","title":"Noob vs Zombie","description":"Welcome to Noob vs Zombie. Go through labyrinths of biomes with different zombies and enemies. Pro betrayed Noobik and left him in labyrinths with various zombies. Go through mysterious labyrinths defeating zombies in deadly battles. You need to go through the labyrinths in each biome in order to find Pro and fight with him, while the cheater with his insidious technologies will interfere with you. Collect coins, buy weapons and upgrade. Super entertaining gameplay: beat zombies and skeletons, beat inhabitants of biomes, earn coins and level up. All characters give coins and values. Open chests with mysterious items and gold. Do you have the courage to go through all the biomes with zombies and bosses and fight with Pro and Cheater. Go through villages, caves, deserts and the North Pole, dodge traps, escape enemies and solve riddles.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2EM1B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":41781,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ISO19","slug":"noob-huggy-kissiy","title":"Noob Huggy Kissiy","description":"You must help them survive in the jungle and get home. Huggy and Kissiy miss their home so much and there are many dangers on the way to go home. It's snowing and it's getting cold. They need to watch out for the enemies in the snowy forest. You have to watch out for the bees and slime or you may die. Complete 10 different maps and reach home.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys                 \n*Double Jump available                 \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ISO19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-huggy-kissiy/embed?sid=1","plays":41775,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40439","slug":"beach-bowling-3d","title":"Beach Bowling 3D","description":"Beach Bowling 3D is a game where you can test your bowling skills on summer beach in gorgeous 3D. Defeat opponents in hundreds of levels. Or just play with your friends on one device. Just throw the ball and get a score. Very easy to start, but hard to master.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40439/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beach-bowling-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":41765,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RMSR4","slug":"puppets-cemetery","title":"Puppets Cemetery","description":"Shoot as many puppets as you can in this top down shooter full of pumpkins!\n\nWASD or ARROW KEYS to move the player\nMOUSE to aim and shoot\nRMB / E / SPACEBAR to pick up weapons","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RMSR4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puppets-cemetery/embed?sid=1","plays":41753,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"75C06","slug":"checkers-legend","title":"Checkers Legend","description":"Le jeu de plateau classique et très simple que tout le monde connaît depuis son enfance. Il existe de nombreuses variantes, alors les règles sont fournies dans le jeu. Vous pouvez jouer simplement contre l'IA ou utiliser cette application pour jouer contre un ami sur le même appareil.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/75C06/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/checkers-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":41741,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ARR64","slug":"funny-hair-salon","title":"Funny Hair Salon","description":"George's hair is in a no bueno situation. His scalp is full of mites and pimps. The only way to fix his hair is going to the salon. Let's cure his scalp and plant new hair to his head, so he can show his true outter beauty!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ARR64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-hair-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":41734,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OFO69","slug":"knife-io","title":"Knife io","description":"Knife.io is a multiplayer game. In the game, you can win by killing everyone. In the game, find a way to avoid the enemy’s attack. While killing the enemy, you will get different random skills to strengthen your attack power. Note that the game map will shrink automatically over time, hurry up and enter the experience, I wish you a happy game!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OFO69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knife-io/embed?sid=1","plays":41729,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40411","slug":"hockey-hero","title":"Hockey Hero","description":"Choose your hero and compete against 3 fierce opponents in the Ice Hockey event. Avoid the attacking players to approach the goal line. Once in front of the goal time your shot to score! Will you win a Gold Medal by scoring in all 3 periods? Be a Hockey Hero!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40411/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hockey-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":41724,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"03772","slug":"just-golf","title":"Just Golf","description":"Just Golf combines minimalism with puzzle in 210 levels with gradual difficulty. You must drop the ball into the hole with the red flag. The plays are unlimited and you'll have guided aim to facilitate your shots. You can also use your skill to try to collect the 3 stars in each level!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/03772/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/just-golf/embed?sid=1","plays":41711,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AL37X","slug":"galaxy-warriors","title":"Galaxy Warriors","description":"\"Combattez avec votre vaisseau ! Parcourez la galaxie et tirez sur des flottes extraterrestres ennemies. Récupérez des crédits pour améliorer votre vaisseau spatial.\n\nMéfiez-vous des ennemis qui ripostent et des boss puissants ! Vous pouvez éliminer les hordes d'ennemis grâce à différents bonus au choix. Esquivez l'enfer des balles et tirez !\"\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AL37X/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-warriors/embed?sid=1","plays":41708,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"THREM","slug":"stickman-archero-fight","title":"Stickman Archero Fight","description":"Jouez à Stickman Archero Fight. Artisanat, mise à niveau, batailles avec stickman ennemi. Faites tout pour la victoire. Faire la meilleure fatalité. Devenez un pro !\n\nAméliorez votre stickman, combattez les ennemis dans le jeu Stickman Archero. Créez des fatalités cool et dynamiques. Beaucoup de magie et de batailles ! Le jeu est similaire à SupremeDuelistStickman. Combats dans le village avec d'autres stickman.\n\nAppuyez sur les touches W/A/S/D pour vous déplacer. Appuyez sur \"E\" pour interagir avec les éléments. Appuyez sur le bouton gauche de la souris pour frapper.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/THREM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-archero-fight/embed?sid=1","plays":41702,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"215ES","slug":"tennis-open-2020","title":"Tennis Open 2020","description":"L'excitation du monde du tennis est prête ! Prenez une raquette et participez à tous les événements de tennis importants du monde ! Pouvez-vous gagner ? Pouvez-vous surmonter tous les obstacles ? Entraînez-vous dur, jouez bien et devenez une légende imbattable. Atteignez le sommet et écrivez l'Histoire. Montrez ce que vous valez et triomphez !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/215ES/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tennis-open-2020/embed?sid=1","plays":41694,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7LTEK","slug":"ultimate-strike","title":"Ultimate Strike","description":"Ultimate Strike features big arsenal of weapons which consists of twenty seven different guns and intense multiplayer battles across nine highly detailed maps, you spawn with random weapons loadout and your mission is to shoot all rival players in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7LTEK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ultimate-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":41689,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71HB1","slug":"football-heads","title":"Football Heads","description":"Entrez sur le terrain, décimez votre adversaire avec diverses frappes puissantes et des bonus amusants et décalés. Enfin, montre-lui qui est le boss avec le système d'émoticones - devenez une légende du football aujourd'hui !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71HB1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-heads/embed?sid=1","plays":41688,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RYI7D","slug":"real-city-driving-2","title":"Real City Driving 2","description":"Select different super cars and drive them as fast as you can across the city.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RYI7D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/real-city-driving-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41673,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y50DT","slug":"my-sweet-candy-outfits","title":"My Sweet Candy Outfits","description":"Welcome to the My Sweet Candy Outfits. Rainbow high girls Skyler, Sunny, Ruby, and Violet are planning a weekend party. But a party without a theme is not fun! So they planned to be in Sweet candy themes. Help the girls to browse the wardrobe and pick the cute candy outfit for them. Play and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y50DT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-sweet-candy-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":41671,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SD226","slug":"red-and-blue-stickman-rope","title":"Red and Blue Stickman Rope","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of two very cute brothers, namely blue and red stickman? Brothers red and blue need to get the key and reach the door. Be two people and get them to the door with your friend. reach the door and pass it to the new level. You will face multiple challenges but reach the door.   \n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys                    \n*Double Jump available                    \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SD226/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-blue-stickman-rope/embed?sid=1","plays":41665,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OM649","slug":"moto-maniac-2","title":"Moto Maniac 2","description":"Overcome all the obstacles as fast as you can. This game is a sequel to Moto Maniac set in a different environment. This time it's a bridge in the night. It's under construction so you have to be careful not to fall into the abyss and not to hit your head. On top of the obstacles on the way, it's dark! Fortunately you have a drone that will light your way. ","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OM649/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moto-maniac-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41631,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RLL94","slug":"roll-this-ball","title":"Roll this Ball","description":"Vous aimez les jeux de pousse-pousse classiques ? Alors ce jeu est fait pour vous ! Déplacez les tuiles en bois pour vous frayer un chemin et permettre à la boule en acier d'atteindre le but rouge et brillant. Avec ce casse-tête populaire, vous passerez d'agréables moments et vous ferez travailler vos méninges !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RLL94/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roll-this-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":41630,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S121Y","slug":"funny-bone-surgery","title":"Funny Bone Surgery","description":"Leah went to play stakeboard on the street. But she was distracted and hit a car! She got a nasty broken arm and foot. Help fix her injuries and broken bones!\n","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S121Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-bone-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":41618,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"510IG","slug":"boxing-stars","title":"Boxing Stars","description":"Passez de la boxe clandestine aux championnats et devenez une star de la boxe. Améliorez vos compétences avec des récompenses pour participer à de meilleurs tournois.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/510IG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boxing-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":41611,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RR6SE","slug":"space-tower-defense","title":"Space Tower Defense","description":"Tower Defense est un jeu de stratégie où le but du joueur est de protéger ses territoires et la tour principale des attaques ennemies. Pour ce faire, le joueur construit des structures défensives le long de la trajectoire d'attaque, dont la force dépend du coût de l'énergie que le joueur reçoit pour vaincre l'équipement ennemi.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RR6SE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-tower-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":41594,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P93LE","slug":"block-puzzle-jewel","title":"Block Puzzle Jewel","description":"Le but est de déposer des blocs afin de créer et de détruire des lignes complètes sur l'écran à la fois verticalement et horizontalement. N'oubliez pas d'empêcher les blocs de remplir l'écran dans ce jeu de puzzle addictif.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P93LE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-puzzle-jewel/embed?sid=1","plays":41586,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3RR15","slug":"roar-of-city","title":"Roar of City","description":"Roar of City is a 2D isometric Beat 'em up game with high quality graphic and suitable gameplay for mobile and desktop. Fight with criminals gang and arrest their commander to rescue the city. But now the city is angry and the horrible roar of the city can be heard.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3RR15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roar-of-city/embed?sid=1","plays":41579,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40412","slug":"slalom-hero","title":"Slalom Hero","description":"Choose your hero and compete across 3 courses in the Slalom event. Steer between the slalom gates and collect boosts to improve your times. Will you win a Gold Medal? Be a Slalom Hero!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40412/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slalom-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":41572,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I45E2","slug":"line-of-defense","title":"Line of Defense","description":"Line of Defense is a fun battle of defense against attacking enemy tanks. Using you defensive rockets painted with colors, match it with the color of attacking tanks and shoot in order to destroy it. If the color mismatches, you will lose. If tanks reaches the front line you will lose. Use your defense rockets effectively and watch out for enemy tanks coming from different sides.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I45E2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-of-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":41566,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LNAOI","slug":"2d-platformer-coin","title":"2D Platformer Coin","description":"Help the dude collect coins, to win and pass the round !\n\nThe game is that you need to collect coins and win the round, Coins are collected by a character, you must pass a series of tests to reach the coins and pick it up, To pass and win you need to collect 8 coins, but you do not think that this is easy. Try and test your skills and mind!\n\nHow to play:\nControls: Button-W-jump up,\nButton-S-walk down,\nButton-D-walk right,\nButton-A-walk left,\nAnd if you jump to hold the SPACE button, the character will slowly descend to the ground as if gravity has turned off.","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LNAOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2d-platformer-coin/embed?sid=1","plays":41552,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64L1R","slug":"water-sort-puzzle","title":"Water Sort Puzzle","description":"À propos de ce jeu\nWater Sort Puzzle est un jeu de puzzle amusant et addictif! Essayez de trier l’eau colorée dans les verres jusqu’à ce que toutes les couleurs dans le même verre. Un jeu stimulant mais relaxant pour exercer votre cerveau!\n\n★ COMMENT JOUER :\n• Tapoter n’importe quel verre pour verser de l’eau dans un autre verre.\n• La règle est que vous ne pouvez verser l’eau que si elle est liée à la même couleur et qu’il y a suffisamment d’espace sur le verre.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64L1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/water-sort-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41545,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TDO3T","slug":"d-copter-reloaded","title":"D. Copter Reloaded","description":"Reloaded D.Copter is a brand new shooting 3D game. You need to take a helicopter and perform shooting missions!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TDO3T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/d-copter-reloaded/embed?sid=1","plays":41524,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4A866","slug":"baby-hazel-birthday-party","title":"Baby Hazel Birthday Party","description":"Hurray! Baby Hazel is celebrating her 3rd birthday. Let us join Hazel to enjoy dancing, feasting and magic shows at her birthday party. On this special occasion, keep Baby Hazel happy by fulfilling all her needs. Someone who is very dear to Hazel has planned a surprise for her to make her birthday more fun-filled. Let us see what the surprise is and who has planned it.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4A866/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-birthday-party/embed?sid=1","plays":41518,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5R4XE","slug":"2048-x2-merge-blocks","title":"2048 X2 Merge Blocks","description":"Une combinaison du jeu classique 2048 et de Tetris. Les nombres descendent et continuent d'affluer. Gérez la fusion des nombres et gardez la zone de jeu dégagée aussi longtemps que possible. Quelle est la meilleure fusion que vous puissiez faire ?\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5R4XE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-x2-merge-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":41510,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40123","slug":"kuli","title":"KULI","description":"Vous revenez d'une ballade en montagne quand vous apprenez qu'une épidémie zombie vient d'avoir lieu. Que faites-vous ? Ce que vous savez faire le mieux pardi! Construire des défenses, les faire évoluer et vous battre! Tenez les zombies à distance et massacrez-en le plus possible grâce à vos tourelles et vos armes défensives, préparez votre stratégie le jour et combattez la nuit. Survivrez-vous à KULI?","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40123/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kuli/embed?sid=1","plays":41508,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40416","slug":"boss-level-shootout","title":"Boss Level Shootout","description":"Gamer boy Billy loved to play video games but one day his retro console ate him. Now Billy is inside the retro style game and must beat the bosses in this ultimate shootout. Test your skills in shooting, running, picking power-ups and be a winner!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40416/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boss-level-shootout/embed?sid=1","plays":41507,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"II007","slug":"warzone-strike","title":"Warzone Strike","description":"Warzone Strike features next gen graphics and big arsenal of weapons which consists of 38 different guns to shoot rival players on various highly detailed maps.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/II007/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/warzone-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":41502,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7796R","slug":"tower-defense","title":"Tower Defense","description":"Une horde d'horribles monstres attaque votre royaume, bâtissez vos tours rapidement et survivez à toutes les vagues. Si les flèches et les pierres ne suffisent pas, utilisez les éléments à votre avantage et tuez-les tous.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7796R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":41499,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9R3ET","slug":"steve-adventurecraft-nether","title":"Steve AdventureCraft Nether","description":"The nether section of the adventurecraft game, which is full of adventures, has 10 different levels and flying, crying creatures, zombies and many monsters are waiting for you. collect animals they are your friend. hunt monsters they are your enemy. complete the levels and achieve victory!     \n\nHow to Play?\n*WASD + F / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9R3ET/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-adventurecraft-nether/embed?sid=1","plays":41497,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2PI32","slug":"lipuzz-water-sort-puzzle","title":"Lipuzz - Water Sort Puzzle","description":"You will think a lot and have a lot of fun while playing the Lipuzz game. A great game to exercise memory. The aim of the game is to collect liquids of the same color in a container by transferring the liquids in the containers to each other. The most important rule in the game is that the container you want to pour the liquid into must either be empty or the other container must have the same color liquid. If you can't pass the level in the game, you can get another container from the top menu.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2PI32/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lipuzz-water-sort-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41493,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2R310","slug":"roller-coaster-simulator","title":"Roller Coaster Simulator","description":"Roller Coaster Simulator is a realistic 3D simulator game where you have to drive on winding tracks. With stunning 3D graphics, intuitive controls, and addictive mechanics this simulation 3D game is sure to keep to you addicted for hours. Take care of your passengers and make sure your reach the destination safely. Don’t lose your balance as you will be going to shake on the twisty turns and loops. On the way you will cross the murky seas and the gigantic mountains. Just keep equilibrium as it will much needed. ","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2R310/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roller-coaster-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":41489,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7D81","slug":"super-drive","title":"Super Drive","description":"Super Drive features cool graphics and lots of super cars to drive across the big city crowded with pedestrians, drive as fast as you can and try to perform different stunts on your way.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7D81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-drive/embed?sid=1","plays":41486,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40414","slug":"soccer-hero","title":"Soccer Hero","description":"Choose your hero and compete against 3 fierce opponents in the World Soccer event. Will you win a Gold Medal by scoring all 3 chances? Be a Soccer Hero!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40414/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":41480,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71BTT","slug":"battlebox","title":"BattleBox","description":"Battle Box is ad Idle game where the more you risk, the more you get! Try to collect all the jewels in each level and to memorize their location!\nBe careful tough! Under some blocks there is a devil that will hurt you! If you find three of them the game will be over! By the way, you can restore your health if you find a strawberry, so keep an eye on it.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71BTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battlebox/embed?sid=1","plays":41480,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40421","slug":"penalty-superstar","title":"Penalty Superstar","description":"You are the goalkeeper starting his career from scratch: use power-ups to get better and try to catch the ball. Win all cups and become the champion of all leagues!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40421/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-superstar/embed?sid=1","plays":41477,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40435","slug":"pudding-monsters","title":"Pudding Monsters","description":"Les monstres sont en mission pour sauver leurs amis d'un propriétaire de frigo sans coœur! Devenir un SUPER MONSTRE ULTIME semble être le meilleur plan…Depuis la table jusqu'aux abords de la maison, pour finir au cœur de la ville – agglutinez ensemble les monstres et sauvez leurs amis!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40435/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pudding-monsters/embed?sid=1","plays":41476,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9PF8M","slug":"fidget-spinner-mania","title":"Fidget Spinner Mania","description":"Un fidget spinner, c'est quoi ? C'est un jouet sympa qui tourne dans votre main. C'est un jeu très simple, mais le divertissement qu'il procure est sans limite. Le fidget spinner vous aide à vous détendre et à évacuer le stress en quelques tours seulement. Arrêtez de vous ronger les ongles ou de faire tourner votre stylo. C'est un jouet qui permet aux adultes et aux enfants de faire passer le temps. Récupérez tous les différents fidget spinners. \n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9PF8M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fidget-spinner-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":41473,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P1538","slug":"panda-fight","title":"Panda Fight","description":"Panda Fight is an action game with a drag and drop mechanic. Your main objective is to beat all the levels to save Panda Princess. Collect all the stars scattered throughout the levels to finish the game with 100% success. Save the princess from terrible enemy pandas. A game with colorful and beautiful pixel art graphics! Good fun!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P1538/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/panda-fight/embed?sid=1","plays":41470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IN3K6","slug":"tiny-chick","title":"Tiny Chick","description":"Tiny Chick is inspired by the conception of“easy-to-play, hard-to-master”, it is not only a simple casual game you can play all the time, but also very challengable. Just tap, hold, and then release, the chick will jump over the pillars!\nAlthough it is easy to play, it will be hard to get high score. Players have to figure out when and where to go so as to make the chick jump over the pillars! The more pillars you can jump over, the more scores you can claim! With the scores, you can unlock more characters!\nHow long can you persist? How best can you score? Let's wait and see!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IN3K6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-chick/embed?sid=1","plays":41467,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7UM2S","slug":"stickman-huggy-2","title":"Stickman Huggy 2","description":"Help the cute blue monster huggy cross paths full of obstacles! stickman huggy must cross the obstacles and reach the finish line. Help him and get him to the finish.  \n\nhow to play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7UM2S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-huggy-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41464,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00AAA","slug":"baby-hazel-at-beach","title":"Baby Hazel At Beach","description":"Hurray! This vacation Baby Hazel is glad to be gifted with a beach treat from her mom and dad. Hazel is excited to play under sunny sky with golden sand, swim in blue water of sea, relax and sip exotic drinks and indulge in other beach activities. Play the game to have lots of fun with Baby Hazel at the beach. Help her in packing important accessories and gears and take care of all her needs.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00AAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-at-beach/embed?sid=1","plays":41464,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"233ZE","slug":"idle-zoo","title":"Idle Zoo","description":"Devenez un riche investisseur et restaurez des zoos à travers le pays. Réparez les habitats naturels d'origine et construisez-en de nouveaux. Découvrez de nouveaux animaux et regardez votre zoo prospérer.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/233ZE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-zoo/embed?sid=1","plays":41463,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20052","slug":"speed-pool-king","title":"Speed Pool King","description":"Enfin un jeu de billard frénétique pour mobiles et tablettes! Mettez les boules dans les trous aussi vite que possible, et défiez la montre pour devenir le meilleur!","category":"Course","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20052/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speed-pool-king/embed?sid=1","plays":41454,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"171PE","slug":"jigsaw-puzzle","title":"Jigsaw Puzzle","description":"Rencontrez des animaux mignons, visitez des endroits inconnus ou découvrez de nouvelles choses. Expérimentez tout cela en jouant confortablement sur votre téléphone. Choisissez la difficulté qui convient à votre rythme et terminez chaque puzzle.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/171PE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jigsaw-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41453,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2G124","slug":"going-up","title":"Going up","description":"Help a lonely bird to reach its nest. Avoid obstacles and collect coins to unlock new skins.\n\nTouch the screen or Left Click to fly upwards","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2G124/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/going-up/embed?sid=1","plays":41446,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"35013","slug":"car-defender","title":"Car Defender","description":"Play, Merge cars, and collect coins to Win Free Coins.\nEnjoy the car Defender game where you have to Merge & unlock new cool cars.\n\nHow to play:\n-Merge two cars of the same level to get higher level cars and defeat your enemies.\n\nFeatures:\nDestroy all of the bosses.\nDifferent car models to be merged!\nSimple 1-tap gameplay","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/35013/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-defender/embed?sid=1","plays":41445,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40448","slug":"go-chicken-go","title":"Go Chicken Go","description":"The chickens escaped from their hideous farm and the last obstacle between them and an everlasting life of freedom is a mere highway. Test your cold blood and truck dodging skills. 25 chickens put their lives in your trustworthy hands. Go Chicken Go!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40448/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/go-chicken-go/embed?sid=1","plays":41433,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O2T25","slug":"the-eggsecutioner","title":"The Eggsecutioner","description":"If you don't like eggs, this is the game for you!\n\nUse the mouse or touch the screen to stop the marker in the middle of the bar","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O2T25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-eggsecutioner/embed?sid=1","plays":41432,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40324","slug":"zombie-massacre","title":"Zombie Massacre","description":"Zombies are invading the wild west! Grab your guns and protect innocent people from those pesky lifeless folk. Upgrade your guns, equip yourself or hire some help. Don't get killed! Outnumbered, but never outgunned!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40324/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-massacre/embed?sid=1","plays":41432,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4482P","slug":"call-of-ops-2","title":"Call of Ops 2","description":"Call of Ops 2 features next-gen graphics and big arsenal of weapons to shoot rival players on different maps.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4482P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/call-of-ops-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41422,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0914B","slug":"biozombie-outbreak","title":"Biozombie Outbreak","description":"Biozombie Outbreak features intense zombie shooting on the city streets crowded with blood thirsty zombies, use different types of weapons to shoot all incoming zombies and try to survive before the time runs out.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0914B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/biozombie-outbreak/embed?sid=1","plays":41421,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7111H","slug":"baby-hazel-bathroom-hygiene","title":"Baby Hazel Bathroom Hygiene","description":"Its high time for Baby Hazel to learn the importance of bathroom hygiene. If proper hygiene standards are not maintained, Hazel may easily come in contact of germs. Today, Hazel will be learning techniques of bathroom hygiene. Guide her on clearing all the mess, removing clogs in wash basin and cleaning stained bathroom accessories. Keep Hazel healthy by maintaining good personal hygiene so that she is shielded from germ infection.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7111H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-bathroom-hygiene/embed?sid=1","plays":41418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A4LRB","slug":"baby-hazel-ballerina-dance","title":"Baby Hazel Ballerina Dance","description":"Cheerful morning of Baby Hazel starts with surprise gifts. While having shower, she is given interesting tasks to complete and on winning receives ballerina toys from mom. Another reason for Hazel to be very excited is that she is going to learn ballerina dance. But our little doll is feeling bit nervous and uneasy in her dance class. Can your encourage Hazel and make her comfortable so that she follows the instructions of teacher carefully.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A4LRB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-ballerina-dance/embed?sid=1","plays":41418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N976N","slug":"sliding-slide","title":"Sliding Slide","description":"Enjoy and relax with a classi puzzle game. Six different images with 3 difficulty levels to satisfy the tastes of every players!\nBeat your highscores trying to solve the puzzle as fast as you can!\n\nTouch / Click the screen to move the blocks","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N976N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sliding-slide/embed?sid=1","plays":41365,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YH597","slug":"the-lost-joystick","title":"The Lost Joystick","description":"They stole your joystick… but they don’t know who you are!\nYou will do everything to get it back\nIn this psychedelic pixel-artish platformer, you have to jump around the levels looking for coins and keys, killing monsters and avoiding traps . Simple as that.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YH597/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-lost-joystick/embed?sid=1","plays":41364,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8R08I","slug":"robot-bar-find-the-differences","title":"Robot Bar - Find the differences","description":" Spot the differences game in a sci-fi environment full of happy robots enjoying their free time in a club.\n\nTry to find all the differences in each picture before the time runs out. Be careful though: Do not touch the screen randomly trying to catch all the differences this way!\nIf you touch the screen 5 times without touching one of the differences is game over!\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8R08I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-bar-find-the-differences/embed?sid=1","plays":41359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R821H","slug":"ghost-walker","title":"Ghost Walker","description":"Ghost Walker is a game about a ninja who went on a hunt for reputable bandit leaders. This game will amaze you with cool ninja controls in Slow Motion and dynamism.\n\nYour main task is to destroy the bosses. And whether you will kill their entire team while you go to them or do without bloodshed is your choice.\n\nThis is a game in which you will fully feel like an unsurpassed, elusive, super dexterous and strong master of melee weapons.\n\nKey features of the game:\n- Dynamic battles in Slow Motion\n- Lots of weapons\n- Cool assassin skins to choose from\n- Lots of bosses and enemies\n\nTry to experience this incredible feeling of elusiveness yourself, defeat all the bandits without a single scratch and become a legend.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R821H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ghost-walker/embed?sid=1","plays":41358,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40130","slug":"your-queen-destiny","title":"Your Queen Destiny","description":"Quel genre de reine auriez-vous aimé être ? Toutes les reines ne sont pas forcément pleines de beauté, de grâce et de sagesse. Faites le quiz et découvrez quelle reine vous auriez pu être. Peut-être serez-vous une reine gentille, peut être aussi une reine maléfique ? Essayez-vite pour le savoir!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40130/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/your-queen-destiny/embed?sid=1","plays":41358,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40253","slug":"king-of-thieves","title":"King of Thieves","description":"Mettez vos talents de voleur à l'épreuve dans ce mélange unique de jeu de plateformes et de jeu multijoueur JcJ. Profitez de cette expérience époustouflante avec King of Thieves, l'un des meilleurs jeux de 2015. Rivalisez avec plus de 24 millions de joueurs dans le monde et créez votre propre clan de voleurs. Introduisez-vous dans le donjon de vos ennemis et volez leurs trésors. Prouvez que vous êtes plus intelligent et plus adroit. REMARQUE : le jeu est très addictif et vous fera inévitablement rencontrer de nouveaux amis.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40253/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-of-thieves/embed?sid=1","plays":41357,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R6NMN","slug":"gold-mine","title":"Gold Mine","description":"Make riches by collecting gold and diamonds in mines. The bigger the nugget, the more money you earn, stay away from the gallons so you don’t lose money and the stones that end up taking your time. You can find dynamite, use it wisely so you don’t waste time or money. There are 10 levels for fun.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R6NMN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gold-miner/embed?sid=1","plays":41342,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"90Y88","slug":"final-freeway","title":"Final Freeway","description":"Experience arcade racing over many diverse levels of fast-paced driving fun.\nBeat the clock and speed through each goal to proceed to the next stage.\nBoasting a diverse range of exciting levels, this popular title has reached #1 on racing game charts for major mobile platforms.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/90Y88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/final-freeway/embed?sid=1","plays":41339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40440","slug":"street-freekick-3d","title":"Street Freekick 3D","description":"Street Freekick 3D takes freekick game in modern city streets. Curve the ball and defeat opponents in hundreds of levels in gorgeous 3D. Play on any of your devices. Just kick the ball in gates and get a score. Very easy to start, but hard to master.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40440/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/street-freekick-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":41336,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40188","slug":"key-shield-2","title":"Key & Shield 2","description":"L'île de Gorlik n'est toujours pas sûre! Un sort a été lancé et a recouvert l'île de rochers alors que vos amis s'y trouvent toujours prisonniers. Attrapez votre bouclier et votre clé et parcourez l'île pour libérer vos amis et en finir une bonne fois pour toute!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40188/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/key-shield-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41334,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40313","slug":"get-10","title":"Get 10","description":"Associer des nombres n'a jamais été aussi amusant! Trouvez et connectez les nombres pour obtenir le nombre et score les plus élevés. Chaque nombre plus élevé représente un nouveau défi. Jusqu'où pouvez-vous aller?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40313/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/get-10/embed?sid=1","plays":41334,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1L8EP","slug":"penalty-challenge-multiplayer","title":"Penalty Challenge Multiplayer","description":"Penalty Challenge Multiplayer is a HTML5 Sport Game. Select between 32 different team your favorite one. \nYou have 5 attempts to pass the goalie and other 5 to save your opponent’s kicks!\nIt’s all in your hands and feet! 3 Game’s Mode: - Multiplayer mode - Play against the pc - Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1L8EP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-challenge-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":41333,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3R02S","slug":"drink-drive-survive","title":"Drink Drive Survive","description":"Have you ever tried to drive while drunk? If the answer is no, good for you! me neither! So, what about a simulator that shows you the all the issues that a drunken driver has to face?\n\nUse the mouse / or touch the screen to drive the car around","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3R02S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drink-drive-survive/embed?sid=1","plays":41332,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E6O54","slug":"cerkio","title":"Cerkio","description":"Touch the screen at the right time to throw the ball in the white circle.\nRepeat it for more than 30 levels and prove yourself you are skilled enough to complete the game!\n\n34 levels\nNice music\nRelaxing game\none hand game","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E6O54/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cerkio/embed?sid=1","plays":41326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5W86","slug":"jigsaw-collections","title":"Jigsaw Collections","description":"Jigsaw puzzle is one of the entertaining, educational games that requires perseverance, accuracy, patience, and most importantly - to be attentive to the little things. Online jigsaw puzzles always attract a huge audience of completely different ages. In our game, everyone can find interesting collections for themselves! A game of this kind is an intrigue, a mystery that both an adult and a child would like to unravel. Search and combine the pieces into a single picture. For convenience, you can zoom in or out on the work surface. We wish you only victories!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5W86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jigsaw-collections/embed?sid=1","plays":41323,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6I66L","slug":"island-puzzle","title":"Island Puzzle","description":"$7","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","classics","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6I66L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/island-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41310,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4AC46","slug":"crap-attack","title":"Crap Attack","description":"A man, a woman, a date,  and tons and tons of pooh.\n\nYou are the miraculous pill that can fix the situation!\n\n\n\n        \n\nTry to keep clean the man that swallowed you, and kill all the crap before it is too late!     \n\nNobody but you can do that! You have only 5 minutes per level to clean the man's intestine and save the date.\n                                                                               \n\nABOUT THE GAME\n\n- 7 Levels full of \"crappy monsters\" to defeat.\n\n- Two different modes: Story Mode and Crap Hysteria Mode (NOTE: you have to finish the Story Mode to unlock this mode).\n\n- Two endings (with 2 different FMV.)\n\n- Try to finish the game without swear like a trooper (The Crap Hysteria  Mode is REALLY HARD, so we're not responsable of your frustration).","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4AC46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crap-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":41297,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40257","slug":"donutosaur-2","title":"Donutosaur 2","description":"Help Donutosaur get his donut! Collect candies by changing the shape of Donutosaur and switching the direction of gravity. Donutosaur's friends will be of great help - they can push, pull and destroy objects.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40257/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/donutosaur-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41295,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18255","slug":"jurassic-run","title":"Jurassic Run","description":"Un voyage d'aventures qui a mal tourné ! Un dinosaure sanguinaire est à vos trousses ! Pas le temps de descendre un rocher et escalader l'autre. Vous devez utiliser le bâton pour passer de l'autre côté. Veillez à ce que le bâton soit de la bonne longueur, sinon vous tomberez ou vous serez mangé ! Et n'oubliez pas de ramasser les œufs de dinosaure pour avoir une deuxième chance.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18255/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jurassic-run/embed?sid=1","plays":41288,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40312","slug":"flow-mania","title":"Flow Mania","description":"Un jeu de casse-têtes simple mais addictif. Reliez des paires de points colorés avec des tuyaux pour créer du courant entre eux. Vous devez aussi remplir le plateau de jeu de tuyaux. Les tuyaux ne peuvent ni se croiser, ni se chevaucher.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40312/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flow-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":41284,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8A3W8","slug":"tac-tac-way","title":"Tac Tac Way","description":"Tac Tac Way, the only game who require a personal Zen master to be played.\nYou are the ball that needs to drive around psychedelic states of consciousness. Be careful to stay on the wall and follow the path as much as you can!\n\nTap the screen to change the direction or to teleport over lava. If you fall off the edges, you're gone!\n\nHow far can you go? Someone will tell you you need no stress and anxiety if you want to succeed in this Zen game, are you calm enough?\nMaybe you'll need a personal Zen master to play this game.\nRemember, this is not a classic zigzag game!","category":"Course","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8A3W8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tac-tac-way/embed?sid=1","plays":41284,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N0NS8","slug":"angry-sharks","title":"Angry Sharks","description":"Le requin a été exposé à des radiations et il a muté. Il flotte dans la mer et mange des poissons. Plus il en mange, plus il grossit. Les gens ont peur de lui et essaient de le détruire. Essayez de survivre à leurs attaques.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N0NS8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angry-sharks/embed?sid=1","plays":41275,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"555ER","slug":"red-and-green-3","title":"Red and Green 3","description":"red and green 3 is a two player game. An adventurous game for two, depicting the friendship between the red man and the green man, consisting of 10 chapters. collect candies and earn points. watch out for lasers.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/555ER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-green-3/embed?sid=1","plays":41274,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P731E","slug":"pop-pop-kitties","title":"Pop-Pop Kitties","description":"Play a cute puzzle as you pop-pop all the kitties using strategy and reflexes! With 100+ challenging puzzles and adorable kitties this kawaii Match-3 Puzzle Shooter game will charm players for hours. Can you collect all the stars?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P731E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-pop-kitties/embed?sid=1","plays":41272,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0004P","slug":"robot-police-iron-panther","title":"Robot Police Iron Panther","description":"When the monster alien come to attack the earth, there's no body can save us except the police robot. Build your own Iron Panther robot and fight the monster in an epic fighting! It's not finished yet...","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0004P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-police-iron-panther/embed?sid=1","plays":41268,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"022EE","slug":"open-dune-2","title":"Open Dune 2","description":"Dune 2 is a Westwood Studios game put together back in 1992, and it's probably best known for being the prototypical RTS, one of the first games to put together all of the elements that later led to the genre that made StarCraft and Command & Conquer so popular. \n\nThis version is authentic. It's a nice trip down memory lane, or maybe just a free introduction to a piece of PC gaming history.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/022EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/open-dune-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41267,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T0OO6","slug":"dotto-botto","title":"Dotto Botto","description":"Dotto Botto is a classic platformer game.\n\nHelp Dotto to find his way home and try to beat all the levels!\n\nYou will face deadly enemies, weird creatures and hideous obstacles on your way back home, so be careful!\n\nFEATURES\n\n10 Levels full of moving platforms, obstacles, power-ups, spikes, enemies and much more! (not so much more, actually)\n2 game endings! (yes, not 1 but 2!!!! unbelievable!!!)\nColorful pixelated graphics\n\nA monstrous Final Boss!\n4 Different enemies\nDozens of traps and obstacles!\n","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T0OO6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dotto-botto/embed?sid=1","plays":41260,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LE29T","slug":"creative-puzzle","title":"Creative Puzzle","description":"Loves coloring? Even puzzles? This game have 32 pictures to satisfy your loves for coloring and puzzles. Play this game to have a blast fun in coloring and puzzles!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LE29T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/creative-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41244,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40349","slug":"princess-nail-art","title":"Princess Nail Art","description":"Princess Nail Art is more-games-in-one of manicure and pedicure, just for girls! It's full of tips for all girls and there are lots of colors to paint nails and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40349/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-nail-art/embed?sid=1","plays":41244,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8G55I","slug":"fishing-io","title":"Fishing.io","description":"Dans ce jeu amusant et facile aux beaux graphismes, vous allez devenir le premier pêcheur à avoir atteint le fond de l'océan. Collectez des poissons et des trésors pour acheter des améliorations de filet de pêche qui vous permettront d'aller plus profondément. Trouvez plus de personnages pris au piège en mer et remplissez votre salle des trophées.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure","arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8G55I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fishing-io/embed?sid=1","plays":41234,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40125","slug":"fun-summer-holiday","title":"Fun Summer Holiday","description":"L'été est enfin là! Et que faites-vous quand l'été est là? Vous partez à la Plage? En vacances? Certainement les deux, tout comme Ashley et ses amis, qui veulent passer leur été ensemble mais n'ont pas encore décidé quelles seraient leurs activités nautiques. Aidez Ashley à choisir ses plus beaux maillots de bain et à passer un été de folie!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40125/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fun-summer-holiday/embed?sid=1","plays":41232,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5","slug":"duelers","title":"Duelers","description":"Sauvez la Princesse du mal absolu qui s'apprête à s'abattre sur le monde ! Dégainez votre épée et venez à bout de tous vos ennemis!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duelers/embed?sid=1","plays":41232,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MM125","slug":"drag-me-ow","title":"Drag me-ow","description":" Drag and drop game where you have to  bring a cat to his beloved cushion without getting killed.\n\nUse the mouse or touch the screen to drag the cat around bring it to its soft pillow","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MM125/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drag-me-ow/embed?sid=1","plays":41223,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R6TS4","slug":"steve-adventurecraft","title":"Steve Adventurecraft","description":"Hunt down zombies, skeleton men and exploding monsters with Steve, but don't forget the designs, they are your friends. Use with Steve through the gates of kill monsters world to reach victory and finish the game! 20 different levels 3 different monsters and 5 different friends!\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + F / Mobile Control Touch","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R6TS4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-adventurecraft/embed?sid=1","plays":41221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L06IR","slug":"loaf-clicker","title":"Loaf Clicker","description":"Loaf clicker est un jeu de clicker dans lequel vous devez collecter des pains. Vous pouvez acheter diverses améliorations pour augmenter votre collection de pains. Débloquez toutes les réalisations et devenez un milliardaire!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L06IR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/loaf-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":41219,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61067","slug":"a-mole-in-a-hole","title":"A Mole in a Hole","description":"Help a forgetful mole to find his way home!\nLook at the map and choose the right path!\nGo home to your wife before dinner is ready! She'is waiting for you!\n\nFeatures:\n-20 Levels to dig\n-10 Achievements to unlock\n- Many different ways to die\n- Plenty of distractions to avoid\n- That's it! This is a game about a mole that digs holes, what else do you want?","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61067/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/a-mole-in-a-hole/embed?sid=1","plays":41215,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40419","slug":"the-green-mission-inside-a-cave","title":"The Green Mission Inside a Cave","description":"The Green Mission Inside a Cave! Buddy is a green cucumber who has an ability to change color. Go through the mysterious cave to find secret recipes. Switch colors to solve puzzles, avoid red enemies and fly on the Buddy Rocket to finish all levels!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40419/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-green-mission-inside-a-cave/embed?sid=1","plays":41214,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E47I","slug":"red-and-green-pumpkin","title":"Red and Green Pumpkin","description":"Slime pumpkins and scary pumpkin monsters are waiting for you in the red and green pumpkin game, the scariest series of the red and green series. be careful, it is the game of the hardest series. You need teamwork. The game is for two players.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Use \"WASD\" keys to move red.\n*Use \"Arrow Keys\" keys to move Green.\n*Jump twice to jump higher! ( Double Jump available )\n*Watch out for monsters, you may die to them.\n*Find the key and reach the door!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E47I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-green-pumpkin/embed?sid=1","plays":41214,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40341","slug":"diggy","title":"Diggy","description":"Diggy is back! Dig all the way to the center of the moon. Collect treasure and upgrade your mining equipment to help you along the way.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40341/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/diggy/embed?sid=1","plays":41201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4","slug":"octane-racing","title":"Octane Racing","description":"Vous conduisez une puissante voiture de sport et devez éviter les véhicules adverses aussi longtemps que possible. Faites attention, chaque Crash vous coûtera une vie!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/octane-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":41192,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S11I6","slug":"big-shark","title":"Big Shark","description":"Big Shark is a fish-eating game with many challenges. Through each level, you will discover many animals in the ocean.\n\nHow to play: Tap on the screen to control the shark avoids bigger fishes and eat smaller fishes. Your shark will grow up when he eats enough food.\n\nPufferfish, ray, swordfish, whale, killer whale (orca), sunfish, whale shark, electric eel... is waiting for you to discover.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S11I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-shark/embed?sid=1","plays":41191,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40133","slug":"collect-the-gift","title":"Collect the Gift","description":"Le père-Noël a des ennuis! C'est déjà le soir de Noël et tous les cadeaux ne sont pas encore prêts..vite, coupez des cordes, utilisez votre fronde et activez des tas de boutons pour l'aider à finir tous les cadeaux à l'heure!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40133/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/collect-the-gift/embed?sid=1","plays":41188,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4ER7I","slug":"noob-huggy-winter","title":"Noob Huggy Winter","description":"It is snowing in game 2 of the series and are you up for the adventure of a noob huggy running with a christmas hat on a cold winter day? In this adventure, we must protect ourselves by jumping from dangerous slime and thorns in the snow-covered forest. We have to be careful with the bees, they can sting, if they do, you may die. collect the diamonds, get the key and go through the door. You can nature in a cave or in a forest, but don't give up, go straight to the door!   \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD\" to move & \"Arrow Keys\" to move         \nMobile Touch Control         \nDouble jump is active in the game.            ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4ER7I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-huggy-winter/embed?sid=1","plays":41185,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"73LEY","slug":"cycle-extreme","title":"Cycle Extreme","description":"Take part in a mountain bike downhill racing challenge. \n\nYou control a bicycle rushing down from the mountains. Be careful - the track is very steep, and there are several obstacles and deadly holes ahead. Be careful and finish each of 20 levels as fast as you can to gain 3 stars!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/73LEY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cycle-extreme/embed?sid=1","plays":41173,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KOI6G","slug":"cooking-korean-lesson","title":"Cooking Korean Lesson","description":"Do you love Korean foods? Do you know how to make kimchi? Or do you know how to make bibimbap? Let's play and find out together in this fun cooking game where you will learn how to cook and serve the best kimchi and bibimbap you can make!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KOI6G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cooking-korean-lesson/embed?sid=1","plays":41168,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7O68O","slug":"takeover","title":"Takeover","description":"Takeover is a real-time strategy game where you command squads of units to protect your strongholds from enemies and seize their buildings to win.\n\nFor centuries the Rivadis Empire ruled the continent in its shine and glory. But now it fell into necromancers’ hands and dying. Time for Takeover has come! \n\nLead one of 3 nations in the battle for Rivadis. Each nation has 5 types of squads, 3 types of strongholds and magic spells. In addition, you can build gold mines, farms to hire more squads, and obelisks to get more mana.\n\nKey features:\n- Real-time strategy with squads\n- 3 nations that you can control (and an extra Necromancers nation)\n- 5 squad types\n- 3 spells and a powerful Grand Spell for each nation.\n- Edicts - upgrades that make your army stronger\n- 8 levels for each nation","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7O68O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/takeover/embed?sid=1","plays":41165,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3RE59","slug":"extreme-drift-racing","title":"Extreme Drift Racing","description":"Extreme Drift Racing est un jeu de course. Le jeu dispose de cinq emplacements où le joueur dérive et accumule des points pour lesquels il peut acheter des véhicules (13 voitures).","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3RE59/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/extreme-drift-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":41151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7105F","slug":"furious-speed","title":"Furious Speed","description":"Speed is the essence of this game! Get a super cool sport car and drive as fast as you can! Avoid collision with other cars and don’t let the police to get you. Unlock new cars be scoring enough points. You get points for overtaking the other cars (if the car is on the lane next to yours). Let the speed make you furious!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7105F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/furious-speed/embed?sid=1","plays":41137,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20063","slug":"top-shootout","title":"Top Shootout","description":"Devenez la meilleure gachette de tout le Far West! Des bandits ont capturé des otages et les retiennent prisonniers dans le saloon. Vous êtes le seul à pouvoir les sauver! Rechargez votre arme et descendez tous les malfrats ainsi que leurs chefs!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20063/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/top-shootout/embed?sid=1","plays":41133,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OIGOI","slug":"city-blocks","title":"City Blocks","description":"City Blocks is a match-3 puzzle game. Strategically place new buildings and upgrade them to build the largest possible city before you run out of space.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OIGOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-blocks-highscore-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":41129,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40380","slug":"don-t-touch-the-red","title":"Don’t touch the red","description":"Un jeu conçu pour vous divertir dès le début. Chaque mode respecte une seule règle: toucher autant de tuiles vertes que possible, et ne pas toucher la tuile rouge!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40380/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-touch-the-red/embed?sid=1","plays":41125,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40159","slug":"mixed-world","title":"Mixed World","description":"Mixed World est un jeu de puzzle particulièrement cool et fun dans lequel vous devrez faire disparaitre toutes les balles rouges de la plateforme en faisant glisser votre personnage dessus. Vous pourrez aussi utiliser différents objets pour vous aider à passer les niveaux les plus difficiles.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40159/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mixed-world/embed?sid=1","plays":41118,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YA1N9","slug":"final-freeway-2r","title":"Final Freeway 2R","description":"Speed through several exciting stages. Pick a character and choose your path as you drive!\nThe impressive sense of speed, catchy tunes and a super-retro look, will kick you back to the 80s! Beat the clock to the next checkpoint and don't let the pesky challenger beat you!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YA1N9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/final-freeway-2r/embed?sid=1","plays":41107,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"830T0","slug":"save-kitten","title":"Save kitten","description":"CATASTROPHE! Angry Tom Cat decoyed kittens into his tower. Save as many kittens as you can!\nRun, catch them with a trampoline, and carry them to their Mother Cat’s basket!\nKittens are desperate for your help. Who will save them, if not you?\n\n- Colorful HD graphics and animation\n- Buy cool clothes and improve them\n- Complete exciting missions and earn coins\n- Discover the magic chest and receive gifts\n- Catch super boosters: time increase, super speed and magnetism, but beware of bombs\n- Raise your level and beat the records of other players!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/830T0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-kitten/embed?sid=1","plays":41104,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"323G7","slug":"going-right","title":"Going Right","description":"Bring the bird to its nest without getting hit by the obstacles\nA simple one touch avoid and collect game, with five differents game modes:\n20 Hard Levels to enjoy!\n\nNORMAL MODE: You can start the game from any level you have already completed.\nDEATH MODE: You got only 10 attempts to complete all the levels.\nTIME ATTACK: Beat your best time in this game mode, and show yourself what you can do.\nINFINITE RUN: Fly as long as you can avoiding the obstacles and collecting coins.\nSHOP: Buy new skins and choose different colors to customize your bird.\n\nThat’s all!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/323G7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/going-right/embed?sid=1","plays":41102,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0SSTD","slug":"shotwildwest","title":"ShotWildWest","description":"ShotWildWest is an arcade game set in the wild west.\nTest your fingers by challenging the speed,\ntrain your mind to hit obstacles quickly and accurately, trying to break all records!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0SSTD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shotwildwest/embed?sid=1","plays":41085,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"811YS","slug":"funny-rescue-gardener","title":"Funny Rescue Gardener","description":"Samantha is a great gardener, but even the best will get accidents sometimes. Let's play and rescue Samantha from the horrible accident! Help her recover from the wounds and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/811YS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-rescue-gardener/embed?sid=1","plays":41085,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91EM7","slug":"demon-killer","title":"Demon Killer","description":"Vous êtes le seul à pouvoir sauver le monde ! Armez-vous d'un arsenal d'armes et arrêtez l'invasion de démons. Ne vous arrêtez pas et utilisez votre potentiel de tir.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91EM7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/demon-killer/embed?sid=1","plays":41083,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1O81W","slug":"runaway-toad","title":"Runaway Toad","description":"$8","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1O81W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/runaway-toad/embed?sid=1","plays":41082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1MIC9","slug":"moto-maniac","title":"Moto Maniac","description":"This trial bike game is simple yet challengling - the levels look short, but it's not that easy to reach the finish line. Get through the piles of logs, boxes and even boats carefully - this is what 'trial' is all about.\n\nOvercome all the obstacles and don't let the biker hit head or flop. The balance is key - lean back or forward for the best grip.\n\nCompete for the best score with the other players via highscore table - show your skills to everyone.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1MIC9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moto-maniac/embed?sid=1","plays":41082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16B4U","slug":"noob-huggy","title":"Noob Huggy","description":"You must be a partner in the adventure of a huggy living in a cute block world. Huggy, who is both noob and funny, needs to escape from slimes. You have to get the key and activate the door and help him move to the next level.    \n\nHow to Play?\n\"WASD\" to move & \"Arrow Keys\" to move    \nMobile Touch Control    \nDouble jump is active in the game.          \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16B4U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-huggy/embed?sid=1","plays":41076,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2UAPU","slug":"super-cute-cat","title":"Super Cute Cat","description":"You need to help super sweet cat hunt the mutated cats. You must destroy the mutated cats and get the key and move on to the next level. There are different difficulties in each level, do not forget to collect candies.  \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile touch control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2UAPU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-cute-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":41067,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64O55","slug":"moto-fury","title":"Moto Fury","description":"Un jeu de course palpitant. Découvrez le plaisir des virées en moto sur une autoroute infinie et très empruntée. Plus vous roulez dangereusement, plus vous accumulez d'argent et de points. Avec votre argent, vous pouvez acheter de meilleures motos plus puissantes. Devenez un rebelle et semez la pagaille sur la route ! Essayez juste de ne pas vous écraser en roulant à une vitesse folle.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64O55/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moto-fury/embed?sid=1","plays":41060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40438","slug":"3d-darts","title":"3D Darts","description":"Darts 3D, a famous classic game now on your device in gorgeous 3D, defeat opponents in hundreds of levels. Or just play with your friends on one device. Just throw the dart and get a score. Very easy to start, but hard to master.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40438/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-darts/embed?sid=1","plays":41060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"24OP4","slug":"popit-vs-spinner","title":"Popit vs Spinner","description":"Try to remove all the popits in those 3 levels by matching at least 2 of the same tiles at once. Use the spinner mode when no matches are left to generate new ones and clean the whole level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/24OP4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popit-vs-spinner/embed?sid=1","plays":41054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6270S","slug":"slimoban-2","title":"Slimoban 2","description":"In each level, you need to collect the golden coin, escape from the slimes, and destroy them if possible. The girl can collect magic potions that help to lift big wooden blocks and slimes. After lifting the blocks or the slimes, you need to drop them in the right places. There is also water in the game, and you can drop things in there. You can move blocks, collect them, and drop them. You also need to lure the slimes in the trap, throw boxes in them, and push them into the water. But all of these things you can do are not obligatory, the main thing you need to do to pass the level is to collect the coin.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6270S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slimoban-2/embed?sid=1","plays":41050,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IISR2","slug":"slalom-ski-simulator","title":"Slalom Ski Simulator","description":"Slalom Ski Simulator is a HTML5 Sport Game. \nGo around gates to complete the track and try to improve your best time on each track!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IISR2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slalom-ski-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":41046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R33T3","slug":"morphit","title":"Morphit","description":"Morphit is a hypercasual game where you have to change your shape to pass trough the obstacles.\nTry to last as long as you can and unlock all the achievements!\nGame Controls:\ntouch the buttons to change the shape of the player and match the obstacles'ones.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R33T3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/morphit/embed?sid=1","plays":41037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00UT9","slug":"funny-pet-haircut","title":"Funny Pet Haircut","description":"Take your messy pets, alpaca and cat to the hair salon. Wash and dry your pets before\ngiving them a brand new look by changing their colors and giving them pattern look.\nDress up too. And turn them into a stylish beauty!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00UT9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-pet-haircut/embed?sid=1","plays":41036,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40454","slug":"cricket-championship","title":"Cricket Championship","description":"Choose your favorite International teams and start playing Cricket Championship. Watch the line of the ball and swing your bat in time to hit the ball out of the park. This game is really fun for all true cricket fans who like to smash boundaries and win the match in style.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40454/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cricket-championship/embed?sid=1","plays":41028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26A1R","slug":"saguaro","title":"Saguaro","description":"Help Saguaro, a mexican cactus, to go for a jog without hit his balloon friends. Avoid them as long as you can. Every time you hit a balloon you will lose one your beloved items, like his hat or one of his maracas! You can restore your lives collecting the glowing maracas you will find on the road!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26A1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/saguaro/embed?sid=1","plays":41023,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2OD06","slug":"maze-of-death","title":"Maze of Death","description":"Escape from a maze full of zombies in this old style first person shooter like doom. You can use all the weapons you can find in the game to make your way through hordes of zombies. Find the exit as fast as you can.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2OD06/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maze-of-death/embed?sid=1","plays":41020,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LEL11","slug":"doll-queen-designer","title":"Doll Queen Designer","description":"Create her dream toy by collecting the dresses and coloring them.\nDoll Queen Designer have smooth controls and over 100 levels.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LEL11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doll-queen-designer/embed?sid=1","plays":41017,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40451","slug":"amazing-sheriff","title":"Amazing Sheriff","description":"Pin on your shiny sheriff's badge, load up your six-shooters, and get ready for some amazing action. Take control of this high flying Sheriff on a wheel-spinning, bottle-breaking wild ride! Yee-haw!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40451/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-sheriff/embed?sid=1","plays":41006,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"90E9T","slug":"poppy-strike","title":"Poppy Strike","description":"Poppy Strike is a 3D shooting game which features gun game mode with big arsenal of weapons and famous dust 2 map crowded with huggy wuggy, your mission is to shoot all incoming huggy wuggy and try to survive by the end of each round in order to get new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/90E9T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":40996,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7079I","slug":"hit-em-up","title":"Hit Em Up","description":"Hit Em Up is a very cool game to destroy zombies and you have a bazooka with super bombs. Save the whole world by clearing the planet from the zombie invasion!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7079I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hit-em-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40988,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40293","slug":"doctor-teeth","title":"Doctor Teeth","description":"Become a dentist and take care of your patients' teeth! Use different tools to treat caries, bad breath and extract teeth. Play fun mini games and use the stethoscope hints in case you're stuck on your to-do list. Can you give all your patients their smile back?","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40293/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doctor-teeth/embed?sid=1","plays":40986,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T7RIP","slug":"super-pop-it","title":"Super Pop It","description":"Super Pop It! is a fun relaxing game and a unique game to play on. This is a super relaxing game to play for hours.\nWe have got different shapes of pop gadgets, click on the pops to smash them and clear the board.\nBe quick and smash all the pops and feel the relax from the tensions, this game is for all ages and you can play for hours. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T7RIP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-pop-it/embed?sid=1","plays":40977,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60T90","slug":"santa-games","title":"Santa Games","description":"Collect some gifts along the way to find the magic sleigh! In this pixel-art game there are 7 levels to play. Besides gifts, you can also collect magic letters and then play another 7 special levels (minigames): Diamond rain, Drop gift, Brick out and more!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60T90/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40975,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40148","slug":"pixeroids","title":"Pixeroids","description":"Naviguez avec votre vaisseau spatial et détruisez les astéroïdes qui vous barrent le chemin sans les percuter! FEU!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40148/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixeroids/embed?sid=1","plays":40964,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40120","slug":"intergalactic-battleship","title":"Intergalactic Battleship","description":"Détruisez les vaisseaux alien pour sauver la planète terre! Appuyez ou cliquez sur la grille ennemie pour localiser et détruire les vaisseaux des envahisseurs…avant qu'ils n'anéantissent les votres!","category":"Action","tags":["classics","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40120/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/intergalactic-battleship/embed?sid=1","plays":40959,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66C9L","slug":"incredible-box","title":"Incredible Box","description":"Incredible Box is a very traditional puzzle game. Roll the box to the target position, nothing more.\n\nIt looks simple, but this game is hard, very hard.\n\nIn order to help all of you can finish all of the levels. We have provided the solution of all levels.\n\nThe control is simple. Simply touch the box and roll it. And the game is completely 3D with very beautiful water effect.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66C9L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/incredible-box/embed?sid=1","plays":40957,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NSL3","slug":"gun-simulator","title":"Gun Simulator","description":"Gun Simulator Shooting Range offers realistic and closest experience for semi-automatic and modern weapons shooting on the firing range. Imagine classic gun shooting closest experience with dynamic weapons sounds when you pull off the trigger aim for bull's eye.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NSL3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gun-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":40955,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58851","slug":"road-fury","title":"Road Fury","description":"Libérez votre fureur sur l'autoroute et abattez tout ce qui bouge ! Si vous ne pouvez pas tirer sur quelque chose, prenez-le... ce sont des bonus ! Améliorez votre voiture pour réaliser un trajet plus long, abattez les boss et allez aussi loin que vous pouvez pour pouvoir comparer vos meilleurs scores avec les autres ! Devenez le roi de la route !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58851/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/road-fury/embed?sid=1","plays":40950,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LU96E","slug":"triangle-run","title":"Triangle Run","description":"Play Triangle Run a Hypercasual game that will make your head spin!\n\nJust one click/tap to play!\n\nJust press and hold once on the screen and the triangle changes direction as soon as you release the button the triangle returns to the initial direction as the world rotates around you!\n\nSo try to complete the impossible level and try to get the best possible record!\n\nIt sounds easy but instead it will be a tough task!\n\nEnjoy Triangle run!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LU96E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/triangle-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40946,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40300","slug":"baseball-for-clowns","title":"Baseball for Clowns","description":"Henk was the best baseball player in the world before jokers cheated and defeated him with false means. And now, after Henk has retired, the jokers are back again to cause trouble! Help him get rid of the jokers once and for all!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40300/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baseball-for-clowns/embed?sid=1","plays":40943,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40437","slug":"cricket-hero","title":"Cricket Hero","description":"Are you ready to test your reaction times? In Cricket Hero you’ll face the thrills and ecstasy of being a cricket player. Besides regular cricket balls, they may throw at you some other stuff too.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40437/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cricket-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40072","slug":"cut-the-rope-time-travel","title":"Cut The Rope: Time Travel","description":"Remonte le temps avec Om Nom pour nourrir ses ancêtres avec des bonbons ! Cut the Rope: Time Travel est une nouvelle aventure remplie d'action et basée sur la physique qui te fera voyager à travers le temps pour aller croquer du bonbon!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40072/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cut-the-rope-time-travel/embed?sid=1","plays":40925,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R467U","slug":"funny-nose-surgery","title":"Funny Nose Surgery","description":"Mia has always had a snotty nose. But now it has been gone too far, and she need to clean it. Help fix her nose problems, maybe with some surgery. You can also put stickers on her nose after that!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R467U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-nose-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":40925,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R7R75","slug":"dark-world","title":"Dark World","description":"Dark World, the platformer you're been waiting for!\nComplete 30 unique levels to escape the dark world but but careful with your enemies. There is always an easier way to reach the end of the level, check all the game platforms to find useful items\n\n-instructions-\n\nJump - Touch/click the jump button or press `w` on your keyboard\nSword Attack - Touch/click the hit button or press `space` on your keyboard\nThrow sword - Touch/click the sword button or press `c` on your keyboard\n\n-key game features-\n\n30 Unique levels\n2 types of attacks\nMobile browser optimized\nlightweight\nHD graphics\n3 enemies, each having their own attack\n20 languages localization\npause option\nLandscape orientation\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R7R75/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dark-world/embed?sid=1","plays":40923,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40413","slug":"skating-hero","title":"Skating Hero","description":"Choose your hero and compete across 3 programs in the Figure Skating event. Hit the matching button (or swipe) as they line up with the top slot. Time your moves perfectly to boost your score and win!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40413/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skating-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K3V1A","slug":"las-vegas-blackjack","title":"Las Vegas Blackjack","description":"Profitez de l'ambiance authentique du casino de Las Vegas. L'occasion unique de tenter votre chance et gagner de superbes prix dans le monde dangereux du black jack. Testez différentes stratégies et trouvez celle qui vous assurera la victoire.  \n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K3V1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/las-vegas-blackjack/embed?sid=1","plays":40916,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U11U6","slug":"coins-rush-run","title":"Coins Rush Run","description":"Join the crazy Coins Rush Run and multiply your virtual coins, select the best gates and collect lots of cash!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U11U6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coins-rush-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40912,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0A7MN","slug":"battalion-commander","title":"Battalion Commander","description":"Get armed to the teeth and fight your way through the enemy territory. You’ll need the help from your fellow soldiers trapped by the foe, ton of upgrades and mighty skills to survive.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0A7MN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battalion-commander/embed?sid=1","plays":40909,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A3FN","slug":"funny-camping-day","title":"Funny Camping Day","description":"Do you want to take part in a summer camp?! Funny Camping Day is an exciting camping adventure game ever! Go outdoor with your forest-loving friends. Help them to do amazing camp activities: Clean up the camp, set up your tends, enjoy fishing, and light the campfire. Play the role of your friends in different activities. Have fun with Funny Camping day!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A3FN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-camping-day/embed?sid=1","plays":40904,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DOM50","slug":"model-wedding-girl-games","title":"Model Wedding - Girl Games","description":"$9","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DOM50/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/model-wedding-girl-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40898,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81AAO","slug":"las-vegas-roulette","title":"Las Vegas Roulette","description":"Préparez-vous à ressentir les sensations fortes du jeu de hasard de Las Vegas. Cette application de roulette est idéale pour apprendre les bases et élaborer la bonne stratégie ! Jouez à la roulette à tout moment et  n'importe où !\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81AAO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/las-vegas-roulette/embed?sid=1","plays":40894,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I841E","slug":"zombie-killer","title":"Zombie Killer","description":"Survivez dans une ville apocalyptique envahie de morts-vivants. Choisissez votre héros et débarrassez la ville des zombies. Utilisez des armes et des explosifs. Gagnez des pièces et réalisez des améliorations pour survivre plus longtemps.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I841E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-killer/embed?sid=1","plays":40885,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H9G7J","slug":"journey-through-hell","title":"Journey Through Hell","description":"Journey Through Hell  is a free 3D platformer game with a beautiful low poly graphics.\n\nStory\n\nAfter burning in Hell for decades, Hitler takes a few days off from Hell officials to see other parts of Hell.\n\nGame Features\n\nBeautiful low poly environment\nFun and challenging 3D platformer gameplay\nEasy to pick up and play\nFunny and strange ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H9G7J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/journey-through-hell/embed?sid=1","plays":40885,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44H12","slug":"gt-ghost-racing","title":"GT Ghost Racing","description":"Choose your vehicle and race through the various tracks compete against the ghosts of racing legends to prove you are the best of the best and collect all the stars! Race through the seasons, night tracks, winter tracks and futuristic neon tracks. \n\n8 Cars, 9 Tracks, 27 Stars. Race during the seasons, at night and even an icy track.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44H12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gt-ghost-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40880,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40408","slug":"dunk-up-basketball","title":"Dunk Up Basketball","description":"Dunk Up Basketball is a crazy arcade that anybody will enjoy... Shoot the hoops, unlock new balls, become a basketball star!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40408/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dunk-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40880,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EE7L","slug":"ludo-legend","title":"Ludo Legend","description":"Faites une petite partie de Ludo ! Le jeu de plateau préféré de tous ! Jouez seul ou avec vos amis sur un seul appareil ! Il suffit de se le faire passer ! Le design coloré et la mécanique de jeu simple vous divertiront pendant des heures ! \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EE7L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ludo-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":40874,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40321","slug":"street-driver","title":"Street Driver","description":"Drive dangerously fast on a highway in traffic, overtake every vehicle, earn cash and buy better cars! Try not to crash at the highest speed. Time to start your engine!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40321/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/street-driver/embed?sid=1","plays":40870,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OA2OC","slug":"my-ice-cream-shop","title":"My Ice Cream Shop","description":"$a","category":"Stratégie","tags":["junior","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OA2OC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-ice-cream-shop/embed?sid=1","plays":40858,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E495","slug":"let-me-in","title":"Let me in","description":"It’s time to test your real skills. A puzzle game. At a bus stop in a bustling big city, as an assistant policeman, you have to get everyone on board safely, and you can’t be overstaffed, and overstaffed cars will be crowded Explosion, so you have to direct the platform personnel to get on and off the bus in an orderly way. Be careful not to hit the passengers on the opposite car, otherwise you will lose, come on.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E495/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/let-me-in/embed?sid=1","plays":40854,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N17Q4","slug":"bunny-quest","title":"Bunny Quest","description":"Ce lapin se lance dans une folle chasse aux carottes ! Aidez-le à atteindre son but en faisant glisser les tuiles pavées pour former un chemin. Un jeu de casse-têtes classique plus difficile qu'il n'y paraît ! Des tonnes de niveaux à travers trois modes à maîtriser. Testez vos compétences et rejoignez le lapin dans son aventure !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N17Q4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40848,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40449","slug":"water-me-please","title":"Water Me Please!","description":"This family-friendly puzzle game ‘Water Me Please!’ is beautifully designed to keep everybody happy. It is a perfect mix between puzzles and your childhood memories in a grassy land. Enjoy these easy-to-love characters, a small watering can and a lovely flower in a green farm. Ready to keep your lovely flower happy?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40449/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/water-me-please/embed?sid=1","plays":40846,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"04R15","slug":"wall-painter","title":"Wall Painter","description":"Wall Painter  is a casual but very fun puzzle game in which you need to fill all the wall spaces on a building. It can get very tricky at some times, so make sure you move in the right way to ensure that you don’t miss any spot. How many levels can you beat in this game? How far can you go ? We are waiting to see ! Enjoy.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/04R15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wall-painter/embed?sid=1","plays":40846,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5S42","slug":"line-of-defense-2","title":"Line of Defense 2","description":"The best digital battle: shoot approaching enemies tanks and destroy them all! Do not let the enemies cross the red border line!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5S42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-of-defense-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40843,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40428","slug":"fidget-spinner-creator","title":"Fidget Spinner Creator","description":"Do you like fidgets spinners and have you always wanted to create your own? Design your own spinner and start spinning. Each 5 spins you earn 1 coin.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40428/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fidget-spinner-creator/embed?sid=1","plays":40841,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51953","slug":"swim-or-die","title":"Swim or Die","description":"Save a drowning pet touching the screen as fast as you can.\nCollect Time Points and unlock new pets' skins!\nSee the world changing around you and try to not drown!\nWho knows what could happen if you hang in there long enough...","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51953/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swim-or-die/embed?sid=1","plays":40840,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40432","slug":"switch-colors","title":"Switch Colors","description":"Tap the ball and follow the color pattern on each obstacle to cross it! Be careful not to pass through the wrong color, or you’ll have to start again.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40432/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/switch-colors/embed?sid=1","plays":40840,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4U604","slug":"anime-dress-up","title":"Anime Dress Up","description":"Create your perfect anime character!\nMake a screenshot and use it as your avatar.\n\nFeatures:\n1. Graphics in anime style\n2. 10 692 000 combinations of the appearance\n3. Many unusual items\n4. Cute cats\n5. Screenshot button\n6. Random button","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4U604/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-dress-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40832,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8I51T","slug":"trz-battleship","title":"TRZ Battleship","description":"In alternate turns, you must guess the positions of all enemy ships, one shot at a time, and defeat them all. But do it before the opponent annihilates all yours!","category":"Action","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8I51T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trz-battleship/embed?sid=1","plays":40831,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1Y335","slug":"crazy-knife","title":"Crazy Knife","description":"Chop in the kitchen like a real master. It's so satisfying! - Easy control - Addictive gameplay - Crazy Knife is simple and fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1Y335/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-knife/embed?sid=1","plays":40826,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L2H09","slug":"fall-heroes-guys","title":"Fall Heroes Guys","description":"Fall heroes Guys.io Finish dozens of courses and collect crowns. Be the winner of the day! Buy the costumes and change your image. Race with 10-40 people, be the winner of the race! Join the world of Fall heroes guys.io . Race with different costumes on different maps! Make the Difference.\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + ZQSD and Arrow Keys - Mobile Control","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L2H09/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fall-heroes-guys/embed?sid=1","plays":40821,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2QE95","slug":"jewel-blocks-quest","title":"Jewel Blocks Quest","description":"Testez vos compétences logiques dans ce puzzle d'arcade complexe. Jouez à un nombre infini de niveaux dans un environnement mystique et battez votre score. Facile et amusant ! Essayez toutes les fonctionnalités de jeu uniques.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2QE95/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-blocks-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40820,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40441","slug":"mahjong-master-2","title":"Mahjong Master 2","description":"Le solitaire classique qui consiste à connecter des tuiles chinoises est à portée de main. Pensez bien chacun de vos coups et videz le plateau de ses tuiles empilées en pyramides complexes. Cherchez des tuiles libres similaires pour les connecter et les enlever. Il n'est possible de connecter que les tuiles qui ont au moins un côté libre. Jouez rapidement et marquez des points bonus. Gagnerez-vous toutes les étoiles dorées de tous les modes de jeu ?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40441/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-master-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40820,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66TN7","slug":"pop-it-infinity","title":"Pop it Infinity","description":"Pop It Infinity is a fun relaxing game and a unique game to play on.\nWe have got over 160 different shapes of pop gadgets, click on the pops to smash them and clear the board.\nBe quick and smash all the pops and feel the relax from the tensions, this game is for all ages and you can play for hours.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66TN7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-it-infinity/embed?sid=1","plays":40803,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U6AL0","slug":"neon-king-a-local-multiplayer-platformer","title":"Neon King - A local multiplayer Platformer","description":"Neon King est un jeu de canapé multijoueur local\n\n dans lequel ton seul but est\n\n pour éliminer votre adversaire.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6AL0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-king-a-local-multiplayer-platformer/embed?sid=1","plays":40782,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E9OI8","slug":"chiellini-pool-soccer","title":"Chiellini Pool Soccer","description":"Try now \"Chiellini Pool Soccer\" and you can play the new game of Pool billiard soccer themed.\nTest the different game modalities, choose your best tactics, you can use 4 different modules, choose the your favorite shirt team and then sign your best record possible, and then see what position you have in the ranking! don't give up plays and replays to beat all your opponents !","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E9OI8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chiellini-pool-soccer/embed?sid=1","plays":40774,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MNI6O","slug":"neon-slimes","title":"Neon Slimes","description":"Make your opponent fall. Jump on his had to make him weak and small.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MNI6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-slimes/embed?sid=1","plays":40765,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40256","slug":"donutosaur","title":"Donutosaur","description":"Feed hungry adorable monster named Donutosaur. He likes candies but the thing he likes the most is a sweet yummy Donut!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40256/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/donutosaur/embed?sid=1","plays":40764,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20060","slug":"pixzombies","title":"PixZombies","description":"Dans Pix Zombies, un jeu 100% arcade, explosez tous les zombies  que vous croiserez et sauvez le monde!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20060/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixzombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40764,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SQSO7","slug":"squid-hero-impostor","title":"Squid Hero Impostor","description":"Green 456 hero squid impostor watch out for the guys. kill them and find the key get the key reveal the invisible door. You must kill the impostors. Kill them all.\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SQSO7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-hero-impostor/embed?sid=1","plays":40763,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U8R5E","slug":"yummy-churros-ice-cream","title":"Yummy Churros Ice Cream","description":"Create your own Churros Ice Cream! Go through every step in the tasklist to make your delicious ice cream. Pick your favorite flavour and finish it with a combination of syrups and toppings. Complete your tasklist and unlock achievements!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U8R5E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-churros-ice-cream/embed?sid=1","plays":40763,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21DBU","slug":"bunny-graduation-double","title":"Bunny Graduation Double","description":"Two cute blue and purple bunnies escape from the forest. They must escape from the forest because everything is getting snow white more and more. they need to reach the guard at the end of each level reach the guard and pass the levels!  \n\nHow to Play?\n*Purple Rabbit Control : WASD  \n*Blue Rabbit Control : Arrow Keys  \n*Double Jump Available","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21DBU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-graduation-double/embed?sid=1","plays":40760,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GK233","slug":"street-food-cooking-game","title":"Street Food - Cooking Game","description":"Welcome to Street Food - cooking games the number one free cooking games in the world that puts you in charge of your own street food truck & become a kitchen chef!\n\nBe a master chef of street food and start cooking delicious snacks in this virtual cooking games. There are hot dogs van, pizza van, hamburgers van, French fries van and nachos van! Which one do you want to try first? They all look so yummy! Let's cook the yummy & delicious street food with add some amazing toppings on them so they look as good as the taste. You will love playing chef free cooking games as you make your favorite foods, and you'll love that cooking up a chef quality snack doesn't mess up your whole kitchen!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GK233/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/street-food-cooking-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40749,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SEA12","slug":"funny-shopping-supermarket","title":"Funny Shopping Supermarket","description":"Help Hippo n friends to find all products in their shopping list. There are lists of goods you must find. Pick and put them to their grocery bags. Don't forget to go to the cashier to pay! Funny Shopping Supermarket sells varieties of products: vegetables, candies, clothes, fruits, meats, n carpentry tools. Unlock the achievements, have fun and enjoy the game!\n","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SEA12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-shopping-supermarket/embed?sid=1","plays":40746,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40164","slug":"paper-craft-wars","title":"Paper Craft Wars","description":"Envahis les bâtiments ennemis pour gagner la bataille! Rassemble une armée de chats, de taureaux ou de renards dans Paper Craft Wars. Au début de chaque querelle, toutes tes troupes gardent un bâtiment. Déploie tes forces pour contrôler tout le champ de bataille!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40164/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paper-craft-wars/embed?sid=1","plays":40737,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0CEE0","slug":"tactical-penguin","title":"Tactical Penguin","description":"Help the penguins not to starve!🥴\n\nThis game is inspired to the classic Missile Command gameplay.\nDefend your fishies from the pelicans, the penguins will starve if there are not at least 5 fishies.\nWhen the missile is armed by one penguin, simply click to aim at pelican is in a dive, but be careful to blizzard and the wind that affects the flight path.\n\nhave fun!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0CEE0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tactical-penguin/embed?sid=1","plays":40710,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40427","slug":"drop-dunks","title":"Drop Dunks","description":"Slide your finger to guide the falling balls into the hoop. How many balls can you get?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40427/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drop-dunks/embed?sid=1","plays":40709,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O1DI7","slug":"quiz-squid-round","title":"Quiz Squid Round","description":"Quiz Squid Game is a trivia-style game to see if the player has paid attention to the details of the series, let's go show us your best!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O1DI7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quiz-squid-round/embed?sid=1","plays":40709,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N274","slug":"knives","title":"Knives","description":"Knives - Extreme - arcade game in which you will throw knives on a rotating surface, trying not to get into knives. Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N274/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knives/embed?sid=1","plays":40709,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"526A7","slug":"moto-maniac-3","title":"Moto Maniac 3","description":"This is a tilty bike game that will challenge your trial skills to the max. The trial competition is set up in the forest, so be ready to climb over trees and rocks. Your main goal is to overcome all the obstacles as fast as you can. But there is a second (yet important) goal - a wild bear was annoyed by the loud engine sounds and it is chasing you, so be quick not to be caught by the beast!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/526A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moto-maniac-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40704,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NGW6","slug":"swimming-pool-romance","title":"Swimming Pool Romance","description":"Lucas is looking for a girl, obviously, at the swimming pool. And he find one, Natasha. She's so cute, he can't resist. Help him attract her with his mojo so they can spend a romantic evening together!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NGW6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swimming-pool-romance/embed?sid=1","plays":40696,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9618T","slug":"catch-cats","title":"Catch Cats","description":"Welcome to Catch Cats, have fun in this fantastic game where you have to catch all the cats to increase your best score, what are you waiting for? go and play catch cats and the fun will be guaranteed !!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9618T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-cats/embed?sid=1","plays":40692,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40093","slug":"little-bouncing-guys","title":"Little Bouncing Guys","description":"La tribu des petits hommes-gommes s'est perdue…en laissant un de ses membres derrière elle! Aidez-le à rejoindre les siens, faites-le sauter toujours plus fort et toujours plus haut. Utilisez votre adresse et votre intelligence pour venir à bout des 30 niveaux qui attendent ce petit homme gomme!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40093/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-bouncing-guys/embed?sid=1","plays":40688,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3AHG1","slug":"hill-racing","title":"Hill Racing","description":"Hill Racing! Race your way uphill            \nIf you're looking for a racing game that does what it takes to be classic, Hill Racing! is the game for you. In Hill Racing, you race your way uphill towards the finish line with plenty of challenges in between! This physics-based game is perfect for those who love to race their cars, and we know how you feel: we've put together a full game cassette containing all the tools you need to drive these hills!            \nIn Hill Racing, you take on the challenge of driving your way uphill in order to reach the top of the hill. The game features a variety of unique hill climbing environments, as well as different cars that can be upgraded with coins and tricks. You'll need to use your skills and luck to make it to the top, and beware of obstacles along the way!            \n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3AHG1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hill-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40688,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66LT1","slug":"music-tools","title":"Music Tools","description":"Play music on three instruments, piano, drums, and guitar.\nBecome a pro musician by learning and playing all the instruments and have a fun time by playing online.\nJust use your skills and show them here online and play more games here only with Mapi Games.","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66LT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/music-tools/embed?sid=1","plays":40687,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"34I2O","slug":"big-donuts-mania","title":"Big Donuts Mania","description":"Big Donuts Mania is all about these ring-shaped sweets. In this fun and addictive game, you need to match a combination of 3 donuts or \nmore. You simply need to swap donuts position by tapping or dragging them. Sounds \nIf you've made a match, the donuts will be clear, and you will get the points! The more \nyou get, the better you will rank in the high score.\nWarning: Big Donuts Mania is as addictive as a box of donuts!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/34I2O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-donuts-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40685,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NRSET","slug":"funny-rescue-carpenter","title":"Funny Rescue Carpenter","description":"Leia is a great carpenter, but even the best will get accidents sometimes. Let's play and rescue Leia from the horrible accident! Help her recover from the wounds and have fun!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NRSET/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-rescue-carpenter/embed?sid=1","plays":40672,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3A434","slug":"yummy-toast","title":"Yummy Toast","description":"Yummy Toast is the funnest cooking game ever!\nYour goal is to make delicious toast by tapping the correct materials and ingredients u needed. Make the tastiest toast and serve to ur customers. Be the best toast master and to unlock all the achievements!","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3A434/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-toast/embed?sid=1","plays":40668,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40401","slug":"basketball-master-2","title":"Basketball Master 2","description":"Play through the 40 challenging levels and try to solve physics based puzzles. You’ll need to avoid solid obstacles, players, smash through glass and wood and figure out how to put the ball through the hoop!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40401/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-master-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40668,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"89M21","slug":"bike-mania-2","title":"Bike Mania 2","description":"The most famous bike game of the flash era is back! Tilt and balance your way over the obstacles. Containing 20 levels of sheer frustration and \"just one more go\" addictiveness, Bike Mania 2 is the ultimate in driving games for those who like a challenge.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/89M21/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bike-mania-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40661,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R4VUG","slug":"comics-456-survival-game","title":"Comics 456 - Survival Game","description":"🧩 Comics 456 - Squid Survival Game - Mind-bending erase game and fun comedy!\n\nComics 456 - S-quid Survival Game is an erase game full of comedy stories. Comics 456 - Squid Story is created to bring you the story of the player 456 trying to pass all challenged to be the last survivor and reach 45.6 billion won. In each level, you will laugh out loud with classic but funny scenes of the K-drama.\n\nWhat are you waiting for? 👀 👀\nDownload Comics 456 - Survival Game and discover the unexpected twists 🔥🔥\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R4VUG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/comics-456-survival-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40660,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AO2ID","slug":"a-day-in-the-countryside","title":"A day in the countryside","description":"A pleasant and relaxing day in the countryside?\nYou will play the role of a farmer struggling with the cultivation of his fields... and some funny and spiteful animals.\n\nMOVE:\n- Use arrow keys\n- Click or touch and hold on left/right of the character\n\nACTIONS:\n- Click or touch in the animals, something will happen\n- Use mouse wheel to zoom\n- In winter, click or touch on the screen to jump​ \n\nHOW TO PLAY\n- Take the moles and send them to sleep\n- Take the blackbirds with bomb and send them away\n- Feed the cute animals for an extra life\n- In winter, save snowmen from snowballs","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AO2ID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/a-day-in-the-countryside/embed?sid=1","plays":40659,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O8O7P","slug":"bloxdhop","title":"BloxdHop","description":"Play through parkour inspired obbys and make your way to the end of the maps! Twist, turn, run and jump your way through large themed worlds - all without falling to your demise. Race to the end, get a high score and earn gold while doing so.\n\n\nControls:\n\nWASD - movement\nShift - Run (alternately, double tap w)\nCrouch - C (alternately, Z, | or CAPS LOCK)\nChat - T or ENTER\nOpen Shop - B\nStart command - /\n\nCommands:\n\n/rtv - not a fan of this map? Vote to skip it!\n/players - see the current players in your lobby.\n/xp - See your level and xp.\n/played - See how much time you've spent having tons of fun.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O8O7P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bloxdhop/embed?sid=1","plays":40652,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B0209","slug":"daddy-rabbit","title":"Daddy Rabbit","description":"Daddy Rabbit must find all his lost babies inside the most amazing underground burrow you've ever seen. These baby rabbits sleep peacefully everywhere, but when daddy rabbit passes by, they will follow him all the way.    \nBaby bunnies will follow dad but will cry if they are awake and his dad wanders too far. When that happens, the zombies will get upset and go straight to eat them. That's when daddy rabbit will defend his sons with a carrot punch and give those evil zombies what they deserve. ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B0209/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/daddy-rabbit/embed?sid=1","plays":40650,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S5L11","slug":"basketball","title":"BasketBall","description":"Let’s experience the Retro Style Basketball in 3D. Start shooting the ball and score as much as you can.\nThere are 3 deadly challenging modes to make you addictive with Basketball action game.\n\n1. Time Attack\n2. Sudden Death\n3. Challenge\n\nIt’s time to dribble, shoot, score, WIN! Choose the ball and head to the basketball court for some awesome shoots. Flick the ball towards the basket to take a shot and feel the fun on playing real basketball. Basketball 3D is an awesome real feel game which can really challenge your shooting skills.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S5L11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":40648,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40236","slug":"master-checkers","title":"Master Checkers","description":"Master Checkers is the best Board Game. Play this stylish version ot the classic board game Checkers.\nThe game is based on the Italian Checkers gameplay!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["casino","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40236/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/master-checkers/embed?sid=1","plays":40648,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SCM86","slug":"carmiss","title":"CarMiss","description":"A great action game with you. You have to dodge the attacks with the car you have. They are attacking missiles from all sides. You can get yourself a new and faster vehicle by collecting gold while escaping. If you wish, you can increase the protection of the vehicle with gold or you can strengthen the protection shield by purchasing an anti-rocket gun. To destroy the rockets, you have to collide them with each other.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SCM86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/carmiss/embed?sid=1","plays":40639,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40079","slug":"cowboy-vs-martians","title":"Cowboy VS Martians","description":"Les martiens ont débarqué sur terre et ils n'ont pas l'air de venir en amis! Attrapez votre fusil, peignez votre belle moustache et commencez à les dézinguer! Serez-vous le cowboy qui les abattra tous ?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40079/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cowboy-vs-martians/embed?sid=1","plays":40635,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40126","slug":"panda-hair-do","title":"Panda Hair-do","description":"Vous aimez les pandas ? Cette jeune fille les adore mais ce qu'elle aime encore plus, c'est de prendre soin de son apparence! Aidez-la à s'occuper de ses cheveux, à s'habiller et à se préparer à passer une super journée. Commencez déjà par lui laver les cheveux avant de passer à la suite!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40126/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/panda-hairdo/embed?sid=1","plays":40634,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6PD09","slug":"car-rapide","title":"Car Rapide","description":"Drive and avoid obstacles on the roads of Senegal.\nCollect coins and unlock special cars!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6PD09/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-rapide/embed?sid=1","plays":40632,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"748S4","slug":"endless-car-chase","title":"Endless Car Chase","description":"Préparez-vous à une montée d'adrénaline ultime avec Endless Car Chase, le jeu rapide qui vous met derrière le volant d'une course-poursuite à grande vitesse ! Collectez de l'argent et des power-ups alors que vous foncez à travers les rues de la ville, mais attention à la police qui est à vos trousses. Avec des contrôles faciles à utiliser et un gameplay addictif, ce jeu est prêt à jouer directement hors de la boîte. Mais pourquoi se contenter de l'expérience par défaut quand vous pouvez personnaliser le jeu selon vos préférences ? Modifiez l'environnement, les voitures, et même la musique pour créer une expérience de jeu unique et personnalisée. Préparez-vous à semer la loi et devenir le meilleur pilote de fuite dans Endless Car Chase !","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/748S4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/endless-car-chase/embed?sid=1","plays":40626,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7300A","slug":"parmesan-partisan","title":"Parmesan Partisan","description":"You are the last defence, you are a lonely cheesy partisan who has to protect his people from the menace of the Mice People, who wants to conquer an eat all the cheese they can find! You are the last hope of your people: defend them with your shotgun, kill as many rats as you can, and free your nation from the rodents conquerors!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7300A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parmesan-partisan/embed?sid=1","plays":40623,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U2G53","slug":"bowling-hero-multiplayer","title":"Bowling Hero Multiplayer","description":"\"Compete with your friends on the same device or with other players from all over the world.\n\nChoose a hero from the six available.\n\nThrow the ball and shoot down as many pins as possible!\n\nHow many strikes will you hit?\"","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U2G53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bowling-hero-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40619,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40436","slug":"mafia-billiard-tricks","title":"Mafia Billiard Tricks","description":"Mafia Billiard Tricks is a billiard arcade game in which you can play the challenging game of billiards. You are not only playing for fun though; your opponents are part of the infamous mafia. You must earn their respect by beating each crew member!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics","sports","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40436/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mafia-billiard-tricks/embed?sid=1","plays":40619,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I6ST5","slug":"cross-the-bridge","title":"Cross the Bridge","description":"In this fun game you must try to complete the path for the car to pass before time runs out, agility and reasoning are a good combination for this game.","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I6ST5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cross-the-bridge/embed?sid=1","plays":40612,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L35GT","slug":"nastya-cute-blogger","title":"Nastya Cute Blogger","description":"Cute Nastya is a very popular blogger. Her mom and dad help her make cool videos. In this episode, Nastya's family will decorate the house for the holiday, and Nastya herself will choose stylish outfits and help her dad turn into a glamorous fairy. Let's join her and master her makeup skills. Have fun with cute blogger Nastya!","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L35GT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nastya-cute-blogger/embed?sid=1","plays":40611,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RO492","slug":"run-gun-robots","title":"Run Gun Robots","description":"Run Gun Robots is a run and gun game, where you have to jump from building to building destroying aggressive robots and avoiding deadly traps. Earn money buy defeating enemies and buy new powerups to to better address this new threat.\n\nControls:\nMobile: Touch the button on the screen to Jump, Shoot or pass trough a platform.\nKeyboard: W or Up to jump, X or Spacebar to shoot, S or Down to pass trough a platform\nGame pad: A or LT to Jump, B or RT to shoot, D-pad Down to pass trough a platform\n\n-4 different enemies\n-10 levels with increasing difficulty\n- Engaging music","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RO492/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-gun-robots/embed?sid=1","plays":40610,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40080","slug":"fantasy-star-pinball","title":"Fantasy Star Pinball","description":"Atteignez les sommets du high score dans ce magnifique jeu de flipper fantasy en 3D! Shootez la boule, et trouvez les scénarios cachés pour booster vos points.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40080/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fantasy-star-pinball/embed?sid=1","plays":40598,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"146AA","slug":"maga-run","title":"MAGA run","description":"Le président sortant doit s'échapper du FBI.\nTrouve les bulletins de vote perdus, collecte suffisamment d'argent et utilise Twitter pour réussir.\nPeut-être peux tu regagner ta présidence?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/146AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maga-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40598,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TAPQO","slug":"two-impostor-squid-challenge","title":"Two Impostor Squid Challenge","description":"Are you ready for the two impostor squid challenge game that you can play with your friend for two? Play with your friend in two player green light red light game and tug of war game.\n\nHow to Play?\nBlue Player \"A\" Press Key & Mobile Touch Control / Red Player \"P\" Press Key & Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TAPQO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/two-impostor-squid-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40596,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"064S4","slug":"crossword","title":"Crossword","description":"Solve thousands of crossword puzzles for free, no subscription required!\nSolving crosswords is like mental excercise, it's challenging and relaxing at the same time. Let’s get solving! Play  \"Crossword\" now and join the thousands of crossword enthusiasts!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/064S4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crossword/embed?sid=1","plays":40594,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CEE94","slug":"office-io","title":"Office.io","description":"Office.io is an office simulator game in which you are the boss. Hire employees and accept or deny their requests. Be careful! Your decisions will make your employees happy or sad. If motivation is too low, employees will do crazy things!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CEE94/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/office-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40593,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40147","slug":"astro-digger","title":"Astro Digger","description":"Astro Digger est un jeu d'arcade solo fun et addictif qui se joue avec les flèches de votre clavier ou simplement au doigt. Faites la connaissance de Astro Digger, le mineur de l'espace, et aidez-le à accomplir sa tâche en récupérant de l'or et des minerais sur les plus gros astéroïdes. Attention car il y a de grandes distractions sur le chemin, alors utilisez les téléporteurs et plantez des bombes si vous vous retrouvez coincé.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40147/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/astro-digger/embed?sid=1","plays":40591,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40423","slug":"rabbit-samurai","title":"Rabbit Samurai","description":"Rabbit Samurai is on a big adventure to help his Sensei. Your goal is to find all mice and rescue them from the wolf's lair. Use the rope and sticking grappling hook to fly over the land. Launch yourself from the ninja cannon, collect all carrots and find hidden crystals. Avoid dangerous spikes!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40423/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rabbit-samurai/embed?sid=1","plays":40590,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6778N","slug":"candy-bubble","title":"Candy Bubble","description":"Amazing candy bubble buster game comes, it's the best Bubble\nShooter with amazing effects! Your goal is to match groups of three or more same-colored candy bubbles to clear the playing field; use the least small ball to end level.\nUse the superb technique to break in one fell swoop, and experience the happiness of success!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6778N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-bubble/embed?sid=1","plays":40590,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7R19C","slug":"one-card-game","title":"ONE Card Game","description":"Le jeu amusant et passionnant ONE vous manque ? Ou bien peut-être vous n’avez pas joué à ce jeu merveilleux auparavant ? Alors allez-y, sélectionnez un personnage et participez à des batailles amicales remarquables. Vous aurez une atmosphère parfaite de jeu, des règles détaillées, une gestion facile et plusieurs adversaires intéressants qui sont prêts à vous tenir compagnie à tout moment.","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7R19C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-card-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40586,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"642G0","slug":"my-golf","title":"My Golf","description":"Do you like golf? Try one shot hole in My Golf, unlock new levels and new balls by completing the world with all the stars... ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/642G0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-golf/embed?sid=1","plays":40583,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NL9HE","slug":"spear-toss-challenge","title":"Spear Toss Challenge","description":"How far can you throw a spear?","category":"Sport","tags":["sports","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NL9HE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spear-toss-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40581,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"444E0","slug":"towerland","title":"Towerland","description":"Towerland is a top-down shooter with game mechanics inspired by the famous Binding of Isaac.\nFeatures:\n-Dozen of monsters\n-Unlockable Powerups\n-3 Different game modes\n-3 Bosses\n\nGAME CONTROLS\n\nKeyboard:\n\nWASD to move\n\nArrow Keys to Shoot\n\nP to Pause the game\n\nGamepad:\n\nLeft Analog / D-pad Move\n\nRight Analog / XYBA to Shoot\n\nStart/Menu to Pause the game\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/444E0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/towerland/embed?sid=1","plays":40580,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FE9I1","slug":"soldiers-fury","title":"Soldiers Fury","description":"C'est la guerre ! Et en tant que soldat d'élite, vous avez des missions à accomplir ! Foncez, récupérez des armes et des bonus, et tirez sur tous les ennemis en tentant de survivre ! Améliorez votre arsenal et laissez libre cours à votre fureur ! Les soldats ennemis ne cessent d'arriver par vagues, mais vous pouvez utiliser votre environnement.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FE9I1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soldiers-fury/embed?sid=1","plays":40580,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20","slug":"sweet-monsters","title":"Sweet Monsters","description":"Sweet Monsters est un jeu de Parkour en 2d qui vous fera courir et sauter des tonnes d'obstacles pour déguster des friandises. Le but n'est pas forcément d'aller le plus loin possible, car plus vous mangerez, plus vous ferez de combos et boosterez votre score pour obtenir des récompenses. Plus vous jouerez, plus la difficulté augmentera. Etes-vous prêt à relever le défi?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-monsters/embed?sid=1","plays":40577,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T124","slug":"hit-master","title":"Hit Master","description":"Are you ready to become a hero, spy, and legend? Solve puzzling challenges, show off your deadly accuracy and take aim at the enemies. Come experience the shooting phenomenon.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T124/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hit-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40570,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AP482","slug":"perfect-car-parking","title":"Perfect Car Parking","description":"Perfect Car Parking game created specially for whom wants to park car very carefully. \n\nAre you annoyed by all the similar parking games, and lack of high quality graphics and uniqueness? Are you looking forward to have a new car parking to park your vehicle as much as you want? We know you are here with a hope to find a game that suits you perfectly.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AP482/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/perfect-car-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":40570,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RR76","slug":"rope-draw","title":"Rope Draw","description":"Rope draw is a puzzle game in wich you will push ropes to make new arrangements with them. Your objective is to copy the arrangement that will appear above. If needed, there is a hint button that will show you the first moves. There are 120 different levels and the 'Fun' mode (unlocked after beating level 40), in which you can insert new ropes or even push them as you wish.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RR76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rope-draw/embed?sid=1","plays":40569,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66EE6","slug":"airspace2","title":"AirSpace2","description":"Bienvenue dans Airspace, passez tous les astéroïdes sans détruire votre vaisseau, marquez des points en prenant toutes les sphères bleues, qu'attendez-vous ?? Allez jouer à Airspace maintenant et le plaisir sera garanti !!!!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66EE6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6EMO6","slug":"design-my-home-makeover","title":"Design My Home Makeover","description":"Home Design est une passion, et si vous voulez transformer les rêves en réalité en aidant les familles chanceuses à concevoir une maison de rêve. Ce jeu de conception de maison - Dream House Makeover est un gameplay parfait avec un mode hors ligne de plaisir relaxant sans fin pour transformer des maisons obsolètes en un magnifique manoir familial. Vous pouvez redessiner un beau manoir en rénovant la maison et en la relookant en concevant et en restaurant pour concevoir et décorer ma maison de chacun de vos clients.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6EMO6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/design-my-home-makeover/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9G14G","slug":"gems-swipe","title":"Gems Swipe","description":"gems swipe is an html5 match 3 game, match gems and execute and get the highest score ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9G14G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gems-swipe/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"49311","slug":"infinity","title":"Infinity","description":"Welcome to Infinity, you control your character, avoid the red apples and collect the yellow ones to accumulate points, what are you waiting for, go now to play Infinity and the fun is guaranteed !!!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/49311/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinity/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PAN42","slug":"ninja-in-cape","title":"Ninja in Cape","description":"Are you ready for adventure with the ninja in cape?\nA journey full of action and adrenaline awaits you!\nThere are 20 adventurous levels for you to play without breathing.\nYou have weapons that you can use against enemies.\nLet's start the adventure now and complete the levels!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PAN42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-in-cape/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KT6O8","slug":"retro-basketball","title":"Retro Basketball","description":"Retro Basketball a fun sport game to play on.\nThis basket ball game gives always fun to play.\nThis is the game just to throw as many balls as you can and achieve high score.\nAim the ball exactly in the basket and achive goal.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KT6O8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15S18","slug":"sea-rush","title":"Sea Rush","description":"Utilisez votre imagination et découvrez ce que renferme l'océan. Sauvez tous les poissons dispersés à travers les niveaux et admirez toutes leurs belles couleurs.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15S18/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sea-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40567,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IA1AO","slug":"mad-mad-unicorn","title":"Mad Mad Unicorn","description":"Mad Mad Unicorn is a game about a nasty flying unicorn who is out for blood!\nHelp him in is hell race against poor and defenceless birds!\nBut the humankind won't let this evil unicorn do whatever he wants: they will try to shoot him down with powerful misseles launched from any direction!\nMaybe a magic carrot will give him the power to whitstand those deadly weapons...\n\nFEATURES:\n- One endless sky level with increasing difficulty\n- 10 artworks to unlock\n- Achievements\n- A crazy flying unicorn\n- Misseles, explosive birds, and other funny visual effects\n- One Touch game controls.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IA1AO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mad-mad-unicorn/embed?sid=1","plays":40565,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77F6O","slug":"fireblob-winter","title":"FireBlob Winter","description":"Sequel to FireBlob, now with more levels and detail, better graphics, new puzzles, speedrun mode, and a final boss battle!\n\nFireBlob is a Platform-Puzzle game where you command a small fireball in order to reach and ignite a wood fire; use the ball's heat abilities to melt the ice or use some level objects to help her to complete his task. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77F6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fireblob-winter/embed?sid=1","plays":40559,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40115","slug":"tic-tac-toe-html5","title":"Tic Tac Toe HTML5","description":"Retrouvez le célèbre \"Morpion\" en version HTML5 et profitez de nouveau modes de jeu en 3X3, 5X5 et même 7X7 où vous devrez remplir 4 cases au lieu de 3!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40115/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tic-tac-toe-html5/embed?sid=1","plays":40554,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40447","slug":"superstar-kitty-fashion-award","title":"Superstar Kitty Fashion Award","description":"Express your fashion and unique style to transform your little kitty in real beauty like a superstar in this amazing Superstar Kitty Fashion Award game with new hairstyles and fabulous makeover. Start with a spa treatment for a lovely facial and make her skin smooth, shinny, and glowing to look good at the award show.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40447/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superstar-kitty-fashion-award/embed?sid=1","plays":40550,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16645","slug":"2048-hex-chain-merge","title":"2048 Hex Chain Merge","description":"248 merge is an amazing block merge game.\n ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16645/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-hex-chain-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":40549,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E23EK","slug":"bike-mania-3-on-ice","title":"Bike Mania 3 On Ice","description":"Slip and slide your way through 20 levels of classic Bike Mania action! Frustration, adrenaline and the potential for a broken keyboard all await you as you take on the original and the best bike trail game of all time!","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E23EK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bike-mania-3-on-ice/embed?sid=1","plays":40546,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SMMM1","slug":"456-impostor","title":"456 impostor","description":"You are astronaut number \"456\" trying to survive in space. Your only solution is to destroy the men in the red suits. you have to jump on them and crush them to destroy them. destroy them and reach the final level. every 10 levels there is an endless run and men in red suits you have to kill.\n\nHow to Play\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SMMM1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/456-impostor/embed?sid=1","plays":40544,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36BI9","slug":"brick-breaker-retro","title":"Brick Breaker Retro","description":"Welcome to the Brick Breaker Retro. If you like breaking bricks, this is your game. Will you be able to overcome all the levels? What about getting the highest score?\n\nEvery time you pass four levels, you can unlock the next ones and continue from there, although you can also start from the beginning to obtain a higher score.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36BI9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brick-breaker-retro/embed?sid=1","plays":40543,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8S62","slug":"soccer-heroes","title":"Soccer Heroes","description":"Show all your skill in this football game. Choose your dream team and get into the fast-paced football action where you control um jogador. You can score goals with just a swipe of your finger or mouse. You are in charge of both the offense and the defense in this game, so you have to be quick to gain the upper hand.\n\nInstructions:\nTouch and drag your player to move.\nUse your player to attack and defend the goal.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8S62/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-heroes/embed?sid=1","plays":40542,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20066","slug":"broom","title":"Broom","description":"Broom est un jeu de course en pixel art qui vous fera traverser une autoroute sans fin. Utilisez vos super réflexes à bon escient pour exploser votre high score. Plongez dans un univers minimaliste et hyper arcade, et confrontez-vous à une difficulté de jeu très élevée!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20066/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/broom/embed?sid=1","plays":40538,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4NOI1","slug":"noob-vs-stickman-zombies","title":"Noob vs Stickman Zombies","description":"Noob vs Stickman Zombies un matin d'été tranquille, alors que Noob dormait encore doucement dans sa cabane confortable, quelqu'un a allumé une musique assourdissante qui a fait trembler toute la maison. Quand il est sorti, il a découvert que juste à côté de lui, un groupe de Stickmen organisait une soirée dansante féroce, comme s'il essayait exprès de l'ennuyer. Dans un accès de rage, Noob retira son arc du mur pour venger sa journée gâchée et instruire tous ceux qui osaient troubler sa tranquillité ! \"Noob vs Stickman Zombies\" est un jeu d'arcade amusant avec une histoire intéressante dans laquelle vous devez donner une leçon aux voisins ennuyeux !","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4NOI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-stickman-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40537,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40161","slug":"glauron-dragon-tales","title":"Glauron: dragon tales","description":"Glauron, le premier né du clan des Dragons Ailés, s'est finalement échappé de sa prison dans laquelle il était retenu depuis 500 ans! Bien sûr il souhaite se venger et vous allez pouvoir l'aider en répandant chaos et désolation parmi les citoyens innocents...mais méfiez-vous car ces derniers sont armés et tenteront de se défendre!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40161/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glauron-dragon-tales/embed?sid=1","plays":40535,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20065","slug":"zombie-invasion","title":"Zombie Invasion","description":"Plongez dans Zombie Invasion, le jeu de survie par excellence. Survivez à la horde zombie aussi longtemps que vous le pouvez et empêchez-les de traverser le pont. A chaque zombie qui passe entre les mailles de votre défense, vous perdez des points d'énergie. Prenez soin de ne pas blesser les survivants et éliminez tous les zombies!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20065/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":40533,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENTOS","slug":"monster-popsy-dolls","title":"Monster Popsy Dolls","description":"Rencontrez un monstre incroyable-popsy. Ces jouets sont à la fois beaux et terribles! Choisissez parmi une variété de coiffures et de tenues pour créer votre propre poupée unique. Utilisez vos compétences de maquilleur pour choisir le bon maquillage pour votre popsy. Essayez des robes, des hauts, des vestes en cuir, des bottes et des bijoux amusants.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENTOS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-popsy-dolls/embed?sid=1","plays":40524,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2S2KM","slug":"clash-of-kingdom","title":"Clash of Kingdom","description":"Clash of Kingdom is a free online game featuring a war among kingdoms. Now, it’s not just the fun games on the computer that you can enjoy completely free \nIf you are looking for an amazing game to play this weekend, I can highly recommend Clash of Kingdom. This game is wonderful and all types of people can enjoy it, rich or poor, beginner or the most experienced gamer out there.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2S2KM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clash-of-kingdom/embed?sid=1","plays":40523,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44NA6","slug":"ant-maze","title":"Ant Maze","description":"A leading ant must find his way home, for that he must eliminate the enemy blue ants, but he is not alone, he has allies to turn to to be stronger","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44NA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ant-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":40522,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10035","slug":"brazil-cup-2014","title":"Brazil Cup 2014","description":"Embarquez pour la Coupe du Monde 2014 grâce à \"Brazil Cup 2014\", un des meilleurs jeux de football disponible sur le web.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10035/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brazil-cup-2014/embed?sid=1","plays":40518,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T6I69","slug":"trimat","title":"Trimat","description":"Trimat is a video game set in space with some levels. Avoid lasers, bombs, lava and cannonballs and travel the vastness of the galaxy!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T6I69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trimat/embed?sid=1","plays":40517,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ATHD","slug":"football-champ-3d","title":"Football Champ 3D","description":"Football Champ 3D is the best football and matchless combination for footballlovers. Enjoy this fantasy football game!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ATHD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-champ-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40514,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S9STO","slug":"bowmastery-zombies","title":"Bowmastery - Zombies!","description":"Bowmastery zombies is a fascinating game that will give a lot of pleasure to children and adults. Your job is to kill terrible zombies. You have a bow and arrows, but only on the first level you can directly shoot your opponents. At other levels, obstacles will arise between the hero and the zombies. Think where you can shoot to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S9STO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bowmastery-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40514,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"666B3","slug":"run-rabbit-run","title":"Run Rabbit Run","description":"Imagine you are a cute blue bunny and you have to reach the guard at the end of each level! Reach the guards and join the army in the latest episode and defeat enemies and monsters!   \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD & Mobile Touch Control (Double Jump Available)","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/666B3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-rabbit-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40513,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76K67","slug":"snake-brawl","title":"Snake Brawl","description":"Swipe your finger to guide a snake of balls and break the bricks on SNake Brawl!\nTry to break as many bricks as possible and increase your score.\nGet additional balls and make the biggest snake ever!\nVery easy to play but very hard to reach high scores!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76K67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snake-brawl/embed?sid=1","plays":40510,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NRLO0","slug":"mandala-coloring-book","title":"Mandala Coloring Book","description":"Détendez-vous tout en coloriant de belles images. Coloriez-les selon vos goûts. Tout ce que vous avez à faire, c'est laisser libre cours à votre imagination et colorier tout ce que vous aimez. Essayez de créer une œuvre d'art à couper le souffle.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NRLO0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mandala-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":40509,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6P4N1","slug":"open-ttd","title":"Open TTD","description":"OpenTTD is a business simulation game in which players try to earn money by transporting passengers and freight via road, rail, water and air. It is an open-source remake and expansion of the 1994 Chris Sawyer video game Transport Tycoon Deluxe. \n\nTo start building a transport empire, the player must construct transport routes, consisting of stations near industries or towns, and in the case of trains or road vehicles, near physical routes. One transport route can utilize several different forms of transport, e.g. truck→ship→train. The player's company and the individual stations each have ratings that depend largely on their efficiency at moving goods from one stations to the other. A station with high ratings may attract more goods. ","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6P4N1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/openttd/embed?sid=1","plays":40508,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16PA5","slug":"space-war","title":"Space War","description":"Space War est un jeu unique et innovant en son genre, en effet en plus de présenter une version classique du \"Space Shooter\", il dispose d'un mode complètement innovant dans lequel vous devrez utiliser le microphone pour tirer sur les ennemis, le jeu peut être joué à la fois sur ordinateur et sur mobile, qu'attendez-vous ? Jouez à Space War maintenant !\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16PA5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-war/embed?sid=1","plays":40507,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I1A3S","slug":"princess-kawaii-swimwear","title":"Princess Kawaii Swimwear","description":"La saison de baignade est ouverte! Les princesses vont à la plage. Quel est le vêtement le plus chaud sur la plage? Maillot de bain, bien sûr! Il suffit de regarder cette nouvelle collection de maillots de bain kawaii mignons: il y a suffisamment de tenues pour satisfaire même la princesse la plus maussade. La couleur délicate-bleu, rose, tons pastel-soulignera la sophistication de n'importe quelle fille. Choisissez votre maillot de bain princesse kawaii et détendez-vous avec style!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I1A3S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-kawaii-swimwear/embed?sid=1","plays":40504,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40294","slug":"jelly-bomb","title":"Jelly Bomb","description":"Jelly Bomb has spread all over your kitchen tables! You can get rid of it by dripping it with a jelly remover, but watch out: there are only a few drops left, you will have to use them wisely to ensure the perfect splashing chain reaction!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40294/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jelly-bomb/embed?sid=1","plays":40504,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P1526","slug":"jump-bottle","title":"Jump Bottle","description":"Bouteille Flip - Jeu de défi de saut. Vous devez simplement sauter! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P1526/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-bottle/embed?sid=1","plays":40503,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40292","slug":"fox-adventurer","title":"Fox Adventurer","description":"Play Fox Adventurer and help Mr. Fox in his magical adventure.. Switch between day and night to choose the right way to finish level. Create stone clones to jump higher and collect green gems.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40292/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fox-adventurer/embed?sid=1","plays":40501,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9TM1L","slug":"tic-tac-toe-multiplayer","title":"Tic Tac Toe Multiplayer","description":"Ultimate Tic Tac Toe is a HTML5 Board Game. \nEnjoy this nice version of the classic Tic Tac Toe Game. 3 Game’s Mode: \n- Multiplayer mode \n- Play against the pc \n- Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9TM1L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tic-tac-toe-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40496,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0159B","slug":"unblock-that","title":"Unblock That","description":"Unblock That est un jeu de casse-têtes simple et addictif. Le but est de faire sortir le bloc rouge du plateau de jeu en faisant glisser les autres blocs qui sont sur le chemin. Faites-le avec le moins de coups possible. Le jeu comprend 4 niveaux de difficulté allant de Débutant à Expert. Unblock That peut vous aider à entraîner votre cerveau et à garder un esprit aiguisé au quotidien.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0159B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/unblock-that/embed?sid=1","plays":40494,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40172","slug":"fancy-diver","title":"Fancy Diver","description":"Votre but est d'aider tous les plongeurs à remonter jusqu'en haut de l'écran avant que leur oxygène soit à zéro. Touchez les groupes de coraux de couleur similaire (3 ou plus) de façon à les faire disparaitre. Faites disparaitres de grands groupes de coraux de manière à gagner des mines spéciales et des power-ups!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40172/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fancy-diver/embed?sid=1","plays":40491,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S068C","slug":"kids-cute-pairs","title":"Kids: Cute Pairs","description":"Laissez vos enfants jouer à un jeu de concentration traditionnel. Il y a trois difficultés différentes, chacune avec ses propres images incluant des fruits et des légumes, des instruments de musique et des animaux. C'est un jeu stimulant pour les enfants de tout âge. Il comprend aussi un mode Deux joueurs pour vous permettre de jouer ensemble ! \n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S068C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-cute-pairs/embed?sid=1","plays":40489,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M46I6","slug":"kobadoo-emojis","title":"Kobadoo Emojis","description":"Kobadoo Emojis is a browser game that trains your brain by memorizing funny emojis in the right order.\n\nWhen you play Kobadoo Emojis you are actively using your working memory. Several scientific studies suggest that training of working memory has beneficial effects and can increase your cognitive functions.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M46I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kobadoo-emojis/embed?sid=1","plays":40487,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E83S5","slug":"mahjong-sweet-easter","title":"Mahjong Sweet Easter","description":"Easter eggs and candies, what could be better? Celebrate easter with our new game! Match as many tiles as you can before time is up and try to deal with \"gravity\"!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E83S5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-sweet-easter/embed?sid=1","plays":40484,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40396","slug":"color-blocks","title":"Color Blocks","description":"Color Blocks is easy to play and a pleasurable game for all ages! Simply drag the blocks and fill up all colored grids. Once you start, you will definitely be hooked: this 3D-style game awaits you!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40396/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":40483,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8407E","slug":"barbarian-run","title":"Barbarian Run","description":"barbarian run is a retro endless run game, run and kill monster with jump and collecting coins to get a lot of scores \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8407E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fire-soldier/embed?sid=1","plays":40480,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13T40","slug":"jet-strike","title":"Jet Strike","description":"Jet Strike is the super arcade casual game everyone is playing right now. Enjoy!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13T40/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jet-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":40480,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0410S","slug":"smash-the-flies","title":"Smash the Flies","description":"This is a cool, easy, and fun to play, endless game.\nTap or Click on the Flies with your fingers to smash them, before they leave the screen.\nBut don't tap the red one, or you finish the game! Be fast and quick to smash all of them and achieve high scores.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0410S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smash-the-flies/embed?sid=1","plays":40480,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5C9TC","slug":"ocean-kids-back-to-school","title":"Ocean Kids Back to School","description":"Welcome to Ocean Kids Back to school. It’s back to school time for these Kids. Can you help them get ready for their first day of classes? They’ll need to pick some cool outfits, new hairstyles, accessories, and school supplies too in this online dress-up and design game for girls. After you’re all done, help them to repair their vespa. Play and have fun!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5C9TC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ocean-kids-back-to-school/embed?sid=1","plays":40479,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20526","slug":"gs","title":"GS","description":"Easy and simple game, you have to pass two levels to be able to catch all the birds and fly them within a time limit","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20526/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gs/embed?sid=1","plays":40478,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U66A7","slug":"urban-sniper-multiplayer-2","title":"Urban Sniper Multiplayer 2","description":"Urban Sniper Multiplayer 2 features ultimate sniper warfare in grand city, use different sniper rifles to shoot rival players across vast highly detailed map and try to get the highest amount of frags in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U66A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/urban-sniper-multiplayer-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40478,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7BO15","slug":"shadobirds","title":"Shadobirds","description":"Don't download this game! it's too hard for you! You won't complete this game! Never! Trust me, I programmed this, I know what I'm saying. I literally lost the best part of my life trying to beat it. I made it at last, but the price was too high! I lost everything I love to beat it, and now I'm alone and lonely, but at least I can say \"I completed Shadobirds\". Can you say the same?\nFEATURING:\n20 Levels full of obstacles\nBirds\nBlack Shadows\nOther Birds\nNest\nObstacles\nand when you think you are done... More obstacles!\nEnjoy... if you can","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7BO15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shadobirds/embed?sid=1","plays":40478,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5516C","slug":"blueguy-escape","title":"BlueGuy Escape","description":"blue guy escape is an adventure html5 retro game, run collect score by eating many fruits and avoid obstacles by flipping up and down ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5516C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blueguy-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":40477,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6C187","slug":"fruit-clicker","title":"Fruit Clicker","description":"A game about collecting as much FruitCoins as you can. The FruitCoins can be used to purchase upgrades at the store. Play this game now and try to unlock the secret reward.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6C187/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":40474,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L26C1","slug":"flashcount","title":"FlashCount","description":"Guess how many red dots appear disappear from the screen","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L26C1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flashcount/embed?sid=1","plays":40471,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46OMG","slug":"olympian-mahjong","title":"Olympian Mahjong","description":"Match identical sport tiles to remove them from the playing field. All mahjong tiles represent kinds of winter sports that will be played at the Olympic Winter Games in Beijing 2022.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46OMG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/olympian-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":40471,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W81OB","slug":"cowboy-s-shooter","title":"Cowboy's Shooter","description":"Cowboy's Shooter est un jeu qui se déroule dans l'ouest antique. Œil! De nombreux bandits voudront votre prime, tuez-les tous mais faites attention aux tirs ! La charge est assez lente, alors choisissez le bon moment pour charger ! Jouez à Cowboy's Shootooter sur votre ordinateur, smartphone ou tablette ! De nouvelles armes sortiront chaque mois, alors revenez de temps en temps ! Qu'est-ce que tu attends? Plongez dans le jeu !\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W81OB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cowboy-s-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RAS9H","slug":"dark-chess","title":"Dark Chess","description":"It is a very interesting chess, it is using Chinese Chess to play but the game rule is very different.\n\nOnly higher level chess can eat lower level chess, if all of your chesses are eaten or you cannot move any chess. You will loss.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RAS9H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dark-chess/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UL1OA","slug":"domino-multiplayer","title":"Domino Multiplayer","description":"Domino Multiplayer is a HTML5 Board Game. \nEnjoy this stylish version of the classic Domino Game. \n3 Game’s Mode: \n- Multiplayer mode \n- Play against the pc \n- Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board","classics","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UL1OA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/domino-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TAAOS","slug":"dots-attack","title":"Dots Attack","description":"Switch color dot! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TAAOS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dots-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91E14","slug":"fast-finders-io","title":"Fast Finders IO","description":"Find colored shape of a requested type faster than your opponents!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91E14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fast-finders-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IMEMG","slug":"squid-game-survival-challenge","title":"Squid Game Survival Challenge","description":"Welcome to the opportunity of a lifetime. Just try to give your best at the squid game challenge.\nAre you short on money?\nYou can earn 45.6 Billion Won just by sticking to fair play. There is only one rule, don’t get eliminated.\nRemember our card? Call us now. Challenge for our childish game event, it will be fun, but the stakes are deadly.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IMEMG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-game-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UD8U4","slug":"tap-double-tap-remake","title":"Tap Double-Tap REMAKE!","description":"A simple video game in which you will have to send the central ball to the half screen of the correct color. You will have to tap once to send the ball to the left, to send the ball to the right instead, you will have to tap it twice!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UD8U4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-double-tap/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7EEE1","slug":"east-runner","title":"East Runner","description":"Help the prince to run faster than everyone! Run as far as you can. Collect coins and buy things in the store. Become the best runner of the East!\nEndless game with great graphics to keep you playing.\nRun without hitting obstacles in the eastern safari.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7EEE1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/east-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40470,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40189","slug":"space-cord","title":"Space Cord","description":"Explore the space and collect all trophies through its energy platforms avoiding dangerous traps on your way! Try to hold on as long as possible in a space race!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40189/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-cord/embed?sid=1","plays":40469,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6B1OB","slug":"bigboom","title":"BigBoom","description":"Reach more and more objectives increase the mines","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6B1OB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bigboom/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F2W1I","slug":"fairy-wingerella","title":"Fairy Wingerella","description":"Wingerella is a fairy girl that is going to become the most cool and powerful fairy in the world.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F2W1I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-wingerella/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S4173","slug":"neon-block","title":"Neon Block","description":"A fun casual game with a neon theme. try to pass all levels with the least amount of deaths possible. Challenge your friends.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S4173/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/teste/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CAR76","slug":"red-and-green-color-rain","title":"Red and Green Color Rain","description":"Crazy sharp wheels and diamonds you need to collect welcome you in 6 games of the red and green series. collect diamonds, overcome obstacles and go to the next level!\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD and Arrow Keys - Mobile Touch","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CAR76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-green-color-rain/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3BUBI","slug":"road-builder-simulator","title":"Road Builder Simulator","description":"Using heavy machinery like heavy excavator, crane, road roller and a dumper truck in this City Road Construction 2020, learn and build your city with excellent fine-tuned construction simulation. This is a fun to construct like a real builder with hydraulic controls that provides an excellent driving view. Know inside story of road construction with the use of heavy machinery. Enjoy heavy machinery simulator to repair and construct new roads","category":"Stratégie","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3BUBI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/road-builder-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S6AU1","slug":"squid-game-3d-survival-squad","title":"Squid Game 3D Survival Squad","description":"$b","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S6AU1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-game-3d-survival-squad/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10O49","slug":"touchme","title":"Touchme","description":"Welcome to Touch Me, have fun accumulating points by touching the yellow ball and avoiding the yellow blue and white ones including bats, what are you waiting for ??? Go play Touch me now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10O49/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/touchme/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MM7AW","slug":"two-x2","title":"Two x2","description":"A very addicting Puzzle Game, similar to the popular 2048 game, but with a different logic. Connect the numbers and don’t run out of moves! Make lines connecting as many numbered points as possible. The longer is the line, the more points you get. Every time you connect numbers, you get a new doubled number.\nChallenge your friends, play it right now!\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MM7AW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/two-for-2-match-the-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4766P","slug":"simply-breakout","title":"Simply Breakout","description":"This is the best Brick Breaker that everyone can play, extremely simple, but really fun.\nThere are many elements and object, various levels and easy game controls.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4766P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/simply-breakout/embed?sid=1","plays":40468,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KZI7R","slug":"zombie-strike-2","title":"Zombie Strike 2","description":"You are trapped in a farm crowded with zombies and your mission is to survive five waves of zombies with increasing difficulty, use big arsenal of weapons to shoot hordes of incoming zombies and try to survive in order to successfully complete your mission.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KZI7R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-strike-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40465,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L6H44","slug":"alien-hunter-remastered","title":"Alien Hunter Remastered","description":"alien hunter remastered is an html5 platformer game, explore levels earn coins and destroy aliens ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L6H44/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-hunter-remastered/embed?sid=1","plays":40464,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17786","slug":"silent-asylum","title":"Silent Asylum","description":"You are trapped in silent asylum crowded with scary monsters and your mission is to shoot your way through dark corridors and find all keys to unlock the exit.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17786/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/silent-asylum/embed?sid=1","plays":40463,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2PE91","slug":"apples","title":"Apples","description":"Welcome to the apple game. only pick apples, be very careful not to get hit by the bullet, you have three chances to lose to get your high score","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2PE91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/apples/embed?sid=1","plays":40462,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z69R9","slug":"merge-block-puzzle","title":"Merge Block Puzzle","description":"MERGE BLOCK PUZZLE is a FREE and FUN puzzle game for all ages;\nMERGE BLOCK PUZZLE is a good game to help you relax and train your brain;\n\nHow to play this puzzle game?\n• Drag the number blocks to move them.\n• 2 same numbers could be merged into a larger numbe","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z69R9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40462,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZI893","slug":"zoo-trivia","title":"Zoo Trivia","description":"Il est temps de montrer votre connaissance des animaux ! Combien d'entre eux en connaissez-vous ? Pouvez-vous épeler les noms correctement ? Des dizaines d'animaux vous attendent. Des mammifères, chiens, chats, poissons, insectes et beaucoup plus ! C'est plus difficile que vous ne le pensez ! Mais ne vous inquiétez pas, vous pouvez toujours utiliser l'élégant système d'indices pour vous aider à surmonter les difficultés.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZI893/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zoo-trivia/embed?sid=1","plays":40462,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19616","slug":"exploder-io","title":"Exploder.io","description":"Exploder is a game similar to the classic Bomberman but with a space theme. Players need to fight other players as well as monsters by planting bombs and running away from attacks and explosions. Starting the game is pretty easy and straightforward; though, it is incredibly hard to master all the game tricks. All graphical game assets are pixel artwork to reflect on the original game. Battles in Exploder are very entertaining and challenging, with virtual coins and experience points as gratification! In the game shop, you can use the coins to upgrade your character's appearance by buying new skins and other aspects.","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19616/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/exploder-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40461,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"48O2T","slug":"retro-speed","title":"Retro Speed","description":"Feel the thrill of high speed racing in Retro Speed. It is an arcade racing game in which the speed of your car constantly increases as you keep collecting coins. Overtake as many cars as possible and emerge as the leader. Don't miss playing this highly addictive and fun game.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/48O2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-speed/embed?sid=1","plays":40461,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W393C","slug":"m3-power-3d-city-racing","title":"M3 Power 3D City Racing","description":"7 different bmw m3 survival games. be the last and be the first to achieve victory collect points you own the best car of the day! Are you ready to be the winner of m3 power 3d city racing?","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W393C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/m3-power-3d-city-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40459,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40389","slug":"crazy-switch-color","title":"Crazy Switch Color","description":"Faites sauter prudemment la balle à travers chaque obstacle lorsqu'il est de la même couleur que la balle.\nAttention de ne pas traverser la mauvaise couleur, sinon vous devrez recommencer.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40389/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-switch-color/embed?sid=1","plays":40457,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HACSD","slug":"head-ball-hyper-casual-game","title":"Head Ball Hyper Casual Game","description":"The Head Ball Hyper Casual Game is a new type of sport that involves the player's head. It was designed with an emphasis on creativity, agility and balance in mind while also ensuring they have fun!  \nAt Head Ball, they are always looking for new ways to make the game more exciting. One way is by giving their head coaches an opportunity to show off their creative and innovative side while staying competitive on all levels!  \n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HACSD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/head-ball-hyper-casual-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40457,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"99110","slug":"traigon","title":"Traigon","description":"Traigon is an obstacle course game, where we will be able to jump over ravines and spikes to reach the end of the level.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/99110/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/traigon/embed?sid=1","plays":40454,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9ER29","slug":"extreme-way","title":"Extreme Way","description":"You are a ninja who has to go through a bunch of obstacles! Run, jump and destroy walls on your way! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9ER29/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/extreme-way/embed?sid=1","plays":40453,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61FAB","slug":"baby-hazel-african-safari","title":"Baby Hazel African Safari","description":"Baby Hazel and her parents along with Bruno have gone on holiday to South Africa. After experiencing the beautiful scenic of Cape Town, they have decided to spend a night in the jungle safari tent. Isn't that exciting? Do you want to be part of this jungle adventure? Join Baby Hazel and her family and taste the wilderness of the Jungle. You need to be careful as jungles are a bit risky for young girls like Baby Hazel. Be with the little one and help in her needs. Make sure she does not get lost in the wilds.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61FAB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-hazel-african-safari/embed?sid=1","plays":40450,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6BE8B","slug":"mech-battle-simulator","title":"Mech Battle Simulator","description":"Simulateur de combat - robots, tanks et tourelles! La bataille réveille l'épopée!\n\nLes robots à fourrure jouent un rôle décisif lors de la guerre de 3070.\n\nCaractéristiques:\n• Simulateur de combat (Battle Simulator)\n• Dommages et coups de bélier complètement renversants et réalistes\n• Beau champ de bataille 3D\n• Unités des chars de forme, robots d'araignées, guerriers de robot de fourrure\n\nMaintenant, chaque robot de combat vaut son pesant d'or, et chaque bataille est un véritable test de jeu.\n\nSounds_freesound_org\nMusic_McGorilla42_Hidden-Tension","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6BE8B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mech-battle-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":40450,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40418","slug":"doctor-acorn-2","title":"Doctor Acorn 2","description":"Doctor Acorn travels through a puzzle world: fly on the bumblebee, jump from cloud to cloud, collect all stars and beware of wild boars!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40418/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doctor-acorn-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40449,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6SSG6","slug":"christmas-fishing","title":"Christmas Fishing","description":"Le Père Noël est allé à la pêche. Aidez-le à attraper autant de poissons que possible et à atteindre le fond. Il y a même des cadeaux avec des décorations de Noël qui flottent. Prenez-les et décorez le sapin de Noël dans la pièce du Père Noël.\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6SSG6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-fishing/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HS445","slug":"catch-the-beats","title":"Catch the Beats","description":"\nAll you need to play this game is your spacebar, your ears and your eyes! Watch and listen carefully, and hit the spacebar when the beat is in the patch.\n\nUse your listening skills for this game! Hit the spacebar every time the yellow dot is in the patch space! Sounds easy to you? Every level gets harder, every beat is faster and every second matters! Remember to keep your eyes on the patch space and hear every beat. Can you beat your own high score by listening to the beats? Let’s see!\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HS445/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catchthebeats/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1IN3R","slug":"neon-guitar","title":"Neon Guitar","description":"“Neon Guitar” is an inspired musical game in the critically acclaimed “Guitar Hero”, developed for the enjoyment of all people. Hit as many notes as fall on the screen to accumulate points and beat your highscores. Great game to train your reflexes and have fun at the same time! The designs are Neon style, very colorful and beautiful! Have a good time!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1IN3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-guitar/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6NI8R","slug":"parking","title":"Parking","description":"Jouez à l'un des jeux de stationnement les plus réalistes du marché. Conduisez différentes voitures, chacune avec un comportement unique. Découvrez de nombreuses missions variées dans un monde complètement simulé physiquement.","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6NI8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parking/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ALEA","slug":"slaky-ball-touch-ball-game","title":"Slaky Ball - Touch Ball Game","description":"$c","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ALEA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-fall-touch-ball-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E16WR","slug":"where-is-multiplayer","title":"Where is - Multiplayer","description":"Where is is a multiplayer PvP game in which the first to reach 10 points wins. Whoever starts the game will be the one who will check the cups and decide the object to hide under them. The opponent will have to guess under which cup the object is hidden or which object is hidden.\nWhere has also a local mode that will allow you to play against an artificial intelligence.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade","board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E16WR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/where-is/embed?sid=1","plays":40447,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W9OOK","slug":"blockworld-parkour","title":"Blockworld Parkour","description":"Welcome to the world of blocks. Pass different maps and follow the track. Beware of the lava you might die in the falling block world. If you die, you start from scratch, don't die! \n\nHow to Play?\n*Use WASD keys to play!                      \n*Use mouse cursor to rotate 360 ​​degrees.                      \n*Press the \"p\" key to stop the game.                      \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W9OOK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blockworld-parkour/embed?sid=1","plays":40446,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I5IS4","slug":"multiplication-simulator","title":"Multiplication Simulator","description":"Which of the tasks will be more fun for primary school students? Of course, the multiplication table. And such an educational game as “Multiplication Simulator” is perfect for children to quickly learn the multiplication tables in a playful way.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5IS4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/multiplication-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":40444,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40101","slug":"swipe-art-puzzle","title":"Swipe Art Puzzle","description":"Si vous aimez l'art - voici un jeu de puzzle pour vous. Déplacez les pièces pour recréer des peintures ultra célèbres faites par les plus anciens grands maîtres (qui ont été un peu \"améliorées\" avec notre humour étrange ;) Entraînez votre cerveau et faites le plein de beauté et d'humour en même temps!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40101/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swipe-art-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40443,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40154","slug":"mega-slots","title":"Mega Slots","description":"Mega slots est un simulateur de machines à sous diaboliquement excitant! Gagnez soit en horizontal soit en vertical en combinant 3 objets du même type. Tentez la roulette et booster encore plus vos gains. Le démon du jeu vous tient!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40154/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mega-slots/embed?sid=1","plays":40443,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A4F21","slug":"minigolf-master","title":"Minigolf Master","description":"Amusez-vous avec différents parcours de minigolf truffés d'obstacles et animé par la physique simulée. Atteignez le par ou obtenez un résultat encore meilleur pour déverrouiller d'autres niveaux, paramètres de difficulté et commandes. Chaque niveau de difficulté a ses propres commandes. Pouvez-vous terminer tout un parcours sous le par ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A4F21/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minigolf-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40442,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13OT7","slug":"attack-robots","title":"Attack Robots","description":"Attack Robots is a 3D action game with 10 levels playable in 3 difficulty modes. The goal in each is to eliminate all enemies. The game offers 3 weapons and option to buy medical kit that increases health. Have fun.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13OT7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/attack-robots/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TP565","slug":"don-t-drop-the-sponge","title":"Don't Drop the Sponge","description":"Don' Drop the Sponge is a cool endless game, very easy and intuitive to play, but it will be hard to stop playing.\nHit with your finger the blowing up balloons on the screen and touch the Sponge to prevent it from falling down.\nEnjoy this cool game the more you can!\nYou can play with your kids.\n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• very very easy to play\n• nice 2D graphics\n• endless game play\n• very fun game for kids and babies\n• cool sound effects","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TP565/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-drop-the-sponge/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62266","slug":"get10-plus","title":"Get10 Plus","description":"Vous aimez les maths ou les jeux de logique ? Grâce à cet amusant jeu de connexion de nombres, vous allez les adorer ! Associez les mêmes nombres voisins pour les transformer en un plus grand nombre. Associez davantage pour atteindre 10 et au-delà ! Un jeu facile à apprendre, mais difficile à maîtriser !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62266/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/get10-plus/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1M96","slug":"match-earth-online-game","title":"Match Earth Online Game","description":"Match Earth is an addictive match-3 puzzle game with relaxing gameplay and beautiful graphics. Match 3 or more of the same symbols in a row to clear the level.   \nPlay Match Earth online free. Destroy all the asteroids with your spaceship and don't crash into them.Match Earth is a fun and addicting match-3 game. Play on your phone or tablet for free.Match Earth is a free game where you can match the colors of the planets to their respective orbits.   \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1M96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-earth-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65305","slug":"memory","title":"Memory","description":"Play by heart and let's see what level you can get to","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65305/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memory/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S6RMO","slug":"platform-shooter","title":"Platform Shooter","description":"\"Platform Shooter\" est un jeu de tir de plateforme, avec beaucoup d'armes et plusieurs niveaux difficiles et différents ennemis.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S6RMO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/platform-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S2155","slug":"princess-maid-academy","title":"Princess Maid Academy","description":"La princesse a besoin d'une nouvelle femme de chambre, car elle a tellement de choses à faire - réceptions, rencontres avec les ambassadeurs d'autres États, bals de charité. Et quelqu'un à ce moment-là doit maintenir l'ordre dans le palais et dans la garde-robe de la princesse. Où trouver la bonne personne? Bien sûr à la princess maid academy! Ce n'est qu'ici que les femmes de chambre de la plus haute classe sont formées, leurs tenues ne sont que légèrement inférieures en beauté aux robes des princesses, et leur coiffure et leur posture sont toujours impeccables. Le style strict des tenues en noir et blanc peut parfois être dilué avec des nuances de rose, de bleu et de lilas. Un tablier blanc est un must-have pour une femme de chambre diligente. Choisissez la femme de chambre la plus élégante et la plus impeccable pour votre princesse!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S2155/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-maid-academy/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6008Q","slug":"red-square-adventure","title":"Red Square Adventure","description":"Welcome to the adventurous life of a cute red square. The red square has to pass the levels one by one and it needs you. Pass the obstacles and get the red square to the end of the level!\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control \n*Double jump available","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6008Q/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-square/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O3161","slug":"sandro-s-world","title":"Sandro's World","description":"sandro's world is a platform game full of obstacles and enemies to avoid","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O3161/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sandro-s-world/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AIMNW","slug":"sandwich-master","title":"Sandwich Master","description":"Plein de niveaux difficiles, ce jeu est conçu pour vous éviter l'ennui. Délicieux et très intéressant! À quelle hauteur pouvez-vous empiler votre sandwich?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AIMNW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sandwich-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40070","slug":"scratch-fruit","title":"Scratch Fruit","description":"Scratch Fruit est un jeu de gain instantané. Grattez et découvrez si vous avez gagné un prix ! C'est tout, juste de la simplicité, de la chance et du fun!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40070/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scratch-fruit/embed?sid=1","plays":40439,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"214N5","slug":"bomb-is-in-the-air","title":"Bomb is in the air","description":"How do you park a plane?\nA crazy aviator and his journey to discover the world. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/214N5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bomb-is-in-the-air/embed?sid=1","plays":40438,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NEESI","slug":"the-simple-piano","title":"The Simple Piano","description":"Simple piano application to learn play the piano and with realistic sounds of instruments.   \nHow to Play Piano:   \nJust run your fingers over the real piano tiles, playing live music and feel like a real musician.   \nFeatures:   \n• It works with all screen resolutions   \n• Full piano keyboard   \n• Multi-Touch   \n• Easy for children","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NEESI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-simple-piano/embed?sid=1","plays":40436,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UTA2U","slug":"fruit-smash-master","title":"Fruit Smash Master","description":"Fruit Smash Master Fruit Cutter is a fun and challenging fruit slicing game.    \nfruit smashing is an essential skill for cooking and eating. By slicing fruit, you can make it easier to get the most out of your fruits by making them more accessible and tasty. Fruit Smash Master offers a unique and challenging experience that will have you coming back for more! \n \nThe objective of the game is to cut as many pieces from a fruit as possible in the shortest time. The player can use different fruits, but care should be taken that they are not too heavy or too thin so that they do not break during cutting. The fruit slices can be set on different surfaces such as a desk, table, or floor and there are several levels of difficulty available for players to increase their chances of winning.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UTA2U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-smash-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40432,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14L1B","slug":"8-ball-pool-multiplayer","title":"8 Ball Pool Multiplayer","description":"8 Ball Pool has introduced a new level system to keep you entertained. With this new system, you'll always face a challenge and get access to more exclusive match locations, where you play against only the best Pool players. You can also compete in tournaments and win rewards that improve your ranking.      \n","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14L1B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/8-ball-pool-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"533A0","slug":"aster-supreme","title":"Aster Supreme","description":"Build traps and fight enemies using your boomerang witch you can draw the path of and other weapons and traps.\n\nYou play as Aster in a dungeon crawler zelda like game\n\nPress Q to open the Quick selection menu and change your weapons and traps on the fly\n\nPress space to jump to avoid obstecles and enwmy attacks\n\nLeft shift to roll.\n\nMouse left click for the main attack right click for the boomerang to attack the nearest enemy\n\nE to place traps\n\nThis Game contains:\n\n3 uniqe weapons melee sword a boomerang and a cannon\n\n4 unique traps to synergiese\n\nTotal of 10 unique enemies in addition to some platforming in a top down zelda like game.\n\n2 unique boss fightes.\n\nYour objective is to defeat leviathan the Demon God in his differant incornation","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/533A0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aster-supreme/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46EBO","slug":"balls-collect-bounce-build","title":"Balls Collect - Bounce & Build!","description":"Balls Collect is the first choice for casual puzzle games.\n\nYou just need to control the ball to double and double continuously. Feel the explosive growth of the ball!\n\nStart with 3 balls, use your wisdom, feel the super cool experience of increasing to thousands of balls.","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46EBO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-collect-bounce-and-build/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IP5SC","slug":"black-white-escape-cars","title":"Black & White Escape Cars","description":"Control two cars at the same time.\nClick to change the track car.\nRun away from the police and get the gas to keep the car always fueled.\nSee how many points you can score by taking as many gasolines as you can.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IP5SC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-and-white-escape-cars/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6U46Z","slug":"buzzy-bugs","title":"Buzzy Bugs","description":"Use your finger and flap your wings to fly be careful to try to avoid all dangerous trunks!\nHave Fun! Fly as long as you can without hitting the trunks and\nachieve high scores.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6U46Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buzzy-bugs/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A4T3E","slug":"cat-strapped","title":"Cat Strapped","description":"Cat Strapped is an off-the-wall word puzzler that will keep you coming back for more.      \nYou start the game with 8 lovable Cats strapped with C4!!! As you play the game you guess letters.      \nFor each letter, you guess wrong a poor little kitty will explode! With every correct puzzle, you will get 2 cats back.      \n      \nThe game is over when you run out of cats.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A4T3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-strapped/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HI71Z","slug":"dizzy-sushi","title":"Dizzy Sushi","description":"Dizzy Sushi a fun reflex game to match as many items as you can. this game is a mix of speed, memory, and skills!\nYou want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test in this game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HI71Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dizzy-sushi/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8EVLD","slug":"doodle-game","title":"Doodle Game","description":"On smartphone or i-Phone:\ndrag your finger left or right depending on where you want to go.\nOn pc:\ndrag your finger left or right depending on where you want to go or press right arrow and left arrow.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8EVLD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doodle-game-ver-2-00/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"109CS","slug":"esther-the-penguin-return-to-antartica","title":"Esther the Penguin - Return to Antartica","description":"Esther has gone on vacation and has to go home to Antarctica. She doesn't remember how to come back and you have to help her. \nYou have to tap on the wooden objects so that Esther falls on the dock and Josè, her friend, can get her on the boat. \nEsther hasn't learned to swim yet, if she falls in the water it's a problem. Beware of pitfalls and sharks.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/109CS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/esther-the-penguin-return-to-antarctica/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OCI4I","slug":"immune-system-command","title":"Immune System Command","description":"This is a simplified and modern take on a retro classic game!!!\n\nThe one where you are the immune system command o protect your body from an endless hail of creepy Virus!\n\nSimple one tap game play.\n\nYou can never win this game, only survive as long as possible, because in war, all is lost in the end!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OCI4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-objects-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L117L","slug":"kill-birds","title":"Kill Birds","description":"Tap the birds out of the sky in this fast paced action strategy game from Mapi games.\nTry to finish all round in less time you can! have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L117L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kill-birds/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7M718","slug":"match-2d","title":"Match 2D","description":"Get ready for a new, challenging and original matching pair game? You need to match 2D extra cute characters on the ground and pop them all! When you clear a level, you will find new match to pair.\nThis matching pairs cute match game is so easy that anyone can play it.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7M718/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L651E","slug":"mumble-jumble","title":"Mumble Jumble","description":"Your GOAL:   \nunscramble as many five-letter words as you can with out running out of time.   \nWith two game modality, you will be entertained for hours. In Endless mode, you get 20 seconds to unscramble each word.   \nIn Time mode, solve as many words as you can in 3 minutes.   \n   \nFeatures Bullets:   \n• Over 3.000 common 5-letter words   \n• 2 action-packed game modes   \n• Best score and word count tracker   \n• Next word indicator   \n• 3 word skips per game   \n• Awesome puzzle App for all family   \n• Amazing graphics effects   \n• Cool music sounds   \nHave Fun with this great word puzzle game!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L651E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mumble-jumble/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A77G4","slug":"percentage-game","title":"Percentage Game","description":"Whoever says that math is boring has clearly never played Percentage, a fun and challenging fraction-based game.\nA percentage is a fraction based number game, the objective is to select the floating bubble of a fraction which is equal to the percentage displayed above, for every correct answer you score points and collect awesome Christmas themed baubles and trinkets to make sure that you’ve got the best Christmas decorations but make sure you don’t forget about the timer, This game is a must-try for everyone who wants to make math a little more fun and understandable.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A77G4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/percentage-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4S81A","slug":"pop-balloons","title":"PoP Balloons","description":"PoP Balloons is a cool action game very easy and intuitive to play, but it will be hard to stop playing.\n\nPop with your finger the color balloons on the screen, came on don’t let them vanish away!\nRed give more points than the others; don't touch the Black one!\n\nEnjoy popping balloons the more you can!       \n\nProduct feature bullets:\n • Ideal for all Kids and Children\n • Cool cartoon graphics\n • Easy to play\n • Very cool funny sound effects\n • Local scoreboard to sign your records\n • Easy to start hard to stop","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4S81A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8TIL1","slug":"poppy-it-playtime","title":"Poppy it Playtime","description":"Complete all Poppy pop it toys to Escape From The Factory! Try to do that as faster as you can! If you ever know about Poppy scary character, it's Playtime for you to get start in this game.! enjoy it!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8TIL1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-it-playtime/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N6619","slug":"snail-run","title":"Snail Run","description":"The snail run game is an interactive way to get your blood sprinting through you. All it takes are two people, some space in which they can move around freely (the bigger the better), and this simple but fun activity! The person who starts off goes on their toes while holding onto one side of whatever object or surface will be used for balance like a pondside log; then behind them follows another player ready with hand spoons so both may share lightly tapping feet together as if dancing Lindy hop style without stepping too far forward nor backward - making sure only light taps adorn each step towards success until reaching finish line at center stage where victory awaits those able enough runners slow down enough before.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N6619/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snail-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U9TAG","slug":"squid-dentist-game","title":"Squid Dentist Game","description":"Take care of all the Squid patients in this great Dentist Office game!       \nNow let yourself be a great dentist and take care of your Squid\npatient.\nDon't be a crazy dentist!\n\nKey Features:\n- 6 Squid Character!\n- Great effects!\n- Totally awesome dentist tools!\n- All funny sound\n- Great graphics\n- It's a great Kids quite game ;)\nWhat are you waiting for?\n\nGet started playing Squid Dentist NOW!!!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U9TAG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-dentist-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"146AP","slug":"tap-ninja","title":"Tap Ninja","description":"Tap Ninja is a fun and addictive game to play on.\nWe all know about the reflexes have with ninja, so here you have to become one of them.\nSo tap repeatedly on the items which are falling and keep away from the dynamites and achieve high scores.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/146AP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21GM7","slug":"trick-or-treat-halloween-games","title":"Trick or Treat Halloween Games","description":"Trick or Treat Halloween is a cute puzzle game with all funny and scary Halloween items.\nHere is the season of Halloween where you see lots of similar items like pumpkins, hats. eyeballs, skeletons, spiders, and more scary stuff.\nHere in this game select any scary item and try to solve the jigsaw puzzle by matching all the pieces.\nComplete all the scary items and win the game.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21GM7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trick-or-treat-halloween-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T46UO","slug":"winter-house-quest","title":"Winter House Quest","description":"Very unique puzzle game.\nTry to solve how to get from this creepy house!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T46UO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/winter-house-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40431,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0DRBN","slug":"battalion-commander-1917","title":"Battalion Commander 1917","description":"TBD","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0DRBN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battalion-commander-1917/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69D53","slug":"bridge-race-stairs-run-build","title":"Bridge Race Stairs Run Build","description":"Pave the way by collecting bricks to see who is the fastest one. Don't let others steal your bridge! \n \nHave you ever wished to build a bridge? Try this collecting game! Enjoy a bridge-building race from rooftop to rooftop. Collect logs of your colour, choose a bridge, place them to build yours, and get to the finish line before others build the bridge and win the race!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69D53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A15T2","slug":"card-match","title":"Card Match","description":"Try this nice game of cards, you must find all pairs equally among all the cards using your memory, this game is designed for children, the sound effects are delightful and make you laughing all the children, the graphics are simple but very clean, beautiful and colorful! if he touches the animals that appear on the screen feel of funny lines that will make anyone laugh.\n\nThere are three different themes, animals, toys and objects.\n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Best memory exercise for your kids.\n• Graphics in high definition.\n• Sound effects likeable.\n• Fun music and sound fx.  \n• Colorful graphics.\n• Gameplay immediate.\n• Three different subjects.\n• Different backgrounds.   \n• Hours of fun for your kid.\n\nMatch HD is simple to play but hard to stop ...especially suitable for small children at play.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A15T2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/card-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G6H21","slug":"fly-ghost","title":"Fly Ghost","description":"Fly Ghost - It's a fun game in a simple but challenging way, a ghost slowly flies by the man dodging pipes and without touching the ground.\n\nGameplay:\n\nYou need to constantly control the frequency of clicks on the screen to adjust the flight height and landing speed of the bird, so that the bird can smoothly pass through the tube space on the right side of the screen. If the ghost accidentally cleans and touches the tube, you lose.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G6H21/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fly-ghost/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"45E5T","slug":"fruits-shooter-pop-master","title":"Fruits Shooter Pop Master","description":"Fruits Shooter Pop Master is a free online game. Shoot fruits and pop all the fruits in this fun puzzle game! \nIn this free online game, you are a fruit shooter. You must shoot all the fruits in order to win! The objective of the game is to pop as many fruits as possible in each level. There are five levels with different obstacles and challenges that you must overcome. Your goal is to pop all the fruits in each level before time runs out!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/45E5T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruits-shooter-pop-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3NKT4","slug":"kenny-the-cow","title":"Kenny the Cow","description":"Downhill skiing fun and mayhem in this great game!\nAvoid the obstacles, move up and down the hill, collect the stars, hit the ramp and perform tricks and stunts for more points\nALL WHILST SKIING AS A COW! Sounds crazy? It is!\n\nParallax scrolling at on an angle, watch trees and rocks whoosh past you as you whizz down the ski slopes; and just watch as Kenny our hero flays down the slopes!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3NKT4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kenny-the-cow/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2EAE9","slug":"maze-game-kids","title":"Maze Game Kids","description":"A fun maze game to exercise your mind. Try to go through the 15 mazes as fast as possible and compare the time with your friends.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2EAE9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maze-game-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0OT14","slug":"robot-ball","title":"Robot Ball","description":"robot ball is an html5 arcade game, touch the screen to control the player avoid the falling robot and get score from it ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0OT14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-chopter/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R0O66","slug":"rocket-fly-forward","title":"Rocket Fly Forward","description":"Control one Fly Rocket and try to collect the more you can!   \nEnjoy it!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R0O66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-fly-forward/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O34V3","slug":"shadoworld-adventure","title":"Shadoworld Adventure","description":"“Shadoworld Adventure” is a very fun platform / retro game! The character, a brave creature of the shadows, must cross the dark valley and defeat the enemies. Jump on enemies to eliminate them and watch out for the angry obstacles that fall on your head. Dodge the spikes to avoid losing the game! Find the key to open the portal at the end of each level. The game has 50 levels! Have a good time!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O34V3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shadoworld-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67P24","slug":"flappybird","title":"flappybird","description":"flappy bird!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67P24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappybird/embed?sid=1","plays":40430,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U0ONT","slug":"just-tap-or-not","title":"Just Tap (or not)?","description":"Un jeu simple où il suffit de taper non ? Eh bien, c'est à vous de répondre à cette question intrigante, essayez-le maintenant ! En effet attendez, avant de jouer, faites la charge de patience dont vous aurez besoin !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U0ONT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/just-tap-or-not/embed?sid=1","plays":40428,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40255","slug":"bread-pit-2","title":"Bread Pit 2","description":"If you liked the first episode, help Pit again in becoming the most crispy toast ever! Watch out for all traps and enjoy a nice asiatic design!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40255/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bread-pit-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40428,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91M1J","slug":"emoji-game","title":"Emoji Game","description":"Le jeu Emoji est un jeu stimulant où le joueur doit choisir 4 emojis et espérer toucher chaque emoji correspondant à la colonne, ce n'est pas une tâche facile, mais c'est possible, allons-y.\n\nChoisissez vos meilleurs emojis","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91M1J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emoji-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40428,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EHNA9","slug":"super-slashman","title":"Super Slashman","description":"super slashman is a html5 platformer game, evil robots attack the city it's time for action, explore 5 levels, slash enemies with cyber swords, earn coins in levels to score, get green energy balls for next levels ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EHNA9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-slashman/embed?sid=1","plays":40428,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TNE1B","slug":"domino-battle","title":"Domino Battle","description":"Les dominos sont de retour, en mieux. Vous pouvez choisir votre style de jeu préféré, que ce soit Piocher ou Bloquer. Le niveau de divertissement est le même !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TNE1B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/domino-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40425,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1T1U","slug":"buggy-battle-royale","title":"Buggy - Battle Royale","description":"Are you ready to win in the buggy battle royale game? If you want to be a winner, you must be the last person to fall off the cliff. you have to be first on the road to victory. Be the first and be the most survivor. grab the scores, be the winner   \n\nHow to Play?\nArrow Keys and Space Button / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1T1U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buggy-battle-royale/embed?sid=1","plays":40425,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LSU86","slug":"superstar-family-dress-up-game","title":"Superstar Family Dress Up Game","description":"$d","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LSU86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superstar-family-dress-up-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40422,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TA85H","slug":"ball-thief-vs-police","title":"Ball Thief vs Police","description":"Ball Thief vs Police is a 2D platformer where you play as thief and you have to collect bags of money while avoiding the police and spikes. You have only 5 lives to start with.       \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TA85H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-thief-vs-police/embed?sid=1","plays":40420,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RBO3","slug":"noob-vs-blue-monster","title":"Noob vs Blue Monster","description":"Noob, whom everyone finds funny and cute, is in trouble and is running away from a huge blue monster in this series.Noob trying to escape from the blue monster has to cross the cliffs or he is in big trouble. Hey you come on help noob and help him reach the statue portal at the end. help him get out of the place he got stuck and get out. Join the exciting adventure of noob and the blue monster.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RBO3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-blue-monster/embed?sid=1","plays":40419,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TC257","slug":"cute-cats-2048","title":"Cute Cats 2048","description":"\"Cute Cats 2048\" is a hypercasual game where you have to merge blocks of the same type to double your score whenever you join two identical tiles. Try to reach tile 2048 to get a lot of points and beat your records. A very fun game and at the same time, a great resource to stimulate our brain, improving our agility, memory and reasoning. Our ability to make decisions and solve puzzles can be greatly improved by playing games of this genre. Good fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TC257/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-cats-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8S2F1","slug":"cute-elements-fun-elementals","title":"Cute Elements - Fun Elementals","description":"Elemental characters with special powers have been caged, use the water element to free the rest of the team and combine their powers, beat the levels by getting keys and locks, unlock many funny costumes, win elemental cards, beat the missions and get trophies for your achievements.\nARE YOU READY?","category":"Course","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8S2F1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-elements-fun-elementals/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E00AD","slug":"forest-ranger-adventure","title":"Forest Ranger Adventure","description":"forest ranger adventure is a html5 platformer game, journey the level collect coin and get the diamond to the next level","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E00AD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/forest-ranger-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"39NBT","slug":"green-battle","title":"Green Battle","description":"Fight against time and hunger of Handit the frog,eat as many bees as you can by throwing your long tongue,avoid hornets and other small enemies.\n\nCommand :\nMove : Arrows\nShoot : Space\nor mouse-Mobile","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/39NBT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/green-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TE2CD","slug":"head-to-head-tic-tac-toe","title":"Head to Head Tic Tac Toe","description":"It's a Classic Tic Toc Tae Game!\n\nThe aim of the game is to get 3 in a row.    \n2 players take turns until someone gets 3 in a row.    \nIf all the spaces are used and no one wins that is called    \na Cat's game!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TE2CD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/head-to-head-tic-toc-tae/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EKO16","slug":"noob-vs-hacker-zombie","title":"Noob vs Hacker Zombie","description":"In the Noob and the Hacker series, the hacker gets sick and turns into a zombie, and Noob goes after him to kill him. noob escape hacker has sword in hand and he will kill noob. Noob runs away to avoid dying. The noob needs to reach the portal ahead of time or he may die. Oh beware, poisonous water is rising, you can never look back. You have to run all the time to not die.  \n\nHow to Play?\n\"WD\" to move & \"Arrow Keys\" to move            \nMobile Touch Control            \nDouble jump is active in the game.       ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EKO16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-hacker-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1WA6I","slug":"twin-space-ships","title":"Twin Space Ships","description":"Avoid all enemy items and collect the bonus in this great endless space arcade game!\nYou control two ships one Red and another one Blu, the mission is really simple:\nAvoid all obstacles and collect all bonus that you see in the screen!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1WA6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twin-space-ships/embed?sid=1","plays":40418,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OC636","slug":"circle-shooter","title":"Circle Shooter","description":"Tap the screen to shoot the white balls ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OC636/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circle-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"59N3A","slug":"flappy-wings","title":"Flappy Wings","description":"Flappy wings - You know what to do... Your mission is very simple: Tap the bird to fly as far as you can... Fly along the deadliest way and reach high scores. Help the cute little bird as far as you can.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/59N3A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-wings/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1L69I","slug":"girl-dress-maker-2","title":"Girl Dress Maker 2","description":"Girl Dress Maker 2 a fun dress-up game. Hello, girls here is the game to select the latest dresses and hairstyles.\nSelect from the wardrobe and make her look perfect.\nPlay a lot more games only with Mapi Games!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1L69I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/girl-dress-maker-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42OAT","slug":"para-shoot","title":"Para Shoot","description":"Save the soldiers as they fall from the sky by tapping them to open the parachutes but be careful if you touch them again they will close and it may be too late to save them.\nHave fun with great cool game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42OAT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/para-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8IR1T","slug":"pumpkin-story","title":"Pumpkin Story","description":"A Pumpkin Story is a fun adventure ride of the little pumpkin in this Halloween season. Here in this fun adventure game, the little pumpkin is moving around to collect the keys to unlock the portals for the exits. For that pumpkin needs to collect the key on the way, but we all know the hurdles there in the abandoned area, but some are for your convenience, use the blocks to climb up and collect the keys and reach the end-fire to complete the level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8IR1T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-story/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SWS4L","slug":"swampy-assault","title":"Swampy Assault","description":"Our swamp shack is under attack by crocodiles, turtles, you name it, they all want to attack it. Grab your shot gun and start shooting, there are loads of challenging levels Guns, Swaps and a Redneck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SWS4L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swampy-assault/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"48O81","slug":"tiny-owl","title":"Tiny Owl","description":"Escape! Avoid Bats and Mines in Tiny Owl! Tiny Owl takes the Endless runner (i guess endless flyer) genre! Help our friend \"Pinky\" the little Owl to get as high as he can, avoiding the obstacles such as rolling mines, spikes, bats on the way and collecting as many coins as possible. Don't hit any enemies or it's game over for Pinky! Challenge your friends scores on the local leader boards to see who comes out top in this addictive, challenging and entertaining arcade game.\nKey Features:\n- Play as a happy cute little Pinky Owl character!\n- Fantastic graphics with a great soundtrack !\n- Beat your friends' World scores in the leaderboard!\n- Fly as high as possible touching each side of the screen\n- It's extremely easy just one touch to play!\n- Your kids love it!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/48O81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-owl/embed?sid=1","plays":40416,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3AE71","slug":"endless-maze","title":"Endless Maze","description":"Ready to test your reaction? In this project you will have to think 2-3 steps ahead,\nas you only have the option to speed up, but not to stop. An interesting puzzle,\nmaze game that offers a unique gameplay, which was not in any other project. In\nthe game you will find:\n- Simple mechanics, a timekiller.\n- Unique gameplay\n- Good visuals\nStart passing obstacles and earning points! Good luck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3AE71/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/endless-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":40415,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17863","slug":"jeffer","title":"Jeffer","description":"jeffer, skill game, you have to jump over the spheres, if you hit them from below you lose","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17863/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jeffer/embed?sid=1","plays":40415,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7D592","slug":"julia-s-food-truck","title":"Julia's food truck","description":"Play as an adventurous, enterprenatural businesswoman Julia, who's running a small business on her own. \nHer goal is to prepare the most delicious burgers in the whole city. \nNews about the superb burgers travel fast and soon her little food truck is constantly visted by hungry customers. \nEach customer approaches the food truck and tells about his favourite burger. \nJulia has very little time to prepare the meal, but if she manages to do that quickly, customers are very generous. \nPlay the game and see how many burgers you would be able to cook!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7D592/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/food-truck/embed?sid=1","plays":40415,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CMM65","slug":"park-my-car","title":"Park My Car","description":"Draw a road with you finger and park the car safely.\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CMM65/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/park-my-car/embed?sid=1","plays":40411,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ASYLT","slug":"candy-star-jelly-saga","title":"Candy Star Jelly Saga","description":"Candy Star Jelly Saga makes everybody relaxing and comfortable, it was made carefully with beautiful graphics and abundant,interesting gameplay.\nCandy Star Jelly Saga includes 200 level wih difference challenge. \nThis game is accordant for every ages with easy way to play, you can play anywhere and anytime.","category":"Course","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ASYLT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-star-jelly-saga/embed?sid=1","plays":40407,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40381","slug":"castle-defense","title":"Castle Defense","description":"Un poème épique de l'archimagicien envers le mal cheminant. En tant que meilleur magicien du royaume tu a été rappelé de le protéger. C´est le temps de bien les mettre au profit. Vise, enchante et détruis!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40381/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/castle-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":40407,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y8OK3","slug":"adventure-joystick-winter","title":"Adventure Joystick Winter","description":"In the 2nd series of the world full of adventures of the cute joystick, it is snowing, I guess, winter is approaching. You must collect all the ores before winter comes. Collect all the ores and get the key and reach the door. Be careful, thorns and spinning wheels can hurt you.  \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile touch control ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y8OK3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventure-joystick-winter/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"80U7C","slug":"apples-lemons","title":"Apples & Lemons","description":"Apples & Lemons is a hyper casual puzzle game that is set in the fictional town of Lemons. You are a character who loves to play puzzles, and your focus is on completing tasks within the limited time frame. The game is built around a south-American take on the style of Apples and Lemons, where the focus is on the individualism of players’ tweets as they participate in a dialogue about the game.   \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/80U7C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/apples-and-lemons-hyper-casual-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JRLDC","slug":"coloring-objects-for-kids","title":"Coloring Objects for Kids","description":"Coloring Objects For Kids is a painting, drawing and coloring tool for kids!    \nPick your colors and start drawing and painting with your finger when done.     \nKids will enjoy painting using theirs creative ideas.     \nHave fun using this great kids paint app    \n    \nKey Features:     \n-Really simple!    \n-Really addictive!    \n-Really fun!    \n-Over 40 objects to color!    \n-it's a baby quite game!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JRLDC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coloring-objects-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6A15O","slug":"crazy-cow","title":"Crazy Cow","description":"Roll the Cow In the Hole! Press left or right on screen to get the cow into the hole!\nControl a Crazy Cow and try to collect all ice cream that you see on the screen!\nComplete all levels and enjoy this funny puzzle game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6A15O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-cow/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"441Z6","slug":"dizzy-donut","title":"Dizzy Donut","description":"It’s Dizzy Donut the hottest game on the charts at the moment! \nTap To Match The Crazy Donuts As Many As You Can! \n \nMemory Test: \nDizzy Donut Game new mix of speed, memory and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test it this game! \n \nKey Features: \n- Memory Test! \n- Super cute graphic! \n- Smooth Gameplay! \n- No Load Times! \n- 3 difficult levels! \n \nSo the question is: \nHow long could you follow these crazy Donuts with no errors?","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/441Z6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dizzy-donut/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55453","slug":"enemy","title":"Enemy","description":"Welcome to Enemy, challenge the virus, grab the coin and try your hand at the adventure, what are you waiting for? go play Enemy now and fun will be guaranteed","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55453/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anemy/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17A47","slug":"eutagora","title":"Eutagora","description":"Dodge the geometric figures and try not to fall off the circle, if you do this, is Game Over!\nCopyright: https://chifeletto-secco.itch.io/eutagora","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17A47/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eutagora/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7C7T","slug":"fruit-fetch","title":"Fruit Fetch","description":"What are you waiting for? Whether you're playing for some mindless fun and trying to relax and pass the time, or trying to improve your skills as a Fruit Fetch, this is the game for you. Enjoy the awesomeness and believe the hype of Fruit Fetch.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7C7T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-fetch/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E88Z7","slug":"fruit-frenzy","title":"Fruit Frenzy","description":"Help Wagoo Collect all of the Fruits of a certain kind.\nSimple yet addictive, collect all of the fruits requested at the time.\nBut hurry, you only have so long to match all the fruits required.\nKey Features:\n• Beautiful Graphics\n• Fast Paced Gameplay\n• Brain Teasing action\n• A new twist on the puzzle genre\n• Farm those fruits","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E88Z7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FK030","slug":"happy-farm-for-kids","title":"Happy Farm for Kids","description":"Designed especially for toddlers 1 to 5 years, this exciting and educational game will teach your kids the names of farm animals and their sounds.    \nThe pictures are big and colorful so it is easy for your kid's small fingers to touch it, but at the beginning, your assistance might be helpful for younger children.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FK030/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-farm-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0JKPB","slug":"jump-the-block","title":"Jump the Block","description":"Jump the Blocks is an endless jumping game that will both frustrate and entertain you.\nThis is an arcade-style game similar to other jumping games like the classic.\nJump on the obstacles and boost your reflexes to achieve high scores.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0JKPB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-the-block/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JPU17","slug":"jumpjump","title":"JumpJump","description":"Welcome to JumpJump, a simple game to play, overcome levels and challenge the final boss in a duel to the last goal, remember that if you are mobile, in the second level you just need to hold down on the screen to stop the character, if you are from pc there is no need. What are you waiting for, go play now and fun is guaranteed.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JPU17/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumpjump/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N65N3","slug":"kingdom-of-ninja-5","title":"Kingdom of Ninja 5","description":"In the 5 series of the kingdom of ninja game, survival awaits you in a dark dungeon covered with lava. Be careful monsters obstacles are everywhere. watch out for the sharp bladed wheels, they can injure you jump over the obstacles and reach the chest, complete the level.     \n\nHow to Play?\n\"Z\" Jump + \"Arrow key\" Move / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N65N3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-of-ninja-5/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84066","slug":"picpu-dog","title":"PicPu-Dog","description":"PicPu is a very attractive photo puzzle. Just like Jigsaw puzzle, it is the best kill time game.\n\nPicPu is a block puzzle, you need assemble the block to correct position.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84066/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/picpu-dog/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"505AS","slug":"play-with-santa-claus","title":"Play With Santa Claus","description":"Play With \"Santa Claus\" It's a cool action game, very easy and intuitive to play, fun for the entire family! it will be hard to stop playing.\n\nHit with your finger the balloons on the screen, came on don’t let them vanish away! and help Santa Claus to popping this Christmas balloons enjoy and popping balloons the more you can! feel and share the holiday spirit with this cool Christmas Game! C'mon...let's play!\n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• 1 Christmas and Winter Background.\n• Many Holiday Inspired Songs.\n• 4 Holiday Themed Sounds.\n• Very Cool Graphics effects.\n• Merry Fun for All Ages.\n• 3 Different Gameplay Modality.\n• 1 Bonus game inside.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/505AS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/play-with-santa-claus/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HM57L","slug":"pum-mole-whack-a-mole","title":"Pum Mole Whack a Mole","description":"This is a fun game for you , your friends and your family! Your objective is to hit all the popping monsters to get points the more you can! Do you like \"Whack A Mole\"? then you will love this game too!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HM57L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pum-mole-whack-a-mole/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U09UT","slug":"rule-out-the-dangerous-circle","title":"Rule out - The Dangerous Circle","description":"$e","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U09UT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rule-out-the-dangerous-circle/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NN369","slug":"run-fast-run","title":"Run Fast Run","description":"Run Fast Run! is a fun adventure game to play on. Here is our little hero who has been stuck in middle with a whole lot of traps, help him to dodge them. There are really fast-paced obstacles passing by, keep away from them and survive as long as you can. This game will boost your reflexes while the hardest objects moving on him.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NN369/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-fast-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"166R0","slug":"sky-diver","title":"Sky Diver","description":"Skydiver a fun sports game to play on. transiting from a high point in the atmosphere to the surface of Earth with the aid of gravity. Transiting from a high point in the atmosphere to the surface of Earth with the aid of gravity.\nCollect as many rings as you can and achieve high scores.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/166R0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-diver/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4G818","slug":"smash-bugs-x","title":"Smash Bugs X","description":"Smash those bugs with your finger in this awesome game! smash the ants, smash the bugs but don't touch the red Ant it's very dangerous! You have five lives to smash the more bugs you can and after sign your personal record.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4G818/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smash-bugs-x/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I77I6","slug":"windmill","title":"WindMill","description":"Objective of the game: Collect bags by color, green bag to green mill, red bag to red mill, blue bag to blue mill, yellow bag to yellow mill.Avoid collision of other colors with the mill.\nManagement\n\nControl of the game Button on the left-turn the mill to the left Button on the right-turn the mill to the right","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I77I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/windmill/embed?sid=1","plays":40405,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"641LF","slug":"balls-will-fall","title":"Balls will Fall","description":"Balls will fall!\nIts out of the question...\nBut can you dodge them? \nLet's find out!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/641LF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-will-fall/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DH8AA","slug":"black-and-white","title":"Black and White","description":"Black And White is an endless jumping game that will both frustrate and entertain you.\nThis is an arcade-style game similar to other jumping games like the classic.\nJump on the obstacles and boost your reflexes to achieve high scores.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DH8AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-and-white/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SFHU5","slug":"blue-fighting-friends","title":"Blue Fighting Friends","description":"Blue Fighting Friends tue les personnages rouges de l'arc-en-ciel","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SFHU5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blue-fighting-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C901L","slug":"cannon-balls","title":"Cannon Balls","description":"$f","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C901L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cannon-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"956VA","slug":"flappy-penguin","title":"Flappy Penguin","description":"Flappy Penguin is an online jumping arcade game. The objective of the game is to guide the penguin through a series of pipes, avoiding gaps and obstacles.    \nFlappy Penguin Online is an arcade game that will have you jumping for hours of fun that challenges players to help a little penguin flap its wings and fly through a series of obstacles.    \n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/956VA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6P8E6","slug":"flipper-3","title":"Flipper 3","description":"welcome to best Flipper, good play","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6P8E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flipper-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"865EA","slug":"hallowen-match","title":"Hallowen Match","description":"hallowen match is a puzzle match game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/865EA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hallowen-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16C4B","slug":"jake-black-cat-2","title":"Jake Black Cat 2","description":"Jake Black Cat 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as a black cat whose mission is to collect the bowls containing cat food while avoiding the enemy cats, flying robot cats, spikes, and saws and reach your cat house in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Jake Black Cat\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16C4B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jake-black-cat-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"90OK7","slug":"knockout-rps","title":"Knockout RPS","description":"To play this game you have to be quick witted and even quicker to the draw.\nRock Paper Scissors is a classic game that people of all ages enjoy,\nthats why this could be the right game for you and your family.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/90OK7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knockout-rps/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6N2S5","slug":"ninja-gems","title":"Ninja Gems","description":"pull the line horizontal or vertical make a match of three or more of the same color, eliminating those gems from the board and replacing them with new ones, which could potentially create further matches.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6N2S5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-gems/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6PS4U","slug":"physics-puzzle","title":"Physics Puzzle","description":"Réalisez ce défi intellectuel dans ce jeu de réflexion addictif.\nPhysics Puzzle est le meilleur des passe-temps car chaque casse-tête peut être résolu de manière créative.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6PS4U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/physics-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4TLTH","slug":"pull-the-thread-puzzle","title":"Pull the Thread - Puzzle","description":"Pull The Thread - Puzzle - this is a fun puzzle game. You need to stretch the thread between all the screws on the screen.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4TLTH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pull-the-thread-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NR1E","slug":"redland-water-is-life","title":"RedLand Water is life","description":"The reds are thirsty in redland. You must find the water immediately and bring the water back. Remember, as you turn on the water, the water level will rise and you can drown. find water and bring water. Throw them all into the air don't let them drown protect all your people catch all the red men. Collect purple cubes that are money for you if you wish!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NR1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redland-water-is-life/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"37762","slug":"run-rainbow-friends","title":"Run Rainbow Friends","description":"Run Rainbow est un jeu de course sans fin rapide à travers des niveaux difficiles.\nSauvez l'arc-en-ciel bleu des obstacles en courant, en sautant et en collectant des pièces.\nOn vous demande d'aider le monstre bleu à collecter toutes les pièces\nRainbow boy le monstre bleu est le joueur principal du jeu, mais les deux monstres seront ajoutés, comme les monstres verts et rouges.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/37762/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/orbit/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AS54C","slug":"secret-inca","title":"Secret Inca","description":"Secret Inca is a platform game .\nHelp Jack to esplore and find as many ancient INCA's Diamonds as possible \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AS54C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/secret-inca/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4AAT1","slug":"tanking-tank","title":"Tanking Tank","description":"Try to destroy your enemies in a hard battle! Good luck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4AAT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tanking-tank/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T11H4","slug":"the-dead-among-us","title":"The dead among us","description":"You're An Impostor.                  \n                  \nThe game shows one of the options for what could happen after sabotage on the ship. Through the explosion of the reactor, all the crew members were killed, but only you remained alive.                  \nBeing very hungry you are driven by the thirst to eat all the bodies of the crew members. Climb over the wreckage of the ship with your creepy and long tongue, but be careful, you can easily get hurt on the wreckage. Eat more and more bodies to accumulate more points, be the best traitor! The game will be updated and will not stand still, so you will not get bored with it. Become the top 1 of the world in this game!                  \n                  \n* This app is entertainment and does not claim copyright in any way. All rights to the product Among Us belong to the developer Innersloth.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T11H4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-dead-amon-us/embed?sid=1","plays":40400,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y28AA","slug":"fairy-falls","title":"Fairy Falls","description":"The Fairy Falls Online Jump Wall Game is a fun and challenging way to test your skills. Players must help the fairies jump over the wall by timing their jumps correctly. The game features beautiful graphics and sound, and is suitable for all ages. Fairy Falls is an online game that challenges players to jump over walls. The game is simple but addicting, and it's a great way to pass the time. The Fairy Falls online game is a wall-jumping game that is both challenging and fun. Players must use their timing and coordination to jump between walls and avoid obstacles. The game is perfect for players of all ages and skill levels.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y28AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-falls/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U6R5S","slug":"superhero-adventure","title":"Superhero Adventure","description":"Superhero Adventure Online Shooting Game is an online game that lets you play as a superhero. You can choose to play as a superhero or a villain, and you can use your powers to fight other players. The game features an extensive character customization system, allowing you to create the perfect superhero or villain for your playstyle. Superhero Adventure Online Shooting Game is a fast-paced and action-packed game that will keep you coming back for more.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6R5S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superhero-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S33A3","slug":"12-minibattles-two-players","title":"12 MiniBattles - Two Players","description":"$10","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S33A3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/12-minibattles-two-players/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T2AIA","slug":"animals-pairs-match-3","title":"Animals Pairs Match 3","description":"It's no secret that players love matching three or more objects together in order to complete a task. And now, they can do so with animals in an online game called Animals Pairs Match 3. This game is based on the popular matching games you may have played on mobile devices or computers, but with animals as the main focus.    \nThe object of the game is to match up two of the same animals and then move on to the next level. Levels get harder and faster as you go, and if you can't complete a level within a certain time limit, the game will end and you'll have to start over. The game is simple to play but hard to master, so be sure to try it out today!    \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T2AIA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animals-pairs-match-3-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B54B2","slug":"book-of-ra-slot-machine","title":"Book of Ra Slot Machine","description":"Book of Ra is a terribly classic, conservative slot that has become a template for many other slot machines. See for yourself: 5 game reels with three lines of symbols. Today, such mechanics are embedded in most of the modern slots. And there is nothing surprising in this: it is extremely simple and works perfectly.\nWhen 3-5 golden books fall out, the bonus game begins. It is no different from the usual one, with the only difference that the next 10 spins will be completely free. Thus, the player can significantly increase his capital without any risks. Well, in the event that 3-5 golden books fall out on the reels again during the bonus game, then 10 more are added to the remaining number of free spins! By the way, if you have 4 books at once, then your winnings will increase 20 times, and if 5, then 200!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B54B2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/book-of-ra/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GN82B","slug":"bouncing-bug","title":"Bouncing Bug","description":"Bouncing Bug is a classic avoid and collect game where you are a lonely and greedy fly that wants to get all the gold it can find... But avoid the bigger flies that are orbiting around! With the coins you collect, you can buy new skins. Make the best highscore and show the world who is the best fly out there.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GN82B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncing-bug/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5739O","slug":"bug-destroyer","title":"Bug Destroyer","description":"In this game you have to smash bugs! all bugs except for red ants.\nWhen you smash a bug that you are not supposed to, you lose the game.\nReady to play? Good luck!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5739O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bug-destroyer/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9HHTC","slug":"cartoon-clash","title":"Cartoon Clash","description":"Cartoon Clash features cool graphics and multiplayer battles across various cartoon maps, you must use different types of weapons to shoot all rival players on your way and try to get the highest score in order to win each round.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9HHTC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cartoon-clash/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1796C","slug":"cross-shot-ball","title":"Cross Shot Ball","description":"A simple and additive game to play with balls match","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1796C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cross-shot-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ASSIO","slug":"crush-the-ants","title":"Crush the Ants","description":"Crush the Ants!\nIn this very nice game you have to crush all the ants that emerge from the ground avoiding to make them escape from the screen! but be careful not to touch the red ones or the game will end immediately!\n\nTry to hold out as long as possible and score your personal best score.\n\nHave fun with this hilarious little game!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ASSIO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pesta-formica/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"161IS","slug":"fort-clash-survival","title":"Fort Clash Survival","description":"Fort Clash Survival features battle royale with bots in minecraft world, your mission is to search for weapons and loot on different maps and try to survive before the time runs out.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/161IS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fort-clash-survival/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IS9W2","slug":"fruit-snake","title":"Fruit Snake","description":"Fruit Snake is a casual game about snakes. Unlike traditional snake games, the game tests your intelligence and strategy. You need to manipulate the snake to choose the right route and get the flag, seemingly simple but hidden secrets. Puzzling levels and funny graphics will take you to a whole new brain-burning world!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IS9W2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swat-vs-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UGE16","slug":"huggy-wuggy-pixel-nights","title":"Huggy Wuggy Pixel Nights","description":"Huggy Wuggy Pixel Nights is a 3D horror game where you are lost in dark pixel town and your mission is to find all bunny toys in order to successfully survive each night and try to avoid scary huggy wuggy encounters.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UGE16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/huggy-wuggy-pixel-nights/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A6RER","slug":"let-s-fart-brandon","title":"Let's Fart Brandon","description":"Let's Fart Brandon is a free funny horror/comedy game featuring Mr Biden and his infamous farts.\n\nThe Story:\nMr. Biden falls asleep at a conference and has nightmares. In the world of his nightmare, his only weapon is fart.\n\nGame Features:\n    Funny top down actin horror/comedy gameplay\n    Easy to pick up and play\n    For fans of fun and comedy games\n    Suitable for both female and male players\n    Good graphic with stable performance on older PCs\n    Unique surreal nightmare world with sense of humor","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A6RER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/let-s-fart-brandon/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M361M","slug":"mmmr","title":"MMMR","description":"This math game is a learning tool to teach kids and teenagers to find mean, median, mode and range of sets.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M361M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mmmr/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6O6MX","slug":"maxoo","title":"Maxoo","description":"Maxoo is a 2D platformer where you need to collect silver keys while avoiding the ball enemies, flying robots, pins, and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6O6MX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maxoo/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51E7I","slug":"mini-steps","title":"Mini Steps","description":"Jump in Steps to reach the goal!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51E7I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-steps/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0O549","slug":"munnazzaro","title":"Munnazzaro","description":"A horror game set in a remote town","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0O549/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/munnazzaro/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N0IS","slug":"ninja-vs-zombies","title":"Ninja vs Zombies","description":"Zombies are invading in this Jumper/Shooter game and obviously the only thing that can stop the horde is a... NINJA! Double jump to each new level and throw ninja stars to kill the zombies. Don't get touched and watch out for spike beyond level 15!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N0IS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-vs-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0N616","slug":"no-problamas","title":"No Problamas","description":"Get ready for the fiesta! There are llamas flying everywhere - hit them for candies. Beware of the wolf though!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0N616/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/no-problama/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ILP16","slug":"pixel-pipes","title":"Pixel Pipes","description":"Pixel Pipes is a logic game in which you have to make the pipes connect taking water from one point to another. Just tap the pipes to rotate them. As you play you unlock more levels for a total of 60 levels!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ILP16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-pipes/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6M4TR","slug":"platformer-war-day","title":"Platformer War Day","description":"Platformer War Day\nPlayers who day pass 27 different places in each stage and have 30 bullets and 1 additional ammo in each stage and one additional life in each stage. In playing this game desktop mode with arrows for direction, Shift to jump and Ctrl to shoot to pause can use Esc and back again using ctrl or keys to shoot in this game the action category and platformer sub category with one player in each type is different as in the previous version. android provides touch buttons and for the PC version it uses the same keyboard as the html5 version. Have a nice play\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6M4TR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/platformer-war-day/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2NA1H","slug":"rise-up-hero","title":"Rise Up Hero","description":"Rise Up Hero is an online strategy based mobile game that consists of three parts: Heroes, Warriors and Armies. Invaders from other worlds come to invade the planet to obtain relics. The goal is defend the power core! Different warriors can be acquired. Link up with friends to defeat powerful bosses together!.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2NA1H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/iron-man-the-marvel-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IKS7P","slug":"space-pumpkin","title":"Space Pumpkin","description":"You're a Mr. Pumpkin and You're in to the deep space... so try to resist the more you can and try to sign you best record!\nEnjoy!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IKS7P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-pumpkin/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22ETE","slug":"the-cube","title":"The Cube","description":"Relaxed and pleasant elimination games","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22ETE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-mania-full/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WO163","slug":"towra","title":"Towra","description":"Towra is a 2D platformer where you have to collect the keys while avoiding the enemies, saws and spikes and reach the tower door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or\" Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WO163/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/towra/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9N7A1","slug":"wild-west-gun-game","title":"Wild West Gun Game","description":"Shoot as fast as you can to kill all incoming enemies and unlock new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9N7A1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-west-gun-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40399,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H3RA4","slug":"adventure-in-space","title":"Adventure in Space","description":"play this game, run away from enemy ships and resist as much as possible!!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H3RA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventure-in-the-space/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NP7A7","slug":"anime-girl-fashion-make-up","title":"Anime Girl Fashion Make Up","description":"Êtes-vous un fan de dessins animés? Voulez-vous être une fille d’anime mignon? Si vous le faites, vous pouvez manquer ce jeu de maquillage populaire! 🎉🎉🎉 Choisissez votre anime fille préférée, faire un spa facial pour elle. Puis appliquer son maquillage à la mode et lui habiller dans de belles tenues. Faites de votre fille la plus belle.\n\nCaractéristiques :\n💖Jolies filles d’anime pour vous de jouer comme\n💖Beaucoup de rouges à lèvres, eyeliners, fards et fards à paupières à la mode\n💖Divers styles d’habillage au choix\n💖Décorations luxueuses pour satisfaire le sens de la mode d’une fille","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NP7A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-girl-fashion-make-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GBG9G","slug":"ball-juggling","title":"Ball Juggling","description":"Ball Juggling is a  super fun game with the reflex booster.\nHere in this game, you have to help the players to juggle the soccer balls. Can you juggle one...two....100 balls?\nWatch as you play this smash hit and juggle up to and past 100 balls.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GBG9G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-juggling/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6OBS6","slug":"blow-out-bomb-blast-ninja","title":"Blow Out Bomb Blast Ninja","description":"$11","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6OBS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blow-out-bomb-blast-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WHOLA","slug":"choco-ball-draw-line-happy-girl","title":"Choco Ball-Draw Line & Happy Girl","description":"$12","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WHOLA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/choco-ball-draw-line-and-happy-girl/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RAAA7","slug":"christmas-matching-game","title":"Christmas Matching Game","description":"Christmas Matching Game is a fun and interactive game that will keep you and your family entertained during the holidays. Play the Christmas Matching Game online for free.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RAAA7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-matching-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N33VR","slug":"classic-space-invader","title":"Classic Space Invader","description":"defend your ship from space invasions\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N33VR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-space-invader/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TNESL","slug":"duo-with-friends-multiplayer-card-game","title":"DUO With Friends - Multiplayer Card Game","description":"DUO With Online Friends game is a challenging game with unlimited entertainment. DUO cards game is an advanced version of the UNO game with new tournaments, rules, gameplay modes, special cards and much more. It provides room for up to 8 players. So, you can enjoy with family and friends to double the fun. ","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TNESL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-with-online-friends-multiplayer-card-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5TKKE","slug":"falling-blocks-the-tetris-game","title":"Falling Blocks - the TETRIS game","description":"\"Falling Blocks – the TETRIS Game\" is a game strongly inspired by the classic TETRIS. The goal of the game is to drop down the blocks and complete as many horizontal lines as you can. A lot of fun, Play it right now!","category":"Sport","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5TKKE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-blocks-the-tetris-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"649IT","slug":"gas-station","title":"Gas Station","description":"Welcome to Gas Station, have fun refueling as many machines as possible and accumulating money that can be used to increase your earnings, at each end of the day you will also have a daily report of your budget so that you can manage your business in the best possible way, what are you waiting for? ? go play Gas Station now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/649IT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gas-station/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CG1S1","slug":"glacier-dash","title":"Glacier Dash","description":"GLACIER DASH is a fun game where you Swim, dash, and rush your narwhal buddy around the tumbling ice blocks and eat as many fish as you can! An epic Glacier! A fun game with epic possibilities! · One-touch control system! · Simple and addictive gameplay! Awesome! . The Best. Period. Glacier it up old school as you rush and dash ARCADE STYLE!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CG1S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glacier-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1U142","slug":"just-idle","title":"Just Idle","description":"Join millions of other players around the world and start your adventure fighting the hordes of monsters, defeating powerful bosses.\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Idle system\nIf you don’t have time to be online, don’t worry, the offline system will not leave you without rewards\n\n* Hero roles:\n- Warrior\n- Paladin\n- Wizard\n- Archer\n- Assassin\n\n* Boss fight\nEach stage will be ended with boss fight which will allow player to get more rewards\n\n* Inventory system\nAll equipments can be improved by upgrading its level or synthesising to higher quality. No equipments in shop, everything can be obtained from monsters and bosses.\n\n* Stats system\nYou can decide if your hero will be heavy and impenetrable or light and dodgy.\n\n* Roulette. Spin the wheel and test you luck!\n\n* Soul. Do you know that everything has a soul? Even your game character have it! Enhance it and evolve to get more bonus stats!\n\n* Pvp. Play duel matches against other players all over the world!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1U142/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/just-idle/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A0LPC","slug":"kids-flurry-educational-puzzle-game","title":"Kids Flurry Educational Puzzle Game","description":"Kids Flurry Puzzle is an educational game that challenges children to use their logical thinking skills. The pieces are colorful and engaging, with each shape representing something different than what it looks like - for example one square might be in blue while another has green writing on it!  \nThe goal of this puzzle isn't just about putting together the picture; rather kids must find all nine animals hidden among five sets around four levels by asking themselves questions such as \"Have I seen any birds?\", and then search until finding no other matching responses before answering them correctly so they can move onto next level where more challenging tasks await...  \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A0LPC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-flurry-educational-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E1EZ8","slug":"merge-master-puzzle","title":"Merge Master - Puzzle","description":"Merge Master: Puzzle is an addictive block and number puzzle game that is great for brain training!\n\nWelcome to an incredibly addictive puzzle game with an original plot of events!\n\nThere are no time limits or tasks in the game.\n\nThe graphics of the game are suitable for all ages, that game will be interesting to play for both children and adults!\n\n\nGame Features:\n⭐️ Availability of ready-made various themes.\n⭐️ A game for all ages.\n⭐️ Many auxiliary bonuses for passing the game\n⭐️ Night theme to relax your eyes and play comfortably before going to sleep.\n\n\nTrain, play and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E1EZ8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-master-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D9K6E","slug":"rocket-defender","title":"Rocket Defender","description":"Defend your Earth from a meteor storm in this classic arcade game. Use your cannon to destroy all falling meteors and play through endless levels and protect your houses. Never give up and hold on for as long as possible, and after then put your personal record.\nImmerse yourself in this fantastic 80's Missile Command style Arcade game.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D9K6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-defender/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5666","slug":"searching","title":"Searching","description":"Searching is a game where you are challenged to find all the images with the requested letter in 30 seconds. Have fun and see how far you can go.","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5666/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/searching/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"98I8S","slug":"twist","title":"TWIST","description":"Avoid enemies and take coins, making a ball rotate in TWIST, an hyper-casual game with a minimalistic graphic that will make you stick to your phone.\n\nClick on the right side or the left side of the screen to make the rotating ball change direction. Use this mechanic to avoid all the green capsules that are moving from left to right. Be careful of the malus stars that spawn on the path: they'll make you lose!\nTry to catch the coins that will appear on the path and increase your high-score!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/98I8S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twist/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NUN13","slug":"undead-walking","title":"Undead Walking","description":"Kill all the undead by your shotgun and try to hold on as more you can.\nStory: My name is Brando...I'm one of the survivors undead are everywhere...they killed my family my friends my dog...now I can just survive to kill all of them!\nKey features:\n- Fantastic 3D pre-render graphics.\n- Amazing animations.\n- Good music keep you entertaining.\n- Splat and gore effects.\n- Increase your weapons.\n- Local Scoreboard.\nSo grab your shotgun and destroy all the walker!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NUN13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/undead-walking/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W6127","slug":"wonder-vending-machine","title":"Wonder Vending Machine","description":"This simulation game is easy and very fun! choose among three vending machines: one with toys, one with sweet treats and one with food.\nEach item inside the vending machines has a price; you have a set of coins at your disposal to insert the right sum you can see on the display.\nIf you’ re right, the vending machine will release the item, if you’re wrong you’ll receive an error message. Collect all the items! then you can see them again.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W6127/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wonder-vending-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78O57","slug":"yolo-dogecoin","title":"Yolo Dogecoin","description":"This is a real stock exchange game)   \nWhere you can soar to millions or become bankrupt...  \nEverything is in your hands! Good luck!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78O57/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yolo-dogecoin/embed?sid=1","plays":40398,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LMZ61","slug":"boomer-zombie","title":"Boomer Zombie","description":"Boomer Zombie is a game that you can play with friends as well. The goal of the game is to make it through every level by eliminating zombies in order for the world to be saved from them. With its unique zombie-killing features, Boomer Zombie may just become your next favorite interactive way of spending time with friends and family!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LMZ61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boomer-zombie-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40396,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T3SAH","slug":"falling-blocks","title":"Falling Blocks","description":"\"Falling Blocks Mobile – the TETRIS Game\" is a game strongly inspired by the classic TETRIS. The goal of the game is to drop down the blocks and complete as many horizontal lines as you can. You can play it both from your smartphone or from your Browser. A lot of fun, Play it right now!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T3SAH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-blocks-mobile-the-tetris-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40396,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OSOOU","slug":"oomee-rush","title":"Oomee Rush","description":"The Oomee is on a roll, can you help him collect the fruit?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OSOOU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/oomee-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40395,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IE0O0","slug":"hyper-jumper-mr-jump-offline","title":"Hyper jumper Mr Jump offline","description":"Today there are a huge number of mobile games for every taste and color. Of all this variety, absolutely everyone can easily, and what is especially important for free to choose a really ideal option for themselves.\n\nSome games are made for fun, others just to pass the time. However, there is a special category that brin￼gs not only pleasure, but also real practical benefits. This genre belongs to Jimmy Ball Jump to color boxes.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IE0O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jimmy-ball-jump-the-colored-boxesjimmy-ball-jump-the-colored-boxes/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EE9E","slug":"meteorite-destroyer","title":"Meteorite Destroyer","description":"Meteorite Destroyer a space shooter game.\nAsteroid belters have manipulated the asteroid and meteor to reach earth and destroy the planet along with other spaceship enemies.\nShoot them all before they destroy you and survive as long as you can and achieve high scores.\nThis is the remake of a classic arcade 80's shooting space game.\nTry to avoid and destroy huge meteorites in space by using fire button!\nHow long can you survive?Do your best and try to get higher score!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EE9E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meteorite-destroyer/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3C8CK","slug":"noback","title":"Noback","description":"It's 2098, and you, a nuclear knight, are going to an underground castle to find your sister Mary, who disappeared a few days back.\n\nGame made for Ludum Dare 50 by AraTheDev using Godot Engine.\n\nAll the credits are at the end of the game.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3C8CK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noback/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"98NN4","slug":"silent-speeder","title":"Silent Speeder","description":"Prepare for a visit onto the silent film era, with these artfully crafted and simply engaging race avoider game! The main goal is to avoid the cars as you speed past them. You can tilt to stear, and hold down on the screen to do a speed boost.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/98NN4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/silent-speeder/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U1GSF","slug":"snow-rain-fall-jumping","title":"Snow Rain Fall Jumping","description":"$13","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U1GSF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snow-rain-io-fall-guys-jumping-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M955N","slug":"the-fallen-moai","title":"The Fallen Moai","description":"It's time to catch the moais! Click on them in order to increase your score, however you must be careful, the easter eggs are dangerous!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M955N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-fallen-moai/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K0I66","slug":"undead-walking-experiment","title":"Undead Walking Experiment","description":"Undead Walking is back! with another gameplay.\nNow you can use your skill to destroy the damned Undead! or you can upgrade your arsenal by buying different weapons in the items shop, but remember always, the weak point of Undead is the Head!!! Kill them all and win the game.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K0I66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/undead-walking-experiment/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E6L9T","slug":"vegetables-rush","title":"Vegetables Rush","description":"vegetables rush is a html5 match 3 game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E6L9T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vegetables-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40394,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E376E","slug":"hedgehog-throne","title":"Hedgehog Throne","description":"We all know what the hedgehog's enemy is, a smart and smiling fox ... but it's up to you to stun as many foxes as possible to protect your throne and the valley of hedgehogs. What are you waiting for, shoot your sting!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E376E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hedgehogthrone/embed?sid=1","plays":40391,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IIVI2","slug":"rotative-pipes-puzzle","title":"Rotative Pipes Puzzle","description":"Rotative Pipes Puzzle is a game with 70 levels. For each level, you must touch in tiles, rotating them. But the player must make all the tiles interconnected with each other.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IIVI2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotative-pipes-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40391,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22","slug":"ufo-run","title":"Ufo Run","description":"Dirigez votre Ovni et récoltez un maximum d'étoiles ! Cherchez des trésors cachés dans les mystérieux couloirs de ce vieux château pour booster votre score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ufo-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40391,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O555O","slug":"one-line","title":"One Line","description":"A brain-training puzzle in which you draw 1 line, that will sharpen your wits.\nIn this free-to-play puzzle game, you merely have to draw one line. It is deceptively simple, yet profoundly deep.\nPlay through the extensive stages, sharpening your wits as you have fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O555O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-line/embed?sid=1","plays":40391,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4GO4L","slug":"ghost-float","title":"Ghost Float","description":"An HTML5 arcade game where you have to tap to avoid obstacles, collect boosters, and score as high as you can.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4GO4L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ghost-float/embed?sid=1","plays":40388,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E283D","slug":"doomsday-shooter","title":"Doomsday Shooter","description":"Fight back against hordes of sinister creepers. Choose from 11 different weapons. \nDefend the pixel world from demons. Avoid shooters, kamikazes and golems, spirits and poisonous plants. \nDestroy pixel enemies with a bazooka or axe. Take them out with machine gun or sniper rifle bursts. Punish anything that moves and get to the prince of darkness!\n\nFeatures:\n- pixelated style\n- large arsenal of weapons\n- unique enemies\n- addictive gameplay\n- fast dynamics","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E283D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doomsday-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40388,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1UOH3","slug":"yummy-hotdog","title":"Yummy Hotdog","description":"Make your own yummy hotdog from the scratch. Get the materials and ingredients you needed. Start mixing them and getting your batter ready. Control everything, garnishing with sauce and add toppings to make ur hotdog even tastier. Finish your perfect hotdog and unlock all the achievements of the game!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1UOH3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-hotdog/embed?sid=1","plays":40388,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ENEO","slug":"meme-match-3-connect","title":"Meme Match 3 Connect","description":"Match 3 connect type of game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ENEO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meme-match-3-connect/embed?sid=1","plays":40388,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A9T4G","slug":"skeleton-knight","title":"Skeleton Knight","description":"Skeleton Knight is an innovative new action-adventure hack and slash online game that offers a unique gaming experience. Players take on the role of a skeleton warrior who must fight through hordes of demonic foes in order to save the world from destruction.    \n    \nSkeleton Knight is fast, furious, and fun, perfect for players who love action-packed games with plenty of villainous bloodletting. With its intuitive controls and fluid combat, Skeleton Knight is a must-have for fans of online gaming.    \n","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A9T4G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skeleton-knight-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40388,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TS033","slug":"santa-s-quest","title":"Santa's Quest","description":"Le Père Noël a eu un accident ! Il a perdu son chemin, ainsi que tous les cadeaux. Aidez-le à atteindre son but en faisant glisser les tuiles pavées pour former un chemin. Un jeu de casse-tête classique plus difficile qu'il n'y paraît ! Des tonnes de niveaux dans trois modes à maîtriser. Testez vos compétences et rejoignez le Père Noël dans son aventure ! Quand vous êtes coincé, utilisez un indice. Êtes-vous prêt à relever le défi ?\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TS033/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-s-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40387,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41SS8","slug":"coloring-dinosaurs-for-kids","title":"Coloring Dinosaurs for Kids","description":"Coloring Dinosaurs For Kids is a painting, drawing and coloring game for kids!\nHello my little friend, have fun with Dinosaurs in this fantastic Coloring Book App designed especially for you!\nIt will be fantastic to watch your baby coloring, interacting, having fun and improving his technique thanks to this fantastic musical and educational application.\nThe whole game is accompanied by 6 different fun and relaxing soundtracks.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41SS8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coloring-dinosaurs-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40386,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8U119","slug":"golf-hunting-3d","title":"Golf Hunting 3D","description":"Waves of ducks are flying over the golf course and we need you to take care of them… See if you can sink a few while you’re at it! Upgrade your gun while progressing through the stages. Unlock more powerful weapons as you increase your level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8U119/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/golf-hunting-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40386,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"95K67","slug":"sky-warrior","title":"Sky Warrior","description":"sky warrior is an html5 arcade game, enemy planes attack it's time for action ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/95K67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-warrior/embed?sid=1","plays":40385,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B6EOI","slug":"hidden-objects-superthief","title":"Hidden Objects: Superthief","description":"Dans une ville pleine de manoirs, de musées et d'ateliers, il y a des tonnes d'opportunités de voler des artefacts mystérieux. Pour Mme Smith, voleuse professionnelle, c’est l'endroit parfait. Aidez-la à trouver les objets que ses clients désirent ! Fouinez dans beaucoup de scènes différentes, accomplissez des missions secondaires et récupérez des équipements spéciaux. La disposition et la difficulté des scènes changent à chaque fois que vous jouez, et en fonction de votre niveau de maîtrise !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B6EOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-objects-superthief/embed?sid=1","plays":40384,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64M4D","slug":"moon-bridge","title":"Moon Bridge","description":"Go higher and higher! and make your best score!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64M4D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moon-bridge/embed?sid=1","plays":40383,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I16HT","slug":"shooting-range","title":"Shooting Range","description":"Le jeu \"champ de Tir\" est parfait pour les amateurs de jeux de tir à la première personne! Dans ce jeu de tir, vous devez, comme dans le tableau de bord, tirer sur les cibles en peu de temps, en marquant des points. Le plus de points, plus d'argent que vous pouvez dépenser pour de nouvelles armes et de nouveaux types de cibles. Chaque bannière a ses propres zones uniques-multiplicateurs de points. Dans le même temps, certaines cibles ont l'apparence de personnages familiers: Huggy Waggy, Steve de Minecraft, Stalker, etc. le Jeu est parfait pour la formation de sa précision et de précision, à la fois à partir de l'ordinateur et du téléphone sur Android!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I16HT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shooting-range/embed?sid=1","plays":40382,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NMI0I","slug":"stickman-fighting","title":"Stickman Fighting","description":"Lutte Stickman est venu! Il est temps de tuer les Stickman ennemis dans ce jeu en 3D! Choisissez l'un des nombreux personnages et descendants de bâton 3D bataille!\n \n\n- Graphiques 3D\n- La physique 3D réaliste\n- Beaucoup de personnages de Stikman 3D: normal, zombie, démon, cyber, par Kyle\n\n \n \nDevenir Stickman - champion! La bataille est venu!\n \nMusique:\nCzySzy:Paul ter-Voorde-vsZombies\nDiePflanze:Lutte boucle\nHanupo:Bug-Bot","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NMI0I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-fighting/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S0SJ6","slug":"bobby-s-bolts","title":"Bobby's Bolts","description":"Pick as many Bobby's bolts you can pick! Hey this will not be easy!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S0SJ6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/just-some-bosses/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1BP94","slug":"buba-jump","title":"Buba Jump","description":"hey bubba jump is an arcade, platformer game. consists in reaching the absolute maximum score, what are you waiting for, try it now!!!!!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1BP94/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buba-jumpe/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C51K1","slug":"candy-blocks","title":"Candy Blocks","description":"Chocolate Block is an exciting game for the whole family. Match 6 candies in a row and score points! Collected coins and a sweetie smiley will help you with this. Any figure from the candies presented at the bottom of the playing field can be rotated and changed by spending coins. You can replenish coins by clicking on the \"Plus\" button.\nHave a good time!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C51K1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chocolate-block/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E3YR2","slug":"escape-from-the-toys-factory","title":"Escape From the Toys Factory","description":"Complete all Poppy pop it toys to Escape From The Toys Factory! Try to do that as faster as you can! If you ever know about Poppy scary character, it's Playtime for you to get start in this game.! enjoy it!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E3YR2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-from-the-toys-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9AW63","slug":"faraway","title":"Faraway","description":"First of all\n\nTHIS GAME IS HARD\n\nVERY HARD\n\nBEST OF LUCK\n\nYou opened your eyes in a spaceship and found out that you are in an unfamiliar place. You tried to remember your arrival in this place but you can't remember clearly. Now you have chosen the only option you have left, Which is to escape from this so called planet Earth. Because your mind reminds you every time that you are very FARAWAY from your home.\n\nBesides a simple but good physics and side scroll system, this game has a beautiful but yet dark environment where you are going to tackle obstacle, take right time and chance to move in this world where there is a chance of fall in every moment you move forward. And at last, you need to be a very patient person and do no harm to your PC in the possession of anger to complete this game. We hope you will enjoy this small piece of entertainment by XG games.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9AW63/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/faraway/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"254JI","slug":"jelly-phil-2","title":"Jelly Phil 2","description":"Jelly Phil 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect pink jellies while avoiding the jelly enemies, saws and reach the exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.      \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Jelly Phil\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/254JI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jelly-phil-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"86EEE","slug":"lay-the-egg","title":"Lay the Egg","description":"Late one night a farmer makes a mysterious discovery, that his barn has a little stowaway living inside! What's more is that this little fellah lays....Golden Eggs! Help our little friend successfully lay his golden eggs safely int his nest. Combining a wonderful physics engine, extremely clever puzzles and beautiful graphics. Lay the Eggs is a must have game.\nLay the Eggs Features:\n• Combines realistic physics with simple, yet accurate, and precise touch control.\n• An incredible 3 worlds to conquer.\n• Use precise timing to avoid obstacles.\n• Collect three golden stars in each stage.\nSome are easy, some are a little on the harder side!\n• Avoid jagged spikes and fight the power of a magnetic pull!.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/86EEE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lay-the-egg/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I7I13","slug":"mini-springs","title":"Mini Springs","description":"Use Springs to reach the goal!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I7I13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-springs/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LL88S","slug":"rainbow-girls-halloween-salon","title":"Rainbow Girls Halloween Salon","description":"Welcome to the Princess Happy Halloween Party. Princess Anna and Elsa arrange a Halloween party at Arendelle. They invite their friends Jasmine and Moana to the party. Before the party started, they need to be in traditional halloween costumes. Join and help the girls to pick a perfect party costumes. Have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LL88S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-girls-halloween-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D26R4","slug":"roodo-2","title":"Roodo 2","description":"Roodo 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect the Golden keys while avoiding the yellow and green enemy robots, flying bots, spikes and ground saws and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.      \nThis is the second installment of the original Roodo game.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D26R4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roodo-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RDIPL","slug":"snake-and-ladders-multiplayer","title":"Snake and Ladders Multiplayer","description":"Snake and Ladders Multiplayer is a HTML5 Board Game. \nEnjoy this funny version of the classic Snake and Ladders Game. \n3 Game’s Mode: \n- Multiplayer mode \n- Play against the pc \n- Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RDIPL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snake-and-ladders-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TS9S","slug":"stickman-prison-counter-assault","title":"Stickman Prison Counter Assault","description":"Jouer en tant que Stickman prisonnier ou en tant que police / forces spéciales.\n\nLa grève dans la prison (émeute) dans la ville stickman a échappé à tout contrôle - chaque prisonnier a un gan et il faut arrêter de s’évader de prison! Heureusement, le commandement spécial de la police lance une contre-attaque et des incendies contre des terroristes.\n\n◘ Jouer en tant que prisonnier terroriste ou en tant que forces spéciales\nControl Contrôle facile Stickman de nombreuses armes à feu!\n◘ Beaucoup d'endroits pour le camping et les contre-attaques\n◘ Modèles 3D Stickman et prisons\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TS9S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-assault-prison-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13EAR","slug":"red-and-green-rainbow","title":"Red and Green Rainbow","description":"The most legendary of the red and green rainbow series will challenge you and your friend with more enemies and more features. Watch out for slime and bat! use the jump ramps. Remember take the key and make the invisible door visible. Only green can remove the laser.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13EAR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-green-rainbow/embed?sid=1","plays":40381,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ORRE7","slug":"popcorn-master","title":"Popcorn Master","description":"Burst popcorn and complete all the popcorn making levels! Pop the popcorn bursting and shoot the popcorns out of it.   \n   \nBest ASMR casual puzzle game to get you relaxed. Relax yourself with casual puzzle popcorn bursting game and pop your way to the top!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ORRE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popcorn-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40375,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4NI6P","slug":"plugin","title":"Plugin","description":"Plugin is an innovative puzzle game with levels tasking player to plug a number of appliance to a power source ","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4NI6P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/plugin/embed?sid=1","plays":40374,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6167Y","slug":"catch-the-fly","title":"Catch the Fly","description":"The fun game Catch the Fly is now on gamepix. Play the fun Classic game now ,and dont forget to Like.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6167Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-the-fly/embed?sid=1","plays":40374,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ATRS9","slug":"battleship-war-multiplayer","title":"Battleship War Multiplayer","description":"Battleship War is a HTML5 Multiplayer Game.\nHit all the ships of your enemy and lead your fleet to the victory!\nCollect points and buy special power-up!","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ATRS9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battleship-war-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40374,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12RA4","slug":"winter-adventures","title":"Winter Adventures","description":"Help a little guy to decorate his Christmas tree, collecting falling stars, for buy new toys, but be careful, there to easy be frozen in this cold winter evening.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12RA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/winter-adventures/embed?sid=1","plays":40372,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TV7OB","slug":"tora-boy-adventure","title":"Tora Boy Adventure","description":"tora boy adventure is a html5 platformer game, exciting adventure of a tiger boy, explore 10 levels and eat cake to get score, jump avoid obstacles and defeat enemies, get 5 keys to unlock levels ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TV7OB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tora-boy-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IL3M8","slug":"banana-joe-triple-jump","title":"Banana Joe Triple Jump","description":"Avoid the dangerous obstacles or your character will explode and the game will be over! Key Features: - Insanely simple and addictive game - Endless gameplay that never gets old - Beat your high scores How to play:\nPlaying Colorful Triple Jump is simple.\n1) Just tap the screen and make up to three jumps before touching the ground again.\n2) Avoid the dangerous obstacles or your character will explode and the game will be over! How far can you go? ;)","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IL3M8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banana-joe-triple-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2726C","slug":"cubic-cubic","title":"Cubic Cubic","description":"Welcome to Cubic Cubic, have fun between 5 different levels with different and increasingly difficult difficulties, will you be able to reach the bonus level and accumulate as many points as possible? What are you waiting for? go play Cubic Cubic now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2726C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cubic-cubic/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"27DSF","slug":"find-7-differences","title":"Find 7 Differences","description":"Can you find the difference between the two pictures? Observe the details in the picture, learn to be a detective, and download this free spot the difference puzzle games!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/27DSF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-7-differences/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"614IE","slug":"fireworks","title":"Fireworks!","description":"Link and pop all the colored spheres to load the firework and launch it to the sky! Make the higher score and share it with your friends!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/614IE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/firework/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8T5GT","slug":"get-the-word","title":"Get the Word!","description":"\"You have six attempts to find the hidden word.\n\nStart by guessing the first word.\n\nAfter each guess, the letters will change color to indicate whether they are in the mystery word. \"","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8T5GT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/get-the-word/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5205K","slug":"kly-kly","title":"Kly Kly","description":"Kly Kly is an arcade platform game in which you have to help a magical creature named Klu-Klu defeat 4 monsters that are located in each dimension. The game has 4 exciting worlds, each with 8 levels of varying difficulty and a BOSS. Your task is to defeat all the bosses!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5205K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kly-kly/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L6T7R","slug":"mister-lifter","title":"Mister Lifter","description":"Tap the Weight Lifter as fast as possible with your finger to lift the weights.\nTry to achieve the best time ever! it's a great casual game for everyone!\nHave fun with this cool casual sport game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L6T7R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mister-lifter/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"696GI","slug":"racing-project-kit","title":"Racing Project Kit","description":"Race Constructor est un jeu de course intéressant avec de nombreuses fonctionnalités:\n\n- Choisissez les modes de jeu.\n- Jouez ensemble en divisant l'écran.\n- Créez votre propre piste de course et jouez dessus.\n- Personnalisez la course.\n- Choisissez et personnalisez une voiture.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/696GI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/racing-project-kit/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U58V4","slug":"ungravity","title":"Ungravity","description":"A normal interstellar journey, suddenly became a nightmare for our fellow astronaut.\nThe Gravity-control system blew-up. Now the only hope for the astronaut is to go through all the spaceship modules and flee using an escape pod.\nWill he be able to save his life using only his jetpack…?\n\nWASD or Gamepad directional buttons = MOVE\nARROW KEYS or Gamepad ABXY Buttons = ACTION","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U58V4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ungraivty/embed?sid=1","plays":40371,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5KE5","slug":"car-chase-parking","title":"Car Chase Parking","description":"Car chase is a fun driving game where you have a mini super fast car and you have to run away from the cops    \n    \nCar Chase is a cool arcade racing game in which you try to survive as long as possible without crashing your car, in a police chase situation, parking location.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5KE5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-chase-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":40370,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83H96","slug":"monster-machine","title":"Monster Machine","description":"This is a game made in 7 days by LudowS as a developer and Shikimo as a game designer, using  the graphics from 0x72. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83H96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40367,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1L11","slug":"medieval-farms","title":"Medieval Farms","description":"Retro themed Pixel Farming game with casual gameplay and cute graphics. Grow many different crops, raise livestock, tend orchards, vineyards and more\nMobile Friendly on all devices","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1L11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/medieval-farms/embed?sid=1","plays":40367,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FOG01","slug":"frog-block","title":"Frog Block","description":"Frog Block is an online platformer game that is free to play. The objective of the game is to help the frog reach the end of the level by avoiding obstacles and enemies. There are many different levels to play, and each one gets more difficult as you progress.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FOG01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-block/embed?sid=1","plays":40366,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N0NT6","slug":"icedland-adventure-2","title":"Icedland Adventure 2","description":"icedland adventure 2 is a html5 platformer game, journey the beautiful iceland  collect treasure on every level, defeat enemy with snowball and hammer or you can use special attack SPIN","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N0NT6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/icedland-adventure-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40366,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15R76","slug":"space-stormtrooper","title":"Space Stormtrooper","description":"Space Stormtrooper is a game where it is easy for you to destroy the coronavirus infections and also to last as long as possible. Earn intergalactic coins and buy new ships. There are 30 types of ships available in the game.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15R76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballshooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40366,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GP2GK","slug":"super-monkey-juggling","title":"Super Monkey Juggling","description":"Super Monkey Juggling super fun game with the reflex booster.\nHere in this game, you have to help the monkeys to juggle the coconuts. Can you juggle one...two....100 coconuts? Watch as you play this smash hit and juggle up to and past 100 coconuts.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GP2GK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-monkey-juggling/embed?sid=1","plays":40366,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E97H","slug":"the-maze-2","title":"The Maze 2","description":"The seuquel of 'The Maze' is now here! Our main character has been locked up again, and this time it will be harder yet funnier.\n ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E97H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-maze-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40362,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FAO8P","slug":"flappy-footchinko","title":"Flappy FootChinko","description":"Flappy FootChinko is a highly addictive hyper casual soccer game. It has 2 game modes, in the story mode you can win 7 international tournaments. The endless mode will challenge your sync skills. Tap to impulse the ball, beat your rivals, dodge all obstacles and score epic goals.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FAO8P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-footchinko/embed?sid=1","plays":40360,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"614R6","slug":"desire-fps-online","title":"Desire - FPS online","description":"Dynamic multiplayer game with a first-person view! Unlock and upgrade fighters, complete tasks and compete with other players in tournaments!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/614R6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desire/embed?sid=1","plays":40359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9504T","slug":"link-four","title":"Link Four","description":"An HTML5 turn-based board game where you can tap to drop the colored disks. Get four single-colored disk in a row or diagonally to win","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9504T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/connect-four/embed?sid=1","plays":40359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"696E6","slug":"monster-maker-2000","title":"Monster Maker 2000","description":"Are You Ready to create the next Creepy Spooky Monster?\nStart here!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/696E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-maker/embed?sid=1","plays":40359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OOTDR","slug":"the-patriots-fight-and-freedom","title":"The Patriots Fight and Freedom","description":"About\n\nThe Patriots: Fight and Freedom is a free action / shooter game with a beautiful low poly graphic.\n\nStory\nThe game is about a young woman named Ashley who lives with her husband and child in a small town in the United States. One day, suddenly, explosions and an alarms sounded. Military vehicles move in the city. Television reports say a group has staged a coup against the US government, seized power and imprisoned the president. Ashley takes up arms and joins the resistance to save her country.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OOTDR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-patriots-fight-and-freedom/embed?sid=1","plays":40359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40426","slug":"dot-snap-battle","title":"Dot Snap Battle","description":"Tap, hold and shoot the dot into the box. Collect stars and unlock new dots. Play with or without your friends on the same device. Play more, Shoot more.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40426/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dot-snap-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40359,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NYCO0","slug":"city-traffic-control","title":"City Traffic Control","description":"$14","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NYCO0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-traffic-control/embed?sid=1","plays":40358,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5RNI6","slug":"smashy-racing","title":"Smashy Racing","description":"Drive HARD but don’t get SMASHED.Extreme gameplay mechanics and loads of fun!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5RNI6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smashy-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40357,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6183I","slug":"find-the-missing-letter","title":"Find the Missing Letter","description":"The game is really simple and fun for everyone! just follow the instructions in this order:\n\nHOW TO PLAY:\n1: TOUCH ONE OF THE THREE LETTERS IN THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE SCREEN.\n2: DRAG ONE OF LETTER OVER THE MISSING BOX AREA.\n3: DROP THE FINGER TO RELEASE THE LETTER IN TO THE MISSING AREA.\n4: IF THE LETTER IS RIGHT YOU WILL SEE A BONUS MESSAGE; OTHERWISE YOU WILL SEE AN ERROR MESSAGE.\n\nAnyway You can’t lose because it’s just a simple kids letter game; also when play you can learn the correct name of the objects and the alphabet letters.\n\nKey Features:\n- Over 60 objects\n- High Resolution Images.\n- Super cute graphics.\n- Amazing sound effects.\n- Really funmusic.\n- Kid's quite game.\n- Just one touch to play.\n- Really easy gameplay.\n\nEnjoy this game is really suitable for all kids and toddlers.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6183I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-missing-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":40355,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5IAA6","slug":"cerchi-vs-quadrati","title":"cerchi vs quadrati","description":"cerchi vs quadrati is a simple platforn","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5IAA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cerchi-vs-quadrati/embed?sid=1","plays":40353,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z7RE0","slug":"dop-puzzle-displace-one-part","title":"DOP Puzzle Displace One Part","description":"DOP Puzzle: Displace One Part is a DOP game that will help you have fun testing your IQ. The game is a DOP puzzle game where each level is a funny story.\n\nEnjoy the charming design in a bright cartoon style and charming animation.\n\nThe game is simple, however, there are several challenging puzzles among the puzzles. Test your brain and have fun!\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\n🧠 Pleasant brain training\n🔍 Solving puzzles by dragging objects\n🧩 More than 50 puzzles\n🤩 Fun and creative animation","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z7RE0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dop-puzzle-displace-one-part/embed?sid=1","plays":40346,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NT16F","slug":"laser-overload-reflection-time","title":"Laser OverLoad Reflection Time","description":"Hey you student, are you on a break right now?\n\nWhat do you think of download and play this game, just to take a moment from studying and energise?\n\nFast Energy Loop Cycle Classes you will have now!\n\nConnect the energy sources to the batteries to recharge them, relieve stress and relax in this puzzle game. You can do this by rotating the mirrors and reflecting the rays of electricity.\n\nIn Laser Overload: electric joy, a great puzzle game, you’ll be able to build this immersive and feeling-based experience so that every time you complete the puzzle game, the entire grid is electrified and connects so that you can also feel it until you start to relax.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NT16F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/laser-overload-reflection-time/embed?sid=1","plays":40346,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55M5L","slug":"littleyellowman","title":"Littleyellowman","description":"The super fun and funny little yellow guy is trying to escape from the purple guys and he has friends among the purple guys and he has to save them. He must save all the men, collect all the coins and achieve victory. purple poison is rising from underground be careful it can turn you into purple monsters too. You must not turn into a purple monster.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55M5L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/littleyellowman/embed?sid=1","plays":40346,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3O633","slug":"riyoo","title":"Riyoo","description":"Riyoo is a 2D little platformer where you play as a girl who have to collect flowers while avoiding the enemies, and spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3O633/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/riyoo/embed?sid=1","plays":40346,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3621C","slug":"spaceship-2023","title":"Spaceship 2023","description":"spaceship 2023 is game arcade ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3621C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaceship-2023/embed?sid=1","plays":40346,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A5AA8","slug":"christmas-memichan","title":"Christmas Memichan","description":"Christmas Memichan is a 2D Christmas themed platformer where you play as a Santa Cat called Memichan who have to collect all of the chocolate bars while avoiding the enemy demon cats, spikes. saws and reach your cat house door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A5AA8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-memichan/embed?sid=1","plays":40345,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O4P36","slug":"don-t-explode-the-ball","title":"Don't Explode the Ball","description":"In the game Don't Explode the Ball, you control the ball and must do everything possible not to touch the spikes and not explode. The upper and lower sides of the screen are completely covered with spikes, but spikes randomly appear on the side walls. You have to tap the ball, jump and guide the ball so that you hit the side walls without touching those spikes. Every time you touch the wall, you earn one point, and you have to keep doing it and earn more points. But keep in mind that as you progress, the game will become more difficult, and in addition to increasing the number of spikes, they also move to higher levels. Every few seconds a heart will appear on the screen, you will be able to catch it. These hearts are used in the store to unlock new skills. There are 5 different theme colors and 5 different balls to choose from.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O4P36/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/don-t-explode-the-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40345,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8VVN8","slug":"fruit-adventure","title":"Fruit Adventure","description":"“Fruit Adventure” is a very fun and colorful platform game! The player, a brave Strawberry, must go through the forest and defeat the enemies. The enemies are the sweets that if consumed in excess, can be very bad health! Jump over the sweets to eliminate them and watch out for the rabid chocolates. Dodge the spikes to avoid losing the game and restart the level! Find the key to open the portal at the end of each level. The graphics are very beautiful and captivating! Have a good time!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8VVN8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40345,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G541O","slug":"gloo-bot","title":"Gloo Bot","description":"Gloo Bot is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to play as a robot who have to collect all of the battery cells while avoiding the enemy robots, flying bots, spikes and reach your Robot House in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G541O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gloo-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40345,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60K1P","slug":"rotating-flappy-jack","title":"Rotating Flappy Jack","description":"In this great addictive funny game the Pumpkin must tap to flap and help the bird make it through the gaps, but you do it while in Orbit! Have Fun with this great addictive funny App!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60K1P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotating-flappy-jack/embed?sid=1","plays":40345,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0A0G7","slug":"anksunamun-the-queen-of-egypt-slot-machine","title":"Anksunamun the queen of Egypt Slot Machine","description":"Beautiful queen Anksunamun, Nefertiti daughter, will help you unravel the mystery of pharaoh's tomb. Are you ready for a thrilling adventure? Great treasures, severe gods, pharaohs and pyramids - enjoy the breathtaking world of Ancient Egypt! Video slot. 96.6. ... Gold Wild Symbol. Gold Wild Symbol substitutes all symbols, including Wild and Scatter. Takes part of a combination which starts free games. Free Spins feature with Sticky Wilds. Free games with additional Gold Wild symbols which transform into Sticky Wild during the time of a free game. 3 Extra Free Spins with guaranteed winnings. 3 middle reels of identical Gold Wild symbols promise big winnings for additional free games. Play for free. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0A0G7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anksunamun-the-queen-of-egypt/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5T5E","slug":"cubes-street","title":"Cubes Street","description":"Cubes Street is a simple arcade game, I'm a novice in game programming as you can see, but I hope to keep making games as I improve. Having said that, don't waste time and start playing!\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5T5E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cubes-street/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RR464","slug":"arrow-lite","title":"Arrow Lite","description":"arcade game classic","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RR464/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shooting-arrows/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41673","slug":"box-shooter","title":"Box Shooter","description":"Box Shooter - c'est un excellent jeu de tir d'arcade. Vous devez tirer sur des murs et des blocs numériques. Essayez d'obtenir le meilleur score et menez le classement mondial. Essayez de ne pas entrer en collision avec les blocs.\n\nCaractéristiques:\n- gameplay addictif\n- système de points\n- 6 skins différents\n- table des dirigeants","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41673/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/test1/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4I563","slug":"child-skate","title":"Child Skate","description":"Child Skate Become the best skateboarder! Take your skateboard and collect coins. hey kid be careful you can turn into mommy long and huggy at night. You have to be cautious at night. be careful, if you're worth touching the thorns, you may be eliminated. 25 different sections and challenging sections from each other.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4I563/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/child-skate/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9LH11","slug":"cute-jelly-rush","title":"Cute Jelly Rush","description":"cute jelly rush is a match3 html5 game, slide and match jelly according to shape and color and get score","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9LH11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-jelly-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60II0","slug":"kobadoo-arithmetic","title":"Kobadoo Arithmetic","description":"Kobadoo Arithmetic is a game that trains your brain by memorizing and adding up numbers.\n\nWhen you play Kobadoo Arithmetic you are actively using your working memory. Several scientific studies suggest that training of working memory has beneficial effects and can increase your cognitive functions.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60II0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kobadoo-arithmetic/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2666W","slug":"ricochet-arrow","title":"Ricochet Arrow","description":"Pick up your bow! Kill dangerous skeleton in 50 different levels. Aim before launching your arrow. You have unlimited arrows, but be smart and don’t shoot yourself an arrow. Let's start destroying the skeletons! There is also the option to challenge your friends in local PvP mode","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2666W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ricochet-arrow/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C60MI","slug":"tile-master-classic-match","title":"Tile Master - Classic Match","description":"Tile Master - Classic Match：Relaxing and enjoyable zen game. It is a free simple and exciting puzzle game. The game is suitable for entertainment, intense study and relaxation after working hours.\n\nTap any block to drag and drop it onto the board. Three identical blocks will be removed from the board. Clear all blocks as soon as possible. When all blocks are cleared, you have completed the level! When there are 7 blocks on the board, you lose!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C60MI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tile-master-classic-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40344,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2D7D4","slug":"bobb-s-world","title":"Bobb's World","description":"Bobb is very hungry and he wants all the food in the universe to feed himself!\nHelp him to go from planet to planet, and eat all the food in each stage! \nAvoid hazards and jump on the enemies to defeat them, and collect all the food!\nFace 30 different levels, find all the food and eat it all!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2D7D4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bobb-s-world/embed?sid=1","plays":40343,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N85AN","slug":"yarn-untangled","title":"Yarn Untangled","description":"Help the kitty untangle the yarn balls.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N85AN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yarn-untangled/embed?sid=1","plays":40343,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40314","slug":"jewel-bubbles-3","title":"Jewel Bubbles 3","description":"Jewel Bubbles 3 back again in dazzling colours! The classic turn-based match 3 with lots of challenging levels to beat! Various goals in different game modes and useful bubble combinations to use tactically. Warning! Includes a bonus pack of levels for the best!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40314/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-bubbles-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40342,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NC0SC","slug":"slots-collection-3in1","title":"Slots Collection 3in1","description":"Des machines à sous cooles, rutilantes et attrayantes, comme dans un vrai casino. Joue pour t'amuser, sans risque de perdre de l'argent. Plus de 20 lignes de gains uniques, un guide détaillé de toutes les combinaisons, chance et prix quotidiens, une roue de la fortune, des mini-jeux dans les machines à sous... Même les joueurs les plus expérimentés seront sous le charme. Tente ta chance et joue à une machine à sous classique, visite une ferme lucrative ou va voir des zombies... Tout ceci t'attend dans une collection incroyable de machines à sous.","category":"Action","tags":["board","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NC0SC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slots-collection-3in1/embed?sid=1","plays":40342,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U6663","slug":"jungle-treasure","title":"Jungle Treasure","description":"Jungle Treasure a side scrolling auto runner game, tab to jump and avoid the obstacle. Collect coin and jewel go to finish, pause the game with the space bar or the button. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6663/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jungle-treasure/embed?sid=1","plays":40342,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55914","slug":"temple-quest","title":"Temple Quest","description":"Vous n'auriez pas dû voler cet artefact ! Maintenant vous devez courir pour sauver votre vie dans le labyrinthe infini d'un temple en ruines ! Récupérez des idoles en or, des pièces anciennes et des power-ups. Maîtrisez divers obstacles, améliorez les power-ups et remplissez les objectifs pour augmenter votre multiplicateur de score. Essayez différentes tenues avec des compétences spéciales pour aller plus loin. Jusqu'où pourrez-vous aller ?\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55914/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/temple-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40341,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57EIO","slug":"dinogen-online","title":"Dinogen Online","description":"Dinogen Online is a fast-paced 2D multiplayer top-down shooter with plenty of weapons, game modes, and maps. Play as a human or dinosaur in objective-based game modes. Unlock new weapons, dinosaurs, equipment, items, and more by earning XP in game!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57EIO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dinogen-online/embed?sid=1","plays":40340,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"93494","slug":"1up-gunman","title":"1UP Gunman","description":"You're the last soldier and you need to defense the base with your super machine gun! enjoy it.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/93494/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/1up-gunman/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"95OOI","slug":"among-tito","title":"Among Tito","description":"Among Tito is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect all of the adamant stones while avoiding the enemy robots, flying bots, bullets, ground saws, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/95OOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/among-tito/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TET6M","slug":"animal-match-master","title":"Animal Match Master","description":"Animal Match Master is a puzzle game that you can play online. The objective of the game is to link three animals of the same kind. You can play the game by yourself or with other people. Animal Match Master is a fun and challenging online game that tests your memory and matching skills. There are three difficulty levels to choose from, and you can even compete against other players online.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TET6M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animal-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6565U","slug":"break-your-brain","title":"Break Your Brain","description":"Un puzzle insolite pour adultes et enfants! Le jeu intellectuel est déjà là!\n\nArrêtez de perdre du temps, entraînez votre cerveau, développez votre esprit. La pensée et la connaissance sont de votre côté!\n\nDans ce jeu, on vous proposera des énigmes logiques, dans chacune desquelles vous devrez choisir la bonne solution pour ouvrir le niveau suivant et aller plus loin. Au fur et à mesure que le niveau augmente, les tâches deviendront plus compliquées et il faudra plus de temps pour les résoudre.\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu:\n\n⭐ Chaque niveau est un puzzle unique\n⭐ Mécanismes de jeu incroyables\n⭐ Commentez chaque niveau!\n⭐ Développement du cerveau dès les premiers niveaux\n⭐ Puzzles pour adultes et enfants","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6565U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/break-your-brain/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ET2F5","slug":"crime-detective-spot-differences","title":"Crime Detective - Spot Differences","description":"$15","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ET2F5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crime-detective-spot-differencs/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"273SO","slug":"deca-vs-rooko","title":"Deca vs Rooko","description":"Deca vs Rooko is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect all of the hotdogs(food) while avoiding all of the enemies, spikes and giant blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/273SO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deca-vs-rooko/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9RT9R","slug":"fort-craft","title":"Fort Craft","description":"Fort Craft features multiplayer battles within minecraft world, use different types of weapons to shoot all enemy players and try to get the highest amount of frags by the end of the round in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9RT9R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fort-craft/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K7AG5","slug":"gakkul","title":"Gakkul","description":"Gakkul is a 2D platformer where you play as a boy who have to collect mangoes from the gardens while avoiding the garden owners, and traps like spikes, and pins and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K7AG5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gakkul/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"665OS","slug":"goals","title":"Goals","description":"Welcome to Goals, have fun in two different difficulty levels facing the CPU and scoring as many points as possible, what are you waiting for? Go play Goals now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/665OS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goals/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H3TG1","slug":"huggy-shortcut-run","title":"Huggy Shortcut Run","description":"Race with opponents and collect as much boards as you can along the track! As you build shortcuts, you’re going to start running faster. But the more you stack boards the more you slow down.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H3TG1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/huggy-shortcut-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MNKK5","slug":"jack-pumpkin","title":"Jack Pumpkin","description":"In this game you control Jack the Pumpkin so moving them around a world that revolves around you.\nAs you move around the landscape your character clings o the ground via gravity – use it your advantage to move from one platform to the next; try to collect all pearls and completa all levels!\nThis is a fun exploring adventure games enjoy it!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MNKK5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jack-pumpkin/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5OPTO","slug":"john-the-pirate","title":"John the Pirate","description":"John is a fearless pirate and has ventured to seek treasure in uncharted lands inhabited by creatures from another world! With only his pistol he decided to face them alone – even though he was not aiming well!. John's Adventures is a platform game with 9 challenging levels and a boss. Collect coins to earn extra lives.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5OPTO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/john-the-pirate/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2E6IL","slug":"line-side-ball","title":"Line Side Ball","description":"play line side ball with matching ball colors as same as seqaures.\nsimple game and easy to play","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2E6IL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-side-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CR6AY","slug":"mad-city-matrix","title":"Mad City Matrix","description":"Mad City Matrix features intense combat with agents in big open world city, use powerful punches and lots of weapons to defeat all incoming agents and try to survive each level before the time runs out.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CR6AY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mad-city-matrix/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61C82","slug":"mincraft-ballance-challenge","title":"Mincraft Ballance Challenge","description":"Minecraft Ballance Challenge is super fun action game free to play on PC and mobile. The aim of the game is to stay on the platform and hold ballance until the time runs out. Avoid obstacles and have fun.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61C82/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minecraft-ballance-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"99MO6","slug":"mr-babo","title":"Mr Babo","description":"Mr Babo is a 2D simple platform game where you need to collect golden keys in order unlock the Golden door while avoiding enemies, spikes, and saws. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or arrow keys for the player movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/99MO6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-babo/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EORN1","slug":"orange","title":"Orange","description":"Orange is a unique and interesting game to play on.\nYou have to collect all the plankton organisms deposited by Orange creatures funny! Be careful not to touch the oranges or you'll lose a life! The main goal of the game is to collect as much plankton as possible and mark your personal record in the rankings.\nIn the meantime you will be released with the bonuses with the red balls collect them and mark the bonuses.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EORN1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/orange/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"036B6","slug":"owl-block","title":"Owl Block","description":"Owl Block is a free online platform game that challenges you to use your agility and speed to overcome obstacles and reach the finish line. With over 100 levels, there is plenty of game play to keep you engaged.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/036B6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/owl-block/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I9L39","slug":"pitfall","title":"Pitfall","description":"Imagine a world where everything is invisible. You have to use your special ability to see it. Watch out for unseen dangers in space. use your special power! so you can see obstacles and enemies. hey alien please be careful you must survive!\n\nHow to Play?\n*WASD + Space for movement and jumping\n*Mobile Touch Control \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I9L39/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pitfall/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TR86T","slug":"rabbitii-2","title":"Rabbitii 2","description":"Rabbitii 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the carrots while avoiding the enemy rabbits, flying rabbit bots, spikes and reach the pink flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \nThis is the second installment of the original Rabbitii game.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TR86T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rabbitii-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"V11EL","slug":"rescue-love","title":"Rescue Love","description":"Tirez les épingles dans le bon ordre et rassemblez vos amis.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/V11EL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-love/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69I88","slug":"slips","title":"Slips","description":"Welcome to the slide game, you will have to dig under the cubes to hit the white target within a few seconds","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69I88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slips/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PEBR0","slug":"starlight-driver","title":"Starlight Driver","description":"There are yellow rings that a spaceship must collect to save its world. Collect all the yellow rings and save your world. Everything is in your hands, pilot. Fulfill your duty as a pilot.\n\nHow to Play?\nUse the arrow keys to move.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PEBR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mpostor-boxer/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67U56","slug":"touba","title":"Touba","description":"Touba is a 2D platformer where you play as a yellow bird and you have to collect the bowls of grains while avoiding enemy birds, spikes and reach the bird nest which leads you to the next level. There are 8 levels with increased difficulty.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67U56/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/touba/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OST2I","slug":"twin-opposite","title":"Twin Opposite","description":"move each one of the twin frog moves in the opposite direction try to get the highest score and run from lava","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OST2I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twin-opposite/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PO045","slug":"multi-player-pong-2-players","title":"Multi-player Pong - 2 players","description":"Challenge your friends to a game of pong,\nthe first to reach 3 points wins!\n\nThe player one to move press \"w\" , \"s\" and player 2 press \"o\", \"l\"","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PO045/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/multi-player-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I5Q5O","slug":"rotating-squid","title":"Rotating Squid","description":"Rotating Squid Game is a unique platform puzzle game where you rotate the world to guide Player N°456 to his lost stars.\nThis is a great puzzle game with 40 challenge levels, push your logical brain abilities to the limit!\nProduct feature bullets:\n• 40 different levels\n• Very Fun for children\n• Brain training for whole family\n• Cute graphics\n• Precise game physics\n• Great sounds\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5Q5O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotating-squid/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7234D","slug":"swing-dice","title":"Swing Dice","description":"swing dice is a html5 arcade game, tap and hold to make dice swing and avoid the obstacle","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7234D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swing-dice/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NT651","slug":"turn-light-on","title":"Turn Light On","description":"urn Light On is a reflex addictive game where you have to turn on the lights; be quick while turning on the lights.\nOnce the timer slows down the lights will turn off again.\nTurn on all the lights before the lights turn off.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NT651/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/turn-light-on/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T3OH","slug":"color-pumpkin-match","title":"Color Pumpkin Match","description":"Skyscraper is an online game that challenges you to fly through an endless cityscape. The game is simple but addictive, and it's perfect for anyone who loves spending time in the virtual world.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T3OH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-pumpkin-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LB848","slug":"mathtest22","title":"MathTest22","description":"Une application simple pour améliorer vos compétences en calcul.\nUn jeu pour améliorer vos compétences en calcul. Devinez le résultat et obtenez le meilleur score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LB848/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magicball22/embed?sid=1","plays":40339,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DML7A","slug":"ball-popping-games","title":"Ball Popping Games","description":"$16","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DML7A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shot-arcade-ball-popping-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11716","slug":"ball-puzzle","title":"Ball Puzzle","description":"Si vous voulez exercer votre cerveau et augmenter votre capacité de réflexion, alors essayez ce jeu de puzzle simple mais addictif. C'est un classique, mais avec une touche moderne et stimulante. \n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11716/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"138H9","slug":"hero-adventure","title":"Hero Adventure","description":"A Hero Adventure Shooter is an action shooting game. It's an interesting game. The main objective of this game is to eliminate the enemies by shooting them. You are going to experience a whole new level of shooting fun with this game. All ages will enjoy playing this game as it is great for everyone.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/138H9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hero-adventure-shooter-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60RLZ","slug":"little-cute-summer-fairies-puzzle","title":"Little Cute Summer Fairies Puzzle","description":"C'est l'heure des puzzles! Il suffit de regarder ces belles et jolies fées. Ils sont si différents, mais tous charmants à leur manière. Essayez de collecter toutes les énigmes dans les plus brefs délais; établir des records et rivaliser avec vos amis. Collectionnez toutes les photos de ces merveilleuses fées et amusez-vous!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60RLZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-cute-summer-fairies-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96NMO","slug":"match-monster","title":"Match Monster","description":"Match Monster is a Free Online Match 3 Puzzle Game! Match 3 or more monsters to make them disappear, disappear but be careful not to let them reach the top! Match Monster is a fun and addicting match 3, bubble shooter, and shooter puzzle game. Play now for free! Match Monster is the best place to find flash games to play online. We have a great collection of puzzle games, bubble shooter games, matching games, board games, and many more. Play now!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96NMO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-monster/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GSMR8","slug":"monsters-merge","title":"Monsters Merge","description":"There was an ordinary farmer, but on an unfortunate day, monsters attacked his farm and ruined the entire harvest. But he did not lose heart, he caught them, creating his own farm of monsters. Selling tickets for the opportunity to see each monster, he set himself the goal of becoming a successful farmer again.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GSMR8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monsters-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3O4T8","slug":"neon-shot","title":"Neon Shot","description":"“Neon Shot” is a very fun casual game in NEON Style that will test your skills and reasoning. With a “Drag and Drop” system you can pull the elastic to make the ball bounce and knock down the targets. Try to finish each level with as few balls as possible to get more points. You can pop boxes of TNT explosives to break more than one target at the same time and save balls. The designs are beautiful and colorful.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3O4T8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-shot/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6E97N","slug":"penguin-runner","title":"Penguin Runner","description":"In Penguin Runner you control a little penguin who's running to collect his Dinner Fish!\nWatch out for the obstacles in his path though and beware of the polar bears! With simple controls, just tap the left or right side of the screen to move and collect as many fish as you can!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6E97N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"V75E3","slug":"save-the-egg","title":"Save the Egg","description":"Save the Egg online is an entertaining action game where you have to save a chicken egg that got hit by a truck. Jump through various obstacles in its way and take it as far as possible! Collect the coins and golden eggs along the path and invest those earned capital into upgrades to your truck, egg, or even better - both! Play Free Games at the best festival in town, Save the Egg Online Free game and have fun with our free games. Are you still looking for the best free online games to play? ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/V75E3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-egg/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H7NS1","slug":"that-s-my-brain","title":"That's My Brain","description":"That's My Brain is a vertical scrolling Arcade Game where there is a football player who discovers during the match that his rivals are not humans, but brain-eating zombies! The aim is to cover as much ground as possible avoiding the hungry enemies and collecting brains that you will find on the field to unlock new aspects of the character. Let the race begin!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H7NS1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/that-s-my-brain/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2W615","slug":"walter","title":"Walter","description":"Welcome to Walter, have fun in this game in 5 levels of increasing difficulty by changing weapons and facing all the various enemies and the various pitfalls, what are you waiting for? Go play Walter now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2W615/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/walter/embed?sid=1","plays":40338,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15K13","slug":"tricky-test","title":"Tricky Test","description":"Une énigme lumineuse et colorée avec laquelle vous ne risquez pas de vous ennuyer.\nDes graphiques et des animations sublimes qui seront un vrai régal pour vos yeux.\n\nLa musique, les bruitages et les voix des personnages ont été créés par un compositeur professionnel.\n\nToutes les tâches du jeu sont en lien avec l'histoire ; pour les réussir, il va vous falloir faire preuve de créativité. Cela va vraiment développer votre capacité de réflexion !\n\nSauvez des extraterrestres, comptez des abeilles, occupez-vous d'un chien et bien plus...\nSecouez, penchez, tournez votre téléphone pour résoudre les problèmes.\n\nLe jeu propose un mode « Tirelire ». C'est la façon la plus surprenante d'obtenir des pièces bonus.\nVous n'avez jamais vu ça avant.\n\nVivez tout plein d'émotions inoubliables et développez votre intelligence !\nTestez ce jeu maintenant, c'est totalement gratuit !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15K13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tricky-test/embed?sid=1","plays":40336,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40111","slug":"klondike-solitaire","title":"Klondike Solitaire","description":"Retrouvez le célèbre \"klondike Solitaire\" dans cette version HTML5 fidèle à l'original!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/klondike-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":40336,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B209H","slug":"bop-the-blox","title":"Bop the Blox","description":"If you love matching games, and fun strategy games, this one is for you!   Help Professor Bop keep track of that pesky Blox by Bopping them!\nThis game requires a fast mind and quick reflexes, destroy as many bops as you can before the timer runs out.\nThis game requires a fast mind and quick reflexes!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B209H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bop-the-blox/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6464R","slug":"mr-jone","title":"Mr Jone","description":"Mr Jone is a 2D platformer where you need to collect all of the blue gems while avoiding enemies and spikes and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and is moderately difficult.\n\nControls:\nUse WASD or arrow keys for player's movement.  \nUse \"W\" or \"Up arrow key\" twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6464R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-jone/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I272P","slug":"pinkii","title":"Pinkii","description":"Pinkii is a 2D Simple platformer where you need to avoid enemy monsters and spikes and reach the pink flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and difficulty increases as you proceed.  \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I272P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pinkii/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12ASB","slug":"push-ball","title":"Push Ball","description":"Push ball is physics based puzzle game.\nRotate the screen to get the ball to the exit.\nDon't touch the spike and don't fall down.\nTest your skills with 15 unique levels.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12ASB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/push-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A741N","slug":"run-away","title":"Run Away","description":"run away using the arrows, while they shoot you from a central tower","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A741N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-away/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OOECC","slug":"soccer-squid-game","title":"Soccer Squid Game","description":"Squid Soccer Game a fun great soccer game! Stop an onslaught of incoming soccer balls; this free kicks challenge puts you in control of a star Squid Goalkeeper.\nThe objective is to save every shot on goal; You can dive in any direction at any height; stop the last goal to enter the bonus round!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OOECC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-squid-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L3LGU","slug":"sunny-golf","title":"Sunny Golf","description":"Sunny Golf! A simple 2D golf game with 30 main levels. Explore this wonderful cartoon world, unlock the special levels and collect every star to complete the game! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L3LGU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sunny-golf/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G3YDM","slug":"sweet-matching","title":"Sweet Matching","description":"Play Ladybug Sweet Matching Game is a match-3 type game. Swap to match 3 or more of the same candy pieces together! you can use Bomb, Swap and Color picker item to make it more fun to play. After completing a level, you will get a bonus coin that you can use to buy game item in game shop.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G3YDM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/play-ladybug-sweet-matching-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8E51I","slug":"the-infinity-stones-slot-machine","title":"The Infinity Stones Slot Machine","description":"A slot game in which you can win virtual game currency.Place your bets and win! Before you start, place a bet and then launch the slot.\nGame Control: AUTO-button to automatically start the game.\nSTART-the button for manually starting the game.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8E51I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-infinity-stones/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"122R9","slug":"vector-venom","title":"Vector Venom","description":"A retro styled vector  game. vector, who has superpowers, can fly from wall to wall by throwing nets on the walls, completing the game by passing the sections from the wall. Be careful, there are many obstacles. Help venom pass the levels.  \n\nHow to Play?\nUse the arrow keys to move around.  \nPress «Z» to jump.  \nPress «X» to use the hookshot.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/122R9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vector/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA1EN","slug":"zombie-land","title":"Zombie Land","description":"Monster Live Online Free Game. Survive the undead with friends in Monster Live, available on the Web! Level up your character by customizing your combat abilities via skill points earned after killing endless hordes of the living dead.     \nHello, friend! Have you played Monster Live yet ? It's actually an online survival game with a modern take on the genre - you can enter solo or in a group, and every new level gives you three skill points that you can invest in your strengths to become even more awesome!     \nYou know online live games? Survive the undead with us. It's an online game with a cool take on the genre - you can enter solo or with your friends and every level gives you skill points that you can use to become more awesome!     \n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA1EN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-land/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7L2AO","slug":"halloween-hidden-object","title":"Halloween Hidden Object","description":"Welcome to Hallowen hidden, have fun finding the hidden objects in the various difficulty levels, what are you waiting for ???? Go play Halowen hidden now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7L2AO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hallowen-hidden/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7Y7I7","slug":"nitro-rally-evolution","title":"Nitro Rally Evolution","description":"Nitro Rally Evolution is a fun classic 2D arcade racing game similar with the classic racing games of the 80's.\nPlay 20 different circuits to race in a car that runs automatically;\nunlock two or more powerful cards that are hidden and discover other features while playing.\nUse the turbo when you need an extra speed boost and set the best lap time.\nThe game shows colorful and detailed graphics and a nice sound effects you will enjoy.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7Y7I7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nitro-rally-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YR66R","slug":"archery-hero-pro","title":"Archery Hero Pro","description":"Archery Hero is the brand new best archery game available on the web.\nPerfect physics, great 3d graphics and professional experience.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YR66R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archery-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3630A","slug":"catch-dots","title":"Catch Dots","description":"Click to move the dots in the other direction. Catch the dots of the same color falling","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3630A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-dots/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KP721","slug":"enderstick-skymap","title":"EnderStick Skymap","description":"enderstickman has to survive in the white forest full of fears. He must be very careful to survive and collect all the emeralds. Follow the path and reach the portal while collecting emeralds. Remember, not the fastest, but the strongest reaches the portal. Don't be in a hurry, watch out for the monsters.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KP721/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/enderstick-skymap/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0OB66","slug":"jelly-bro","title":"Jelly Bro","description":"Are you on the adventure of a sweet green sweet jelly bro you have to help her in this adventure she is a jelly brodur bro and make her reach the crown! Don't touch the thorns, you'll die if you're worth it. Cross the thorny roads and you've got to the finish.   \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0OB66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jelly-bro/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UE35R","slug":"shadow-adventure","title":"Shadow Adventure","description":"Take on the ultimate challenge of skill and reflexes in Shadow Adventure. In the realm of the dead, shadows have begun to collect untold power for a mysterious evil force! Dash through a barrage of moving obstacles and use your wits to get over veritable pits of death! Do you enjoy platform games where you will be tasked with jumping on boxes and avoiding obstacles? If so, why not play a game that gives you the chance of becoming an adventurer who is not only capable of making his way through obstacles but also has something to balance or defend against! Come join Shadow Adventure Online Games and other players as you challenge your mind and exercise your body in this epic Game.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UE35R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shadow-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OEZMR","slug":"zombie-runner","title":"Zombie Runner","description":"Zombie Runner is a free online game in which you can kill zombies. Play the best Zombie Run game online. Run as far as you can, avoid the zombies and collect coins and gems.    \nZombie Runner Online Game - Run, hide and survive! Zombie Runner is a fast-paced, action-packed, 2D Top Down zombie shooter game.    \n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OEZMR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40335,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76E2E","slug":"alien-slime","title":"Alien Slime","description":"He needs to have the diamond sword to save the world of slime, the green alien. Become a green alien and complete the level and get the sword. Take the sword and pass all the levels.   \n\nHow to Play?\nArrow keys & Mobile touch control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76E2E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-slime/embed?sid=1","plays":40334,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8333T","slug":"war-bullet","title":"War Bullet","description":"A simple game where you have to shoot enemies that come from the right or left.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8333T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/war-bullet/embed?sid=1","plays":40334,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16NL6","slug":"colors-separation","title":"Colors Separation","description":"This is a relaxing game. Various levels to play freely, all unlocked! Drag the blocks to move them in a corresponding slot by color (red, blue, green, yellow, orange). No time. No pression!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16NL6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colors-separation/embed?sid=1","plays":40333,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LM3G0","slug":"my-little-golf","title":"My Little Golf","description":"Simple and entertaining golf game where the objective is not to run out of ball hits before reaching the hole.\nControl the ball with the mouse/touch by tapping in the direction you want to throw it. The further you move away from the ball when dragging your finger/mouse, the more force it will take.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LM3G0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-little-golf/embed?sid=1","plays":40333,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44A90","slug":"bingo-royal","title":"Bingo Royal","description":"Vous voulez tester votre chance et vos compétences ? Le nouveau jeu classique de bingo offre de beaux graphismes et de gros gains. Choisissez votre difficulté et le nombre de cartes souhaité. Marquez les bons numéros et attendez le bon moment pour crier Bingo. Commencez votre aventure de bingo gratuite n'importe quand et n'importe où ! Le bingo n'a jamais été aussi bon !\n","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44A90/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bingo-royal/embed?sid=1","plays":40331,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40116","slug":"pocahontas-slots","title":"Pocahontas Slots","description":"Tu vas pouvoir jouer aux machines à sous en compagnie de Pocahontas! Dans l'univers des indiens, tu vas pouvoir faire tourner les rouleaux autant de fois que tu le souhaites pour gagner un maximum de sous. Pour cela, tu dois aligner les mêmes symboles sur la ligne du milieu. Alors lance toi!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40116/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocahontas-slots/embed?sid=1","plays":40331,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D0E46","slug":"wild-west-zombie-clash","title":"Wild West Zombie Clash","description":"Wild West Zombie Clash offers intense zombie shooting in western environment, you are a gunslinger and your mission is to use different modern weapons and grenades to shoot all incoming zombie hordes and try to survive each round to unlock new guns.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D0E46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-west-zombie-clash/embed?sid=1","plays":40330,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LL8EC","slug":"animal-cells","title":"Animal Cells","description":"Faites exploser tous les animaux en les touchant ou en les retirant du plateau. Ils ne peuvent exploser que s'ils ont une de la même couleur à proximité.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LL8EC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animal-cells/embed?sid=1","plays":40329,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4LPL6","slug":"block-pile","title":"Block Pile","description":"block pile is an html5 puzzle game, stack blocks of different colors, don't stack the same color or the player will die and you will repeat the game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4LPL6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-piles/embed?sid=1","plays":40326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0F7B3","slug":"butterfly","title":"Butterfly","description":"welcome to butterfly, have fun among the colored butterflies to accumulate points and not die, what are you waiting for? Go play Butterflt now and the fun will be guaranteed","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0F7B3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/butterfly/embed?sid=1","plays":40326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E72E7","slug":"doggy-run","title":"Doggy Run","description":"dog runner is a html5 endless run game, run and jump over obstacles and get snacks to get a high score ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E72E7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dog-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0E1OT","slug":"noobcraft-house-escape","title":"Noobcraft House Escape","description":"You have to help that noob that everyone loves to escape from the house. Help and escape from the house. Noob wants to be a man and take his golden sword and escape from the house and can't break the door. but when he finds that he needs to find the golden key and coin in the house, the secret portal inside the house will be revealed as soon as he gets the coins in the chest. the portal emerges and you are sent to the next world.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0E1OT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noobcraft-house-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":40326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44O6A","slug":"hand-doctor","title":"Hand Doctor","description":"Hey do you want to become a hand doctor? Wearing stethoscope and looking professional?\n\nThen this hand doctor game is a perfect design for you.\n\nYou are going to have an ultimate fun yet a learning experience.\n\nFeatures:\n- Easy click and drag to play\n- Six different characters\n- Friendly content\n- Cool BG music and HD graphics\n- Apply plaster on stitches\n- Use x-ray to fix the broken bone\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44O6A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hand-doctor/embed?sid=1","plays":40326,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OCL65","slug":"cannon-ball-io","title":"Cannon Ball IO","description":"Choose your weapons and try to beat you opponent!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OCL65/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cannon-ball-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40323,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SV7TI","slug":"russian-taz-driving","title":"Russian Taz Driving","description":"Select different russian cars and drive them across the district.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SV7TI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-taz-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":40322,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"86677","slug":"2d-infinite-lap-runner","title":"2D Infinite Lap Runner","description":"Infinite Runner Kit comprend une solution complète pour générer des Terrans aléatoires, des obstacles et des ramassages. Il propose un package prêt à l'emploi et vous pouvez facilement apprendre à créer votre propre jeu de course sans fin.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/86677/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinite-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1D85D","slug":"3dmarble","title":"3DMarble","description":"Welcome to the 3d ticket game, play for fun, hit the first ball and after making a carom you get all the points","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1D85D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3dmarlbe/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"616TM","slug":"battalion-commander-2","title":"Battalion Commander 2","description":"La Patrie a besoin de vous... encore ! Une activité étrange est détectée dans le Nord alors prenez vos armes, roquettes et grenades et sécurisez le territoire. A propos de visage! MARS!\nLibérez les compagnons d'armes retenus captifs sur le territoire ennemi et ils vous rejoindront dans la mission. Collectez de l'or et de l'XP à chaque course et accomplissez des missions pour acheter de précieuses améliorations et débloquer des avantages !","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/616TM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battalion-commander-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HECE6","slug":"chess-master-3d","title":"Chess Master 3D","description":"Feel a new level of chess games. Realistic 3D graphics and gameplay will make you plunge into the immortal battle between the dark side and the light. Use logic and smart strategies to challenge your friends or AI bots and become a true Chess Master! Increase your gaming experience to reach the level of Garry Kasparov and Magnus Carlsen.\n\n- High-quality graphics\n- Customize convenient camera settings\n- Options for 3D and 2D boards\n- Play against friends or AI\n- Step back function\n- Different AI difficulty levels","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HECE6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chess-master-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HHETS","slug":"christmas-deno-bot-2","title":"Christmas Deno Bot 2","description":"Christmas Deno Bot 2 is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as Deno Bot who have to collect the fuel containers while avoiding the enemy bots, flying enemy bots and their bullets, saws, giant blades, and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Christmas Deno Bot\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HHETS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-deno-bot-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7LS02","slug":"clash-of-law","title":"Clash of Law","description":"Ready to solve endless puzzles which are challenging your short-term memory, if you do not know how to deal with it this will be a very good opportunity to learn how to remember big amount of characters and numbers. Moreover, tired of the talent of your own? This can get even more fun the reason is it has a slot machine for you to try your luck, if you get a \"!!!\" then go into trouble but should feel lucky because of you still have a \"Restart\" button with you there for you to try it all again.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7LS02/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clashoflaw/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RR5DE","slug":"crazy-egg-catch","title":"Crazy Egg Catch","description":"Welcome to Crazy Egg Catch Endless. In this game, you have to transport the egg into the correct conveyor belt. If you waste the egg. The chicken will have angry with you and note the egg color to change the portal color. play and have fun.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RR5DE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scary-halloween-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0G1YR","slug":"crazy-gravity","title":"Crazy Gravity","description":"Crazy Gravity is a challenging Platform / Puzzle game about a little Astronaut lost in space, where your main objective is to energize your rocket and go home.\n\nYou will face the challenges of crazy gravity, leaving the gameplay with a greater difficulty.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0G1YR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-gravity/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BR717","slug":"cyber-ball","title":"Cyber Ball","description":"Cyber Ball is a simple running game where you avoid obstacles for as long as possible.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BR717/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cyber-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UL34B","slug":"desert-block-puzzle","title":"Desert Block Puzzle","description":"Desert Block Puzzle is an online game that challenges you to put together blocks in a specific order. This game is free to play, and it's a great way to spend some time when you're looking for a mental challenge. Looking for a fun and challenging online puzzle game? Look no further than Desert Block Puzzle! This free game will keep you entertained for hours as you try to fit the right blocks together to complete the puzzle. With multiple levels of difficulty, there is something for everyone. So what are you waiting for? Start playing Desert Block Puzzle today! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UL34B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desert-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ND3U1","slug":"flying-duck","title":"Flying Duck","description":"Flying Duck, touch to just and avoid the black enemies to get failed.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ND3U1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-duck/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16X76","slug":"maxoo-2","title":"Maxoo 2","description":"Maxoo 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect silver keys while avoiding the enemy balls, flying creatures, pins, and lasers and reach the exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.       \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Maxoo\" game with new enemies and traps.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16X76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maxoo-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1YNN","slug":"mini-golf-funny-2","title":"Mini Golf Funny 2","description":"Are you up for a super game of golf? You need to get the golf ball into the hole. Throw the ball into the hole, pass the level. Pass 11 different levels and finish the game. very challenging wheels and thorns are waiting for you. \n\nHow to Play?\nDrag and Drop / Mouse Left Clicker \nPause \"P\" \nRestart \"R\"","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1YNN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-golf-funny-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"661OU","slug":"printable-coloring-pages-for-adults-flowers","title":"Printable Coloring Pages For Adults Flowers","description":"$17","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/661OU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/printable-coloring-pages-for-adults-flowers/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YTAR0","slug":"russian-grand-city-auto","title":"Russian Grand City Auto","description":"Russian Grand City Auto is a GTA-like third-person action game set in a Russian city of the wild 90s. Play as a chav, steal cars, explore the city and enjoy all the picturesque views that this game has for you.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YTAR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-grand-city-auto/embed?sid=1","plays":40321,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EP7H","slug":"apasheqz","title":"Apasheqz","description":"jump jump jump","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EP7H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/apasheqz/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18S8Z","slug":"green-bit-escape","title":"Green Bit Escape","description":"The gameplay is really basic and simple:       \n- Avoid the Red Squares, and avoid the Red lines.       \n- Stay alive as long as possible.       \nSo help Green Bit to stay alive as long as possible!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18S8Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-heroes/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"624H2","slug":"slash-ninja","title":"Slash Ninja","description":"Slash Ninja is a fun and addictive game to play on. We all know about the reflexes have with ninja, so here you have to become one of them.\n    \nSo tap repeatedly on the items which are falling and keep away from the dynamites and achieve high scores.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/624H2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slash-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YDDCH","slug":"alice-and-the-lost-candy","title":"Alice and the Lost Candy","description":"a short , cute looking challenging platform","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YDDCH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alice-and-the-lost-candy/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T666R","slug":"books-tower","title":"Books Tower","description":"Books Tower! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T666R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/books-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E2CLH","slug":"mannequin-head-jumping-challenge","title":"Mannequin Head - Jumping Challenge","description":"Le Mannequin Head - Jumping Challenge Game est un nouveau défi vraiment excitant!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E2CLH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mannequin-head-jumping-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40320,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06T46","slug":"starship","title":"Starship","description":"🔵About the game:\nBuy the coolest skin and drive your starship through space avoiding planets and getting coins and upgrades!\nYou will find magnets and shields. You will need the magnets to attract coins from afar while the shields will make you invulnerable for 10 seconds. You have 3 lives available, when you run out of lives the game will end and you will have to start over but... Every time you lose a life another one will appear but it will be up to you to recover it!\n\n🎮Controls:\nYou can move your ship by clicking and holding using the mouse or the touch-screen! You can pause with the appropriate button or with the SPACE key on the keyboard.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06T46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/starship/embed?sid=1","plays":40318,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I661U","slug":"mini-jumps","title":"Mini Jumps","description":"You control a little orange blob that only has the ability to jump. Use the platforms on the level to help the blob to reach the goal.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I661U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-jumps/embed?sid=1","plays":40318,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"869GA","slug":"chocolate-tetris-game","title":"Chocolate Tetris Game","description":"Play a fun and challenging game of Tetris in the shape of chocolate!\\ \nPlay The Chocolate Tetris Game online for free. \nThe classic tetras game with a chocolate twist.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/869GA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chocolate-tetris-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40317,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4T43N","slug":"tank-node-4-vs-4-battle","title":"Tank Node 4 vs 4 Battle","description":"Tank Node is a team-based game with tank theme. ​You can control many type of tank with different skill. New maps and tanks are updated daily.\n\nFeatures:\n\n+ 4 vs 4 multiplayer battle.\n\n+ Destroy enemies and their building to get point.\n\n+ Collect gears to upgrade your tank: ammo, damage,...\n\n+ Unlock new tanks.\n\n+ Build a team with your friend to destroy other players","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4T43N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tank-node-4-vs-4-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40317,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6113K","slug":"kevo","title":"Kevo","description":"Kevo is a 2D Platform game where you need to collect keys in order to unlock the door while avoiding saws, spikes and the enemies. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse WASD or arrow keys for movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6113K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kevo/embed?sid=1","plays":40313,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12","slug":"battleship-minesweeper","title":"Battleship Minesweeper","description":"Enfilez votre combinaison et détectez toutes les mines présentes sur la grille. Attention car la partie sera perdue si une seule mine explose!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battleship-minesweeper/embed?sid=1","plays":40313,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAI0A","slug":"pizza-ninja-mania","title":"Pizza Ninja Mania","description":"Des ingrédients à pizza volent dans les airs... Des compétences de tranchage ninja sont requises ! Les clients doivent être servis rapidement, et ils apprécient les beaux spectacles. Alors armez-vous d'un couteau et faites votre travail ! Jouez à chaque mode de jeu et devenez le meilleur ! De nouveaux types de bonus vous attendent !\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAI0A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pizza-ninja-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40312,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1CAIY","slug":"scary-vending-machine","title":"Scary Vending Machine","description":"Scary Vending Machine is an amazing game that helps your child to learn math by playing! Choose among three vending machines: one with toys, one with sweet treats, and one with food.\nEach item inside the vending machines has a price; you have a set of coins at your disposal to insert the right sum you can see on the display.\nIf you’re right, the vending machine will release the item, if you’re wrong you’ll receive an error message.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1CAIY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scary-vending-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40312,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E4AI","slug":"lines-air-balloons","title":"Lines - Air Balloons","description":"The goal of the game is to score as many points as possible by placing five or more balloons in a line.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E4AI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lines-air-balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S9SA3","slug":"miss-tuna","title":"Miss Tuna","description":"Miss Tuna is a 2D Platformer where you need to collect all of the lollipops while avoiding saws, and enemies. There are 8 levels to play and difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nWASD or arrow keys for movement.    \nPress W or up arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S9SA3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miss-tuna/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EAPIY","slug":"flappy-the-pipes-are-back","title":"Flappy the Pipes are Back","description":"Play Flappy The Pipes ara back . Click on the screen, to get started. Fly the bird as far as you can without hitting a pipe.\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EAPIY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-the-pipes-ara-back/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R494R","slug":"flipzuru","title":"Flipzuru","description":"Touchez les carrés pour retourner ceux qui les entourent afin de compléter le modèle ci-dessus. Pourrez-vous terminer les 40 niveaux ?","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R494R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flipzure/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y2C0L","slug":"fly-witch","title":"Fly Witch","description":"In this game you can play with a Fly Witch!\nJust Tap to fly and try to pass across the wood boxes without touching them.\n\nTry to resist the more you can  sign your personal record and collect all medals!\nfly fly little Witch!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y2C0L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fly-witch/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NA46T","slug":"football-soccer-mondial","title":"Football Soccer Mondial","description":"This is a one or two player soccer game where you flick your players across the field. Each team has 5 players including the goalie. Choose your team from one of 8 teams across the Beano and Dandy series.  Set your aim and shot strength then kick the ball. Repeat the process for up to 3 kicks per turn. Avoid fouling the other team to keep control of the ball for your full 3 kicks. Score more points than the opposing team and win the game.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NA46T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-soccer-mondial/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I3O6O","slug":"lamp-of-aladdin-slots","title":"Lamp of Aladdin Slots","description":"A slot game in which you can win virtual game currency.Place your bets and win! Before you start, place a bet and then launch the slot.\nGame Control: AUTO-button to automatically start the game.\nSTART-the button for manually starting the game.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I3O6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lamp-of-aladdin/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"654Z6","slug":"crazy-little-eights","title":"Crazy Little Eights","description":"Great online version of the popular card game. Your goal is get rid of all your cards. You can play with a card of the same rank or suit as the card on the central pile. You can also always play with an eight. After you play with an eight you can change the suit to be played with. If the first card on the table is eight, you can start the play with any card. You can pick multiple cards, but they all have to be of the same rank. That's it. Have fun!","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/654Z6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-little-eights/embed?sid=1","plays":40308,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9G47M","slug":"stickman-huggy","title":"Stickman Huggy","description":"hey i'm a stickman huggy. you have to help me and i have to pass all the chapters. Try to finish the level by paying attention to the obstacles. Be careful, if you hit the obstacle, you will lose. Reach the flag before the time runs out and move on to the next level. each level is challenging and different from each other.   \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9G47M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-huggy/embed?sid=1","plays":40307,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C26AD","slug":"piggy-on-the-run","title":"Piggy on the Run","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of cute piggy in the forest? piggy on the run run piggy run pass the levels in the jungle and dominate the jungle! watch out for enemies watch out for obstacles! You have to be careful in the jungle!\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD! \n*Double Jump Available!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C26AD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-adventurecraft-aqua/embed?sid=1","plays":40306,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"X6TN3","slug":"steve-and-alex","title":"Steve and Alex","description":"Steve needs to help Alex in the love story of Steve and Alex. You have to be in Steven's place and collect the portal pieces from where Alex is stuck. Collect 10 obsidians and create the alexsin portal. and complete the track and go to the portal. be careful don't fall down you may die if you fall down. or you will explode if you touch the TNTs.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/X6TN3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-and-alex/embed?sid=1","plays":40305,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7G20","slug":"ball-sort-color-puzzle-game","title":"Ball Sort - Color Puzzle Game","description":"Ball Sort Puzzle is a fun and addictive puzzle game! Try to sort the colored balls in the tubes until all balls with the same color stay in the same tube. A challenging yet relaxing game to exercise your brain!\n\n★ HOW TO PLAY:\n• Tap any tube to move the ball lying on top of the tube to another tube.\n• The rule is that you can only move a ball on top of another ball if both of them have the same color and the tube you want to move into has enough space.\n• Try not to get stuck - but don’t worry, you can always restart the level at any time.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7G20/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-sort-color-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40304,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1BRI9","slug":"galaxy-bricks-breaker","title":"Galaxy Bricks Breaker","description":"The Galaxy Bricks Breaker Online Game is a great way to pass the time. It is a game that requires quick reflexes and decision making. The object of the game is to clear all the bricks from the screen. This can be accomplished by matching three or more bricks of the same color. The game gets progressively more difficult as more bricks are added to the screen.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1BRI9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-bricks-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":40304,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3C6HK","slug":"kick-the-ball-and-shoot","title":"Kick the ball and shoot","description":"In the game you have to tap the ball with your head, dodging obstacles and using weapons. The game has many different obstacles: rocks, bottles, fire extinguishers, tires, spears, etc. Collect weapons to break obstacles: pistol, machine gun, shotgun, grenade launcher, shield.\n\nComplete achievements to unlock additional power-ups, skins, sounds and music.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3C6HK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kick-the-ball-and-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":40304,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EOAA2","slug":"stickman-3d-legacy-of-war","title":"Stickman 3D Legacy of War","description":"Guerre Stickman - La paix est venu! La bataille a commencé!\n\nVous avez formé des guerriers Stickman, la bataille est sur le point de commencer!\nVotre appel: détruire le château ennemi et devenir le roi du chef Stickman!\nVotre armée est en train de rêver que la lutte a commencé ...","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EOAA2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-legacy-of-war-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40304,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3E071","slug":"number-games","title":"Number Games","description":"You need to know when you should remain silent and when you should take action , if you think you’ve got that figured out, try the Number Game.\n\nThe Number Game is an audio based reflex testing game, the game will play an audio which might correspond to the the number of digits present in the sum displayed, and when that happens you have to press the enter key and when the audio played does not match the number of digits , you have to do absolutely nothing but make sure you keep up with the pace of the game because time is not your friend here,so you have to find the perfect balance between being fast and being accurate to get the highest score.\n","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3E071/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/number-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40304,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P9Z0Z","slug":"barbee-doll-puzzles","title":"Barbee Doll Puzzles","description":"Barbie Puzzles Game is a free online game from genre of puzzle and jigsaw games. You can select one of the 12 images and then select one of the three modes: easy with 25 pieces, medium with 49 pieces and hard with 100 pieces. Have fun and enjoy!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P9Z0Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbie-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9388E","slug":"don-t-drop-the-pig","title":"Don't Drop the Pig","description":"Don' Drop The Pig is a cool action game very easy and intuitive to play, but it will be hard to stop playing.\nTap with your finger the blowing up balloons on the screen and touch the Pig to prevent it from falling down.\nEnjoy this cool game the more you can! You can play with your children it's very funny for your cool sounds effects. \n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• very easy to play\n• nice 2D graphics\n• endless gameplay\n• very fun game for kids and babies\n• cool music sound effects\n• amazing animations\nGreat Game Great Fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9388E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-drop-the-pig/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7RE27","slug":"draw-the-rest","title":"Draw the Rest","description":"Draw what is missing in every photo in this fun online drawing game. Examine the photo, then draw what is missing to complete each puzzle. If you need a hint, press the light button to see the solution to the puzzle. Try to complete all levels using your brain and drawing skills.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7RE27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/draw-the-rest/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ON6E3","slug":"hold-the-line","title":"Hold the Line","description":"Hold The Line is an elegant and simple finger-runner.\nHow to play:\nJust keep your finger on the screen, stay inside the line and walk through randomly generated maze.\nTry top Don't step into obstacles or traps and run as far as you can.\nEnjoy!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ON6E3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hold-the-line/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5HKN5","slug":"jetpackman-shooter","title":"Jetpackman Shooter","description":"jetpacman shooter is a html5 shooter adventure game, shoot the enemy and collect coin to earn score","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5HKN5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jetpackman-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C15L1","slug":"lucky-vs-lou","title":"Lucky vs Lou","description":"Lou, the handsome toy with blond hair, who has evil evils, starts the giant toy-smashing machine. lucky so the toy red bat starts running because it can never fly because it is a toy. He has to get the key or his friends can't reach out and save him. He must get the golden key to save his friends.\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD to move & Arrow Keys to move. Mobile Touch Control. Double jump is active in the game.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C15L1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lucky-vs-lou/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42121","slug":"stumble-run-fall-colors","title":"Stumble Run Fall Colors","description":"Strumble Run c'est un jeu de course pour collecter des couleurs et éviter les obstacles","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42121/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stumble-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PBOUS","slug":"super-ball-down","title":"Super Ball Down","description":"Welcome to super down ball, the ball game, challenge obstacles and drop the ball in positive scores, otherwise your score will decrease, what are you up to? go play Down Ball now and the fun is guaranteed !!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PBOUS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-ball-down/embed?sid=1","plays":40303,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3WM31","slug":"yummy-waffle-ice-cream","title":"Yummy Waffle Ice Cream","description":"Are you a waffle lover? Are you an ice cream lover? This game is perfect for you. Let's make some waffle and decorate it with ice cream and any kind of fruits and syrups! Be a waffle maker!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3WM31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-waffle-ice-cream/embed?sid=1","plays":40302,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WNC4S","slug":"super-candy-jewels","title":"Super Candy Jewels","description":"Essayez ce jeu de combinaisons de bonbons. Partez pour une aventure sucrée pleine de bonbons et essayez de terminer tous les niveaux. Vous serez récompensé avec de délicieux combos de bonbons.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WNC4S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-candy-jewels/embed?sid=1","plays":40300,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20043","slug":"monsterjong","title":"MonsterJong","description":"Jouez à ce solitaire monstrueux en éliminant tous les blocs de monstre du plateau. Pour se faire, Retrouvez les paires assorties et tapez l'écran pour les faire disparaitre!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20043/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monsterjong/embed?sid=1","plays":40299,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8D1M","slug":"yacht-dice-game","title":"Yacht Dice Game","description":"Score as many points as possible by rolling five dices and getting the best combinations.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8D1M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yacht-dice-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40298,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40406","slug":"baseball-hero","title":"Baseball Hero","description":"Hit your baseballs hard and... avoid bombs and tomatoes! Improve your ability hitting multiple balls from different positions. You'll become a Baseball Hero!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40406/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baseball-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40294,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RH6E5","slug":"head-soccer-2023","title":"Head Soccer 2023","description":"Head Soccer 2023 is a sports game. Choose your player and play fast-paced soccer games against your friend or computer. You're in charge of the offense as well as the defense here. Jump, kick. You can also enroll in tournaments if you're looking for a challenge. Go ahead and practice until you can prove you have what it takes to win the tournament! Play and have fun!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RH6E5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/head-soccer-2023/embed?sid=1","plays":40293,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10037","slug":"cave-escape","title":"Cave Escape","description":"Aidez Rudy le mineur à s'échapper de la mine en emportant avec lui un maximum de diamands!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10037/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cave-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":40293,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I61G3","slug":"ugi-bugi","title":"Ugi Bugi","description":"Ugi Bugi, the cute blue plush teddy bear, needs to reach the flag. Help him and reach the flag. Be careful, you may encounter many obstacles. Don't forget to collect gold too. collect the gold and reach the finish line.\n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I61G3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ugi-bugi/embed?sid=1","plays":40292,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"942PR","slug":"trz-pop-it","title":"TRZ Pop it","description":"In this game you have to click all the 'buttons' on each of the 80 possible toys (you will need to unlock them one by one). Have a good time: Pop and relax!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/942PR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trz-pop-it/embed?sid=1","plays":40292,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F4MRC","slug":"cookie-maker-for-kids","title":"Cookie Maker for Kids","description":"Prepare, cut out, bake, and decorate cookies of many shapes and sizes! Bake the cookies and dessert snacks you are the best bakery chef.\nBake and create a cookie that’s too cute to eat!!! Give a treat of sweet yummy cookies to your Friends their cute charming little friends and all of your family members.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F4MRC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cookie-maker-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40291,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9O76O","slug":"iron-mom","title":"Iron Mom","description":"A new machine apocalypse has begun!\nHelp Mom neutralize all opponents and use her armor to become a hero.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9O76O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/iron-mom/embed?sid=1","plays":40288,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F2IG2","slug":"falling-pig","title":"Falling Pig","description":"Felix is the first pig in the world to have launched itself from the isosphere, from an altitude of 130.00 feet. If we don't help him, he'll crash!\nTilt the phone to move Felix and tap on objects to move or destroy them.\nThe mechanics of the game are similar to doodle jump but here, instead of jumping, you fall.\nBetween levels, some funny cartoons will get you to know Felix better.\nYou will discover that there is no such boastful pig in the world.\nAnd you can unlock unique skins to make Felix more aggressive ... or prettier\n","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F2IG2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-pig/embed?sid=1","plays":40288,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"945P0","slug":"jump-with-justin","title":"Jump with Justin","description":"Attrapez un maximum de pièces de monnaie afin de propulser le castor le plus haut possible et atteindre les sommets de la galaxie! Collectez les bonus délirants tels que le magnétiseur de pièces, la fusée ou le ballon d'hélium afin de faciliter votre ascension. Soyez vigilant et rapide afin d'éviter les obstacles qui précipiteront le pauvre castor dans sa chute. Pourrez-vous atteindre les limites de l'espace et aller encore plus loin?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/945P0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-with-justin/embed?sid=1","plays":40286,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22328","slug":"2048-legend","title":"2048 Legend","description":"2048 est un jeu simple dans lequel vous additionnez des nombres. C'est tout. Mais ce n'est pas aussi facile qu'il y paraît. Vous relèverez de véritables défis. Si vous ne connaissez pas encore ce classique, alors vous allez vous régaler ! Êtes-vous prêt à tester votre esprit et à marquer le plus de points possible ? Alors qu'attendez-vous ? Jouez !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22328/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":40285,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66830","slug":"driver","title":"Driver","description":"drive, avoid the obstacles and do your best for rising that score UP!\n\nHAVE FUN!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66830/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/driver/embed?sid=1","plays":40284,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5IT81","slug":"santa-magic-christmas","title":"Santa Magic Christmas","description":"Détendez-vous avec ce jeu de joyaux simple et amusant. Aidez le Père Noël à récupérer les cadeaux perdus dans l'environnement magique de Noël. Utilisez différents bonus pour terminer les niveaux.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5IT81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-magic-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40284,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T252S","slug":"santas-secret-gift","title":"Santas Secret Gift","description":"game of a santa who has a super gift box. Santa Claus can teleport to the place where the gift box is by throwing the gift box in his hand. A gift box with super powers.\n\nHow to Play?\nUse the arrow keys to move. Use the z key to teleport. Use the down arrow key to pass through the doors. Mobile control support is available","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T252S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santas-secret-gift/embed?sid=1","plays":40284,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40318","slug":"pizza-ninja-3","title":"Pizza Ninja 3","description":"Chopping frenzy in Maro's pizzeria again! Orders are still whizzing in and ingredients need chopping! The kitchen needs a ninja hero! Collect bonuses and test your skills with different  game modes!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40318/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pizza-ninja-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40283,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9E55E","slug":"jewel-duel","title":"Jewel Duel","description":"Même les plus vieux ne se rappellent plus depuis quand leur magnifique pays Cartucie est-il dominé par la magie noire de deux mages de feu. Ça fait vraiment longtemps que la Cartucie est plongé dans l´obscurité et souffrance que des serviteurs de mages lui portent tous les jours. La légende dit qu´un héros viendra pour restaurer la paix dans le pays. Mais le temps passe ! Les mages de feu veulent ouvrir le gouffre d´horreur qui fera venir des milliers de démons. Tout serait alors perdu. Tout le monde croit que ce héros c´est justement toi.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9E55E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-duel/embed?sid=1","plays":40282,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5632","slug":"color-tower","title":"Color Tower","description":"Construisez une grande tour de boîtes colorées !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5632/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":40281,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S16D3","slug":"3d-santa-rescue","title":"3D Santa Rescue","description":"An evil hungry skeleton is attacking Santa’s reindeer. Help Old Saint Nick catch up to the skeleton. Choose the right number of steps between each interval to help Santa catch up and overtake the undead menace & rescue the reindeer.\n\nYou can only take 8 steps at a time.\nThe skeleton moves fast, so you should, too.\nPlay through all 20 levels.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S16D3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-santa-rescue/embed?sid=1","plays":40281,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CS5SR","slug":"dangerous-rescue","title":"Dangerous Rescue","description":"Dangerous rescue is fun adventure games \n.! Get into your helicopter and rescue the people. fly as fast as you can and as carefully as you can to not crash in the mountain","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CS5SR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dangerous-rescue/embed?sid=1","plays":40281,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UU02C","slug":"surfer-cat","title":"Surfer Cat","description":"In this game, players take control of a surfing cat who is on a mission to collect shells from the sea. \nThe cat surfs across waves and must avoid obstacles such as rocks and other sea creatures. \nAs the player progresses through the level, the waves and obstacles become more challenging. \nThe game features colorful graphics and a cheerful soundtrack to create a fun and relaxing atmosphere. \nThe cat moves along the lines - swipe up to move the cat up a line and swipe down to move the cat down. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UU02C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/surfer-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":40281,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M81Z3","slug":"zumba-ocean","title":"Zumba Ocean","description":"Améliorez-vous dans l'un des jeux de puzzle les plus populaires. Tirez sur les gemmes et essayez de terminer tous les niveaux avec trois étoiles dans chaque niveau. Ce jeu de gemmes est facile et addictif à la fois.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M81Z3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zumba-ocean/embed?sid=1","plays":40280,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EN168","slug":"cat-runner","title":"Cat Runner","description":"cat runner is a html5 endless run game, run away from the evil monster chase ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EN168/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40280,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51AT7","slug":"adventure-bot-action-platformer","title":"Adventure Bot Action Platformer","description":"$18","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51AT7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventure-bot-action-platformer/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DD91N","slug":"adventurer-s-run","title":"Adventurer's Run","description":"​Drag your character to move around. Your weapons will automatically shoot.\n\nEvade being attacked by monsters or running into objects like trees.\n\nOver time when you reach long distances, you will receive weapon upgrades or unlock new weapons.\n\nCollect coins and unlock new characters. Destroy enemy monsters and get the high score.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DD91N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventurer-s-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"267L2","slug":"circulet-2d","title":"Circulet 2D","description":"Dans \"Circulet\", vous devez esquiver les bombes qui s'abattent sur vous ! Collectez des cœurs pour gagner des points !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/267L2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circulet-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E4EME","slug":"circus-dancer-memory-match","title":"Circus Dancer Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Circus dancer Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Circus dancer Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Circus dancer Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E4EME/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circus-dancer-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P2PA8","slug":"equations-flapping","title":"Equations Flapping","description":"This game is a mix of skills and math reasoning. Touch in the screen to make the bird fly high and pass through the trees avoiding colliding with them, but you must choose the correct number according with math multiplications that will be displayed.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P2PA8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/equations-flapping/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OT1SM","slug":"four-colors-monument-edition","title":"Four Colors Monument Edition","description":"Are you ready to travel around the world?\nHave fun and discover the most beautiful monuments with this new version of Four Colors! \nFace up to 3 real opponents or 3 computer-controlled players.\nMatch cards by color or number. Use play action cards to mix the game up and be the first to get rid of all cards.\nLast but not least: Do not forget to press the 1 button when you have only one card left!","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OT1SM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/four-colors-monument-edition/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57REE","slug":"fruityswipes","title":"FruitySwipes","description":"Fun and relaxing puzzle game, where you need to find chains of the same colored fruits on the board. \nSimply tap on one fruit icon and move your finger around the screen to select more of the same. \nThere are cool bonuses and power-ups waiting for connecting the longest chains. \nThe game ends when energy bar on the top of the screen deplates (you can replenish it with power-ups while you play). \nHave fun!\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57REE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruityswipes/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W7771","slug":"kissy-wuggy","title":"Kissy & Wuggy!","description":"Kissy and Huggy is the best puzzle platformer in the world of HuggyWuggy and KissyMissy. In this adventure you explore 18 different levels.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W7771/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kissy-and-wuggy/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CI13M","slug":"magic-circle","title":"Magic Circle","description":"Hello Welcome to the circle game, you must be skilled in sliding the circle through the rope","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CI13M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magic-circle/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LL558","slug":"pull-the-treasure","title":"Pull the Treasure","description":"The \"Pull the Treasure Online Pull Him Out Game\" is a fun way to pass the time. The object of the game is to pull the treasure out of the ground and then him out of the water. The game is simple and easy to play.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LL558/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pull-the-treasure/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"85691","slug":"space-doodles","title":"Space Doodles","description":"Protect the galaxy from aliens.\n\nIf you are a space shooting lover and want to simulate shooting into the sky, Space Shooter: Galaxy Attack is the game for you.\nOne day, our beautiful galaxy is under attack from cosmic intruders. You are the last hero of the galaxy. Your goal will be quite challenging as you will have to save the galaxy from evil enemies.\nSpace Shooter: Galaxy Attack puts you on the front lines of the battle against space intruders. You will take control of a spaceship and must protect the galaxy from aliens.\nAs the game progresses, you will earn the right to upgrade your spaceship to bring it up to full lethal power.\n\nPOSSIBILITY\n- Amazing lighting and special effects\n- Includes bonuses and bosses!\n- Global leaderboard.\n- Happy circle.\n\nHOW TO PLAY\n- Move the spaceship\n- Kill intruders\n- Upgrade your spaceship\n- Change your weapons.\n\nThe future of the Galaxy is now in your hands. Prepare your weapons for epic battles.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/85691/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-doodles/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5HS23","slug":"sushi-run-2-players-game","title":"Sushi Run - 2 Players Game","description":"Sushi run is a local PvP game. Each player has to use his chopsticks to pick more sushi than his opponent. Each player has a moves counter, which decreases of one point every time you move your chopsticks. If you run out of moves, you'll lose. Sometimes an expired sushi, with rotten green fish on it, can appear on the plate. If you pick it, you'll automatically lose.\nThanks for playing and have a nice play!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5HS23/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sushi-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40279,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ESSPC","slug":"hipsters-vs-rockers","title":"Hipsters vs Rockers","description":"Gaia, Ero and Ai are best friends forever. They like to try the latest fashion and compare with one another that suits them. This time they tried the style of rockers and hipsters. Wonder which fashion is suitable for them?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ESSPC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hipsters-vs-rockers/embed?sid=1","plays":40278,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5186S","slug":"cheese-collector-rat-runner","title":"Cheese Collector-Rat Runner","description":"$19","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5186S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cheese-collector-rat-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40278,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O17GE","slug":"froggy-tower","title":"Froggy Tower","description":"Froggy Tower, Hyper Casual Game - Tap to increase the block to collect coins and survive till end. but if you fail, you have to start your level all over again.  \nFroggy Tower is a fun and engaging hyper casual game that will keep you entertained for hours on end. With its easy-to-play gameplay and easy-to-collect coins, this game is perfect for anyone who loves playing games. The goal of the game is to survive as long as possible until the end, and by tapping on the blocks, you can increase your chances of making it through alive.  \n","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O17GE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/froggy-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":40278,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56618","slug":"off-the-track","title":"Off the Track","description":"Spin the Metal shape and drop all the ring in the hole.Some shapes are tricky so you have to control rotation and speed. use Precision and timing to spin the shape the right way to get the rings off.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56618/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/off-the-track/embed?sid=1","plays":40278,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2DDNU","slug":"red-and-blue-adventure","title":"Red and Blue Adventure","description":"Complete the levels in the best way by escaping from lots of enemies in the adventure-filled levels of the best friend red and blue! The adventure game of the blue and red men.\n\nHow to Play?\n*WASD + Arrow Keys! \n*collect diamonds! reach the door! \n*Double Jump Available","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2DDNU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-blue-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40278,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A2641","slug":"basketball-smash","title":"Basketball Smash","description":"Dans ce jeu de basket, vous devez simplement faire des dunks sans vous arrêter. Cependant, le temps passe vite et vos erreurs peuvent vous coûter cher. Facile à apprendre, difficile à maîtriser. Pouvez-vous déverrouiller tous les ballons ? Sautez avec le ballon et faites des paniers avant la fin du temps imparti.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A2641/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":40277,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LLN6A","slug":"pool-8-ball-mania","title":"Pool: 8 Ball Mania","description":"Le billard classique à 8 boules pour votre téléphone ! Mesurez-vous à un adversaire contrôlé par l'ordinateur ou à un ami. Vous apprécierez la physique réaliste et le gameplay dynamique. Utilisez l'aide à la visée pour réaliser des coups très précis.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LLN6A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pool-8-ball-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40277,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AR1YY","slug":"animals-memory","title":"Animals Memory","description":"Tap or click any card to reveal its card. Memorize it and try to find its pair in board. Match all of the cards on the board and complete level. In total there are 10 levels for you to have fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AR1YY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animals-memory/embed?sid=1","plays":40276,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"503O0","slug":"domino-legend","title":"Domino legend","description":"Un jeu de dominos classique ! Que vous soyez un joueur expérimenté ou que vous n'ayez pas joué depuis votre enfance, ce jeu vous procurera une expérience inoubliable. Vous pouvez découvrir les variantes les plus populaires du jeu, Bloquer et Piocher. Rien ne pourra se mettre entre vous et une partie rapide de dominos !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/503O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/domino-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":40276,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SM91R","slug":"angry-monsters","title":"Angry Monsters","description":"Angry Monsters features challenging physics-based gameplay that offers plenty\nof entertainment. Each stage requires logic, skill and strength to solve.\nThere are 10 stages for you to have fun and kill the monsters.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SM91R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angry-monsters/embed?sid=1","plays":40276,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9SG1E","slug":"glass-ball-puzzle","title":"Glass Ball Puzzle","description":"Glass Ball Puzzle is a fun and challenging color puzzle game with a major breakthrough in puzzle sorting gameplay. Separate the balls of various colors and pour the balls into the cups filled with the same color.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9SG1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glass-ball-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40275,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UK6B1","slug":"bloxy-block-parkour","title":"Bloxy Block Parkour","description":"Bloxy Block Parkour is a fun jumping game that you can play for free on PC and Mobile. No download needed. Here is our adventure man who stuck on the blocky world where he has to reach the portal to win the level. Help him to jump on the platforms and reach the destination. Clear all the levels with unexpected twists and turns and win the game. Start playing and have fun!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UK6B1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bloxy-block-parkour/embed?sid=1","plays":40275,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JN78E","slug":"ninja-samurai-runner-online","title":"Ninja Samurai Runner Online","description":"Escape your enemies by jumping and sliding over and under obstacles with the arrow keys, as you sprint along the 2D landscape, collecting gold to buy upgrades on the way.    \nYou can climb the tower higher by collecting ninjas and get bonuses.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JN78E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-samurai-runner-online/embed?sid=1","plays":40269,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"95L6O","slug":"falling-dots","title":"Falling Dots","description":"Falling Dots est l'arcade mobile plate et minimaliste. Collectez les points rouges. Rivalisez avec vos amis !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/95L6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-dots/embed?sid=1","plays":40268,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7L8P2","slug":"helicopter","title":"Helicopter","description":"fly helicopter to complete the mission, there will be obstacles good luck","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7L8P2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/helicopter/embed?sid=1","plays":40268,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40153","slug":"gold-miner-slots","title":"Gold Miner Slots","description":"Bienvenue sur la table de jeu! Augmentez vos chances de gain en multipliant les lignes de 1 à 5. Boostez vos gains en élevant votre mise jusqu'à 10 crédits. Récoltez coffres et roues de la fortune dans n'importe laquelle des lignes de paris, de façon à remplir la jauge et augmenter vos chances lors des mini-jeux!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40153/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gold-miner-slots/embed?sid=1","plays":40267,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NJ957","slug":"kingdom-of-ninja","title":"Kingdom of Ninja","description":"The story of a ninja who has kingdoms, be careful, it is far from the traps that come in front of you while reaching the kingdom, or you may not pass the level. Watch out for monsters too and don't touch them! Join the fun consisting of 10 different sections.  \n\nHow to Play?\n\"Z\" Jump + \"Arrow key\" Move / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NJ957/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kingdom-of-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40267,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8RH0H","slug":"matryoshka-rush","title":"Matryoshka Rush","description":"Do you know that The largest set of Russian dolls is consists of 51 pieces. Now you must to create your own set of Russian dolls of different sizes.\nYou just need to touch and set the size of the next Russian doll.\nRemember the main rule - the size of the new Russian doll does not go beyond the red border.\nTry to set new personal records and maybe you will be able to break the record of Guinness Book of Records .\nSet a record of more than 15, 25 or 30 matryoshka dolls and get opportunity to use bonuses with additional (5, 7 or 10) matreshka dolls in next 10 games.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8RH0H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/matryoshka-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40266,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O63O5","slug":"go-to-dot","title":"Go to Dot","description":"Click to move to the big point. Watch out for red enemies.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O63O5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/go-to-dot/embed?sid=1","plays":40264,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T2HAU","slug":"santa-haircut","title":"Santa Haircut","description":"Santa is getting ready for the Christmas night. So he went to your salon to get a makeover. Let's help him cut out his messy hair and give the best hair makeover he can get! You can dress him up at the end to perfect his new look! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T2HAU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-haircut/embed?sid=1","plays":40264,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L4O2R","slug":"pick-the-color","title":"Pick the Color","description":"A game where you have to click the different colored dot in order to progress. Will you be able to get past 100 points?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L4O2R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pick-the-color/embed?sid=1","plays":40264,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A3009","slug":"alien-attack","title":"Alien Attack","description":"Try to defend your planet from a terrible Alien Attack! \nMove left and right with the directional arrows and press the left mouse button to shoot. Try to survive as long as you can against this massive endless invasion! Good Luck !","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A3009/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40262,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6T7IC","slug":"air-war","title":"Air War","description":"$1a","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6T7IC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/air-war-action-shooting-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40261,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O414R","slug":"balloon-match-color-match","title":"Balloon Match Color Match","description":"$1b","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O414R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-match-color-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40261,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"144EP","slug":"alphabet-writing-for-kids","title":"Alphabet Writing for Kids","description":"“Alphabet Writing For Kids” is one of the best educational app for toddlers, preschoolers and kindergarten kids to learn how to trace uppercase and lowercase alphabets from A to Z.\nBy this app, kids can also listen to the phonetics of words improving theirs speaking skills.\nEach letter and related word will be read out loud and clearly so that kids will understand them easily.\nKids will learn how to write and read with fun and for free.\nKey Features: \n- ABC Tracing games.\n- Over 60 funny cartoon sticker.\n- Lot of funny sounds and musics.\n- Kids learn english alphabet.\n- Letters, Number and Animals.\n- Uppercase and Lowercase letters.\n- Super simple game interface.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/144EP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alphabet-writing-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40260,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RCE88","slug":"counter-craft-3","title":"Counter Craft 3","description":"Counter Craft 3 features cool graphics and intensive multiplayer battles across block world maps, use different weapons with unique skins to shoot all your opponents on each map and try to get the highest amount of frags in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RCE88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-craft-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40259,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N90S1","slug":"mining-rush","title":"Mining Rush","description":"Dans le jeu Mining Rush, vous pouvez extraire des minéraux, gagner de l'argent et acheter de nouveaux outils miniers. Procurez-vous des matériaux de construction et construisez votre propre ville. Le jeu dispose de 60 outils différents que vous pouvez débloquer!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N90S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mining-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40257,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"071MG","slug":"mango-mania","title":"Mango Mania","description":"Far away in the jungle, there was a small creature, that can not live without the mango! Help him to collect all the fruits!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/071MG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mango-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40257,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A61RC","slug":"speed-racer","title":"Speed Racer","description":"Speed Racer offers two game modes! The \"Loop\" mode will allow you to have an endless experience where you have to dodge cars, obstacles and comply with the rules of the road otherwise you will be chased by the police! The 1vs1 mode allows you, instead, to play a race against the CPU in which you will be the one to drive your car to victory! The game also offers more than 50 different machines to unlock and try! Have fun pilot!​","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A61RC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speed-racer/embed?sid=1","plays":40255,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J15PE","slug":"jump-step","title":"Jump Step","description":"This is Jump Step a game created to entertain and entertain, test your endurance with the classic rope jump in a modern key, in a nostalgic 8/16 bit style!\nThrough the use of a simple \"tap\" you can jump and accumulate points, but be careful not to get hit by the rope. In case of game over you can resume playing by clicking on the yellow button, otherwise you will have to start again.\nFor the rest... Are you ready for the challenge?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J15PE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-step/embed?sid=1","plays":40252,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TSA82","slug":"jewel-christmas","title":"Jewel Christmas","description":"Noël est là ! Quelle meilleure façon de le célébrer qu'avec un jeu de séries de 3 explosif ?! Associez trois bonhommes en pain d'épice, chaussettes, sapins, cannes à sucre, cadeaux ou boules, et regardez-les exploser ! Avec cinq modes de jeu festifs et plus de défis à déverrouiller en cours de route, ce jeu sera le cadeau parfait pour vous ce Noël ! Attendez-vous à beaucoup de bijoux qui éclatent dans cet incroyable jeu de séries de 3 explosif !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TSA82/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40251,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VD843","slug":"ludo-fever","title":"Ludo Fever","description":"Détruisez les jetons ennemis dans ce Ludo moderne. Jouez-y seul, ou avec vos amis et votre famille sur un seul appareil. Lancez les dés et parcourez tout le plateau de jeu avec tous les jetons. Arriverez-vous le premier dans votre zone d'origine ?\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VD843/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ludo-fever/embed?sid=1","plays":40251,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0V0CL","slug":"vik-the-climber","title":"VIK The Climber","description":"In this game you are VIK adn you have to collect as much coin you can.  but you must pay attention to the barriers, the dragons, the barbarians and ZEUS\n\nthe funny thing about this game is that i made with my voice all of the sounds inside it, i hope it will make you laugh","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0V0CL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vik-the-climber/embed?sid=1","plays":40250,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12E86","slug":"the-squared","title":"The Squared","description":"Play as a cute cube, Avoid obstacles and do your best score in this side scrolling game! \n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12E86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-squared/embed?sid=1","plays":40250,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ARTE4","slug":"faded-nightmare-game","title":"Faded Nightmare Game","description":"Faded Nightmare is an action-packed platformed game. Jump from platform to platform as you dodge the Enemy and grab everything you can, all to get the highest score. You can play with friends and family, or go solo and try to beat your previous high score! With a beautifully designed pixel art style and intuitive controls, this game is sure to provide hours of fun.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ARTE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/faded-nightmare-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P1AMP","slug":"animals-party-ball-2-player","title":"Animals Party Ball - 2 Player","description":"Hey you gamers are you ready to survive in this dangerous world with your friend? yes if you are ready survive in very dangerous jungle. Reach the finish gate with the ball-shaped animal with your friend. Remember, reaching alone is not a solution to anything. To get out of the forest, you and your friend have to reach the door. collect coins and buy different animal costumes. Never, ever reach the door without the key.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P1AMP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animals-party-ball-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6A12O","slug":"baby-yoda-photo-jigsaw","title":"Baby Yoda Photo Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Baby Yoda Photo jigsaw, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Baby Yoda Photo jigsaw, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Baby Yoda Photo jigsaw and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6A12O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-yoda-photo-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1CE99","slug":"circle","title":"Circle","description":"Circle is a new project, with an unusual gameplay. Everyone remembers the usual games from the \"Ricochet\" genre. The games were made in 2d design with rectangular levels. What if the level was not rectangular, but circular?  In the game you will find:\n- Unusual gameplay.\n- Good graphics\n- Intuitive controls\nTry the game in unusual conditions, and of course recommend it to your friends. Good Luck!\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1CE99/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circle/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N155I","slug":"clone-jumping","title":"Clone Jumping","description":"Welcome to Clone Jumping. It's a new puzzle game for kids. Use your keyboard right and left keyboard buttons to move the block. To complete the level you have to move it towards the black hole. This new game test your IQ level. Play and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N155I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clone-jumping/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8A881","slug":"darios-quest-2","title":"Darios Quest 2","description":"Darios Quest 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the ice cream bars while avoiding the monsters, flying Demon heads, spikes and saws and reach your girlfriend in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. Will you be able to collect all of the ice cream bars for your girlfriend?    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Darios Quest\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8A881/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/darios-quest-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S7YE7","slug":"emperor-ashoka-memory-match","title":"Emperor Ashoka Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Emperor Ashoka Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Emperor Ashoka Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Emperor Ashoka Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S7YE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emperor-ashoka-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L3883","slug":"fly-dodge","title":"Fly Dodge","description":"Welcome to Dodoge fle, you have to fly and dodge the crates, taking only coins to accumulate points, your points are saved in your best score, you won't lose them","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L3883/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fly-dodge/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6Y2O6","slug":"froggy-man-2","title":"Froggy Man 2","description":"Froggy Man 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you play as a green frog who have to collect all of the flies while avoiding the orange frogs, blue frogs and their bullets, saws, and spikes and reach the green flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Froggy Man\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6Y2O6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/froggy-man-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54RU1","slug":"fruit-hunter","title":"Fruit Hunter","description":"fruit hunter is an html5 arcade game, 2 players challenge to pick up the falling fruit, be careful not to lose, take as many fruits as possible to get a score and beat your rivals and avoid falling boxes. ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54RU1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-hunter/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0HL1L","slug":"helle-bot","title":"Helle Bot","description":"Helle Bot is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as a bot who have to collect precious red jewels while avoiding the enemy bots, flying bots and their bullets, fire, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0HL1L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/helle-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"37P16","slug":"jelly-phil","title":"Jelly Phil","description":"Jelly Phil is a 2D cute little platformer where you play as jelly man who have to collect pink jellies while avoiding the jelly enemies and saws and reach the exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you continue.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/37P16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jelly-phil/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7MTU8","slug":"juggler-memory-match","title":"Juggler Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Juggler Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Juggler Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Juggler Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7MTU8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/juggler-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1AA68","slug":"minescrafter-steve-and-alex","title":"Minescrafter - Steve and Alex","description":"Are you up for a very dangerous adventure? hey alex and steve in this adventure you have to kill the zombies and put the animals in alexsin backpack save them from this dangerous forest. Save the animals from the forest because there are scary monsters in this forest and the animals are very scared. Beware, the zombies have set a trap. If you touch it, you will die. In order not to die, but do not touch the traps.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys  \n*Double Jump available  \n*Mobile Touch Control  \n*Alex can collect animals.  \n*Steve can shoot zombies with his gun.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1AA68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minescrafter-steve-and-alex/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Q7NIO","slug":"nikosan-quest","title":"Nikosan Quest","description":"Nikosan Quest is a 2D platformer where you play as an anime girl called Nikosan who have to collect all of the yellow cubes while avoiding the monsters, spikes, rotating blades and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Q7NIO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nikosan-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"556N3","slug":"paint-sponges-puzzle","title":"Paint Sponges Puzzle","description":"Il s'agit d'un jeu de puzzle amusant avec 90 niveaux différents. Le jeu a une variété de styles qui changent complètement le jeu et apportent plus de plaisir au joueur. Plongez dans le jeu et essayez de terminer tous les niveaux !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/556N3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paint-sponges/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"479AP","slug":"paused","title":"Paused","description":"What do ducks have to do with rabbits? Exactly, adventure and physics stuff is what you are looking for. If you don't mind, please pause a minute and enjoy an easy set of puzzles and a relaxing game with (I think) beautiful pixel art environment.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/479AP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paused/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K2R4P","slug":"pekko-robot-2","title":"Pekko Robot 2","description":"Pekko Robot 2 is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as a  robot who have to collect chicken eggs while avoiding the enemy bots and their bullets, flying bots, ground saws, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Pekko Bot\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K2R4P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pekko-robot-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8GG49","slug":"pocket-gintoki-image-scramble","title":"Pocket Gintoki Image scramble","description":"Welcome to Pocket Gintoki Image scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Pocket Gintoki Image scramble, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Pocket Gintoki Image scramble and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8GG49/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocket-gintoki-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84OU4","slug":"rescuer-boy","title":"Rescuer Boy","description":"rescuer boy is a html5 top down game,  walk and rescue your friends avoid obstacle and collect sugar, life and treasure","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84OU4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescuer-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VE2TE","slug":"save-the-cat","title":"Save the Cat","description":"In this game, you have to get the cat to eat sweets while avoiding obstacles like spiky platforms, bubbles, balloons, and anything that cause air currents. You also have to cut ropes to break uncut chains.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VE2TE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T7981","slug":"stone-wheel","title":"Stone Wheel","description":"Over 1.000.000 downloads all over the world!!!     \n---------------------------     \nStone Wheel is a funny game where you must control a big rolling wheel through 30 levels.\nWhit its original and colorful graphics Stone Wheel will be a pleasant time-killer, simple but addicting .\nChoose from 2 different control styles: touch or accelerometer.\nYou will need to jump, accelerate, break and have a perfect control of your stone in order to complete all levels!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T7981/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stone-wheel/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0ITEP","slug":"urban-sniper-multiplayer","title":"Urban Sniper Multiplayer","description":"Urban Sniper Multiplayer features intense city warfare with other players, use different types of sniper rifles to shoot your opponents and try to get the highest score in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0ITEP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/urban-sniper-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60045","slug":"warun","title":"Warun","description":"You are elite space marine and your mission is to infiltrate martian bio weapon research facility and use your powerful assault rifle to shoot thousands of security guards, try not overheating your weapon to keep your accuracy in order to survive all waves of enemies.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60045/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/warun/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CW21R","slug":"cow-cow-run","title":"Cow Cow Run","description":"A cow was having a nice life, but all changed when the UFO nation came and wants to kidnap the cow. Help the cow avoid the UFOs while collecting coins to buy it’s freedom!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CW21R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cow-cow-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40249,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S11BA","slug":"dumbocalypse","title":"Dumbocalypse","description":"Professor Brain was experimenting to create waves that increase the brain power, like it can make you really smart, but his experiments went horribly wrong (as always) and made every person that came in contact with the waves DUMB. \n\n\n\nNow they don't even know what to do and how to survive in their daily lives. In this disastrous situation professor got an idea to make an app where people can post their questions and get replies for their problems. Don't look surprised there is an app for literally anything these days. So he quickly makes an app and puts YOU in charge to answer all the questions. \n\n\n\nYour job is to reply people the best you can in order to keep the balance of this planet. Just be cautious \n\nDon't populate the earth too much\nDon't make the humans go extinct\nDon't make them too sad\nDon't make them too happy\n\n\nSee how simple this was. Now go on help those poor souls and don't forget to have fun!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S11BA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dumbocalypse/embed?sid=1","plays":40248,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E12T","slug":"eatapples","title":"EatApples","description":"Welcome to Eatapples, collect all the apples without getting killed, what are you waiting for ?? Go play Eat apples now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E12T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eatapples/embed?sid=1","plays":40247,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61871","slug":"c-19","title":"C_19","description":"Desktop version:\npress A to shoot and directional arrows to move \nMobile version:\ntap twice quickly to shoot and swipe your finger to  move ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61871/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/c-19/embed?sid=1","plays":40246,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5O7N1","slug":"time-dungeon","title":"Time Dungeon","description":"Hey knight, can you survive in the dungeon? Let's find out\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5O7N1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/time-dungeon/embed?sid=1","plays":40244,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2H2E5","slug":"alien-shooter","title":"Alien Shooter","description":"Alien Shooter is a classic arcade shooter game that you can play online. Enjoy this popular shooting game! Alien Shooter is a free online game — Just Point and Shoot. It's a rather simple game, but it does include some elements of cool strategy. You'll do well to upgrade your weapon in the beginning because you'll want to make sure you have a powerful gun!    \nTake control of a powerful armor that is armed with weapons and go on epic adventures in various missions, pass through simple tasks, eliminate hordes of attacking enemies and complete the main plot of this game and save the human race.    \nAlien Shooter is a classic game, you can play it online for free. It's one of the best Alien games.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2H2E5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40244,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8DO4T","slug":"undead-crate-boy","title":"Undead Crate Boy","description":"Jump around and shoot your way through enemies as you collect the crates in order to finish the level in this fun and addictive yet very challenging game! Shoot the monsters, jump around the screen and collect the crates! There are multiple enemies and different actions that help make this game more immersive!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8DO4T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/undead-crate-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":40243,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1P77","slug":"noob-escape-3d","title":"Noob Escape 3D","description":"In this game you have to go through 30 levels. The player on the way will be waiting for dangerous traps and very attentive pursuers.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1P77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-escape-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40243,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S7L58","slug":"ball-stars-2","title":"Ball Stars 2","description":"ball stars 2 is game arcade","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S7L58/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-stars-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40242,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4146E","slug":"keyton","title":"Keyton","description":"Keyton is a 2D Sci-fi themed platform game where your mission is to find and collect key cards to unlock the door while avoiding enemy robots and spikes. There are 8 levels to play. The difficulty increases as you proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" pr arrow keys for movement.        \nUse \"W\" or \"Up Arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4146E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/keyton/embed?sid=1","plays":40242,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MWO01","slug":"knife-thrower-memory-match","title":"Knife thrower Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Knife thrower Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Knife thrower Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Knife thrower Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MWO01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knife-thrower-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40242,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CI60B","slug":"zombiesmack","title":"ZombieSmack","description":"Kill and smash the zombie virus which attacked the world by surviving yourself. Defend yourself from the Zombie Mobs.\nHave fun by smashing, killing Zombies in this Zombie Smack Game.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CI60B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombiesmack/embed?sid=1","plays":40242,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SPSS1","slug":"sushi-escape","title":"Sushi Escape","description":"Sushi Escape is an endless run where all you have to do is press the up arrow to fly, making the \"nigiri\" avoid the obstacles. \nIn Sushi Escape you have another object: to collect the more soy sauces you can. When you avoid one obstacle, the score increases by one.\nReach an high score and achieve an always higher top score. \n\n*CREDITS*\n\nCODE, menu+gameover graphic: Samuele Gervasoni\n\nOther GRAPHICS: taken by itch.io \n\nMUSIC: Folk Chinese by PeriTune | http://peritune.com\nCreative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported License\nhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/deed.en_US\nMusic promoted by https://www.chosic.com/","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SPSS1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sushi-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":40242,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5723","slug":"test-love","title":"Test Love","description":"Have you ever wanted to find out how much that person likes you? Well, put the name of your dear friend and find out how much you match, haha. But don't be discouraged, he might like it a lot more than you think.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5723/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/test-love/embed?sid=1","plays":40241,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EATRE","slug":"red-and-green-christmas","title":"Red and Green Christmas","description":"How would you like to play the last and special part of the red and green game series? Unlike other series, there is a portal in the new year's special section, jump from the portal and overcome the obstacles, save your friend, reach the door, complete the sections.   \n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys            \n*Double Jump available            \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EATRE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-green-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40241,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40403","slug":"chess-challenges","title":"Chess Challenges","description":"Test your wits playing against Rupert the Red King and solve all challenges. Chess Challenges wraps up the chess experience as a series of puzzles, making it more casual but still quite challenging!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40403/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chess-challenges/embed?sid=1","plays":40240,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YE2L6","slug":"prickle-enemy-ball","title":"Prickle Enemy Ball","description":"A simple game to play, just touch your mouse on the ball and it will move automatically to the ball, and you will get the score, avoid the black enemies to get failed","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YE2L6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/prickle-enemy-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40239,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A9622","slug":"rude-races","title":"Rude Races","description":"Welcome to Rade Races, have fun in this game where you have to avoid obstacles to accumulate points and increase your bestscore, what are you waiting for?? go play Rude Races now and have fun!!!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A9622/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rude-races/embed?sid=1","plays":40239,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77A7L","slug":"4-colors-multiplayer","title":"4 Colors Multiplayer","description":"Four Colors is a HTML5 Card Games.\nFace up to 3 computer-controlled opponents.\nMatch cards by color or number, play action cards to mix the game up and be the first to get rid of all cards.\nLast but not least: Do not forget to press the 1 button when you have only one card left!\n\n3 Game’s Mode: \n- Multiplayer mode \n- Play against the pc \n- Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77A7L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/4-colors-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40238,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77HL5","slug":"planet-hop","title":"Planet Hop","description":"It's just a really simple endless hyper casual game! \nTry to avoid the Red triangle when you run; is simple: \nyou just make a jump! but you run in a planet so you need to resist the more you can and sign the best record possible! \nThis game i suitable for every one, enjoy it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77HL5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/planet-hop/embed?sid=1","plays":40238,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P0E6M","slug":"super-zombie-sniper","title":"Super Zombie Sniper","description":"Shoot all Zombies before the time is over!       \nEnjoy!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P0E6M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-zombie-sniper/embed?sid=1","plays":40238,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67UHA","slug":"akochan-quest","title":"Akochan Quest","description":"Akochan Quest is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as Akochan, a girl, who have to collect all of the necklaces while avoiding the zombies, the heart monsters, saws, rotating blades and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you continue.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67UHA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/akochan-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UO188","slug":"bhoolu-2","title":"Bhoolu 2","description":"Bhoolu 2 is a 2D platformer where you need to collect all of the candies while avoiding enemies, saws, spikes and reach the magic hole which leads you to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.       \nThis is the second installment of the original Bhoolu series. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UO188/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bhoolu-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6DB5B","slug":"birdy-bird","title":"Birdy Bird","description":"Welcome to Flying Bird, fly with your bird to overcome obstacles and accumulate as many points as possible","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6DB5B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/birdy-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O4S29","slug":"book-of-treasures-2-slots","title":"Book of Treasures 2 Slots","description":"This is a slot machine where you can win virtual coins.In this game, everything is for luck.\n Game Control: AUTO-button to automatically start the game.\nSTART-the button for manually starting the game.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O4S29/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bookoftreasures2/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4ATE4","slug":"centerball","title":"CenterBall","description":"Welcome to Center Ball, have fun making the background larger and without getting hit by the enemy, what are you waiting for ???? Go play Center Ball now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4ATE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/centerball/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EE1R","slug":"desert-survival","title":"Desert Survival","description":"Desert Survival Online Game is a fun, addictive and fast-paced game that lets you play in the desert. Desert Survival Online Game is a free online game that lets you survive in the desert. The game is designed to teach you about survival skills, and will also test your knowledge of the desert environment.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EE1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desert-survival-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"63A41","slug":"falling-blocks-2048-2d","title":"Falling Blocks 2048 - 2D","description":"Falling Blocks 2048 is an addictive block and number puzzle game that is great for brain training!\n\nWelcome to an incredibly addictive puzzle game with an original plot of events!\n\nFalling Blocks 2048 is a simple logical but difficult puzzle game to complete.\n\nThe graphics of the game are suitable for all ages, that game will be interesting to play for both children and adults!\n\n\nGame Features:\n⭐️ Availability of ready-made various themes.\n⭐️ A game for all ages.\n⭐️ Many auxiliary bonuses for passing the game\n⭐️ Night theme to relax your eyes and play comfortably before going to sleep.\n\n\nTrain, play and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/63A41/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-blocks-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N68LI","slug":"flying-pig-clicker","title":"Flying Pig Clicker","description":"Guide the flying pig through obstacles and feed him apples in order to get the highest score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N68LI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-pig-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L18HI","slug":"hill-monkey","title":"Hill Monkey","description":"Hill Monkey is an online hill climbing game that will test your agility and reflexes. In this game, you will need to use your monkey climbers to race up the hill as fast as you can. There are three different modes to choose from, and you can compete against other players from around the world. Whether you are a casual player or a competitive one, Hill Monkey will provide you with a fun and challenging experience.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L18HI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hill-monkey/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6OMN2","slug":"monkey-sky","title":"Monkey Sky","description":"Welcome to Monkey sky, try to be fast try to avoid the killing balls","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6OMN2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monkey-sky/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAMJR","slug":"run-jump-jumbo-runner","title":"Run & Jump Jumbo Runner","description":"Run & Jump: Jumbo Runner is an online runner game that will keep you on your toes! You'll need to use your quick reflexes to jump over obstacles and run to the finish line.    \n\"Run & Jump: Jumbo Runner online Runner Game\" is an addicting and exciting game that will keep you on your toes! With its simple controls, you can guide your runner through an endless course, avoiding obstacles and picking up power-ups along the way. The longer you stay alive, the higher your score will be. So put on your running shoes and see how far you can go in \"Run & Jump: Jumbo Runner online Runner Game\"!    ","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAMJR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ran-and-jump-jambo-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16W85","slug":"run-and-win","title":"Run and Win","description":"Welcome to the run and win game, select your car and try to win, your records remain recorded","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16W85/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-and-win/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"412D4","slug":"sandstrike-io","title":"SandStrike.io","description":"Are you ready for the ultimate adrenaline-fueled adventure in the desert? SandStrike is the game for you! This action-packed multiplayer shooting game is perfect for kids who want to experience the excitement of high-speed battles and outmaneuvering their opponents.\n\nWith four different game modes to choose from, including classic team deathmatch and capture the flag, SandStrike offers endless possibilities for thrilling gameplay. And with a wide range of customizable weapons and equipment, you can tailor your loadout to suit your play style and dominate the competition.\n\nSo what are you waiting for? Grab your friends and get ready to experience the ultimate in multiplayer shooting excitement with SandStrike. The battle for supremacy in the desert is on – are you ready to emerge victorious?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/412D4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sandstrike-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A3A7T","slug":"snoop-froggy","title":"Snoop Froggy","description":"Looking for some fun and exciting arcade games to play? Look no further than Snoop Froggy Arcade Pong Games! With a wide variety of games to choose from, there's sure to be something for everyone. So come on over and start playing today!    \nWelcome to the world of Snoop Froggy Arcade Pong! Here you can test your skills against other players from all around the world in exciting online games. Whether you're a seasoned pro or just starting out, we hope you'll have a blast playing our games. Thanks for tapping in!    \n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A3A7T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-frog/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4TEW5","slug":"tiger-jigsaw-image-challenge","title":"Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge","description":"Welcome to Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge! Our Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge picture. With a wide variety of Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Tiger Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4TEW5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiger-jigsaw-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ERUU9","slug":"tom-runner","title":"Tom Runner","description":"Tom Runner, join Tom and help him run through an endless level filled with various obstacles. How far do you think you can run without getting caught? Run To Run! The character must move and jump over obstacles as soon as he can. Your goal in this game is to make Tom run while avoiding obstacles as best as possible.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ERUU9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tomrunner/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A5MTD","slug":"undisputed-mma","title":"Undisputed MMA","description":"INSTRUCTIONS:\nKEYBOARD CONTROLS:\nW,A,S,D- FOR MOVEMENT\nJ- FOR PUNCHES\nL- FOR KICKS\nSHIFT- STRONG ATTACK MODIFIER(HOLD THE ATTACK BUTTON ON MOBILE DEVICES)\nI- TO BLOCK\nK- TO ATTEMPT A TAKEDOWN WHEN YOUR STAMINA (THE BLUE BAR) IS OVER 50%\nM- FOR A SUBMISSION WHEN YOU'RE IN MOUNT POSITION\nK- WHEN THE RED MARKER IS OVERLAPPING THE BLUE BAR TO SUCCESSFULLY PERFORM OR ESCAPE A TAKEDOWN ATTEMPT OR SUCCESSFULLY PERFORM A SUBMISSION\n\nTHERE ARE TOUCH CONTROLS FOR MOBILE DEVICES\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nUPDATE 17!!!\nIMPROVED AI WITH QUICKER RESPONSE TIME\n\nWHAT'S NEW?\n-YOU CAN NOW PLAY CAREER MODE, KINDA.\n-SOUNDS! SOUNDS!! SOUNDS!!! - SFX, MUSIC AND CAMERA OPTIONS\n-A REFEREE\n-NEW HEALTH SYSTEM\n-SOME OTHER RANDOM FIXES\n\nYOUTUBE:\nyoutube.com/channel/UCHHQcN6tMElKGcPjAmmVzFQ\n\nWHAT TO EXPECT:\n-CAREER MODE UPDATES\n-NEW ARENAS\n-GAMEPAD SUPPORT\n-MORE FIGHTERS AND WEIGHT CLASSES\nAND IN THE FUTURE\n-CHARACTER CREATION\n-I'LL EVENTUALLY GET AROUND TO MAKING AN IN GAME TUTORIAL. FOR NOW, THE CONTROLS ARE LISTED ABOVE","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A5MTD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/undisputed-mma/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ME44M","slug":"unno-game","title":"Unno Game","description":"Uno Card Game the fun, classic card game that is the favourite of all the card games. Its really easy to pick up and play and difficult to put down. Its simple to play but still has a strategic component to it \n \nThe objective of Uno Card Game is to empty all your cards before the other players get rid of theirs. The player reduces cards by discarding cards that match the top card in the Discard pile.","category":"Course","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ME44M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/uno-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22MGM","slug":"brain-games-2","title":"Brain games 2","description":"This is the second Brain Games.\nBrain Games is a series of challenges, riddles and puzzles. Test your logical thinking, accuracy, memory and creativity and have fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22MGM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-games-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I79A4","slug":"ballmania","title":"BallMania","description":"Can you catch the marble without being hit by the marble that kills you?","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I79A4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballmania/embed?sid=1","plays":40237,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1NF2K","slug":"kingdom-of-ninja-3","title":"Kingdom of Ninja 3","description":"Hello from the 3 series of kingdom of ninja game. Remember you are a ninja and you have to pass various monsters, some are flying and some are crawling. watch out for all of them they may kill you. Kingdom of ninja 3 game, which consists of 15 different levels, will challenge you. If you want to join this adventure, what are you waiting for?   \n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1NF2K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kingdom-of-ninja-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40236,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OR94E","slug":"pcasteroid","title":"PcAsteroid","description":"Welcome to PCAsteroid, have fun among the meteors to defeat your opponents and collect as many coins as possible. What are you waiting for??? Go play PCAsteroid now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!!!!!!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OR94E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pcasteroid/embed?sid=1","plays":40236,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20037","slug":"adventures-of-indiara","title":"Adventures of Indiara","description":"Les aventures d'Indiara commencent! Incarnez Indiara, une jeune aventurière qui adore collectionner d'anciens artefacts. Elle doit maintenant récupérer 8 crânes dorés qui se trouvent dans une grotte infestée de pièges mortels. Et pour couronner le tout, un gigantesque rocher roule à toute vitesse vers elle! Aidez-la vite à s'échapper!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20037/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventures-of-indiara/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"118AR","slug":"emperor-julius-caesar-memory-match","title":"Emperor Julius Caesar Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Emperor Julius Caesar Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Emperor Julius Caesar Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Emperor Julius Caesar Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/118AR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emperor-julius-caesar-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ONI6","slug":"inuko","title":"Inuko","description":"Inuko is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the orange ice cream while avoiding the enemies, spikes, saws and giant blades and reach the purple flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.         \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ONI6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/inuko/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N2578","slug":"nekoman-vs-gangster-2","title":"Nekoman vs Gangster 2","description":"Nekoman vs Gangster 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as a cat who have to collect all of the silver keys while avoiding the Gangsters, and their bullets, saws and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Nekoman vs Gangster\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.         \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N2578/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nekoman-vs-gangster-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MRI9M","slug":"trezimon2","title":"TreZimon2","description":"Do you have a good memory ?! Try it on this clone of the famous game Simon. With 4 levels. Memorize the color of the sequence, and repeat it!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MRI9M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trezimon2/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7G4YA","slug":"among-yetto-bots","title":"Among Yetto Bots","description":"Among Yetto Bots is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect all of the golden balls while avoiding the enemy bots, flying bots and their bullets, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7G4YA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/among-yetto-bots/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"581A6","slug":"avatar-the-way-of-love-dress-up","title":"Avatar The Way Of Love Dress-up","description":"Welcome to Avatar The Way Of Love. Can you guess what day it is? Okay, maybe we can give you a clue. Love is in the air tonight. Yeah, it’s Valentine’s Day alright. These Avatar couples love to spend time together this valentine’s in the city. They plan to wear new trendy clothes. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/581A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/avatar-the-way-of-love/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"047IE","slug":"nice-diamont","title":"Nice Diamont","description":"Welcome to Nice Diamont, the game is about collecting as many diamonds as possible, but you have to be careful of the snake and the spiders that will try to kill you. Have fun","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/047IE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nice-diamont/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CNOWB","slug":"rainbow-with-pot-of-gold-coloring-pages","title":"Rainbow With Pot Of Gold Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Rainbow With Pot Of Gold Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Rainbow With Pot Of Gold Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Rainbow With Pot Of Gold Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Rainbow With Pot Of Gold Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CNOWB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-with-pot-of-gold-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7JAA","slug":"the-jersey-devil-image-scramble","title":"The Jersey Devil Image scramble","description":"Welcome to The Jersey Devil Image scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Jersey Devil Image scramble, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Jersey Devil Image scramble and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7JAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-jersey-devil-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7HI6I","slug":"zig-zag-switch","title":"Zig Zag Switch","description":"Zig Zag game where the ball moving like zigzag so come and zig zag our ball you will zigzag the ball till you reach the end fun zigzag game come and join us","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7HI6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zig-zag-swiitch/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TS6EB","slug":"kawaii-levi-slider-block-blitz","title":"Kawaii Levi Slider Block Blitz","description":"Welcome to Kawaii Levi Slider Block Blitz, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Kawaii Levi Slider Block Blitz, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Kawaii Levi Slider Block Blitz and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TS6EB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kawaii-levi-slider-block-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":40235,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"28EES","slug":"pigeons-pigeons","title":"Pigeons Pigeons","description":"Everybody knows that pigeons are the greatest menace to the safety of the humankind, but no one in world has the courage to face them and erase them from earth. There is an exception though, and that exception is you!\nTake the shotgun and free the world from the most nasty creature that has ever existed.\n\nFeatures:\n30 Levels\n1 Shotgun\n12 Different kinds of pigeons\nDestructable Objects\nAn ending with an unexpected twist...\n\nGAME CONTROLS:\nTouch to shoot when the viewfinder is above the pigeon","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/28EES/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pigeons-pigeons/embed?sid=1","plays":40234,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46SO5","slug":"crash-the-comet","title":"Crash the Comet","description":"Basically you need to control the comet, and keep it flying on the track.\nLook easy, but the comet will continue speed up. It is not easy!\n\nSpecially on two hands mode, you may crash immediately. \n\nRemember, this game is challenging your brain.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46SO5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crash-the-comet/embed?sid=1","plays":40234,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UR1KO","slug":"fast-furious-skyline","title":"Fast Furious Skyline","description":"Beat 2 different survival games with skyline, which is the best of cars, and collect the score and get the rank and hat you deserve. Legendary hats are waiting for you. If you want to own a hat, hurry up! start Game!\n\nHow to Play?\nArrow Keys and Space Button / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UR1KO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fast-furious-skyline/embed?sid=1","plays":40231,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RPW47","slug":"super-crowd","title":"Super Crowd","description":"Super Crowd, a hyper-casual fighting game that's all about high-energy action. Your goal is straightforward: navigate through dynamic tracks, grow your crowd by strategically adding characters, collect money, and dodge those tricky spinning spikes and laser blasters. The intensity builds as you advance, leading to an epic face-off against a massive wave of monsters at the end. Use strategy to emerge victorious. Beyond survival, Super Crowd is a journey of growth – unlock new skins, as well as hats for your leader, exhibit your style, and revel in the satisfaction of achieving new records.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RPW47/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-crowd/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0B31I","slug":"grand-skibidi-town-2","title":"Grand Skibidi Town 2","description":"Grand Skibidi Town 2 features sandbox style gameplay with big city to explore and variety of cars to drive, your mission is to shoot given amount of skibidi toilets in order to progress and unlock new weapons.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0B31I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-skibidi-town-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N17ER","slug":"evolution-of-hamster-clicker","title":"Evolution of hamster - Clicker","description":"\"Evolution of hamster: Clicker\" is a game about the hard life of a hamster. Find out what you can become!\n\n- Make the critter rich by earning 5 QUINTILLION points.\n- See how much you can transform yourself. And become the best hamster ever.\n- Don't waste your time, start now!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N17ER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evolution-of-hamster-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00T73","slug":"tank-1990","title":"Tank 1990","description":"$1c","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00T73/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tank-1990/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HEGG0","slug":"charlie-charlie-challenge","title":"Charlie-Charlie Challenge","description":"The Charlie Charlie Challenge is a divination game in which the putative answer to a yes–no question is found by waiting for a balanced pencil to point towards the word “Yes” or “No” written on a sheet of paper.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HEGG0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/charlie-charlie-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40WEM","slug":"mixed-up-power-ups","title":"Mixed Up Power Ups","description":"A small 2D platformer with interesting powerup mechanics.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40WEM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mixed-up-power-ups/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1736","slug":"gt-cars-super-racing","title":"GT Cars Super Racing","description":"Get into the adrenaline-pumping world of GT Car Super Racing, a game that pays homage to the classic arcade racing games of the 80s.\nFeaturing fantastic gameplay and a precise car control system, the experience unfolds across 21 diverse circuits with numerous surprises awaiting discovery.\nVibrant and detailed graphics, coupled with an impeccable car control system, deliver an immersive racing adventure.\nRevel in the engine sounds as you maintain optimal speed, strategically deploying the turbo for that crucial boost.\nWith its compelling features, GT Car Super Racing stands out as a top-tier rally arcade racing game.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1736/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gt-car-super-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"24P66","slug":"motocross-jumper","title":"Motocross Jumper","description":"Motocross Jumper game with realistic physics, fun and nice graphics!!! Motocross features many cool tricks, including multiple animation states depending on the bikers actions. Perform tricks, 360, wheelies, front ends and more.\nControl the bike as you perform cool tricks and pull off some in-air stunts. The mechanics include crash detection, with animations and various physics detection routines.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/24P66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motocross-jumper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11H3D","slug":"wood-whacker","title":"Wood Whacker","description":"Welcome to Wood Whacker, where your lumberjack skills are put to the test as you chop wood and dodge branches! Think its an easy task?\nThink again! While the gameplay is simple to grasp, mastering it is a whole different challenge.\nWith two variable environments and 10 characters to unlock, the excitement never ends! So grab your axe, rush through the forest, and chop those trees as fast as you can! Wood Whacker offers a one-touch control system, addictive gameplay, and a nostalgic arcade style experience thats completely free!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11H3D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wood-whacker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3188","slug":"tiny-cars","title":"Tiny Cars","description":"Experience the adrenaline in pixel-art style with Tinycars, an exhilarating top-down racing game by Mapi.\nIgnite the tracks on 15 diverse circuits, competing against 6 rivals in this captivating arcade racing adventure.\nEmploy every cunning maneuver at your disposal, including shortcuts, teleports, electric weapons, and nitro speed bursts, to outpace your opponents and etch your name in the hall of fame while unlocking even more thrilling tracks.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3188/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-cars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8C17N","slug":"dinos-coloring-book","title":"Dinos Coloring Book","description":"Coloring Dinosaurs Book is a painting, drawing and coloring game for kids! Hello my little friend, have fun with Dinosaurs in this fantastic Coloring App designed especially for you! It will be fantastic to watch your baby coloring, interacting, having fun and improving his technique thanks to this fantastic musical and educational application. The game is a classic color the dinosaurs but you can choose to color them freehand or you can choose the version where you click on the images to color them.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8C17N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dinos-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YY20P","slug":"pop-it-party","title":"Pop It Party","description":"Pop It Party is a fun relaxing game and a unique game to play on.\nThis is a super relaxing game to play for hours; we have got different shapes of pop gadgets, click on the pops to smash them and clear the board, Enjoy it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YY20P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-it-party/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DC0IM","slug":"empire-estate-kingdom-conquest","title":"Empire Estate - Kingdom Conquest","description":"Welcome to Empire Estate - Kingdom Conquest, where strategic prowess meets real estate \ndominance in the ultimate buying and selling extravaganza for up to 4 players. Build your '\nempire, negotiate shrewd deals, and outmaneuver your opponents to become the undisputed tycoon \nof the game. With its key features, Empire Estate - Kingdom Conquest offers a thrilling digital \nadaptation of the classic board game, ensuring hours of competitive and strategic fun for you and \nyour friends.\n\nKey Features:\nEmpire Building Beyond the Board\nInteractive Auctions and Negotiations\nMultiplayer Showdowns and Alliances","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DC0IM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/empire-estate-kingdom-conquest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1DSU","slug":"duck-dash-hunter-s-challenge","title":"Duck Dash - Hunter's Challenge","description":"Duck Dash invites you to step into the immersive world of duck hunting, where you and your trusty \ncanine companion embark on an exciting arcade mobile adventure. Immerse yourself in the thrill of \nthe hunt as you navigate lush landscapes and aim to outsmart and outshoot your feathered adversaries. \nWith dynamic gameplay, Duck Dash delivers an engaging experience that will keep you hooked from the \nfirst shot to the final quack.\n\nFeatures:\nDynamic Hunting Grounds\nCanine Companion AI\nAngle Upgrades and Customization","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1DSU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duck-dash-hunter-s-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7IIA1","slug":"alien-spaceship-chaos","title":"Alien Spaceship Chaos","description":"alien spaceship chaos is an html5 spaceshooter game, shoot the enemies that come, get items to upgrade weapons and also get the highest score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7IIA1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-spaceship-chaos/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ERC5T","slug":"cartoon-space","title":"Cartoon Space","description":"cartoon space is a casual html5 game, move to the star image and wait after that the shot has moved","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ERC5T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cartoon-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3NJJ0","slug":"block-ninja","title":"Block Ninja","description":"block ninja swipe is an html5 arcade game, control 2 ninjas up and down so they don't hit the obstacles","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3NJJ0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-ninja-swipe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M0E14","slug":"animal-kids-memory","title":"Animal Kids Memory","description":"animal kids memory is a brain memory game for children, sharpen children's brain skills by playing this game by matching the same pictures when the cards are opened","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M0E14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animal-kids-memory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9C7HH","slug":"alien-shooting-block","title":"Alien Shooting Block","description":"alien shooting block is an html5 arcade shooting game, pull and shoot blocks and get stars for the score\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9C7HH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-shooting-block/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E3I68","slug":"double-driver","title":"Double Driver","description":"Double Driver is an HTML5 car game, control 2 cars at the same time, avoid obstacles, get petrol for the score\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E3I68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/double-driver/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VN11E","slug":"redneck-vs-zombie","title":"Redneck vs Zombie","description":"redneck vs zombies is an html5 arcade jumping game, run and jump up avoid the obstacles that come and shoot the zombies","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VN11E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redneck-vs-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"972EM","slug":"mini-soccer","title":"Mini Soccer","description":"Mini Soccer is a casual HTML5 game, drag and shoot the ball into the enemy's goal and be the winner\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/972EM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-soccer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1OR6","slug":"noobs-arena-bedwars","title":"Noobs Arena Bedwars","description":"Are you ready for the noobs battle? You need to defend your bed. Quickly collect coins and buy cannonballs. Fire the cannonballs from the cannon to break the bed. The first one to break the bed wins. Fire the cannonball to explode the bed. Fight with your friend and win this battle.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*Press the Bottom Arrow key and the S key to fire and buy cannons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1OR6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noobs-arena-bedwars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11RE7","slug":"friends-battle-gunwars","title":"Friends Battle Gunwars","description":"In the new game of the Friends Battle series, weapons are drawn and magazines are loaded. Fire your weapon and hit your friend. The fastest and most skilled shooter wins. Shoot the flying drops in the game and change your weapon. Remember, the red team starts with a shotgun and the blue team with an assault rifle, but you can change these weapons. The one who takes 20 bullets loses the game. To win, you must dodge bullets, collect drops, and defeat your enemy.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*Hit twenty times, lose.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11RE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-gunwars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HMT7T","slug":"temple-battle-lightsaber","title":"Temple Battle Lightsaber","description":"Are you ready to fight with your friend? Engage in battle with your friend and the one who achieves the most kills wins.Swords drawn. Beam swords ready. Fight with your friend and be the winner of the temple. Choose to be from the blue or red team and kill the opposing team to win. You must be careful, poisonous water is rising every second. If you touch the poisonous water, you die. Also, watch out for the TNT falling from above, as they can kill you too. Survive and kill to win.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*The one who reaches 10 kills wins.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HMT7T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/temple-battle-lightsaber/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"038SA","slug":"gunwars","title":"Gunwars","description":"Guns drawn, are you ready to battle with your friend? Grab your weapon and fire away. You need to fight against your friend. Be either the red or blue player and shoot with your gun. Defeat your friend. The one who hits the most wins. There are drop balloons passing by in the air, find them and change your weapon. Remember, each weapon has its own unique features, so every weapon is powerful.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*The one who gets hit 20 times loses.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/038SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gunwars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"077AD","slug":"friends-battle-water-die","title":"Friends Battle Water Die","description":"Are you ready to fight with your friend? Engage in battle with your friend and the one who achieves the most kills wins. You must fight with your friend. Draw your sword and be ready for battle. The water is rising every second, so you must be very careful of the water. The water will kill you; fight with your friend before the water comes and reach the highest kill count.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*The one who reaches 10 kills wins.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/077AD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-water-die/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UUNDE","slug":"friends-battle-crepgun","title":"Friends Battle Crepgun","description":"Are you ready to battle with your friend? Arrows are coming from all directions, so be careful. If you want to defeat your friend, you must avoid the arrows. If you can go on without getting hit by arrows for 10 seconds, you win the game. Every time an arrow hits you, the duration will increase by 1 second, so you must be very careful. You need to defeat your friend. Beat your friend and be the winner. You have 10 seconds to win. Be very careful, arrows are everywhere.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*Dodge arrows for 10 seconds and win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UUNDE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-crepgun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0F0IA","slug":"friends-battle-diamonds","title":"Friends Battle Diamonds","description":"Hey! Are you or your friend going to collect diamonds faster? Lets see. You need to collect diamonds, and the one who collects them the fastest wins. Are you up for a friendly match with your friend? Race and be the quickest to collect the diamonds. Collect the diamond and head to the chest.\n\n*The red player moves using the WASD keys. \n*The blue player moves using the arrow keys.\n*Collect 20 diamonds and win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0F0IA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-diamonds/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"142T9","slug":"red-and-blue-castlewars","title":"Red and Blue Castlewars","description":"Are you ready to battle your friend? Throw cannonballs at your buddy and destroy their castle. Are you up for the red versus blue cannonball fight? Load up the cannon and fire away. Purchase a cannonball and launch it. The first castle to crumble wins. Battle your friend and emerge victorious.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/142T9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-and-blue-castlewars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DP1E0","slug":"poke-the-presidents","title":"Poke The Presidents","description":"\"Poke the President\" is the perfect stress-reliever game. Defeat politicians by throwing various weapons. The objective is to creatively inflict damage upon the politicians and watch them react in humorous and exaggerated ways. Earn money to buy various weapons and items in the shop. Have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DP1E0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poke-the-presidents/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17OI5","slug":"diner-in-the-storm","title":"Diner in the Storm","description":"Diner in the Storm is a thrilling escape game where you take shelter in a diner from a sudden storm. You are safe for now, but its not long before you realize theres something dangerous outside the thin diner walls. Leaving is easy, but convincing everyone else to come with you might not be.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17OI5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/diner-in-the-storm/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C7O70","slug":"abcpop","title":"ABCpop","description":"Learn capital letters with ABCPop, the game that mixes letters and pop-it. Relax by completing the pop-it capital letters. If you take too long, the bubbles return to their original position.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C7O70/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/abcpop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EM92D","slug":"grandma-recipe-ramen","title":"Grandma Recipe Ramen","description":"It's time to serve a delicious Ramen! Ask grandma for the recipe. Prepare the tools and gather the ingredients. Mix the ingredients perfectly, then decorate the Ramen. Keep following grandma's instructions to finish making the Ramen! Don't forget to dress up in various cute costumes. Making Ramen has never been more fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EM92D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grandma-recipe-ramen/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55LNC","slug":"ball-balance-challenge","title":"Ball Balance Challenge","description":"Unique physics game where you try to score the most points by guiding the ball by tilting the series of balance beams.\nThe faster you are the more points you score and climb to the top of the leader board.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55LNC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-balance-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"04H04","slug":"sky-clash-air-hockey-vs-pong","title":"Sky Clash Air Hockey vs. Pong","description":"2 Sport games\nAir Hockey and Pong Game","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/04H04/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-clash-air-hockey-vs-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9IER8","slug":"dragon-s-defense-reign-of-fire","title":"Dragon's Defense Reign of Fire","description":"Control the dragon, defend your kingdom against enemy invasion","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9IER8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dragon-s-defense-reign-of-fire/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2CELL","slug":"police-craft-block-car-race","title":"Police Craft Block Car Race","description":"Take the wheel of your blocky police vehicle in this adrenaline-fueled mobile game! Race against other players, showcasing your speed and skill to emerge victorious.\nNavigate through dynamic environments, dodging obstacles and outmaneuvering opponents to claim the top spot. Are you ready to show off your driving prowess and dominate the competition\n\nUse left and right arrows to rotate your police Car in the Air. press up to accelerate","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2CELL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/police-craft-block-car-race/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9IVAA","slug":"city-apocalypse-zombies-invasion","title":"City Apocalypse Zombies Invasion","description":"Shoot the zombies attacking people in the city. If one zombie kills a human, you lose the game. Collect ammunition and be quick.\n\nPress 'X' to shoot, press 'Z' to detonate, and use the left and right arrow keys to move your scope\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9IVAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-apocalypse-zombies-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0017R","slug":"blocks-army-craft","title":"Blocks Army Craft","description":"Shoot at the block opponent hiding behind obstacles, each hit on the block destroys it, hitting the figure wins the level\n\nKeyboard: \"Press and hold the left mouse button to shoot. Holding the button longer increases the speed of your shooting.Mobile: \"Press and hold anywhere on the screen to shoot. The longer you hold your finger, the faster your shooting speed becomes","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0017R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocks-army-craft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NN87D","slug":"old-man-and-demon","title":"Old Man and Demon","description":"What are you ready for for your friend? Are you ready to fight the devil himself? You decide what you are capable of!\nAbout the game\nThe player will have to go through all the horrors of hell and meet Satan himself! All this to save your friend!\nThe game has one large underground world full of creepy, dangerous monsters and deadly traps.\nHow to play\nMove carefully, the dim light of a lantern is the only hope for salvation.\nWatch your step and avoid monsters! Find a way out and save your friend.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NN87D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/old-man-and-demon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65ULZ","slug":"blocks-of-puzzle","title":"Blocks of Puzzle","description":"$1d","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65ULZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocks-of-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EA23","slug":"crazy-ball-space","title":"Crazy Ball Space","description":"It is a trial of my first game development by HTML5 series.\nit's quite interesting game.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EA23/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-ball-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"997S7","slug":"help-me-story-tricky","title":"Help Me Story Tricky","description":"Help Me Story Tricky est un jeu de puzzle comportant de nombreuses énigmes et puzzles délicats. Il existe plus de 275 niveaux de casse-tête conçus pour tromper le joueur et tester son cerveau. Réfléchissez sur vos pieds et sortez des sentiers battus pour résoudre ces énigmes. Tout ce que vous voyez à l'écran peut être utilisé pour résoudre le problème. Toutes les questions divertissantes de Brain Test vous épateront !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/997S7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/help-me-story-tricky/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U17RU","slug":"cat-sorter-puzzle","title":"Cat Sorter Puzzle","description":"Voilà un vrai chaos félin ! Ces adorables boules de poils espiègles se sont installées dans différents sièges et attendent que quelqu’un de suffisamment futé vienne les empiler par couleur.\n\nConcentrez-vous et faites bon usage de votre esprit logique pour obtenir les meilleurs scores dans ce jeu de réflexion.\n\nVous y trouverez divers modes de jeux avec des règles distinctes, de nombreux niveaux à difficulté croissante, et des mini-jeux. En somme, c’est un excellent moyen de passer un bon moment tout en améliorant votre concentration!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U17RU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-sorter-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2A91N","slug":"scaler-adventure","title":"Scaler Adventure","description":"The game \"Scaler Adventure\" is an interesting puzzle game about a dungeon explorer, a Scaler, and his drone. Resize items to go through all the rooms and send the results to your company. Carry items by drone, thanks to the hook, to activate all the switches and open the main door. Use your logic and ingenuity to the maximum to complete all levels!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2A91N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scaler-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HHEAU","slug":"bubble-shot-master","title":"Bubble Shot Master","description":"$1e","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HHEAU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-shot-master-classic-bubble-shooter-match-3-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U10NH","slug":"pac-rush-man","title":"Pac Rush Man","description":"Pac-Man\" is a classic arcade game originally released by Namco in 1980. It quickly became one of the most iconic and recognizable video games of all time. In \"Pac-Man,\" players control the titular character, a yellow, circular creature with a large mouth, navigating through a maze-like grid filled with dots or pellets.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U10NH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pac-rush-man/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"027CL","slug":"poppy-playtime-chapter-3-jigsaw-puzzle","title":"Poppy Playtime Chapter 3 jigsaw puzzle","description":"Casse-tête Poppy Playtime Chapitre 3\nc'est le premier jeu à utiliser ce format et cette image spécifiques, ce sera donc une toute nouvelle expérience pour vous tous.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/027CL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-playtime-chapter-3-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A56SA","slug":"mr-macagi-adventures","title":"Mr. Macagi Adventures","description":"Embark on a daring expedition through the whimsical landscapes of Mr. Macagi's Adventure! \n\nGuide Mr. Macagi through perilous terrains, braving cunning monsters. With 4 stages set amidst the dense foliage of the forest and 4 in the unforgiving heat of the desert, prepare for a test of skill and strategy.\n\nCan you help Mr. Macagi collect apples and gold coins, and outsmart the cunning monsters that inhabit them? Explore, strategize, and conquer in this thrilling platformer adventure!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A56SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-macagi-adventures/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"REB1H","slug":"turbo-cars-challenge","title":"Turbo Cars Challenge","description":"Take control of high-speed racing action right in the palm of your hand with our thrilling mobile game! Navigate your car through intense arena races, where every turn and every drift counts. Win heart-pounding duels against fierce opponents, showcasing your skills and dominating the competition\n\n\nUse arrow keys on keyboard to steer your car","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/REB1H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/turbo-cars-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"QRLAB","slug":"blocks-dash-jump-square","title":"Blocks Dash Jump Square","description":"Navigate a bouncing square through a maze of obstacles for endless fun!\npress the left mouse button or touch the screen on your phone to jump, passing obstacles on your way\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/QRLAB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocks-dash-jump-square/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8MZE2","slug":"zombie-siege-commando-warfare","title":"Zombie Siege Commando Warfare","description":"Engage in an epic battle against hordes of invading zombies as you step into the shoes of a super commando armed with an array of unique weapon. Your mission: to decimate the relentless army of enemy zombies lurking on the horizon. Brace yourself for intense action as you strategically navigate the battlefield, unleashing devastating firepower to obliterate everything in your path. It's a relentless fight for survival, where every shot counts in your quest to thwart the monstrous invasion and emerge victorious\n\nKeyboard: \"Press and hold the left mouse button to shoot. Holding the button longer increases the speed of your shooting.Mobile: \"Press and hold anywhere on the screen to shoot. The longer you hold your finger, the faster your shooting speed becomes.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8MZE2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-siege-commando-warfare/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5TVE7","slug":"crystal-flight-aztec-adventure","title":"Crystal Flight Aztec Adventure","description":"Control a flying character with a jetpack in the Aztec world, avoiding traps that can kill upon touch, collecting crystals, and fly as far as possible\n\nTo fly, press or hold down the left mouse button. On your phone, hold your finger anywhere on the screen. When you release your finger, the character descends","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5TVE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crystal-flight-aztec-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7E1AC","slug":"archer-arcane","title":"Archer Arcane","description":"Archer Arcane est un jeu d'aventure fantastique où vous incarnez - vous l'avez deviné - un archer ! Prenez votre arc et vos flèches, frayez-vous un chemin à travers des hordes de monstres et évitez les obstacles dangereux. À la fin de chaque niveau, une amélioration magique vous attend.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7E1AC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archer-arcane/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC8DT","slug":"cosmic-defender-space-assault","title":"Cosmic Defender Space Assault","description":"Take control of your spaceship and fend off incoming enemies\" in this thrilling arcade shooter.\n\nKeyboard: Use arrows to move your ship left or right, space to shoot. Mobile: Use buttons to move your ship, use the red button to fire","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC8DT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cosmic-defender-space-assault/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B2L12","slug":"blocky-vs-zombies","title":"Blocky VS Zombies","description":"Dans Blocky VS Zombies, vous partez à l'aventure dans un monde rempli de monstres ! Avec votre fidèle arc et votre hache, c'est à vous de vaincre des hordes de zombies, de squelettes et d'autres ennemis. Pour y parvenir, vous devrez devenir fort ! Couper du bois vous aidera à devenir un archer meilleur et plus rapide, tandis que dépenser des pièces vous aidera à couper du bois plus rapidement. En améliorant les deux, vous deviendrez la meilleure combinaison d'un bûcheron et d'un archer en un rien de temps ! Parviendrez-vous à vaincre tous les boss, à réparer le portail et à rentrer chez vous ?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B2L12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocky-vs-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"80A73","slug":"basketball-2024","title":"Basketball 2024","description":"30-Second Hoop Challenge: Aim for the Basket and Collect Stars for Bonus Points\n\nObstacle Slam Dunk: Use Obstacles to Bounce the Ball and Score!\n\nBasketball Flicker: Aim and Flick the Mouse to Shoot the Ball!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/80A73/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5755T","slug":"basketball-arena-ultimate-hoops-showdown","title":"Basketball Arena Ultimate Hoops Showdown","description":" Aim and Flick the Mouse to Shoot the Ball!\n\n\t.\tStart by pressing the left button anywhere on the screen.\n\t.\tWhile holding down the button, slide it to increase the power of your ball throw.\n\t.\tRelease the button to throw the ball.\nRemember, you only have three ball throws per level, so use them wisely!\nEnjoy the game and make those shots count!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5755T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-arena-ultimate-hoops-showdown/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YOTR0","slug":"pomni-circus-ball-toy-collector","title":"Pomni Circus Ball Toy Collector","description":"Join the Digital Circus Ball on its journey through a whimsical world of circus wonders! Help the playful little black ball collect pomni toys while navigating through thrilling challenges. Fun for all ages\n\nKeyboard: Use the left and right arrows to move your character\nMobile: Touch the left or right side button to move your character","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YOTR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pomni-circus-ball-toy-collector/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U7001","slug":"ball-bounce","title":"Ball Bounce","description":"Ball Bounce is a casual game that is very fun and challenging. Your task is to guide the ball which continues to bounce towards the portal while passing through obstacles","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U7001/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bounce-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H57C7","slug":"rocketto-dash","title":"Rocketto Dash","description":"Roketto dash is a running game that makes players addicted, control a rocket that continues to accelerate to avoid obstacles while enjoying music that matches the gameplay, collect coins and diamonds and complete each challenging level","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H57C7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UP161","slug":"popsicle-jigsaw-puzzle-quest","title":"Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest","description":"Welcome to Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest! Our Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest picture. With a wide variety of Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Popsicle Jigsaw Puzzle Quest Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UP161/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popsicle-jigsaw-puzzle-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8P0O8","slug":"flower-tile-block-puzzle","title":"Flower Tile Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Flower Tile Block Puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Flower Tile Block Puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Flower Tile Block Puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8P0O8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flower-tile-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62TW7","slug":"groot-jigsaw-tile-mania","title":"Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania","description":"Welcome to Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania! Our Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania picture. With a wide variety of Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Groot Jigsaw Tile Mania Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62TW7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/groot-jigsaw-tile-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AASAA","slug":"valentine-s-day-slider-image-scramble","title":"Valentine s Day Slider Image Scramble","description":"Welcome to Valentine s Day Slider Image Scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Valentine s Day Slider Image Scramble, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Valentine s Day Slider Image Scramble and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AASAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/valentine-s-day-slider-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"080Y0","slug":"fall-words","title":"Fall Words","description":"$1f","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/080Y0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fall-words-physics-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"STS1T","slug":"princesses-waiting-for-santa","title":"Princesses Waiting For Santa","description":"Princesses Waiting For Santa invites you to a world of fashion and creativity! Mix and match stunning outfits in this dress-up game, specially designed for girls. In Princesses Waiting For Santa, you'll discover an endless variety of styles and accessories, ensuring every creation in Princesses Waiting For Santa is uniquely yours. Dive into the fun of styling in Princesses Waiting For Santa!\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/STS1T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princesses-waiting-for-santa/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AMSI1","slug":"christmas-mandala-coloring-book","title":"Christmas Mandala Coloring Book","description":"Calling all coloring connoisseurs! Christmas Mandala Coloring Book is the quintessential coloring game that blends fun with relaxation. Whether you're into doodling, painting, or coloring, this game has it all. With an easy-to-navigate interface and a vast selection of coloring pages, Christmas Mandala Coloring Book is perfect for artists of every skill level.\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AMSI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-mandala-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G7SG3","slug":"easter-egg-coloring-games","title":"Easter Egg Coloring Games","description":"Easter Egg Coloring Games invites you to a painter's paradise! With an endless array of coloring pages featuring animals, nature, and abstract patterns, this game is a dream for coloring enthusiasts. Dive into this coloring journey, mix and match hues, and give each painting your personal touch. Come express yourself in Easter Egg Coloring Games and create your masterpiece!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G7SG3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/easter-egg-coloring-games/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ICA70","slug":"the-prison-escape","title":"The Prison Escape","description":"Des prisonniers se sont échappés de votre emprise ! Montez dans la voiture et poursuivez-les. Méfiez-vous du sentier dangereux entouré de falaises ! Remettez les prisonniers capturés au travail.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ICA70/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-prison-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FRMBL","slug":"farm-block-puzzle","title":"Farm Block Puzzle","description":"C'est le jeu parfait pour satisfaire votre envie d'un jeu logique inspiré de Tétris avec une touche de fraîcheur. L'esthétique champêtre captera votre attention avec ses beaux graphismes et sa musique agréable. \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FRMBL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/farm-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ORDU5","slug":"pet-s-adventure-a-day-to-remember","title":"Pet's Adventure A Day To Remember","description":"Join Midge, Polly, Doug, Cooper, and Luca in the wildest Petventure! Each pet has a unique quest: Midge craves a glamorous makeover, Polly prepares for Coronation Couture, Doug tackles mud clean-up, Cooper heals wounds, while Luca embarks on adventure dress-up! Experience the chaos, silliness, and giggles as they chase joy together. Dive into a world of laughter and create pet-tastic memories that last a lifetime! Get ready to embark on an unforgettable journey with these adorable buddies!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ORDU5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pet-s-adventure-a-day-to-remember/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BKO42","slug":"bff-st-patrick-s-day-look","title":"Bff St Patrick's day Look","description":" Welcome to Bff St Patrick’s day Look. Have you ever heard about St. Patrick’s Day? Prepare your girlfriends for the holiday party in the game BFF St. Patricks Day game. The main color of the holiday is green, so the outfits are mainly made in this color. First, select a unique outfit, hat, hairstyle, and stylish accessories.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BKO42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-st-patrick-s-day-look/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KD1FA","slug":"bff-st-patrick-s-day-preparation","title":"BFF St Patrick's day Preparation","description":"Hey Girls! These cute princess are ready for patricks day celebration. So help them to prepare for the carnival by choosing best outfit, hairstyles and accessories. And also help them to decor their hats. It will become so much fun and excitement. Help them.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KD1FA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-st-patrick-s-day-preparation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7R2A9","slug":"stellar-style-spectacle-fashion","title":"Stellar Style Spectacle Fashion","description":"Stellar Style Spectacle Fashion invites you to prep four besties for a futuristic red carpet bash. Your mission: choose attention-grabbing outfits from a virtual wardrobe of holographic gowns, metallic accessories, experiment with gravity-defying hairstyles, and glowing-in-the-dark makeup, and avant-garde accessories. Immerse yourself in a world of creativity, innovation, and stellar fashion. Ready to make a statement on the most spectacular runway of the future? let the fashion spectacle begin!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7R2A9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stellar-style-spectacle-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"97EEE","slug":"flappybee","title":"FlappyBee","description":"An addictive and fast-paced game that tests players' reflexes!\nThe rules are simple: tap the screen to make your little bee's wings flap and rise into the air. But beware. Each bloom requires precision and perfect timing. One mistake and your adventure is over.\nFlappy Bee is a game that tests your patience, concentration and skill.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/97EEE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappybee/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VI7D3","slug":"hidden-among-thieves","title":"Hidden Among Thieves","description":"Collect loot to win the round. You can choose to be bad or greedy, but that will make you worth more to the other players & may tempt them to take you down! There are plenty of hidden rooms & items to help you win! Rounds get longer & open up more secrets!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VI7D3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-among-thieves/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TZZCZ","slug":"help-me-tricky-puzzle","title":"Help Me Tricky Puzzle","description":"Help Me Tricky Puzzle Cliquez simplement sur le gros bouton de lecture pour commencer à vous amuser","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TZZCZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/help-me-tricky-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"59IAJ","slug":"ninja-parakite","title":"Ninja Parakite","description":"Avez-vous voulu être un ninja avec à la fois un parachute et un cerf-volant attachés à vous pour pouvoir voler? Ne cherchez pas plus loin que Ninja Parakite  ! Prenez le contrôle d'un ninja traversant un terrain difficile qui serait autrement impossible à traverser pour un ninja sans votre fidèle parakite ! Il y a des tonnes d'obstacles dans chaque niveau à éviter mais aussi quelques petites friandises, voyez si vous pouvez trouver votre ami qui attend patiemment que vous vous donniez des objets sympas ! Le but est de collecter le régime de bananes dans chaque niveau et de maîtriser l'utilisation du parakite !","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/59IAJ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-parakite/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AT60A","slug":"sword-battle-io","title":"Sword Battle.io","description":"Swordbattle.io is a multiplayer game where you PvP with 2D swords, and try to gain coins. The more coins you have, the more bigger and powerful you get! Try to become the biggest of them all..\n\nThis exciting multiplayer game features biomes, skins, upgrades, mobs, evolutions and a fun fighting experience! Team up with your friends and rule the land in Swordbattle.io","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AT60A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sword-battle-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5Y1T8","slug":"taco-kitty","title":"Taco Kitty","description":"Taco Kitty is a game Designed with Scratch. It is Easy-to-play, fun and mobile friendly (Not only for pc but also for mobile phones). Follow the instructions in the Game then use the mouse pointer to move the kitty or your finger.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5Y1T8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/taco-kitty/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OO3GT","slug":"getting-over-it","title":"Getting Over It","description":"A fun strategic game made in the 19's. Then it was recreated and then remixed by me.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OO3GT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/getting-over-it/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EKC38","slug":"gem-clicker","title":"Gem Clicker","description":"Gem clicker is a unique but simple clicker game, click on the big gem to get money and eventually break it. Click on the four small gems to charge them up until they generate income for a small amount of time automatically. Upgrade your click DMG, get an auto-clicker, upgrade the small gems, and get a reward for each big gem broken. This game has no end and you can infinitely upgrade as the big gems get progressively harder and harder to break.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EKC38/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gem-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10EAM","slug":"taxi-empire-airport-tycoon","title":"Taxi Empire - Airport Tycoon","description":"Do you want to become the owner of a cool taxi and airport service? This taxi business simulator game is for you! Earn money, unlock new cars and increase their number. Upgrade your airport to carry more people and earn even more!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10EAM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/taxi-empire-airport-tycoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D8DA2","slug":"hero-birds-hidden-stars","title":"Hero Birds Hidden Stars","description":"Hero Birds Hidden Stars est un jeu d'objets cachés et d'enfants en ligne gratuit. Découvrez les étoiles cachées dans les images spécifiées. Chaque niveau comporte 10 étoiles cachées. Il y a 8 niveaux au total. Le temps est limité, alors soyez rapide et trouvez tous les objets cachés avant la fin du temps imparti. Cliquer plusieurs fois au mauvais endroit réduit le temps de 5 secondes supplémentaires. Alors si tu es prêt","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D8DA2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hero-birds-hidden-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I5S7H","slug":"hook","title":"Hook","description":" Hook est un jeu d'adresse dans lequel vous incarnez un stickman qui se balance à travers des centaines de niveaux difficiles. Ce jeu de stickman amusant et coloré propose plus de 100 niveaux stimulants. Débloquez des personnages uniques en cours de route pour changer les choses pendant que vous vous balancez. Faites attention à l'angle et à la direction de votre swing pour atteindre la ligne d'arrivée ! Pouvez-vous contrôler votre swing?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5S7H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-hook-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"68HFT","slug":"stick-hero-tower-defense","title":"Stick Hero Tower Defense","description":"Stick War: Hero Tower Defense est la meilleure action pour les jeux Stickman et le jeu d'arcade de combat sur Google Play.\n\nÊtes-vous prêt à être le dernier bâton-héros debout dans les meilleures batailles ? Votre devoir est de charger le pouvoir: grandissez en tant que guerrier et battez des ennemis bien armés et tuez leur boss géant comme Wugy, Mommy et Bunny. Rassemblez votre stickman avec une stratégie judicieuse et menez-le à la victoire !\n\nStick War: Hero Tower Defense est une combinaison de jeux d'action, de stratégie et de puzzle de combat. Réfléchissez avant chaque glisser-déposer, calculez chaque mouvement, utilisez votre cerveau pour élaborer une stratégie pour votre prochaine action afin de surmonter d'innombrables obstacles. Nous avons pris les meilleures ressources du thème Stickman classique, pour que vous ne regrettiez jamais","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/68HFT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stick-hero-tower-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46E63","slug":"crowd-enhance","title":"Crowd Enhance","description":"\"Crowd Enhance\" is a casual arcade game in which you have to lead a squad of armed infantry to destroy all the enemies in your way! There are plenty of exciting levels ahead of you, in which you have to overcome various dangerous obstacles and fight against hordes of enemies trying to stop you.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46E63/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crowd-enhance/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ER5R5","slug":"stick-merge","title":"Stick Merge","description":"Stick Merge est un jeu d'action et de fusion simple. Votre objectif est de combiner diverses armes pour créer des armes plus puissantes et de les utiliser finalement sur les figurines mobiles du champ de tir. Préparez votre arsenal, améliorez votre pistolet, explorez tous les bonus et devenez le meilleur tireur de la ville. Quelle puissance pouvez-vous obtenir dans Stick Merge? Restez dans le coin pour le découvrir.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ER5R5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-driller-mini/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57A50","slug":"macagi-adventures","title":"Macagi Adventures","description":"Macagi Adventures est un jeu en ligne auquel vous pouvez jouer gratuitement dans les navigateurs modernes.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57A50/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/macagi-adventures/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENRLP","slug":"granny-jigsaw-puzzle","title":"Granny Jigsaw Puzzle","description":"Granny Jigsaw Puzzle est un jeu de puzzle d'horreur amusant. Vous pouvez sélectionner l'une des neuf images, puis sélectionner l'un des quatre modes (16, 36, 64 et 100 pièces). Sélectionnez votre image préférée et complétez le puzzle dans les plus brefs délais ! Amusez-vous et profitez-en!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENRLP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/granny-jigsaw-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UGIAG","slug":"autumn-coloring-seasons-pages","title":"Autumn Coloring Seasons Pages","description":"Discover the joy of digital art with Autumn AI - Color Seasons, where each stroke adds color to your world. This interactive coloring book provides an array of thematic coloring pages suitable for all. It's more than a game; it's a journey through a spectrum of scenes and motifs where your paint choices make all the difference. Indulge in the art of coloring with Autumn AI - Color Seasons!\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UGIAG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/autumn-coloring-seasons-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TL145","slug":"sky-blitz","title":"Sky Blitz","description":"This game is Sky Blitz, a simple arcade game you can play anywhere.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TL145/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZAGG1","slug":"weather-jigsaw-puzzle-frenzy","title":"Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy","description":"Welcome to Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy! Our Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy picture. With a wide variety of Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Weather Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZAGG1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/weather-jigsaw-puzzle-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HYECM","slug":"robot-memory-match","title":"Robot Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Robot Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Robot Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Robot Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HYECM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L5SWI","slug":"the-skinwalker-tile-picture-challenge","title":"The Skinwalker Tile Picture Challenge","description":"Welcome to The Skinwalker Tile Picture Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Skinwalker Tile Picture Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Skinwalker Tile Picture Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L5SWI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-skinwalker-tile-picture-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZU8NL","slug":"fantasy-creatures-tile-block-puzzle","title":"Fantasy Creatures Tile Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Fantasy Creatures Tile Block Puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Fantasy Creatures Tile Block Puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Fantasy Creatures Tile Block Puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZU8NL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fantasy-creatures-tile-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E1LDT","slug":"tanks-jigsaw-slide-challenge","title":"Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge","description":"Welcome to Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge! Our Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge picture. With a wide variety of Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Tanks Jigsaw Slide Challenge Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E1LDT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tanks-jigsaw-slide-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40198,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60L1H","slug":"the-chupacabra-photo-tile-quest","title":"The Chupacabra Photo Tile Quest","description":"Welcome to The Chupacabra Photo Tile Quest, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Chupacabra Photo Tile Quest, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Chupacabra Photo Tile Quest and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60L1H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-chupacabra-photo-tile-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ICLGL","slug":"my-little-pony-sliding-tile-challenge","title":"My Little Pony Sliding Tile Challenge","description":"Welcome to My Little Pony Sliding Tile Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn My Little Pony Sliding Tile Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to My Little Pony Sliding Tile Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ICLGL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-little-pony-sliding-tile-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RV77A","slug":"paperly-paper-plane-adventure","title":"Paperly - Paper Plane Adventure","description":"Paperly: Paper Plane Adventure is an exciting game where you must fly a paper plane and reach your destination. Avoid any objects that will hinder your way, collect extra time and Quantum as you fly, accelerate your paper plane, and reach the finish. Gravity will be your best friend in your journey of exploration, and it will act as an engine for your paper plane, so make sure to make the best use of it. Diving down will give you more momentum, and going up will take momentum from your airplane. Take a wind boost and dash on the air like crazy!\n\nFeatures\n\n- Explore worlds: Dry Deserts, Tropical Forests, Ice Caves, etc.\n- 11 unlockable paper planes\n- 7 unlockable paper plane skins","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RV77A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paper-plane-adventure-paperly/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5TTTT","slug":"monster-truck-adventure-expedition","title":"Monster Truck Adventure Expedition","description":"Drive the awesome monster truck, watch out for chasms, explore new terrains like deserts, volcanoes, and islands\n\nMobile: Use buttons on the left side of the screen to rotate a monster truck, use gas to accelerate.\nKeyboard: Press X to drive right, Z to drive backward. Use arrows to rotate your monster truck in the air.","category":"Aventure","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5TTTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-truck-adventure-expedition/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2YYYI","slug":"thor-treasury-viking-key-conquest","title":"Thor Treasury Viking Key Conquest","description":"Embark on an epic journey as a fearless Viking warrior delving into the depths of the underworld. Navigate through labyrinthine passages, encountering mythical creatures and overcoming challenges to collect ancient keys. keys unlocks a new levels of the underground realm, filled with treasure and mysteries waiting to be discovered\n\nKeyboard users: Use the left and right arrows to move your hero, use the Z and X keys to rotate the screen. For mobile users, utilize the on-screen buttons","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2YYYI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/thor-treasury-viking-key-conquest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VLBID","slug":"joyful-ball-bounce-mushroom-magic-adventure","title":"Joyful Ball Bounce Mushroom Magic Adventure","description":"Take control of a playful ball in this mobile platform game! Navigate through obstacles and defeat enemies to reach the charming 'little character with a mushroom on its head.' Collect funny little balls along the way to earn points and unlock achievements. Enjoy the charming graphics and festive music as you embark on this thrilling adventure!\n\n\nFor mobile: Use the buttons on the left side to move your red ball, and the button on the right side to jump. Press the jump button twice to jump higher.\nFor keyboard: Use the arrow keys to move, and press the up arrow key twice to jump higher.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VLBID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/joyful-ball-bounce-mushroom-magic-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S9LRL","slug":"black-ball-star-chaser","title":"Black Ball Star Chaser","description":"Roll the ball and collect the stars on the board, being careful not to fly out of the labyrinth\nKeyboard: Use the left and right arrows to move your hero.\nMobile: Touch the left or right side of the screen to rotate the screen\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S9LRL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-ball-star-chaser/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RN1RN","slug":"crocoboy-run","title":"CrocoBoy Run","description":"crocoboy run is an html5 jump running game, run and jump to avoid the monsters and obstacles that come\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RN1RN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crocoboy-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"REA3A","slug":"santa-super-adventure","title":"Santa Super Adventure","description":"Santa Super Adventure is an HTML5 endless run game, run and collect all the scattered prizes, be careful, avoid various obstacles and be the winner.\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/REA3A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-super-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0AT8A","slug":"bunny-adventure","title":"Bunny Adventure","description":"bunny adventure is an html5 endless run game, run and get as many stars as possible, avoid obstacles and monsters","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0AT8A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0O7NN","slug":"bouncing-ball","title":"Bouncing Ball","description":"bouncing ball is a html5 jumping ball game, touch the screen to run the jumping ball and avoid obstacles to reach the finish","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0O7NN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncing-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O2079","slug":"ninja-frog-adventure","title":"Ninja Frog Adventure","description":"frog adventure is an html5 platformer game, a frog adventure to find fruit and score, beat the enemy at each level and complete it","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O2079/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M8M0M","slug":"smart-cup","title":"Smart Cup","description":"smart cup is a filling a glass with water html5 game, hold and press the faucet turns on the water and it flows into the glass until it reaches the limit in the image\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M8M0M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smart-cup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L5229","slug":"car-driving-lesson","title":"Car Driving Lesson","description":"car driving lesson is an isometric arcade html5 game, control the car up and down avoid collisions and get the highest score\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L5229/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-driving-lesson/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M5S18","slug":"christmas-bird-game-s-mission","title":"Christmas Bird Game's Mission","description":"In the game \"Christmas Bird Game's Mission,\" you play as a little bird pilot traveling in a spaceship. Your mission is to reach the base located on the other side of the screen. But watch out! You have limited fuel, so you must manage it carefully.\nYou control the bird using the up arrow key on the keyboard, but remember, each ascent uses a lot of fuel. Try to carefully avoid obstacles such as beams, meteors, and other ships that can halt your journey.\nCollect fuel and fly cautiously to reach the base. Will you be able to overcome cosmic challenges and reach your goal? It's time to begin the adventure!\n\n\nFor mobile devices: Use the left, up, and right arrows on the left side of the screen to control the character. For keyboards: Utilize the arrow keys on the keyboard; left for leftward movement, up to ascend, and right to move to the right","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M5S18/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-bird-game-s-mission/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C119L","slug":"cat-tastic-puzzle-challenge","title":"Cat-tastic Puzzle Challenge","description":"Unleash your inner cat detective! Piece together a purrfectly puzzling scene filled with feline friends. \nFrom playful antics to cozy naps, this jigsaw puzzle captures the essence of cats in all their glory. \nCan you bring the purrfect picture to life?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C119L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-tastic-puzzle-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U3D0L","slug":"rapid-pixie-puzzle-fun","title":"Rapid Pixie Puzzle Fun","description":"Help the pixies in their fruity frenzy! Rapid Pixie Puzzle Fun is a fast-paced bubble shooter where \njuicy fruits replace the bubbles. Match three or more of the same kind to clear the board and rack \nup points. Be quick and strategic, as new fruits fall at a rapid pace.\nCan you keep up and become the ultimate fruit-matching champion?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U3D0L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rapid-pixie-puzzle-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"INE07","slug":"brain-puzzle-quest-bangkok-edition","title":"Brain Puzzle Quest Bangkok Edition","description":"Immerse yourself in the bustling beauty of Bangkok with our cityscape Puzzle game! Piece together \niconic landmarks like the Grand Palace and vibrant street markets. As you assemble the puzzle, feel \nthe energy of this dynamic city come to life through intricate details and vivid colors. Experience \nthe charm of Bangkok from the comfort of your own home!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/INE07/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-puzzle-quest-bangkok-edition/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0ET8L","slug":"fruity-fortune-slot-frenzy","title":"Fruity Fortune Slot Frenzy","description":"Sink your teeth into juicy wins in Fruity Fortune Slot Frenzy! Spin the reels and match vibrant fruits to \nunleash a frenzy of fortune. Line up the winning combinations and watch your payouts grow. With every spin, \na delicious taste of victory awaits! So, crank up the excitement and get ready to be swept away in this fruity \njackpot adventure!","category":"Aventure","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0ET8L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruity-fortune-slot-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5E6TI","slug":"mystic-maidens-puzzle","title":"Mystic Maidens Puzzle","description":"Enter a whimsical world of enchantment with our Mystic Maidens Puzzle game! Piece together magical \nscenes featuring fairies, unicorns, and charming princesses. Delight in the joy of solving intricate puzzles \nwhile surrounded by vibrant colors and delightful characters. Unleash creativity and embark on a puzzle \nadventure that sparks imagination in every piece!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5E6TI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mystic-maidens-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E59R3","slug":"park-safe","title":"Park Safe","description":"Safe Park is an exciting game that tests your focus and timing.\nThe car moves automatically, and your task is to park it in a tight space at just the right moment! Be careful not to crash into other cars, or its game over.\nThis is a free, endless game that offers a fun challenge, but its not easy to master! Are you up for the challenge of becoming a safe parking expert? ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E59R3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/safe-park/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"409A0","slug":"duo-match","title":"Duo Match","description":"Prepare yourself for a fresh and original matching pair game challenge! Your task is to match pairs of extra cute characters on the ground and pop them all! Each cleared level introduces new pairs to match. This cute matching game is designed to be so easy that anyone can play and enjoy it. Are you ready to dive into the world of adorable characters and test your matching skills? ","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/409A0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0704H","slug":"rally-championship","title":"Rally Championship","description":"Rally Championship is a fun classic 2D arcade racing game similar with the classic racing games of the 80s.\nPlay ten different circuits to race in a car that runs automatically; unlock two or more powerful cards that are hidden and discover other features while playing.\nUse the turbo when you need an extra speed boost and set the best lap time.\nThe game shows colorful and detailed graphics and a nice sound effects you will enjoy.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0704H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rally-championship/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O9M96","slug":"image-to-word-match","title":"Image To Word Match","description":"Welcome to our cool word matching game! In this game, you simply need to match the pictures to the correct words.\nHow To Play:\nIts as easy as pie! Just use your mouse to click on a picture, then drag and drop it over the correct word.\nIf you get it right, youll see a message saying Well done! If you make a mistake, youll see an error message.\nWe offer two exciting game modes:\n\nEasy: Play at your own pace without any stress. You can go back and forth in the game whenever you want, making it perfect for kids.\n\nNormal: Challenge yourself with three lives. Match the pictures correctly to the words, or face a game over! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O9M96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/image-to-word-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"280SU","slug":"color-fun-for-kids","title":"Color Fun For Kids","description":"Get on a vibrant journey with Color Fun For Kids! This delightful game offers a kaleidoscope of hues for young minds to explore.\nEnter in a playful world of creativity as children immerse themselves in coloring activities with user-friendly numeric guides.\nUnlock the joy of blending colors, fostering imagination, and enhancing fine motor skills.\nPlay now for an interactive and educational experience that makes learning colors a delightful adventure for your little ones!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/280SU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-fun-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9RTE0","slug":"find-the-lost-letter","title":"Find The Lost Letter","description":"Welcome to our delightful letter matching game! Its simple and fun for everyone. Just follow these instructions:\nHOW TO PLAY:\nTouch one of the three letters on the right side of the screen.\nDrag the selected letter over the missing box area. Release your finger to drop the letter into the missing area.\nIf the letter is correct, youll see a bonus message; otherwise, youll see an error message.\nDont worry about losing because its just a simple kids letter game. Plus, you can learn the correct names of objects and alphabet letters while playing.\nKey Features:\n- Over 60 objects\n- High-resolution images\n- Super cute graphics\n-Amazing sound","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9RTE0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-lost-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10HGE","slug":"santa-match-games","title":"Santa Match Games","description":"Thank you for providing the information about the game Challenging Track. This game sounds like a fun and engaging activity, suitable for players of all ages. In this game, you have to match the pictures to the correct words. Its really simple and intuitive… just use your mouse and click on a picture after drag n drop the picture over the correct Word! If you do right you see a message of well done if you are wrong you see an error message!\nYou have 2 Game Modes:\nEasy: You can play freely without stress because you can go back and forth in the game when you want! Its really suitable for kids.\nNormal: In this mode you have 3 lives","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10HGE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-math-games/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PY7AP","slug":"happy-farm-animals","title":"Happy Farm Animals","description":"Designed especially for toddlers aged 1.5 to 5 years old, this engaging and educational game is a perfect tool for teaching your children the names and sounds of different farm animals. The game features large, vibrant images that make it easy for your childs small fingers to interact with them. While the game is designed to be intuitive, younger children may need some initial guidance and assistance from an adult. By playing this game, your child can learn about various farm animals while developing their fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PY7AP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-farm-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"983AK","slug":"car-wash-for-kid","title":"Car Wash For Kid","description":"Work as a master car mechanic and wash dirty planes in the childrens auto garage plane wash repair game or car wash game where you must perform multiple tasks like car washing, car repair, and test driving the cars.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/983AK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-wash-for-kid/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7OPN0","slug":"coin-drop","title":"Coin Drop","description":"Play at Coin Drop and have fun with this entertaining puzzle game!\nThe goal of the game is to get the coin into the basket without letting it touch the ground! Try to complete all different 24 levels!\nHow to do this? Simply:\ndestroy the boxes and, using the principles of physics to roll the coin into the basket!\nCoin Drop is simple and fun puzzle game for everyone!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7OPN0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coin-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14ES3","slug":"kids-hand-care","title":"Kids Hand Care","description":"Are you interested in becoming a great hand doctor? Embrace the opportunity to wear a stethoscope and exude professionalism with this engaging hand doctor game.\nIt offers a perfect blend of fun and educational experiences.\nDont miss out, grab it now! ","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14ES3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-hand-care/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE09O","slug":"avoider","title":"Avoider","description":"In Avoider you play the role of a bee lost in a quagmire, full of dangerous plants that can kill you with their poisonous thorns. Fly as long as you can in this endless wood, and make the highest score of all time!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE09O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/avoider/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ERNUU","slug":"numberless","title":"Numberless","description":"Numberless is an endless vertical shooter where you have to destroy an infinite horde of monsters that requires a certain number of hit to be destroyed. More the hit you need to kill a monster, more points you will earn once the monster is destroyed! But if a monster touches you is game over, so is better to do your math!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ERNUU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/numberless/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RETJJ","slug":"jumper-bot","title":"Jumper Bot","description":"Jumperbot is a platformer game where you have to jump and avoid all the nasty flying fishes (for real?) moving around on screen. Avoid them at all cost, otherwise it will be game over! Remember you can jump how many times you want, even if you are midair!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RETJJ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumperbot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KH1HO","slug":"clock-head","title":"Clock Head","description":"Clockhead is a game about a weird clock that shrinks in the time if you do not catch the white glowing orbs on screen when the clock arm is overlapping them. Touch or click at right time, to earn points and restore the normal size of your head. If you wait to long the head will disappear and it will be game over.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KH1HO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clockhead/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LNJPP","slug":"bunny-jump-plus","title":"Bunny Jump Plus","description":"Bunny Jump catapults you into an epic vertical adventure! Get ready to jump, jump and jump some more as you try to reach heights you've never seen before! Take on the challenge and see how high you can go!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LNJPP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-jump-plus/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42ZZO","slug":"worms-zone","title":"Worms Zone","description":"Worms.Zone is online game with dynamic storyline and funny graphics. Start grow your worm right now. While trying to get the real anaconda, the small worm never stucks in one place – he is ready to bite everyone. However, there is a danger to be eaten by the more successful player.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42ZZO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/worms-zone/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46A1L","slug":"bandyball","title":"BandyBall","description":"Play BandyBall and have fun dribbling with the balls that made football history.\nEarn STARS by dribbling, unlock and redeem balls and shoes.\nEach item provides additional bonuses to help you earn more and more STARS.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46A1L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bandyball/embed?sid=1","plays":40122,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2O65M","slug":"xmas-pop-it","title":"Xmas Pop It","description":"It's Christmas! so pop all bubbles on the fidget xmas toys!   \nMerry Christmas and happy new year!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2O65M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/xmas-pop-it/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3IA37","slug":"animal-rush","title":"Animal Rush","description":"Animal Rush is a fun game to play. Tap on the screen to change the direction of the animal or make it jump to avoid gaps. Collect diamonds along the way and unlock new animals to play. Don’t fall off the path or the game will be over.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3IA37/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animal-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0261","slug":"amazing-soccer","title":"Amazing Soccer","description":"Looking for an exciting football entertainment in your hands? Here is Amazing Soccer game!Swipe the ball to hit the targets and score.\n\nThere are 2 modes to play with colorful balls\n\nCollect the stars to unlock new balls, environments, nets and goalkeepers. Improve your skills and become the best Football Striker the world has ever seen!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0261/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-soccer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T5957","slug":"right-time","title":"Right Time","description":"In Right Time you have to shoot fast if you want to make points. You have to shoot the enemies when they are under your crosshair. Every time you hit a target you will make a point, but the next one will be faster. How long can you last without missinga a single hit?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T5957/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rigth-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7C19K","slug":"ketchme","title":"Ketchme","description":"The rules of Ketchme are the easiest: You do not have to do nothing more than click on the white character on screen, before the time runs out. Every time you catch it, another creature will spawn on screen, making harder to find your target.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7C19K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ketchme/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5T33T","slug":"tao-tao","title":"Tao Tao","description":"In Tao Tao you have to match the colors of the incoming monsters every time they spawn. Touch the screen to rotate the Tao-monsters, and match based on the incoming creature. As the time passes, the speed of the creatures increases, so be careful!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5T33T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tao-tao/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18B25","slug":"bouncing-blobs","title":"Bouncing Blobs","description":"In Bouncing Blob you have to collect all the orbs that appear on the screen to increase your score. Avoid the blobbing enemies, but if you get hit you can always restore your health collecting the small black blob that spawn on the screen. You can also use your points to unlock new characters.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18B25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncing-blob/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LO7UD","slug":"jump-drop-shell","title":"Jump Drop Shell","description":"Jump Drop Shell est une action réflexe permettant de contrôler une personne pouvant se spécialiser dans les coquillages et les heures de sommeil. Vous pouvez garnir votre carpaccio d'un double sauté. Utilisez cette machine de manière scientifique et réfléchissez. Vous n'avez accès à aucun obstacle dans votre mode de vie dans un siège double pratique qui s'installe à tout moment dans votre coquille.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LO7UD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-drop-shell/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19477","slug":"clones","title":"Clones","description":"Clones vous contrôlez un personnage qui peut se cloner ! Mais vos clones ne sont pas que des copies régulières. Chaque fois que vous créez un clone, vous remontez dans le temps et votre clone copiera toutes les étapes que vous avez effectuées auparavant ! Vous pouvez utiliser ces doubles voyageant dans le temps pour appuyer sur des boutons, sauter sur des plates-formes et déverrouiller des portes.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19477/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clones/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IEEV2","slug":"devil-level","title":"Devil Level","description":"Devil Level online est un jeu de plateforme avec une touche méchante. Le but est simple ; arrivez à la porte à la fin du niveau pour gagner, mais ce n'est pas aussi facile qu'il y paraît... Des trous peuvent apparaître de nulle part, des pointes peuvent bouger de manière inattendue et des plafonds peuvent vous tomber dessus pendant que vous avancez. les nombreux niveaux différents. Un faux pas et c'est la fin du jeu.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IEEV2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/devil-level-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84H31","slug":"money-rush","title":"Money Rush","description":"Are you great at simple math? Or are you looking for interesting games about money? Amazing! This money game is just for you. Roll out your money roll, apply your knowledge of mathematics and choose the best gate to increase your amount and become a real owner of money! The more coins you collect, the higher your income will be.\n\nImmerse yourself in the world of wealth and profit with \"Money Rush\". Adrenaline, big winnings and a real pleasure from the game are waiting for you. Start your journey to financial success right now!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84H31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/money-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"03458","slug":"90-degrees","title":"90 Degrees","description":"Unleash your inner fun banter with 90 Degrees. Get an exclusive, exciting & unique gaming experience with just a tap! Catch a glimpse","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/03458/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/90-degrees/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7R3PP","slug":"drawing-puzzle","title":"Drawing Puzzle","description":"Drawing Puzzle is a logic game. Use your finger or mouse to draw a path on the screen and guide the ball into the cup. This is amazing brain challenge for you. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7R3PP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drawing-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AIO1V","slug":"survival-by-boat","title":"Survival by Boat","description":"Embark on an exciting sea adventure with our Boat Survival game! Explore the vast expanses of the ocean, discover mysterious islands and meet amazing characters in this exciting world of survival. Collect resources, fight monsters and create your own story in this unique journey. Get ready for incredible adventures and unexplored islands – your sea adventure begins right now!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AIO1V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survival-by-boat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NIT03","slug":"untwist-road","title":"Untwist Road","description":"A feature of this game is the unique mechanics - you have to not only collect cylinders and avoid obstacles, but also roll out the road in front of you. Be ready for the challenge, because each level becomes more difficult and requires more skill.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NIT03/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/untwist-road/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0I77D","slug":"zigzag-glide","title":"ZigZag Glide","description":"Embark on a thrilling journey with ZigZag Glide! Guide your nimble ball through an endless array of zigzagging \nbars, skillfully maneuvering through gaps to score points. Master the art of precision as you navigate through \nincreasingly challenging levels, each filled with dynamically placed barriers. \nChallenge your reflexes and concentration to achieve the highest score. With its addictive gameplay, \nvibrant graphics, and endless obstacles, ZigZag Glide promises an exhilarating experience for players of \nall ages.\n\nKey Features:\nZigzag Challenge: Navigate the flappy ball through a zigzagging path, testing your reflexes and precision.\nEndless Obstacles: Encounter an infinite number of successive bar pairs.\nScore Mastery: Increase your score by successfully passing through gaps.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0I77D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zigzag-glide/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T7770","slug":"maze-madness-adventure","title":"Maze Madness Adventure","description":"Embark on an epic journey with \"Maze Madness Adventure,\" a maze-solving extravaganza! Navigate through a \nmultitude of challenging levels, each designed to test your skills and intellect. Choose your preferred \nmode – conquer mazes at your pace in normal mode, race against time in the adrenaline-pumping timed mode, \nor navigate through the shadows in the intense darkness mode. \nWith an abundance of levels and diverse challenges, hone your maze-solving abilities and strive for \nhigher scores in this captivating and versatile gaming experience.\n\nKey Features:\n\nVaried Modes: Engage in normal, timed, and darkness modes.\nExtensive Level Design: Explore a multitude of intricately designed levels\nScore-driven Mastery: Aim for the highest scores by solving mazes efficiently.","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T7770/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maze-madness-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"73IPF","slug":"fliperx","title":"FliperX","description":"The Flipper","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/73IPF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fliperx/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1C0O1","slug":"microbx","title":"MicrobX","description":"Welcome to the MicrobX game, you have to capture all the microbes in the shortest time possible, the record remains recorded so you can try again in less time","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1C0O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/microbx/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2L00M","slug":"merge-challenge","title":"Merge Challenge","description":"A classic 2048 style merge game, try to complete the game in this challenge.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2L00M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3DR33","slug":"short-path-run-3d-fun","title":"Short Path Run 3d Fun","description":"Short Path fun 3d Run is challenging game with 100+ levels. Make race with other users.\nRace against opponents, and stack up all the floorboards you can pick up along the way!\nIf you're clever enough, get out of the way and build bridges and take shortcuts to get to the finish line before everyone else!\n\nCheating has never been so stylish!\n\nSimple gameplay with efficient and easy to learn controls.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3DR33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/short-path-run-3d-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1120","slug":"army-stick","title":"Army Stick","description":"Army Stick is an HTML5 arcade game, pull the stick and adjust the timing to a long or short distance from the ground\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1120/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/army-stick/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"850R1","slug":"super-dice","title":"Super Dice","description":"super dice is an html5 arcade game, roll the dice to the same color and get a score","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/850R1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-dice/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S8D41","slug":"ninja-endless-run","title":"Ninja Endless Run","description":"Ninja Endless Run is an HTML5 arcade game, run and jump, avoid obstacles, get as many coins as possible and get big prizes at the end of the journey\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S8D41/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-endless-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A77M1","slug":"candy-super-match","title":"Candy Super Match","description":"Switch and match the candies and get the highest score to be the winner\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A77M1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-super-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OCNO3","slug":"balloon-crack","title":"Balloon Crack","description":"Ballon Crack is an HTML5 arcade game, pop as many balloons as possible and get a score","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OCNO3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-crack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7AKRE","slug":"zombie-attack-shooter","title":"Zombie Attack Shooter","description":"zombie attack shooter is an html5 arcade shooting game, zombies attack shoot them and get the coins that come, use special powers to destroy them\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7AKRE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-attack-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R0758","slug":"rick","title":"Rick","description":"Welcome to the Dick game 5 levels to overcome to win, Good luck","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R0758/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rick/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T59R3","slug":"northern-lights-the-secret-of-the-forest","title":"Northern Lights - The Secret of the Forest","description":"A new hit for fans of the Connect 3 genre!\n\nThe Scientist Cat is already hiding items throughout the mysterious forest so you can enjoy finding things and earn as many emeralds as possible. The cat is happy to have new guests!\n\nIvan Tsarevich is already chopping wood to build a hut and is waiting for your help. But don't worry! You don’t have to wield an ax: you just need to connect things three at a time, and this way you will build a large tower and even be able to plant a beautiful garden with apple trees on the site. And the apples there are red and liquid! By the way, for combining three fruits in the game they also give a reward.\n\nMarya Morevna is already preparing interesting riddles and puzzles and is looking forward to treasure hunting with you. But the game won't be too difficult: Marya loves to arrange things in threes and will be happy to help you overcome all the obstacles!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T59R3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/northern-lights-the-secret-of-the-forest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SYAM6","slug":"idle-military-base-army-tycoon","title":"Idle Military Base. Army Tycoon","description":"Do you want to become a military tycoon, build your own military base and experience a real military simulator? A military base with nothing on it will fall under your control. Your mission is to expand it! Create the largest military base with equipment!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SYAM6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-military-base-army-tycoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B70LS","slug":"physical-balls-2048","title":"Physical Balls 2048","description":"Your task is to merge the same balls. When two balls with the same number, color and size collide, they merge into one ball with a larger number. The goal is to reach as many numbers as possible by combining the balls. \nThe physics in this game adds an extra level of difficulty. The balls move and bounce realistically. As you progress through the levels, the gameplay becomes more complex, new types of balls and obstacles are added to it. \nThe graphics in this game are amazing, with bright colors and smooth animations that bring the physical balls to life. \nThis physical ball game is perfect for both regular players and puzzle lovers. So what are you waiting for? Start the game right now and start merging these balls!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B70LS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/physical-balls-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EIO86","slug":"legend-of-the-isles-the-hero-s-path","title":"Legend of the Isles. The Hero's Path","description":"Welcome to the exciting world of island battles, where you will play the role of a brave traveler exploring mysterious islands full of dangers and secrets. You will embark on an epic journey across the ocean, mastering the art of combat and strategy to become a true ruler of the archipelago.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EIO86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/legend-of-the-isles-the-hero-s-path/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0075A","slug":"egg-hunt-mania","title":"Egg Hunt Mania","description":"Préparez votre panier et sauvez tous les œufs que vous pouvez d'un terrible destin. Veillez à vider un panier plein dans le magasin. Attention au quota d'œufs qui augmente chaque jour !\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0075A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/egg-hunt-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LKA94","slug":"lucky-vegas-slots","title":"Lucky Vegas Slots","description":"Vous voulez vivre l'expérience de Vegas ? Essayez toutes les différentes machines à sous chanceuses et sentez l'excitation de toucher le jackpot sur votre machine préférée !\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LKA94/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lucky-vegas-slots/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01E2O","slug":"color-runner","title":"Color Runner","description":"In Color Runner you are a stylized man running through an endless row of colored cubes where you have to match the same color of the cube you are running through. Try to run as long as you can without go wrong with the colors!\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01E2O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"82172","slug":"frog-byte","title":"Frog Byte","description":"Frogbyte is a game about a hungry toad sitting on a leaf that wants to eat all the flies flying through its swamp. Try to catch as many bugs as you can avoiding the bombs, otherwise it will be game over!\nMake the best score and share it with your friends!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/82172/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frogbite/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NIE10","slug":"feeding-fish","title":"Feeding Fish","description":"In Feeding Fish you are a little fish who wants to eat all the worm in the ocean. Nobody can stop you, but you are not the only fish in the sea: you will have to avoid the vicious sharks that wander in the deepest ocean, looking for a nice little fish to eat!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NIE10/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/feeding-fish/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1ADB1","slug":"bad-drawings-memory-game","title":"Bad Drawings Memory Game","description":"Bad Drawings Memory Game is a classic memory game but with a twist: in this game you won't find any good drawings to memorize! Instead, you will find ugly handmade drawings that look like they came out from hell! You have 3 different difficulty level to try out in this game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1ADB1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bad-drawings-memory-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HH8TT","slug":"within-the-borders","title":"Within the Borders","description":"In Within the Borders you have to collect the white glowing orbs without leaving the track. If you get out from the black line it will be game over. To turn you have to touch the screen at the right moment. Be careful, because every time you collect a new orb, the players moves faster and faster!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HH8TT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/within-the-borders/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y0211","slug":"they-fall","title":"They Fall","description":"In \"They Fall\" the rules are simple: you have to collect as many  Purple orbs as you can avoiding the falling rotating saw. You can survive to 3 hits before dying. You can recover your health if you avoid the saws for long enough. Try your best and make the highest score!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y0211/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/they-fall/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OWS29","slug":"shadow-shooter","title":"Shadow Shooter","description":"In Shadow Shooter you have to face an assault from an army of shadows. To destroy the shadows you have to shoot them with using bullets of the same colors of the nasty shadows! As you proceed in the game, the shadows spawning rate will increase. Will you be fast enough?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OWS29/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shadow-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BLL5A","slug":"flappy-blob","title":"Flappy Blob","description":"Flappy Blob is a reinterpretation of the famous Flappy Bird. In this game you are a flying pseudo-bat that has to fly through a flock of smoky clouds. To fly you have to touch the screen. If you don't, the bats will falls and you will die. If you touch the cloud you lose. Try to survive as long as you can in this endless flying game.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BLL5A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-blob/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1509","slug":"horror-face-shooter","title":"Horror Face Shooter","description":"In Horror Face Shooter a gang of horrible monsters want to assault you. To defend yourself you have your super powerful laser beam, but it requires some time to get reloaded, so you have to shoot wisely, otherwise the wicked horror face will get you!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1509/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horror-face-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TI9IE","slug":"no-mice-in-the-kitchen","title":"No Mice in the Kitchen","description":"In No Mice in the Kitchen only the chicken are allowed to come in! You have to kill all the mice that will try to deceive you, hiding between the birds. No one want to eat a mouse right? So kill them! But be careful because if you kill too many chicken by mistake you will be fired! Game over!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TI9IE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/no-mice-in-the-kitchen/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AU63O","slug":"alien-bouncing","title":"Alien Bouncing","description":"Alien Bouncing is a game about quick reflexes and right timing. To earn points you have to touch the screen when you are overlapping the white glowing orbs on the screen. Has you earn points the alien moves faster, making harder to catch the orbs.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AU63O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-bouncing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"468U6","slug":"tax-escape","title":"Tax Escape","description":"In Tax Escape you have to flee from a horde of tax collectors that wants your money! You have to avoid them at all cost! Pay attention to the rolling barrels on the street, and touch the screen to jump above them. If you hit them you will slow down, risking to be catched from the evil tax collectors!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/468U6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tax-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D7E0E","slug":"red-or-green","title":"Red or Green","description":"In Red or Green you have to guess if there are more Green Creatures or Red Creatures. You can count or just try to guess approximately if there are more Red or Green Creatures. If your answer is right you will earn a point and then it will asked once again what color is predominant, but every time the timer will run faster!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D7E0E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-or-green/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0R3E","slug":"vertical-slide","title":"Vertical Slide","description":"Vertical Slide is a gravity switch endless runner game where you need quick reflexes to avoid the obstacles and collect the white glowing orb. Touch the screen to switch the gravity and move up and down on the screen. Collect as many orbs as you can e make the best score ever!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0R3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vertical-slide/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9ALSS","slug":"abstract-sliding","title":"Abstract Sliding","description":"Abstract Sliding is a slider game with awful handmade drawings. Try to recompose the image using as less moves as you can. Try three different difficulty level and choose the image that you like the most. Use your brain and solve the puzzle!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9ALSS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/abstract-sliding/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D48M1","slug":"don-t-move","title":"Don't Move","description":"Don't move is a reinterpretation of the famous Red Light Green Light game. You have to guess which one of the monsters on the screen has moved. When the game starts there are only two monsters, but as you proceed in the game, the numbers of monsters on screen will increase. Stay focus if you do not want to kill the wrong monster!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D48M1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/don-t-move/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41E4H","slug":"resuscit-hate","title":"Resuscit-hate","description":"In Resuscit-hate you are an unlucky paramedic that has to resuscitate a man who apparently suffered an heart attack while he was out for a walk. If it wasn't hard enough, you have the man's family on your back, ready to punish you if you won't resuscitate him asap. Touch the screen at the right time, or you will lose his life... and yours!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41E4H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/resuscit-hate/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5199","slug":"morph-shoot","title":"Morph Shoot","description":"In Morphshooter you have to shoot to the right monster looking only at its shape. look carefully the creature's shape on the bottom of the screen and then try to find the same monster, than click on it! But do it  fast, before the time runs out!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5199/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/morph-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K4L7B","slug":"blobkill","title":"Blobkill","description":"Blobkill is a throwing knives game, where you hate to touch the screen at the right time. If you miss the target more than 3 times, it will be game over. Every time you hit a target the knife rotation speed increases, making the game harder and harder","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K4L7B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blobkill/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8D9B0","slug":"double-blob","title":"Double Blob","description":"Double Blob is a game an endless vertical avoid and collect game, where you have to control two birds, and make them pass through small holes in the walls. The game starts slowly, but after a couple of minutes, you will need to draw all your skills to avoid to crash the birds on the moving walls!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8D9B0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/double-blob/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RVOB1","slug":"brickscape-breakout-adventure","title":"Brickscape - Breakout Adventure","description":"Brickscape: Breakout Adventure\nPrepare for an exhilarating journey through a mesmerizing world of vibrant glass-bricks in \nBrickscape: Breakout Adventure, the ultimate Brick Breaker game that seamlessly blends simplicity \nwith dazzling excitement. Challenge yourself as you wield the power to control an array of visually \nstunning balls, each evolving based on your performance to ensure an immersive and personalized gaming \nexperience. Brickscape: Breakout Adventure is not just a game; it's a visual spectacle that adapts to your \nskills, promising hours of colorful fun and addictive gameplay.\n\nKey Features:\nDynamic Ball Evolution\nStrategic Glass-Brick Layouts\nPerformance-Driven Scoring\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RVOB1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brickscape-breakoutadventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9EL29","slug":"pastel-palette-fun","title":"Pastel Palette Fun","description":"Dive into a world of vibrant hues and challenging decisions with \"Pastel Palette Fun\" – the ultimate color selection mobile game - selecting the lighter of two pastel shades! Immerse yourself in a visually stunning experience where your keen eye for shades will be put to the test.\n•\tChoose Wisely\n•\tRace Against Time\n•\tMesmerizing Pastels\nReady for a mesmerizing journey through a world of pastel wonders? Download \"Pastel Palette Fun\" now and prove that you have the perfect eye for the subtle beauty of lighter shades!\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9EL29/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pastel-palette-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78EPE","slug":"sliding-puzzle-the-15-puzzle","title":"Sliding Puzzle - The 15 Puzzle","description":"Silding puzzle (the 15-puzzle game) for people who want to enjoy and relax their mind! Many puzzles to solve. In various difficulty and sizes.\n\nThis offline sliding puzzle game has many classic sliding games and comes in 3 difficulty levels.\n\nFeatures:\n\n- 3 difficulties level. Ability to choose the size of puzzle.\n\n- Clean and familiar interface\n\n- Game is saved automatically, continue where you left off","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78EPE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sliding-puzzle-the-15-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"334AN","slug":"monster-arena","title":"Monster Arena","description":"Monster Arena is a game where humans go to see monsters fighting in an arena.\nYou are one of them and you are fighting for your survival, how many monsters can you kill? and how many waves will you be able to resist? ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/334AN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-arena/embed?sid=1","plays":40178,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"34736","slug":"stunt-rider","title":"Stunt Rider","description":"In this exciting game, you will take on the role of an experienced stuntman, performing daring stunts on your motorcycle at different levels. Unlock new levels and buy cool motorcycles in the Stunt Rider game.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/34736/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stunt-rider/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EK7IU","slug":"wild-blueshark","title":"Wild Blueshark","description":"wild blueshark is an html5 arcade game, play as a hungry shark that will eat anything in the sea, get as many items as possible and get the highest score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EK7IU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-blueshark/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2R857","slug":"super-aircraft-shooter","title":"Super Aircraft Shooter","description":"super aircraft shooter is an html5 top-down shooting game, get the items that appear and defeat the enemy aircraft quickly\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2R857/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-aircraft-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"102M3","slug":"bunny-bomb","title":"Bunny Bomb","description":"Bunny Bomb is an arcade, pixel art game where you're a bunny and you have to avoid the bombs or jump over them to increase your score, use the arrows for the movement and spacebar to pause the game.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/102M3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-bomb/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C076A","slug":"qubycall","title":"Qubycall","description":"Bienvenue dans Qubycall, un jeu 3D captivant qui vous plonge dans un monde de plaisir et d'interactivité illimités ! Prenez le commandement d'une balle et défiez la gravité pour grimper en haut du classement. Laissez votre empreinte et faites-vous un nom dans ce jeu captivant et stimulant.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C076A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/qubycall/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91W92","slug":"gem-twins","title":"Gem Twins","description":"You control two brothers with the ability to turn themselves into stone to help each other.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91W92/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gem-twins/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1L29O","slug":"cannon-balls-arcade","title":"Cannon Balls - Arcade","description":"Cannon Balls is an exciting casual game that puts skills to the test. you only have a limited number of balls at your disposal. Plan your shots wisely to maximize the impact and clear each level. Can you skillfully bring down all the targets with the available cannonballs? Show off your precision and enjoy the thrilling challenge of Cannon Balls!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1L29O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cannon-balls-arcade/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81DMD","slug":"mr-mood","title":"Mr Mood","description":"Embark on an exhilarating odyssey through the vibrant and dynamic world of \"Mr Mood\" This game is a celebration of life, adventure, and discovery, designed to uplift your spirits and ignite a sense of wonder. As you traverse the diverse landscapes filled with color and energy, you'll experience a mood that is both invigorating and uplifting.\n\n\"Mr Mood\" invites you into a realm where every sunrise paints the sky in hues of warmth and where the air is filled with the sounds of nature awakening. The game's vibrant visuals and lively soundtrack create a mood that is positively infectious, fostering a sense of joy and optimism as you navigate through the enchanting environments.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81DMD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-mood/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GCY24","slug":"glitch-guy-gravity-run","title":"Glitch Guy Gravity Run","description":"Glitch Guy gravity run is an arcade, pixel art game where you're a guy that have to avoid ghost and run and change gravity to increase your score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GCY24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glitch-guy-gravity-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M68TC","slug":"monster-school-challenges","title":"Monster School Challenges","description":"The students quarreled together in monster school! Do bottle flip challenge with Herobrine! Become the best, show what you can do.\n\nHelp Noob, Pro, Enderguy, Herobrine, Craftsman and others to complete the training. This funny challenge where floor is lava.\n\nFeatures:\n- 3 monster school challenges\n- funny memes and jokes\n- very emotional game","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M68TC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-school-challenges/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MKNNK","slug":"stickman-that-one-level","title":"Stickman That One Level","description":"Stickman has fallen into a trap and needs to escape from prison! Solve stickman puzzles on non-unique jail levels. Great stick war legacy timekiller with jailbreak quest with stick. Develop intelligence and increase IQ. Find the key and open 100 doors!\n\n• 100 non-unique levels\n• 100 unique ways to win\n• And stickman that rises from the dead again\n• Epic bosses vs your desire to escape from prison","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MKNNK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-that-one-level/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MV1V5","slug":"stickman-vs-monster-school","title":"Stickman vs Monster School","description":"Stickman and Monster School is a game about stickman where you have to pick up different weapons and clear levels from mobs from monster school.\n\nGame contains:\n- 60 levels\n- 10 bosses\n- Many types of different weapons!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MV1V5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-vs-monster-school/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1007H","slug":"house-flip","title":"House Flip","description":"Buy, fix, and flip houses with a click of your mouse or a tap of your finger in House Flip! Browse the listings, then purchase and inspect a house to see what needs fixing. Hold an open house to see which renovations prospective buyers want. Choose a section of the house to clean, repair, or upgrade, and then play mini-games to do the work yourself. Satisfy the buyers with wise choices and high quality work to push their offers higher. Once you're in the profit-zone, flip that house! Make millions!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1007H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/house-flip/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"744R4","slug":"layer-master","title":"Layer Master","description":"One of the most amazing features of the game is how simple it is. All you have to do is collect the hoops scattered all over the track and avoid obstacles in the form of blocks and other stickman in order to defeat the boss at the end! The more hoops you collect, the bigger your head will be, which can give you a nice bonus at the final stage of the level.\n\nWhat are you waiting for? Start playing right now and test your dexterity and concentration skills. Pass all the obstacles in your way and destroy the boss! Whether you are looking for a fun way to pass the time or you are an experienced gamer, this game is sure to provide you with hours of entertainment.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/744R4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/layer-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O8O75","slug":"obunga-s-backrooms","title":"Obunga's Backrooms","description":"Step into the obunga's backrooms, an intense and heart-pounding 3D horror game that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Are you brave enough to navigate through the twisted corridors and try to escape?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O8O75/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/obunga-s-backrooms/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0044R","slug":"arctic-ale","title":"Arctic Ale","description":"After endless festive revelry, the snowman feels awful, and memories of the past holidays seem like hazy clouds. Urgently needing help to restore his health, the key to recovery lies in a special elixir - Arctic Ale. However, obtaining it is not so simple. Assist the snowman in collecting as much of this elixir as possible to restore his vitality and clarity of memories about the mysterious holidays.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0044R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arctic-ale/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N66IS","slug":"mini-stilts","title":"Mini Stilts","description":"Use your stilts to evade obstacles and reach a delicious candy!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N66IS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-stilts/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"34MM9","slug":"space-mamo","title":"Space Mamo","description":"Space Mamo is a open space shooting game. In which you defeating enemies and bosses to complete the levels. The difficulties increases as the level increases. Don't worry you will get power ups during game play. You will feel like real space war. Enjoy : )\n\n*How To Play :\n\n  Virtual Joystick is there \n\n   Left Joystick - For moving Spaceship\n\n   Right Joystick - For shooting bullets","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/34MM9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-mamo/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I4KLR","slug":"duck-duck-clicker","title":"Duck Duck Clicker","description":"If you feel liking petting ducks, you have arrived at the right place! Click, upgrade, make billions of cute little ducklings to conquer the universe. \nMake it yours! Through a wide range of customizations, you can make the most adorable duck yet to exist in the world.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I4KLR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duck-duck-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U778S","slug":"dusya-and-lava","title":"Dusya and Lava","description":"This addictive puzzle game is reminiscent of the classic Sokoban game where you have to move boxes to achieve a certain goal. However, unlike Sokoban, here you have to not only move boxes, but also avoid lava, collect keys and catch a ball that has flown into the portal. This game offers an exciting journey full of interesting challenges and exciting obstacles. Help Dusya overcome all difficulties and return the ball!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U778S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dusya-and-lava/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6478D","slug":"2048-wood-block","title":"2048 Wood Block","description":"A puzzle game where you have to match numbers from wooden blocks. Example: 2+2=4, 4+4=8, 8+8=16, etc. Be careful and choose the right moves so as not to litter the field. Check how far you will reach the top of player ratings around the world. Good game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6478D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-wood-block/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DES8N","slug":"don-t-press-it","title":"Don't Press It","description":"A friend brought you to a secret base,\nbut he had an urgent need to leave.\n\nHe asked you not to touch anything\nbecause it could have dire consequences.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DES8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/don-t-press-it/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I87M8","slug":"biozombie-of-evil-2","title":"Biozombie of Evil 2","description":"Biozombie of Evil 2 is a zombie shooting game where you play role of a skilled biohazard soldier and your mission is to survive zombie contaminated city streets. You can find driveable vehicle on each level and big arsenal of weapons to unlock.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I87M8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/biozombie-of-evil-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RNA1I","slug":"bffs-flowers-inspired-fashion","title":"BFFs Flowers Inspired Fashion","description":"Welcome to the BFFs Flowers Inspired Fashion. These Bffs are true trendsetters, who love to enjoy the latest fashion. They love nature and natural styles in fashion. They are obsessed with floral designs. Browse their wardrobe and select their favorite one. Then pick suitable costumes and hairstyles which match their outfits.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RNA1I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-flowers-inspired-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RTNR0","slug":"bffs-spring-break-fashionista","title":"Bffs Spring Break Fashionista","description":"Welcome to the Bffs Spring Break Fashionista. Spring break is here. Barbie and their friends are can’t wait to have some fun together. They’ve been waiting for the spring break since the beginning of the year. Help them prepare their spring break outfits! They can finally wear skirts and dresses since it’s really warm outside now, so make sure to create a cute look! Have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RTNR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-spring-break-fashionista/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25742","slug":"heartscape-hero","title":"Heartscape Hero","description":"Embark on an enchanting adventure through whimsical lands filled with love and romance. As the protagonist, your mission is to collect hearts scattered, overcoming obstacles and challenges along the way.\n\nImmerse yourself in a vibrant world teeming with charm and excitement, inspired by the magic of Valentine’s Day. Experience the power of love as you journey to become the ultimate Heartscape Hero.\n\nAre you ready to explore this captivating realm and spread love wherever you go?","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25742/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heartscape-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19IG3","slug":"mr-macagi","title":"Mr. Macagi","description":"Embark on a hilarious adventure with Mr. Macagi, on a quest to collect apples. The challenge intensifies as mischievous monsters lurk, adding an element of suspense.\n\nCan you help Mr. Macagi gather apples while evading these comical creatures? Get ready for a delightful and entertaining gaming experience!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19IG3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-macagi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I8EEI","slug":"icewizard-adventure","title":"Icewizard Adventure","description":"icewizard adventure is an action adventure game, explore all levels get items in all levels and defeat enemies and bosses\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I8EEI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/icewizard-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MSI9F","slug":"prism-fashionistas-dress-to-impress","title":"Prism Fashionistas Dress to Impress","description":"Explore Prism Girls, a captivating dress-up game with seven dolls embodying rainbow colors. From fiery Ruby to elegant Luna, each brings a unique vibe. Seamlessly blend makeup and dress-up, experimenting with eyeshadow, lipstick, and more. In the dress-up level, mix accessories and outfits for endless creativity. Prism Girls is a joyful adventure into colorful expression and fashion possibilities. Unleash your creativity and enjoy the pure fun of style exploration!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MSI9F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/prism-fashionistas-dress-to-impress/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7EA4E","slug":"zombie-treasure-adventure","title":"Zombie Treasure Adventure","description":"zombie treasure adventure is an html5 platformer action game, get the treasure stored in the zombie forest, defeat and kill zombies in all levels get items\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7EA4E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-treasure-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S7EAA","slug":"zombies-assault","title":"Zombies Assault","description":"zombie assault is an html5 platformer action game, defend your territory from zombie attacks, shoot them and destroy the enemies that come, get coins in all levels and get gems to go to the next level\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S7EAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-assault/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L32H9","slug":"vegetables-crush","title":"Vegetables Crush","description":"vegetables crush is a match 3 html5 game, draw a line to match and get lots of points\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L32H9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vegetables-crush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y3G25","slug":"sky-fighter-2-groundwar","title":"Sky Fighter 2 Groundwar","description":"sky fighter 2 groundwar is a vertically scrolling shoot 'em html5 game, defeat shooting enemies get items and be the winner","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y3G25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-fighter-2-groundwar/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"107S5","slug":"cyber-knight-slashman","title":"Cyber Knight Slashman","description":"cyber knight slashman is an html5 action platformer game, fight against enemy robots and get items in all stages\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/107S5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cyber-knight-slashman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9K757","slug":"duck-shoot","title":"Duck Shoot","description":"Duck Shoot is an HTML5 arcade shooting game, aim at the duck and shoot first, don't shoot the rooster\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9K757/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duck-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"767T6","slug":"valentine-s-match-3","title":"Valentine's Match 3","description":"Valentins Match 3 and enjoy this addictive hearts matching different colours game as you collect items and complete different missions.Your goal is to clear the hearts by finding and matching all hearts before the time runs out!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/767T6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/valentins-match-3/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LN369","slug":"blondy-in-pink","title":"Blondy in Pink","description":"Rencontrez le favori universel-Blondie! Elle est une vraie fashionista et une fille très mignonne. Et comme toutes les filles, Blondie adore le rose! Passons une journée avec cette charmante blonde. D'abord, nous apprenons comment elle prend soin de son visage. Ensuite, choisissez pour Blondie lumineux maquillage élégant avec toutes sortes de nuances de rose. Après le maquillage vient le tour d'une coiffure magnifique et des bijoux brillants. Et enfin, choisissez l'une des nombreuses tenues brillantes pour notre fille. Ne pas oublier de compléter les vêtements avec des accessoires de mode. Maintenant, emmenez votre animal de compagnie avec vous et partez pour une promenade avec Blondie.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LN369/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blondy-in-pink/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3VE2D","slug":"festival-dia-de-muertos","title":"Festival Dia de Muertos","description":"Le jour des Morts est une joyeuse fête de la vie. L'amour, la mémoire et la vénération sont les thèmes principaux de cet événement. Le jour des Morts est célébré au Mexique et aux États-Unis, dans des endroits où vivent de grandes communautés mexicaines. Cette année, les princesses la petite Sirène, Lisa et Jacqueline participent également au Festival. Aidez les filles à faire un maquillage impressionnant Pour le jour des Morts, créer une coiffure luxueuse avec des tresses et, bien sûr, choisir des tenues décentes pour une fête aussi inhabituelle!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3VE2D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/festival-dia-de-muertos/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IPE60","slug":"princess-sweet-kawaii-fashion","title":"Princess Sweet Kawaii Fashion","description":"La princesse Eliza se rend au Japon pour étudier le style kawaii adolescent. La gamme principale de la garde - robe kawaii-les nuances touchantes traditionnelles: rose, vert pâle, jaune, bleu. Les images des personnages d'anime préférés sont souvent utilisées comme impressions. Et toutes sortes d'arcs, de dentelles et de volants sont utilisés comme ornements. Le style kawaii présente également une couleur de cheveux inhabituelle. Et le maquillage n'est limité que par votre imagination. Il n'y a pas de place pour les nuances ennuyeuses, seulement des tons doux et des paillettes! Créez votre propre look kawaii unique avec la princesse Elisa!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IPE60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-sweet-kawaii-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D72GR","slug":"parking-order","title":"Parking Order","description":"\"Parking Order!\" is a fantastic puzzle game that allows you to test your parking and driving skills. By parking your cars in the correct order, you can unlock new levels and embark on a thrilling adventure, progressing from simple to complex levels.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D72GR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parking-order/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2OPA5","slug":"poppy-stickman-battle-royale","title":"Poppy Stickman Battle Royale","description":"poppy stickman battle royale Game with various Missions of Fighting\nPlay Incredible Stickman Games and Smash all the Superhero Stickman Villains\nBecome poppy Stickman Hero to destroy all the Villains or Gangsters’ Monsters\nShow your Superhero Incredible skills to Smash the City with Monster Fighting.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2OPA5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-stickman-battle-royale/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3OAFS","slug":"lucy-all-season-fashionista","title":"Lucy All Season Fashionista","description":"$20","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3OAFS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lucy-all-season-fashionista/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3XE9I","slug":"spaceship-explorer","title":"Spaceship Explorer","description":"spaceship explorer is an endless flying html5 game, touch and hold the screen to fly through space avoiding incoming enemies and get a score","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3XE9I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaceship-explorer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G0OGN","slug":"jungle-coloring-game","title":"Jungle Coloring Game","description":"Unleash your creativity and immerse yourself in a world of vivid colors with Jungle Coloring Coloring Game! This interactive coloring book brings a delightful experience for artists of all ages. Dive into an expansive collection of designs ranging from serene landscapes to intricate patterns. Jungle Coloring Coloring Game offers an escape to a digital canvas where imagination is your only limit. Choose your palette, fill in the hues, and watch each page come to life with every touch. Whether you're looking to relax, improve your coloring skills, or simply have some fun, Jungle Coloring Coloring Game is the perfect blend of entertainment and relaxation. Ready your colors and bring joy to your day with Jungle Coloring Coloring Game - where every stroke adds brightness to your world!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G0OGN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jungle-coloring-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7U3O0","slug":"autumn-fashion-game-for-girls","title":"Autumn Fashion Game For Girls","description":"Autumn Fashion Game For Girls combines creativity and fun in one stylish package. Assemble chic outfits and accessories to create the perfect look. In Autumn Fashion Game For Girls, every girl gets to be the fashionista she dreams to be. Transform your ideas into fashion statements with Autumn Fashion Game For Girls!\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7U3O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/autumn-fashion-game-for-girls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"V1EHT","slug":"christmas-elves-coloring-game","title":"Christmas Elves Coloring Game","description":"Calling all coloring connoisseurs! Christmas Elves Coloring Game is the quintessential coloring game that blends fun with relaxation. Whether you're into doodling, painting, or coloring, this game has it all. With an easy-to-navigate interface and a vast selection of coloring pages, Christmas Elves Coloring Game is perfect for artists of every skill level.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/V1EHT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-elves-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENE6E","slug":"best-friends-puzzle","title":"Best Friends Puzzle","description":"Embarquez dans une aventure épique avec les héros insectes et aidez-les à vaincre les oiseaux menaçants de la forêt ! Reliez stratégiquement au moins trois symboles de la même couleur pour doter les héros de leurs avantages spéciaux. Explorez les forêts verdoyantes avec vos amis les insectes.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENE6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/best-friends-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P4A13","slug":"asteroids-survival","title":"Asteroids Survival","description":"In Adteroids Survival you objective is to destroy all the asteroids and collect money and power up to improve your ship while surviving at the enemies who will chase you. The controls are simple, press w to go forward and s or d to rotate the ship and the spacebar to shoot. On mobile you can use the simple controls that will appears on your screen. You can spend your money in the shop where you can change ship's skin and statistics.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P4A13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-survival/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"855T5","slug":"twin-ball","title":"Twin Ball","description":"Twin Ball is a HTML5 and Mobile Game.!Let the ball stop within the specified range , you can get high marks","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/855T5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twin-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8L3NE","slug":"tictactoe-vs-ai","title":"TicTacToe vs AI","description":"Take your Tic Tac Toe game to the next level with online multiplayer! Challenge players from around the globe in real-time matches. Experience the thrill of international competition. Discover different playing styles and strategies from all corners of the world. \n\nKey Features:\nComplete with Smart AI with easy and hard modes\nChallenge players from around the globe\nFamily-Friendly\nEndless Fun","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8L3NE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictactoe-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3U536","slug":"ludo-offline","title":"Ludo Offline","description":"Roll the dice, strategize your moves, and experience the timeless joy of Ludo! Play offline, enjoy smart \nAI opponents. Ludo is the ultimate mobile rendition of the classic board game. Download now for endless \nfun and become the Ludo Master! 🏆 #Ludo #BoardGameFun\n\nKey Features:\nClassic Gameplay\nComplete with Smart AI components\nFamily-Friendly\nEndless Fun","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3U536/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ludo-offline/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ABA0N","slug":"balloon-ascending","title":"Balloon Ascending","description":"Balloon Ascending is a fun casual game that requires a minimal amount of interaction. Don’t let the obstacles touch the balloon. Score as many points and reach the highest point.\n\nKey Features:\nFamily-Friendly\nEndless Fun\nUltra casual\nEasy to learn and play","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ABA0N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-ascending/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S775L","slug":"dots-n-lines","title":"Dots n Lines","description":"Dots n Lines is a simple game to learn, but mastery requires strategic thinking. Don't just focus on immediate boxes; anticipate how your lines might create future opportunities for yourself or block your \nopponent. Boxes in the center of the grid offer more potential connections, so try to claim them early.  Sometimes, deliberately drawing lines that benefit your opponent slightly can force them to complete boxes you want, giving you another turn. Don't be afraid to take risks and make unexpected moves to surprise your opponent.\n\n\nKey Features:\nClassic Gameplay\nComplete with Smart AI components\nChallenge players from around the globe\nFamily-Friendly\nEndless Fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S775L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dots-n-lines/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3PCC7","slug":"bullet-and-cry-in-space","title":"Bullet and Cry in Space","description":"Bullet and cry in space is a action horror first person shooter game set in a massive dark spaceship.\n\nExperience the ultimate thrill with our action horror first person shooter game set in a dark spaceship. Immerse yourself in an adventure as you navigate through the eerie corridors of a dark spacecraft. With realistic graphics and intense sound effects, you'll feel like you're truly trapped in this terrifying world. As you make your way through the ship, you'll encounter gruesome creatures lurking in the shadows, you must fight for humanity and uncover the mysteries of the abandoned vessel. Be prepared for intense battles and scares as you uncover the dark secrets hidden within the spaceship.\n\nWith a combination of action, horror, and first person shooter elements, this game is perfect for shooter and horror enthusiasts alike.\n\nGame features\n\n    Varied and atmospheric environment\n    Interesting enemies and monsters\n    Simple and entertaining story\n    Intense action shooter gameplay ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3PCC7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullet-and-cry-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R1RLA","slug":"island-wars","title":"Island Wars","description":"Island Wars. An interesting arcade shooter with many locations. Pass all bosses and destroy all enemies, Explore interesting locations, Play on all your devices, Good mood and good luck in battle. ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R1RLA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/island-wars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YIT0K","slug":"italian-take-away","title":"Italian Take Away","description":"Welcome to Italian Take Away!\nItalian Take Away is a simple but fun game where you can make tasty Italian cuisine such as Pizza, Piadinas and more!\nEarn money by selling food and completing quests.\n\n\nInspired by the food from the Italian region Emilia-Romagna.\nDeveloper: TechTekle","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YIT0K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/italian-take-away/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TA56E","slug":"impossible-car-stunt-game","title":"Impossible Car Stunt Game","description":"$21","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TA56E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/impossible-car-stunt-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JUANJ","slug":"bullet-and-jump","title":"Bullet And Jump","description":"In this adventure, bullets are coming from everywhere, and you must dodge them. Run away from the bullets for 100 seconds and win. Choose either the blue or red player along with your friend and dodge all the bullets. Every time you touch a bullet, the duration increases by 1 second, so be careful and avoid touching them. Compete with your friend and win; you need to defeat your friend.\n\n*Press WASD keys to move the red player. \n*Press the Arrow keys to move the blue player.\n*Dodge for 100 seconds, and the first one to finish the time wins.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JUANJ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullet-and-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9LZGL","slug":"falling-ballz","title":"Falling Ballz","description":"Falling Ballz is an HTML5 and Mobile Game.! Swipe your finger/Mouse to throw the balls down and break different shapes. Try to break as many shapes as possible before they move to the top","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9LZGL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-ballz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TT0H4","slug":"in-the-path","title":"In The Path","description":"In this game your objective is change direction ball for the path for no collision in the walls and obtain gems for purchase more skins and reach the best score and unlock 8 new skins.\n\nControl:\nTap for change ball direction","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TT0H4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/in-the-path/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SSB4B","slug":"sugar-jelly-blast","title":"Sugar Jelly Blast","description":"sugar jelly blast is a match 3 html5 game, match 3 or more candies and crush them to get a score from it\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SSB4B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sugar-jelly-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20AT2","slug":"super-galaxy-fighter-2","title":"Super Galaxy Fighter 2","description":"super galaxy fighter 2 is an endless shooter html5 game, shoot enemy planes and get items for the best score\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20AT2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-galaxy-fighter-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PB4R6","slug":"robot-trooper","title":"Robot Trooper","description":"robot trooper is an html5 platformer game, a scifi robot action game, defeat the enemy by shooting and slash, get all the items to score on all stages","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PB4R6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-trooper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LTGFF","slug":"angela-perfect-valentine","title":"Angela Perfect Valentine","description":"Welcome to the Angela Perfect Valentine game. Angela and Tom love to spend time together on this valentine. They plan to wear new clothes and post them on social media. Tom has a surprise plan for Angela. Browse their wardrobe for perfect clothes. Play and help the couples. Have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LTGFF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angela-perfect-valentine/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L13ET","slug":"cupid-valentine-tic-tac-toe","title":"Cupid Valentine Tic Tac Toe","description":"Engage in the whimsical world of ‘Cupid Valentine Tic-Tac-Toe’! Play the classic game with a love-filled twist as Cupid guides your moves. Enjoy romantic visuals, challenge friends or AI, and experience the joy of strategic fun. Elevate your Valentine’s Day with this charming, heart-filled rendition of Tic-Tac-Toe. Spread the love and embark on a delightful journey with Cupid as your playful companion in this enchanting game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L13ET/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cupid-valentine-tic-tac-toe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TNG1N","slug":"hunting-submarine-attack","title":"Hunting - Submarine Attack","description":"Vous êtes le capitaine d`un sous-marin. Le but de la mission est de torpiller autant de navires de guerre que possible. Les navires civils ne peuvent pas être torpillés.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TNG1N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hunting-submarine-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25GBS","slug":"stickman-upgrade-battle","title":"Stickman Upgrade Battle","description":"Stickman Upgrade Battle est un jeu de Stickman accrocheur et un jeu d'action palpitant propulsé par la technologie HTML5 pour fonctionner dans les navigateurs modernes.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25GBS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-upgrade-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UU74E","slug":"hungry-lion-adventure","title":"Hungry Lion Adventure","description":"Embark on an adventure in 'Hungry Lion's Feast,' where you must master the art of rope cutting to feed a hungry lion. Navigate through jungle obstacles and solve puzzles across numerous levels. With addictive gameplay, stunning visuals, and immersive challenges, will you rise to become the jungle's ultimate feeder?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UU74E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hungry-lion-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G90MI","slug":"missing-number","title":"Missing Number","description":"Find Missing Number Math Educational Game For Kids !\n50 Levels - Easy Math Game for kids - Helps kids to recognize missing number between four choices!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G90MI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/missing-number/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8GH08","slug":"put-it-together","title":"Put It Together","description":"Increase the values of the numeric blocks, thinking over the moves in advance to collect as powerful a combination as possible and collect as many points as possible!\n\nThere are 3 visual styles waiting for you in the game:\nClassic - Sustained style, catchy colors and clear text.\nThe new one is bold in color, but soft in the shape of the blocks.\nNight - For fans of minimalism and comfortable play in the evening and at night.\n\nAlso waiting for you:\n- Nice animation\n- Relaxing gameplay\n- Good soundtrack","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8GH08/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/put-it-together/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"672O0","slug":"ball-dodge","title":"Ball Dodge","description":"Try or die to dodge all the floating red balls for some reason.\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/672O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-dodge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5IQD6","slug":"pandiq-brain-training","title":"Pandiq - Brain Training","description":"Welcome to the world of intellectual development with our unique brain training app!\n\n🧠 Train Your Memory: Play exciting games designed to improve your memory and concentration ability. Unique tasks and puzzles will help you remember information better and for longer.\n\nDevelop Thinking: Our exercises develop logical thinking, improve analytical skills and contribute to more effective decision-making in everyday life.\n\nStrengthen Your Attention: Train your ability to focus and keep your attention on tasks. Effective exercises will help you become more attentive and concentrated.\n\nDon't miss the chance to improve your mind and become more productive in your daily life!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5IQD6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pandiq-brain-training/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4M977","slug":"bomberman-emoji","title":"Bomberman Emoji","description":"“Bomberman Emoji” is a game based on the mechanics of the classic “Bomberman”, destroy the boxes to find the key and go to the next level, be careful not to die to the explosion of the bombs or enemies, can you complete all the levels?","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4M977/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bomberman-emoji/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IAATM","slug":"mahjong-at-home-scandinavian-edition","title":"Mahjong at Home - Scandinavian Edition","description":"Discover the magic of Nordic winter with 'Mahjong Scandinavian Winter Edition'. Immerse yourself in this high-quality Mahjong game, featuring Nordic themes and designs inspired by winter landscapes and the serenity of Scandinavia.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IAATM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-at-home-scandinavian-edition/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A50AA","slug":"ninja-war","title":"Ninja War","description":"Ninja War is an HTML5 platformer action game, fighting between groups of ninjas fighting for territory, destroy your enemy, get 3 gems or more to go to the next level","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A50AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-war/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01TV7","slug":"out-of-lava","title":"Out of Lava","description":"Out of Lava is a very fun and never-ending game.\nThe objective of the game is to get as far as you can through a maze of rooms and traps, where lava chases you through every room.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01TV7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/out-of-lava/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I9ROO","slug":"virology","title":"Virology","description":"Step into the captivating world of \"Virology,\" a 2D platformer where you embody a crafty virus on a mission to infect innocent characters. With its retro-meets-vibrant visuals, this game offers thrilling platforming challenges as you dash, jump, and infiltrate your way through a labyrinthine landscape. Can you outwit and outmaneuver your pixelated prey in this highly infectious adventure?","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I9ROO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/virology/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8WPU5","slug":"pong-with-power-ups","title":"Pong with Power Ups","description":"Pong with powerups is your classic pong game with a twist! Colored blocks will fall down and give you a powerup if your ball hits it! It is also focused on the retro theme. You can play this single player vs an AI or you can play it with a friend!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8WPU5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pong-with-power-ups/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ST4U7","slug":"what-kind-of-santa-claus-are-you","title":"What kind of Santa Claus are you?!","description":"Chaque fois que Morozy a une raison : une situation difficile, une situation difficile et une période inconnue. Est-ce que tu penses que c'est à ce moment-là que tu es le plus grand de tous?\n\nСуществует синдром Деда Мороза. C'est exactement ce qu'il faut faire pour que vous puissiez acheter un sac, des dépenses russes et des dépenses. Si vous êtes un « symptôme » pour marquer votre test, que pensez-vous : « C'est toi, Deed Moroz ?! et c'est ce que tu fais!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ST4U7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-kind-of-santa-claus-are-you/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A748A","slug":"save-the-cats","title":"Save the Cats","description":"Save the cute little cats by throwing the yarn ball toward the handle of the cage, from the cage and set them free.\n\nHow to play:\nDrag your finger or mouse on the screen and after adjusting the angle of the throw toward the cage handle, drop your finger or mouse, so that the yarn ball is thrown to the cage handle and the cage door opens.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A748A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-cats/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IIE01","slug":"deril2","title":"Deril2","description":"Welcome to the Deril 2 game, try to kill your opponent with arrows before he does","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IIE01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deril2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6CL45","slug":"big-velocity","title":"Big Velocity","description":"Big velocity, Speed game","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6CL45/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-velocity/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8O11C","slug":"soccer3","title":"Soccer3","description":"welcome to the Soccer3 game, score goals and don't let them do it","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8O11C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer3/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZLLZ6","slug":"8x8-block-puzzle","title":"8x8 Block Puzzle","description":"The goal of the game is to use your logical imagination to collect blocks, placing them on an 8x8 field.\n\nAdvantages of the game:\n- develops thinking and logic;\n- endless level;\n- use moves wisely to extend the game timer;\n- global rating;\n- a break from everyday activities and relaxation during a calm gameplay!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZLLZ6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/8x8-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SAE81","slug":"organizer-master","title":"Organizer Master","description":"An engaging 3D puzzle with numerous levels. Find pairs and arrange objects so that everything fits. Develop spatial thinking and solve challenges. Enjoy high-quality 3D graphics in this captivating browser puzzle game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SAE81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/organizer-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"02T07","slug":"throw-fast","title":"Throw Fast","description":"Welcome to the Throw Fast knife throwing game, let's see how many you can place...","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/02T07/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/throw-fast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"74277","slug":"boogers","title":"Boogers","description":"Le moment est venu de remettre chaque chose à sa place et de faire plaisir à votre ami avec attention.\n\n\"Boogers\" est un nouveau succès pour une utilisation pratique : vous ouvrez l'application, activez la recherche d'un lieu potentiel d'attraction de morve et regardez l'écran. Quelques instants seulement et vous laisserez votre marque là où elle est nécessaire.\n\nNe perdez pas le moment.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/74277/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boogers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TS0O4","slug":"sword-throw","title":"Sword Throw","description":"Des réflexes rapides, de la précision et une bonne visée sont tout ce dont vous avez besoin dans ce jeu stimulant. Avec la puissance d'un robinet au bon moment, vous pourrez lancer tous les couteaux et gagner les niveaux.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TS0O4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sword-throw/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A3A09","slug":"bananacat-clicker","title":"BananaCAT Clicker","description":"Embark on a charming adventure with \"BananaCAT Clicker,\" an engaging mobile game that combines feline cuteness with addictive tapping fun. Navigate a world filled with banana-wielding cats, each click bringing you closer to banana bonanzas. Upgrade your cat companions and unlock new, whimsical characters as you amass bananas for ultimate satisfaction. With vibrant visuals and delightful sound effects, the game offers a captivating experience that's easy to pick up and hard to put down. Join the craze, enjoy the thrill of accumulating bananas, and immerse yourself in the delightful universe of \"Relaxing BananaCAT Clicker\" for endless entertainment on the go.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A3A09/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bananacat-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ASB15","slug":"stacky-blocks","title":"Stacky Blocks","description":"Des réflexes rapides et de la précision sont tout ce qui est nécessaire dans ce jeu stimulant. Avec la puissance d'un toucher au bon moment, vous pourrez atteindre plus haut !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ASB15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stacky-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R1RE9","slug":"shark-escape","title":"Shark Escape","description":"Dive into «Shark Escape»! Navigate intense chases, level up your ship, and boost lifepoints. Outswim the odds for the ultimate high score!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R1RE9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shark-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AQ05A","slug":"iq-test-brain-training","title":"IQ Test - Brain Training","description":"IQ Test - Brain Training\n\nExercise Your Brain! You have 40 minutes to answer 40 questions. \nCorrect answer +3 points. Wrong answer -1 point. The skip button does not influence your score. GOOD LUCK!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AQ05A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/iq-test-brain-training/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91T5L","slug":"sky-fighter-blazing","title":"Sky Fighter Blazing","description":"sky fighter blazing is an html5 aircraft shooting game, enemy planes are attacking villages and ready for great war, get items for scores save citizens and destroy enemy planes","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91T5L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-fighter-blazing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"165JF","slug":"ninja-boy-flying","title":"Ninja Boy Flying","description":"ninja boy flying is an html5 arcade game, ninja stones to collect coins avoid incoming enemies and get reels to fly","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/165JF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-boy-flying/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S8406","slug":"alchemist-bubbles","title":"Alchemist Bubbles","description":"alchemist bubble is an html5 bubble shooting game, shoot bubbles according to color and get the highest cores","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S8406/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alchemist-bubbles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E3232","slug":"counter-craft-4","title":"Counter Craft 4","description":"Counter Craft 4 features explosive gameplay where your mission is to shoot hundreds of blocky zombies using different types of weapons and explosives to massively destroy blocky undead. Try to survive each round in order to win and unlock new guns.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E3232/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-craft-4/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NMNTN","slug":"mask-man-adventure","title":"Mask Man Adventure","description":"$22","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NMNTN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mask-man-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E777R","slug":"race-time","title":"Race Time","description":"Get the fastest car, upgrade its powers and do your best to get first in the shortest time possible!\nCharge the super boost: once it reaches lv. 5, double-click to activate it!\nWhen the super boost is active, you can knock off the track your opponents to get an higher position and bonus points!\nFinish the race in the shortest time possible and try to beat your friends in the online ranking!\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E777R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/race-time/embed?sid=1","plays":39528,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OBO86","slug":"super-afro-bro","title":"Super Afro Bro","description":"MARIO STYLE PLATFORM GAME. (PLAYING WITH CONTROL PAD IS RECOMMENDED)HAVE FUN WITH A PURE MARIO STYLE GAME","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OBO86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-afro-bro/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"738H3","slug":"popping-sushi","title":"Popping Sushi","description":"Drop those cute little sushi pieces and make them pop!\nWhen two same pieces touch each other, they merge into a bigger one!\nTry to get the biggest piece and make the highest score on the online leaderboard!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/738H3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popping-sushi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TEML0","slug":"platformer-hell","title":"Platformer Hell","description":"use arrow keys for p1\nand wasd for 2 player","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TEML0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/platformer-hell/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55111","slug":"banana-poker","title":"Banana Poker","description":"Poker. It can be hard to learn and surely very hard to master. If you put in the effort, it's a lot of fun and good for your brain. Nice that it's been given a sweet cartoon makeover. Enter Banana Poker...","category":"Course","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banana-poker/embed?sid=1","plays":40054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0W6W","slug":"tower-cube","title":"Tower Cube","description":"Tap & hold to scale a block equal the one below it and stack them up to build a skyscraper! Collect coin to unlock new types of block. Tower Cubes is a simple yet exciting and addictive game that will keep the player entertained for hours!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0W6W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-cube/embed?sid=1","plays":39475,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77AH6","slug":"smash","title":"Smash","description":" Smash est une mise à niveau passionnante du jeu de cache-cache classique ! Dans le jeu, vous serez affecté au hasard à l’équipe Blue hide ou à l’équipe Red Smash. Si vous êtes un cacheur, votre mission est de vous déplacer doucement et rapidement, de vous fondre dans votre environnement en faisant semblant d'être un objet normal et de récupérer toutes les clés avant que vos adversaires ne vous découvrent et ne vous écrasent.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77AH6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MI510","slug":"memorix","title":"Memorix","description":"$23","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MI510/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memorix/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"74C4T","slug":"popcorn-time","title":"Popcorn Time","description":"Popcorn time is a game that is very suitable for those of you who like relaxing games. Popcorn game that you can play anywhere and anytime. With a popcorn popper, you can pop the popcorn until it's completely filled. \n\nYou may be wondering, is the popcorn pop game even fun? So why don't you try playing it now? To play this popcorn game you also have to pay attention to popcorn trivia, because you will be required to fill the bucket until it is full and the popcorn must not spill or get out of the bucket. So you have to be careful when filling the bucket with the popcorn maker. \n\nFeature : \n- 80 Levels \n- Interesting animation \n- Design and effects \n- Popcorn pop with levels full of challenges \n- Easy to understand to play \n\nSo don't hesitate to play this exciting popcorn time. Don't forget to leave a review so we can be even better at developing this popcorn time game. Thank You","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/74C4T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popcorn-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2D5R7","slug":"suika-world","title":"Suika World","description":"This is a popular Japanese puzzle game. In it, you need to score as many points as possible by connecting the same fruits. But the distinctive feature of this particular game is the additional objects on the levels. You may come across a stone that cannot be connected to anything. Or a bomb that will push away all the fruits around it, and at the same time break all the stones. There are other interesting bonuses on the levels.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2D5R7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/suika-world/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"72E1R","slug":"speed-run-platformer-2d","title":"Speed-Run Platformer 2D!","description":"How Fast can You Complete this Timed Platformer?\nSpeed-Run Platformer 2D is a challenge to complete this seemingly simple 2D platformer in as little time as possible!\nHow fast can you complete it?","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/72E1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speed-run-platformer-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SO1S5","slug":"retro-space-dodger","title":"Retro Space Dodger!","description":"Dodge Asteroids, Ships, and other Debris in all new Retro Space Dodger!\n\nAs the ship follows the mouse, Guide your spaceship through the obstacles and gain points and power-ups!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SO1S5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-space-dodger/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R30RR","slug":"retro-racer-3d","title":"Retro Racer 3D","description":"Retro Racer is a great game about overtaking slow cars, but that’s not all. If we hit one of the cars, the police will start chasing us and we have to escape from them! As with any car, you won’t go far without fuel, so don’t forget to collect it.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R30RR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-racer-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0SBSE","slug":"telekinesis-attack","title":"Telekinesis Attack","description":"Use your telekinesis magic power! Gain the ability to control the power of thought! Throw your enemies wherever you want, hit them against whatever you want and deal with them however you want! Using your unique power, defeat all enemies, interact with different objects, take away weapons from enemies and be the strongest!\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0SBSE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/telekinesis-battle-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5044H","slug":"how-many-mice","title":"How Many Mice","description":"In \"How Many Mice\" you have to guess the right number of mice on screen. You can help yourself touching the screen, uncovering the hidden mice, but the more you click, the less points you get.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5044H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/how-many-mice/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ARC60","slug":"soccer-snakes","title":"Soccer Snakes","description":"Two wild, clumsy snakes competing in a soccer match is the perfect mix of humor, chaos, and sports. Play solo or share your keyboard with a friend and score some 'hiss-terical' fun with Soccer Snakes!\n\nRelease the snakes from their cages TAP or pressing SPACE. Use side ARROWS or TAP SIDES on touch devices to steer your snake, and press UP ARROW or TAP BOTH SIDES AT THE SAME TIME to headbutt the ball with more power. Recharge your headbutt energy eating the blue shiny dots.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ARC60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-snakes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S483C","slug":"crizy-balls","title":"Crizy Balls","description":"Crazy Balls is a new and unique casual game. Try not to lose your temper\nSoar in the sky and survive the dash of balls that are different in color from you\nAvoid balls to survive your life and be a real manipulator\n\nThis game is very easy and needs one finger to play, just tap your phone screen and move your finger\n\nInstructions that will help you:\nWhen you touch a ball of the same color or type as the one you are using as a player, all enemy balls will be killed\n\nWhen you kill all the different balls, you will get money that will help you buy skins\n\nYou have to pick up valuable gems because you will use them to develop the player","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S483C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crizy-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENPL6","slug":"guard-my-planet","title":"Guard my Planet","description":"Guard my Planet is a game set in the backdrop of interplanetary warfare. At this moment, your planet is facing the danger of invasion, and it needs your help to overcome every challenge posed by the invaders. It's time to showcase your leadership skills!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENPL6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guard-my-planet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"02HME","slug":"cake-smash","title":"Cake Smash","description":"Unleash your sweet tooth in a delightful adventure! Join and smash a variety of delectable cakes to create the ultimate confectionery masterpiece.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/02HME/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cake-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"47CU0","slug":"fruit-chop","title":"Fruit Chop","description":"Embark on a juicy slicing frenzy! Swipe and skillfully cut through a rainbow of fruits, but beware of the bombs – can you master the art of Fruit Chop without a mishap?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/47CU0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-chop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENR8A","slug":"solitaire-champions","title":"Solitaire Champions","description":"Elevate your solitaire game to legendary status! Solitaire Champions offers a refined experience for those seeking the pinnacle of card mastery – play like a true champion.","category":"Course","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENR8A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-champions/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H78W7","slug":"emoji-with-friends","title":"Emoji with Friends","description":"Express your way to victory! Dive into an engaging emoji puzzle game that challenges your wit and creativity, all while having a blast with friends.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H78W7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emoji-with-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R0TTT","slug":"tetra-twist","title":"Tetra Twist","description":"Our take on a timeless classic, with a twist, known for its addictive gameplay, with its simple yet challenging gameplay and enduring appeal. Clear lines by fitting various geometric shapes.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R0TTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tetra-twist/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4O4EP","slug":"soccer-play","title":"Soccer Play","description":"Casual Soccer at its best with easy to play pull back and strike controls. Get your strikers formation and aim for the goal post. Soccer Strike is the perfect blend of casual and competitive gameplay appealing to every soccer fan out there. This is our instant game take on the most popular sport in the world.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4O4EP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-play/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4DR88","slug":"island-of-treasures","title":"Island Of Treasures","description":"Stuck as Pirate in a forsaken island full of treasures you run for your life while fighting the evil pirates collecting all the treasures on your way. Enjoy a thrilling 3D endless runner experience in Island of Treasures.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4DR88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/island-of-treasures/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4Y33L","slug":"carrom-play","title":"Carrom Play","description":"A good old game of Carrom with a great deal of elegance and sophistication thrown in. Play a variety of challenges in Solo, against a Bot or against a real player and never get bored. Choose from a variety of traditional, contemporary or funky Boards, Strikers and Coins. Carrom Play is one of those games that one can get lost into for hours together.","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4Y33L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/carrom-play/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ETAIN","slug":"fire-and-water-ball","title":"Fire and Water Ball","description":"Are you willing to help Fire and Water, the adventurous siblings, in the temple? Help them to escape from the temple. Both siblings need to work together to get out of the temple. Collect keys and coins in the temple. To activate the portals, all keys and coins need to be collected. Both siblings need to reach the portal.\n\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ETAIN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fire-and-water-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BA8IP","slug":"noob-vs-bacon-jumping","title":"Noob vs Bacon Jumping","description":"Hello! An exciting adventure awaits you where you need to escape sharp spikes rising from the ground. The spikes are coming from below, and you must constantly climb higher without stopping. Reach the highest point either alone or with your friend. Be careful of the spikes coming from below. Collect all the coins on the way and buy yourself different costumes.\n\nUse the WASD keys to move and jump in the game.\nUse the Arrow Keys keys to move and jump in the game.\n*Mobile Control Available ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BA8IP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-bacon-jumping/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00120","slug":"steve-and-alex-vs-fnaf","title":"Steve and Alex vs Fnaf","description":"Steve and Alex need to escape from the FNAF monsters in their adventure. They must evade the FNAF monsters everywhere, or eliminate them all. Collect all the gold and become the owner of the keys. The red player should collect the red key, and the blue player should collect the blue key.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  \n*double jump available  \n*jump on it to kill!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00120/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-and-alex-vs-fnaf/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2728T","slug":"2troll-cat","title":"2Troll Cat","description":"In the world of black and white, inhabited by two troll cats, survival is crucial. Gather all the paws and advance towards the portal. To rescue the troll cats, you must successfully complete each level. Collect the paws with your friend. Guide the cats to the portal. Complete the levels and finish all the stages.\n\n*Use the Arrow Keys to move the Black Cat.\n*Use the WASD to move the White Cat.\n*both mobile and desktop playability.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2728T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2troll-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E57EE","slug":"lemonade-war","title":"Lemonade War","description":"Would you like to pick lemons and win the race? Collect lemons to defeat your friend. You must help the blue and red players win the lemon race. Grab the lemons from the tree in the middle of the map and take them to the lemon stand. The person who collects the most lemons wins the race. Gather lemons and win the game. The water is slowly rising, and your only chance is to collect lemons as quickly as possible.\n\n*Press WASD keys to move the red player. \n*Press the Arrow keys to move the blue player. \n*Collect lemons from the tree and take them to the lemon stand to score points.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E57EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lemonade-war/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EDT19","slug":"friends-battle-tnt","title":"Friends Battle TNT","description":"Are you up for an intense challenge with your friends? You should compete against your friend. Its the perfect time for a race with your friend. The one who collects flying TNTs the fastest wins. There are two teams, red and blue. The team that collects the most TNTs wins. The first to collect 20 TNTs wins. You must collect them before your friend does. Catch the TNTs flying in the air.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. The blue player moves using the arrow keys. Collect the TnT and bring it to the chest.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EDT19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-tnt/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I5EEA","slug":"friends-battle-tag-flag","title":"Friends Battle Tag Flag","description":"In the second game of the Friends Battle series, two friends are racing for the flag this time. Whoever holds the flag loses. Avoid the flag for 2 minutes, and win the game. The one who grabs the flag is the loser. Catch your friend and give them the flag. Remember, you should run away from whoever holds the flag. Dont forget, time is running out, and you might lose the game. Join this adventure with your friend.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. \nThe blue player moves using the arrow keys.\nRun away from the flag; whoever has the flag loses.\nAvoid the flag for 2 minutes.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5EEA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-tag-flag/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16DS4","slug":"friends-battle-swords-drawn","title":"Friends Battle Swords Drawn","description":"In the third episode of the Friends Battle series, swords have been drawn, and the war is about to begin. The battle starts; sharpen your sword, you need a sharp blade. Together with your friend, the one who captures the flag the most wins. The winner is the one who stays with the flag for 20 seconds. Dont forget, you have a sword and you also need to set up your flag. While setting up your flag, you must reach the enemys flag. Kill your friend with the sword and capture the flag.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. \nThe blue player moves using the arrow keys.\nStay at the flag for 20 seconds.\nYou can press S and DOWN ARROW to kill the enemy.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16DS4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-swords-drawn/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TE2WO","slug":"polltheflowers","title":"PollTheFlowers","description":"$24","category":"Action","tags":["junior","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TE2WO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/polltheflowers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8L218","slug":"fruity-memory-challenge","title":"Fruity Memory Challenge","description":"Embark on a vibrant journey of memory mastery with \"Fruity Memory Challenge,\" a thrilling make-a-pair game that blends fruity fun with brain-teasing excitement. Immerse yourself in a world of luscious fruits, hidden images, and challenging puzzles that will test your memory skills and leave you craving for more.\n\nFruitful Pairing Adventure\nVisual Feast of Fruits\nProgressive Challenge Levels\nMultiplayer Fruity Showdown","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8L218/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruity-memory-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z57YZ","slug":"fruity-quiz-extravaganza","title":"Fruity Quiz Extravaganza","description":"Dive into the world of succulent flavors and tantalizing aromas with \"Fruity Quiz Extravaganza,\" the ultimate name-the-fruit game that promises a bountiful harvest of fun and knowledge. Test your fruit IQ, challenge your taste buds, and embark on a juicy journey through a fruity wonderland!\n\nFruit Identification Challenge:\nDelicious Visual Treats:\nEducational Fun for All Age\nChallenge Friends in Multiplayer Mode","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z57YZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruity-quiz-extravaganza/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I053I","slug":"wildlife-jigsaw-challenge","title":"Wildlife Jigsaw Challenge","description":"Dive into the enchanting world of nature with \"Wildlife Jigsaw Challenge,\" a captivating puzzle game that brings the beauty of the wild to your fingertips. Immerse yourself in stunning wildlife scenes, piece together intricate jigsaw puzzles, and embark on a relaxing yet challenging journey to uncover the wonders of the animal kingdom.\n\nBreathtaking Wildlife Scenes\nVaried Difficulty Levels\nEducational Insights\nTimeless Relaxation","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I053I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wildlife-jigsaw-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5IN5","slug":"difference-detective-find-them","title":"Difference Detective- Find them!","description":"Sharpen your observation skills and embark on an exciting visual journey with \"Difference Detective: Find them!\" This immersive find-the-differences game challenges players to spot subtle distinctions between seemingly identical images. Put on your detective hat and enjoy a thrilling, visually engaging experience like never before.\n\nVisual Puzzles Galore\nChallenging Levels\nImmersive Themes\nMultiplayer Showdowns","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5IN5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/difference-detective-find-them/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66TRS","slug":"asmr-stye-treatment","title":"ASMR Stye Treatment","description":"OMG! Our patient came with dirty pimply face and a stye problem. Help her to take care of the pimples, and prove your medical skills by performing this ASMR Stye Treatment game. After finishing the treatment, style our patient with the best outfit and make up from our collections to create the perfect look!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66TRS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asmr-stye-treatment/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57FF2","slug":"bff-math-class","title":"BFF Math Class","description":"It's time for BFF girl to go to Math Class! Can you help the girl get ready for the class? Prepare the bag and create the perfect look for her. There are lots of hairstyles, outfits, and accessories. The girl is gonna be cool at school, so pick up the most fashionable outfits for her. Train your fashion stylist skills! And also help her to finish all math excersice.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57FF2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-math-class/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"125A7","slug":"fashion-repair","title":"Fashion Repair","description":"Oh no, the girls stuff got broken and so dirty! Let's help them to fix their stuff! Remove the dirt on the phone, clean the bag, and sew rips in the cap. Paint with a new color and add some cute accessories. Decorate as nicely as possible and make their stuff look like new again. Don't replace it, repair it!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/125A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fashion-repair/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NMI4","slug":"plush-eggs-vending-machine","title":"Plush Eggs Vending Machine","description":"Do you like to collect surprise plush toys like Skibidi, Poppy, Pomni etc... etc...\nSo what waiting for? Try to open all chocolate eggs in this great surprise eggs games?\nIf you say \"yes\"... Welcome to the world of cute\nsurprise Plush Toys Lol!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NMI4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/plush-eggs-vending-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0VNNA","slug":"valentine-hidden-heart","title":"Valentine Hidden Heart","description":"Dive into a world of love and discovery with \"Valentine Hidden Heart\" - the ultimate romantic hidden object adventure! Unleash your inner cupid as you embark on a delightful quest to find the 10 hidden hearts in each of the 15 enchanting levels.","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0VNNA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/valentine-hidden-heart/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19R66","slug":"fruit-merge-reloaded","title":"Fruit Merge Reloaded","description":"Dive into the juicy and colorful world of Fruit Merge Reloaded, a captivating merging game that combines the addictive gameplay of 2048 with the sweetness of your favorite fruits! Your task is to merge identical fruits to create new and exotic varieties, aiming to reach the ultimate fruit fusion.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19R66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-merge-reloaded/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ODTAI","slug":"celebrity-social-media-adventure","title":"Celebrity Social Media Adventure","description":"Welcome to the Celebrity Social Media Adventure. Celebrity girls planned to try some adventure fashion over social media. Each one tries different fashions and posts them on social media and finds who trends the most. Sounds fun! right? Help the girls by browsing their wardrobes and picking the suitable costumes in each fashion. And then pick cute accessories and hairstyles. ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ODTAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/celebrity-social-media-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S8ISA","slug":"princess-cheongsam-shanghai-fashion","title":"Princess Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion","description":"In this new cute game Princess Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion, Princesses want to play and enjoy their time, making cute dress up styles. Being BFFs forever, they have tried all possible outfits. Curiosity helps them to think past the current century. As they grace through history, they decide to adopt Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion in Princess style. Anna and Elsa finally land upon interesting dress-up costumes in Qing-style tops, modern Qipao with high-slit cuts & mini dress. Help them choose the right color, dresses, and present them in majestic imperial fashion.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S8ISA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-cheongsam-shanghai-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N2C7O","slug":"princess-valentine-preparation","title":"Princess Valentine Preparation","description":"With valentine’s day around the corner, the Princess Valentine preparation has become exciting and thrilling. To celebrate Valentine’s day, the princess has decided to be in their best! Let’s check out their closet and look at our options. They have a few dresses in their colors of choice, both long and short, sometimes it’s more fun to mix it up a bit! You have the additional task of decorating their card and make them geared up for the royal date.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N2C7O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-valentine-preparation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FFNN4","slug":"bffs-pinafore-fashion","title":"BFFs Pinafore Fashion","description":"Welcome to the BFFs Pinafore Fashion. Bffs planned to try new fashion with their old collection in their wardrobe. Yes! its Pinafore. Help them to put together a cute pinafore dress by first choosing a shape for the dress. Then decide if the dress should be in a single color or in one of the pre-made prints. Then you have to choose if the fabric of the dress should have a texture and add-ons like a zipper or buttons. After you’ve designed the dress, it’s time to dress up and style the model! ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FFNN4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-pinafore-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OG4DO","slug":"cooking-world-reborn","title":"Cooking World Reborn","description":"The goal of the game is to go all the way from a small food truck to a large cafe in the center of the airport.\n\nWhat awaits you:\n\n- More than 50 large levels\n\n- Various improvements to kitchen equipment\n\n- Several game modes\n\nHow to play:\n\nYou need to prepare food for clients within a certain time frame. Get bonuses for speed and buy new, more advanced kitchen equipment.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OG4DO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cooking-world-reborn/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R57C3","slug":"boxbulletcraft","title":"BoxBulletCraft","description":"There are as many as five unique arenas available in this game, each of which is a unique battlefield full of dangers and opportunities. Choose your favorite arena and get ready for battle!\n\nHere you will find not only an exciting single player game, but also an exciting mode for two players on the same device! Fight with your friend back to back against monsters!\n\nThe game offers you as many as eight types of monsters that use unique attack strategies and have their own special characteristics. Challenge them and develop your own winning strategy!\n\nWeapons are the key to your victory! The game features as many as eight different types of weapons, each of which has its own power and special abilities. Experiment with weapons and find your perfect monster killing kit.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R57C3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boxbulletcraft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZIZ9S","slug":"express-delivery-puzzle","title":"Express Delivery Puzzle","description":"Express Delivery Puzzle est un jeu de type puzzle à glissière, dans lequel vous devez faire glisser les blocs de route pour relier le camion de livraison à toutes les maisons, chaque niveau n'ayant qu'une solution unique. Chaque niveau n'a qu'une seule solution. Profitez d'un total de 100 niveaux stimulants de complexité variable.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZIZ9S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/express-delivery-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T2OIO","slug":"grand-skibidi-town","title":"Grand Skibidi Town","description":"Grand Skibidi Town features gta style sandbox, drivable vehicles and big arsenal of weapons, your mission is to destroy given amount of skibidi toilets in order to successfully complete each level and unlock new weapons.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T2OIO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-skibidi-town/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FC8SF","slug":"find-the-difference-merry-christmas","title":"Find the Difference Merry Christmas","description":"Introducing the New Year game \"Find the Differences: Merry Christmas\"! The theme of this captivating quest is entirely dedicated to the Christmas holidays, aiming to provide you with unique experiences and festive vibes!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FC8SF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-difference-merry-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"72E29","slug":"rebel-wings","title":"Rebel Wings","description":"$25","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/72E29/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rebel-wings/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"72177","slug":"babyscape","title":"BabyScape","description":"Play as a baby on the hunt for candy. Dont expect it to be a walk in the park. Defeat monsters and overcome challenges to reach the fridge!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/72177/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/babyscape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0M310","slug":"miner-merge","title":"Miner Merge","description":"This is a merge game in which you have to merge little miner minions to pgrade them the rocks upgrade to you click he fast forward button repeatedly to speed up things.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0M310/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miner-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5SN6P","slug":"minesweeper-classic","title":"Minesweeper Classic","description":"Minesweeper Classical is a classic puzzle game. When you find the location of all the bombs, you will pass the level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5SN6P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minesweeper-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UR7TX","slug":"bike-stunt-bmx-simulator","title":"Bike Stunt BMX Simulator","description":"Ride your BMX on big ramps and get crazy air, or get technical with street skating. Do huge flips and stunts, or chain together awesome combos with manuals, grinds and wallrides.\n\nThe choice is yours with 9 different skate parks made with inspiration from all around the world. You can even create your very own skate parks to ride!\n\nBoth your rider and your BMX bike are fully customizable, with tons of options to make yours absolutely unique! ","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UR7TX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bike-stunt-bmx-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OO455","slug":"concrete-boots","title":"Concrete Boots","description":"Concrete Boots is a mafia simulation game that gives you the possibility to build your criminal empire and take over the city. Hire men, extort businessowners, setup rackets, deal drugs, manage your finances, evade taxes, explore the city, steal cars, gain respect.. or wage war. ","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OO455/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/concrete-boots/embed?sid=1","plays":39812,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YE16E","slug":"s-n-gamer-physics-engine","title":"S N GAMER physics engine","description":"This is a simple physics engine that you can create cool stuff in it.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YE16E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/s-n-gamer-physics-engine/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1451L","slug":"pool-hustlers","title":"Pool Hustlers","description":"Step into the vibrant world of '80s retro-style billiards with a twist. In this single player game, players race against the clock to sink as many balls as possible, adding a thrilling precision challenge to the classic pool experience. The atmosphere is thick with 80s nostalgia, echoing the billiard halls where colorful characters made their fortunes on skillful bets and trick shots.\n\nClick and drag to set the pool cue's angle and power. Release to hit the white cue ball. You can also apply spinning effects to the ball.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1451L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pool-hustlers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83E59","slug":"squid-game-mission-revenge","title":"Squid Game Mission Revenge","description":"C'est l'heure de la vengeance, une mission presque impossible, mais cela va sûrement vous amuser !! Jouez à ce nouveau jeu appelé Squid Squad Mission Revenge, un nouveau jeu dans lequel vous vous vengerez des ennemis cagoulés sans cœur et montrerez à quel point vous êtes doué pour viser et tirer. L'un des survivants de ces jeux de calamars revient pour se venger de ces jeux fous et décide d'éliminer tous les hommes cagoulés et les patrons qui continuent encore à organiser ces jeux fous. Votre mission est de contrôler le petit héros afin qu'il puisse éliminer tous les ennemis dans chacun des niveaux !! Alors aidez le petit personnage en pointant et en tirant. Prenez soin de vos munitions. Vous avez une limite à chaque niveau. Essayez de ne pas gaspiller vos balles. Dépassez chaque niveau, améliorez votre score et vous pourrez obtenir de nouvelles armes qui","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83E59/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-game-mission-revenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NOIIH","slug":"rainbow-monster-impostor-catcher","title":"Rainbow Monster Impostor Catcher","description":"Ne cherchez pas plus loin que Rainbow Monster Impostor Catcher ! Dans ce jeu passionnant, vous prendrez le contrôle de Rainbow Blue alors que vous vous lancerez dans une mission visant à capturer les personnages espiègles de Among Us avant la fin du temps imparti. Avec son gameplay captivant et ses défis addictifs, Rainbow Monster Impostor Catcher garantit des heures de plaisir et de divertissement. Que vous soyez fan de jeux de stratégie, d'aventures pleines d'action ou de quêtes de résolution d'énigmes, ce jeu a tout pour plaire.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NOIIH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-monster-impostor-catcher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KC60S","slug":"zombies-cookies-apocalypse","title":"Zombies Cookies Apocalypse","description":"Zombies Cookies Apocalypse est un jeu occasionnel qui relève du genre action. Le jeu se déroule dans un monde post-apocalyptique où l'invasion des zombies a tout détruit.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KC60S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombies-cookies-apocalypse/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TI66","slug":"skibidi-elastic-head","title":"Skibidi Elastic Head","description":"Dans le jeu de puzzle divertissant Skibidi Elastic Head, votre objectif est d'aider les toilettes Skibidi à échapper au caméraman et à terminer chaque niveau. Jouez le rôle d'un courageux skibidi toilette et voyez si vous pouvez échapper à l'équipe de tournage. Assurez-vous de terminer chaque niveau avant que l'alarme ne se déclenche ; si vous le faites, vous gagnerez beaucoup d'argent, mais si vous faites une pause trop longue, vous serez attrapé et tué.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TI66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-elastic-head/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TELAI","slug":"adventure-capitalist-hole","title":"Adventure Capitalist Hole","description":"Le jeu en ligne passionnant Adventure Capitalist Hole a pris d'assaut la communauté des joueurs. Ce jeu récréatif plonge les joueurs dans une quête périlleuse pour amasser richesses et capitaux.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TELAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventure-capitalist-hole/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FIRL2","slug":"roblox-flip","title":"Roblox Flip","description":"Il est temps de perdre le contrôle du corps de Roblox comme une poupée de ragdoll et de vous retourner dans votre lit ! Dans Roblox Flip. Vous devriez vous préparer à sauter et à voler à travers tous les obstacles de votre maison jusqu'à une chambre. Attention et ne touchez pas le sol ! Collectez de l'argent et des diamants pour débloquer de nouveaux personnages et terminer tous les niveaux.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FIRL2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roblox-flip/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M57EM","slug":"murder-mafia","title":"Murder Mafia","description":"Kill the real Don, disguise as him, and don't get caught! Be careful of the betrayers, catch and throw them into jail. Use the hints to survive and collect pictures in the album.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M57EM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/murder-mafia/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"38YTN","slug":"infinite-bird","title":"Infinite Bird","description":"This a recreation of the game doodle jump in which you have to make the bird jump on logs with your finger or mouse by moving it left or right it jumps automatically.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/38YTN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinity-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"93O33","slug":"color","title":"Color","description":"Color is a game in which you have to lead the ball by tapping to the wall with the same color as the ball.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/93O33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AMR08","slug":"quiz-trivia-guess-the-animal-music-flags","title":"Quiz Trivia Guess The Animal Music Flags","description":"$26","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AMR08/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quiz-trivia-gues-the-animal-music-flags/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"50935","slug":"tall-fat-man-run","title":"Tall Fat Man Run","description":" Tall Fat Man Run is a fun and addictive hyper casual game where you control a tall and fat man who loves to run. Your goal is to avoid the obstacles that can make you lose your height and weight, such as spikes, saws, and lasers. You also want to enter the gates that can make you gain more height and weight.\nHow tall and fat can you get? Try it now and find out!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50935/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tall-fat-man-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R4B24","slug":"colorful-art-coloring-book","title":"Colorful Art - Coloring Book","description":"Colorful Art - Coloring Book is a vibrant coloring game that will captivate you with its interactive coloring pages and rich palette. Explore different themes and styles as you paint your way through each challenge. With Colorful Art - Coloring Book, you have the power to turn blank pages into colorful masterpieces. Pick up your virtual brush and let the colors flow!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R4B24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colorful-art-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19III","slug":"christmas-ai-art-draw-paint","title":"Christmas AI Art Draw Paint","description":"Experience the tranquil pleasure of coloring with Christmas AI Art Draw Paint, a game that combines the simplicity of painting with the sophistication of a coloring book. Each page presents a new challenge and an opportunity to showcase your coloring finesse. Whether you're a novice painter or a seasoned artist, Christmas AI Art Draw Paint welcomes you to a coloring haven.\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19III/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-ai-art-draw-paint/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5YR0","slug":"happy-new-year-2024-coloring-game","title":"Happy New Year 2024 Coloring Game","description":"Experience the tranquil pleasure of coloring with Happy New Year 2024 Coloring Game, a game that combines the simplicity of painting with the sophistication of a coloring book. Each page presents a new challenge and an opportunity to showcase your coloring finesse. Whether you're a novice painter or a seasoned artist, Happy New Year 2024 Coloring Game welcomes you to a coloring haven.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5YR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-new-year-2024-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NED7N","slug":"steampunk-coloring-adventure","title":"Steampunk Coloring Adventure","description":"Unleash your creativity and immerse yourself in a world of vivid colors with Steampunk Coloring Adventure! This interactive coloring book brings a delightful experience for artists of all ages. Dive into an expansive collection of designs ranging from serene landscapes to intricate patterns. Steampunk Coloring Adventure offers an escape to a digital canvas where imagination is your only limit. Choose your palette, fill in the hues, and watch each page come to life with every touch. Whether you're looking to relax, improve your coloring skills, or simply have some fun, Steampunk Coloring Adventure is the perfect blend of entertainment and relaxation. Ready your colors and bring joy to your day with Steampunk Coloring Adventure - where every stroke adds brightness to your world!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NED7N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steampunk-coloring-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1JPM9","slug":"jojo-jump","title":"Jojo Jump","description":"JOJO JUMP - HTML5 Game , Construct 3 & Construct 2 template (c3p) and (capx)\n\njojo jump  is an Endless Jumping Game .\n\npress right arrow to move right, press left arrow to move left,try not to fall and try not collision with the enemy","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1JPM9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jojo-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GA4N4","slug":"autumn-coloring-game","title":"Autumn Coloring Game","description":"Ready for a coloring quest? Autumn Coloring delivers an array of beautiful, detailed coloring pages designed to spark your imagination. This game isn't just about coloring; it's about creating art. Fill each page with colors, patterns, and life. Whether it's with a simple crayon stroke or a complex paint blend, Autumn Coloring turns your device into an artist's studio.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GA4N4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/autumn-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UGS04","slug":"banban-jigsaw-puzzle","title":"Banban Jigsaw Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Garte Banban! Our Garte Banban Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Garte Banban picture. With a wide variety of Garte Banban images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Garte Banban Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UGS04/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banban-jigsaw-garte-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AIPD8","slug":"anime-kawaii-dress-up-dresses","title":"Anime Kawaii Dress Up - Dresses","description":"\"Anime Kawaii Dress Up - Dresses\" offers a playful platform for dressing up characters in adorable, Kawaii-inspired outfits, featuring a wide array of cute dresses.\n\n  \n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AIPD8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-kawaii-dress-up-dresses/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MM0U2","slug":"arab-girls-dress-up-salon-makeup","title":"Arab Girls Dress-Up - Salon Makeup","description":"\"Arab Girls Dress Up Saloon Makeup” is an engaging game inviting players to explore traditional and modern Arab fashion, accessorizing and styling characters in diverse, elegant outfits.","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MM0U2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arab-girls-dress-up-salon-makeup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7MNG","slug":"anime-girls-fashion-makeup","title":"Anime Girls Fashion Makeup","description":"\"Anime Girls Fashion Makeup\" is a dynamic game where players design stylish looks, apply dazzling makeup, and create hairstyles for anime characters.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7MNG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-girls-fashion-makeup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KU9DR","slug":"charming-dress-up-and-makeup","title":"Charming Dress-up and Makeup","description":"$27","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KU9DR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/charming-dress-up-and-makeup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MAE1A","slug":"wednesday-dress-up-adames","title":"Wednesday Dress Up Adames","description":"$28","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MAE1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wednesday-dress-up-adames/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E57BA","slug":"balls-bricks-breaker","title":"Balls Bricks Breaker","description":"You will get:  \nAdvance levels - As you progress through the game, the patterns of the bricks will become more challenging, but with each level you complete, your score will increase.  \nPower-ups - Some of the bricks contain power-ups, such as extra balls, rocket balls. Break these bricks to activate the power-ups and enhance your gameplay.  \nEndless fun - With each level, the pattern of the bricks will change, making the game an endless source of fun and excitement. So get ready to test your reflexes and strategic skills with this classic arcade-style game! \nEasy to play - With its simple controls and intuitive gameplay, this game is easy to pick up and play for players of all ages and skill levels.  \nChallenging levels - The game features an increasing difficulty level, with the patterns of the bricks becoming more complex as you progress through the levels.  \nFun sound effects - The game's sound effects add to its overall fun and excitement, enhancing the brick-smashing experience.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E57BA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-bricks-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NC5SS","slug":"screw-puzzle-nuts-and-bolts","title":"Screw Puzzle - Nuts and Bolts","description":"$29","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NC5SS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/screw-puzzle-nuts-and-bolts/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RI6EU","slug":"muscle-clicker-2","title":"Muscle Clicker 2","description":"$2a","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RI6EU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/muscle-clicker-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O0S0S","slug":"skibidi-toilet-madness-clicker","title":"Skibidi Toilet Madness Clicker","description":"This is madness carzy and funny clicker game about skibidi toilets!!\n\nGreat skibidi toilet adventure","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O0S0S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-madness/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78HRS","slug":"astro-shooter","title":"Astro Shooter","description":"Astro Shooter offers a straightforward and immersive space-shooting experience with a focus on intense gameplay. Players can seamlessly control their sleek spaceship using either touch or keyboard inputs, navigating through space to destroy diverse asteroids. The game is providing a pure and engaging challenge for players who seek a no-frills, action-packed gaming session","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78HRS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/astro-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1AF24","slug":"2048-fnaf","title":"2048 - FNAF","description":"2048 is a classic puzzle game, but in this game instead of numbers there will be FNAF(fife find it freddy) characters.\nFind all 14 characters.\n\n- Classic 2048, but in the FNAF setting.\n- Suitable for all ages. Will appeal to both boys and girls\n- 14 characters available\n- Endless game\n\nCombine tiles with the same value to get points.\nWhen two tiles with the same number are combined, they merge into one.\nTo move tiles on mobile devices use Swipe Up, Swipe Down, Swipe Right and Swipe Left.\nOn computer use W,A,S,D or arrow keys on your keyboard.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1AF24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-fnaf/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H310H","slug":"richman","title":"Richman","description":"In Richman, players buy, trade, and develop properties to accumulate wealth, aiming to bankrupt opponents through strategic real estate management and financial transactions.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H310H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/richman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"50555","slug":"save-the-boy","title":"Save The Boy!","description":"Unique Rescue Puzzle\n The most fun and easiest puzzle game in the world!\n Help the guy.\n He is tied up and locked in a room.\n Run your finger along the rope and cut it.\n Will he be able to cling to a chance of escape?\n It all depends on you!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50555/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71E4C","slug":"crowcity-battleground","title":"CrowCity Battleground","description":"$2b","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71E4C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battle-crow-city/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40IIU","slug":"bouncing-chick","title":"Bouncing Chick","description":"In Bouncing Chick you have to reach your nest as fast as you can, avoiding obstacles and hazards. Go to the top of the level and try to beat your record! There are 24 levels to beat, so what are you waiting for? Start your climbing to the top!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40IIU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncing-chick/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O275R","slug":"color-sort-mania","title":"Color Sort Mania","description":"Oubliez la vie quotidienne et plongez dans un monde simple où le tri est un art. Placez les bulles dans le flacon le plus stratégique et appréciez que tout se mette en place.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O275R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-sort-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"94C90","slug":"jetpack-boy","title":"Jetpack Boy","description":"jetpackboy is an html5 arcade game, fly and avoid the obstacle that come and get coins to earn score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/94C90/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jetpack-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NRA4E","slug":"sugarland-adventure","title":"Sugarland Adventure","description":"sugarland adventure is an html5 platformer game, help the little girl find a house and get scores by eating cakes and candy in the stages, defeat enemies by jumping and overlapping","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NRA4E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sugarland-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11477","slug":"sky-fighter-alien-invader","title":"Sky Fighter Alien Invader","description":"sky fighter alien invader is an html5 shooting arcade game, aliens attack the earth and cause riots, save the citizens, get items for scores and shoot as many aliens as possible","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11477/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-fighter-alien-invader/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VRV70","slug":"ninja-boy-adventure","title":"Ninja Boy Adventure","description":"Ninja Boy Adventure is an HTML5 action platformer game, monsters attack the city, it's time for action, defeat enemies with slashes or throwing kunai, get coins on all stages, get gems, everything must be complete to go to the next level\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VRV70/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-boy-adventure-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7DVDD","slug":"kido-adventure","title":"Kido Adventure","description":"Kido Adventure is an HTML5 platformer adventure game, explore each stage and defeat the enemy, get 5 or more keys to proceed to the next stage\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7DVDD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kido-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A75A6","slug":"super-santa-run-jump","title":"Super Santa Run & Jump","description":"Super Santa Run and Jump is an HTML5 endless run game, run and get coins avoiding all the obstacles and enemies that come your way","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A75A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-santa-run-and-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"