Galaxy Fighter is an HTML5 space shooter game, fight enemies with laser shots, get all the items that appear and get the highest score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1HH3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-fighter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H4LIL","slug":"flying-change","title":"Flying Change","description":"flying change is an html5 arcade game, touch and hold to fly and get as many coins as possible, if the score is sufficient the player will change to another character","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H4LIL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-change/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UETRR","slug":"forrest-treasure-adventure","title":"Forrest Treasure Adventure","description":"forrest treasure adventure is an html5 platformer game, explore the stages and defeat the enemy by shooting, get treasure in each stage to go to the next level","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UETRR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/forrest-treasure-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TRRL","slug":"colour-jelly-touch","title":"Colour Jelly Touch","description":"Color Jelly Touch is an HTML5 up-down touch game, touch colorful jelly and get a score","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TRRL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colour-jelly-touch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"943JJ","slug":"bunny-fall-jump","title":"Bunny Fall Jump","description":"bunny fall jump is a top down html5 game, touch the screen to play up and down the player controls get the items that appear and avoid enemies","ca