escription":"Ninja Girl Escape is an HTML5 endless run game, run to avoid obstacles, get items and coins for the best score\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2IEC0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-girl-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NSU26","slug":"super-jetpackman","title":"Super Jetpackman","description":"super jetpackman is an endless flying html5 game, fly upwards and avoid various falling objects, be careful if you hit you will die, get as many gold coins as possible","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NSU26/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-jetpackman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HV841","slug":"white-knight-adventure","title":"White Knight Adventure","description":"white knight adventure is an html5 platformer game, explore each level and get items for scores, defeat enemies with shots and slashes\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HV841/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/white-knight-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3ZG88","slug":"doggy-vs-zombie","title":"Doggy vs Zombie","description":"doggy vs zombies is an endless run html5 game, run from chasing zombies and jump to avoid the zombies that come, get a score by taking as many items as possible\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3ZG88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doggy-vs-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E00E7","slug":"dead-stones","title":"Dead Stones","description":"dead stone is an html5 arcade game, jump and avoid falling objects and get a score, watch out for your head getting hit","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E00E7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dead-stone/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10IK4","slug":"chopter-kid","title":"Chopter Kid","description":"chopter kid is an html5 arcade game, fly up and avoid obstacles to get score\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10IK4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chopter-kid/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5P6EZ","slug":"crazy-super-car","title":"Crazy Super Car","description":"crazy super car is a top down html5 car game, drive your car and avoid hitting other cars get items for score","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5P6EZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-super-car/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H0CH0","slug":"chicken-shooter","title":"Chicken Shooter","description":"Chicken shooter is an HTML5 shooting game, shoot as many chickens as possible to get a score, be careful not to shoot the birds or the score will be lost again","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H0CH0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chicken-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7IL16","slug":"escape-the-killer","title":"Escape The Killer","description":"escape the killer is an html5 endless run game, run to avoid obstacles and save yourself from the threat bandit who will kill you at any time","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7IL16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-the-killer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YE3JE","slug":"bunny-jumping-jet","title":"Bunny Jumping Jet","description":"bunny jumping jet is an html5 endless jump game, jump and avoid teh enemy, get carrot for score and get rocket for super dash","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YE3JE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-jumping-jet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00629","slug":"blastman","title":"Blastman","description":"blastman is an html5 platformer game, enemy robots have taken over your area, destroy them before they become powerful, explore all stages, kill enemies with shots, and get items for the score","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00629/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blastman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BBB01","slug":"bubble-touch","title":"Bubble Touch","description":"Bubble Touch is an HTML5 bubble breaking game, burst as many bubbles as possible so you don't get through or you lose your score","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BBB01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-touch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SN68C","slug":"alien-escape-run","title":"Alien Escape Run","description":"alien escape run, is an html5 endless run game, run and avoid or kill the enemy by jump, get gold for earn score and lets be best player","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SN68C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-escape-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77307","slug":"alien-space-war","title":"Alien Space War","description":"Alien Space War is an HTML5 arcade shooting game, shoot all the aliens who come down and will move to the next stage and get lots of scores","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77307/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-space-war/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3E0O1","slug":"escape-boy","title":"Escape Boy","description":"escape boy is a topdown arcade html5 game, run and save your friends from monsters, get the items that appear for score and be the best player","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3E0O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"70917","slug":"cyberbots","title":"Cyberbots","description":"cyberbots is a scifi platformer html5 game, explore all levels, defeat enemies by shooting destroy obstacles, get items for score and be the winner\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/70917/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cyberbots/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06731","slug":"super-robo-max","title":"Super Robo Max","description":"super robo max is an HTML5 shooting arcade game, run and jump shoot the enemies that come, get items for the score, watch out for the enemies coming from above destroy them as much as possible","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06731/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-robo-max/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22277","slug":"flip-bot","title":"Flip Bot","description":"flip bot is an html5 arcade game, touch the screen and flip the robot to avoid enemies get batteries for your energy\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22277/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flip-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RSBPH","slug":"space-battleship-orion","title":"Space Battleship Orion","description":"space battleship orion is an html5 arcade shooting game, shoot as many enemy spaceships as possible to get items for the highest score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RSBPH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-battleship-orion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1MK24","slug":"blockmatch","title":"BlockMatch","description":"$2c","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1MK24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blockmatch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31NI0","slug":"epic-ninja-dash","title":"Epic Ninja Dash","description":"$2d","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31NI0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/epic-ninja-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"519N3","slug":"super-soccer-noggins","title":"Super Soccer Noggins","description":"Choose your favourite country and lead them to victory in the craziest soccer tournaments. 10 powerups and dozens of different fields will give every match its unique quirky style. Will you be able to claim the 6 trophies in this game?","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/519N3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-soccer-noggins/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T0CMI","slug":"memory-match-magic","title":"Memory Match Magic","description":"Plongez dans le monde enchanteur de « Memory Match Magic », un délicieux jeu occasionnel qui met votre mémoire au défi et vous emmène dans un voyage magique de paires ! Plongez-vous dans un royaume fantaisiste rempli de cartes colorées et d'animations charmantes.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T0CMI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memory-match-magic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5E45","slug":"gladiators-merge-and-fight","title":"Gladiators Merge and Fight","description":"Gladiators: Merge and Fight is an engaging arcade game that combines character attribute creation and enhancement with combat. In this game, you start with basic materials and improve your gladiator's attributes by upgrading weapon, shield, armor, and helmet materials. Every decision affects your hero's stats. After preparing your gladiator, press the \"Start\" button to begin the second part of the game: arena battles. Fight against other gladiators, utilize your skills and tactics to claim victory, and become an arena legend.\n\nGladiators: Merge and Fight offers a unique blend of two captivating gameplay mechanics, where your ability to enhance your gladiator is crucial in the pursuit of victory and glory in the arena.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5E45/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gladiators-merge-and-fight/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JTII7","slug":"ninja-stealth","title":"Ninja Stealth","description":"\nWelcome to the thrilling world of \"Shadow Sprint: Ninja Express\"! Embark on an incredible journey as a skilled ninja, where your reflexes and abilities are the key to success. Dodge shurikens flying your way, collect sparkling crystals, and strive to accumulate as many points as possible.\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JTII7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-stealth/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23072","slug":"money-merge","title":"Money Merge","description":"Money Merge is a delightful and interactive tap-and-match extravaganza! Your mission? Unite a gleeful parade of coins, regal crowns, alluring money bags, and enchanting treasure chests while leveling up with mind-blowing explosions that determine their worth.\nMagically merge three or more coins of the same color to conjure up magnificent sparkling ruby gems that hold even greater value. Fuse your moolah masterfully until you've created a blindingly dazzling collection, and bask in the glory of bonus points for reaching spectacular scores!\nPrepare for a merry monetary adventure in Money Merge: where merging coins is both exhilarating and lucrative!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23072/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/money-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19109","slug":"15-puzzle-classic","title":"15 Puzzle Classic","description":"15 Puzzle Classic Game, the classic puzzle brain games. Tap and move the wood number blocks, enjoy the magic of logic puzzles, and coordinate your eyes, hands, and brain. Challenge your logic and brainpower, have fun, and enjoy number games!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19109/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/15-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RI585","slug":"eliza-winter-coronation","title":"Eliza Winter Coronation","description":"$2e","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RI585/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eliza-winter-coronation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G2W9I","slug":"new-year-s-kigurumi","title":"New Year's Kigurumi","description":"Que faut-il pour faire de cette Nouvelle année la fête la plus confortable? C'est très simple: au lieu de choisir une tenue fastidieuse, vous pouvez vous habiller dans un pyjama maison amusant - Kigurumi! Ce sera une vraie fête de pyjama du nouvel an! Rejoignez les princesses Elise et Jacqueline, faites une cure de jouvence amusante pour le nouvel an et choisissez votre pyjama préféré. Cela peut être un tigre Kigurumi, un arbre de Noël ou le Père Noël, ou peut-être que vous voulez être une licorne joyeuse ou un dragon? Habillez plutôt un pyjama, de jolies pantoufles et versez du chocolat chaud! Rencontrez le nouvel An confortablement en jouant le jeu Kigurumi Nouvel an!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G2W9I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/new-year-s-kigurumi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SNE6Y","slug":"incredible-princess-eye-art-2","title":"Incredible Princess Eye Art 2","description":"Welcome to an incredible tutorial from a fabulous makeup artist. Try your hand at makeup on the beautiful eyes of cute princesses. Use extraordinary artistic solutions to create a striking and non-standard look. Use new trends: angel makeup, rhinestones, animal prints, neon effects. Grab your makeup brush and get started! Try out new art options for the eyes.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SNE6Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/incredible-princess-eye-art-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5G7KG","slug":"zentangle-coloring-book","title":"Zentangle Coloring Book","description":"All children love to draw and color. It develops the brain and calms the nerves. Meet the original coloring in the Zentagle technique! This style was invented in 2006. Drawings in this style usually consist of some kind of repeating patterns. Many patterns can be combined in one drawing, and the technique itself is quite free and intuitive. Anyone can master it. Features of the Zentagle technique: meditativeness and composition of a whole from repeating patterns. In this coloring, the figures of owls are used as the basis. It is perfect for both children and adults. Take a screenshot and share the result with your friends!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5G7KG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zentangle-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7CEN","slug":"cute-witch-princess","title":"Cute Witch Princess","description":"The princesses decided to change their usual outfits, turning them into a witch dress! Do you want to know what your favorite princess will look like in the image of a witch? Then rather play this wonderful game called «Cute Witch Princess». Make up a festive make-up, a traditional hairstyle and try on a witch's robe and a pointed hat. Don't forget about shoes or boots, as well as accessories that will make your look unforgettable.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7CEN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-witch-princess/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7A1A","slug":"matryoshka-maker","title":"Matryoshka Maker","description":"Matriochka est une petite poupée en bois peinte avec plusieurs copies plus petites à l'intérieur. Créons notre propre poupée gigogne unique! Choisissez des couleurs et des motifs pour différentes parties de la matriochka-corps, tablier, support, chemise et écharpe. N'oubliez pas de mettre un souvenir amusant entre vos mains.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7A1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/matryoshka-maker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4R0HA","slug":"onesearch","title":"OneSearch","description":"Welcome to game one serch, search the balls where the corresponding number is hidden, dragging it into the large ball","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4R0HA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/onesearch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NO979","slug":"nooblox-vs-garten-2-player","title":"NoobLox vs Garten 2 Player","description":"You must help Noob and Bacon in their adventure. Garden monsters are everywhere, and you must eliminate all the monsters. Get rid of the monsters and collect all the coins. You must do your best to win. Together with your friend, overcome all obstacles. Work together with your friend to eliminate all the monsters. Be careful, there is poisonous water that can kill you.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  \n*double jump available  \n*jump on it to kill!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NO979/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nooblox-vs-garten-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6T144","slug":"therobot","title":"TheRobot","description":"Welcome to the robot game that has to overcome levels to win","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6T144/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/therobot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NOS7","slug":"prison-business","title":"Prison Business","description":"Noob went to jail, and this time it's serious! It is almost impossible to escape, but if you try hard and organize a business, the way will be open!\n\nRenovate the prison!\n- Organize a business producing batons, burgers and milk!\n- Open a modern high-tech laundry, soda production and much more in the exciting game \"Prison Business\"!\n- Hire workers, make them work and earn tons of money!\n- Build a store and start selling goods to visitors!\n\nHow to play:\nYour task is to repair the prison and build various production facilities. Hire workers and earn money!\n\nControl:\nMove: W, A, S, D or keyboard arrows.\nMobile devices: Touch the screen and a virtual joystick will appear.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NOS7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/prison-business/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7TII1","slug":"gemfit-frenzy","title":"GemFit Frenzy","description":"In GemFit Frenzy dive into a jewel-fitting challenge on a 7x7 grid. Test your agility and strategy as you race against time to form complete rows and columns.\n\nConfront the Gem Frenzy and achieve incredible scores!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7TII1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gemfit-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87C0S","slug":"witch-s-hats","title":"Witch's Hats","description":"Don’t be manipulated by the witch, she will do anything to keep your book inaccessible, hiding it between her hats. You must be smart and agile enough not to lose sight of it. Can you really beat the witch?!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87C0S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/witch-s-hats/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7452U","slug":"classic-master-sudoku","title":"Classic Master Sudoku","description":"Classic Master Sudoku is a type of game or number puzzle that is quite popular. Many people, both young and old, play this game just to fill their free time or with the aim of sharpening their brain a little. Even though it is classified as an old school game, in fact up to now sudoku enthusiasts are still emerging and increasing.\n\nSudoku, originally called Number Place, is a logic-based combinatorial number placement puzzle. In classic sudoku, the goal is to fill a 9×9 grid with numbers so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 3×3 subgrids that make up the grid (also called squares, blocks, or regions) contains all the numbers from 1 to 9.\n\nIn sudoku there are usually several grids that are already partially filled, which can then be used as a guide to complete the filling. French newspapers featured variations of the Sudoku puzzle in the 19th century, and the puzzle has appeared ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7452U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-master-sudoku/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1HG70","slug":"golf-hill","title":"Golf Hill","description":"Golf Hill is a golf sports simulation game, a very popular game for honing patience and accuracy. The game's simple and intuitive controls make it easy for kids to play, while the challenging obstacles and endless levels make it engaging for both kids and adults. A free sports game that offers addictive gameplay and hours of fun for players of all ages.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1HG70/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/golf-hill/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"30E4L","slug":"elemental-rescue-adventure","title":"Elemental Rescue Adventure","description":"Elemental Rescue Adventure est un jeu de plateforme en ligne captivant qui vous emmènera dans une aventure passionnante dans le monde numérique et vous offrira des heures de plaisir et d'amusement. Ce jeu s'inspire du film populaire Elemental et met les joueurs dans le rôle du protagoniste héroïque, Wade, alors qu'il tente de libérer la belle Ember de ses ravisseurs en complétant une série d'étapes de plus en plus difficiles. Elemental Rescue Adventure, un jeu gratuit, combine","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/30E4L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/elemental-rescue-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE01G","slug":"jingle-juggle-merge","title":"Jingle Juggle Merge","description":"Plongez dans le monde festif de « Jingle Juggle Merge », où la magie des fêtes rencontre la stratégie sphérique ! Plongez dans le défi de fusionner des orbes de Noël, créant des motifs harmonieux qui dansent au rythme des airs des fêtes. Naviguez à travers un paysage enneigé en maîtrisant l’art d’associer des ornements.\n\nPouvez-vous jongler avec les décorations et créer le spectacle de Noël ultime ? Embrassez l'esprit des fêtes et découvrez la fusion enchanteresse de plaisir et de festivités dans « Jingle Juggle Merge » !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE01G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jingle-juggle-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01ERW","slug":"watermelon-merge","title":"Watermelon Merge","description":"What is Watermelon Merge?\nCombine two small fruits to make a new large fruit. Merge fruits is a game that is currently popular, because apart from being able to fill your time when you are relaxed or bored, it can also sharpen your brain with watermelon game.\n\nWatermelon merge cute: with various kinds of fruit such as cherry, strawberry, grapes, pineapple, apple, orange, melon and watermelon, it makes it like a fresh fruit salad. Apart from being very fun, Merge Fruit will certainly train your brain and train your competitive spirit to compete to get the highest score.\n\nHow to play this watermelon game puzzle?\nYou only need to direct the fruit to drop to the position you want, of course make sure the fruit will hit the same type of fruit so that it becomes a big fruit. In this fruit game, make sure not to stack them too high, because if they exceed the maximum limit on the glass tube then the game will end","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01ERW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/watermelon-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DR97E","slug":"catnrobot-idle-td-battle-cat","title":"CatnRobot Idle TD Battle Cat","description":"Amusez-vous avec ce jeu divertissant CatRobot Idle TD Battle Cat est un jeu de tower defense dans un monde magique qui appelle à défendre votre tour contre les vagues d'ennemis magiques qui viendront avec l'intention de vous détruire !!! Apprécier","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DR97E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catrobot-idle-td-battle-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FTK0E","slug":"bricks-breakers-infinity","title":"Bricks Breakers Infinity","description":"Destroy all the rocks with the ball, and don't let the ball fall down, survive like that to get the highest score","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FTK0E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bricks-breakers-infinit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R8BER","slug":"super-kart-turbo-racers","title":"Super Kart Turbo Racers","description":"Get ready for a mind-bending racing experience in \" Super Kart Turbo Racers,\" where the track is not the only thing testing your skills! Navigate through a visually mesmerizing world filled with color-based challenges, thrilling races, and strategic decision-making. Will you conquer the track, or will the Stroop Effect leave you in a kaleidoscopic whirlwind?\n\nColorful Cognitive Racing\nStrategic Power-Ups\nOptions of Gate Entry","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R8BER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-kart-turbo-racers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9D292","slug":"zombie-derby","title":"Zombie Derby","description":"Zombie Derby is a small 3D racing action in the world of zombie apocalypse. Drive to survive! How far can you get \nbefore they get you?\n\nKey features\n 5 killer cars to drive\n 5 levels to explore\n 3 extreme levels  Massively customisa","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9D292/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-derby/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01TE7","slug":"tebo","title":"Tebo","description":"Tebo is a physics-based platform game with 50 challenging and brain-boosting levels. You have to help Tebo (little alien) reach the portal to complete the level","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01TE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tebo/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2ENR9","slug":"pac-ring-adventure","title":"Pac Ring Adventure","description":"Embark on a thrilling journey with \"Pac Ring Adventure,\" a captivating arcade-style game that brings a fresh twist to the classic Pac-Man experience. Maneuver through challenging mazes, collect power-ups, and face formidable foes as you strive to conquer the ever-expanding ring of excitement!\n\nInnovative Ring Gameplay\nPower-Up Extravaganza\nMulti-enemy Mayhem","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2ENR9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pac-ring-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S51DD","slug":"sudoku-guru-classic-sudoku","title":"Sudoku Guru - classic sudoku","description":"Develop your logic and train your brain in \"Sudoku Guru - Classic Sudoku\"!\nEnjoy Sudoku, solve daily challenges and get trophies for completing tasks.\n\nThere are 5 different difficulty levels available to you: easy, medium, difficult, expert and guru. Each level is a unique puzzle.\nTrack your progress and challenge yourself with the statistics report. This feature adds a competitive element to the game, motivating you to become a real guru.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S51DD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sudoku-guru-classic-sudoku/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H0771","slug":"salads-by-chef","title":"Salads by Chef","description":"Find out the story of the chef who creates the most delicious salads on the planet!!!\n\nPrepare popular Russian salads - Olivier, Herring under a fur coat, Vinaigrette, Mimosa, Greek, Caesar, Crab, etc.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H0771/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/salads-by-chef/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B777L","slug":"diablo-ball","title":"Diablo Ball","description":"Adventure of Diablo Ball is waiting for you! Travel through the colorful world where you will find many amazing rewards. You will be hindered by square enemies who patrol this amazing world, deal with them, if you do everything right - they will not be able to catch you, because you can jump far and roll quickly on the ground!\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B777L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/diablo-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SSK7K","slug":"traditional-klondike-spider-solitaire","title":"Traditional Klondike Spider Solitaire","description":"$2f","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SSK7K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/klondike-spider-solitaire-free-android-card-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L55O1","slug":"rolly-ball","title":"Rolly Ball","description":"$30","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L55O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rolly-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MRM8D","slug":"malware-madness","title":"Malware Madness","description":"An evil virus has taken over every robot on the continent, and you're the only one not forced to do its bidding. Destroy the virus's transmitters and put the virus out of commission!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MRM8D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/malware-madness/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ATEI6","slug":"crime-theft-gangster-paradise","title":"Crime Theft Gangster Paradise","description":"Crime Theft Gangster Paradise is an action-packed gaming experience set in the neon-lit streets of Las Vegas. Players become ruthless gangsters, armed with a vast array of weapons, stylish costumes, and exotic cars. Engage in intense shootouts, daring missions, and high-speed street races while collecting valuable loot\nWelcome to the city of sin—the place where you can drown yourself in riches! Be prepared to live a new life and experience a limitless world where you make the rules. Do whatever it takes to quickly rake in a vast fortune and become a billionaire. In a world where there is no law, be ready to defend yourself at the drop ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ATEI6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crime-theft-gangster-paradise/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"110PC","slug":"block-puzzle-merge","title":"Block Puzzle Merge","description":"$31","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/110PC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-puzzle-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SPPJ7","slug":"back-to-school-jigsaw-picture-puzzle","title":"Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle! Our Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Back To School Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SPPJ7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/back-to-school-jigsaw-picture-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NS8S","slug":"mummies-slider-image-challenge","title":"Mummies Slider Image Challenge","description":"Welcome to Mummies Slider Image Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Mummies Slider Image Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Mummies Slider Image Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NS8S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mummies-slider-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U1159","slug":"music-notes-tile-image-scramble","title":"Music Notes Tile Image Scramble","description":"Welcome to Music Notes Tile Image Scramble! Our Music Notes Tile Image Scramble Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Music Notes Tile Image Scramble picture. With a wide variety of Music Notes Tile Image Scramble images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Music Notes Tile Image Scramble Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U1159/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/music-notes-tile-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9OH19","slug":"dunk-hoop","title":"Dunk Hoop","description":"\"Dunk Hoop\" is an exhilarating and fast-paced basketball-themed mobile game that brings the excitement of the court to the palm of your hand. Developed with stunning graphics and intuitive controls, this game offers an immersive and addictive experience for players of all ages.\n\nGet ready to showcase your basketball skills as you embark on a journey to become the ultimate Dunk Hoop champion. The objective is simple: slam-dunk the basketball through a series of challenging hoops to score points and progress through levels. The game features a variety of dynamic and visually appealing environments, from classic basketball courts to futuristic arenas, providing a diverse and engaging backdrop for your slam-dunk adventures.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9OH19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dunk-hoop/embed?sid=1","plays":40094,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9YBYA","slug":"crazy-baskets","title":"Crazy Baskets","description":"Crazy Baskets is an arcade basketball game to shoot the balls through the rings successfully.\n\nFeatures:\n\nDifferent levels, themes, and leagues\nReward box\nBall customization\nA new league every month\nPractice and get ranks\nPowerups system","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9YBYA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-baskets/embed?sid=1","plays":39897,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23A33","slug":"archer-2023","title":"Archer 2023","description":"Vous êtes un archer. Touchez la cible le plus de fois possible !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23A33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archer-2023/embed?sid=1","plays":39870,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC9E6","slug":"cat-clicker","title":"Cat Clicker","description":"Make cats by clicking. The cat bubbles growth accelerates when you start buying upgrades that increase the number of cat bubbles in production. Eventually, you’ll spawn billions of cat bubbles with each click, sending the cat world spiralling into a cuteness endless tunnel. You can use the reset button to start over and receive a permanent buff on your next game if you feel like a fresh start.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC9E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"133U8","slug":"bruum","title":"Bruum","description":"Bruum is a video game where you have to overtake other cars. By clicking on the screen your car will change lanes.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/133U8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bruum/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GG1EO","slug":"goal-keeper","title":"Goal Keeper","description":"Save goals and get your team to glory, be the best gaolkeeper in the world!\n\nGoalkeeper is a very addictive and intuitive soccer game for football fans to feel like a pro goalkeeper in the field.\n\nThe stadium is waiting to their soccer hero, you are under the crossbar very focused on the shot. Your opponent is going to shot to score a goal... don't permit it! ","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GG1EO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goal-keeper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E3UIR","slug":"elip-adventure","title":"Elip Adventure","description":"in this game you will play as an ellipse where you have to look for all the stars in the map to open the elliptical house so that you can proceed to the next stage.\n\nAt each level there are many obstacles and enemies trying to hinder you, you can avoid the enemies or defeat them.\n\nGame Features\n- Very attractive 2d graphics\n- The game is very light and supports all devices\n- Various kinds of obstacles and puzzles\n- There are many others","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E3UIR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-adventure-elip/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"30PT3","slug":"my-poky-virtual-pet","title":"My Poky Virtual Pet","description":"My Pou Virtual Pet, adoptez le mignon petit animal virtuel Poky et profitez d'innombrables heures de jeu passionnant et amusant. Avec des émotions réalistes, des graphismes époustouflants et des animations fluides, vous aurez l'impression que Moy est réel et, espérons-le, vous l'aimerez comme un véritable animal de compagnie. Gagnez des pièces, lavez votre animal de compagnie, achetez de la nourriture, jouez à des jeux et voyagez dans le parc avec ce jeu amusant sans fin.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/30PT3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-pou-virtual-pet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44ZH3","slug":"pair-matching-puzzle-2d","title":"Pair Matching Puzzle 2D","description":"Engage your mind with Pair Matching Puzzle 2D! Exercise your memory and concentration in this addictive matching game. Explore various levels of challenge, from easy to expert, and enjoy vibrant visuals. Sharpen your cognitive skills, unlock new levels, and immerse yourself in the joy of pair matching. Perfect for all ages, this 2D puzzle game is a delightful way to entertain and stimulate your brain. Get ready for hours of fun and mental agility!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44ZH3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pair-matching-puzzle-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OITOI","slug":"backrooms-skibidi-shooter","title":"Backrooms Skibidi Shooter","description":"Backrooms: Skibidi Shooter features endless backrooms crowded with skibidi toilets and your mission is to shoot your way through each level and try to find the exit to successfully complete each level and unlock new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OITOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/backrooms-skibidi-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N74T","slug":"pomni-blast","title":"Pomni Blast","description":"Hey Pomni needs Your help to escape from this Digital Circus world!\nThe main goal is to land Pomni in the safe area with the least number of attempts!\nYou just use the explosive to move Pomni in the right direction; but be aware at the dangerous obstacles!\nAre you able to get the three stars for each level?","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N74T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pomni-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RMBG2","slug":"pomni-coloring-book","title":"Pomni Coloring Book","description":"Pomni Coloring Book is fun coloring book for everyone! If you like digital circus characters then you will love this fun cartoon themed coloring book! Choose one of the cute images, pick your favorite color and start coloring! Enjoy it!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RMBG2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pomni-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1M060","slug":"giddy-pomni","title":"Giddy Pomni","description":"It’s Giddy Pomni the hottest game on the charts at the moment!\nTap To Match The Pmni As Many As You Can!\nMemory Test: Giddy Pomni Game new mix of speed, memory and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test it this game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1M060/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/giddy-pomni/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SPISI","slug":"ice-princess-all-around-the-fashion","title":"Ice Princess All Around The Fashion","description":"Welcome to the Ice Princess All Around The Fashion. Enter the enchanting world of the Ice Princess, where fashion knows no bounds! Explore a realm of icy elegance and timeless style. From regal ball gowns to chic modern looks, discover a wardrobe fit for a princess. Join her on a journey through the world of fashion, where every outfit tells a story. Unleash your inner fashionista and embrace the magic of the Ice Princess’s style!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SPISI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ice-princess-all-around-the-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H2ENS","slug":"insta-celebrity-hashtag-goals","title":"Insta Celebrity Hashtag Goals","description":"Unlock your inner star with Insta Celebrity Hashtag Goals! Celebrities plan to elevate their fashionista in social media. Join and help them to complete their goal at each level. Mix and match the outfit on each level. Take a picture and post it on social media to earn more points. Have fun! ","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H2ENS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/insta-celebrity-hashtag-goals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TOK2N","slug":"pocong-ketemu-kuntilanak","title":"Pocong Ketemu Kuntilanak","description":"pocong and kuntilanak is horror folklore from indonesia","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TOK2N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocong-ketemu-kuntilanak/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AECEL","slug":"flappy-helicopter-2-player","title":"Flappy Helicopter 2 Player","description":"Are you up for a two-player helicopter battle? To win in the helicopter battle, you must be the one who detonates the most. Engage in combat with your friend and emerge victorious. The one who detonates the most helicopters wins. The player who explodes 10 times loses. Remember, its not just bullets; if you fly too high and hit the ground or the sky, youll explode. Are you up for the duel with your friend?\n\n*To use the red helicopter, press the W key. \n*To use the blue helicopter, press the Up Arrow Key. \n*The first to reach 10 points wins.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AECEL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-helicopter-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7J074","slug":"jump-or-lose","title":"Jump or Lose","description":"The water level is rising every second, the best will win. The one who survives the most wins. You have 5 lives. Winning or losing is up to you. Compete and win with your friend. If you want to beat your friend, reach the highest level.Choose a red or blue player color and start the game. Win and buy yourself a hat with the coins.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7J074/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-or-lose/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1P727","slug":"pixbros-2-player","title":"PixBros - 2 Player","description":"Are you up for an adventure in the pixel world? Our quest involves dangerous monsters and diamonds to collect. You must survive in the cave throughout the adventure. Defeat the monsters and reach the portal. Collect all the diamonds and the key. You should reach the portal with your friend. Work together as a team with your friend to complete all the levels.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.\n*Mobile touch control is available\n*Double jump available","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1P727/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixbros-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"007A0","slug":"stickboys-xmas","title":"StickBoys Xmas","description":"Are you ready for the Christmas fun of the red and blue stick boys? Help them during Christmas and get them to the door. A more challenging day awaits you in the Christmas adventure. You must survive with your friend. Collect the keys and own all the candies. Watch out for obstacles. Reach the door together with your friend in Christmas.\n\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/007A0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickboys-xmas/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"112L5","slug":"hardxel","title":"Hardxel","description":"Help the twin siblings reach the portal located in the cave. Assist the twin siblings in their adventure. Help them reach the chests, open them, and find the key. While searching for the key, collect all the coins. Once you complete all the tasks, reach the door together with your sibling.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.\n*Mobile touch control is available\n*Double jump available","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/112L5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hardxel/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9S9SR","slug":"tanks-2d-war-and-heroes","title":"Tanks 2D War and Heroes","description":"A real epic tank battle!\nEverything is simple: take a tank, improve your weapons, start the military action.\nHuge selection of real historical tanks for the game: MC1, BT2, T60, T127, T28, T50, T34, KB1 and others in new updates! Each tank can be selected and pumped.\nA wide range of unique enemies and bosses will not let you get bored! Can you defeat them all?\nChoose, buy and upgrade your tank. Collect your deadly weapons and show who's boss!\n\n- Enjoy the exciting gameplay and let the whole world wait.\n- Fight with armored vehicles, infantry, fortified objects, bosses and planes and, of course, with other tanks!\n- Sophisticated ballistics\n- Useful game bonuses\n\nStart and play Tanks 2D: War and Heroes!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9S9SR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tanks-2d-war-and-heroes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0ED0R","slug":"spider-hidden-difference","title":"Spider Hidden Difference","description":"Spider Hidden Difference is a well-designed brain challenge about find any difference between spider object.\nFind Differences Spider Hidden Difference will take you through a relaxing and enjoyable journey. Explore hundred of free-to-play levels and have fun while trying to spot differences between spider picture.\n\nImprove your concentration and detective skills. Search and spot hidden objects. Relax your mind.\nBut beware of spider!!!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0ED0R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider-hidden-difference/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D7660","slug":"grand-crime-auto-6","title":"Grand Crime Auto 6","description":"Welcome to the city of sin—the place where you can drown yourself in riches!\nBe prepared to live a new life and experience a limitless world where you make the rules.\nDo whatever it takes to quickly rake in a vast fortune and become a billionaire.\nIn a world where there is no law, be ready to defend yourself at the drop of a hat.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D7660/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-crime-auto-6/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OONGL","slug":"pocong-and-kuntilanak-terror-horror","title":"Pocong and Kuntilanak Terror Horror","description":"pocong and kuntilanak, a horror folk from indonesia make terror again.\nin abandoned restrict area!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OONGL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocong-and-kuntilanak-terror-horror/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MVRA9","slug":"asami-mom-adventure","title":"Asami Mom Adventure","description":"Asami Mom Adventure is a 2D Christmas themed platformer where you play as a mom who have to collect all of the gift boxes and bring them to your daughter while avoiding the enemy monsters, spikes, and moving saws in order to go to the next level. \n\nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up' arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MVRA9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asami-mom-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KO002","slug":"axoskibiki-world","title":"Axoskibiki World","description":"Axoskibiki World is a 2D platformer where you play as a cute gray cat who have to collect all of the bananas while avoiding the enemy cats, skibidi cats, spikes, rotating blades, and bullets to reach the pink flags in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KO002/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/axoskibiki-world/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31TA1","slug":"a-sniper-s-vengeance-the-story-of-linh","title":"A Sniper's Vengeance The Story of Linh","description":"An action first person shooter game set in time of Vietnam war.\n\nThis game, set in the backdrop of the Vietnam War, follows the journey of Linh, a young girl who  joins the Vietnamese Army and trains to become a sniper, determined to avenge .\n\nAs players step into the shoes of Linh, they will experience a simple story line filled with intense action gameplay. The game offers a unique perspective on the war, as players witness it through the eyes of a female protagonist who is not only fighting for her country but also for her personal vendetta.\n\nGame feautres\n\nIntense and exciting shooter gameplay\n\nBeautiful environment\n\nEasy to pick up and play","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31TA1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/a-sniper-s-vengeance-the-story-of-linh/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8A864","slug":"darkness-in-spaceship","title":"Darkness in Spaceship","description":"Darkness in spaceship is a first person action horror game set in a sci fi space base.\n\nStory\n\n The story takes place in the future when the Earth has become uninhabitable and other planets are not suitable for life, so humanity lives only in large spaceships. The hero lives in the spaceship called Light and is a special agent. One day their ship is attacked by enemies. Enemies first bring monsters into the ship and then send robot soldiers. The hero must destroy the enemies and save his people.\n\nGame Features\n\n    Intense action horror gameplay\n\n    Beautiful  and atmospheric sci-fi environment \n\n    Entertaining and simple story\n\n    Good graphics","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8A864/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/darkness-in-spaceship/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36CF3","slug":"fit-cats","title":"Fit Cats","description":"Cats love boxes! Launch cats of different sizes into the box. If two cats of the same size touch each other, they merge into one larger cat. \n\nIn the game, you can also use the mouse to drive any cat out of the box. Also, from time to time you can catch mice that give this opportunity.\nTry to unlock all the cats.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36CF3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fit-cats/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"52468","slug":"santa-bomber-3d","title":"Santa Bomber 3D","description":"Get ready for an explosive and jolly adventure in \"Santa's Gift Drop,\" the most festive bombing game of the holiday season! Santa Claus has traded in his sleigh for a high-tech bomber, and he needs your help to deliver presents to children around the world in record time.\n\nTake control of Santa's state-of-the-art gift bomber as you soar through the skies, navigating challenging terrains and avoiding obstacles. Drop presents with precision to ensure they land safely in the chimneys of eagerly waiting children","category":"Aventure","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/52468/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-bomber-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S5SLU","slug":"baseball-super","title":"Baseball Super","description":"Step up to the plate and experience the ultimate baseball showdown in Baseball Super! This web-based sports sensation delivers a home run with its realistic gameplay, stunning graphics, and an immersive baseball experience like never before.\n\nFeatures:\n\nRealistic Gameplay: Feel the thrill of a live baseball game with realistic physics, accurate player movements, and authentic ball dynamics.\n\nStadium Experience: Play in iconic stadiums with dynamic weather conditions, day-night cycles, and a lively crowd that reacts to every swing and pitch.\n\nSuper Skills: Unleash special super skills unique to each player. Hit colossal home runs, throw blazing fastballs, and make incredible catches to dominate the game.\n\nEasy Controls: Enjoy intuitive controls that make playing Super Baseball accessible for players of all skill levels. Swing for the fences with a simple tap or click.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S5SLU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baseball-super/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O947O","slug":"fragilefloor","title":"FragileFloor","description":"Vous devrez briser le sol sous vos adversaires pour les empêcher de survivre! Surpassez-les et prenez la première place pour vous!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O947O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fragilefloor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62R49","slug":"drawin","title":"DrawIn","description":"Draw In is an HTML5 Arcade Game. In this HTML5 game, you should draw a straight line to fit the perimeter of the given shape. Continue drawing the line until you guess it will fit After fitting the line, you’ll see the funny colored shape! This addictive game sounds easy but it’s NOT!! You should be very careful to draw the exact straight line! Suitable for all types of audiences including kids.\n\nThe graphics of this HTMLL5  game is really beautiful and every level has a nice object, animal, fruit, and other things that you can see after winning.\n\n\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62R49/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drawin/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0F584","slug":"mergeface","title":"MergeFace","description":"Merge Face is an HTML5 Puzzle Game . In this game, there are funny face blocks on a puzzle board with different emotions. Each emotion has a number, and by tapping on them their number increases to one more. You should merge three same faces beside each other and make a higher number. By merging three or more faces together, you will receive coins. With your coins, you can use three options: decrease a block’s number increase a block’s number to 2 more breaks a block.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0F584/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mergeface/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PSCP7","slug":"space-ship-survivor","title":"Space Ship Survivor","description":"$32","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PSCP7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-ship-survivor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"38E7I","slug":"drift-race-in-the-open-world","title":"Drift Race in the Open World","description":"Welcome to the world of adrenaline drift racing! Are you ready to plunge into incredible adventures on the asphalt?\nGame Features\nHuge vehicle fleet: choose from numerous powerful cars, each of which has its own character and features. From classic sports cars to exotic race cars, the possibilities are endless!\n\nCar tuning: Pump and customize your car down to the smallest detail. Prepare for street battles by customizing the engine, suspension, aerodynamics and even the color of your car.\n\nMultiple cities to play in the open world: a variety of locations. Explore fascinating cities full of secret streets and incredible drift spots.\n\nCrash mode (test mode): ready to test yourself to the limit? Turn on crash mode and try to complete a series of exciting tests in which you will have to drive a car in the most extreme conditions.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/38E7I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drift-race-in-the-open-world/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PG0C4","slug":"rainbow-girls-christmas-party","title":"Rainbow Girls Christmas Party","description":"Welcome to the Rainbow Girls Christmas Party game. Skyler and Sunny are best friends. They decided to attend the Christmas party at Rainbow High. Both have a secret crush on Collin, who also come to the party. So the girls try to impress him with their stunning look. Join and help them. Have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PG0C4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-girls-christmas-party/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TT78S","slug":"princess-winter-style","title":"Princess Winter Style","description":"Princess Winter Style has just begun. Princesses want to get out in the winter but are in dilemma in choosing the best outfit. Help them get cute with warm outfits and enjoy spending time with them in this cute new dress up game!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TT78S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-winter-style/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O825E","slug":"ellie-and-ben-christmas-preparation","title":"Ellie And Ben Christmas Preparation","description":"Welcome to the Ellie And Ben Christmas Preparation. Ellie and Ben are the new couples going to celebrate the upcoming Christmas together. They have some plans to do!. Like decorate the interior with beautiful Christmas things and decorate their Christmas Tree. Join and Help the couples to make this Christmas the most memorable one!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O825E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ellie-and-ben-christmas-preparation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4NRNO","slug":"rotating-pomni","title":"Rotating Pomni","description":"Rotating Pomni is a unique platform puzzle game where you rotate the world to guide Pomni to his lost stars. This is a great puzzle game with 40 challenge levels, push your logical brain abilities to the limit! Product feature bullets:\n• Grimace on board!\n• 40 different levels!\n• Very Fun for children!\n• Brain training for whole family!\n• Cute graphics!\n• Precise gameplay!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4NRNO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotating-pomni/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"US6EO","slug":"santa-and-the-dungeon-of-doom","title":"Santa And The Dungeon Of Doom","description":"Santa and The Dungeon Of Doom  is an epic adventure through 100 levels of monsters, traps and danger!!!\nHave you got the brains and fast reflexes to escape all 100 dungeons in this unique action puzzle game?\nBats will chase you, Ghosts will try and trick you, Monsters around every corner, Hazards include Spikes, Guillotines, Poison gas and more...\nHave you got what it takes?\nProduct feature bullets:\n- Xmas Game!\n- 100 epic levels!\n- Cute graphic!\n- Cool Xmas music!\n- Really addictive! \n- Easy to play!\nEnjoy with this great Christmas Puzzle Adventure game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/US6EO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-and-the-dungeon-of-doom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"883AO","slug":"pomni-math-game","title":"Pomni Math Game","description":"Youre good at maths?\nwell then try to answer all the questions about the tiles where an image of Pomni is hidden underneath!\nHow to play:\ndrag all the left numbered blocks on to the corresponding right tiles covering the picture.\nHave fun and try to discover all Pomni pictures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/883AO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pomni-math-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3177I","slug":"xmissilex","title":"XmissileX","description":"Welcome to the classic game XmissileX go and shoot and destroy all the ships, your high score remains saved","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3177I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/xmissilex/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2906Y","slug":"crazybird2","title":"CrazyBird2","description":"Welcome to CrazyBird2, you will have to pass through the columns but collect coins and watches for a long time to survive, what are you waiting for?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2906Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazybird2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C3806","slug":"ric","title":"Ric","description":"Welcome to the Ric game, click and jump over the boulders that will try to kill you, you always have to beat your record...","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C3806/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ric/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1NNR0","slug":"stick-runner","title":"Stick Runner","description":"Stick Runner is an adrenaline-pumping game that challenges your reflexes and agility. Navigate through a treacherous landscape filled with obstacles that test your skills to survive. Jump over hurdles using the touch buttons or the space key to keep your character safe, or swiftly slide under barriers by pressing the down arrow. The game's fast-paced action and dynamic obstacles promise an exciting experience for players aiming to achieve the highest scores and conquer the leaderboard.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1NNR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stick-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AI00S","slug":"save-the-cute-aliens","title":"Save The Cute Aliens","description":"In \"Save The Cute Aliens,\" immerse yourself in an intergalactic adventure where your planet is threatened by a devastating meteor, and only you can save the alien population!\n\nThe inhabitants of your home planet, a variety of adorable and colorful aliens, are in imminent danger. The lethal meteor is rapidly approaching, but there is hope: a special spaceship appears on the left side of the screen, indicating the color of the aliens that can reverse time and delay the catastrophe for another minute.\n\nYour mission is to match three or more aliens of the same color to eliminate them from the playing field. But here's the crucial challenge: you need to focus on uniting three or more aliens of the exact color that corresponds to the spaceship on the left. When this happens, the countdown timer for the meteor's arrival is reset, granting more precious time to save more aliens.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AI00S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-cute-aliens/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0088A","slug":"alien-merge-2048","title":"Alien Merge 2048","description":"Alien Merge 2048 is a modified version of the game 2048, but with the same objective.\nJoin equal numbers until you reach the number 2048.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0088A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-merge-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RRMR","slug":"metamorphosis-survivor","title":"Metamorphosis Survivor","description":"Metamorphosis Survivor: Challenge metamorphosis and survive constant transformation! In this exciting and challenging game, dive into a world in constant flux, where survival depends on the ability to adapt and transform. Take control of a character in constant evolution, whose goal is to become part of an identical group to destroy others. Face the challenge of constantly changing your form, assimilating other identities to thrive. Every collision with a different character leads to an instant metamorphosis. Uncover a world full of transformation possibilities, each with its unique advantages and challenges. Master the art of adaptation while navigating through an ever-evolving environment. Be agile, strategic, and cunning to ensure your survival in the fascinating and unpredictable universe of Metamorphosis Survivor!.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RRMR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/metamorphosis-survivor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0D1RR","slug":"words-cords","title":"Words Cords","description":"In the game you need to find words in a given word.\nTo pass the level you need to find all the words in the crossword puzzle.\nIf you can't find a word, use the hint.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0D1RR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/words-from-words/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3S41","slug":"find-words","title":"Find Words","description":"In the game you need to find words in a given word.\nIf you can't find a word, use the hint.\nUse the hint if you get stuck.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3S41/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-words/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C960C","slug":"simple-words-search","title":"Simple Words Search","description":"Try to find all the words in the game.\nWords on the field can be placed: horizontally, vertically and diagonally.\nAt the top are the words you need to find.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C960C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/words-search/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2T0IA","slug":"simple-spider-solitaire","title":"Simple Spider Solitaire","description":"You are invited to play Spider Solitaire.\nIn the game you need to place cards from king to ace.\nYou can choose the number of suits to play.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2T0IA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider-solitaire-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"53953","slug":"simple-klondike-solitaire","title":"Simple Klondike Solitaire","description":"You are invited to play Klondike solitaire.\nIn the game you need to move cards to the four right fields.\nArrange the cards from Ace to King.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/53953/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/klondike-solitaire-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14EAE","slug":"simple-free-cell-solitaire","title":"Simple Free Cell Solitaire","description":"You are invited to play Card Solitaire - Free Cell\nIn the game you need to move cards to the four right fields.\nArrange the cards from Ace to King.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14EAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/free-cell-solitaire-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O6717","slug":"simple-domino","title":"Simple Domino","description":"Play domino against your computer opponent.\nPlayer and computer get 7 domino tiles each.\n14 domino tiles are placed to a base.\nPlayer with minimal double tile points (1:1, 2:2, etc.) starts first.\nTo win you have to put all items first. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O6717/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/domino/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LUB1E","slug":"bubble-poke","title":"Bubble Poke","description":"Poke the bubbles of the same color.\nTouch them and they will burst.\nGet higher score for the number.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LUB1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-poke/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TOJIP","slug":"hidden-objects-power-of-love","title":"Hidden Objects - Power of Love","description":"Help Mary to find her husband.\nExplore different locations, talk to people.\nFind hidden objects and solve the puzzles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TOJIP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-objects-power-of-love/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"227O1","slug":"simple-8-pool","title":"Simple 8 Pool","description":"Put all balls into the holes.\nFor each ball you will get a score.\nSet your new time record.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/227O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pool/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UT3L1","slug":"ball-adventure","title":"Ball Adventure","description":"Help the Ball to save his girlfriend.\nHe can move and change the size.\nPass the levels as fast as you can.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UT3L1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2GC2G","slug":"simple-checkers","title":"Simple Checkers","description":"Play Checkers against the computer.\nSelect white or black checkers.\nTry to be smart and think better.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2GC2G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/checkers-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"02C69","slug":"minicars-racing","title":"MiniCars Racing","description":"Drive your car to win the race.\n20 unique tracks are waiting for you.\nBecome the fastest driver ever.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/02C69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cars-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L0U68","slug":"sudoku-simple-puzzle","title":"Sudoku Simple Puzzle","description":"Play a classic Sudoku game.\nFill free cells with digits from 1 to 9.\nYou can put numbers so that in a row, in a column\nand in a small square 3x3 the digits were encountered only once.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L0U68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sudoku-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G1G91","slug":"gems-match","title":"Gems Match","description":"Collect gems.\nMake them in a row of three or more.\nUse bonuses to speed up the game.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G1G91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gems-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LT867","slug":"bet-ball-blitz","title":"Bet Ball Blitz","description":"Bet Ball Blitz is a casual simulation game where you drop balls down a randomly generated course and see who can reach the finish line first. You also get to bet on which ball you think will win and then you can spend your money to buy more balls and more backgrounds! Don't feel discouraged when you lose as there are coins spread around the map to help you get you money back up!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LT867/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bet-ball-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91887","slug":"volley-boys","title":"Volley Boys","description":"Volley Boys; It is a sports game that you can play with one click. Just jump and hit the ball in time. score points if your opponent makes a mistake. Be sure to jump in time, you will have a chance to Dunk at a good height!. Earn trophies and reach high scores. Become one of the winners of the most matches. Your opponents come randomly every game and the one with 3 points wins!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91887/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/volley-boys/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21INI","slug":"home-pin-2","title":"Home Pin 2","description":"Welcome to chapter 2 of the Home Pin. Start your adventure of the pin world in the secret manor!\n\nYou want to protect the family? You want to create your own manor and restore the beautiful manor to its former glory? Play Home Pin 2: Family Adventure now - an unique pull pin game with a family storyline you can’t ignore. No more fake ads, this is the game you are looking for!\n\nIn Home Pin 2: Family Adventure, you need to help a mom and her little girl in an abandoned house survive through the cold weather by pulling the pin. Use your wisdom to help them get the matchbox, the charcoal or collect money to restore the manor.","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21INI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/home-pin-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R2R13","slug":"monster-duelist","title":"Monster Duelist","description":"\"Monster Duelist\" immerses players into a mysterious world where they assume the role of a monster duelist. Exploring vast territories, they capture various unique monsters. Through battles against formidable opponents, players enhance their combat prowess, striving to become the ultimate duelist. Utilizing the monsters they capture, they assemble a powerful team, engage in battles, and demonstrate their skills and courage!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R2R13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-hunter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5TEX","slug":"mahjong-butterflies-deluxe","title":"Mahjong Butterflies Deluxe","description":"Enjoy an original and very interesting game - mahjong puzzle. In it you will find marvelous butterflies, unlock fun weirdos and of course, you will be waiting for the original mahjong dice. Especially for mahjong lovers - collect butterflies, earn stars and unlock new tiles! Explore the amazing world! This colorful mahjong trains concentration and visual perception!\n\n⦁ More than 160 different mahjong tiles,\n⦁ Easy to understand gameplay suitable for all ages,\n⦁ Helpful hints are always available when you need them,\n⦁ 6 different kinds of mahjong tiles,\n⦁ Collect stars on an epic journey,\n⦁ Unlock new mahjong tiles,\n⦁ Train your concentration and visual perception!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5TEX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-butterflies-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F3617","slug":"farm-life","title":"Farm Life","description":"Farm Life is a casual game that immerses you in a serene and delightful countryside experience.  Within this game, you'll engage in a variety of activities—planting, harvesting, breeding, and managing your very own farm.\n\nPlanting and Trading\nCultivate crops to nurture and expand your farm!  After harvesting wheat, tomatoes, and more, head to the market to trade with fellow players, selling your produce and building your envisioned dream farm!\n\nProduction Plant\nWithin your own production facility, process different crops into refined industrial products for trading, securing higher returns on your investments.\n\nCollection and Decoration\nThe farm's cottage brims with charming furniture and unlockable decorative sets, enabling you to style your farm to reflect your unique taste!  Cottages can generate passive income and expedite the growth of your farm!\n\nIn Farm Life, relish the tranquility of country living as you delve into a tapestry of agricultural pursuits, trade, and creative farm development!\"","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F3617/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/farm-life/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H031A","slug":"hotel-manager","title":"Hotel Manager","description":"Vous rêvez depuis toujours d’être l’un des plus grands promoteurs immobiliers au monde ?\n\nAlors, saisissez votre chance dans ce jeu extrêmement addictif !\n\nBâtissez des hôtels, développez-les et ruinez vos rivaux pour attirer leurs clients dans vos établissements !","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H031A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hotel-manager/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MR3SA","slug":"backrooms-skibidi-escape","title":"Backrooms Skibidi Escape","description":"Backrooms Skibidi Escape is a horror game where you are trapped in the backrooms chased by skibidi toilet and your mission is to find the exit or given number of video tapes to successfully complete each level.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MR3SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/backrooms-skibidi-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M7PGR","slug":"watermelon-pang-pang","title":"Watermelon Pang Pang","description":"Merge Fruits to Watermelon!\nPlay a fruit-matching game, where you collide identical fruits to evolve them and keep them from falling out of the box. But here's the twist: when the same fruits collide, they transform into an entirely new fruit. Can you merge your way to the grand watermelon?\n\nStrategically match fruits, and aim to become the ultimate Fruit Pang Pang. Keep the fruits from spilling out and challenge your mind with dynamic transformations.\n\nRemember, every merge counts! \n\nJoin the Ultimate Fruitful Adventure Now!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M7PGR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/watermelon-pang-pang/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1LB11","slug":"boneless","title":"Boneless","description":"A poor man with just one arm left tries to escape from alien monsters and survive with limited ammo. How long you can survive against growing army of alien monsters, while they getting stronger and crowded each wave?\n\nUpgrade your bullets' damage, your health and movement speed with coins that you gain when you killed an animal monster each time!\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1LB11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boneless/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A12O1","slug":"assault-on-the-evil-star","title":"Assault on the Evil Star","description":"Assault on the Evil Star is a browser scifi third person shooter inspired by games  like Halo and Doom.\n\nStory\n\nThe story is about a special forces soldier who finds out about a big conspiracy to destroy humanity and tries to save people. He encounters enemy soldiers and scary monsters on his adventure.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A12O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/assault-on-the-evil-star/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CBLTK","slug":"skibidi-toilet-clicker","title":"Skibidi Toilet Clicker","description":"This is madness carzy and funny clicker game about skibidi toilets!!\n\nGreat skibidi toilet adventure\n\n\nClick to get points!!!!\nBuy cool upgrades!!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CBLTK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"45NN6","slug":"lines","title":"Lines","description":"Remove the balls of same color from the field.\nMake lines of 5 and more to remove a line.\nWhen a line of balls is removed new balls appear.\nTry to place balls in a good positions.\nThe longer line - the higher score.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/45NN6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lines/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W8AW2","slug":"robot-warfare","title":"Robot Warfare","description":"robot warfare is a game when you have to kill the enemies robots, but be careful, don't get caught or you lose.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W8AW2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-warfare/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15N35","slug":"call-to-lethal-company","title":"Call to Lethal Company","description":"L’entreprise meurtrière a un besoin urgent de stagiaires !\nAppelez d'urgence les salariés de l'entreprise et pas seulement pour savoir ce que c'est que de travailler dans une entreprise meurtrière !!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15N35/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/call-to-lethal-company/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44K53","slug":"clickerdon","title":"Clickerdon","description":"Le but du jeu est simple : appuyez sur le bouton. Plus vous appuyez sur le bouton plusieurs fois, plus vous gagnez de points et plus vite vous atteindrez le sommet du classement Clickerdon.\nIl n'y a pas de stratégie, pas d'énigme - seulement du hardcore et du push.\n\nLe Clickerdon le plus rapide gagnera.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44K53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/clickerdon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6704M","slug":"enemy-attack","title":"Enemy Attack","description":"\nEnemy Attack, a game where you have to defend yourself from evil bats.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6704M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/enemy-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"07795","slug":"do-it-up","title":"Do it up!","description":"Faites-le ! - et rien d'autre!\nSi parfois vous ne comprenez pas ce qui se passe autour de vous, alors ici vous comprendrez certainement tout - c'est l'endroit pour vous !\n\nA votre disposition se trouve une petite ville dans laquelle vous pourrez courir, sauter et marcher.\nBougez, amusez-vous et rappelez-vous - seulement vers le haut !","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/07795/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/do-it-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6R7SA","slug":"meteorite-assult","title":"Meteorite Assult","description":"You are in a spaceship, be careful of the meteorites and don't get hit otherwise you will lose, try to get the highest score and collect coins to be able to buy other spaceships for extra advantages.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6R7SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meteorite-assult/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9HIAT","slug":"titan-the-way-to-the-bottom","title":"Titan - The Way to the Bottom","description":"Les océans de notre planète ont été étudiés à un peu plus de 4 %, chaque expédition devient donc l'occasion d'apprendre quelque chose de nouveau sur nous, sur notre planète.\n\nNous vous invitons à participer à une plongée passionnante non seulement au fond, mais aussi au fond du célèbre navire Titanic. Mais ce chemin n'est pas facile : pour sauver l'équipe et votre bateau, vous devrez le gonfler suffisamment pour atteindre l'objectif - LE BAS. Distribuez correctement vos ressources gagnées pour survivre et ramener votre équipe.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9HIAT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/titan-the-way-to-the-bottom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A2232","slug":"spacescape","title":"SpaceScape","description":"Enjoy over 100 beautiful images from the NASA archives while you learn new words, expand your vocabulary and exercise your mind with these addictive word puzzles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A2232/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spacescape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"08612","slug":"20482048","title":"20482048","description":"2048 2048 - le monde a besoin de ce genre de mathématiques !\nLes jeunes et les moins jeunes dotés d'un esprit mathématique et d'un esprit humanitaire peuvent jouer avec les chiffres en toute sécurité.\n\nOui, nous n’avons pas inventé le vélo, nous avons simplement modernisé le célèbre jeu des chiffres.\nNotre design vous surprendra agréablement : des dés 3D, furieusement empilés, prêts à lancer leurs numéros.\n\nJouez, amusez-vous, profitez du nouveau design du jeu que vous aimez déjà.\nJuste K.Corp.\n\nUne autorisation est requise pour participer aux classements.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/08612/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I17AA","slug":"moonshine-runners-samogonki","title":"Moonshine Runners Samogonki","description":"$33","category":"Course","tags":["adventure","arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I17AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/moonshine-runners-samogonki/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K5951","slug":"kids-alphabet","title":"Kids Alphabet","description":"Educational Game, Specifically Made for Children!\nIntroducing “Kids Alphabet”, the latest educational game developed by RolinkStudio, specially crafted for children! Within this engaging game, kids will explore the wonders of the alphabet, practice writing skills, and expand their vocabulary.\n\nFeaturing a captivating blend of vibrant visuals and a delightful female voice, children will be immersed in an enchanting kindergarten-like experience! This game is ideal for businesses and portals seeking to provide both education and entertainment.\n\n ","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K5951/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-alphabet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4RF14","slug":"fruitmasslice","title":"FruitMasSlice","description":"Do You Want an Attractive Arcade HTML5 Game? Here You Are!\nBecome a master of slicing fruits in this Christmas HTML5 Arcade Game, Fruitmas. Slice fruit, don’t slice bombs – that is all you need to know to get started with Fruitmas! This HTML5 3D Game is mobile-friendly and can be played on both browser and mobile.\n\nWhy you’ll love Fruitmas:\n\nBeautiful Christmas theme\nLots of juicy fruits\nCool animations and SFX\nSimple & intuitive controls\nEasy and fun to play\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4RF14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruitmasslice/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2I12I","slug":"fruitmaster","title":"FruitMaster","description":"A Fun Arcade Game for Your Portal to Attract Users!\nFruit Master is an addictive HTML5 Casual Arcade HTML5 Game. You should target fruits with a knife and explode them, this is very funny ?? In this HTML5 game, you should throw the knife toward different fruits of each level and cut all of them. You have a limited number of knives. So, be careful and don’t waste your knives easily! Fruit Master has many levels with different mixes of fruits which excites you. By passing the levels the types of fruits will change and you will enjoy them!\n\nThis game has a cool and beautiful graphic design that makes it a good game for your kid audience. \n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2I12I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruitmaster/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9RDDG","slug":"amazing-wording","title":"Amazing Wording","description":"A Word Game With High User-Engagement !\nAmazing Wording is an HTML5 Word Game suitable for creative game lovers! On each level of this HTML5 game, there are some letters and some blank spaces. You should match the letters and make new words! The words can be in different numbers of letters! Challenge your knowledge of words in this game! Can you guess difficult words? Well, use a dictionary or use your coins to get a hint. By guessing every word you will get some scores you can pay as a guide. You may find some extra words which are not in the puzzle. Your extra guesses will add to another place for more scores! So let’s try!\n\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9RDDG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-wording/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7B8R","slug":"football-rumble","title":"Football Rumble","description":"Welcome to \"Football rush\" a game where you can select your favourite squad and take it to the victory before the time run-out.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7B8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-rumble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OOB1O","slug":"color-tower-2-drop-the-box-3d","title":"Color Tower 2 - Drop The Box 3D","description":"Color Tower 2 - Drop The Boxes 3D - is an exciting arcade game where you need to build a tower of colored boxes. Compete with players from all over the world, show the best result in this game, top the ranking in the leaderboard, share with friends and win!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OOB1O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-tower-2-drop-the-box-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6I421","slug":"smileys","title":"Smileys","description":"Toutes les émoticônes doivent être amusantes","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6I421/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smileys/embed?sid=1","plays":39879,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CCL27","slug":"color-circle","title":"Color Circle","description":"Testez votre vitesse de réaction. Vous pouvez être le plus rapide ?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CCL27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-circle/embed?sid=1","plays":40042,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T1T1","slug":"bright-ball","title":"Bright Ball","description":"Bright Ball! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T1T1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bright-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39779,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15PBP","slug":"blocks-puzzle","title":"Blocks Puzzle","description":"If you like puzzles, this game is for you. Build and fill lines with blocks, score as many points as possible.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15PBP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocks-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CAN2E","slug":"amazing-cube-adventure","title":"Amazing Cube Adventure","description":"Amazing Cube Adventure - new cool challenge game for you! Ready your reflexes! You need simply run and jump!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CAN2E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-cube-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":39970,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T4YB","slug":"arrow-hit","title":"Arrow Hit","description":"Embarquez pour une aventure exaltante dans le royaume virtuel avec « Arrow Hit », le jeu d'arcade ultime qui met vos compétences en tir à l'arc à l'épreuve ! Plongez-vous dans un monde captivant où la précision, le timing et l'exactitude sont les clés de la victoire.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T4YB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cowboy-hits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96SS0","slug":"mushy","title":"Mushy","description":"\nA little mushroom is looking for food in the forest help him not to eat poisoned logs and get points, good luck!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96SS0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mushy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KHCRT","slug":"trick-shot-world-challenge","title":"Trick Shot - World Challenge","description":"Trick Shot - World Challenge - est un jeu d'arcade html5 intéressant pour vous et vos amis. Plus de 200 niveaux sont disponibles dans ce jeu addictif. Lancez autant de balles que possible dans la coupe et arrivez en tête du classement mondial.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KHCRT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trick-shot-world-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DS6KD","slug":"speakerman-skibidi-dop-yes-yes","title":"Speakerman-Skibidi Dop Yes Yes","description":"“Speakerman: Skibidi Dop Yes”, is a fun game to play. To move to the next pillar, all you have to do is make the wood log to the required length. But it’s not as easy as you think. You need perfect timing to make a perfect length wood log. Do not make it too long or too short; otherwise, you will fall. Play now and have fun. \n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DS6KD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speakerman-skibidi-dop-yes-yes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T0OE5","slug":"speakerman-vs-skibidi-toilet","title":"Speakerman Vs Skibidi Toilet","description":"The game is set in a post-apocalyptic world where the Speakerman and the Skibidi Toilet are the two most powerful forces. The Speakerman is a giant robot with a powerful speaker that can emit destructive sound waves.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T0OE5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speakerman-vs-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64P0I","slug":"air-hockey-cup","title":"Air Hockey Cup","description":"Attachez vos patins et votre veste d'hiver. Votre sport de glace préféré est ici sous une nouvelle forme amusante. Déplacez vos jetons comme de vrais joueurs et maîtrisez le palet. Grimpez les échelons et détruisez les tournois !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64P0I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/air-hockey-cup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LG022","slug":"2048-x2-legend","title":"2048 X2 Legend","description":"L'insaisissable bloc 2048 est presque à votre portée. Combinez et comptez vos blocs. Atteignez des scores de plus en plus élevés, tout en aiguisant votre esprit. \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LG022/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-x2-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54622","slug":"farming-life","title":"Farming Life","description":"Repartez à zéro dans une petite ville avec une minuscule ferme. Construisez-la et vendez vos produits sur le marché local. Devenez le fermier local le plus populaire avec la plus grande et la meilleure ferme du coin !\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54622/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/farming-life/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H751O","slug":"the-day-of-zombies","title":"The Day of Zombies","description":"The Day of Zombies is a zombie survival shooter game where you play as an american ranger and your mission is to search for weapons across the map in order to survive. The game features vast location to explore and big arsenal of weapons to find.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H751O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-day-of-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K37O7","slug":"stickman-football","title":"Stickman Football","description":"Do you like football and stickmen? Then this game is for you!\n\nWhat awaits you in the game:\n- Field, ball, goal and blue men\n- Realistic physics\n- Endless level for the record\n- Tutorial level\n- 31 levels, from simple to difficult\n- Cool music\n- Epic game over screen!\n\nDo you want to see him? Complete the game to the end!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K37O7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-football/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1KEA6","slug":"tanks-battle-royale","title":"Tanks Battle Royale","description":"$34","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1KEA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battletanks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25NC3","slug":"mcatlantis","title":"Mcatlantis","description":"In this new adventure, you must reach the portal. To reach the portal, you should collaborate with your friend and work as a team. Teamwork is essential to survive in the Atlantis world. Work together with your friend and triumph. Defeat all the monsters. You must vanquish all the monsters and collect the black coins. The black coins are necessary to create the portal.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.\n*Mobile touch control is available\n*To throw the sword, use the Q and P keys.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25NC3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mcatlantis/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7EC2T","slug":"two-cat-cute","title":"Two Cat Cute","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of two sweet cats? The cats need to return to their clubhouse. To get back to the clubhouse, you must overcome obstacles. Collect the cat paws; they are very cute. Be very careful. Jump with the sweet cats and reach the clubhouse.\n\n*Use the Arrow Keys to move the Black Cat.\n*Use the WASD to move the White Cat.\n*both mobile and desktop playability.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7EC2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/two-cat-cute/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0601","slug":"rescue-hero","title":"Rescue Hero","description":"The hero begins his journey for treasure and save princess, but the puzzles in front of the hunter trapped him. What you need to do is to pull the pins in the right order, so that the hero can take the hidden treasure and save princess away from dragon, wolf and monster safely.\n\n\nSolve puzzles and rescue hero collect all the treasures, kill monster and save princess. Pull the pin and destroy your enemies by pulling lava and poisonous gas into their puzzle units. Cut the ropes in order to rescue the princess from the scary monster.\n\n\nFEATURE:\n\n- Free to play, play it anywhere anytime\n\n- Suitable for all ages\n\n- Graphic, visual, music & sounds are outstanding\n\n- Use your brain to solve the puzzles\n\n- No time & live limited, enjoy yourself\n\n- Collect gold and build your own kingdom\n\n\nGet money and build your kingdom or buy more hero skin. Help the hero rescue the princess now.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0601/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0E117","slug":"home-pin-1","title":"Home Pin 1","description":"$35","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0E117/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/home-pin-1/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7955","slug":"hero-tower-wars","title":"Hero Tower Wars","description":"Many monsters and enemies in the tower. You need to defeat them, get treasures and save hostages.\n\nYou can play everywhere ,every time. It is a boring killer game.\n\n\nHOW TO PLAY:\n\n1 - Use your brain to move your hero\n\n2 - Kill all enemies\n\n3 - Increase your power\n\n4 - Defend your tower\n\n\nCollect all treasures and become the best hero in Hero Tower Wars.\n\nEnjoy your time.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7955/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hero-tower-wars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H3133","slug":"the-fair-hook","title":"The Fair Hook","description":"Game based on the hook of the fair where we can win different types of stuffed animals.\n\nWill you be able to get them all?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H3133/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-fair-hook/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44Y7M","slug":"geometry-maze-maps","title":"Geometry Maze Maps","description":"simple and challenging game, jump to pass all obstacles","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44Y7M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometry-maze-maps/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TLC1L","slug":"collect-like-items","title":"Collect Like Items","description":"Un jeu de casse-tête intéressant dans le genre des matchs-trois! Parcourez une variété de niveaux, organisez un entraînement pour développer vos capacités!\n\nRelevez le défi et devenez le meilleur dans ce jeu intellectuel passionnant!\n- 30 niveaux divers!\n- Thème du Nouvel An pour créer une bonne ambiance!\n- Compétitions avec d'autres joueurs basées sur le nombre total de points!\n\nPour collecter des objets, cliquez dessus avec la souris ou appuyez sur l'écran! Collectionnez 5 objets identiques pour créer un objet chargé qui prendra tous les objets autour de lui! Pour passer au niveau suivant, accomplissez tous les objectifs!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TLC1L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/collect-like-items/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0RS71","slug":"kiddie-farmers","title":"Kiddie Farmers","description":"Kiddie Farmer is an interactive game that takes players to a delightful world, where kids run their own farm-to-table market. Get ready to experience a vibrant and busy atmosphere as these charming young business owners create and sell a variety of products to their peers.\n\nIn this role, you will embody a young entrepreneur in charge of overseeing and expanding the operations of the mart. Your main goal is to support these aspiring young business owners in growing their enterprise, ensuring that the supermarket flourishes and becomes the preferred destination for all children in the community.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0RS71/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kiddie-farmers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B19CT","slug":"concrete-boots-2","title":"Concrete Boots 2","description":"Concrete Boots 2 is a mafia simulation game and the 2nd part of the series. Eliminate your enemy rival and build your criminal empire. ","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B19CT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/concrete-boots-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"419T5","slug":"txt","title":"TXT","description":"This game is a real test of your attractiveness and speed. You need to click on the numbers appearing on the screen as soon as possible. The faster you do it, the higher your record.\nThe whole game is made in the style of old TVs. There is eternal interference on the screen, and the rest of the menu is stylized under the old interfaces. All this is complemented by pleasant retro sounds and music.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/419T5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/txt/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EO21G","slug":"geom-etrys","title":"Geom-etrys","description":"Create combinations of 3 or more figures to score points and continue the game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EO21G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geom-etrys/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HISEE","slug":"treasure-fishing","title":"Treasure Fishing","description":"$36","category":"Aventure","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HISEE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/treasure-fishing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E302P","slug":"penalty-shooters-3","title":"Penalty Shooters 3","description":"\"Penalty Shooters 3\" continues the legacy of the popular series with a casual and enjoyable soccer experience. Featuring two modes - the progressive 'Tier Mode' and the national pride-filled 'World Cup Mode' - the game offers a variety of challenges.\n\nChoose from over 250 fictional teams, each with its unique characteristics. The 3D graphics enhance the gaming atmosphere, while the option to edit teams adds a personal touch.\n\nDesigned for solo play, the game provides an easy-to-understand interface suitable for both seasoned players and newcomers. Its mobile-friendly nature ensures accessibility across various devices.\n\nWith a focus on simplicity and enjoyment, \"Penalty Shooters 3\" lets you take charge of the penalty shootout in a relaxed gaming environment. No frills, just soccer fun at your own pace.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E302P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-shooters-3/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8HEP2","slug":"hero-pipe-rescue","title":"Hero Pipe Rescue","description":"$37","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8HEP2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hero-pipe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2669Y","slug":"lovie-chics-black-friday-shopping","title":"Lovie Chics Black Friday Shopping","description":"Indulge in the ultimate Lovie Chics Black Friday Shopping spree! BFF girls are excited to go out for shopping on Black Friday. Explore exclusive deals, trendy fashion finds, and must-have accessories. Elevate your style and make the most of this exciting shopping extravaganza. Join us for a day of style and savings!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2669Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lovie-chics-black-friday-shopping/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VL0A2","slug":"remove-balls","title":"Remove Balls","description":"Try to remove all balls.\nTouch them and they will disappear.\nGet higher score for the number.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VL0A2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/remove-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IA627","slug":"mike-and-mia-camping-day","title":"Mike and Mia Camping Day","description":"It's time to have fun with Mike and Mia camping day! You will face several interesting challenges and take part in lots of fun activities. Catch the bugs, find cute animals, and pretty flowers. Don't forget to setup the tent on the camping site and dress up Mike and Mia! Camping day with them can be such fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IA627/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mike-and-mia-camping-day/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CS526","slug":"max-mixed-cuisine","title":"Max Mixed Cuisine","description":"Max wants to become a master chef! Help him to make some good recipes by mixing ingredients in his kitchen. Pick some ingredients, mix them, and taste it. You will get a good ending if you successfully find the right recipe. Be careful and avoid bad ingredients if you don't want to get a shocking ending.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CS526/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/max-mixed-cuisine/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C6HE3","slug":"matchshapes","title":"MatchShapes","description":"A Special Match3 Game For Attracting New Audiences and Engaging Them!\nMatch Shapes is a New Attractive HTML5 Match3 Game . In this puzzle game, there are blocks in different shapes and you should merge three or more similar shapes. New shapes will open on each level by merging. In this HTML5 game, you will collect coins by passing each level.\n\nYou can use your coins for options in the game:\n\nUndo your last move\nUse bombs to destroy nearby blocks\nReroll to shuffle new blocks\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C6HE3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/matchshapes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23P32","slug":"parking-line","title":"Parking Line","description":"Test your driving skills by drawing the line to park the car properly at the designated location. There are different levels to play, each one presents a different parking spot and set up.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23P32/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parking-line/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OR5EW","slug":"super-watermelon","title":"Super Watermelon","description":"Welcome to Super Watermelon! In this relaxing and fun game, you will experience an addictive fruit merge adventure.\n\nWe offer four game modes!\n\nMode 1: The classic and popular \"Super Watermelon\" mode, where you can experience the joy of the classic game!\n\nMode 2: The challenging \"Jade Series\" with higher synthesis coefficients and strong Chinese style!\n\nMode 3: The fun \"Zuma Mode\" that challenges you with circular synthesis and requires a different way of thinking!\n\nMode 4: Reverse! For the tiny sesame, you need to use big fruits to synthesize in reverse, with endless possibilities!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OR5EW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-watermelon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4P9AV","slug":"save-my-pet","title":"Save My Pet","description":"Watch out! The cute dog is in danger.\n\nThe evil bees have come out to sting him. The only way you can save the dog is to draw a line to stop those bees.\n\nBees aren't the only thing that can hurt him. The dog must also overcome lava, water, spikes and bombs to get to safety. Help him please!  Website Developer <a href=\"https://www.gamesmunch.com/\">https://www.gamesmunch.com</a>\n\nHOW TO PLAY:\n- Touch and drag to draw a line.\n- Protect the dog is safe for 10 seconds.\n- The longer the line, the less stars you get.\n- Save the cute dog!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4P9AV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-my-pet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I73EH","slug":"mincraft-archer","title":"Mincraft Archer","description":"Get ready for a wild pixelated showdown in  a 2D faceoff that's pure chaos! No crafting, just fast-paced arrow-shooting action. Will you lead Steve to glory, or can the wily Skeleton outmaneuver you? \nBrace yourself for an indie game thrill, where every arrow counts and victory hangs in the balance. Get your game face on – the clash is on!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I73EH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minecraft-archer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7NC13","slug":"drifting-car","title":"Drifting Car","description":"racing car is a game where you drive a car and doge barrels chose the car and get ready to race.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7NC13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/macchina/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41013","slug":"greenbal","title":"GreenBal","description":"This game is a complex logical strategy game. Imagine that you are playing chess or checkers with an opponent who makes two moves in response to your one! It seems that such a game cannot be won - however, logical thinking will gradually take over. No matter how strong and fast the opponent is, a smart player will be able to outwit the enemy. You will be surprised when you begin to understand that there is a way out, even from the most difficult situation.\n\nThis game is not for everyone, but if \"a feast of intelligence\" is your element, then you will have great fun! If you manage to win once, don’t rush to rejoice, maybe it’s just an accident. Try to play again, will you be able to follow the same path and win again? It has been proven that if you act correctly, you will win no less than 99.9% of cases. This game is a truly difficult and severe test - but it develops the will and ability to solve even very difficult life situations. Challenge yourself!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41013/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/greenbal/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8U818","slug":"box-journey","title":"Box Journey","description":"Simple Platform game. Use arrow key or touch to control player.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8U818/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/box-journey/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"117X0","slug":"arena-box","title":"Arena Box","description":"Are you up for a competitive match with your friend? Swords are drawn, lets start attacking. Buy the best sword and defeat your enemy. Run to the box and collect it. If you stay by the box for 20 seconds, it will open, and you win. Stand by the box for 20 seconds and claim victory.\n\n *Use the WASD keys to move the red player. Use the S key to attack with the sword. *Use the Arrow Keys to move the blue player. Use the Down Arrow key to attack with the sword.Wait by the box for 20 seconds and win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/117X0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arena-box/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"49A49","slug":"flag-war","title":"Flag War","description":"Are you ready to fight with your friend? Fight with your friend and reach victory. The best player from the blue team and the red team wins. Swords are drawn; its time to kill each other. Kill your enemy and reach the flag. Capture the flag and win the victory. The one that stands by the flag the most wins. Drop the flag and win.\n\n *Use the WASD keys to move the red player. Use the S key to attack with the sword. *Use the Arrow Keys to move the blue player. Use the Down Arrow key to attack with the sword. *Wait in the flag area for 20 seconds and win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/49A49/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flag-war/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CT2C6","slug":"crash-test-auto-3d","title":"Crash Test Auto 3D","description":"Realistic crash test with excellent 3D graphics. Excellent physics of car destruction will not let you get bored!\nDestroy cars by any means: collisions with obstacles at high speed, jumping from huge jumps, hitting huge hammers, passing through the press, etc. In heavy collisions, the car will have different parts flying off: from headlights and tyres to bonnet and doors!\nLots of descents and jumps, long roads, similar to roller coasters, where you will need to show all your driving skills! Come up with new ways to destroy the car, bring the car to the fire engine. You can drift, bypass dangerous obstacles, develop great speed and of course destroy the car!\nFeel the full freedom of action, playing \"Crash Test Auto 3D\"!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CT2C6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-car-crash-test/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NOP6A","slug":"pongball","title":"Pongball","description":"Control your paddle to score epic goals against your opponent. Fast, fun, and highly addictive, this soccer-inspired game based on the classic Pong formula. Can you outmaneuver your rival and become the GoalMaster? Kick off the excitement now!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NOP6A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pongball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NIDIL","slug":"the-best-russian-billiards","title":"The Best Russian Billiards","description":"Are you ready to play The Best Russian Billiards? This realistic billiards featuring stunning 3D graphics is for players of all levels. Worthy rivals are waiting for you! Get in the game and let them know who you are!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NIDIL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-best-russian-billiards/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0EN68","slug":"pet-pics-meowconnect","title":"Pet&Pics Meowconnect","description":"🧩 Solve Slide Puzzles picking adorable handcrafted cat images from your media gallery on MeowConnect, the favorite social media to solve puzzles of cute cats! Relax, slide the pieces and unlock more cats to reveal!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0EN68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/petandpics-meowconnect/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19K11","slug":"3sudoku","title":"3Sudoku","description":"Welcome to sudoku game, you have three difficulty levels. good fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19K11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3sudoku/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7UL07","slug":"goblinup","title":"GoblinUp","description":"Welcome to the goblinUp game, you have to click to the right and left of the character to make a small or large jump, have fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7UL07/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goblinup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8161","slug":"theblocks","title":"TheBlocks","description":"Move the blocks left and right so that they fit together well and make the lines and dots","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8161/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/theblocks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0099Y","slug":"crazybird","title":"CrazyBird","description":"Let the bird fly, collecting the apples to set your record, but be careful of the owl and the other obstacles you will find","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0099Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazybird/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LBL7S","slug":"ballsdestroy","title":"BallSdestroy","description":"you have a certain amount of time to destroy the marbles in series,,, at each level the time available to you decreases,, go and make your record","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LBL7S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballsdestroy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"37SS4","slug":"superxtrue","title":"SuperXtrue","description":"Welcome to the SuperXtrue game, leaderboard game, you have 60 seconds, let's see if you can climb the leaderboard","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/37SS4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superxtrue/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14010","slug":"sxtrue2024","title":"Sxtrue2024","description":"Welcome to Sxtrue2024, have fun with this fantastic game where you will have to overcome the two difficulty levels and show everyone who is the strongest, what are you waiting for??? Go and play Sxtrue2024 now and the fun will be guaranteed!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14010/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sxtrue2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R1SM6","slug":"satyr-memory-match","title":"Satyr Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Satyr Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Satyr Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Satyr Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R1SM6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/satyr-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GTIAE","slug":"superkitties-jigsaw-image-challenge","title":"SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge","description":"Welcome to SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge! Our SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge picture. With a wide variety of SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our SuperKitties Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GTIAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superkitties-jigsaw-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3I8WR","slug":"rocket-jigsaw-picture-puzzle","title":"Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle! Our Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Rocket Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3I8WR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-jigsaw-picture-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"II123","slug":"wizard-memory-match","title":"Wizard Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Wizard Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Wizard Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Wizard Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/II123/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wizard-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LE1GC","slug":"eiffel-tower-jigsaw-block-puzzle","title":"Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle! Our Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Eiffel Tower Jigsaw Block Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LE1GC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eiffel-tower-jigsaw-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DR2DM","slug":"pumpkinhead-tile-image-scramble","title":"Pumpkinhead Tile Image Scramble","description":"Welcome to Pumpkinhead Tile Image Scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide ti