ctive of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Queen Isabella I Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96989/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/queen-isabella-i-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4N4EW","slug":"cavegirl-down","title":"Cavegirl Down","description":"cavegirl down is an html5 arcade game, run and down get meat for score, watch out for your head getting hit by dangerous obstacles","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4N4EW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cavegirl-down/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AI1S1","slug":"galactic-chaos","title":"Galactic Chaos","description":"Galactic Chaos is a spaceship shooting game, shoot and destroy as many enemies as possible, get the items that appear and get the highest score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AI1S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galactic-chaos/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UN44M","slug":"milky-run","title":"Milky Run","description":"Milky Run is an HTML5 endless run game, run to avoid obstacles and monsters, get fruit for scores and be the best player","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UN44M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/milky-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P39PG","slug":"piggy-jump","title":"Piggy Jump","description":"piggy jump is an endless html5 jumping game, jump and get eggs to earn score, avoid enemies and obstacles and get thunder items for speed","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P39PG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/piggy-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0UU7E","slug":"mr-explorer-run","title":"Mr Explorer Run","description":"mr explorer is an html5 arcade game, run and get as many coins as possible and avoid obstacles or kill enemies with jumps\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0UU7E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-explorer-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10EP2","slug":"superbot","title":"Superbot","description":"superbot is a html5 adventure game, explore action packed levels get gems and some items to get score, defeat the monsters by shooting","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10EP2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superbot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I38KI","slug":"falling-rock","title":"Falling Rock","description":"falling rock is an html5 arcade game, jump and avoid falling rocks and get as many scores as possible\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I38KI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-rock/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"70M8J","slug":"pinkman-jump","title":"Pinkman Jump","description":"pinkman jump is an html5 endless jump game, jump and get the fruits to earn score, don't get hit by obstacle or you'll die","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/70M8J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pinkman-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4R61T","slug":"kitty-run","title":"Kitty Run","description":"kitty run is an endless running HTML5 game, run fast and avoid obstacles, destroy enemies by throwing boxes and get as much score as possible","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4R61T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kitty-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3CPT5","slug":"spaceship-destruction","title":"Spaceship Destruction","description":"spaceship destruction is a arcade shooter html5 game, attack enemy planets and destroy all obstacles and enemies, get points at each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3CPT5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaceship-destruction/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZAM92","slug":"zombie-grassland","title":"Zombie Grassland","description":"zombie grassland is an html5 topdown shooter game, zombie attack shoot and kill the zombie by gun and riffle and get best score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZAM92/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-grassland/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ER374","slug":"sky-heroes-z","title":"Sky Heroes Z","description":"sky heroes z is a html5 arcade shooter game, fighter planes have risen to destroy the attacking enemy, get as many scores as possible to become the winner","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ER374/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-heroes-z/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"979O8","slug":"raccoon-retail","title":"Raccoon Retail","description":"Oopsy! Clumsy ​customers are making a big mess and it's your job to keep the supermarket clean. Drive around, collect trash and empty it in the dumpster. The faster you clean to more money you earn. Upgrade your retail store to increase your revenue. \n\nKeep your store clean!\n\n\nDrive around with WASD or arrow keys.\nSwitch view by clicking the camera icon in the top.\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/979O8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/raccoon-retail/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I7I4N","slug":"fishing-dancing","title":"Fishing Dancing","description":"Plongez dans la pêche dans le style des années 80 ! Plongez-vous dans une autre époque en lançant votre canne à pêche et en dansant sur Retrowave. Découvrez la combinaison parfaite de nostalgie et d’excitation dans cette combinaison unique de pêche et de musique. Prenez le poisson ! Obtenez le rythme!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I7I4N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fishing-dancing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ULFTY","slug":"my-new-year-s-sparkling-outfits","title":"My New Year's Sparkling Outfits","description":"Welcome to My New Year’s Sparkling Outfits. BFF girls plan for a new year surprise party. They are so excited to try new fashion trends for this new year. Help the girls to pick a cute sparkling outfit and pick cute matching accessories for each girl. Don’t forget to choose a unique hairstyle.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ULFTY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-new-year-s-sparkling-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HRATC","slug":"mr-and-mrs-santa-christmas-adventure","title":"Mr And Mrs Santa Christmas Adventure","description":"Welcome to Mr. and Mrs. Santa Christmas Adventure.  Christmas is around the corner. Mr. and Mrs. Santa preparing for the celebration. Unfortunately, Mr. Santa met an accident. Santa and his pet got severe injuries and also his sleigh was damaged totally. Help Santa and his pet for a quick recovery so that he can tour around the world to share his Christmas gift with the children. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HRATC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-and-mrs-santa-christmas-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1A4A4","slug":"dark-war","title":"Dark War","description":"Welcome to the world of adrenaline, magic and the fight against evil! an exciting role-playing game with a view from above, the action of which takes place in modern reality. In this game, you will be embodied in the role of a brave exorcist of an ancient order who devoted his life to fighting the forces of evil.\n\nGame Features: 🔥 Diverse Weapons: Your fighting skills include not only swords, but also firearms. You also have magical abilities.\n\nYour task is to clear the city and return it to civilians.Explore huge locations.\n\n👹 Destroy the main bosses: epic battles with powerful demonic bosses are waiting for you. Develop a strategy and use your unique abilities to defeat evil.\n\nMulti-faceted gameplay: Switch between weapons, magic and sword to overcome various challenges and adapt to the situation.\n\n🏆 Character Leveling: Upgrade your hero's skills and ammunition to become a true master of exorcism.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1A4A4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dark-war/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4SB3A","slug":"tank-blast","title":"Tank Blast","description":"Destroy enemies with your tank, take money from enemies to update your tank,and beat your score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4SB3A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tank-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RLB9R","slug":"breakers-football","title":"Breakers Football","description":"The Breakers are an American football team that you can play online. They're a great team to play with if you're looking for a challenge, and they have a lot of dedicated fans.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RLB9R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/breakers-football/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1CSHA","slug":"city-cash-race","title":"City Cash Race","description":"The ultimate and fun arcade chase game! Race through vibrant cityscapes, grab cash, evade police, and upgrade your car. Become the City Cash King!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1CSHA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-cash-race/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7616H","slug":"is-it-right","title":"Is it right?","description":"This puzzle game will challenge your wits and attentiveness - do it right!\nLook for pumping logic, look for the right colors, go through levels, open skins!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7616H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/is-it-right/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71101","slug":"santa-drop","title":"Santa Drop","description":"Help Santa to escape from dark forest prison!\nSanta Drop is a 60 levels of fun physics puzzle game! all boxes except the grass must be removed where the prison is standing.\nSimply click or tap on the boxes or blocks to destroy them; carefully use the set blocks in what ever way you can to get the Santa Drop safely into the grass.\nSolve this fun physics game and help Santa to escape from prison!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71101/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SU01E","slug":"bubble-classic","title":"Bubble Classic","description":"The goal of the game is not to lose as early as possible and to score as many points as possible. Improve your accuracy thanks to very competent rolling of balls. The more blocks with balls you destroy, the more points you accumulate. Check your results in the world rankings, maybe you are already number 1.\n\nAdvantages of the game:\n- endless level;\n- global rating;\n- increasing accuracy, accuracy;\n- relaxation after a hard day;\n- you can play at work by minimizing or opening the game tab at the right time.\n- attention, the game is very addictive!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SU01E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ICP5","slug":"world-cricket-champ","title":"World Cricket Champ","description":"Embark on an exciting journey to the pinnacle of cricket glory in the Cricket World Cup Game! Lead your nations team to victory through intense matches, strategize your tactics, and experience the thrill of the chase as you compete against formidable opponents from around the globe. The Cricket World Cup Game captures the essence of the Cricket World Cup, providing an exhilarating cricket simulation that will test your skills, challenge your strategic thinking, and allow you to experience the thrill of leading your nation to glory on the international stage.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ICP5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cricket-world-cup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0H1AO","slug":"mahjong-at-home-xmas-edition","title":"Mahjong At Home - Xmas Edition","description":"Experience the holiday spirit with 'Mahjong at Home: Christmas Edition'! Dive into this high-quality Mahjong game featuring festive themes and cozy, winter-inspired designs.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0H1AO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-at-home-xmas-edition/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3RN3","slug":"king-endless-runner","title":"King Endless Runner","description":"n the endless world of King of Oil, you are the ruler of a vast oil-rich kingdom. Your mission is to extract as much oil as possible while keeping your kingdom stable and prosperous.\n\nAs you drill for oil, you will need to manage your resources carefully. Build refineries to process the oil, construct pipelines to transport it, and establish trade routes to sell it around the world. Use the profits from your oil sales to upgrade your kingdom, build new infrastructure, and hire skilled workers.\n\nBut beware of the dangers that lurk beneath the surface. Rival kingdoms, environmental disasters, and economic downturns can all threaten your reign. Use your strategic skills and resourcefulness to overcome these challenges and become the ultimate oil tycoon.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3RN3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-endless-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TA744","slug":"gold-aztec","title":"Gold Aztec","description":"In the game \"Aztec Gold\" you have to pick up the \"keys\" to the doors behind which there are countless treasures.\n Rules of the game:\nOn the playing field is a stone door, consisting of 16 blocks. On blocks are located colored crystals and rings. Number of crystals of each color is always equal to the number of rings of the same color. You must place the crystals so that they coincide with the color of the color ring.\n To move the crystals click the screen in the center portion of the four blocks. In this case, four crystals located on these blocks will immediately move clockwise to the next position. Keep doing this as long as all the 16 colored crystals will be in the rings with the same color. Think carefully about each move. Try to open the door in the minimum number of moves, this determines how many treasures you will find. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TA744/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gold-aztec/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7P1LD","slug":"spider-ball","title":"Spider Ball","description":"Swing and shoot your way to victory in this fast-paced 2D Spiderball game!\n\nTake control of a fearless arachnid adventurer and navigate through treacherous obstacles, avoiding enemies and collecting valuable gems. Utilize your sticky webs to grapple across the environment and launch powerful projectiles at your foes. Outsmart your opponents and become the ultimate Spiderball champion!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7P1LD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5OT0R","slug":"geometry-monster","title":"Geometry Monster","description":"Geometry monster you can collect as many you can geomtry","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5OT0R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometry-monster/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10N74","slug":"nail-salon-sim","title":"Nail Salon Sim","description":"This is a game in which you have to decorate the nails and hand of a girl","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10N74/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nail-salon-sim/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10P14","slug":"dress-up-boys","title":"Dress Up Boys","description":"“Dress Up Boys” is the boys dress up game version of the other game “Dress Up Girls”, made for boys and girls to play, dress up your character in the most beautiful way possible.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10P14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dress-up-boys/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"609BB","slug":"rabbit-run-3d","title":"Rabbit Run 3D","description":"Rabbit Run Endless 3D is a fast-paced, arcade-style endless runner game. The game is set in a vibrant, colorful world and features a cute rabbit as the main character. The player must help the rabbit avoid obstacles and collect carrots as they run through the game world. The game is easy to pick up and play but can be challenging to master.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/609BB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rabbit-run-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z178E","slug":"jigsaw-casual-puzzle","title":"Jigsaw Casual Puzzle","description":"$38","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z178E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jigsaw-casual-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"868F7","slug":"tile-my-floor","title":"Tile My Floor","description":"Join our adorable chicken on a Shikaku puzzle adventure! From easy to challenging levels, this delightful puzzle game will both engage your mind and soothe your senses. It's the perfect balance – relaxing, yet demanding enough to kill time and give your brain a light workout.\n\nHow to Play?\nYour goal is to tile the floor. Each number must be located within a rectangle or square that spans exactly that many tiles. For instance, a \"4\" indicates the cell should be within a rectangle or square covering four tiles in total. Dive in and let the puzzles begin!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/868F7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tile-my-floor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0O6R8","slug":"frog-escape","title":"Frog Escape","description":"Frog Escape is a block puzzle game in a \"escape room\" style, where you have to move the specific blocks in order to help the frog to escape the room. Each block has a specific action, you activate it by clicking/touching it.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0O6R8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1A25","slug":"hit-animals","title":"Hit Animals","description":"the game consists of catching as many animals as possible, without getting confused with the good animals.\nThe more animals you capture, the more points you will have. Don't let the animals you capture escape otherwise you will lose points","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1A25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hit-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8SSH0","slug":"fish-cach","title":"Fish Cach","description":"the game consists of catching as many animals as possible, without getting confused with the bad animals.\nThe more animals you capture, the more points you will have. Don't let the animals you capture escape otherwise you will lose points","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8SSH0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fish-cach/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5LE59","slug":"apostle-s-creed-i","title":"Apostle's Creed I","description":"Apostle's Creed 1 is a Christian game. The game has ten levels that our apostle character needs to finish. Inspired by an apostle of Christ but instead of sharing or learning the Holy Scriptures, the apostle in this game need to collect the scriptures or scrolls.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5LE59/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/apostle-s-creed-i/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1I80I","slug":"pumpkin-pursuit","title":"Pumpkin Pursuit","description":"As twilight blankets the Halloween landscape, you venture into a haunted minefield to collect pumpkins. Unbeknownst to you, a mysterious and restless entity lurks, awaiting the opportune moment to make its presence felt. Your choices will shape the outcome of this surreal Halloween adventure, where secrets hide in the shadows.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1I80I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-pursuit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2SI92","slug":"snile-game","title":"Snile Game","description":"Snail Game is an arcade game where you have to jump over obstacles and get the highest score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2SI92/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snile-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N3L6E","slug":"arsenal-online","title":"Arsenal Online","description":"Arsenal Online is a high-octane 2D shooter. Jump into some quick and explosive shoot-em-up action!\n\nSOLO AND CO-OP GAME MODES\nPlay one of many fun game modes either solo or with a friend online! Each game mode has a different objective, such as Sniper where accuracy is rewarded, or Time Attack where maximum kills is the goal.\n\nHUNDREDS OF WEAPONS AND ATTACHMENTS\nUnlock hundreds of weapons and attachments, ranging from pistols, SMGs, assault rifles, LMGs, sniper rifles, and more!\n\nFIRING RANGE\nJust want to equip a weapon and shoot targets? Enter the firing range where all weapons and attachments are immediately accessible.","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N3L6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arsenal-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"89M4I","slug":"climbing-pomni","title":"Climbing Pomni","description":"An exciting game is waiting for you, where you have to jump on a rock, boldly clinging to handles, collecting coins and deftly avoiding various obstacles. In this exciting adventure game, your skill and dexterity will be put to serious tests. Climb mountains, collect treasures and reach new peaks!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/89M4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/climbing-pomni/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"997IA","slug":"banban-saves-friends","title":"Banban Saves Friends","description":"Team up with friends, avoid or fight enemies on the level and make your way to the exit.\n\nThe exit is blocked by a door, the key to which is on the level, find it and open this door as soon as possible!\n\nBut don't forget that you won't be able to leave the level until you save all your friends!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/997IA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banban-saves-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ARTLG","slug":"amazing-digital-circus-puzzles","title":"Amazing Digital Circus Puzzles","description":"$39","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ARTLG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amazing-digital-circus-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z7P2Y","slug":"huggy-puzzle-wuggy-playtime","title":"Huggy Puzzle Wuggy Playtime","description":"$3a","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z7P2Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/huggy-puzzle-wuggy-playtime/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3O286","slug":"double-up","title":"Double Up","description":"Double Up is a relaxing 2048 merge game. Take a rest, get yourself a coffee, and enjoy the game. You have all day to think about your moves. No rush! Double Up the number to up and beyond.\n\nFeature\n\nOn a train? in a bus? in a taxi? On a ship? Play and quit anytime, and the game will save your progress even while you're on the move. Don't do it while driving, though it's dangerous.\n\nNo rushing, take your time to think your next move.\n\nIt's a long haul to reach the infinity, can you reach the summit?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3O286/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/double-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6IAS8","slug":"monster-truck-jigsaw-frenzy","title":"Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy","description":"Welcome to Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy! Our Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy picture. With a wide variety of Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Monster Truck Jigsaw Frenzy Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6IAS8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-truck-jigsaw-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"98696","slug":"pong-game","title":"Pong Game","description":"pong gameis a minigame when you have to get the ball as much as possible to increase the score","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/98696/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pong-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AM686","slug":"space-game","title":"Space Game","description":"Space Game is a game where you have to shoot enemy spaceships, dodge their bullets and don't let the spaceships pass otherwise they will damage you and take 1 life from you","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AM686/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"37137","slug":"gravity-ninja","title":"Gravity Ninja","description":"In “Gravity Ninja”, you take on the role of an incredibly skilled ninja, on an exciting journey full of challenges and unbridled action. In this game, gravity is not an obstacle, but rather a tool in your character’s nimble hands.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/37137/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gravity-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U37R0","slug":"bubble-shooter-space","title":"Bubble Shooter Space","description":"Bubble Shooter Space is an exciting intergalactic adventure in game form. In this captivating challenge, your mission is to shoot groups of three or more balls of the same color to score as many points as possible. Get ready to embark on a cosmic journey filled with colorful bubbles, clever strategies and endless fun! The more you match the balls, the more points you will earn. So, adjust your aim and shoot accurately to achieve the highest score possible.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U37R0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-shooter-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"077ND","slug":"ninja-sword-adventure","title":"Ninja Sword Adventure","description":"Ninja Sword Adventure Embark on an epic journey filled with action, secrecy and mystery with “Ninja Sword Adventure”! This exciting turn-based game puts you in the role of a skilled ninja on a mission that will decide the fate of a land in danger.\n\nGet ready for an unforgettable ninja adventure where your choices shape destiny and your sword is your best friend. “Ninja Sword Adventure” is the turn-based game that will make you feel like a true master of the shadows as you face unimaginable dangers and discover deep secrets in pursuit of ninja glory. Accept the challenge and become the legend that all ninjas aspire to be!","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/077ND/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-sword-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P7PO1","slug":"only-parkour-skill-up","title":"Only Parkour Skill up","description":"There are many different activities in the world, but for those who want to test themselves, the parkour club has opened. Your goal is to climb only to the top to reach the finals of the course. Who will reach the elevator the fastest, will be the first in the leaderboard. Also on the location scattered collectibles and you can prove yourself in their search. Find them all will be quite difficult, but if you believe in yourself - you can do it!  Running around the map you will not be alone, because the online system allows you to see the ghosts of other players, which allows you to jump around the map with friends.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P7PO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/only-parkour-skill-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TSBOO","slug":"scooter-brothers","title":"Scooter Brothers","description":"Start the scooters and escape with your friend. Dont let the police catch you. Flee together on the scooter. Be careful while riding the scooter. Riding a scooter is difficult. There are police everywhere. Pay attention to the police; they want to catch you. Evade the police and get gas for the scooter.\n\n*Collect all the badges, activate the Black Hole. \n*Playable on both desktop and mobile. \n*Jump by pressing the W key and the Arrow up key.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TSBOO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scooter-brothers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TT77","slug":"black-and-white-stickman","title":"Black and White Stickman","description":"Would you like to join the adventure of the black and white stickmen? Help them in this adventure and guide them to the portal. The black and white stickmen need to collect all the star points and monster balls to reach the portal. Remember to collect not only the stars but also the monster balls. Be cautious of obstacles; if you collide with them, youll lose and fail. Stay alert to avoid losing.\n\n*Collect all the Stars, activate the Black Hole. \n*Playable on both desktop and mobile. \n*Jump by pressing the W key and the Arrow up key.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TT77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-and-white-stickman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EA8N","slug":"santa-and-the-chaser","title":"Santa And The Chaser","description":"Hey Santa needs Your help to escape from the Chaser! Avoid all obstacles and try to resit the more you can! try to complete all 20 Levels to go back in to the North Pole! Enjoy this Christmas season with this great arcade game!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EA8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-and-the-chaser/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R11CK","slug":"strike-galaxy-attack","title":"Strike Galaxy Attack","description":"Strike Galaxy Attack: Shoot 'Em Up war Chicken Shooter is the best chicken gun shooting online games PVP - The best arcade game on all global and promising to create a major earthquake on Google Play. You can play it on all smartphone and tablet. In immense space, there are always dust settle brutal forces with plots to invade Earth: May be air force aliens or animals that is as intelligent as human: venom stickman, black defenders, gravity stellaris, zero gunny bima, fury reavers, shootero genome, wolf hunter, ben cricket, max steel, flying jatt 10, battleclaw robot wala, beyblade oyunlari… They can attack our beautiful earth anytime!\nStrike Galaxy Attack: Alien Space Chicken Shooter free fire game bring you a epic war against chicken invader squadron. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R11CK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/strike-galaxy-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"09PI9","slug":"daily-puzzle","title":"Daily Puzzle","description":"Daily Puzzle is a great choice for those who like to spend time putting together puzzles. Check back every day so you don't miss a single new puzzle. Earn stars and unlock a collection of unique pictures. Several difficulty levels will help you both learn how to solve puzzles and really hone this skill. Each piece in the game is unique!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/09PI9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/daily-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15741","slug":"hero-rescue","title":"Hero Rescue","description":"Join the Hero Rescue to help the hero get treasures in the best pin rescue game. You have a task is pull the pin puzzle, and then kill monsters, rescue the princess and collect treasure\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15741/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hero-rescue/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LN53Y","slug":"penalty-rivals","title":"Penalty Rivals","description":"Step into the virtual stadium and face off against rivals in a high-stakes penalty shootout league where your shooting and goalkeeping skills are put to the ultimate test.  Can you climb your way to the top of the table and claim glory?","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LN53Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penalty-rivals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IN2GN","slug":"endless-siege","title":"Endless Siege","description":"A new map everyday! Play everyday for a brand new challenge as you try to top wave after wave of invaders trying to destroy your kingdom. Place your defenses along the path, then purchase upgrades to help you survive. The longer you survive the higher your end score will be. Check back every day to play the map of the day.\n\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IN2GN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/endless-siege/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9B0EB","slug":"baby-the-great","title":"Baby the Great","description":"Baby the great is a fun and exciting hack and slash game featuring a warrior baby.\n\nGame Features:\n\n     Fun action  sword fighting \n\n    Easy to pick up and play\n\n    For fans of hack and slash / Beat em up games\n\n    Suitable for both female and male players\n\n    Beautiful environment and scenery","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9B0EB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-the-great/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"676RK","slug":"darts-king","title":"Darts King","description":"Affrontez vos adversaires dans un jeu d'adresse et de précision. Progressez dans les ligues et prouvez encore et encore que vous êtes le meilleur joueur de fléchettes. Améliorez vos fléchettes et créez votre propre jeu de fléchettes.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/676RK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/darts-king/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IA5RI","slug":"triangle-trip","title":"Triangle Trip","description":"This is a fun recreation of the game Flappy bird.\nThis is my first game so please show kind support.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IA5RI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/triangle-trip-flappybird/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NH616","slug":"santa-math-game","title":"Santa Math Game","description":"Youre good at maths?\nwell then try to answer all the questions about the tiles where an image of Santa is hidden underneath!\nHow to play:\ndrag all the left numbered blocks on to the corresponding right tiles covering the picture.\nHave fun and try to unlock all Santa pictures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NH616/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-math-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EL74O","slug":"football-superstars-2024","title":"Football Superstars 2024","description":"Lancez votre carrière de footballeur et accédez à la célébrité. Testez vos compétences dans un match amical ou dirigez votre équipe de rêve dans le tournoi mondial contre des équipes internationales. Personne ne s'est jamais noyé dans la sueur !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EL74O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-superstars-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N0O2","slug":"santa-soosiz","title":"Santa Soosiz","description":"In this game you control Santa moving them around a world that revolves around you!   \n     \nAs you move around the landscape your character clings o the ground via gravity – use it your advantage to move from one platform to the next. to collect all missing Gifts to save the Christmas!    \n     \nThis is a fun Christmas theme exploring adventure games enjoy it!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N0O2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-soosiz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N0NNN","slug":"hungry-plant","title":"Hungry Plant","description":"In Hungry Plant you are a flying monster that wants to eat the magical seeds that grows inside a dangerous plant. But the plant is hungry too, and wants your fresh blood. Try to catch as many seeds as you can without getting bitten by the carnivorous plant!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N0NNN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hungry-plant/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2A1V1","slug":"ellie-thanksgiving-day","title":"Ellie Thanksgiving Day","description":"Welcome to Ellie Thanksgiving Day. It’s Thanksgiving Day, and like every year, young Ellie is in charge of the Thanksgiving dinner. Her friends will start arriving soon, and there are still a few things that need her attention. Will you help her with the last preparations? Join and help beautiful Ellie to surprise her guests with a perfect dinner!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2A1V1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ellie-thanksgiving-day/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7EN7S","slug":"frozen-sisters-dream-wedding","title":"Frozen Sisters Dream Wedding","description":"Welcome to the Frozen Sisters Dream Wedding. Princesses are more excited about their dream day with their beloved ones. Yes, It’s their wedding. Help them to get ready for this occasion. And make this occasion a more memorable one in her life! Browse their wardrobe and pick suitable outfits and costumes. Help them to decorate the cake and invitation card. Join them and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7EN7S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frozen-sisters-dream-wedding/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20OBL","slug":"bffs-black-friday-collection","title":"BFFs Black Friday Collection","description":"Welcome to BFFs Black Friday Collection. Bffs already filled the closet with a new Black Friday outfit. Help them to pick the perfect costume. Don’t forget to pick a fabulous hairstyle. They are all excited like us for this day. Join and help the girls with your skill. Play and have fun! ","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20OBL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-black-friday-collection/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I70S0","slug":"thanksgiving-squad-style","title":"Thanksgiving Squad Style","description":"Step into the world of Thanksgiving Squad Style! Explore a fusion of cozy elegance and festive fashion as the squad celebrates the season. From warm layers to stylish accents, discover the perfect ensemble to make this Thanksgiving unforgettable. Join the squad and embrace the spirit of gratitude and style! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I70S0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/thanksgiving-squad-style/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LZZ00","slug":"cute-cat-jigsaw-puzzle","title":"Cute Cat Jigsaw Puzzle","description":"Are you a cat lover with a passion for puzzles? If so, get ready for an adorable and engaging adventure with “Cute Cat Jigsaw Puzzle.” This delightful game features 15 levels of feline-themed fun that will captivate your heart and challenge your mind.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LZZ00/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-cat-jigsaw-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0P0T2","slug":"stone-pile","title":"Stone Pile","description":"stone pile is an html5 arcade game, stack the stones according to color otherwise the stones will be destroyed and you will die, stack them to the top and get the highest score","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0P0T2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stone-pile/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O1E69","slug":"toms-adventure","title":"Toms Adventure","description":"Les extraterrestres ont envahi la terre et ont kidnappé la sœur de Tom ! Aidez Tom à sauver sa petite sœur à travers 21 niveaux difficiles dans ce superbe jeu de plateforme !","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O1E69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/toms-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TF9BL","slug":"swift-ball","title":"Swift Ball","description":"The goal of the game is to control the ball so as to collect all the bonuses, avoid hitting any mines and central traps and meet the allotted time.\n\nGreen ball \"Bonus\" + 1 point.\nThe central cone +10 points.\nThe ball \"Mine\" - 3 points.\n\nFor a new level, the points are multiplied by 2, the collected points are also credited to the bonus account if the player has met the allotted time, collected all the bonuses and there is at least one mine left on the field.\n\nThe second mode is endless, when time is unlimited, the number of balls is constantly updated and the score is saved every 30 seconds - more complex, but also more exciting.\n\nThe game menu is at the top left above the clock in game mode..\nCamera Change button - changes the view of the arena\nThe transition to the next level occurs automatically when the conditions of the game are met.\n\nIn the Settings menu, you can select a previously purchased skin, change the difficulty level and change the game mode.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TF9BL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swift-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L9G0M","slug":"demon-village","title":"Demon Village","description":"demon village is an html5 adventure game, the village has been attacked by demons explore the village and destroy them","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L9G0M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/demon-village/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0N07R","slug":"train-battle","title":"Train Battle","description":"Place Tracks. Outrun your opponent. Make their train explode\n\nA deceptively simple strategy game. Think a turn-based version of the light bikes from Tron, a game of “go” with train tracks, or the love child of chess and centipede.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0N07R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/train-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7926S","slug":"squid-shapes","title":"Squid Shapes","description":"In this game you must switch between the three possible shapes (circle, triangle, square) that are contained in the lower circle.\n\nOther shapes will descend through the center of the screen and as they meet the lower figure they must match!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7926S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-shapes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C2DA5","slug":"space-words","title":"Space Words","description":"There is a meteor shower containing letters. You should see the image at the top and write the word correctly.\nDestroy only the meteors with the letters of the correct word – and in their correct order!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C2DA5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-words/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2I909","slug":"pictures-swap","title":"Pictures Swap","description":"Welcome to the captivating world of \"Pictures Swap, the ultimate puzzle challenge! The pictures are initially complete, but they get jumbled up, with pieces from one puzzle intermingling with others. Your task is to unscramble the chaos and restore the images to their original perfection.\nWith each successfully completed puzzle, you earn coins that can be used to unlock even more intriguing images, providing endless hours of brain-teasing fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2I909/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pictures-swap/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"661R2","slug":"guessmaster-bingo","title":"Guessmaster Bingo","description":"Embarquez pour un voyage exaltant de prédiction et de chance avec « Guessmaster Bingo » ! Plongez-vous dans l'excitation du bingo traditionnel avec une touche passionnante. Au fur et à mesure que les chiffres défilent, défiez votre intuition en devinant si le prochain sera supérieur ou inférieur.\n\nÊtes-vous prêt à maîtriser l'art de la prédiction et à embrasser l'imprévisibilité de « Guessmaster Bingo » ? Tentez votre chance, faites vos devinettes et laissez les sensations fortes du bingo se dérouler!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/661R2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guessmaster-bingo/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4RIFR","slug":"train-drift","title":"Train Drift","description":"Train Drifting is an addictive arcade racing game that offers players a unique and incredible train drifting experience. In this game you will become a real master of drifting on iron horses.\n- Extreme Train Drifting: Feel the adrenaline rush by driving huge trains and performing incredible drifts on various tracks.\n- Incredible clashes with other trains!\n- Variety of trains: The game features different types of trains, each with its own characteristics. Choose your ideal composition for maximum control and speed.\n- Exciting locations: Explore a variety of tracks\n- High Quality Graphics: Immerse yourself in the amazing world of train drifting with stunning graphics and impressive special effects.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4RIFR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/train-drift/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CA181","slug":"collect-balloons","title":"Collect Balloons","description":"Are you ready to fight with your friend? But this time, speed wins rather than weapons. Collect the balloons as quickly as possible to defeat your friend. Gather all the balloons and bring them to the balloon machine. The one who collects 20 balloons in the shortest time wins. Be on the red or blue team and gather all the balloons. Jump and catch them, then bring them to the machine.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. The blue player moves using the arrow keys. Collect the balloon and bring it to the balloon machine.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CA181/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/collect-balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BN04S","slug":"santa-blast","title":"Santa Blast","description":"Hey Santa needs your help to escape from this dark world!\nThe main goal is to land Santaclaus in the safe area with the least number of attempts!\nYou just use the explosive to move Santa in the right direction but be aware at the dangerous spikes!\nAre you able to get the three stars for each level?","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BN04S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R02F7","slug":"friends-pug","title":"Friends Pug","description":"Collect all the food with your dog friend and return to your nest. Both friends need to collect their respective foods, overcome obstacles, and reach the nest together. Reach the nest with your friend. Catch the bone to gain special powers and have a superpower.\n\n*Use the Arrow Keys to move the Brown Dog.\n*Use the WASD to move the Grey Dog.\n*both mobile and desktop playability.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R02F7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/friends-pug/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NN310","slug":"santa-wheel","title":"Santa Wheel","description":"Santa Wheel is a funny game where you must control a big rolling Santaclaus through 30 levels!\nWhit its original and colorful graphics Santa Wheel will be a pleasant time-killer, simple but addicting.\nSo accelerate, break and have a perfect control of your Santa in order to complete all levels!\n\nThe main goal is to help Santa to complete each levels and to escape from Monster Land and go back to North Pole to save the Christmas!\n\nEnjoy this game in this magic Christmas season!\ntips: follow the stars!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NN310/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-wheel/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"27ERO","slug":"merge-grabber-race-to-2048","title":"Merge Grabber Race to 2048","description":"Merge Grabber: Race to 2048 is a level runner, in which you must destroy the columns to pick up characters and thus enhance the power of your group. On the way there are various obstacles, gates with improvements, destructible cubes and much more. To win, you have to reach the finish line with as many high-level characters as possible and destroy the zombies who want to attack you!\n\nBut be careful, keeping characters on the way will not be easy: they can fall off the track,bump into the column or other obstacles, that you will encounter in your way.\n\nThe game has upgrades like firing rate and damage that will help you on your way, good luck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/27ERO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-grabber-race-to-2048/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4L809","slug":"slime","title":"Slime","description":"Oh no you fell off the cliff when you were looking out in the sky and need to climb back up to get home!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4L809/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slime/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66S9O","slug":"donuts-of-hanoi","title":"Donuts of Hanoi","description":"The Donuts of Hanoi is a mathematical game or puzzle (based on Tower of Hanoi) consisting of three rods and a number of donuts of various diameters, which can slide onto any rod. The puzzle begins with the donuts stacked on one rod in order of decreasing size, the smallest at the top, thus approximating a conical shape. The objective of the puzzle is to move the entire stack of donuts to one of the other rods, obeying the following rules:\n\nOnly one donut may be moved at a time.\nEach move consists of taking the upper donut from one of the stacks and placing it on top of another stack or on an empty rod.\nNo donut may be placed on top of a donut that is smaller than it.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66S9O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/donuts-of-hanoi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P3US3","slug":"beat-the-plush","title":"Beat the Plush","description":"Bienvenue dans le monde fascinant de « Beat the Plush » - un jeu de clic passionnant ! Dans ce jeu unique, vous devez combattre Skbidi en utilisant le pouvoir de votre main. Esquivez ses attaques et frappez-le en lui infligeant un maximum de dégâts. Améliorez les dégâts de vos armes pour devenir plus efficace dans les batailles. Achetez de nouvelles armes pour élargir votre arsenal et augmenter vos chances de gagner. N'oubliez pas d'augmenter également vos revenus pour atteindre de nouveaux sommets plus rapidement.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P3US3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beat-the-plush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MU6V6","slug":"adventures-thomas-draw-and-erase","title":"Adventures Thomas Draw and Erase","description":"Bienvenue dans le monde passionnant de « Thomas's Adventures : Draw and Erase » — un jeu passionnant qui vous proposera des aventures et des défis incroyables ! Dans ce jeu passionnant, vous devez aider Thomas à trouver toutes les étoiles et à les relier entre elles ! Dessiner une route : tracez un chemin pour Thomas afin qu'il puisse éviter habilement les obstacles sur son chemin. Effacez les obstacles : effacez tout ce qui vous gêne pour accéder à l'une des 38 étoiles.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MU6V6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventures-thomas-draw-and-erase/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R6D2D","slug":"wheel-draw-master","title":"Wheel Draw Master","description":"🏞️ Niveaux uniques : explorez une variété de niveaux captivants et uniques.\n\n🌟 Physique réaliste : découvrez la physique du vélo fidèle à la réalité pour une sensation de conduite authentique.\n\n💥 Améliorez votre vélo : utilisez des power-ups pour turbocharger votre vélo et vaincre les obstacles !\n\n🚴‍♂️ Choisissez votre cavalier : visitez la boutique de skins et débloquez tous les cavaliers !\n\n🎁 Récompenses quotidiennes : jouez tous les jours pour réclamer des récompenses passionnantes !\n\n🏆 Grimpez dans le classement : affrontez des joueurs du monde entier et visez la première place du classement !","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R6D2D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wheel-draw-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L6P5E","slug":"toilet-paper-please","title":"Toilet Paper Please","description":"In Toilet Paper Please! You are a Toilet Paper Roll that has to collect all the toilet paper pieces scattered around the level, before the time runs out! But you won't battle only against the time, but you will have to avoid vicious poo bouncing around the levels along with dangerous obstacles. Beat 45 levels and 3 bosses in this challenging and fun game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L6P5E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/toilet-paper-please/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T3999","slug":"traffic-light-clicker","title":"Traffic Light Clicker","description":"Murphy wants to cross the road, but he always waits that the traffic light turn green! Help him to cross the road! How, are you asking? just push the traffic light  button 1 milion times! it's so easy!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T3999/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/traffic-light-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0IK8R","slug":"skibidi-strike","title":"Skibidi Strike","description":"Skibidi Strike is a shooting game where you play as special forces soldier and your mission is to shoot given amount of skibidi toilets in order to survive and unlock big arsenal of guns awarded after completing each level with increasing difficulty.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0IK8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13CRO","slug":"rocket-stars","title":"Rocket Stars","description":"$3b","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13CRO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9OCIM","slug":"police-ladies-anime-clicker","title":"Police Ladies - Anime Clicker","description":"Jouez à un jeu de clicker animé attrayant mettant en vedette des beautés époustouflantes ! Utilisez la monnaie du jeu pour débloquer et collecter de nouveaux personnages. Votre objectif ultime est d’ouvrir les 20.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9OCIM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/police-ladies-anime-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UY9CG","slug":"tough-guys-anime-clicker","title":"Tough Guys - Anime Clicker","description":"Jouez à un jeu de clicker animé attrayant mettant en vedette des personnages époustouflants ! Utilisez la monnaie du jeu pour débloquer et collecter de nouveaux personnages. Essayez d’ouvrir les 20 comme objectif ultime.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UY9CG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tough-guys-anime-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"II871","slug":"alien-high","title":"Alien High","description":"Go with the Alien, dodge lasers, and climb as high as you can.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/II871/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-high/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T691P","slug":"sweet-raspberry","title":"Sweet Raspberry","description":"$3c","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T691P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-raspberry/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MT10H","slug":"fairy-match","title":"Fairy Match","description":"Welcome to the magical world of Fairy Match!\n\nJoin Ulyasha the snail on her magical journey through the world of Match Three!\nUlyasha is the most common snail that lives in the vastness of the magical forest. One day, she discovers a mysterious portal that takes her to the wonderful world of Match Three. In this world, the snail must overcome many levels filled with magical puzzles and exciting tasks.\n\nSee you in the game!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MT10H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I91I4","slug":"duo-robot-skibidi","title":"Duo Robot Skibidi","description":"The robot toilet men are trying to escape. Work together with your friend to overcome all obstacles and reach the door. Progress in sequence and teamwork. First one, then the other should advance. Strive to reach the door with your friend. Be careful, some floors can disappear, and make sure not to die. There are sharp rotating saws everywhere.\n\n*Player1, use Arrow keys to move.\n*Player2, use WASD to move.\n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I91I4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-robot-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N3G3N","slug":"mien-bugr-skate","title":"Mien Bugr Skate","description":"Would you like to join the adventurous journey of two cute friends on their skateboards? They need to get home right away. Both friends pink and brown pets have escaped into the streets, so find them and safely return home. Dont forget to collect all the gold coins along the way. Be cautious, as monsters are lurking everywhere, and they might try to devour you.\n\n\n*Collect all the badges, activate the Black Hole. \n*Playable on both desktop and mobile. \n*Jump by pressing the W key and the Arrow up key.","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N3G3N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mien-bugr-skate/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2EX16","slug":"extreme-volleyball","title":"Extreme Volleyball","description":"The game Extreme Volleyball is a variation on the subject of volleyball. \nIn this game, players will be robots. And unlike \"normal volleyball\" instead of the ball will be a bomb. A bomb is known to have a tendency to explode ... \n The purpose of game to blow up a bomb on the territory of the opponent.\nThe bomb blows up, if it concerns a floor, there were more than three contacts of a bomb or time of burning of a fuse ended.\nIn the game settings menu you can select the number of bombs,  bomb fuse burning time, game difficulty level and location of your robot. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2EX16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/extreme-volleyball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"115N4","slug":"inferno-drift","title":"Inferno Drift","description":"Race for survival in this high-stakes racing game, where you'll need to outlast opponents on a unique course that changes every time you play.  Navigate the twists and turns to avoid being shoved into the lava by rival racers. It's a battle for survival – can you stay ahead and come out on top?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/115N4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/inferno-drift/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EUKRU","slug":"pink-rush-speedrun-platformer","title":"Pink Rush Speedrun Platformer","description":"Get ready for the ultimate platformer experience with this action-packed game that combines the thrill of speedrunning with the challenge of conquering 60 different levels. Each level presents its own unique obstacles and traps, making every moment a heart-pounding adventure.\n\nTap into your speedrunning skills and embark on this 2D offline game that guarantees hours of endless fun. Your mission is to conquer all 60 levels, maneuvering through deadly traps while setting the fastest times possible.\n\nWith \"Pink Rush Speedrun Platformer,\" you'll race against the clock, climbing to the top of the leaderboards. Are you up for the challenge?\n\nSo, whether you're an experienced speedrunner or looking to start your platforming journey, \"Pink Rush Speedrun Platformer\" offers the classic speedrun experience you crave. Download the game now and immerse yourself in this breathtaking adventure. Get ready to become the ultimate speedrunning champion!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EUKRU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pink-rush-speedrun-platformer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LBZ18","slug":"crazy-balls","title":"Crazy Balls","description":"A game for those who love to drive along crazy tracks, knocking down everything in their path! Roll, jump, fly, overtaking the balls and be the first to reach the finish line! Climb the rankings and become a racing king!\nRace crazy balls on bizarre tracks. Swipe quickly to gain more speed, flying over gaps and avoiding obstacles to reach the finish line first!\nSwipe quickly to gain more speed, flying over gaps and avoiding obstacles to reach the finish line first","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LBZ18/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LU9DD","slug":"dino-fusion-bubble-evolution","title":"Dino Fusion Bubble Evolution","description":"\"Dino Fusion: Prehistoric Bubbles\" is a captivating arcade game that challenges your matching and strategic skills. In this game, you release dinosaurs within colorful bubbles, and your objective is to match two bubbles with identical dinosaurs to create new and exciting prehistoric creatures. As you combine dinosaurs, your collection evolves, and you unlock new thrilling prehistoric species.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LU9DD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dino-fusion-bubble-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21ED6","slug":"jump-red-square","title":"Jump Red Square","description":"Vous n'avez qu'à tirer ! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21ED6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-red-square/embed?sid=1","plays":39493,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R6RRR","slug":"super-speed-runner","title":"Super Speed Runner","description":"Il vous suffit de courir et de sauter ! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R6RRR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-speed-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40166,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YI7AY","slug":"jewel-christmas-story","title":"Jewel Christmas Story","description":"Les vacances les plus attendues de l'année sont arrivées ! Noël arrive à grands pas et de nombreuses réjouissances pleines de cadeaux et de sucreries vous attendent dans ce nouveau jeu de match 3. Collectez la monnaie du jeu, réalisez des combos et utilisez des boosters dans diverses missions.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YI7AY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-christmas-story/embed?sid=1","plays":39922,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NRN0R","slug":"stickyman-run","title":"Stickyman Run","description":"Sautez et retournez ! Testez votre vitesse de réaction. Vous pouvez être le plus rapide ?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NRN0R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickyman-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40215,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EJUE4","slug":"juice-bottle-fast-jumps","title":"Juice Bottle - Fast Jumps","description":"Vous devez simplement sauter! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EJUE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/juice-bottle-fast-jumps/embed?sid=1","plays":40082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5V996","slug":"cars-movement","title":"Cars Movement","description":"Vous n'avez qu'à tirer ! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5V996/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cars-movement/embed?sid=1","plays":39327,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"706IC","slug":"circle-flip","title":"Circle Flip","description":"Retournez! Retournez! Retournez!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/706IC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circle-flip/embed?sid=1","plays":40005,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31119","slug":"tap-10-sec","title":"Tap 10 Sec","description":"How Many Touches You Can Do In 10 Seconds?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31119/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-10-sec/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEA81","slug":"fallen-apples","title":"Fallen Apples","description":"A simple game where you have to take the falling apples before they touched the ground,there are also golden apples that increase the number of \"Fallen\" and you can buy power ups with them.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEA81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fallen-apples/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N7ON0","slug":"lunch-shop","title":"Lunch Shop","description":"It’s time to make a snack, customers are eager to try new and delicious Lunch Shop dishes, prepare the recipe and serve them.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N7ON0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lunch-shop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"591UF","slug":"fall-guy","title":"Fall Guy","description":"Guide the characters' descent avoiding the spikes, be careful as the speed will increase over time.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/591UF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fall-guy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E219T","slug":"let-s-fly","title":"Let's Fly!","description":"Welcome to \"Let’s Fly!\". In this game your goal is to jump higher than everyone and earn as many points as possible to climb all the leaderboards! Jump to the platforms paying attention to the various enemies and helping you with the power-ups you will find in your climb. Collect coins and unlock many different maps and skins from the store! Have fun in \"Let’s Fly!\" and good luck.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E219T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/let-s-fly/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EI9FE","slug":"line-of-battle","title":"Line of Battle","description":"Line of Battle is a fast-paced war game, battle game, and tank war game. \nA tough and breathtaking battle on the zero-point borderline...\nDefend your land against waves of enemy attacks.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EI9FE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-of-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19A37","slug":"bow-master-challenge","title":"Bow Master Challenge","description":"$3d","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19A37/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bow-master-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13CTL","slug":"squirrel-tic-tac-toe","title":"Squirrel Tic Tac Toe","description":"A tic-tac-toe where you can use special item","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13CTL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squirrel-tic-tac-toe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7957","slug":"zxtrue","title":"Zxtrue","description":"Welcome to the Zxtrue game, in the forest only take the red apples, try to be fast to beat your record, have fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7957/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zxtrue/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D5D54","slug":"birdy-bird-2","title":"Birdy Bird 2","description":"Welcome to Birdy Bird 2, have fun in the second chapter of the game where this time you won't have to go through the pipes but collect the coins and watches for a long time to survive, what are you waiting for?? go and play now and the fun will be guaranteed","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D5D54/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/birdy-bird-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8921I","slug":"missilexx","title":"MissileXx","description":"Velcom to MissileXx game, try to take the protective barrier, to score more points","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8921I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/missilexx/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8774H","slug":"archerx","title":"ArcherX","description":"hit the target with the arrows to beat your record again, watch out for obstacles","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8774H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archerx/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D4GT1","slug":"right-and-left-2","title":"Right and Left 2","description":"Welcome to right and left, have fun in this fantastic game where you can climb over platforms and accumulate platforms, what are you waiting for?? Go play right and left and the fun will be guaranteed!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D4GT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/right-and-left2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3OT00","slug":"rotante","title":"Rotante","description":"Welcome to Rotante, have fun in this fantastic game where you can rotate around the world accumulating best scores, what are you waiting for?? go and play rotary now and the fun will be guaranteed!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3OT00/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotante/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"29C22","slug":"tap-the-color","title":"Tap the Color","description":"select the color that matches the background that appears and disappears","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/29C22/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-the-color/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AM1AL","slug":"small-jump","title":"Small Jump","description":"Welcome to the small jump game, easy game to play but you have to be quick to jump and avoid zombies and enemies","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AM1AL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smalljump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ALE33","slug":"london-snapshot-tile-mania","title":"London Snapshot Tile Mania","description":"Welcome to London Snapshot Tile Mania, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn London Snapshot Tile Mania, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to London Snapshot Tile Mania and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ALE33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/london-snapshot-tile-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M6AAX","slug":"phoenix-memory-match","title":"Phoenix Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Phoenix Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Phoenix Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Phoenix Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M6AAX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/phoenix-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IUPM7","slug":"makeup-jig-it-up","title":"Makeup Jig it Up!","description":"Welcome to Makeup Jig it Up!! Our Makeup Jig it Up! Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Makeup Jig it Up! picture. With a wide variety of Makeup Jig it Up! images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Makeup Jig it Up! Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IUPM7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/makeup-jig-it-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1MV5K","slug":"king-louis-xiv-memory-match","title":"King Louis XIV Memory Match","description":"Bienvenue dans King Louis XIV Memory Match, un jeu de puzzle classique où les joueurs doivent faire glisser des tuiles pour réassembler une image. Déplacez les blocs en les touchant ou en cliquant dessus pour résoudre le puzzle.\n\nDans King Louis XIV Memory Match, les joueurs sont mis au défi de résoudre le puzzle en faisant glisser des tuiles pour réassembler une image. L'objectif du jeu est de déplacer les blocs en les touchant ou en cliquant dessus jusqu'à ce que l'image soit complète. Bienvenue dans King Louis XIV Memory Match et amusez-vous à résoudre le puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1MV5K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-louis-xiv-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EGI59","slug":"hamburger-jigsaw-rush","title":"Hamburger Jigsaw Rush","description":"Welcome to Hamburger Jigsaw Rush! Our Hamburger Jigsaw Rush Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Hamburger Jigsaw Rush picture. With a wide variety of Hamburger Jigsaw Rush images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Hamburger Jigsaw Rush Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EGI59/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hamburger-jigsaw-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G2AY8","slug":"rat-jigsaw-joyride","title":"Rat Jigsaw Joyride","description":"Welcome to Rat Jigsaw Joyride! Our Rat Jigsaw Joyride Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Rat Jigsaw Joyride picture. With a wide variety of Rat Jigsaw Joyride images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Rat Jigsaw Joyride Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G2AY8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rat-jigsaw-joyride/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ST22","slug":"impossible-tracks-2d","title":"Impossible Tracks 2D","description":"\"Impossible Tracks 2D\" is an exciting 2D game where you'll encounter a series of tricky levels. Each level is packed with challenging obstacles that will test your skills and reflexes. Navigate these treacherous tracks and conquer the obstacles to reach the finish line. Get ready for an adventure filled with fun and excitement in this thrilling game!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ST22/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/impossible-tracks-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O9E99","slug":"little-woodpecker","title":"Little Woodpecker","description":"Help the parents provide food for the little woodpecker and help it grow bigger and bigger. \nBe careful if the % reaches 0 the little woodpecker dies.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O9E99/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-woodpecker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1U363","slug":"redball-adventure","title":"RedBall Adventure","description":"Get ready for an exciting ride in RedBall Adventure! Roll your ball through the levels. Collect coins and face tricky challenges along the way. With lots of levels to beat and a never-ending mode, have a blast rolling and bouncing to win!","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1U363/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redball-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65S61","slug":"the-soundless-space","title":"The Soundless Space","description":"Hi!\nI wanted to try and make a game that anybody could play, also blind people.\nI think that play has no limits so why don't make a game like this?\nI hope you enjoy my idea and have fun playing in The Soundless Space!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65S61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-soundless-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5O1F5","slug":"football-kickoff","title":"Football Kickoff","description":"Step onto the gridiron and embrace the challenge of one of the most demanding roles in American football. Put your precision to the test as you aim to send the football soaring between the goalposts. Factor in the wind direction, choose the perfect angle, and apply the right amount of power to secure your spot at the pinnacle of the leaderboard. Lead your team to triumph with each successful kick!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5O1F5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-kickoff/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PKP19","slug":"templok","title":"Templok","description":"Plunge into the depths in this Tetris-inspired puzzle adventure. Tasked with arranging sets of three pieces, strategically place them on the board. Complete lines vanish, scoring points. Aim for multi-line clears for a high-score surge.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PKP19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/templok/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E15T","slug":"tennis-open-2024","title":"Tennis Open 2024","description":"Les plus grands tournois de tennis du monde ne seraient rien sans les meilleurs joueurs. Alors prenez votre raquette et montrez à tout le monde ce que vous savez faire !\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E15T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tennis-open-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58045","slug":"snowboard-king-2024","title":"Snowboard King 2024","description":"Êtes-vous prêt à relever un défi ? Dévalez les pentes enneigées. Évitez les arbres et les rochers et dérapez sur la neige glacée. Explorez chaque pente et trouvez le chemin le plus court pour descendre. Pourrez-vous aussi échapper à l'avalanche ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58045/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowboard-king-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A3GN","slug":"santa-fright-night","title":"Santa Fright Night","description":"Help Santa Claus to collect all missing Gifts!\nUse the physic to move and rotate Santa!\nEnjoy this great Christmas puzzle Game!\nControls:\nUP/W Key= Make a Jump\nLeft/A Key= Rotate Left\nRight/D Key= Rotate Right","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A3GN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-fright-night/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"XP6PX","slug":"super-jump-box","title":"Super Jump Box","description":"Nouveau défi addictif ! Appuyez simplement sur les boutons colorés qui sauteraient sur la couleur que vous voulez, collectez des points et affrontez des amis ! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/XP6PX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-jump-box/embed?sid=1","plays":40089,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"932PL","slug":"jump-ball-arcade","title":"Jump Ball Arcade","description":"Jump on the platform, accelerate down, don't touch on spikes!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/932PL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-ball-arcade/embed?sid=1","plays":39626,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1170O","slug":"pocket-jump","title":"Pocket Jump","description":"Pocket Jump est un excellent jeu d'arcade. Vous devez sauter le plus haut possible pour obtenir le meilleur résultat !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1170O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocket-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40116,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5H905","slug":"shot-pong","title":"Shot Pong","description":"Défi Pong !!! Vous pouvez faire le meilleur score mondial?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5H905/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shot-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":39792,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91JE3","slug":"jump-box-hero","title":"Jump Box Hero","description":"Jump Box Hero – c'est un excellent jeu d'arcade avec de très beaux graphismes. Sauter Sauter Sauter!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91JE3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-box-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40074,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T301","slug":"santa-runner","title":"Santa Runner","description":"Il vous suffit de courir et de sauter ! Affrontez des joueurs du monde entier !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T301/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39998,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O2S9D","slug":"retro-speed-2","title":"Retro Speed 2","description":"Retro Speed 2 - is an endless arcade racing. Drive your car on the road with a fast traffic. Collect coins and buy new cars. Your task is to become the fastest driver - a leader in the global race for the first place world ranking. Go for victory!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O2S9D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-speed-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40009,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EU753","slug":"rescuers","title":"Rescuers","description":"Become a real hero! Save people from burning houses!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EU753/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescuers/embed?sid=1","plays":39692,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61011","slug":"rotare","title":"Rotare","description":"Tap the screen to change the direction of the hero. Be careful when cornering. Score more points!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61011/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotare/embed?sid=1","plays":39843,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3TW9","slug":"fast-arrow","title":"Fast Arrow","description":"Press to release the arrow. Be careful, shoot at point-blank range!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3TW9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fast-arrow/embed?sid=1","plays":39721,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58605","slug":"don-t-drop-the-white-ball","title":"Don't Drop the White Ball","description":"Move the platform to catch falling balls. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58605/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-drop-the-white-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39957,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1AIIB","slug":"don-t-drop-the-white-ball-2","title":"Don't Drop the White Ball 2","description":"Don't Drop The White Ball 2 is a game for all ages. Enjoy this new arcade game where in you have to simply save the falling balls from dropping. Navigate the stick from left to right and stop the balls from dropping.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1AIIB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-drop-the-white-ball-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39933,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0SA11","slug":"saws","title":"Saws","description":"Jump on the platform, accelerate down, don't touch on Saws!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0SA11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/saws/embed?sid=1","plays":40135,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31317","slug":"lemonade","title":"Lemonade","description":"If there’s one thing I’m really terribly fussy about, it’s freshly squeezed juice. It’s not just ensuring that not a single drop is lost, I also have to make sure I squeeze everything possible out of each pitiful piece of fruit! Lemonade understands this. To the sounds of nostalgic carnival music, juice gets squeezed to your heart’s content from oranges, lemons or melons right up to the brim into ever smaller glasses. And woe betide you should anything be lost. A juicy amount of accuracy is in demand!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31317/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lemonade/embed?sid=1","plays":39748,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GLLL4","slug":"flying-triangle","title":"Flying Triangle","description":"Fly between obstacles constantly accelerating! Score the highest score and become a leader!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GLLL4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-triangle/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P86N2","slug":"mr-pong","title":"Mr Pong","description":"Mr. Pong is a funny mustachioed hero who has to constantly jump and push off the platforms. Be careful - don't touch the thorns!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P86N2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":39535,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6F902","slug":"flip-cube","title":"Flip Cube","description":"Click to jump to the opposite side of the path. Be careful not to touch the spikes","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6F902/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flip-cube/embed?sid=1","plays":39611,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"336HS","slug":"choose-gravity","title":"Choose Gravity","description":"Tap the screen to change gravity. Enjoy the new fast arcade! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/336HS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/choose-gravity/embed?sid=1","plays":39787,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01040","slug":"dots-pong","title":"Dots Pong","description":"Tap the screen to switch colored dots! Catch only the appropriate colors! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01040/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dots-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":39729,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D0X3O","slug":"destroy-boxes","title":"Destroy Boxes","description":"Shoot on the moving blocks, destroy everything! Don't miss a single one! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D0X3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/destroy-boxes/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MA914","slug":"racing-game-challenge","title":"Racing Game Challenge","description":"Become the best driver! Challenge a friend!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MA914/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/racing-game-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40148,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1M6E3","slug":"impossible-rise","title":"Impossible Rise","description":"Impossible Rise! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1M6E3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/impossible-rise/embed?sid=1","plays":39476,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T9O61","slug":"put-bacon","title":"Put Bacon","description":"Put Bacon! Put your record in this addictive arcade!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T9O61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/put-bacon/embed?sid=1","plays":39568,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0EIOI","slug":"zombie-coming-roguelike-siege","title":"Zombie coming - roguelike siege","description":"Zombie coming: roguelike siege is a game where you need to defend against hordes of zombies by using all your skills, mines, barriers, and turrets.\n\nUse mines and other stuff to stop zombies who are coming. Placing mines and barriers on the field to build the line of defense. Only they are helping you to defend yourself. It would be best if you used tactics to make mines more effective at killing zombies.\n\nEvery surviving day you will get the reward. Choose wisely. Listen! They are coming!\n\nUse unique hero skills. They are helping to defend. Hero can call for an excavator which crashes into the crowd of zombies and pulls them like splinters in different directions or can throw a bunch of small bombs on the field.\n\nDefeat all types of zombies. They are small and big, fast and slow, flaming and icy. Try to survive in this mess.\n\nTry all the tactics you can imagine. Build the line of defense in your own style.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0EIOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-coming-roguelike-siege/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TLIIR","slug":"skibidi-toilet-creator","title":"Skibidi Toilet Creator","description":"Are you ready to create your own Skibidi Toilet? Choose a variety of accesories and weapons to customize your skibidi. Why not take a screenshot when you've finished?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TLIIR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toiley-creator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6TV5V","slug":"vulture-valley","title":"Vulture Valley","description":"Vulture Valley is a casual game where players control a vulture  navigating through obstacles. Similar to Flappy Bird, the gameplay involves tapping the screen to make the vulture flap its wings and stay afloat.With simple controls and addictive gameplay.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6TV5V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vulture-valley/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8TR8O","slug":"heart-box","title":"Heart Box","description":"Le professeur Rat adore les puzzles physiques et les jeux avec des robots ! Par conséquent, il a créé Robby, mais lui a donné une batterie faible, c'est pourquoi le petit robot doit constamment se recharger et participer à des expériences folles.\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu :\n\n- Plus de 180 niveaux pour votre cerveau !\n- Éditeur de niveau et collection de niveaux QR\n- Base de données en ligne \"Niveaux communautaires\"\n- Divers skins pour le robot !\n- 4 modes de jeu amusants\n- Physique réaliste\n- Beaucoup de dessins animés !\n- Classement et réalisations","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8TR8O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heart-box/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DK16K","slug":"spirited-skully","title":"Spirited Skully","description":"Spirited Skully is a casual game where players control a skull  navigating through obstacles. Similar to Flappy Bird, the gameplay involves tapping the screen to make the skull flaps and stay afloat. With simple controls and addictive gameplay.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DK16K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spirited-skully/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R89C8","slug":"fun-colors","title":"Fun Colors","description":"Fun Colors - jeu qui vous aidera, vous ou votre enfant, à réaliser leurs idées créatives !\nDans ce jeu gratuit, vous trouverez différentes catégories de pages à colorier et un mode dessin !\nEn plus d'une palette infinie de couleurs et d'une variété de pinceaux, Fun Colors a la possibilité de télécharger vos propres images et photos ! Et pour que vos yeux ne se lassent pas de rester longtemps devant l'écran, vous pouvez basculer l'interface en mode nuit !\nVous avez terminé votre prochain chef-d'œuvre ? - envoyez-le à imprimer sans quitter le jeu !\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu :\n- Téléchargez vos propres pages à colorier (NOUVEAU !)\n- Mode pour dessiner et colorier\n- Coloriages de différentes catégories\n- Téléchargez vos propres photos dans le jeu\n- Thème de la nuit\n- Sauvegarder la progression du jeu\n- Enregistrer des dessins sur votre appareil\n- Impression des dessins du jeu (PC)\n- Réglage de la taille et du type de pinceau\n- Zoom avant/arrière de la toile\n- Annuler la dernière action","category":"Action","tags":["junior","board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R89C8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fun-colors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1S6A1","slug":"pop-it-master","title":"Pop It Master","description":"Jouez gratuitement à Pop It Simulator et collectionnez toute la collection de 140 jouets Pop It et Simple Dimple ! Soulagez le stress après l'école avec ce jeu simple!\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu :\n- Jeu relaxant et anti-stress\n- Collection de Pop-it et simple-dimple de différentes formes et couleurs\n- Mode de jeu secret","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1S6A1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-it-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AN443","slug":"banana-duck","title":"Banana Duck","description":"Have you been in a situation where you are craving bananas, but the only things left in the fridge are tomatoes and carrots and you are also a duck that can't swim and dies when it touches the water?  If so, search no more, I've got the perfect game that realistically simulates your troubled situation. With Banana Duck, you will experience the sweet taste of pursuing bananas and avoiding all the evil vegetables and saw blades that are there for absolutely no reason. Enjoy!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AN443/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banana-duck/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4I118","slug":"ice-bricks","title":"Ice Bricks","description":"Avec Ice Bricks, vous devrez avoir des réflexes rapides et vous déplacer plus vite que la petite boule de neige.\nLes mécaniques de jeu sont les mêmes que celles du célèbre Pong mais le thème est entièrement basé sur la glace.\nEssayez de collecter autant de rebonds que possible et rappelez-vous que la difficulté augmentera de plus en plus !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4I118/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ice-bricks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"97T78","slug":"path-ice","title":"Path Ice","description":"Chill the soda, add some ice, but here's the problem, it's not so easy to get into the glass, you need to draw a path for the ice.\n\nDraw the path as you like.\nGo through many levels\nDiscover all kinds of ice and glasses","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/97T78/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/path-ice/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4FIS6","slug":"winter-gifts","title":"Winter Gifts","description":"Make children happy on Christmas by giving them gifts!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4FIS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/winter-gifts/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OE86N","slug":"cat-evolution-clicker","title":"Cat Evolution Clicker","description":"CAT EVOLUTION: CLICKER - a game with cats. Get ready for endless fun and start playing it right now!\nThe gameplay in CAT EVOLUTION: CLICKER gives you the opportunity to play endlessly.\nBecome a Cat God when you get 5 BILLION coins!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OE86N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-evolution-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"040I9","slug":"capybara-beaver-evolution-idle-cliker","title":"Capybara-Beaver Evolution - Idle Cliker","description":"Capybara-Beaver Evolution: Idle Cliker - a game with Capybara or Beaver? Get ready to have fun with a capybara or beaver, start playing it right now!\nThe gameplay in Capybara-Beaver Evolution: Idle Cliker gives you the opportunity to play endlessly.\nBecome a Capybara-Beaver  God when you get 200 millions coins!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/040I9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/capybara-beaver-evolution-idle-cliker-gamepix/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69NP6","slug":"pumpkin-fright-night","title":"Pumpkin Fright Night","description":"Help Mr. Jack Lantern to collect all missing pumpkins!\nUse the physic to move and rotate Mr. Jack!\nEnjoy this great Halloween puzzle Game!\nControls:\nUP/W Key= Make a Jump\nLeft/A Key= Rotate Left\nRight/D Key= Rotate Right","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69NP6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-fright-night/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3PA1M","slug":"match-3d-pro","title":"Match 3D pro","description":"I-Match 3D Master ingumdlalo oyinselele nowangempela wokufanisa! Ungathuki. Kulula kakhulu ukufunda indlela yokudlala yawo wonke umuntu!\n\nIngabe uyinhlakanhlaka? Ubona izinto ze-3D zinqwabelene phansi, ingabe ufuna ukuzikhulula? I-Match 3D Master ikunikeza amazinga ayinselele wokubhanqa futhi uqondanise lezi zinto!\nUkufanisa amapheya ukuze ushaye amazinga! Uzothola isikhathi sindiza uma umatasa nokulungisa isikrini sakho.\nUfuna ukuba yi-Match 3D Master? Thola izinto eziningi ezifakiwe, qoqa ama-booster amaningi futhi ushaye amazinga amaningi!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3PA1M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-3d-pro/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6454O","slug":"pixel-gold-clicker","title":"Pixel Gold Clicker","description":"Get gold and gems and buy all upgrades, eliminate the butterflies and get rich in this great game clicker","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6454O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-gold-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A736","slug":"arrow-shot","title":"Arrow Shot","description":"Shoot the arrow and destroy the circles without hitting the spikes and obtain the best score\n\nInstructions:\n-Tap for shot the arrow","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A736/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arrow-shot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R9A45","slug":"swap-color","title":"Swap Color","description":"Change color by turning the color wheel to the same color of the ball to get a new score until you reach the highest score but be careful if the ball is not the same color the game will end and you will have to start over.\n\nMobile controls:\nTap on the left side of the screen to turn left.\nTouch to the right of the screen to turn right.\n\nComputer controls:\nLeft rotation from A/Left Keyboard Keys\nRight rotation from D/Right Keyboard Keys","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R9A45/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swap-color/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TPCE","slug":"retro-gold-clicker-pocket","title":"Retro Gold Clicker Pocket","description":"Play in this game to get coins and gems, buy upgrades to be rich and destroy monsters for recover you money stealed in this incredible clicker game.\n\nFeatures:\n-2 purchase sections: coins and gems\n-Monster for steal your money\n-Retro pixelart","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TPCE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-gold-clicker-pocket/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36R71","slug":"fruit-merge","title":"Fruit Merge","description":"Identical fruits merge into a new, more valuable one. Each combination brings points, and several combinations in a row form a combo multiplier.\n\nFill the bar at the top of the screen with points to gain new levels and unlock new boosters and features.\n\nThe game will end when the field is filled to the top, so strategy and planning will be required to get the most out of the game. There is no time limit, score as many points as possible!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36R71/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6PERR","slug":"battle-farmer-2-player","title":"Battle Farmer - 2 Player","description":"Have you ever caught runaway chickens before? You must catch all the chickens. To catch the runaway chickens, you need to act fast. Farmers are competing. The red and blue farmers must win the race. Be any farmer and win the race. Play with your friend and collect the chickens as quickly and early as possible. You must catch all the runaway chickens. The one who collects 10 chickens the fastest wins.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6PERR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battle-farmer-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E16B2","slug":"agent-skibidi","title":"Agent Skibidi","description":"Hey, agents, load your weapons! All the toilet monsters have awakened and are coming to kill you. Eliminate all the monsters and collect the highest score. Remember, you can always reach a higher score. Monsters are coming from both the right and left. Work together with your friend to take them all down. Use different weapon modes to kill all the monsters.\n\nPress A-D keys to shoot. You will move in the direction youre firing. * Press the Arrow keys to shoot. * Mobile gameplay is available.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E16B2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/agent-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LLO46","slug":"jewel-block","title":"Jewel Block","description":"Step into a world where jewels aren't just treasures, they're the very essence of the game! Introducing \"Jewel Block\" – a captivating puzzle experience set on a 10x10 board, brimming with radiant gems waiting for the perfect fit.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LLO46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-block/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEF25","slug":"tower-defense-kingdom-2d","title":"Tower Defense Kingdom 2D","description":"Welcome to the exciting world of TD Kingdom 2D! This is a classic 2D tower defense game with retrompixeleded graphics and addictive gameplay.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEF25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-defense-kingdom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46STC","slug":"sell-tacos","title":"Sell Tacos","description":"Are you ready to be a taco seller? In this game, you will become a taco vendor. You'll need to craft your own taco recipe, purchase supplies, upgrade your food cart or food truck, and buy items to boost your sales.\n\nYou'll start with a limited balance, a basic food cart, and no items. Can you become a successful taco seller?\n\nTips:\nPurchase the \"Refrigerator\" item as soon as your balance is sufficient. The refrigerator can help your supplies last longer.\n\nInstructions:\nDefault recipe is not good enough, you need to adjust the recipe yourself.\n\nClick plus (+) button to increase the amount of ingredient\nClick minus (-) button to decrease the amount of ingredient\n\nThen set your own margin","category":"Course","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46STC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sell-tacos/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9YIPP","slug":"wavy-trip","title":"Wavy Trip","description":"Wavy Trip is a relaxing and addictive game.\n\nControl the little ship gliding through a beautiful exotic world.\n\nCollect coins and unlock cool spaceships.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9YIPP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wavy-trip/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ACC12","slug":"color-ball","title":"Color Ball","description":"color ball is game arcade","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ACC12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9693M","slug":"oh-my-goth","title":"Oh My Goth","description":"The Oh My Goth dress-up game shows that there are many ways to express your gothic style. Get inspired by this new trend that emerged from the collision of gothic and whimsical styles. It fuses codes from the 80s gothic style with surrealist evasions inspired by fairy tales and cinematic darkness. Gothic, grunge and gothfied fashion trends don't have to be restricted to the streets, that's why we are here to teach you all about their aesthetics and how to integrate them into your wardrobe. ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9693M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/oh-my-goth/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OCON2","slug":"noob-army-tycoon","title":"Noob Army Tycoon","description":"Welcome to Noob Army Tycoon!\nNoob Army Tycoon is a tycoon game inspired by the popular Roblox game, Noob Army Tycoon.\n\nBuy and Upgrade Workers\nBuy new Troops\nUnlock Pets\nAnd Much More!\n\nDeveloper: greenaliengeneral_pm","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OCON2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-army-tycoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EES66","slug":"robot-escape","title":"Robot Escape","description":"Help the robot escape, collect all coins and reach the end before the trap reaches you to win.For PC use the arrows to move","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EES66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9LI9E","slug":"pixel-asteroids-rage","title":"Pixel Asteroids Rage","description":"Jump into space with your spaceship and get money to buy more spaceships and avoid the dangers of entering in the space as asteroids and turrets that will do everything possible to destroy you.\n\nFeatures:\n\n-Space at random so it will never be the same\n\n-10 spaceships to buy and control\n\n- 2 dangers for avoid: turrets and asteroids\n\nControls mobile:\nTouch left screen for move left\nTouch right screen for move right\n\nControls desktop:\nA and Left Key move left\nD and Right Key move right","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9LI9E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-asteroids-rage/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"09ITT","slug":"delivery-by-tractor","title":"Delivery by Tractor","description":"You play as a tractor driver. Like \"Hill Climb\" only on a tractor and with a trailer.\nYour task is to collect the required number of fruits and deliver them to the customer. \n\nThe more products you deliver, the more coins you will receive, and you will receive bonus coins for completing the order.\nWith coins, you can upgrade your tractor, as well as purchase a new tractor or trailer.\n\nShow who is the best deliveryman on a tractor!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/09ITT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/delivery-by-tractor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y6BX9","slug":"gbox-memory","title":"GBox Memory","description":"A game of the \"memory\" genre with a variety of modes. Search for pairs of identical tiles. Perfectly develops attention, memory, observation. Suitable for all ages.\nGame types:\n+ Classic: Open the tiles on the board to find the same images, colors, or numbers.\n+ Search: You need to find only the second tile to the displayed image or number.\n+ Three of a kind: Find three identical tiles at once.\n\nThere is a field of tiles in front of you. Remember where they are. The player's task is to open two identical tiles in a row. A correctly opened pair is removed. If two tiles that are opened in a row are not the same, they will be turned over. The game ends when all the pairs have been found.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y6BX9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gbox-memory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1469","slug":"landland","title":"LandLand","description":"Avoid the spinning balls that kill you and get as many diamonds as you can","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1469/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/landland/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4V4B9","slug":"bewildered-lover","title":"Bewildered Lover","description":"The cute and confused emoji character is on the road to save his girlfriend. His lover is waiting locked in the cellar. He needs to collect enough hearts to save her. The more hearts he can collect, the happier his lover will be. Of course, he will do all this thanks to you.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4V4B9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bewildered-lover/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P5779","slug":"pac-vs-ghosts-2024","title":"Pac vs Ghosts 2024","description":" pac vs ghosts 2024 is game classic ","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P5779/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pac-man-2023/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8H91Y","slug":"rhythm-of-the-spheres","title":"Rhythm of the Spheres","description":"Rhythm of the Spheres is game arcade","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8H91Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rhythm-of-the-spheres/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P99O0","slug":"the-boy-escape","title":"The Boy Escape","description":"the boy escape is game arcade","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P99O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-boy-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12166","slug":"asteroix-2","title":"Asteroix 2","description":"ASTEROIX 2 IS GAME ARCADE","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12166/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asteroix-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA6GL","slug":"girls-on-the-beach-clicker-game","title":"Girls on the beach - clicker game","description":"Exciting virtual dates in high quality with a choice of actions. A game in which there are ordinary and fantasy girls with different emojis!\n\nWe had a virtual date in the park, in the city or on the beach. Seductive girls in bikinis, girls in dresses, octopus girls, sea queens and pirates. \n\nFeatures of the game:\n- Choose the available actions to seduce the girl more successfully and faster.\n- More than 25 unique outfits from dresses to swimwear!\n- More than 10 different cute chibis!\n- Collect a collection of beautiful anime girls.\n- Enjoy the incredible atmosphere and pleasant sounds.\n- Simple controls: you can play with one hand so that nothing distracts! Pump up an anime girl!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA6GL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/girls-on-the-beach-virtual-dating/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5NIEI","slug":"plane-shooting","title":"Plane Shooting","description":"Plane Shooting is a 2d  game, where user can easly shoot the enemy plane by using mouse or touch to navigate and have a fun,","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5NIEI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/plane-shooting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7N0X1","slug":"running-bros-x","title":"Running Bros X","description":"Running Bros X est un jeu de course sans fin passionnant et addictif qui met les joueurs au défi de naviguer à travers un monde sans fin rempli d'obstacles, d'ennemis et de défis, en collectant des pièces et des bonus en cours de route. Au fur et à mesure que les joueurs progressent dans le jeu, ils peuvent débloquer des améliorations et des bonus pour améliorer les capacités de leurs personnages et les aider à relever des défis encore plus difficiles. Avec des graphismes vibrants et colorés et un gameplay intuitif et facile à apprendre, Running Bros est le jeu parfait pour les joueurs de tous âges et de tous niveaux.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7N0X1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/running-bros-x/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83EV8","slug":"lost-delivery","title":"Lost Delivery","description":"Drive your white electric van on the motorway. Collect lost packages to increase your battery level. Don't drive too long over the lane separation lines. Watch out for other drivers, fog and other obstacles.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83EV8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lost-delivery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LEA2U","slug":"snowball-adventure","title":"SnowBall Adventure","description":"Get ready for an exciting ride in 'SnowBall Adventure'! Roll your snowball through snowy levels. Collect coins and face tricky challenges along the way. With lots of levels to beat and a never-ending mode, have a blast rolling and bouncing to win!","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LEA2U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowball-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N0GNI","slug":"chasinghunters","title":"ChasingHunters","description":"Defeat the bad guys and become a sharpshooter","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N0GNI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chasinghunters/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8EE2T","slug":"knife-shooting","title":"Knife Shooting","description":"Stress-relieving casual games","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8EE2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knife-shooting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5EC08","slug":"piano-music-tiles-deluxe","title":"Piano Music Tiles Deluxe","description":"The Top of free music games in the world!\nLoved by all players in the world, combining rhythm and music, a challenging free music mobile game!\nGame feature:\n1. Simple graphics, easy to play and everybody gets playing the piano!\n2. Breath-taking rhythm will challenge your handspeed limit!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5EC08/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/piano-music-tiles-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EWD87","slug":"correct-word","title":"Correct Word","description":"“Correct Word” is an educational game designed to help children learn words or exercise existing knowledge.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EWD87/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/correct-word/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8ES9","slug":"help-santa-claus","title":"Help Santa Claus","description":"Help Santa and his friends organize the presents coming out of the factory. Be careful not to put the gift in the wrong bag. Make as many points as possible, the more points, the more gifts will be delivered. Compete with your friends.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8ES9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/help-santa-claus/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D9TDO","slug":"roll-the-dice","title":"Roll The Dice","description":"“Roll The Dice” is an infinite click style game, where the player has to get the highest possible score. You can also complete the game after unlocking all the achievements.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D9TDO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roll-the-dice/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"28YU8","slug":"my-auto-service","title":"My Auto Service","description":"\"My Auto Service\" combines the best features of business management simulators, but adds its own unique twist - the world of car service.\nIn the game you need to repair, paint and wash cars and develop your car service! You can buy equipment to take on more clients, as well as hire employees to help speed up your work!","category":"Course","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/28YU8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-auto-service/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22EUE","slug":"merge-squares","title":"Merge Squares","description":"\"Merge Squares\" is an exciting puzzle game, where your task is to connect squares with same numbers. Using logic and strategic mind, you have to decide how to arrange the squares to combine them into one. Each level gets harder, how far can you go?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22EUE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-squares/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1NEW","slug":"makeup-studio-halloween","title":"Makeup Studio - Halloween","description":"Halloween is coming, and you girls deserve a treat! We have created this spookylicious game for all of you so that you can have a professional makeup artist helping you to create unique, sassy, and witchy loos. In the Makeup Studio - Halloween game, we bring you the spookiest Halloween looks inspired by three famous influencers. Just check them out! You can find some trendiest Halloween aesthetics in our makeup game from jaw-dropping villain-inspired makeup looks to Monster High ghouls.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1NEW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/makeup-studio-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"961IN","slug":"rainbow-squid-challenge","title":"Rainbow Squid Challenge","description":"Help! The rainbow friends are invading our world with the Blue Monster leading the charge. They are working together with the Alphabet Monster to take it all. The only hope left is the controller in your hand to defend yourself.\n\nWalk through each level to defeat these rainbow friends or convert them to your cause. Simply press the power button or change their state using the program button.\n\nHOW TO PLAY:\n- Aim your controller at the monster.\n- The laser will turn green when being pointed.\n- Press a button and see how they work.\n- Defeat the monsters or neutralize them.\n- You win when there is no threat left.\n\nNEW FEATURES.\n- Familiar controller scheme.\n- Fun characters design.\n- Featuring the rainbow friends.\n- Exciting gameplay.\n- Cool dynamic.\n- Unlimited game time.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/961IN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-friends-survivors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AW55D","slug":"duo-water-and-fire","title":"Duo Water and Fire","description":"Have you ever participated in the adventure of Stickman Fire and Water before? You need to collect the key and reach the door. As Fire and Water, you must overcome all obstacles. You are two opposite siblings, one with the power of fire and one with the power of water. Collect the red and blue keys. After collecting the keys, gather all the gold and reach the doors. Be careful, sometimes its like a puzzle. It can challenge your intellect.\n\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control\n*The red player can pass through red water, and the blue player can pass through blue water. Neither player can pass through green water.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AW55D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-water-and-fire/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R2PIP","slug":"chicken-escape-2-player","title":"Chicken Escape - 2 Player","description":"Have you ever caught runaway chickens before? You must catch all the chickens. To catch the runaway chickens, you need to act fast. Farmers are competing. The red and blue farmers must win the race. Be any farmer and win the race. Play with your friend and collect the chickens as quickly and early as possible. You must catch all the runaway chickens. The one who collects 10 chickens the fastest wins.\n\n*Use the WASD keys and Arrow keys to move. \n*The fastest to collect 10 chickens wins. \n*Collect all the chickens in 120 seconds.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R2PIP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chicken-escape-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W2GF5","slug":"find-the-flag-world-cup-2022","title":"Find The Flag World Cup 2022","description":"In this fun game, find the flags of the participating countries of the 2022 world cup. Play the competitive mode and try to get the highest score possible, or play the fun mode for as long as you want.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W2GF5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-flag-world-cup-2022/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T8TA9","slug":"paint-the-numbers","title":"Paint The Numbers","description":"“Paint The Numbers” is an educational game for children, perfect for learning and exercising learning numbers.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T8TA9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paint-the-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2O9IW","slug":"cat-girl-halloween-preparation","title":"Cat Girl Halloween Preparation","description":"Welcome to Cat Girl Halloween Preparation. Join Cat Girl in her Halloween Preparation journey! From spooky decorations to creative costumes, get inspired for the spookiest night of the year. Discover Cat Girl's tips and tricks for the ultimate Halloween celebration and make this year’s festivities unforgettable! Play and have fun with this new Halloween game! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2O9IW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-girl-halloween-preparation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H0A20","slug":"jump-in-the-wall","title":"Jump In The Wall","description":"Jump in the wall and obtain points for reach the best score and gems for purchase new skins","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H0A20/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-in-the-wall/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5M33M","slug":"dice-merge","title":"Dice Merge","description":"Embark on a thrilling journey of strategy and chance in \"7 Dice Match\" – the ultimate dice merge game for iOS! Immerse yourself in a captivating world where rolling the dice isn't just luck, but a skillful art form.\n\nMerge and Evolve: Combine identical dice to create higher-value dice with every roll. Strategize and plan your moves to reach the coveted legendary dice. Fuse dice strategically to dominate the game!\n\nPower-Up Your Play: Unleash powerful abilities by merging special dice. Watch as explosions, lightning strikes, and more unfold on your screen, turning the tide of battle in your favor. Strategic use of these abilities is the key to victory!\n\n Global Tournaments: Compete with players from around the world in thrilling tournaments. Climb the leaderboards, earn prestigious rewards, and prove your mastery of dice merging.","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5M33M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dice-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AS0IM","slug":"ladies-of-paris-anime-clicker","title":"Ladies of Paris - Anime Clicker","description":"Clicker d'anime chaud avec des beautés lumineuses et attrayantes ! Utilisez la monnaie du jeu pour débloquer de nouveaux personnages ! Le but du jeu est d'ouvrir tout le monde !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AS0IM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ladies-of-paris-anime-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5YU45","slug":"bouncy-bullet-physics-puzzles","title":"Bouncy Bullet - Physics Puzzles","description":"$3e","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5YU45/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bouncy-bullet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TO1T4","slug":"soccer-shoot-star","title":"Soccer Shoot Star","description":"Head and kick the ball in this mini soccer game.\nBe a football legend one on one. Choose your football player, the field, the ball and play. Control your hero skillfully, jump and shoot amazing shots.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TO1T4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-shoot-star/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1MTJO","slug":"jumping-ships-from-outer-space","title":"Jumping Ships from Outer Space","description":"Pilot your ship through the obstacles, collect as many stars as you can and watch out for enemy ships. How many points will you be able to score?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1MTJO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumping-ships-from-outer-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5417O","slug":"trash-factory","title":"Trash Factory","description":"Help the trash pandas take out the garbage!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5417O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trash-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51CO1","slug":"save-rocket","title":"Save Rocket","description":"It is a dynamic arcade game. Sleight of hand does not hurt. The rocket is accelerating all the time. Don't crash on the platform!!! Set records, and compete with your friends :) ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51CO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-rocket/embed?sid=1","plays":39900,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31Z19","slug":"2048-ballz","title":"2048 Ballz","description":"2048 Ballz - is an endless physics puzzle with 2048 mechanics! \nYou have to combine balls of the same color to get new one!\nSet a record!\nEnjoy this beautiful and relaxing game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31Z19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-ballz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9ELRL","slug":"metal-driller","title":"Metal Driller","description":"Metal Driller is a mining game featuring drills, mines, levels and lots of upgrade options. Control the drill that the character with Ragdoll physics is holding on to and try to reach the bottom. Diversify your gameplay by creating new builds with the skill tree, which resets at the end of each chapter. Get new Drill costumes as you progress through the chapters and dress yourself and your little Drill friends in different outfits.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9ELRL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/metal-driller/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6RR3O","slug":"ban-ban-parkour","title":"Ban Ban Parkour","description":"Have you ever run to the door in the dark like this before? Run to the door with your friend in the dark one by one. Collect the toys you need to gather. Collect the toys to open the door. We need all the toys. You must race against time in the dark to survive. Reach the door before time runs out. Otherwise, you will die in the dark. Or you might get lost in the dark.\n\n*Use WASD Keys to move and jump.\n*Collect the Bowling Toy first and then the remote control Toy in order. \n*Both mobile and desktop playability.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6RR3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ban-ban-parkour/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0L98","slug":"stay-alive","title":"Stay Alive","description":"Are you ready to survive? You have an axe in your hand, start cutting down all the trees. First, cut down the trees and build a tent. After the tent, you should build walls around it so that cannibals dont attack and eat you. Either run away from the cannibals or fight them to make them flee. Collect rocks, bushes, and wood. You need to make a fire. If your health is low, eat mushrooms, or you might die. Finally, as the last task, build a raft and complete the game.\n\nTo move the player, press the Arrow keys. Use the Space key to hit the cannibals or cut down trees. Press E to pick up rocks from the ground. Collect mushrooms to replenish your health.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0L98/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stay-alive/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"768OR","slug":"meteor-io","title":"Meteor.io","description":"Collect the shards, dodge the meteorite! A simple and addictive casual game that will test your reaction and agility. Become the best shard collector and show how far you can reach without getting hit by a barrage of meteorites!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/768OR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meteor-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"010A4","slug":"speedy-car","title":"Speedy Car","description":"In this  Speedy Car game user have to save his /her car to avoid collision with other cars to get score .\nIt's 2d portrait game suitible for mobile browsers as well.\n\nControl: window left and right arrow keys ,touch.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/010A4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speedy-car/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61SCR","slug":"tanks-across-the-desert","title":"Tanks Across the Desert","description":"This game simulates the British war effort in Libya, Egypt, and the Eastern Mediterranean.  The game uses deck builder mechanics, which is appropriate because Commonwealth forces needed to build an army that could stop Rommel and the Afrika Korps from scratch.  Finding a way to get tanks, infantry, artillery, Englishmen, Australians, Frenchmen, and Indians to work together was a major undertaking.  It took the Germans the better part of a decade to figure all of this out.  The British pulled it off in two years.  Intelligence plays a big part in this game:  there are ways to see what your opponent will do, and knowing this gives you a big advantage.  Good luck!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61SCR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tanks-across-the-desert/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"996E5","slug":"bat-escape","title":"Bat Escape","description":"Bat Escape is a casual game where players control a bat navigating through obstacles. Similar to Flappy Bird, the gameplay involves tapping the screen to make the bat flap its wings and stay afloat.With simple controls and addictive gameplay.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/996E5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bat-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7RWN","slug":"halloween-makeup-trends","title":"Halloween Makeup Trends","description":"If you're still seeking inspiration for your Halloween look, then stop right here. Our social media influencers bring three jaw-dropping makeup looks that are going to help you steal the spotlights during the spookiest night of the year. In the Halloween Makeup Trends game for girls, you can learn from Kiki how to create a unicorn makeup look, from Riri how to obtain a colorful Dia de Los Muertes-inspired makeup look, and from Regina the secrets of sophisticated fantasy makeup. Play now!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7RWN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-makeup-trends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SSA16","slug":"highschool-mean-girls-2","title":"Highschool Mean Girls 2","description":"The mean girls are back to school, this time in a brand-new formula. You can join them in our online dress-up game for girls called Highschool Mean Girls 2 and help them style up their looks for the first day of school. Get it started, and have a great time creating jaw-dropping outfits for these 2 groups of BFFs competing in the high school fashion challenge. Only one group will be the next fashion queen, but who will be our winners? The supermodels or the singers?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SSA16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/highschool-mean-girls-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BL0LS","slug":"bffs-unique-halloween-costumes","title":"BFFs Unique Halloween Costumes","description":"Join the BFFs Unique Halloween Costumes adventure! These best friends are on a mission to find the most creative and distinctive Halloween outfits. Get ready for a one-of-a-kind Halloween experience as they plan, choose, and showcase their unique costumes. Unleash your creativity and celebrate Halloween like never before with the trendiest and most original looks!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BL0LS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-unique-halloween-costumes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4IB1I","slug":"celebrity-halloween-costumes","title":"Celebrity Halloween Costumes","description":"Welcome to Celebrity Halloween Costume Adventure! Your favorite celebrities are planning the perfect Halloween outfits together. Get ready for a star-studded Halloween experience as they choose and showcase their ultimate costumes. Unleash your inner celebrity with the hottest Halloween trends!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4IB1I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/celebrity-halloween-costumes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CA6H3","slug":"halloween-head-soccer","title":"Halloween Head Soccer","description":"Are you ready to go head to head on a football match? Choose mode 1P or 2P to get started. Choose your favorite Halloween character! Hit the ball into the goal to score points before the time runs out. The player with the most goals wins the game","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CA6H3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-head-soccer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1OLWE","slug":"war-of-noobs-for-two-players","title":"War of Noobs for two players","description":"Play together with a friend! The Noobs War on the computer or phone! 6 cool maps for Noob's battles and 5 cool weapons. Jump on the cards and shoot at your friend's nasty ones! Decide which of you is the best Noob! This game is very addictive!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1OLWE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/war-of-noobs-for-two-players/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6N66M","slug":"pumpkin-wheel","title":"Pumpkin Wheel","description":"Pumpkin Wheel is a funny game where you must control a big rolling Pumpkin through 30 levels!\nWhit its original and colorful graphics Pumpkin Wheel will be a pleasant time-killer, simple but addicting.\nSo accelerate, break and have a perfect control of your Pumpkin in order to complete all levels!\n\nEnjoy this game in this magic halloweens season; and follow the stars!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6N66M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-wheel/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I189P","slug":"pumpkinoide","title":"Pumpkinoide","description":"Pumpkinoid is a simple one touch arcade game that is a little like break out and a little like pinball.\nThere are three medals to be achieved based on score and there are three new paddles that can be unlocked also based on score.\nThere are seven backgrounds will be picked each time you play.\nEnjoy with Pumpkinoid!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I189P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkinoide/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D1CA6","slug":"cursed-dreams","title":"Cursed Dreams","description":"In Cursed Dreams you have to save your family from their nightmares.\nBeat 5 different mini-games with unique game mechanics. Explore a the mansion and find all the secrets around, then go back to sleep to see if your actions changed your family fate...\nFeaturing:\n5 Different Endings\n5 Different Minigames\nExploration\npre-rendered graphics","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D1CA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cursed-dreams/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SII6M","slug":"ladies-princesses-anime-clicker","title":"Ladies Princesses - Anime Clicker","description":"Clicker d'anime chaud avec des beautés lumineuses et attrayantes ! Utilisez la monnaie du jeu pour débloquer de nouveaux personnages ! Le but du jeu est d'ouvrir tout le monde !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SII6M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ladies-princesses-anime-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OA3N1","slug":"pumpkin-and-the-dungeon-of-doom","title":"Pumpkin And The Dungeon Of Doom","description":"Pumpkin and The Dungeon Of Doom  is an epic adventure through 100 levels of monsters, traps and danger!!!\nHave you got the brains and fast reflexes to escape all 100 dungeons in this unique action puzzle game?\nBats will chase you, Ghosts will try and trick you, Monsters around every corner, Hazards include Spikes, Guillotines, Poison gas and more...\nHave you got what it takes?\nProduct feature bullets:\n- Halloween Game!\n- 100 epic levels!\n- Cute graphic!\n- Cool creepy music!\n- Really addictive! \n- Easy to play!\nEnjoy with this great Halloween Puzzle Adventure game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OA3N1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-and-the-dungeon-of-doom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KGIPI","slug":"pumpkin-night","title":"Pumpkin Night","description":"Pumpkin Nigth is a fun adventure ride of in this Halloween season. \nHere in this fun adventure game, the little Jack is moving around to collect the keys to unlock the portals for the exits.\nFor that Jack needs to collect the key on the way, but we all know the hurdles there in the abandoned area, but some are for your convenience, use the blocks to climb up and collect the keys and reach the end-fire to complete the level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KGIPI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-night/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PMLK1","slug":"pumpkin-roll","title":"Pumpkin Roll","description":"The winter season is coming and Mr. Pumpkin needs help to find all missing Gifts!\nSo help Mr. Pumpkin to find all the missing Christmas Gifts! enjoy this fantastic game in a Christmas/Halloween atmosphere.\nSpin Mr. Pumpkini, avoid obstacles and dangers and travel through three different worlds to recover all the missing Gifts.\nEnjoy Halloween season with this great puzzle cool game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PMLK1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-roll/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BAKB6","slug":"pumpkin-blast","title":"Pumpkin Blast","description":"Hey Jack needs your help to escape from this dark prison!\n\nThe main goal is to land Jack the pumpkin in the safe area with the least number of attempts!\n\nYou just use the explosive to move Jack in the right direction but be aware at the dangerous spikes!\n\nAre you able to get the three stars for each level?","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BAKB6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4TAI0","slug":"christmas-tree","title":"Christmas Tree","description":"Decorate your Christmas tree and make it as beautiful as possible.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4TAI0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-tree/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CPS0C","slug":"advanced-physics-puzzles-challenges","title":"Advanced Physics Puzzles-Challenges","description":"“Physics puzzles” is a puzzle-style game mixed with physics, where the player has the objective of hitting the ball inside the basket using the available objects to make the path that the ball must follow to pass through the obstacles.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CPS0C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/physics-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4IRTR","slug":"autumn-solitaire-tripeaks","title":"Autumn Solitaire Tripeaks","description":"Play Classic TriPeaks or 100 different autumn  levels. Remove all cards from the tableau, you can remove top cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value than the open card on the bottom. Click on the closed stack to get a new open card.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4IRTR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/autumn-solitaire-tripeaks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA9AL","slug":"math-balls","title":"Math Balls","description":"“Math Balls” is a casual game to exercise your reasoning and also your mathematical ability, play and see if you are good.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA9AL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MRNA7","slug":"ai-anime-streamers","title":"AI Anime Streamers","description":"Welcome to the exciting world of \"AI anime streamers\"! This is an exciting clicker game that will take you into the virtual reality of streaming and exciting adventures. You have to click, unlock all the streamer girls and improve your clicks in search of fame and fortune!\n\nAttention, is everyone ready? Let's get started! Your main goal is to unlock all the streamer girls who delight their viewers and earn coins on their streams. But to do that, you'll have to improve your clicks! Pump up your skill and stamina, increasing the profit from each click and maximizing your potential.\n\nTo further increase your income, you will need your loyal cats. Collect them to heat up the atmosphere and increase profits. Each cat has its own unique look.\n\n\nThis is your chance to become an AI anime streamer legend! Only you have everything you need to succeed and make your name known. Become a virtual star that everyone knows and adores!","category":"Sport","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MRNA7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ai-anime-streamers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2AAC5","slug":"sweet-excavation","title":"Sweet Excavation","description":"In \"Sweet Excavation\" you will find a sweet puzzle game where your dexterity and ability to strategically plan the game will be put to a serious test. Here you have to collect a variety of sweets in a limited number of taps, keeping a balance between mouth-watering treats and limited resources.\n\nBonuses are your loyal ally. You will be able to activate a variety of bonuses that will help you achieve goals and save clicks. For example, a candy bomb that collects all the sweets horizontally.\n\nA skillful combination of dexterity and strategy.\nLots of different levels with unique goals.\nA variety of bonuses that help save clicks and achieve goals.\nColorful graphics and musical accompaniment, creating an atmosphere of sweet excitement.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2AAC5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-excavation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40073","slug":"sudoku-html5","title":"Sudoku HTML5","description":"Pour chaque grille, le bouton Indice peut vous indiquer les techniques nécessaires pour progresser. Les instructions sont faciles à comprendre et spécifiques à chaque grille, avec des animations très utiles et des illustrations en couleur. Les indices ne vous donnent pas juste la réponse, ils vous aident à la comprendre. Cette fonctionnalité vous aidera à apprendre toutes les techniques nécessaires pour résoudre les grilles de Sudoku, que vous soyez novice ou expert.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40073/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sudoku-html5/embed?sid=1","plays":35900,"rating":4.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GTU0T","slug":"manga-math-tutor","title":"Manga Math Tutor","description":"Manga Math Tutor est un jeu de réflexion qui vous met au défi de faire des calculs mathématiques. L'objectif est que vous soyez meilleur et plus rapide lorsque vous effectuez des calculs mentaux de manière amusante et agréable.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GTU0T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/manga-math-tutor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E4A78","slug":"task-manager-the-game","title":"Task Manager The Game","description":"$3f","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E4A78/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/task-manager-the-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4EMC7","slug":"alchemist-tower-defense","title":"Alchemist Tower Defense","description":"This game is in beta, you are welcome to try it but some bugs are to be expected.\n\nYou get 5 gems each round. Keep one, the others will turn to rock. Use the rocks to build a maze to prolong the time the monsters spend walking and taking hits.  \n\nFor gold you can upgrade your chances to get better gems. And with better gems you can create \"special\" gems that have abilities like stun or poison. The monsters can be different: fast, mob (less HP - more headcount), boss.\n\nYou can combine gems by drag-and-dropping two of the same type together.\n\nBuild a long maze but cannot block their path entirely. The monsters always check if there is a path to your base before coming out of the cave, and if it is blocked, they will stay.\n\nUpcoming features:\n\nmore monster types (regenerating, boss, teleporting)\nmore special gems\nnicer user interface\nAndroid version\nmaybe some bloons and monkeys ;)\nmore scenarios (maybe some only to be included in a future premium version)","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4EMC7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alchemist-tower-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":40121,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O82OL","slug":"noob-vs-choo-choo-charles","title":"Noob VS. Choo-Choo Charles","description":"$40","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O82OL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-choo-choo-charles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5N5ST","slug":"simon-says-palette","title":"Simon Says Palette","description":"How strong is your memory? The most fun way to test this is with the \"Simon Says Palette\". New records are waiting for you\nEnjoy","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5N5ST/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/simon-says-palette/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"709LA","slug":"escape-ball","title":"Escape Ball","description":"escape ball is game arcade","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/709LA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11L62","slug":"putblock","title":"Putblock","description":"In this game you must the block move right left horizontal and you must with touch on screen to put it in the right place the block","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11L62/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/putblock/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0A9U8","slug":"cute-dinosaur-run","title":"Cute Dinosaur Run","description":"Dinosaur Running is a fun game about a little trex who runs through obstacles and bigger dinosaurs.\nTap the screen to jump over obstacles. Game speed will increase gradually. The dinosaur will run through new lands with new dangers.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0A9U8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dinosaur-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"50RL7","slug":"your-silver-wife","title":"Your Silver Wife","description":"Click on the Anime girl to increase your level of sympathy and achieve the most important goal - To become her companion in life!\n\nPump up your click power or the chance of getting a gift that you can give to your girlfriend.\n\nDo not forget about the Autoclick, which helps you achieve your cherished goal.\n\nThe Anime Girl reacts to every touch with the help of her voice, and she will thank you for the gift that you give her.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50RL7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/your-silver-wife/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7694N","slug":"grimace-night","title":"Grimace Night","description":"Grimace Nigth is a fun adventure ride of in this Halloween season. \nHere in this fun adventure game, the little Grimace is moving around to collect the keys to unlock the portals for the exits.\nFor that Grimace needs to collect the key on the way, but we all know the hurdles there in the abandoned area, but some are for your convenience, use the blocks to climb up and collect the keys and reach the end-fire to complete the level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7694N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-night/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A20K7","slug":"mountain-tank","title":"Mountain Tank","description":"A tank shooting game with multiple tanks, enhanced upgrades, and various terrain levels.Button controlled tank movement and shooting.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A20K7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mountain-tank/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E564T","slug":"tile-triple","title":"Tile Triple","description":"Not like classic puzzle - tile journey & magic jigsaw puzzle, Tile Triple - Free Tile Master & Connect Brain Game is not only an addictive matching puzzle game but also help to release your stress with tons of happy color 3D objects, candy crush, cute animals; cool toys, yummy fruits and etc,... ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E564T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tile-triple/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TCC4C","slug":"rescue-toilet-head-cut","title":"Rescue Toilet-Head Cut","description":"Vous voulez un petit jeu à jouer quand vous vous ennuyez ? Alors allumez le jeu Rescue Toilet-Head Cut !\nRègles du jeu :\nPour aider quelqu'un coincé dans une corde,\nFaites glisser la corde avec votre doigt et coupez-la,\nPour le sauver avec succès.\nLe jeu Rescue Toilet-Head Cut ne nécessite qu'une opération de jeu simple, faites glisser l'écran pour jouer, très simple et amusant","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TCC4C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-toilet-head-cut/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N47E","slug":"duo-nether","title":"Duo Nether","description":"Things are getting even tougher in the second part of the series, so are you up for this adventure? The adventure is getting increasingly difficult. There are monsters and traps everywhere. Tell your friend right away and join this adventure. Remember, youre in for an even more challenging adventure. Steve and Alex are now stronger with their swords. You must be high off the ground to throw the sword. Jump-Throw the sword and kill all the enemies. Collect all the white bone dust stones. Open the chests and both of you reach the door.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.\n*Mobile touch control is available\n*To throw the sword, use the Q and P keys.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N47E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-nether/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5346Y","slug":"noob-s-chicken-farm-tycoon","title":"Noob's Chicken Farm Tycoon","description":"Aidez Noob à gérer un élevage de poulets : élevez et améliorez des poulets, achetez des outils utiles pour la ferme.\nMettez les têtes des masques à plumes de Noob, zombies, démons, chats et plus encore.\nVous en avez marre du poulet ? Échangez-les contre des toilettes Skibidi qui fabriquent du papier toilette au lieu d'œufs.\nOu achetez un dinosaure - ses œufs sont plus gros et plus chers à vendre !\nConstruisez une ferme à différents endroits : dans la forêt, les jours de mer ou en enfer.\nProtégez vos poules du renard - achetez un chien pour protéger les oiseaux.\nAffrontez d'autres éleveurs de poulets pour voir qui gère les meilleurs poussins !","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5346Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-s-chicken-farm-tycoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4SU8C","slug":"matchstick-puzzles","title":"Matchstick Puzzles","description":"Résoudre des énigmes et des tâches avec des allumettes est une activité passionnante et surtout utile !\n\nDe tels puzzles entraînent parfaitement la mémoire, la débrouillardise, développent la pensée logique, l'imagination spatiale.\n\nIls plairont aussi bien aux petits qu'aux grands.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4SU8C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/matchstick-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ORI5","slug":"darts-pro-multiplayer","title":"Darts Pro Multiplayer","description":"4 games in one!\nIn practice mode, you can play against the computer, a friend on the same device, or a real opponent from anywhere in the world.\nYour goal is to decrease your starting 501 score.\n\nIn the competitive mode, the first one to reach 0 points wins.\nThe last dart must hit either the bullseye or the doubling zone.\nDoubles and trebles multiply the number of points that will be deducted from your score by two and three, respectively.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ORI5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/darts-pro-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GOL5G","slug":"move-gather-your-belongings","title":"Move - Gather your belongings","description":"Welcome to the captivating world where every move becomes an exciting puzzle! Help the characters pack their belongings and set off on their journey.\n\n- Captivating Levels: Each level introduces a new character with unique items to be packed into the truck.\n- Tetris-Style Puzzle: As you play, you'll encounter shapes reminiscent of the logical figures from the tabletop game Tetris.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GOL5G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/move-gather-your-belongings/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IDEGA","slug":"dog-training-idle-clicker","title":"Dog Training - Idle Clicker","description":"Dog Training: Clicker - an exciting game with dogs. Are you ready to dive into a world of endless fun? Start playing right now!\n\nDog training is an engaging process, and playing with dogs can continue endlessly.\n\n- Conquer the heights of the dog world, reaching the infinity of coins!\n- Every 10 levels, a new breed of dog appears!\n- There are 10 breeds of dogs in the game!\n- Don't postpone it, start playing right now!\n\nYour friends are already actively training their dogs, and you should hurry not to fall behind!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IDEGA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dog-training-idle-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18AS0","slug":"classic-backgammon","title":"Classic Backgammon","description":"Move all your checkers around the board and bear off all your pieces from the board before your opponent!\nTwo game’s mode:\n- Play against a friend locally\n- Challenge the computer","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18AS0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-backgammon/embed?sid=1","plays":39615,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K6661","slug":"skibidi-blocks","title":"Skibidi Blocks","description":"Skibidi Blocks Game is a fast-paced and challenging building block runner game that will test your reflexes and strategic thinking skills. A stack of blocks through a series of obstacles, collecting Poo along the way. The blocks will automatically move forward, so you must carefully plan your jumps and movements to avoid falling off the screen.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K6661/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06039","slug":"flappy","title":"Flappy","description":"Guide the cute square through the maze of tricky pipes, keeping it airborne.  With its captivating pixel art style, Flappy offers a visually stunning journey; full of fun and surprises.  Easy to play and simple to understand, but hard to master.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06039/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96146","slug":"1line","title":"1Line","description":"$41","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96146/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/1line/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAX64","slug":"taxi-simulator-3d","title":"Taxi Simulator 3D","description":"$42","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAX64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/taxi-simulator-3d-taxi-games/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"229I1","slug":"sinner-eye","title":"Sinner Eye","description":"Sinner Eye is a casual game where players control a monster navigating through obstacles. Similar to Flappy Bird, the gameplay involves tapping the screen to make the monster flap its wings and stay afloat.With simple controls and addictive gameplay.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/229I1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sinner-eye/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4RBYR","slug":"cute-capybara-clicker","title":"Cute Capybara Clicker","description":"Help the cute capybara make money! Earn, feed and scratch the capybara's back.\nWill you be able to complete all the achievements?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4RBYR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-capybara-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9I9CL","slug":"the-lost-campfire","title":"The Lost Campfire","description":"\"The Lost Campfire\" is an exciting game where daylight gives way to night darkness and danger. You have to fight for survival in the heart of the wild.\n\nDuring the day, you'll explore the dark depths of the forest surrounding your camp. Explore the territory, collect valuable resources and free allies captured by terrible monsters.\n\nWith the onset of darkness, the world will change. Mysterious creatures and insidious monsters will begin to emerge from their hiding places, trying to devour you and your fire. You will have to prove your courage and skill by defending your camp from hordes of hungry monsters. Speed and accuracy in shooting and skillful use of resources will become your faithful companions in the battle against darkness.\n\nCan you survive this harsh struggle between light and darkness by making good choices during the day and fighting fearlessly at night? Show off your skills and lead your mysterious camp to victory in The Lost Campfire.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9I9CL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-lost-campfire/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9VIII","slug":"cowboy-vs-skibidi-toilets","title":"Cowboy vs Skibidi Toilets","description":"Cowboy vs Skibidi Toilets is a shooting game set in wild west where you play as cowboy and your mission is to shoot all skibidi toilets using different weapons, try to survive each round to unlock new guns.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9VIII/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cowboy-vs-skibidi-toilets/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AI997","slug":"bffs-high-school-first-date-look","title":"BFFs High School First Date Look","description":"Welcome to BFFs High School First Date Look. Get ready to style BFFs for their exciting high school first date! Mix and match trendy outfits, hairstyles, and accessories to create the perfect look that will make them feel confident and impress their date. Can you help them to find the ultimate outfit that captures their unique style and personality? Let the fashion fun begin! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AI997/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bffs-high-school-first-date-look/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"412H1","slug":"whaito-2","title":"Whaito 2","description":"Whaito 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect all of the red cubes while avoiding the spikes, man eater monsters, enemies, flying creatures and their bullets, and reach the white flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Whaito\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/412H1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/whaito-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UO2S1","slug":"design-with-me-superhero-tutu-outfits","title":"Design With Me SuperHero Tutu Outfits","description":"Welcome to Design With Me SuperHero Tutu Outfits. We all love superheroes very much! Likewise, our favorite princesses are inspired more by superhero tutu fashion. They planned to organize the fashion events under this theme. Join and help each princess to pick a suitable superhero tutu outfit. Play them and have fun! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UO2S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/design-with-me-superhero-tutu-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"45606","slug":"ellie-and-friends-pre-fall-outfit","title":"Ellie and Friends Pre Fall Outfit","description":"Transition into fall with the Ellie and Friends Pre-Fall Outfit collection. Explore a fusion of style and comfort as they curate trendy ensembles featuring cozy layers, versatile accessories, and seasonal hues. Embrace the upcoming season with fashion-forward choices inspired by the experts themselves! Join and have fun! ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/45606/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ellie-and-friends-pre-fall-outfit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9ASI9","slug":"bts-signature-fashion-style","title":"BTS Signature Fashion Style","description":"Dive into the world of BTS Signature Fashion Style. Explore the iconic looks of the global superstars and discover how to incorporate their trendsetting fashion into your own wardrobe. From stage outfits to everyday streetwear, get inspired and elevate your style with a touch of BTS’s unparalleled flair. Join us on a fashion journey that transcends borders and celebrates individuality with the influence of these K-pop icons. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9ASI9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bts-signature-fashion-style/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UTS5U","slug":"monster-girls-high-school-squad","title":"Monster Girls High School Squad","description":"Unleash your inner fashionista with the Monster Girls High School Squad dress-up game! Mix and match captivating outfits, accessorize with magical charms, and create spellbinding looks for supernatural students. Dive into a world of style, friendship, and enchantment as you explore the fantastic wardrobe options and dress up the alluring characters. Join the squad and let your creativity run wild in this thrilling fashion adventure! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UTS5U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-girls-high-school-squad/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H1H6T","slug":"hunter-steve","title":"Hunter Steve","description":"Hunter Steven needs to hunt down all the monsters. Take your weapon and hunt down all the monsters. Be careful, some monsters are stronger, and its harder to kill them. But, of course, you can buy a more powerful weapon and kill them all. Go to the store, get a stronger weapon, and hunt down all the monsters.\n\nTo move, use the WASD keys. To fire, use the Mouse left-click. \nKill all the zombies and complete the missions.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H1H6T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hunter-steve/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I66IA","slug":"organize-the-alphabet","title":"Organize The Alphabet","description":"Learn about the letters of the alphabet and exercise your knowledge of the letters.\n\nArrange the letters in the correct alphabet order, learn by playing.\n\nPerfect for kids learning letters and reading.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I66IA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/organize-the-alphabet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6G6TS","slug":"what-organ-is-this","title":"What Organ Is This?","description":"An educational game where the player puts into practice their knowledge about the organs of the human body.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6G6TS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-organ-is-this/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46640","slug":"city-building","title":"City Building","description":"Strategy city building game playable on any device with great 3D graphics in lowpoly.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46640/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-building/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4O4EO","slug":"undead-world-skeleton-warriors","title":"Undead World Skeleton Warriors","description":"Immerse yourself in the thrilling adventure of Undead World: SkeletonWarriors, where every touch matters! Enter a dark and mysterious world where your mission is to continuously touch or click on the ground, summoning powerful skeleton warriors to join your army. As you progress, you will witness the mesmerizing spectacle of skeleton warriors emerging from the depths, ready for battle.","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4O4EO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/undead-world-skeleton-warriors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FNTRT","slug":"garten-of-banban-obby","title":"Garten of Banban Obby","description":"Obby must survive the Garden of Banban monsters. There are two different tasks available: you can either help Obby on your own or team up with two friends to assist Obby and Nooby. Collect all the gold coins and buy the most beautiful costumes for yourselves. Become the owners of super cool costumes. While escaping, never look back. The monster is right behind you, dont stop running. Run from the monster.\n\n*Steve , Press WASD keys to move and jump.\n*Alex , Press Arrow Keys keys to move and jump.\n*Mobile Control Available","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FNTRT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/garten-of-banban-obby/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NS42","slug":"guns-zombie","title":"Guns Zombie","description":"Hey soldier, quickly grab your weapon and protect the world; there are zombies everywhere, killing people. Take your weapon and grab your ammunition. Shoot at the zombies quickly. Your mission is to kill all the zombies. Eliminate the zombies and collect their gold. The best and most powerful weapons should be yours.\n\nTo move, use the WASD keys. To fire, use the Mouse left-click. \nKill all the zombies and complete the missions.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NS42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guns-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21S2O","slug":"steve-and-alex-dungeons","title":"Steve and Alex Dungeons","description":"Steve and Alex are trapped in a dungeon in the dark, and you must help them escape. You need to rescue both of them one by one. The dungeon is very dangerous and filled with obstacles. Be careful of jumping over obstacles and watch out for spinning wheels. Collect the diamonds you need and escape from the dungeon. You must reach the door at the end of the dungeon.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21S2O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-and-alex-dungeons/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SE0N9","slug":"mazes-and-keys","title":"Mazes and Keys","description":"Mazes and keys is a puzzle game in which you must help the character to get out of the maze, reaching the colored star.\n\nThere are paths that will be blocked by doors, you must collect keys to unlock them.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SE0N9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mazes-and-keys/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I6A0E","slug":"square-clicker","title":"Square Clicker","description":"Click in the white square for obtain money and purchase upgrades for improve the square and obtain more money.\n\nInstructions:\n-Touch the square for obtain money\n-Touch the upgrades for obtain more benefits","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I6A0E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MLHAI","slug":"mahjong-solitaire-world-tour","title":"Mahjong Solitaire - World Tour","description":"Mahjong Solitaire: Tour du monde transforme le jeu de tuiles. Terminez des niveaux pour découvrir des villes mondiales. Avec des graphismes superbes et un gameplay fluide, c'est un must pour les fans de puzzles. Vivez votre aventure Mahjong ultime dès maintenant!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MLHAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-solitaire-world-tour/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S33RA","slug":"espada-de-sheris","title":"Espada de Sheris","description":"Espada de Sheris is an indie game of 2D platformer focused parkour where we control a European ninja cat called Kibo, He uses the Espada de Sheris to defeat masked duzkers and save progression and evolution. in a post apocalyptic world aliens from the year 4000's over the course of the chapters\n\nHow play:\nW = Jump\nA = Left\nD = Right\nEnter = Attack/Confirm","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S33RA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/espada-de-sheris-gamepixmode/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"119RM","slug":"barbiemania","title":"Barbiemania","description":"Experience the ultimate makeup adventure with Barbiemania! Join the iconic doll, Ellie, and create stunning looks for three occasions. Let's dive into the magical world of Barbiemania and unleash your inner stylist!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/119RM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbiemania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1MAM9","slug":"komera","title":"Komera","description":"Komera is a game about making the thing right!\nTry to make an identical copy of the image on the left using the controls on the screen befor the timer on the screen reache the zero.\nThe difficulty increase as you progress in the game, adding new controls to match the figure on the left!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1MAM9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/komera/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ES5SY","slug":"fry-skibidi","title":"Fry Skibidi","description":"Fry Skibidi is the coolest physics-based puzzle game.\nDrop the Skibidi down onto a metal block by destroying all the other blocks.\nOnce all the blocks are gone and the Skibidi is on a metal block press the ZAPPER button to fry the Skibidi!\nExplore all three worlds and clear all the puzzles.\nThis is a great halloween games!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ES5SY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fry-the-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"24O66","slug":"crow-smasher","title":"Crow Smasher","description":"Crow Smasher est un jeu difficile dans lequel vous devez détruire les corbeaux sur les plateformes à l'aide d'un canon. Positionnez le canon et visez les corbeaux en tirant sur les cailloux. Profitez des 36 niveaux amusants et stimulants.\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/24O66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crow-smasher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5II20","slug":"ski-king-2024","title":"Ski King 2024","description":"Vos pistes préférées sont enfin ouvertes. Alors n'hésite pas à dévaler la pente, à collecter les pièces, à améliorer tes compétences et à devenir le roi du ski. Pouvez-vous échapper à l'avalanche aussi ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5II20/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ski-king-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G5I55","slug":"parking-lot","title":"Parking Lot","description":"Do you like car games? Then you'll definitely like our new game! You'll manage the parking lot, maintain cleanliness and order, as well as develop your character and hire workers. Are you ready to accept the challenge and become the king of parking lot?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G5I55/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parking-lot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0TOEK","slug":"noob-archer-monster-attack","title":"Noob Archer Monster Attack","description":"In the game, you start playing as a beginner archer, a complete nub from which you have to make a pro archer. Can you defeat all bosses, unlock all achievements, get the best bow and helmet, and become the top 1 archer in the world?\n\nGame Features:\nUpgrade - by increasing the parameters of the archer make up your personal build.\nEnemies - a variety of enemies, bosses and targets, fight them all.\nWind - changes the trajectory of the arrow, watch him.\nEquipment - open all bows and helmets and get the best one.\nRevenge – defeated, lost half of the coins, go back and get them back if you can.\nEffects - freeze, poison or set fire to the enemy, but beware yourself.\nLevels - a huge number of levels pass the most you will enter the top.\nAchievements - try to complete all the different missions and get achievements.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0TOEK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-archer-monster-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9T178","slug":"t20-cricket","title":"T20 Cricket","description":"Come and join the T20 cricket game! It takes place in a busy stadium with excited fans. The game is played on a green field. Pick the Bangladesh cricket team and show off your amazing skills and strategies. In this game, the bowler runs quickly towards the wicket and throws the ball fast. You have to play the role of the batsman and have to react quickly and either defend the ball or hit it hard. Showcase your cricket skills in front of others in your group. ","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9T178/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/t20-cricket/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N3DIV","slug":"rainbow-friends-among-survival-adventures","title":"Rainbow Friends Among Survival Adventures","description":"$43","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N3DIV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-friends-among-survival-adventures/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R159R","slug":"mask-buddy-run","title":"Mask Buddy Run","description":"Mask Buddy run is a casual, pixel art game, like the offline dino run game. In thsi game you have to run, jump and dodge obstacle to increase your score! \nUse the arrows or touch the screen to increase your highscore.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R159R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mask-buddy-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2I5LI","slug":"stickman-fall","title":"Stickman Fall","description":"Step into a world where the primary goal is descending from heights using only plungers. This game presents players with a unique challenge: it's not merely about descending but adeptly maneuvering around obstacles that stand in the way.\n\nControl mechanics are straightforward: utilize the space key on a keyboard or a long press on mobile devices. But don't let this simplicity mislead you. With each progressing level, the difficulty escalates, and the obstacles become increasingly unpredictable.\n\nWho is this protagonist daring to descend in such a risky manner? What tales are intertwined with these pillars and barriers?\n\nGameplay hinges on reaction time and precision. It's not just about swift responses but also about accurately calculating when to halt, especially when aiming to stop at the designated finish zone.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2I5LI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-fall/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U3S3O","slug":"sushi-supply-co","title":"Sushi Supply Co.","description":"Build a sushi empire with Kitty Chef!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U3S3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sushi-supply-co/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"247R7","slug":"where-s-the-crook","title":"Where's the Crook?","description":"A puzzle game in the genre of \"Hidden objects\". Help find the Crook, who stole the bag from the unfortunate lady. Play with friends or the whole family. Game inspired by the book and animated series \"Where's Wally?\" (author Martin Handford, 1987). You need to find the Crook, who hid in the crowd and reach level 30. With each level, the passage of the game becomes faster and more difficult. The game trains visual perception and quick thinking. Good luck finding the Crook!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/247R7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/where-s-the-crook/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IL469","slug":"skibidi-roll","title":"Skibidi Roll","description":"The winter season is coming and Skibidi Toilet needs help to find all missing sweets!\nSo help Skibidi to find all the missing Christmas sweets! enjoy this fantastic game in a Christmas atmosphere.\nSpin Skididi, avoid obstacles and dangers and travel through three different worlds to recover all the missing sweets.\nEnjoy this great puzzle cool game!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IL469/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-roll/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"551IK","slug":"rotating-skibidi","title":"Rotating Skibidi","description":"Rotating Skibidi is a unique platform puzzle game where you rotate the world to guide Skibidi Toilet to his lost stars.\nThis is a great puzzle game with 40 challenge levels, push your logical brain abilities to the limit!\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Skibidi on board!\n• 40 different levels!\n• Very Fun for children!\n• Brain training for whole family!\n• Cute graphics!\n• Precise game physics!\n• Great sounds!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/551IK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotating-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SI7IK","slug":"skibidi-2","title":"Skibidi 2","description":"In this game you control Skibidi Toilet; so moving them around a world that revolves around you.\nAs you move around the landscape your character clings o the ground via gravity – use it your advantage to move from one platform to the next.\nThis is a fun exploring adventure games enjoy it!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SI7IK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I65A5","slug":"rotating-grimace","title":"Rotating Grimace","description":"Rotating Grimace is a unique platform puzzle game where you rotate the world to guide Mr Grimace to his lost stars.\nThis is a great puzzle game with 40 challenge levels, push your logical brain abilities to the limit!\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Grimace on board!\n• 40 different levels!\n• Very Fun for children!\n• Brain training for whole family!\n• Cute graphics!\n• Precise game physics!\n• Great sounds!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I65A5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotating-grimace/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"86877","slug":"skibidi-blast","title":"Skibidi Blast","description":"Hey Skibidi needs your help to escape from this dark prison!\nThe main goal is to land Skibidi in the safe area with the least number of attempts!\nYou just use the explosive to move Skibidi in the right direction but be aware at the dangerous spikes!\nAre you able to get the three stars for each level?","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/86877/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M4T3B","slug":"grimace-shake-skibidi-tetris","title":"Grimace Shake & Skibidi Tetris","description":"When Grimace Shake play tetris with skibidi toilet!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M4T3B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-shake-and-skibidi-tetris/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SV5EB","slug":"zombie-hunter-survival","title":"Zombie Hunter Survival","description":"Combattez et survivez aux assauts incessants des zombies. Améliorez votre équipement et vos armes pour faire face à des ennemis plus forts. Votre principal objectif dans ce monde sinistre est de survivre.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SV5EB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-hunter-survival/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L4333","slug":"basketball-kings-2024","title":"Basketball Kings 2024","description":"Entrez dans l'un des quatre terrains de basket et surpassez tout le monde où que vous alliez. Visez le panier et tirez ! Atteignez un score élevé pour débloquer de nouveaux ballons. Avec quel ballon jouerez-vous le mieux ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L4333/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-kings-2024/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EPM5A","slug":"zombie-apocalypse","title":"Zombie Apocalypse","description":"Préparez-vous à un assaut incessant de zombies dans ce jeu de plateforme bourré d'action. Courez, sautez et tirez dans des paysages apocalyptiques, en débloquant des avantages et en ouvrant des caisses pour améliorer vos objets. \n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EPM5A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-apocalypse/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N9964","slug":"tankbattle-2-player","title":"TankBattle 2 Player","description":"Are you ready for the battle of tanks? Its duel time, the tanks are going to war. Two enemies must defeat each other. The player who maneuvers the fastest and the best wins. You fire first and destroy the enemy tank. Be the best player to defeat your opponent. Fight against your friend and defeat them.\n\n\n*To move the blue tank, use the WASD keys. Press the Q key to fire a shot.\n*To move the brown tank, use the Arrow Keys keys. Press the P key to fire a shot.","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N9964/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tankbattle-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5E583","slug":"zombie-siege","title":"Zombie Siege","description":"The city has been attacked by a horde of zombies.. you are the only hope left to the inhabitants. Defend the streets at all costs, and don't let the zombie enter the centre of the city for any reason!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5E583/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-siege/embed?sid=1","plays":40231,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13013","slug":"yummy-cupcake","title":"Yummy Cupcake","description":"Are you ready to become the best Cupcake Chef? You are invited to the Yummy Cupcake maker game. Bake the dough, choose the right paper cups, and decorate each cupcake with different kinds of toppings, frosting, and many more! Then sell all the cupcakes to your customers. Let's play!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13013/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-cupcake/embed?sid=1","plays":40228,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NIB6T","slug":"car-nabbing-race-the-police-car-chase","title":"Car Nabbing Race - The Police Car Chase","description":"$44","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NIB6T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-nabbing-race-the-police-car-chase/embed?sid=1","plays":40227,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1168R","slug":"pharaoh-slots-casino","title":"Pharaoh Slots Casino","description":"Si vous aimez les jeux de machine à sous gratuits, Pharaoh Slots Casino est fait pour vous. Faites tourner les roues et croisez les doigts ! Aucun argent n'est requis pour jouer. Vous gagnez des pièces virtuelles. Ressentez l'excitation suscitée par les machines à sous sans craindre de perdre de l'argent. Jouez à des parties de machines à sous gratuites avec les fonctionnalités Wild, tours gratuits et partie bonus comme à Las Vegas.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1168R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pharaoh-slots-casino/embed?sid=1","plays":40226,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EBL4","slug":"some-little-bosses","title":"Some Little Bosses","description":"It's a little game with some bosses to fight i made for you, have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EBL4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/some-little-bosses/embed?sid=1","plays":40226,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4ABMA","slug":"football-tournament","title":"Football Tournament","description":"Football Tournament online Game is a football game that is played in a tournament format. It is a great time killer and a fun way to pass the time. Play Football Tournament online Game with your friends, family or classmates. You can play a Football Tournament online Game against the computer or against other players.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4ABMA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-tournament/embed?sid=1","plays":40224,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I4A1L","slug":"flapnglide","title":"FlapNGlide","description":"- Flap and glide through the obstacles while balancing within the frame. \n- Players will die if they touch the left and right frames at any point in the game. \n- Scoring is based on how many obstacles a player crossed.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I4A1L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flapnglide/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O7OO8","slug":"buuno-2","title":"Buuno 2","description":"Buuno 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as an office worker who have to collect the important documents while avoiding the Evil coworkers, drones, their bullets, spikes, rotating saws, and reach the purple flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.  \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Buuno\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O7OO8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buuno-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55NSI","slug":"find-in-space","title":"Find In Space","description":"In this game, you must find several planets and space objects in space, learn the name of the planets and have fun playing at the same time.\nUse the fun mode to play to learn, without any difficulty.\nUse the competitive mode to show what you have learned and then make the highest score possible, be careful, the more points you make, the more difficult the game gets, can you do it?","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55NSI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3111R","slug":"hordes-of-orc","title":"Hordes of Orc","description":"Resist as much as you can by facing the different waves of orcs, your base and fortify your position and do not forget to hurl large boulders at the orcs with the mouse, Have fun!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3111R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horde-of-orcs/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BE7DC","slug":"kids-educations-abc","title":"Kids Educations ABC","description":"Dans cette application, il y a environ 20 pages différentes où les enfants peuvent apprendre et comprendre l'anglais. Cette application est TRÈS DYNAMIQUE et n'ennuiera pas les enfants !\n\nCette application concerne l'éducation des enfants. L'application la plus complète pour que les enfants apprennent l'anglais :","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BE7DC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-educations-abc/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6L03B","slug":"rogue-ball","title":"Rogue Ball","description":"rogueball\ne un gioco di strategia a livelli \nlo scopo del gioco\nraccogliere tutte le monetine senza morire\nraccogliere la chiave per sbloccare il livello successivo\ncomandi gioco\ntouch su mobile\nle freccette su tastiera su pc","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6L03B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rogueball/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2286P","slug":"vampires-memory-match","title":"Vampires Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Vampires Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Vampires Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Vampires Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2286P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vampires-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40222,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L8WA6","slug":"alphabet-lore-jigsaw-wonderland","title":"Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland","description":"Welcome to Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland! Our Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland picture. With a wide variety of Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Wonderland Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L8WA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alphabet-lore-jigsaw-wonderland/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31111","slug":"always-go-up","title":"Always Go Up","description":"climb high with the ship, don't get crushed by the electric barriers","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/always-go-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KO2SA","slug":"among-akero-bots-2","title":"Among Akero Bots 2","description":"Among Akero Bots 2 is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as Akero Bot who have to collect red magical gems while avoiding the enemy bots, flying robots, bullets, rotating lasers, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Among Akero Bots\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KO2SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/among-akero-bots-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CIN80","slug":"animals-coloring","title":"Animals Coloring","description":"$45","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CIN80/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/animalscoloringforadults/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7ALA","slug":"ants","title":"Ants","description":"$46","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7ALA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ants-tap-tap-color-ants/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1446L","slug":"ball-crazy","title":"Ball Crazy","description":"ball crazy is arcade game ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1446L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-crazy/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IBA1A","slug":"ball-domino","title":"Ball Domino","description":"Boule de domino\n\nPouvez-vous placer tous les dominos Impact?\nAlignez le domino à travers les obstacles jusqu'au but et au jeu de puzzle！\nRenversez-les et regardez-les tomber un par un.\n\nLe but de la boule domino est de faire basculer les dominos !\nDomino Falling Collectez tous les cristaux pour obtenir des points bonus et renversez tous les dominos pour passer au défi suivant - plus vous en collectez, plus vous recevez de points。\nAvec suffisamment de pratique, vous déposerez rapidement des dominos lors de l'impact de la balle Domino.\nDécouvrez maintenant et roulez et écrasez!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IBA1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-domino/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L96AT","slug":"ball-to-ball","title":"Ball to Ball","description":"welcome to ball to ball, you will have to hit the white area in the wall, while your opponent tries to punch his ball","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L96AT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-to-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1572A","slug":"ballmania-2","title":"BallMania 2","description":"Can you catch the marble without being hit by the marble that kills you? beware in harder v2 new enemies turn against you","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1572A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballmania-v2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18666","slug":"balloon","title":"Balloon","description":"pop 35 balloons in 30 seconds","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18666/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballon/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L0RAA","slug":"balloon-artist-memory-match","title":"Balloon Artist Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Balloon artist Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Balloon artist Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Balloon artist Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L0RAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-artist-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2BB53","slug":"blacko-ball-2","title":"Blacko Ball 2","description":"Blacko Ball 2 is a 2D simple platformer where you have to collect the small red balls while avoiding Red and Orange enemies, spikes and ground saws and reach the exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n     \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Blacko Ball\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2BB53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blacko-ball-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NO331","slug":"bowling-pipe","title":"Bowling Pipe","description":"The goal is simple: collect the bowling balls with a pipe and get them to the goal. But be careful, it's not all that easy. There are bombs hidden among the balls that can explode and make you lose all the points. You will have to use your skill and your wits to avoid them and collect as many balls as possible in time. Are you up for the challenge, then let's play!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NO331/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bowling-pipe/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IQAT1","slug":"brain-iq-test-mincraft-quiz","title":"Brain IQ test Mincraft Quiz","description":"Know more than others and are ready to test it? Then you should definitely play the our game \"Brain IQ test: Minecraft Quiz\".\n\nWe have collected in the game different questions that will test your knowledge and erudition. Without them or masterful intuition, you can not beat your opponents.\n\nThe game is multiplayer, so before entering the level there is a random selection of opponents from your league.\n\nAll the characters in the game are made in the style of Minecraft. Connoisseurs of this genre will definitely like the art of the game. But to see it, you will need to raise your ranking and go to the top leagues. To do this you need to score points by defeating opponents in intellectual duels. For victories will be given not only points, but also new characters, as well as HAKI. These can be used in any tricky situation, when you don't have enough time to answer (Froze) or when you don't know the right answer (Save).\n\nGood luck!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IQAT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-iq-test-minecraft-quiz/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11L1N","slug":"brick-out-candy","title":"Brick Out Candy","description":"$47","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11L1N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brick-out-candy-online/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B62C2","slug":"bricks-breaker-deluxe","title":"Bricks Breaker - Deluxe","description":"Détendez-vous et jouez au meilleur jeu de casse-briques cette année.\nTouchez et tirez des balles pour casser toutes les briques. Vous devez effacer toutes les briques pour terminer chaque niveau. Trouvez le meilleur angle de visée pour casser un maximum de briques.\nLes briques sont détruites lorsque leur score atteint 0. Casser les briques avant qu'elles ne touchent le bas de l'écran.\n\nIl y a plus de 3000 niveaux à jouer !!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B62C2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bricks-breaker-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UL0NL","slug":"bullet-bender","title":"Bullet Bender","description":"Bullet Overload is the new biggest hit about rotating elements to point the gun at the mafia boss. Eliminate all enemies to win!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UL0NL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullet-blender/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2ARNU","slug":"bunny-jump-carrots","title":"Bunny Jump Carrots","description":"bunny jump carrots is an arcade game, jump and get carrots avoid obstacles and enemy.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2ARNU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buny-jump-carrots/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44SU6","slug":"buto-square","title":"Buto Square","description":"Buto Square is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the special red hats while avoiding the square enemies, spikes, ground saws, flying square enemies and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.  \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44SU6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buto-square/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LEHLL","slug":"castle-knight-run","title":"Castle Knight Run","description":"castle knight is a run and jump game, make it through obstacles by running and jumping through out the castle to reach the end.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LEHLL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/castle-knight/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FR5EV","slug":"cat-chef-vs-fruits-2-player","title":"Cat Chef vs Fruits - 2 Player","description":"Help two adventurous fruits escape from the cook cat and get the broccoli and avocado to the fridge with your friend or if you don't want the cook cat to eat them, help them and reach the fridge. Be careful on the way there are cookie monsters obeying the cook cat, they can eat you. jump over the obstacles, get rid of the cookies and reach the refrigerator.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Broccoli \"W+D\" moves with keys.   \n*Avocado \"Arrow Keys\" moves with keys.   \n*Double Jump available   \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FR5EV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-chef-vs-fruits-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CT031","slug":"chibi-totoro-tile-picture-challenge","title":"Chibi Totoro Tile Picture Challenge","description":"Welcome to Chibi Totoro Tile Picture Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Chibi Totoro Tile Picture Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Chibi Totoro Tile Picture Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CT031/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chibi-totoro-tile-picture-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7I5E8","slug":"chicken-ko","title":"Chicken Ko","description":"Chicken Ko is a 2D platformer where you have to collect bowls of grain and reach the red flag while avoiding enemies and spikes. The difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse WASD or Arrow keys for player's movement.     \nUse W or up arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7I5E8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chicken-ko/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60OTR","slug":"christmas-slot-machine","title":"Christmas Slot Machine","description":"Ho-ho-ho... Merry Christmas! Today it's time to spin and win with Slots Christmas! The game has never been so realistic when you make your way to the casino hall with bonuses and exciting excitement that you can play on your computer, phone or tablet!\n\nThis classic slot machine will make you spin non-stop all day and night! And it won't cost you a dollar, a penny, or a penny....! Spin your way to bonuses that grow as you play! Can you get 10x? Unwind on Slots Christmas and take a look!\n\nSlots Christmas is simple, free and fun. Just place a bet and then let the reels of slot machines spin! Maintain your winning streak with these online slots and you will earn brand new bonuses that will continue to multiply your winnings even more than ever! Win big and watch the slot machines go crazy with excitement!\n\nDon't waste your time stealing hundreds of bad slot machines online, just play the best with Slots Christmas!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60OTR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-slot/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IC1GE","slug":"cinderella-tile-slide-challenge","title":"Cinderella Tile Slide Challenge","description":"Welcome to Cinderella Tile Slide Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Cinderella Tile Slide Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Cinderella Tile Slide Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IC1GE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cinderella-tile-slide-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HCLCT","slug":"collect-the-rain","title":"Collect the Rain","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter autant de gouttes de pluie que possible. Pour déplacer le seau, cliquez avec le pointeur de la souris sur l`endroit où vous souhaitez déplacer le seau. Sur les appareils à écran tactile, appuyez sur l`écran avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HCLCT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/collect-the-rain/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TS56C","slug":"color-shot","title":"Color Shot","description":"Aim your color-specific ball at the correct color's radius, aim the ball back with your finger, and see how high a score you can get!\n\nPass the levels with colorful balls and enjoy the game.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TS56C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-shot/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LLLOA","slug":"color-wall-ball-flappy-ball","title":"Color Wall Ball - Flappy Ball","description":"Amazing and additive game to play, simple game to play with one touch only to jump the ball and match the correct color of the ball with the lines.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LLLOA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-wall-ball-flappy-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6EN7S","slug":"dinosaur-endless","title":"Dinosaur Endless","description":"Dinosaur Endless you must jump on spikes and make a score ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6EN7S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dinosaur-endless/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6M67O","slug":"dragon-memory-match","title":"Dragon Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Dragon Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Dragon Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Dragon Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6M67O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dragon-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5WOWO","slug":"droppy-tower","title":"Droppy Tower","description":"Construisez une tour en faisant tomber des blocs un par un ! Visez avec précision et empilez les blocs les uns sur les autres pour former le plus haut gratte-ciel ! Droppy Tower est un jeu simple mais passionnant et addictif qui divertira le joueur pendant des heures.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5WOWO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/droppy-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R30A1","slug":"emperor-constantine-memory-match","title":"Emperor Constantine Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Emperor Constantine Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Emperor Constantine Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Emperor Constantine Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R30A1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emperor-constantine-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2CT0Y","slug":"emperor-shah-jahan-memory-match","title":"Emperor Shah Jahan Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Emperor Shah Jahan Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Emperor Shah Jahan Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Emperor Shah Jahan Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2CT0Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emperor-shah-jahan-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18W98","slug":"fairy-woods-hidden-objects","title":"Fairy Woods Hidden Objects","description":"In this relaxing game the main goal is to find all the lost objects in the fairy Woods!\nThe only rule isthat You've thirty seconds of time to complete each level!\nSutable for everyone.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18W98/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-woods/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81C8R","slug":"fall-beans","title":"Fall Beans","description":"Fun and colorful races on different race areas await you in the Fall Beans game. The aim of the game is to advance in each race without being eliminated.\n\nControls : Use arrow keys to move and space key to jump on desktop.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81C8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cartoon-candy-match2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2AL2F","slug":"fallingman-io","title":"Fallingman.io","description":"Fallingman.io game is a fun game with colorful platforms. The aim of the Fallingman.io game is to reach the end point without falling. Show your skills in different maps and make moves at the right time to be the 1st! Each map is different from each other and therefore requires different skills. A game that can be played with fun awaits you","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2AL2F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fallingman/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9R182","slug":"fish-rescue-go-shark-attack","title":"Fish Rescue Go - Shark Attack","description":"🐟 Fish Rescue Go Survival : 🦈 Shark Attack.\nYou are alone in the ocean with an angry 🦈 shark.\nAvoid obstacles and 🐡 explosive fish, Go on your way and don't stop.\nDo your best to survive underwater and save you Little 🐟 fish.\nGo 🐟 fish and fond your way to survive.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9R182/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fish-rescue-go-shark-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A9OFA","slug":"flap-arrow","title":"Flap Arrow","description":"This is a hard game. Touch in the screen to make the Arrow fly high and pass through the pipes avoiding colliding with them. But be careful, because every time you fly you change the angle where the Arrow points, so to pass through the pipes you must do it with the corresponding symbol, but there are also cases where the symbol allows more than one angle.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A9OFA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flap-arrow/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21HWA","slug":"flappy-huggy-wuggy","title":"Flappy Huggy Wuggy","description":"In this game you can play with a Flappy Haggy Waggy! Just Tap to fly and try to pass across the robot poppy hands without touching them. Collect all medals and try to sign your personal highest score. Enjoy it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21HWA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-haggy-waggy/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"49299","slug":"flappy-jelly","title":"Flappy Jelly","description":"Avoid obstacles to level up, find fantastic treasures.  \nHelp the fish to swim among the obstacles and discover the interesting regions under the oceans and most importantly, survive as long as you can and beat world's best high score!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/49299/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-jelly/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0AY8N","slug":"flappycat-crazy-halloween","title":"FlappyCat Crazy Halloween","description":"Flappy Cat: Crazy Halloween is a game with little bit of horror theme. And\nkeeping the difficulty of other Flappy Cat games.\nFlappy Cat is back, and all dressed up for some Halloween fun game! Just like the other Flappy Cat games, your skill levels will be tested for this is a challenging game. Not just that, you will also have a tiny bit of horror thrown into the mix, to make things more exciting! Help Flappy Cat zoom back and forth, evade the Halloween tower and get the highest score!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0AY8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappycat-crazy-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA8B4","slug":"flipper-brick-mania","title":"Flipper Brick Mania","description":"Simple old school arcade fun with ball shooting Game, Pin Ball. Classic PinBall turned into breath taking Arcade mode with unlimited fun and excitement with Realistic Ball physics.\n\nKeep stacking the Balls by targeting '+' and get more score.\nMake sure you smash all the Blocks before it hits top","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA8B4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pinballbrickmania/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EG3E5","slug":"golden-move-quest","title":"Golden Move Quest","description":"Partez à la recherche de trésors dans ce captivant jeu de puzzle. Avec son élégant design doré et son gameplay stimulant, ce jeu vous tiendra en haleine pendant des heures. Faites glisser et combinez les gemmes colorées pour marquer des points, mais attention - à chaque mouvement que vous faites, une nouvelle rangée de gemmes apparaît.\n\nPour vous aider dans votre quête, vous avez accès à des power-ups, comprenant la possibilité de supprimer toutes les gemmes d'une couleur choisie, diviser une gemme en pièces séparées, supprimer toutes les gemmes d'une rangée sélectionnée, et même gagner un mouvement supplémentaire!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EG3E5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/golden-move-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6O6DU","slug":"golf-and-biliard-for-kids","title":"Golf and Biliard for Kids","description":"$48","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6O6DU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-and-round/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RR44C","slug":"grass-cutting-puzzle","title":"Grass Cutting Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Crazy Chicken Jump. Crazy Chicken Jump is a jumping puzzle game. In this game, you have move the chicken left and right to avoid the obstacle.  Crazy Chicken Jump contains tricky 30 levels. Play and have fun.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RR44C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-chicken-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17R02","slug":"harvy-runner","title":"Harvy Runner","description":"Harvy Runner is a non stop action running game where you have to keep Little Harvy safe while he collects stars.\nClear a safe path for Harv by destroying bombs, killing monsters, operating bridges and avoiding hazards. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17R02/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/harvy-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O49N0","slug":"haton-2","title":"Haton 2","description":"Haton 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect oranges while avoiding enemies, flying robots, spikes, and saws in order to reach the red flag which leads you to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\nThis is the second installment of the original Haton series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.         \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O49N0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/haton-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NEE01","slug":"jeno-the-big-eater","title":"Jeno the Big Eater","description":"Jeno The Big Eater is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the tasty cup cakes while avoiding the goblins, saws, spikes and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NEE01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jeno-the-big-eater/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0261I","slug":"jeno-the-big-eater-2","title":"Jeno the Big Eater 2","description":"Jeno The Big Eater 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the cup cakes while avoiding the Goblins, flying creatures, bullets, saws, spikes and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.       \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Jeno The Big Eater\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0261I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jeno-the-big-eater-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z5818","slug":"jezaa-2","title":"Jezaa 2","description":"Jezaa 2 is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as an anime girl who have to collect purple cubes while avoiding the monsters, flying creatures, their bullets, ground saws, lava, and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play with increasing difficulty. This is the second installment of the original 'Jezaa' series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z5818/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jezaa-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5AP41","slug":"jump-fast","title":"Jump Fast","description":"welcome to the fast jump game, you have to jump fast to pass the levels that will increase each level its speed","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5AP41/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-fast/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9B314","slug":"kazu-bot","title":"Kazu Bot","description":"Kazu Bot is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect all of the tablets containing confidential information related to technology, while avoiding the enemy bots, spikes, rotating saws and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9B314/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kazu-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7IMR0","slug":"king-henry-viii-memory-match","title":"King Henry VIII Memory Match","description":"Welcome to King Henry VIII Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn King Henry VIII Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to King Henry VIII Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7IMR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-henry-viii-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NI8LI","slug":"line-jumping-ball","title":"Line Jumping Ball","description":"A simple and fun game to play, with ball like jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NI8LI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-jumping-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4LIA7","slug":"little-kurama-sliding-image-adventure","title":"Little Kurama Sliding Image Adventure","description":"Welcome to Little Kurama Sliding Image Adventure, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Little Kurama Sliding Image Adventure, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Little Kurama Sliding Image Adventure and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4LIA7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-kurama-sliding-image-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6T61T","slug":"magic-forest-match","title":"Magic Forest Match","description":"\"Magic Forest Match\" est un jeu pour vous rafraîchir l'esprit, faisant référence aux jeux de genre \"match 3\". Vous devez collecter trois objets ou plus à la suite, horizontalement ou verticalement. Lorsque vous collectez plus de trois objets, vous obtenez un objet spécial avec des propriétés uniques, ce qui aide beaucoup dans le jeu. Vous ne pouvez modifier l'emplacement des éléments que s'ils se trouvent à proximité. Profitez de ce jeu intéressant et passionnant.\n\nAmusez-vous dans différents modes de jeu :\nInfinity : gameplay illimité, pas de mouvements, pas de limite de temps.\nAction : Plus de matchs, plus de temps. Évasion : faites exploser les évadés.\nAutomne : obtenez les étoiles de haut en bas.\nBloqueur : Détruisez tous les blocs sur le plateau","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6T61T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magic-forest-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ROY27","slug":"memorymatch","title":"MemoryMatch","description":"This game features three modes: leveled, relaxing and time attack.\n\nIn all modes, the stages have several parts, all of which must be done to finish the levels. In time attack mode, the player has 60 seconds, which will grant you extra time after solving each part. Also, the game’s goal in time attack mode is to achieve a higher score.\n\nIn addition to the mentioned features, the game has a combo system. The points are calculated with higher coefficients in case of faster solving speed.\n\nIn relaxing mode, the player has no time limit, and the cards are arranged infinitely. The game also features in-game hints that players can use to complete the levels.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ROY27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memorymatch/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66M91","slug":"miner-gokartcraft-4-player","title":"Miner GokartCraft - 4 Player","description":"hey dude, take all 4 of your friends and run away from the blue monster! Be careful while avoiding the monster, get the gold and reach the highest score. If the blue monster catches you, don't forget to eat you, everyone has to reach the door. If you can't reach the door, you can't win. Watch out for the thorns, the tire will burst and you will lose. Be careful don't forget the monsters are everywhere.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66M91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miner-gokartcraft-4-player/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6IJ3R","slug":"monkey-jigsaw","title":"Monkey Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Monkey Jigsaw Adventure! Our Monkey Jigsaw Adventure Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Monkey Jigsaw Adventure picture. With a wide variety of Monkey Jigsaw Adventure images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Monkey Jigsaw Adventure Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6IJ3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monkey-jigsaw-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0UO25","slug":"mousy-look","title":"Mousy Look","description":"Mousy Look is a 2D platform game where you need to collect cheese while avoiding mouse traps and spikes and reach the blue flag. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse WASD or arrow keys for movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0UO25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mousy-look/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ISAIB","slug":"mushrooms-jigsaw","title":"Mushrooms Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Mushrooms Jigsaw Block Blitz! Our Mushrooms Jigsaw Block Blitz Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Mushrooms Jigsaw Block Blitz picture. With a wide variety of Mushrooms Jigsaw Block Blitz images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Mushrooms Jigsaw Block Blitz Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ISAIB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mushrooms-jigsaw-block-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1H1O0","slug":"neon-pong","title":"Neon Pong","description":"Hit the neon ball as many times as possible.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1H1O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"REJ98","slug":"ninja-jump-xtreme","title":"Ninja Jump Xtreme","description":"Welcome to this cute 30-level ninja platform jumping game! Your task is to collect all the coins and exit the levels without hitting any spikes.\nThe ninja has already started his training. There are 30 levels in total, your task is to finish all these challenges and help the little cute ninja to become the most outstanding. Avoid all the obstacles on the road and enter the destination to open the next level. Have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/REJ98/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-jump-xtreme/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"59O35","slug":"noob-vs-guys","title":"Noob vs Guys","description":"noob guys welcome to the running race between noob and noob's friends. Don't fall down, if you fall, you'll start over. Nobody wants to start over. Are you ready for a race full of noobs? You must collect crowns to get noob costumes. You should be #1 in the noob guys race. you should be the winner of the race, you should buy the best costume.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/59O35/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-guys/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T468","slug":"oomee-pinata","title":"Oomee Pinata","description":"Smash open the fruit Piñatas for the happy Oomees.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T468/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/oomee-pi-ata/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B6R6O","slug":"otaho-bird-2","title":"Otaho Bird 2","description":"Otaho Bird 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as a bird who have to collect all of the slices of bread while avoiding the enemy birds, flying birds and their bullets, rotating blades, and fire and reach the nest in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.      \n      \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Otaho Bird\" series.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B6R6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/otaho-bird-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6P1A2","slug":"pick-a-color","title":"Pick a Color!","description":"Ready to get involved in a hardcore project? Then it's time to get started! The\ngame \"Pick a Color!\" - is a test of reaction, quick reads and high difficulty.\nIngenious in its simplicity, but at the same time quite difficult. You just need to get\non the different blocks with colors, depending on the color change of the ball\nitself. In the game you will find:\n- Increased difficulty\n- Improved physics\n- Beautiful visuals\nReady? Go for it!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6P1A2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pick-a-color/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"98830","slug":"pieces","title":"Pieces","description":"Shoot a particle of the same color as the ball","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/98830/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pieces/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6TIGC","slug":"psychological-horror-tile-picture-challenge","title":"Psychological Horror Tile Picture Challenge","description":"Welcome to Psychological horror Tile Picture Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Psychological horror Tile Picture Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Psychological horror Tile Picture Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6TIGC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/psychological-horror-tile-picture-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"QII78","slug":"quevi-2","title":"Quevi 2","description":"Quevi 2 is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect all of the metal balls while avoiding the enemy robots, flying robots, their bullets, rotating lasers, giant blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels with increasing difficulty.\nThis is the second installment of the original Quevi series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/QII78/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quevi-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3Z8Z4","slug":"quiz-math","title":"Quiz Math","description":"This is  Math Quiz\nA fully responsive full screen game, for children and for challenging adult brains.\nusing minimal flat design, for simply playing with comfort","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3Z8Z4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quiz-maths/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NSG3R","slug":"rgb-shooting-range","title":"RGB Shooting Range","description":"This game is simple shooting exercise. Shoot the falling color balls with their same color bullets. You can use arrows of keyboard or click the respective buttons to shoot the bullet.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NSG3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rgb-shooting-range/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69O69","slug":"red-boats","title":"Red Boats","description":"How to play\n• Tap the red boats to score points\n• White boats should pass\n• You get 3 Chances","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69O69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-boats/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"674OO","slug":"red-platformer","title":"Red Platformer","description":"Overcome the challenges and be careful not to fall","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/674OO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redplatform/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"707R0","slug":"rescue-dog","title":"Rescue Dog","description":"Hit the wall a certain number of times to decrease the number to 0 to unlock the door and then escape.\n\nChallenge yourself and train your brain To find the best way to pass.\n\n100 awesome levels to play.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/707R0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-dog/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66U1O","slug":"rotuman-2","title":"Rotuman 2","description":"Rotuman 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the golden keys while avoiding red and green enemies, flying creatures, spikes, and reach your house in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.      \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Rotuman\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66U1O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rotuman-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RD666","slug":"round-n-round","title":"Round N Round","description":"Try to resist the more You can!\nClick or Tap to swap the direction and destroy all enemies!\nEnjoy this cool casual game!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RD666/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-n-round/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NEN66","slug":"santa-runner-online","title":"Santa Runner Online","description":"Santa Runner - the online endless runner game that's perfect for gift collecting! With simple controls and addictive gameplay, Santa Runner is the perfect game for anyone who loves a challenge. Collect as many gifts as you can and see how far you can run!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NEN66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-runner-online/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IITTE","slug":"skibidi-toilet-minecraft-2023","title":"Skibidi Toilet Minecraft 2023","description":"A never seen before scary Skibidi Toilet for MCPE creature will appear in the middle of the village. They are called Skibidi Toilet survival mod for MCPE, creatures with scary shapes. Their bodies consist of a walking toilet, complete with an open toilet lid with a large Skibidi Toilet skin for mcpe head poking out between the holes. Their faces were filled with devilish smiles and burning eyes. Skibidi toilet for mcpe adonss maps residents panicked and tried to escape. They run along the road of the village of Skibidi Toilet mobs event mcpe, looking for a place to hide. However, the scary Skibidi Toilet mod for mcpe skins continues to catch ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IITTE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hunt-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2E264","slug":"skull-jump","title":"Skull Jump","description":"Skull Jumper Game, a single-touch jumping reaction game, has everything you need to make your next app store hit!\nUse your skills and agility to survive by jumping over obstacles and avoid getting hit; just tap the screen and makeup to three jumps before touching the ground again.\nAvoid the dangerous obstacles or your Skull will death and the game will be over!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2E264/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/amzing-jumper/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69YSO","slug":"sky-color","title":"Sky Color","description":"Sky Color Is an Online Game Where You Have to Match the Color of the Sky.. \n \nDo you like playing online games? If so, then you will love Sky Color. This game is all about matching the color of the sky. You can play it on your computer or smartphone. The game is easy to learn and fun to play. It is great for kids and adults alike.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69YSO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-color-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LEG6I","slug":"sleeping-unicorn","title":"Sleeping Unicorn","description":"Sleeping Unicorn is an online game that is free to play. The objective of the game is to help the sleeping unicorn wake up by collecting pillows and avoiding obstacles. Our new sleeping unicorn game is the perfect way to wind down and relax. It's free to play and you can enjoy it for as long as you like. If you're looking for a fun, easygoing game that you can escape into, this is it!\n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LEG6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sleeping-unicorn/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M376E","slug":"slime-matching","title":"Slime Matching","description":"Slime Matching is an online game that challenges players to match colors. The game is simple but addicting, and it's a great way to kill time. Slime Matching Online is a game that tests your color-matching skills. The goal of the game is to match as many colors as possible in order to win. Looking for a fun and challenging online game? Look no further than Slime Matching! In this game, you must match colors as quickly and accurately as possible. With multiple levels to choose from, there's a challenge for everyone. So get matching today and see if you can become the ultimate Slime Matching champion!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M376E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slime-matching/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R8IR8","slug":"slipperball","title":"Slipperball","description":"The goal of the game is to deftly control the slipper to throw the ball into the basket.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R8IR8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slipperball/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"38CL2","slug":"space-ball-invaders","title":"Space Ball Invaders","description":"Classic spaceinvaders","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/38CL2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-ball-invaderes/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I7767","slug":"stacking-wood","title":"Stacking Wood","description":"When the wood moves to the top of the pile, press the button to place the wood, aligning the wood as much as possible.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I7767/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stacking-wood/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P18YP","slug":"tappy-plane","title":"Tappy Plane","description":"Préparez-vous à prendre votre envol avec Tappy Plane ! Naviguez à travers des obstacles dangereux et atteignez de nouveaux sommets dans ce jeu addictif et passionnant. Avec des commandes simples à une touche, Tappy Plane est facile à prendre en main mais difficile à maîtriser. Jusqu’où pouvez-vous voler?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P18YP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tappy-plane/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENN7T","slug":"tenno","title":"Tenno","description":"Tenno is a 2D platformer where you play as an employee called Tenno who have to collect important office papers which got stolen by your office rivals. While collecting them you have to avoid your enemy rivals, saws, spikes and reach your office door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENN7T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tenno/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AALAI","slug":"the-addams-family-perfect-fit-jigsaw","title":"The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw! Our The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw picture. With a wide variety of The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our The Addams Family Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AALAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-addams-family-perfect-fit-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0U17","slug":"the-jump","title":"The Jump","description":"Welcome to Jumper Jam, have fun jumping from one rain to another collecting coins and sprinting enemies, immerse yourself in the adventure, Will you be grateful to get to the stars? What are you waiting for?? Go play Jumper Jam now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0U17/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2PITT","slug":"tic-tac-toe-2-player-xox","title":"Tic Tac Toe 2 Player - XOX","description":"Play the classic Tic-Tac-Toe game (XOX) for free online with two players.\n\nThe game is played on a grid that's 3 squares by 3 squares.\nThe first player to get 3 of her marks in a row (up, down, across, or diagonally) is the winner.\nWhen all 9 squares are full, the game is over. If no player has 3 marks in a row, the game ends in a tie.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2PITT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tic-tac-toe-2-player-xox/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7LFC","slug":"traffic-lights-jigsaw-picture-puzzle","title":"Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle! Our Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Traffic Lights Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7LFC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/traffic-lights-jigsaw-picture-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"625N2","slug":"tunko-2","title":"Tunko 2","description":"Tunko 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the grapes while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, spikes, and saws and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Tunko\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/625N2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tunko-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E10WS","slug":"wooden-jewels","title":"Wooden Jewels","description":"Wooden Jewels is a fun and beautiful 3-in-a-row style game with a lot of exciting levels and beautiful graphics.\nYour mission sounds easy: collect all the magic potion made of jewels by creating lines of 3 or more of the same kind and color. Styles are different and the clock is ticking. Can you manage to complete the level before the time runs.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E10WS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wooden-jewels/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0D50D","slug":"wordle-food","title":"Wordle Food","description":"This is a real yoga for the brain, meditation for the mind and vocabulary development — and all this in an easily accessible game that can be played at any age! The theme is food!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0D50D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wordle-food/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71RWW","slug":"words-spy-human-body","title":"Words Spy Human body","description":"Train your visual memory in a playful way. Look for words for a time. The theme is the human body!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71RWW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/words-spy/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R1P14","slug":"words-spy-animals","title":"Words Spy. Animals","description":"Train visual logic in a playful way. Look for words for a while. The theme is ANIMALS!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R1P14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/words-spy-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"694ST","slug":"yatosan-2","title":"Yatosan 2","description":"Yatosan 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect the slices of cheese while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, spikes, ground saws and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 challenging levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Yatosan\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/694ST/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yatosan-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O7357","slug":"zaho-bot","title":"Zaho Bot","description":"Zaho Bot is a Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as a robot who have to collect all of the flasks containing red chemical solution while avoiding the enemy bots, flying bots and their bullets, rotating lasers, giant blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O7357/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zaho-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9O64R","slug":"cross-fire-pvsp-2-player","title":"Cross Fire - PvsP 2 Player","description":"Cross fire is a 2D pixel game for 2 players, based on fighting with swords, in which you will be able to face your friend in fun pvp duels, where you will be able to perform both physical and long-range attacks with the aim of defeating your opponent as much as necessary to be able to cross between levels, ending in the round or level 3 that will determine the winner.","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9O64R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cross-fire/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NI9LB","slug":"lions-jigsaw-jigsaw","title":"Lions Jigsaw Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Lions Jigsaw Tile Scramble! Our Lions Jigsaw Tile Scramble Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Lions Jigsaw Tile Scramble picture. With a wide variety of Lions Jigsaw Tile Scramble images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Lions Jigsaw Tile Scramble Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NI9LB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lions-jigsaw-tile-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4D664","slug":"mad-car","title":"Mad Car","description":"Here is a great arcade game of the famous Car web game, formatted to work on mobile devices. Have Fun!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4D664/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mad-car/embed?sid=1","plays":40221,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"734L0","slug":"brickball","title":"Brickball","description":"brick ball accumulates points, speed will be a problem?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/734L0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brikball/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C51N4","slug":"candy-match-blitz","title":"Candy Match Blitz","description":"Candy Match Blitz is a puzzle game in which you have to line up three or more matching candy's to pop them. You only have a limited amount of time each on level to collect the right candy's and complete the level objectives.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C51N4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-match-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4F13T","slug":"fix-it-gear-puzzle-game","title":"Fix it Gear Puzzle Game","description":"Fix It Gear Puzzle game is a science fiction style puzzle. If you love hi tech, or love sci-fi, or love puzzle Fix It Gear Puzzle game will be your favorite.\n\nIt is easy to learn: only need link all gears. But higher levels have more gears, it is difficult to put them in right place.\n\nMove a given gear and connect all the stationary gears.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4F13T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fix-it-gear-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IEI34","slug":"kid-mermaids-coloring","title":"Kid Mermaids Coloring","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Kid Mermaids game! Whether you're a fan of Kid Mermaids or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Kid Mermaids images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Kid Mermaids masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IEI34/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kid-mermaids/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NNE44","slug":"red-alien","title":"Red Alien","description":"red alien is arcade game 2023","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NNE44/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-alien/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MM968","slug":"super-mushroom-game","title":"Super Mushroom Game","description":"The Super Mushroom is a classic arcade platformer game that you can now enjoy online! Super Mushroom is an online platformer game that is perfect for anyone who loves a challenge. With multiple levels to play through, this game will keep you entertained for hours on end. The best part about Super Mushroom is that it is completely free to play!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MM968/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-mushroom/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GO79N","slug":"dual-control-racing","title":"Dual Control Racing","description":"Control the cars and try to reach the Finish line. Easy to play Hard to master.\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GO79N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dual-control-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40220,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HMELY","slug":"master-checkers-multiplayer","title":"Master Checkers Multiplayer","description":"\"Master Checkers Multiplayer is a HTML5 Board Game.\n \nEnjoy this stylish version of the classic Checkers Game.\n \n3 Game’s Mode:\n \n - Multiplayer mode;\n \n - Play against the pc;\n \n - Challenge a friend playing on the same device;\"","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HMELY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/master-checkers-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40219,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"367YE","slug":"goose-game-multiplayer","title":"Goose Game Multiplayer","description":"Goose Game Multiplayer is a HTML5 Board Game. \nEnjoy this funny version of the classic Goose Game. \n3 Game’s Mode: \n- Multiplayer mode \n- Play against the pc \n- Challenge a friend playing on the same device","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/367YE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goose-game-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40218,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"55095","slug":"jungle-runner","title":"Jungle Runner","description":"Use your mouse to jump and slide through the jungle. Click to jump, swipe right to slide, and swipe down to drop. You can roll past enemies, or jump on top of them. Spend your gems in between rounds to buy powerful upgrades","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/55095/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jungle-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40218,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J6B16","slug":"jellybears","title":"Jellybears","description":"Differently colored bears want to have some fun with you! They are made of delicious jelly and want to be eaten! There’s just one rule - you can only eat jelly bears of one color at a time, and there have to be at least two. There’s a goal of how many bears you need to collect on each level, and limited number of moves per level. How many levels would you be able to complete? Have some jelly fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J6B16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jellybears/embed?sid=1","plays":40218,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71NRN","slug":"minesweeper-mania","title":"Minesweeper Mania","description":"Révélez toutes les mines le plus rapidement possible ! Ce jeu de puzzle classique au gameplay passionnant peut améliorer votre logique et votre vitesse de réaction. Relevez le défi en essayant des niveaux encore plus difficiles ! Vous pouvez également personnaliser les niveaux, changer de thème ou même avoir recours à des indices.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade","board","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71NRN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minesweeper-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40215,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9IAI9","slug":"break-the-ice","title":"Break the Ice","description":"Hi,everyone.Ready for an icy challenge...\nWell,you need to break the ice as long as you can.\nCan you do it?\nI bet you can't.\nThe controls:\n\"C\"-To reset ice cube(Pressed when ice cube's HP become 0)\n\"Spacebar\" or \"left-click\" on your mouse-To break the ice\n\"S\"-To collect coins(Pressed only once either before the ice cube's HP reached 0 or after the ice cube's HP reached 0","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9IAI9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/break-the-ice/embed?sid=1","plays":40214,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NP2CL","slug":"doodlepac","title":"DoodlePac","description":"Pacman 2 - Doodle Game Version - ONLY FOR PC\nThis is the old pacman game known all over the world, a bit modified with new characters and assets to discover!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NP2CL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pacman-2-only-for-pc/embed?sid=1","plays":40213,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"86486","slug":"noob-vs-hacker-2-player","title":"Noob vs Hacker - 2 Player","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of noob and hacker? They will go through a very dangerous road in their adventure and they have to be friends by force. you should imitate their friendship because they are actually enemies but they will pretend to be friends and become friends together to form a portal in the dangerous forest and escape. The hacker can carry the noob so the noob can reach anywhere. Thanks to the hacker, collect all the diamonds with your friend.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/86486/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-hacker-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":40213,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1693B","slug":"zombie-attack","title":"Zombie Attack","description":"Are you ready for the Zombie Attack?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1693B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-attack-1/embed?sid=1","plays":40213,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1BOO1","slug":"bloom-me","title":"Bloom Me!","description":"Choose one of the correct answers that you have been given and click on it. Thus, collect the word BINGO in one of the rows. And move on to the next, more difficult task.\n\nReach the final level with the most lives and more points!\n\nWaiting for you:\n- Beautiful graphics\n- Nice sound effects\n- Relaxing gameplay","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1BOO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bloom-me/embed?sid=1","plays":40212,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6G3OF","slug":"frog-jumping-on-clouds","title":"Frog - Jumping on Clouds","description":"The goal of the game is to help the frog fulfill his dream and reach the stars. To substitute a cloud for the frog to jump, simply click the mouse pointer in the right place on the screen. On touch screens, all of these actions must be performed with your finger.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6G3OF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-jumping-on-clouds/embed?sid=1","plays":40212,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SPSS6","slug":"horses-puzzle-quest","title":"Horses Puzzle quest","description":"Welcome to Horses Puzzle quest, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Horses Puzzle quest, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Horses Puzzle quest and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SPSS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horses-puzzle-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":40212,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CLCP1","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-flower","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Flower","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CLCP1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-flower/embed?sid=1","plays":40212,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R6S74","slug":"soccer-score","title":"Soccer Score","description":"FIFA Score is an online football penalty game that is perfect for fans of the sport looking to improve their skills. The game features real-life football players, so you can test your abilities against some of the best in the business. With a variety of modes to choose from, including single-player and multiplayer, there is something for everyone. So get out there and start shooting some goals!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R6S74/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fifa-score/embed?sid=1","plays":40212,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11TH5","slug":"light-hit","title":"Light Hit","description":"Light Hit is a very active arcade / puzzle game that uses the old breakout game with a moden touch. Enjoy 100s of levels at your finger tips.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11TH5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/light-hit/embed?sid=1","plays":40211,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3PB92","slug":"push-the-block","title":"Push the block","description":"The goal is to push the blocks into their designated craters using the different machines, but in this tricky puzzle game, nothing is as simple as it seems. Even though the game starts off simple, the more levels you complete, the more complex the game gets.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3PB92/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/push-the-block/embed?sid=1","plays":40211,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NI6LH","slug":"handless-millionaire","title":"Handless Millionaire","description":"Welcome to the game \"Handless Millionaire\" (Handless-Millionaire) — play online in a TV show for fans of quick money. This is the craziest remake of the quiz \"Oh, lucky!\", where everyone who wants to become a millionaire gets a chance to get rich. Only instead of the right answers, you need to have time to grab the money before the sharp blade of the guillotine falls on your hand.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NI6LH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/handless-millionaire/embed?sid=1","plays":40210,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40355","slug":"calming-lia","title":"Calming Lia","description":"Sauvez une petite fille de ses cauchemars! Calming Lia est un jeu mobile relaxant, gratuit, de type match 3 Comme une berceuse, il vaut mieux y jouer le soir avant de dormir. Aidez Lia et son ami Bao l’ours en peluche et sauvez ses rêves des horreurs du terrible croque-mitaine!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40355/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/calming-lia/embed?sid=1","plays":40210,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MER6E","slug":"classic-klondike-solitaire","title":"Classic Klondike Solitaire","description":"\"Classic Klondike Solitaire Card Game\" is one of the oldest and most addictive solitaire card games. It is played with a single 52 playing cards. The object of the game is to order all of the cards into the deck’s four suits (diamonds, clubs, hearts, spades) and to do so in ascending order, from ace to king.","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MER6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-klondike-solitaire-card-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6C66G","slug":"escape-girl","title":"Escape Girl","description":"escape girl is a html5 top down game, walk and avoid obstacle, collect treasure to earn score","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6C66G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-girl/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O523A","slug":"hana-bot","title":"Hana Bot","description":"Hana Bot is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as a bot who have to collect all of the test tubes while avoiding the enemy bots, flying bots, giant blades, and spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O523A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hana-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"422O4","slug":"kara-food-drop","title":"Kara - Food Drop","description":"Mangez autant de nourriture que vous le pouvez et n'en gaspillez aucune !\nVous êtes un petit (mais gros !) mignon poulet incapable de voler qui a faim et qui a besoin de manger autant qu'il le peut ! Mais parce que tu ne peux pas voler, tu dois marcher sur le sol et ramasser les aliments qui tombent du ciel. Personne ne sait qui laisse tomber cette nourriture, il suffit de la manger et de ne poser aucune question ! Mais faites attention car il y a aussi d'autres objets parmi ces aliments et s'ils vous frappent, vous perdrez. Alors faites de votre mieux et mangez autant que vous le pouvez.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/422O4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kara-food-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8H6GO","slug":"mah-jong-fish-world","title":"Mah Jong Fish World","description":"Mahjong Fish World is a challenging and fun underwater runner game. Players control a fish as they swim through a series of levels, matching mahjong tiles to remove them from the board. As players progress, they will encounter a variety of obstacles, including sharks, jellyfish, and coral reefs. Players must use their skills to avoid these obstacles and collect as many stars as possible.\nThe game features a variety of levels, each with its own unique challenges. Players can also compete against their friends for the highest score. \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8H6GO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-fish-world/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"07WWK","slug":"mr-kaw-2","title":"Mr Kaw 2","description":"Mr Kaw 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect the golden coins while avoiding the enemies, flying robots and spikes and reach the exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the some of the levels are really challenging and hard to master.\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Mr Kaw\" game.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/07WWK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-kaw-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6TTT3","slug":"one-dot-ball","title":"One Dot Ball","description":"Shooter the correct ball to get the score, and do not miss the ball to get fail","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6TTT3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-dot-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A28I2","slug":"valentines-day-adventures","title":"Valentines Day Adventures","description":"Valentines Day Adventures is a 2D Platform Game where you need to collect Chocolate bars and bring them over to your girlfriend while avoiding saws and Love eater enemies! There are 8 levels to play with increasing difficulty.\n\nControls:\n\"WASD\" or \"Arrow keys\" for movement.    \nPress \"W\" or \"Up arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A28I2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/valentines-day-adventures/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C36TK","slug":"village-attack","title":"Village Attack!","description":"Conquer all enemy villages and homes, earn special skills, and make your army reign!\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C36TK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vilagge-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40209,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6SI3T","slug":"super-droid-adventure","title":"Super Droid Adventure","description":"Super Droid Adventure is an arcade game where you help the little Robot to defeat a powerful boss that has destroyed his castle. During your journey, you'll encounter different traps and dangerous enemies that will try to stop you from reaching your goal. Break blocks to find power-ups, coins and other surprises. Use firepower to make the job easier and good luck!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6SI3T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-droid-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40208,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6616N","slug":"compassion","title":"Compassion","description":"welcome to compassion game","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6616N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/compassion/embed?sid=1","plays":40208,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40129","slug":"the-best-pizza","title":"The Best Pizza","description":"Vous aimez les pizzas et les garnitures copieuses? Faites comme Ezzy, une jeune chef spécialiste de la pizza, et créez vos pizzas préférées : les classiques Pizzas à l'italienne, Hawaïenne et bien d'autres encore. Apprenez grâce à Ezzy et préparez ensemble les meilleures pizzas au monde!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40129/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-best-pizza/embed?sid=1","plays":40207,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6S015","slug":"jewel-dash","title":"Jewel Dash","description":"Essayez ce jeu de puzzle de séries de 3 unique et amusant. Progressez tout au long du jeu et débloquez différents bonus. Relevez divers défis pour débloquer des skins pour vos gemmes.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6S015/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":40207,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I12EI","slug":"pearl-impact","title":"Pearl Impact","description":"This game is about an adventurer, who has the power to throw magic pearls, his goal is to complete all levels","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I12EI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pearl-impact/embed?sid=1","plays":40207,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40301","slug":"yeti-sensation","title":"Yeti Sensation","description":"Bigfoot wanted! Help the embarrassed Yeti find a way to his new home, avoid sly snowmen, dangerous traps and other obstacles, buy new boosts in the supermarket and run away as further as possible!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40301/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yeti-sensation/embed?sid=1","plays":40204,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MN751","slug":"mind-the-fall","title":"Mind the Fall","description":"Make the player land on the platform safely and collect diamonds for bonuses. Game picks up the pace slowly so watch out.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MN751/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mind-the-fall/embed?sid=1","plays":40203,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6DCSD","slug":"medical-shop-cash-register-drug-store","title":"Medical Shop - Cash Register Drug Store","description":"Hey Guys! We have come up with a medical shop game. So are you ready to handle the drug store?\nIn this game, you need to maintain a medical shop. Give the required medicines to the patients and take the cash from them.\nThere will be a number of medicines for different illnesses and the affected body parts. Give patients the exact prescribed medicine,\nget more coins by upgrading the medicine's quality and unlock all the medicines. So do play this addictive drugstore game and don't forget to share with your friends and family.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6DCSD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/medical-shop-cash-register-drug-store/embed?sid=1","plays":40203,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T366T","slug":"stoke-boxes","title":"Stoke Boxes","description":"Control the bridge by stacking one box on top of another without leaving too much on the edge or falling over.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T366T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stoke-boxes/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2045B","slug":"2048-bears","title":"2048 Bears","description":"Welcome to 2048 Bears, have fun in this fantastic game where you will have to try to join the same pairs to increase their number, score as many points as possible and increase your bestscore, what are you waiting for?? Go play 2048 Bears now and have fun!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2045B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-bears/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1A1A6","slug":"blockman-climb-2-player","title":"Blockman Climb 2 Player","description":"Reach the flag at the finish line with the block men in the block world. Do your best to survive in the block world and go to the finish together, do not go to the finish line alone! This is a team game, complete the level with your friend. spin the hammer, climb the walls and win the game. Overcome all the challenges to win, watch out for the thorns and never, ever fall from the abyss or you will lose.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1A1A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blockman-climb/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6L5A0","slug":"bullet-ball","title":"Bullet Ball","description":"Welcome to Bulletball, have fun with your game ball by touching all the various scores and increasing your bestscore, what are you waiting for? Go play Center ball now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6L5A0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullet-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58056","slug":"fuuta-2","title":"Fuuta 2","description":"Fuuta 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the lipsticks while avoiding all of the single-eyed enemy monsters and their bullets, flying monsters, pins and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Fuuta\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58056/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fuuta-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"57HL1","slug":"glamour-beachlife","title":"Glamour #BeachLife","description":"Looking for that perfect summer girl look? You're lucky because this dress-up game will give you all the stylish ideas you need to turn any beach trip into a girly-girl fashion show. Get it started and have a blast discovering how to integrate your chic swimsuits into casual and glamorous beach looks! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/57HL1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glamour-beachlife/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4H2L8","slug":"hoolo-2","title":"Hoolo 2","description":"Hoolo 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the potato chips packets while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, their bullets, ground saws,spikes and reach the green flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Hoolo\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4H2L8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hoolo-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2176R","slug":"monster-jumper","title":"Monster Jumper","description":"monster jumper is game arcade","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2176R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-jumper/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4EOO7","slug":"neochaos-2-player-game","title":"NeoChaos - 2 Player Game","description":"NeoChaos is a sci-fi local multiplayer gun fighting game that takes place in a dystopian future. In this game, players take on the role of fierce warriors, each equipped with high-tech weapons and abilities, battling it out in intense gun fights in futuristic arenas, so grab your weapon, gear up, and get ready for the ultimate showdown in this gun fighting game !","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4EOO7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neochaos/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AOAY4","slug":"queen-victoria-memory-match","title":"Queen Victoria Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Queen Victoria Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Queen Victoria Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Queen Victoria Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AOAY4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/queen-victoria-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C44TI","slug":"quick-target","title":"Quick Target","description":"Play against the time in this challenging game \"Quick Target\".    \nYou have 30 seconds for doing as many points as you can.    \nHit blue - orange targets for extra time.    \nTry to aim the center for higher points    \nAvoid hitting danger skull.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C44TI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quick-target/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"75261","slug":"rajuchan-2","title":"Rajuchan 2","description":"Rajuchan 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect all of the gold coins while avoiding the green and purple enemies, flying monsters, spikes and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Rajuchan\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/75261/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rajuchan-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OYXYE","slug":"steve-alex-spooky-2-player","title":"Steve Alex Spooky - 2 Player","description":"hey you have to escape from big scary and dangerous ghost in scary halloween. Never stop, the ghost is coming after you, it wants to eat you. Collect all the candies and buy yourself beautiful costumes. Never be defeated to be the best.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys  \n*Double Jump available  \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OYXYE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-alex-spooky-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"858D4","slug":"tanks-2d-battle-with-ratte","title":"Tanks 2D Battle with Ratte","description":"Destroy enemy tanks and equipment!\nChoose a tank, pump it up, be ready for battle.\nCause a bomb attack on enemy tanks.\nFight the Mega Boss Ratte.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/858D4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tanks-2d/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"563O3","slug":"utoo","title":"Utoo","description":"Utoo is a 2D platformer where you have to collect the blue cubes while avoiding enemies, saws and spikes and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and it is moderately difficult.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.        \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/563O3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/utoo/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8333O","slug":"utoo-2","title":"Utoo 2","description":"Utoo 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect blue cubes while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, saws and spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.           \nThis is the second installment of the original Utoo series. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.           \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8333O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/utoo-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C1191","slug":"vangers-cx-multiplayer","title":"Vangers CX multiplayer","description":"This is the community eXperiment (CX) mod version of Vangers playable in multiplayer!\nVangers CX is the mind-altering sandbox game that can be described as a racing role-playing adventure game with a complicated storyline. You’ll find a unique atmosphere, complete freedom and lots of gameplay hours to figure out what’s the game is all about.","category":"Aventure","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C1191/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vangers-cx/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y1OUD","slug":"wedding-beauty-makeup-salon-indian-designer","title":"Wedding Beauty Makeup Salon - Indian Designer","description":"Are you ready to help an Indian girl to look beautiful for her wedding like a princess? If yes, play this Indian Designer Sarees Fashion Salon For Wedding game and perform tons of makeover activities and make this girl looks like Princess. In this Indian fashion salon game, start with spa salon treatments and do hair makeover, wash her hair by using shampoo to make it smooth & silky Makeover.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y1OUD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wedding-beauty-makeup-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":40201,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E3U53","slug":"squid-puzzle","title":"Squid Puzzle","description":"Squid Puzzle Game is a free online game from genre of puzzle and jigsaw games. You can select one of the 12 images and then select one of the three modes: easy with 25 pieces, medium with 49 pieces and hard with 100 pieces. Have fun and enjoy!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E3U53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40200,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61A8N","slug":"hanged","title":"Hanged","description":"Welcome to Hanged, have fun guessing the secret numbers and climbing the leaderboard, what are you waiting for ???? Go play Hanged now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61A8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hanged/embed?sid=1","plays":40200,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"79PM4","slug":"atmosphere","title":"atmoSphere","description":"HOW CAN I PLAY:\n-Your goal is to make as many points as you can by destroying as few bounces as possible\n\nCONTROLS:\n-SwipeTouch: MovementSphere\n\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/79PM4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/atmosphere/embed?sid=1","plays":40200,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R763G","slug":"galaxy-crush","title":"Galaxy Crush","description":"A game designed to entertain and remind, for all lovers of old-fashioned video games here is Galaxy Crush.\nWith a simple tap on the meteorites you will help the UFO avoid a horrible end, play with your friends and become the hero of the galaxy! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R763G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-crush/embed?sid=1","plays":40199,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SO82U","slug":"colors-run-ball","title":"Colors Run Ball","description":"touch the squares to change the color of the circle as the same as the ball to get the score, if not the same color you failed","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SO82U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colors-run-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40198,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N17RB","slug":"mcparkour-noob-noob-baby","title":"MCParkour Noob & Noob Baby","description":"In 3d two player mc parkour you have to help two friends reach the finish line. In this game played for two players, you must reach the finish by overcoming serious difficulties. You have to run safely to the finish with noob player and baby noob player. Run dont stop and dont fall into the lava If you fall into the lava you will die! All you have to do is play with your friend and reach the finish.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N17RB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mcparkour-noob-and-noob-baby/embed?sid=1","plays":40198,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40265","slug":"candy-slingshot","title":"Candy SlingShot","description":"Tap, drag and aim to shoot down candy of all kinds. Collect stars to increase your chance to go to the next level. Collect bonus items to destroy more candy and get more points. Be careful, not all items are friendly, and will take your life.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40265/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-slingshot/embed?sid=1","plays":40197,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4I265","slug":"muscle-run-io","title":"Muscle Run io","description":"Collect your own color dumbbell and Build up your body !!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4I265/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/muscle-run-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40196,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40237","slug":"katana-fruits","title":"Katana Fruits","description":"Katana Fruits is a new slicing game in which you have to slice every fruit and avoid bombs. Missing a fruit will cost you a life and hitting one of the bombs will end the game immediately. Do you have good reaction skills?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40237/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/katana-fruits/embed?sid=1","plays":40195,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N5O10","slug":"noob-vs-tnt-boom","title":"Noob vs TNT Boom","description":"Help the beloved noob capture the spell and bring the chest down to the floor! Let the crate land on the floor and be safe. The noob needs those who will come out of the chest that opens as soon as it touches the floor. noob will never stop be careful when you blow up the tnts or you may forget the chest forever. Help keep the chest safe. Are you always ready to use noob magic?","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N5O10/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-tnt-boom/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O44E4","slug":"asteroids","title":"ASTEROIDS","description":"this game is a copy of the asteroids arcade game. You are a spaceship who has to shoot and dodge asteroids to collect scores","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O44E4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asteroids/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8TIRP","slug":"fruit-jump","title":"Fruit Jump","description":"fruit jump is an html5 arcade game, jump over the board and get fruit for a high score be careful avoid the spiked board or you will die.\nnote : touch the screen left or right to move ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8TIRP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T4114","slug":"mathtest21","title":"MathTest21","description":"A new simple math app. Guess the result.\nCheck your calculation skills with this simple app","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T4114/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mathtest21/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NE96I","slug":"halloween-dentist","title":"Halloween Dentist","description":"These Monster have been eating way too much of their candy and need to have their teeth cleaned!\n\nThese Monster have been eating way too much of their candy and need to have their teeth cleaned!\n\nSo use six different dentist tools to help these monsters get back their healthy smiles.\n\nKey Features:\n- 18 different Halloween monsters!\n- Keeps everyone occupied for a long time!\n- The perfect app for this Halloween season!\n\nCan you help all Monsters?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NE96I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-dentist/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40288","slug":"iceberg","title":"Iceberg","description":"Click the shapes that are hanging frozen in the air to unfreeze them. Then gravity will do its work, so you will need to think about the correct order. Have fun with Iceberg, a new physics game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40288/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/iceberg/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7L207","slug":"tower-defense-the-last-realm","title":"Tower Defense - The Last Realm","description":"Tower Defense: The Last Realm includes game modes with specific characteristics, which is a big challenge for Defenders. This is the best game for those who are fans of tower defense games. \nAnd you can enjoy 40 levels with 3 levels of difficulty for players to conquer.\n\nIn tower defense: The Last Realm, there are 7 basic pillars including archer, magic, poison, rocket launcher, gunmen, cannoneer, and thunder. \nTower systems can also be upgraded to 4 levels, with extremely interesting features of defense. \nTower defense: The Last Realm will  bring many new and exciting mission games. Quick hand load and fight!","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7L207/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-defense-the-last-realm/embed?sid=1","plays":40194,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MH1N7","slug":"marshmello-monster","title":"Marshmello Monster","description":"Imagine you are a cute marshmello and you have to reach the finish line. start from the beginning and reach the finish line within the given time. pass many different levels.\n\nHow to Play?\nArrow keys & Mobile touch control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MH1N7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/marshmello-monster/embed?sid=1","plays":40193,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"97979","slug":"slimoban","title":"Slimoban","description":"Slimoban is a variation  of sokoban with slimes. But besides the boxes that you need to move, there are also monsters you can escape from or destroy with a fireball or by throwing them into the water. There are three types of slimes in the game: the green ones just stand still, they cannot be destroyed with a fireball, but they can be pushed into the water. Blue slimes chase the main character and they can be destroyed with a fireball and thrown into the water just like the green ones. Red slimes chase you and they can only be pushed in the water.\n\nFireballs can also move blocks. If blocks fall into the water they destroy both the water and themselves. Some slimes do the same, others just get drowned. Fireball magic bottles and keys can sink as well.\nThe game has 30 levels.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/97979/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slimoban/embed?sid=1","plays":40192,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UC3R6","slug":"besties-summer-vacation","title":"Besties Summer Vacation","description":"In this cute game Besties Summer Vacation, Princess is planning for a cute summer vacation. They decided to arrange a trip to the beach with their old van. But they need some expert help to choose a cute makeup and perfect trip outfit. And also they need some help to modify and decorate their old van. Come and join our princesses and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UC3R6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/besties-summer-vacation/embed?sid=1","plays":40192,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4423N","slug":"danger-land","title":"Danger Land","description":"danger land is an html5 arcade game, jump and avoid falling objects to get a high score ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4423N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/danger-land/embed?sid=1","plays":40190,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7T6L","slug":"little-yellow-tank-adventure","title":"Little Yellow Tank Adventure","description":"Little Yellow Tank Adventure is super fun online game for kids that you can play for free on PC and mobile. No downloads required to play! Drive around with our cute little yellow tank and find a parking spot to park. In some levels you need to find a key or find a way out of a maze to be able to park. Play around and have fun.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7T6L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-yellow-tank-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40190,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U8161","slug":"multyarmy","title":"MultyArmy","description":"Play tank multiplayer, kill your enemies move with arrows and shoot with mouse","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U8161/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/multyarmy/embed?sid=1","plays":40189,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K7101","slug":"kite-kittens","title":"Kite Kittens","description":"Cute kittens flying on the kites through a magical land. Try not to hit the clouds (they are quite hard y'know?) and collect as much wool as you can. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K7101/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kite-kittens/embed?sid=1","plays":40187,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M1AAH","slug":"math-battle","title":"Math Battle","description":"A fun math game where the player exercises his knowledge and still fights a battle between dinosaurs. Perfect game to encourage children’s desire to study, she needs to get the answers right to win the battle.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M1AAH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40187,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A97WR","slug":"robocar-jigsaw","title":"Robocar Jigsaw","description":"Robocar Jigsaw is a free online game from genre of puzzle and jigsaw games. You can select one of the 12 images and then select one of the three modes: easy with 25 pieces, medium with 49 pieces and hard with 100 pieces. Have fun and enjoy!","category":"Course","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A97WR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robocar-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":40187,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8RC27","slug":"chibi-hero","title":"Chibi Hero","description":"Adventure game where little Chibi Hero must cross the shadow valley where he meets many challenges. Collect all stars to achieve a high score in each level. The game features 30 levels that will challenge you to beat it. The designs are very colorful and beautiful!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8RC27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chibi-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40186,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L9E62","slug":"color-merger","title":"Color Merger","description":"Hit the cube with same color wall before the time run out.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L9E62/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-merger/embed?sid=1","plays":40186,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6T8E1","slug":"gone-batty","title":"Gone Batty","description":"Help our friend Batty to get as high as he can, avoiding the enemies on the way and collecting as many coins as possible.\nThe aim of the bat game is to avoid any obstacles such as mines, fire, lightning bolts, monsters, and anything that is any enemy.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6T8E1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gone-batty/embed?sid=1","plays":40186,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1YS11","slug":"funny-eye-surgery","title":"Funny Eye Surgery","description":"Luke and Lora have been neglected their eyes by watching tablet all day, watch TV in dark, and never get their eyes proper rest. That cause problems to the eyes, and now they must go to eye doctor. Let's fix these kids' eyes so they can see better!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1YS11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-eye-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":40185,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9RIR6","slug":"fruit-slots-machine","title":"Fruit Slots Machine","description":"Fruit Machines has got to be the best fruit machine that you have ever played. This game is for real slots lovers who just love to enjoy their time playing slot machines and of course winning an incredible jackpot. Fruit machine slots take you back in time where everything was simpler and easier to grasp. The combination of big wins and lovely nostalgic music make this a fun, yet relaxing experience with great gameplay mechanics of modern slot machines. Play free scatter slots , enjoy the feeling of real slot machines with Free Spins bonuses and collect some wild cards while having tons of fun!","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9RIR6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-slots-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40184,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46226","slug":"kim-cat","title":"Kim Cat","description":"Kim Cat is a 2D platform game where you have to collect and eat cookies while avoiding spikes and enemies and finally, reach the red flag. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse WASD or arrow keys for movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46226/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kim-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1661","slug":"tsoro","title":"Tsoro","description":"Tsoro is based on an ancient board game which has been played for hundreds of years. \nGame play takes place on a wooden board with 10 holes destributed evenly across 2  rows. Before the game starts the player chooses a hole which will act as his bank. For each turn player picks seven coloured balls from the reservoir and drops them in successive holes/cells. Each drop earns the player points, with the most points earned on drops in the bank. The goal therefore is to  drop as many balls in the bank as you can. What makes this tsoro a cut from its peers are star balls. For a pair of diffrent colored balls in the same cell player gets a red star. Likewise four balls of the same colour in the same cell/hole earns the player a stars ball. Each star ball carries out a unique function when droped in a cell, for example the blackstar will change the colour of each ball in a cell.","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1661/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tsoro/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N466J","slug":"banana-joe","title":"Banana Joe","description":"Bananas Joe a fun puzzle game. Here is our cute little monkey which is really very hungry and he needs a whole lot of bananas.\nHe needs your help here, help him to collect all bananas.\nRoll the maze around to collect the bananas.\nTo complete the levels you must collect all Bananas; could you help him to collect all Bananas?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N466J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banana-joe/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEEL7","slug":"get-10-ultimate","title":"Get 10 Ultimate","description":"Compter de 1 à 10 est un défi pour les enfants qui débutent en mathématiques. Ce jeu de casse-tête numérique agréable à regarder et incroyablement amusant à jouer vous mettra au défi dans un ensemble de niveaux différents qui vous fourniront toujours une nouvelle expérience.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEEL7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/get-10-ultimate/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P2M52","slug":"mafia-poker","title":"Mafia Poker","description":"Qui prendra le contrôle de la mafia ? Qui deviendra le patron des patrons ? Cette fois ce sont les cartes qui décideront à qui décerner le titre de « capo di tutti i capi » au lieu des guerres de mafia et de la violence ! Jouez au classique Texas Hold 'em Poker avec des durs, si vous n'avez pas peur ! Choisissez le nombre de joueurs et c'est parti ! Mais ne vous inquiétez pas, ce n'est pas comme si les gangsters allaient vous tuer !\n","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P2M52/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mafia-poker/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40258","slug":"piggy-in-the-puddle-3","title":"Piggy In The Puddle 3","description":"This piggy loves to take a mud bath in a cool smelly puddle just like we love a fragrant relaxing bath, if you already had one today do not pass by and make this piggy happy too.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40258/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/piggy-in-the-puddle-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IAIUA","slug":"pixel-zombie-survival","title":"Pixel Zombie Survival","description":"Pixel Zombie Survival features intense zombie shooting in vast blocky world,  you are special forces soldier and your mission is to use different types of weapons to shoot all incoming blocky zombies and try to survive before the time runs out.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IAIUA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-zombie-survival/embed?sid=1","plays":40183,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0921S","slug":"tennis-1vs1","title":"Tennis 1vs1","description":"Retro style 1vs1 Tennis\nPlay a 1vs1 tennis match with your friend and show your skills and get 10 point","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0921S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tennis-1vs1/embed?sid=1","plays":40182,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1D3H1","slug":"fighter-3d","title":"Fighter 3D","description":"Fighter is an action packed flight shooter game.\n\nDodge bullets from multiple aircraft and collect points whilst shooting the enemy down.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1D3H1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fighter-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40181,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5706","slug":"epic-gaul","title":"Epic Gaul","description":"Help a brave gaul to escape from prison, and back to his family. Collect stars for improve your skills and beat roman warriors.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5706/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/epic-gaul/embed?sid=1","plays":40181,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"157NN","slug":"niko-adventure","title":"Niko Adventure","description":"niko adventure is a html5 platformer game, journey the niko world defeat enemies and avoid obstacle, collect coin to earn score, \nkill the Dinos to collect key ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/157NN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/niko-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40180,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UOBHB","slug":"holetube","title":"HoleTube","description":"Eat everything except the bombs!\n\nCONTROLS:\n- Press to open the hole and eat everything.\n- Release to close the hole.\n- Don't eat the bombs!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UOBHB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/holetube/embed?sid=1","plays":40179,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26K8R","slug":"block-breaker-game","title":"Block Breaker Game","description":"$49","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26K8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-breaker-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40179,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C2733","slug":"kitty-chase","title":"Kitty Chase","description":"kitty chase is an html5 arcade game, run and avoid dogs get candy for score ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C2733/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kitty-chase/embed?sid=1","plays":40179,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CE322","slug":"space-fighter","title":"Space Fighter","description":"space fighter is an html5 endless shooter game, shoot enemy planes and get stars for high score ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CE322/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-fighter/embed?sid=1","plays":40179,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AEANN","slug":"incredible-basketball","title":"Incredible Basketball","description":"The object of the game is to throw a basketball into the basket using various objects: a clapper box, wooden blocks, spinners, escalators, etc. If you fail, try changing the order of \"clicking\" on items or changing their properties. Play BasketGo: Incredible Basketball!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AEANN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/incredible-basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":40178,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06E60","slug":"hurdles","title":"Hurdles","description":"Choose your favourite runner among the 8 available and beat all the others in a breathtaking race!\nJump the hurdles perfectly to not be overtaken by your opponents. Jump on the winner's podium to join the next race and win all the 12 stages to be appointed sole winner!\n\nUse the space bar to jump at the right moment.\nPerform a perfect jump to get more points.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06E60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hurdles/embed?sid=1","plays":40178,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3R166","slug":"kobadoo-numbers","title":"Kobadoo Numbers","description":"Kobadoo Numbers is a browser game that trains your brain by memorizing two-digit numbers in the right order.\n\nWhen you play Kobadoo Numbers you are actively using your working memory. Several scientific studies suggest that training of working memory has beneficial effects and can increase your cognitive functions.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3R166/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kobadoo-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":40177,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RI661","slug":"trispeed","title":"TriSpeed","description":"A classic endless arcade game. Glide at full speed through obstacles, go further than anyone else!\n\nCONTROLS:\n- A-D/Left-Right Arrows/Click on left-right side of the screen to slide accordingly.\n- Avoid the obstacles, pick up the collectible and the powerups.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RI661/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trispeed/embed?sid=1","plays":40177,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N1FCF","slug":"fruit-slot-machine","title":"Fruit Slot Machine","description":"Si vous aimez les jeux de machine à sous gratuits, Fruit Slot Machine est fait pour vous. Un gameplay classique de bandit-manchot qui associe fruits savoureux et gros gains. Jouez à des machines à sous gratuites avec les fonctionnalités Wild, tours gratuits et partie bonus comme à Las Vegas. Il suffit de faire tourner les roues et de tenter votre chance !\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1FCF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40175,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4M746","slug":"monkey","title":"Monkey","description":"Easy game, just kill as many monkeys as possible in 60 seconds of time","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4M746/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scimmia/embed?sid=1","plays":40175,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6Y1DD","slug":"reddy","title":"Reddy","description":"Eat all little fishs avoid the shark !!!!!\n\nHave a fun!\ntouch the screen for swim\n\nBy Cerutti Marco.\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6Y1DD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/reddy/embed?sid=1","plays":40174,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RDB5P","slug":"noobpool-and-noobspider","title":"Noobpool and Noobspider","description":"Noobpool and noobspider must reach the safe zone by avoiding monsters and guns in the city. noobpool must reach the door, take the key. Reach the door with noobspider and noobpool, do not forget that he is your friend, do not reach the door without your friend, that door will not open.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RDB5P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noobpool-and-noobspider/embed?sid=1","plays":40174,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E19EE","slug":"the-letter","title":"The Letter","description":"The Letter: Seeker Of Truths is a story driven stealth/3Dplatformer game with a beautiful low poly graphic. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E19EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":40174,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"422R4","slug":"tronbot","title":"Tronbot","description":"Tronbot is a 2D platformer where you need to collect battery cells in order to unlock the battery-powered security door. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse WASD or arrow keys for player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/422R4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tronbot/embed?sid=1","plays":40174,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0M6MI","slug":"zumba-mania","title":"Zumba Mania","description":"Améliorez-vous au tir de billes et essayez de terminer tous les niveaux avec trois étoiles dans chaque niveau. Ce jeu de billes est facile et addictif à la fois.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0M6MI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zumba-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40174,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12R65","slug":"choosethecolor","title":"ChooseTheColor","description":"Choose the correct color before time runs out - Beta version","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12R65/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/choosethecolor/embed?sid=1","plays":40173,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"990AI","slug":"battleships-pirates","title":"Battleships Pirates","description":"These brave girls love the sea and adventures. Let's play as pirates, crush all enemy's battleships, and seek the treasures! Upgrade your ships, play dodgy, and may the fortune be with you. Now bring back those horizon!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/990AI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battleships-pirates/embed?sid=1","plays":40172,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3469E","slug":"unpark-me","title":"Unpark Me","description":"Unpark Me est un jeu de casse-tête stimulant et prenant. Aidez votre voiture à résoudre de nombreux problèmes de stationnement difficiles. Essayez de terminer le jeu en un minimum de coups possible et augmentez votre QI et votre logique. Vous devez faire passer votre voiture par la Sortie. Pour y parvenir, il suffit de déplacer les véhicules qui vous bloquent la route. Le jeu propose 4 difficultés, allant de débutant à expert.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3469E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/unpark-me/embed?sid=1","plays":40171,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8KO11","slug":"black-thrones","title":"Black Thrones","description":"Incarnez « Black », un assassin qui tente de protéger ceux qu'il aime de légions de morts-vivants sur un mur sans fin. Sautez et glissez sous divers obstacles. N'ayez aucune pitié contre les ennemis qui se dressent sur votre chemin. Boostez votre score en collectant les pièces qui amélioreront les bonus disséminés sur le mur.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8KO11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-thrones/embed?sid=1","plays":40171,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11V68","slug":"ball-vs-beat","title":"Ball Vs Beat","description":"Ball vs Beat is an addictive and challenging game designed and created with Unity. With easily changeable ad ids you can start earning money. Try to get the highest score and collect unique musical notes to unlock new songs to play. This is the best music game.\n\nHow to play?\n\nTap the screen to slide the ball in and out of the line. Hit all the notes perfectly to gain collectables. Follow the rhythm and don’t miss the beat.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11V68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-vs-beat/embed?sid=1","plays":40169,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ITOS","slug":"motocross-zombie","title":"Motocross Zombie","description":"For Mobile:\nUse left and right button to rotate your bike in the Air. Press left button to accelerate\n\nFor PC\nPress the up arrow on your keyboard to accelerate\nPress left and right arrow on your keyboard to rotate your bike in the Air","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ITOS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motocross-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":40169,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AUSN8","slug":"rainbow-jigsaw-puzzle-friends","title":"Rainbow Jigsaw Puzzle Friends","description":"Rainbow Jigsaw Puzzle Friends est un jeu de puzzle avec plus de 10 images magnifiques dans lesquelles de nombreux personnages sont bleus, rouges et verts.\nCette application de haute qualité est le choix parfait pour les amateurs de puzzles.\nscie sauteuse","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AUSN8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-jigsaw-puzzle-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":40168,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40431","slug":"neon-blitz","title":"Neon Blitz","description":"Touch the screen or use the mouse to jump. Avoid all enemies and get the highest score. How many jumps can you get?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40431/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":40167,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P6I83","slug":"ship-up","title":"Ship Up","description":"Ship Up is a simple and fun game where, with your triangular spacecraft, you have to avoid crashing into obstacles.\ngood fun !!!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P6I83/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ship-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40166,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0CTN1","slug":"pick-the-right-one","title":"Pick the Right One","description":"It's an endless moving game where you try to make as high score as possible.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0CTN1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pick-the-right-one/embed?sid=1","plays":40166,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26UPN","slug":"pukiimoon","title":"Pukiimoon","description":"Pukiimon a fun reflexive game to play on. Collect all of the Pukiimon by slicing and dicing the Pukiiballs.\nOver 20 Pukiimon to collect! Progress through the world of the Pukiimon bypassing the progressively harder levels.\nDon't let the Pukiiballs fall, and don't slice the bombs.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26UPN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pukiimoon/embed?sid=1","plays":40165,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2AEM1","slug":"emerald-and-amber","title":"Emerald and Amber","description":"Emerald and Amber is a platform game where you have to get stuck to solid surfaces to reach your loved one. It was inspired by some classics of the NES era with retro-style graphics and mechanics, but with a flexible difficulty aiming to be an enjoyable and relaxing experience.\n\nThe game has 27 levels and a Speedrun mode.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure","arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2AEM1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emerald-and-amber/embed?sid=1","plays":40164,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CBB6U","slug":"candy-blast-candy-bomb-puzzle-game","title":"Candy Blast - Candy Bomb Puzzle Game","description":"$4a","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CBB6U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-blast-candy-bomb-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10330","slug":"car-puzzles","title":"Car Puzzles","description":"Car puzzles is a fun online puzzle game. Drag the pieces into right position using mouse. Solving puzzles is relaxing, rewarding, and keeps your brain sharp. You need to spend $1000 to be able to purchase one of the following pictures. You have three modes for each picture from which the hardest mode brings more money. You have a total of 10 pictures.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10330/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OZ626","slug":"razzon","title":"Razzon","description":"Razzon is a 2D simple platformer where you need to collect dices while avoiding spikes, saws and enemies and reach the red flag. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Upper\" arrow key for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OZ626/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/razzon/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1W1K","slug":"sky-warrior-alien-attack","title":"Sky Warrior Alien Attack","description":"sky warrior alien attack is html5 enldess shooter game, shoot the ufo and get coin, life, bomb, fuel, and civillian, to earn score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1W1K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-warrior-alien-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VA082","slug":"taovip","title":"TaoVip","description":"Discover an aspect of the fantasies of the east through this fun-to-play board game with same screen multiplayer. Please pay attention this is pure fictional and this is not going to offend anyone in this world.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VA082/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/taovip/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25J2G","slug":"flying-jelly","title":"Flying Jelly","description":"flying jelly is an html5 arcade game, break as many jelly and as fast as possible, don't waste it, and don't touch the black jelly or your life is in danger","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25J2G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-jelly/embed?sid=1","plays":40163,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"08I78","slug":"tiny-boxes","title":"Tiny Boxes","description":"Welcome to Tiny boxes world! Swap boxes, stack them three in a row and clear the scene! Open all worlds for more fun! Enjoy!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/08I78/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-boxes/embed?sid=1","plays":40162,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4P948","slug":"spin-in-space","title":"Spin in Space","description":"The smaller the planet the more points you get and points are also awarded for distance travelled.     \n     \nKeep an eye on you fuel but don’t worry we have coded it so it drops between 2 planets so its always accessible.     \n     \nPlanets will start to disappear making it harder the longer you survive.     \n     \nIt's a never ending game made harder by increasing speed and fewer planets.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4P948/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spin-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":40162,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UPP67","slug":"jigsaw-puzzle-cats","title":"Jigsaw Puzzle Cats","description":"A useful game for brain development! If you like cats, then spend time with the benefit of the mind in the game \"Jigsaw Puzzle Cats\".","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UPP67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jigsaw-puzzle-cats/embed?sid=1","plays":40161,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31ASB","slug":"russian-cyber-car-hexagon","title":"Russian Cyber Car - HexagoN","description":"It is a game in which 7 Russian cyber car race against each other and the last one to fall wins. The last time you fall, you survive and win the race.\n\nHow to Play?\nArrow keys to move (Mobile Control)\nSpace Keys to Jump","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31ASB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-cyber-car-hexagon/embed?sid=1","plays":40160,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36VD6","slug":"indovinami","title":"Indovinami","description":"choose a number and then guess","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36VD6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/indovinami/embed?sid=1","plays":40158,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TTYT5","slug":"infinity-tank-battle","title":"Infinity Tank Battle","description":"Tank Battle is very popular TV game since 8-bit console present.\n\nInfinity Tank Battle is a brand new tank battle game. It is following various classic essential features, and add some new interesting elements.\n\nNow provide total 610 map\n\nCore Game Rule:\n- Defence your base\n- Destroy all enemy tanks\n\nKey Features:\n- Different type of enemy\n- Different type of Map style\n- Special items\n- Auto Helper tank\n- Import Super Tank Battle 500 Legend maps\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TTYT5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinity-tank-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40154,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1LA62","slug":"millionaire2019","title":"MILLIONAIRE2019","description":"Millionaire 2019 is an exciting intellectual show for mobile devices. If you want to get rich, you can take part in this competition right now, but prepare all your logical skills. Surely you also dreamed of becoming a millionaire and taking part in the show of the same name. Now such an opportunity has really appeared, and you can connect to the coolest TV show Who wants to become a millionaire. Answer a huge number of questions and move as far as possible. Answer very difficult questions and continue on.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1LA62/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/millionaire2019/embed?sid=1","plays":40154,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M41M4","slug":"make-10-puzzle","title":"Make 10 - Puzzle","description":"Make 10 : Puzzle is an addictive block and number puzzle game that is great for brain training!\n\nWelcome to an incredibly addictive puzzle game with an original plot of events!\n\nMake 10: Puzzle is a simple logical but difficult puzzle game to complete.\n\nThere are no time limits or tasks in the game.\n\nThe graphics of the game are suitable for all ages, that game will be interesting to play for both children and adults!\n\n\nGame Features:\n⭐️ Availability of ready-made various themes.\n⭐️ A game for all ages.\n⭐️ Many auxiliary bonuses for passing the game\n⭐️ Night theme to relax your eyes and play comfortably before going to sleep.\n\n\nTrain, play and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M41M4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/make-10-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40154,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H661T","slug":"touchthemoon","title":"TouchTheMoon","description":"TouchTheMoon est un jeu d'arcade qui se déroule dans l'espace.\nSautez avec votre astronaute entre les Lunes pour battre tous les records !\nSi vous êtes sur des appareils mobiles, utilisez le toucher sur l'écran pour vous déplacer\nvotre astronaute, sinon les flèches directionnelles.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H661T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/touchthemoon/embed?sid=1","plays":40153,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O44B5","slug":"blockminer-run","title":"Blockminer Run","description":"In the block world, a miner has to escape from the giant zombie. Help the miner and don't pass the levels. Be careful, if you don't hit animals, you can't pass. Don't let the zombie catch you.     \n\nHow to Play?\nPress \"W\" to jump! & Mobile Touch Control     \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O44B5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blockminer-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40153,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6526H","slug":"archer","title":"Archer","description":"hit the target with the arrows to break your record play again","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6526H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archer/embed?sid=1","plays":40153,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AA8R1","slug":"ball-thrower-hyper-casual-game","title":"Ball Thrower hyper casual game","description":"Race against an AI player, fill the most rings to win.  Curvy swipe system implemented. Bend the way of the ball with your fingers.  The game contains 3 different level layout which are endlessly rotating.     Chest Manager System, fill the chest by winning matches and gain coins from it.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AA8R1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-thrower-hyper-casual-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40153,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56021","slug":"puzzle-pieces","title":"Puzzle Pieces","description":"Remplissez les cercles dans ce jeu de puzzle passionnant. Gagnez des points, créez des cercles multicolores ou terminez le niveau avant la fin du temps. Explorez les 60 niveaux à travers 6 modes de jeu différents. Pourrez-vous tous les terminer ?\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56021/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-pieces/embed?sid=1","plays":40152,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J6APM","slug":"jump-sheep-game","title":"Jump Sheep Game","description":"$4b","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J6APM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-sheep-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40152,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77151","slug":"giddy-birds","title":"Giddy Birds","description":"It’s Giddy Birds the hottest game on the charts at the moment! Memory Test: Giddy Birds Game new mix of speed, memory and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test it this game! So the question is: How long could you follow these Crazy Birds?\n- Memory Test!\n- Super cute graphic!\n- Smooth Gameplay!\n- No Load Times!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77151/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/giddy-birds/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"611NE","slug":"lemonade-ninja","title":"Lemonade Ninja","description":"Lemonade Ninja is based on the very popular game fruit ninja.\nThe same concept applies in this game too, just slash as many lemons to make yummy lemonade and serve to all your friends.\nBut be careful while slashing, never touch the bombs, and slash as many lemons to achieve high scores.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/611NE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lemonade-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"213S1","slug":"mini-blocks","title":"Mini Blocks","description":"You control a small blob character with the power to turn on or off elements on the level. Use that power wisely to reach the goal to the next stage!\n\nYou can also test your skills on the speedrun mode.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/213S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69T79","slug":"teen-patti-match","title":"Teen Patti Match","description":"The Teen Patti Match 3 Puzzle online game is a fun and challenging way to test your puzzle solving skills. With its unique gameplay, this game is perfect for players of all ages.      \nTeen Patti is a Match 3 Puzzle game that you can play online. The objective of the game is to clear all of the teen patties from the board by matching three or more of them together. Teen Patti is an online puzzle game that challenges players to match three teen patti in a row. The game is easy to learn but difficult to master, and it provides a fun and challenging way to pass the time.      \n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69T79/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/teen-patti-match/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PA69A","slug":"jungle-escape-game","title":"Jungle Escape Game","description":"A fun action game where you are the Viking and you direct your dragon through swarms of enemies to reach the end of each level. There is one big bonus loop within each level that contains a plethora of enemies, but there is only time for one before the bonus ends! The game ends when all of your life and energy runs out. Each weapon gives a different bonus to the Vikings' score so be sure to try them all on each level!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PA69A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jungle-escape-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6I266","slug":"big-jump","title":"Big Jump","description":"Big Jump is a fun game where you can have fun while playing. Try to make the highest point and beat your friends!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6I266/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40452","slug":"candy-buff","title":"Candy Buff","description":"In Candy Buff you need to eat candy to get buff and to refill your energy! Collect bonuses and avoid mice, thorns and birds!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40452/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-buff/embed?sid=1","plays":40151,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5UIOL","slug":"handless-millionaire-unblocked","title":"Handless Millionaire Unblocked","description":"$4c","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5UIOL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/handless-millionaire-unblocked/embed?sid=1","plays":40149,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T5SI8","slug":"retro-tiny-tennis","title":"Retro Tiny Tennis","description":"In this great arcade sports game may be simple to play but it’s a challenge to get high scores.\n\nLike in a greatl tennis game, stopping the tennis balls requires speed and precision - make one mistake and you’re out!\n\nThe longer you stay on ground, the faster the tennis balls will come at you and it is your job to return them while also avoiding flying bottles.\n\nYou're warned! the Platinum medal is VERY hard to complete! only if you're a true grand slam may catch it!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T5SI8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-tiny-tennis/embed?sid=1","plays":40149,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2R1OL","slug":"survival-commando","title":"Survival Commando","description":"Survival Commando is a top-down shooter. Top-Down Shooter Survival Games is an action game with a lot of adrenaline. It is a shooting game, and you must survive in the midst of zombies. In this exciting game, you will have to go through a series of levels, which will get harder as you go.     \nDo you love playing top-down shooter games? It's a zombie outbreak! Solve exciting puzzles while fighting to stay alive in this action shooter game. Planned levels range from tense zombie shootouts to relaxing walks along steep cliffs with breathtaking views as you try to spot the easiest path ahead. Is it an ideal day out? No, but it sure is fun! Try your hand at some amazing motorcycle stunts while saving the world. You can play it on your PC or on your mobile phone.     \n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2R1OL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survival-commando/embed?sid=1","plays":40149,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YEERO","slug":"geometry-fresh","title":"Geometry Fresh","description":"Train your math skills!\n\nGive as much right answers as possible during 60 seconds.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YEERO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometry-fresh/embed?sid=1","plays":40145,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4GG6R","slug":"frog-rush","title":"Frog Rush","description":"Près de la marre contaminée par des substances toxiques, d´étranges grenouilles sont apparues. Le but est d’eliminer le maximum de grenouilles malades visibles à l’écran. Une goutte du liquide „Frog Burst“ permettra de faire grossir la grenouille. Lorsque celle-ci est assez grande, elle éclatera en dégageant plus de liquide. La quantité est limitée, utilisez la solution avec parcimonie. Prenez garde, la grenouille borgne ne dégage du liquide que dans un sens et la grenouille bleue causera l´explosion des grenouilles voisines. La meilleure tactique est de causer une réaction en chaîne.\n","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4GG6R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40145,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4AS9H","slug":"cat-girl-fashion-challenge","title":"Cat Girl Fashion Challenge","description":"Welcome to Cat Girl Fashion Challenge. Cat Girl is more conscious of her fashion. She plans to compete with all other fashionistas. Join and play as a fashion designer for cat girl. Help her to pick a nice costume for each event and compare her costumes with other players. Browse her wardrobe and pick outfits and costumes which is suitable for the events. Play and have fun! ","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4AS9H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-girl-fashion-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40143,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6RT77","slug":"motocross","title":"MotoCross","description":"welcome to the wonderful motocross game can you keep calm and cross the mountains?","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6RT77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motocross/embed?sid=1","plays":40143,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"033L9","slug":"slot-machine","title":"Slot Machine","description":"Simulate playing the slot machine wherever and whenever you want without spending anything. Have fun and see if you can beat the machine.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/033L9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40142,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TRN31","slug":"ninja-adventure","title":"Ninja Adventure","description":"ninja adventure is a html5 platformer game explore levels and get coins for score and gems to unlock next level kill monsters with sword or kunai ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TRN31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40141,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N9146","slug":"bunge-jungle","title":"Bunge Jungle","description":"$4d","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N9146/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunge-jungle/embed?sid=1","plays":40140,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NFP17","slug":"flappy-alien","title":"Flappy Alien","description":"Help the little alien to cross the asteroid belt, but the task seems very difficult.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NFP17/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-alien/embed?sid=1","plays":40140,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40098","slug":"sally-bbq-joint","title":"Sally BBQ Joint","description":"Abattre des arbres au Canada est un métier très dur. C'est pourquoi les bucherons canadiens aiment manger d'énormes steacks dès qu'ils le peuvent. Ca tombe bien car notre héroïne Sally vient juste d'ouvrir un restaurant qui vend des steacks bien juteux pour bucherons!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40098/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sally-bbq-joint/embed?sid=1","plays":40138,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40165","slug":"marble-smash","title":"Marble Smash","description":"Avec Marble Smash, le but du jeu est simple: tu dois faire disparaître les billes identiques par série de 3 ou plus mais bien réfléchir à l'ordre dans lequel tu vas les faire disparaître, sinon tu vas te retrouver coincé! En mode Puzzle, tu as 400 niveaux qui attendent que tu les réussisses, mode Time Attack, tu défies la montre en accumulant le plus de points.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40165/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/marble-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":40138,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BM160","slug":"art-jumble","title":"Art Jumble","description":"Fixed pieces of art together and learn about their history in this cool game made for kids","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BM160/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/art-jumble/embed?sid=1","plays":40138,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0ED2D","slug":"the-adventure","title":"The Adventure","description":"Bienvenue dans The Adventure, surmontez les obstacles, les balles, les ennemis et battez le boss final, essayez-vous à l'aventure en surmontant les trois niveaux de difficulté, qu'attendez-vous !!! Allez jouer à The Adventure maintenant et le plaisir sera garanti","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0ED2D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40137,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76273","slug":"pocket-drift","title":"Pocket Drift","description":"Pocket Drift is a great time trial racing game where you have to finish crazy curvy tracks as fast as you can. Drive your little car through dirt tracks full of coins and try to collect them while dodging obstacles to reach the finish line in record time in this fun free online game on Silvergames.com.\n\nYour car will automatically accelerate, so you only have to focus on turning and braking when necessary. It may take you a while to adjust to the turns, as you'll be looking at your vehicle from more of a spectator's angle, but after a few laps you'll become a master drifter. Open surprise boxes with all kinds of bonus power-ups, such as coin multipliers, magnets and much more. Have fun playing Pocket Drift!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76273/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocket-drift/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64F8P","slug":"fallingpix","title":"Fallingpix","description":"Quick and easy video game. Take the cartridges and try not to die. You have 15 lives, but you will lose them easily!\n\nCopyright: https://chifeletto-secco.itch.io/fallingpix","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64F8P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fallingpix/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2OOL1","slug":"new-noob-mommy-long","title":"New Noob Mommy Long","description":"hey noob run and run don't stop you have to run away from mom as a new noob. mommy long is chasing you noob don't stop. If you stop, they will catch you. Never stop. You must be careful about the obstacles, otherwise you will not be able to pass the levels and you will be defeated. Complete 10 levels and become the best noob.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2OOL1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/new-noob-mommy-long/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6D9E6","slug":"dice","title":"Dice","description":"Easy game of luck, dice game, just click on a dice and see if you are blessed with luck","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6D9E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dice/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E561G","slug":"kids-games-collection","title":"Kids Games Collection","description":"Kids Game Collection fun collective games to play on. Here is the collection of games like piano, drawing, coloring, and drums. Select any game play on and have fun.\nSpend your time with fun playing collective games, color lots of images, and play the drums. Play more games only with Mapi Games","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E561G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-games-collection/embed?sid=1","plays":40136,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5TP5","slug":"puppy-battle","title":"Puppy Battle","description":"Puppy Battle is a war robot game that tests your logic and wit Be brave and fight for victory against other war robots lasers saws and thermometers a great range of enemies and obstacles for your bot so the performance in battle is based on both strategy and players skills Get the game now for free and become the star of the Puppy Battle","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5TP5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puppy-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40135,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"63O76","slug":"stay-road","title":"Stay Road","description":"Show your short space maneuver skills.\n\nTap the screen to perform maneuvers and don't crash into the wall.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/63O76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stay-road/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8265","slug":"3dcube","title":"3Dcube","description":"The cube with the selected number is the one you will need to grab in time","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8265/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3dcube/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62A60","slug":"arrow","title":"Arrow","description":"Welcome to Arrow, have fun getting the fruits by clicking the right arrow, what are you waiting for ???? Go play Arrow now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62A60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arrow/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"JE1SL","slug":"chewy-jelly-rush","title":"Chewy Jelly Rush","description":"Chewy Jelly Rush is a match 3 html5 game, match some jelly to get score ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/JE1SL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chewy-jelly-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L3H3O","slug":"flashcolor","title":"FlashColor","description":"photographic memory of colors","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L3H3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flashcolor/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16R2E","slug":"desert-racing","title":"Desert Racing","description":"Racing in the desert.An exciting game with 15 levels, will immerse you in the atmosphere of the desert and roads! Collect stars in levels and buy new cars.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16R2E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desert-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8O124","slug":"paw-mahjong","title":"Paw Mahjong","description":"In Paw Mahjong you have to match the same animal icons and try to beat all the levels. Select a tile with an animal icon and click again to move it to another tile. If two of the same animals touch each other, you earn points and destroy the adjacent crates. in many levels there are special tiles that allow you to move animals either in a straight line or in a circle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8O124/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paw-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W9194","slug":"wild-west-slot-machine","title":"Wild West Slot Machine","description":"Jouez gratuitement aux meilleures machines à sous de casino sur le thème du Far West et ressentez le véritable frisson de Las Vegas ! Faites vos jeux, faites tourner les roues et gagnez gros dans le meilleur jeu de casino gratuit !\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W9194/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-west-slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40132,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"978AE","slug":"jumper-jam","title":"Jumper Jam","description":"Welcome to Jumper Jam, have fun jumping from one rain to another collecting coins and sprinting enemies, immerse yourself in the adventure with over 6 different environments to play and 8 characters to choose from, Will you be grateful to get to the stars? What are you waiting for?? Go play Jumper Jam now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/978AE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumper-jam/embed?sid=1","plays":40131,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13","slug":"ocean-crash","title":"Ocean Crash","description":"Votre but est d'empêcher que la grille se remplisse. Utilisez les blocs de façon à obtenir au moins 3 animaux du même type. La partie est gagnée quand les blocs remplissent intégralement les rangées de grilles!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ocean-crash/embed?sid=1","plays":40131,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77D7O","slug":"dragons-den","title":"Dragons Den","description":"Collect all the treasure under the red Dragons, be careful don't touch them or you'll lose a life!\nThe main goal of the game is collect as much treasure as possible and sign your personal record in the scoreboard.\nEnjoy with this great nice game.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77D7O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dragons-den/embed?sid=1","plays":40131,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F598S","slug":"what-kind-of-animal-is-this","title":"What Kind of Animal is This","description":"Learn about different types of animals while having fun playing, fun and education all in one place","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F598S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-kind-of-animal-is-this/embed?sid=1","plays":40130,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KP6BS","slug":"school-bus-3d-parking","title":"School Bus 3D Parking","description":"School Bus 3D Parking is super fun online game that you can play for free on PC and mobile. No download needed! You need to park the bus on the parking spot to enter the new level. Do not hit the walls or other obstacles on the way. Collect the coins and have fun playing!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KP6BS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/school-bus-3d-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":40130,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KII24","slug":"pirate-kid","title":"Pirate Kid","description":"Get ready for a incredible sea adventure! Grab your pirate hat and run through the dangerous sea shore. Collect diamonds and avoid evil crabs, birds and spiky shells. Tap anywhere on the screen to jump - and tap again while in the air to do a double jump. How many diamonds would you be able to collect?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KII24/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pirate-kid/embed?sid=1","plays":40130,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77A8C","slug":"casino-collection-3in1","title":"Casino Collection 3in1","description":"Vous pouvez jouer à ces jeux à Las Vegas ou directement sur votre téléphone : machine à sous, vidéo poker et Black Jack. Les jeux les plus célèbres et les plus simples du monde des casinos, des paris et d’énormes gains vous attendent. Ces jeux n'ont pas besoin d'une explication des règles et vous n'avez pas besoin d'argent pour y jouer tout e suite. Tentez votre chance, entraînez-vous sans perdre un sou, car si l'argent virtuel s'épuise, nous allons réapprovisionner votre compte gratuitement. Et quel sera le gain maximum, cela dépend de vous.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77A8C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/casino-collection-3in1/embed?sid=1","plays":40129,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0GRG8","slug":"2048-drag-and-drop","title":"2048 Drag and Drop","description":"2048 Drag and Drop is casual game, in this game player should merge the number so it can reach 2048. its very easy addicting and relaxing. play 2048 drag and drop!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0GRG8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-drag-and-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":40128,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5514","slug":"robot-runner","title":"Robot Runner","description":"Run with your robot into a dark abandoned factory! But beware an infinite path of dangers, put your personal best score; avoid the enemies and not fall from the platform if you will not immediately end your adventure. Your robot is able to jump the platforms with incredible leaps but is also equipped with a \"G\" device capable of reversing gravity! you find yourself running upside down! use this trick to avoid the big obstacles you encounter on your ride.\nKey Features:\n• 3D pre-render graphics\n• Amazing 3D animations\n• Background animations\n• Flawless graphics effects\n• Amazing sound effects\n• Easy to play\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5514/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40127,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DY8O7","slug":"squid-impostor-golden-key","title":"Squid Impostor Golden Key","description":"Are you ready for the dangerous adventure of the squid impostor? you must help him. be careful and crush the enemies crush the enemies and kill them all the invisible golden key will appear. Get the key and complete the level. \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile touch control \n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DY8O7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-impostor-golden-key/embed?sid=1","plays":40127,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UOTE1","slug":"one-odd-out","title":"One Odd Out","description":"Exercise your mind by searching for the single object that doesn't belong to the group. This fun brainer will help you develop your cognitive skills while having fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UOTE1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-odd-out/embed?sid=1","plays":40126,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0TR06","slug":"star-battles","title":"Star Battles","description":"Un jeu dans l'espace simple et amusant. Volez en cercle et évitez de vous écraser contre les vaisseaux ennemis. Remplissez les missions et volez à travers la galaxie. Survivez le plus longtemps possible. Accélérez ou ralentissez, mais ne vous écrasez pas et amusez-vous. Pouvez-vous déverrouiller et voler avec tous les vaisseaux disponibles ? Préparez-vous, pilote !\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0TR06/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/star-battles/embed?sid=1","plays":40126,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YC260","slug":"panda-escape-with-piggy-2","title":"Panda Escape with Piggy 2","description":"How would you like to join the adventure-filled jungle adventure of panda and piggy? In the adventure, obstacles and enemies are waiting for you, be careful, do not die! pass the levels Pass 10 different levels one by one and achieve victory. The fate of the whole forest is left to panda and piggy 2.        \n\nHow to Play?\n*WASD + Arrow Keys!      \n*Double Jump Available","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YC260/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/panda-escape-with-piggy-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40124,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65ALL","slug":"mad-racing-hill-climb","title":"Mad Racing-Hill Climb","description":"Ready to drive in off-road conditions? Fond of driving in tough situations? Then Mad Racing: Hill Climb is the perfect hill climb racer game for you. Relax by rocking the driving wheel. So don't wait anymore because it's time to put the medal on the pedal! Designed with fairly simple controls, Mad Racing: Hill Climb offers you a game with only two buttons: the accelerator and brake. Your job is to manage the perfect balance between them and drive your car in this hilly off-road condition. There are fifteen(15) different levels for you to play, each having a different difficulty level. So let's go off-roading! The latest and coolest off-road game at the Play Store is Hill Racing. In this new endless driving game, you must collect fuel cans and money. ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65ALL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mad-racing-hill-climb/embed?sid=1","plays":40123,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H3IW8","slug":"twining-color-switch-game","title":"Twining Color Switch Game","description":"$4e","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H3IW8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twining-color-switch-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40123,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CNA56","slug":"sweet-candy-mania","title":"Sweet Candy Mania","description":"Le petit Fluffy a besoin de votre aide ! Sa famille a été capturée après un atterrissage en catastrophe sur Candy Planet. Lancez des bonbons colorés et combinez-les pour progresser dans le jeu. En surmontant les divers obstacles pour tenter de les libérer, vous entrerez dans un monde savoureux de bonbons, de chocolat et d'indigéniaux idiots ! Pouvez-vous libérer tous les membres de la famille et récupérer tous les objets nécessaires pour atteindre la fin ?\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CNA56/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-candy-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40123,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69AEM","slug":"hexa-merge","title":"Hexa Merge","description":"Do you like Match 3, Hexa block and 2048 ? Hexa Merge are combination of these games into a single gameplay.\nReach highest score and show what you can do.\n\nDrag block, then drop it into empty tiles.\nTap block to swap between blocks.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69AEM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hexa-merge/embed?sid=1","plays":40123,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D9I9E","slug":"solitaire-tripeaks-garden","title":"Solitaire TriPeaks Garden","description":"Dans Solitaire TriPeaks Garden, vous pouvez jouer à des centaines de niveaux de la version de Solitaire la plus prenante qui soit ! Et vous pouvez le faire avec votre fidèle compagnon le chat. Tout au long du voyage, il vous aidera à remplir vos serres des plus belles fleurs de toutes les couleurs ! Une expérience ludique et détendue vous attend !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","arcade","board","classics","junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D9I9E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-tripeaks-garden/embed?sid=1","plays":40122,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AS6T0","slug":"color-with-santa","title":"Color with Santa","description":"This game is a painting, drawing and coloring tool for kids in a Christmas theme.\nTouch your colors and start drawing and painting with your mouse when done.\n\nKids will enjoy painting and coloring using their creative ideas.\n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Really simple to use!\n• Over 40 Objects to color!\n• Really addictive game!\n• Really fun characters!\n• It's a Kids quite game!\n\nAll the magic of Christmas time in this great color game of color and music; it will transport your children to the wonderful world of Santa Claus and his friends!\n\nMerry Christmas and Happy New Year!","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AS6T0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-with-santa/embed?sid=1","plays":40122,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"32U66","slug":"3d-touch","title":"3D Touch","description":"This is a logic game where you have to tap the cubes generating possible paths. You can't go back, your goal is for everyone to be selected. There are 100 levels with gradual difficulty. You will be able to collect coins and buy new skins to customize your gameplay.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/32U66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-touch/embed?sid=1","plays":40121,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O66O6","slug":"ant-destroyer-2","title":"Ant Destroyer 2","description":"Smash all the ants that appear on the screen with your fingers, before they leave the screen be very careful don't tap the red ants, they are very dangerous.\nYou have in this awesome App seven modality to smash all the Ants that you see on the screen.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O66O6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ant-destroyer-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40121,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"690P4","slug":"paper","title":"Paper","description":"Welcome to Paper, have fun between 5 levels overcoming all obstacles and increasing your bestscore, what are you waiting for? Go play Paper now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/690P4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paper/embed?sid=1","plays":40121,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06FR3","slug":"rudolf-the-searcher","title":"Rudolf the Searcher","description":"Help Rudolf collect the Christmas gifts. Watch out for the Grinch!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06FR3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rudolf-the-searcher/embed?sid=1","plays":40121,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3LC03","slug":"icy-purple-head-3","title":"Icy Purple Head 3","description":" Icy purple head is back. Addicting game for kids with simple controls that has 40 fun levels and cool hats.\n Help post man to deliver parcels in time. Run through all levels to finish the game. \n Unlock fun has to make Icy look even cooler! Be careful with the post birds, and match the right color to hit them.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3LC03/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/icy-purple-head-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40120,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8YAEB","slug":"baby-repeater","title":"Baby Repeater","description":"Baby Repeater is an addictive adaptation of the classic old memory game; adults and children love it, it's addictive & fun!\nSo watch the lights and sounds and try to repeat the sequence as long as you can!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8YAEB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-repeater/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64336","slug":"bobo","title":"Bobo","description":"Welcome to the Bobo game, let's see if you can climb the ropes, jumping from one rope to another to reach the last level","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64336/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bobo/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H5MAM","slug":"bushman-bamboo","title":"Bushman Bamboo","description":"Enjoy your free time exploring bushmen journeys with the help of bamboo.\n\n\n\nFrom all over the internet this free online game is the best just for you. For any activity level it is the perfect game.\n\n\n\nGame features\n\nEntertaining and enjoyable.\n\nHigh quality graphics.\n\nChallenging levels.\n\n\n\nHow to play!\n\nOnline for free play Bushman Bamboo Hyper Casual game. To spend some free time the Bushman Bamboo Hyper Casual game is the perfect way. To keep you entertained for hours on, it's a fast, fun, and challenging online game. That's why Bushman Bamboo Hyper Casual should be played.\n\n\n\nGame controls:\n\nDesktop:\n\nClick the left mouse button to stretch the bamboo.\n\n\n\nMobile\n\nTap on the stick to stretch.\n\n\n\nControls and indicators\n\nLower right side of the screen has the sound and music button which will be shown before starting the game.\n\nThe play button will be shown in the middle before playing.\n\nThe scores are shown in the middle of the screen.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H5MAM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bushman-bamboo/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VINIE","slug":"enenemy-invasion","title":"Enenemy Invasion","description":"Welcome to Enemy Invasion, have fun shooting bullets and destroying enemies and you can also help yourself with the power-ups that you can collect in the game, what are you waiting for ??? Go fast playing Enemy Invasion and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VINIE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/enenemy-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A167R","slug":"galaxy-of-fire","title":"Galaxy of Fire","description":"galaxy of fire is an html5 shooting game. shoot aliens and get as many scores as possible each enemy has a different value ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A167R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-of-fire/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RP27","slug":"sharp-rings","title":"Sharp Rings","description":"Game Controls: In order not to touch the ring on the string, do the following; If the ring pulls down tap on the screen trying to stay on the weight.The position and movement of the ring is constantly changing, if the ring pulls up tap on the screen without letting the ring rise, do it constantly to keep the ring in the air.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RP27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sharp-rings/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"34U52","slug":"snownuts","title":"Snownuts","description":"Snownuts is a wintergame where you get to descent from a snow covered mountain in the innertube, an inflatable donut and make your way to the finish. You can do the obstacle track, race against the cpu and even go head to head with another player in the 2 player mode!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/34U52/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snownuts/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C26F2","slug":"counter-craft-2-zombies","title":"Counter Craft 2 Zombies","description":"Counter Craft 2 Zombies features action packed zombie shooting in minecraft world, your mission is to use three different weapons to shoot hordes of incoming zombies and try to survive each round with increasing difficulty.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C26F2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-craft-2-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40119,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4EE94","slug":"head-the-ball","title":"Head the Ball","description":"Head The Ball is a new way for soccer players to head the ball. By using your head, you can create an impact that is difficult for your opponent to miss. With your head, you can create an impact that is difficult for your opponent to miss. Your opponent will be forced to defend against the ball if it falls off your hand. You can also use this ability to create space on the pitch for your teammates.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4EE94/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/head-the-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40118,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I1A15","slug":"redhead-knight","title":"Redhead Knight","description":"Redhead Knight is a super fun and challenging 2D side scrolling game in the same style as blockbuster games like Super Mario, Donkey Kong and Sonic. The game has 15 levels divided into 03 worlds, which will challenge you to win it. Arthur is a young knight with red hair who has a mission to rescue peace in his village. With many enemies in your path, you will need a lot of courage and bravery! Help Arthur in this challenging adventure! The drawings are very colorful and beautiful!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I1A15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redhead-knight/embed?sid=1","plays":40118,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3K1HI","slug":"sheep-stacking","title":"Sheep Stacking","description":"Welcome to the green alpine meadows! We are gathered here to have a annual sheep stacking competition! Grab your sheep and throw one on top of the another. So much fun! (not for the sheep unfortunately). To stack the livestock simply tap the screen when the top sheep is above the one on the bottom. If your sheep will land correctly - you score points! If your sheep won’t land correctly - you lose the game and the sheep.  Good luck! Disclaimer: No animals were hurt while making this game. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3K1HI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sheep-stacking/embed?sid=1","plays":40117,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"444SO","slug":"cool-cubes-io","title":"Cool Cubes IO","description":"Try to prove the you are the best cube!\nSpawn triangles and attack other cubes with them!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/444SO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cool-cubes-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40117,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"152Y6","slug":"fly-v2","title":"Fly V2","description":"Fly and collect as many stars as you can to get your own high score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/152Y6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fly-v2/embed?sid=1","plays":40117,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RS62A","slug":"brain-games","title":"Brain games","description":"Brain Games is a series of challenges, riddles and puzzles. Test your logical reasoning,\naccuracy, memory and creativity and have fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RS62A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-games/embed?sid=1","plays":40117,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MKM7E","slug":"emoji-strikes-online-game","title":"Emoji Strikes Online Game","description":"Emoji Strikes Online Game is an online game that lets you explore and enjoy the world of Emoji. Your goal is to collect enough emoji to become the most popular emoji in the world.    \nThe game is based on a funny way that you collect and use more of all the different emojis to become the most popular emoji in the world.    \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MKM7E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emoji-strikes-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40116,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96585","slug":"tob-vs-kov","title":"Tob vs Kov","description":"Tob vs Kov is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you play as Tob, the robot, who have to collect red balls while avoiding the enemy robots, and saws and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.        \nUse \"W\" or \" Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96585/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tob-vs-kov/embed?sid=1","plays":40116,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DDRTG","slug":"dotted-girl-wedding","title":"Dotted Girl Wedding","description":"Louis est depuis longtemps et désespérément amoureux de Marie. Et si nous étions dans un univers parallèle, où ils sont destinés à être ensemble? Fantasmons à ce sujet et organisons un magnifique mariage pour Mary et Louis. Choisissez une jolie robe de mariée pour la mariée en rose, blanc ou lilas. N'oubliez pas un voile et un bouquet de fleurs festif. Appliquez un maquillage léger et obtenez une coiffure de mariage pour Mary. Maintenant, prenons soin du marié. Choisissez une coiffure masculine élégante, ainsi qu'un costume dans les couleurs préférées de Luka - turquoise-bleu. Terminez la tenue du marié avec une jolie boutonnière de la couleur de la robe de la mariée. Notre nouveau couple est prêt à se marier!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DDRTG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dotted-girl-wedding/embed?sid=1","plays":40116,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20068","slug":"hidden-objects-pirate-treasure","title":"Hidden Objects Pirate Treasure","description":"Donnez un coup de main à \"Angrybeard\", le capitaine pirate, à retrouver son trésor caché sur une mystérieuse île. Trouvez une liste d'objets définie dans chaque scène mais ne vous trompez pas car chaque erreur vous coutera du temps! Dépêchez-vous de tester ce jeu d'objets cachés pour flibustiers!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20068/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-objects-pirate-treasure/embed?sid=1","plays":40115,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66AA6","slug":"tap-clapp","title":"Tap & Clapp","description":"Do you like puzzles? It's one of the best!\n\nHelp the blue square to reach the bucket, it makes sense!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66AA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-and-clapp/embed?sid=1","plays":40115,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8P875","slug":"thor-king-pig","title":"Thor King Pig","description":"Throwing his ax at every place that has the power of the worlds, Thor must reach the door at the earliest in his adventure to kill the king pig, his arch-enemy. If he stays under water, he can die or be killed by the soldiers of the king pig. collect the diamonds and reach the door but your primary target should be the door reach the door and have the victory!     \n\nHow to Play?\nMove to WASD / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8P875/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/thor-king-pig/embed?sid=1","plays":40114,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40353","slug":"junior-chess","title":"Junior Chess","description":"In Junior Chess you can play on a nice chess board and prove your skills! Use the mouse or your fingers to control the figures. Every figure has special moving abilities. Game on!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40353/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/junior-chess/embed?sid=1","plays":40113,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N2HK7","slug":"pumpkin-smasher","title":"Pumpkin Smasher","description":"The Halloween party time is coming! \nThe evil pumpkins are flying all over the place - simply tap or swipe them to smash them!\nYou can’t miss any of them!\nHow many pumpkins would you be able to destroy with your mighty finger?;)\nAlso - avoid the dreadful horror mines!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N2HK7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pumpkin-smasher/embed?sid=1","plays":40113,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CEIDD","slug":"find-10-errors-christmas","title":"Find 10 errors - CHRISTMAS","description":"10 Mistakes is a game where you must find the 10 errors before time runs out. You may find all 10? The game has a Christmas theme.\nEnjoy this challenge.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CEIDD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-10-errors-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40112,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6AEE6","slug":"halloween-match-3","title":"Halloween Match 3","description":"Match 3 games are puzzle games you need to match 3 or more object by exchanging two pieces or by clicking on a group of 3 or more.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6AEE6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-match-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40112,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8D133","slug":"sound-guess","title":"Sound Guess","description":"Listen to the sound and try to guess it! Difficult? A hint will appear in a few seconds:)","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8D133/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sound-guess/embed?sid=1","plays":40112,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A8OA2","slug":"reaperman-vs-goblins","title":"Reaperman vs Goblins","description":"reaperman vs goblins is a html5 arcade game, kill the goblins use knife, fire, and stick and get more score, use special attack fireball and lighting","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A8OA2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/reaperman-vs-goblins/embed?sid=1","plays":40110,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54188","slug":"4hockey","title":"4Hockey","description":"A fast paced air pong game with increasing balls, speed and number of opponents.\n\nCONTROLS\nPC:\n- A-D/Left-Right Arrow to slide.\nMobile:\n- Press and drag to slide.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54188/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/4hockey/embed?sid=1","plays":40110,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3636M","slug":"kill-the-zombies","title":"Kill the zombies","description":"Welcome to Kill the zombies, the zombie game. challenge them, fight them, kill them, get lives and resist as long as you can, will you be able to reach the night and get to the next day? What are you up to? go play Kill the zombies now and the fun is guaranteed.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3636M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kill-the-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40110,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EKECC","slug":"rocket-balance","title":"Rocket Balance","description":"“Rocket Balance” is a Rocket game where you need skill to control the machine. Beat the levels without touching anything! Dodge enemies and collect energy to keep the rocket from exploding! The game has controls for mobile devices and for desktops. A game to entertain people of all ages. Good fun!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EKECC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-balance/embed?sid=1","plays":40110,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7YNPS","slug":"infinity-jump-christmas","title":"Infinity Jump Christmas","description":"Infinity Jump Christmas is an infinite jumping game where players aim to collect as many presents as possible and avoid the candy dolls, find and get upgrades.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7YNPS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinity-jump-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40109,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z42P7","slug":"dog-puzzle","title":"Dog Puzzle","description":"Welcome to the dog puzzle, you have 20 boxes to move to rebuild the kitten, let's see if you can, good luck","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z42P7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dog-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40109,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SF83H","slug":"spot-the-difference","title":"Spot the Difference","description":"Installez-vous confortablement, détendez-vous et amusez-vous à parcourir d'innombrables images colorées et intéressantes. Trouvez toutes les différences dans ces images et progressez à travers les niveaux. Profitez de la musique apaisante et des beaux paysages.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SF83H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spot-the-difference/embed?sid=1","plays":40109,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81T71","slug":"top-sniper","title":"Top Sniper","description":"A group of mercenaries seized the territory of the plant. Your task is to destroy as many militants as possible, and a powerful rifle in your arsenal will help with its implementation.\n\nThe game is a sniper simulator where shooting will be affected by various indicators such as distance, wind and even the breath of the shooter.\n\nControls:\n\nWASD - movement in space.\nMouse - for a circular view.\nLeft mouse button - fire.\nRight mouse button - optical sight (aiming).\nR key - reload.\nC key - sit.\nLeft SHIFT - accelerate while running, hold your breath while aiming.\nSPACE - jump.\n\nTAB or ESC key - call menus","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81T71/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/top-sniper/embed?sid=1","plays":40109,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MR6E6","slug":"mydream-universe","title":"myDream Universe","description":"$4f","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MR6E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mydream-universe/embed?sid=1","plays":40108,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SC4I5","slug":"chinese-checkers-master","title":"Chinese Checkers Master","description":"Chinese Checkers is a traditional board game, some people call it \"Chinese chequers\" or \"Hop Ching Checker Game\".\n\nThis game named Chinese Checkers Master, because we have develop a powerful and intelligent AI player. You can play with it or other friends.\n\nThis game is very flexible, you can config 0 to 6 human players to play the game.\n\nWhy 0? You can set AI players only, it will demo to you how to play the game!\n\nFor more detail of the game rule, you can find it on:\nWikipedia : https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_checkers\n\nFEATURES:\n\n- Flexible to place the balls\n- Powerful computer players\n- Up to 6 players\n- 3D game board","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SC4I5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chinese-checkers-master/embed?sid=1","plays":40108,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40182","slug":"cat-named-soko","title":"Cat named Soko","description":"It is time to restore order! A little Cat named Soko wants to bring all balls to their correct position.\nWill you help Soko to place the balls on the green box?","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40182/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cat-named-soko/embed?sid=1","plays":40108,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9ER06","slug":"reversi-mania","title":"Reversi Mania","description":"Dans Reversi, vous jouez avec des pions à double face et vous essayez de battre l'autre joueur ! Dans ce jeu très simple, vous devez pouvoir réfléchir à de nombreux coups à l'avance pour pouvoir jouer comme un pro. Vous pouvez même jouer avec vos amis grâce au mode multijoueur ! Qu'attendez-vous ? Perfectionnez votre tactique !\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9ER06/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/reversi-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":40108,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20062","slug":"shinobi-slash","title":"Shinobi Slash","description":"Shinobi Slash est un jeu simple mais incroyable. Utilisez votre souris ou votre doigt pour sauter, esquiver les projectiles et exploser votre score. Réservé aux seuls vrais ninjas!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20062/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shinobi-slash/embed?sid=1","plays":40107,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46ZAR","slug":"happy-color-sort-puzzle","title":"Happy Color Sort Puzzle","description":"The water sort puzzle is a happy, color-based online game that will challenge and engage you. The object of the game is to sort the different colors of water into their respective containers. This can be a difficult task, as the colors all look very similar. However, with a little careful planning and strategic thinking, you can complete the water sort puzzle and be happy with your results.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46ZAR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-color-sort-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40107,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40081","slug":"zero","title":"Zero","description":"Faites bouger la plateforme vers la gauche ou vers la droite en direction de la balle pour avoir le meilleur score. Récoltez autant de pièces que possible et achetez d'autres fonds d'écran!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40081/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zero/embed?sid=1","plays":40107,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40121","slug":"ninja-pig","title":"Ninja Pig","description":"Aidez le cochon ninja à sauver le monde d'une terrible invasion alien! Courez pour récolter des shuriken à travers 10 niveaux et confrontez vous au big boss en personne. Augmentez votre score en complétant des défis, comme finir un niveau en une seule fois, tirer sur des ennemis spécifiques ou encore en conservant vos munitions!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40121/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-pig/embed?sid=1","plays":40106,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1I6D0","slug":"destroy-asteroids","title":"Destroy Asteroids","description":"Destroy asteroids. Defend the Earth from asteroids and launch the missile to Mars.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1I6D0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/destroy-asteroids/embed?sid=1","plays":40106,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6CVU4","slug":"candy-girl-adventure","title":"Candy Girl Adventure","description":"candy girl adventure is a html5 platformer game, explore the sweet world get as much candy as possible and beat the enemies on stage ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6CVU4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-girl-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40104,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4035R","slug":"rusty-biker","title":"Rusty Biker","description":"Rusty Biker is the best online moto bike racing game. With incredible graphics and awesome gameplay, you will be hooked for hours! Moto Bike Racing fans rejoice! The Rusty Biker Online Moto Bike Racing game is online. With three different modes to choose from, there is something for everyone. Test your skills in the career mode, race against friends in the multiplayer mode, or just have some fun in the single player mode. There are also leaderboards so you can see how you stack up against the competition. So what are you waiting for? Get on your bike and start racing!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4035R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rusty-biker/embed?sid=1","plays":40104,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IAS3R","slug":"ant-squisher-2","title":"Ant Squisher 2","description":"$50","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IAS3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ant-squisher-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40104,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5E005","slug":"vip-slot-machine","title":"VIP Slot Machine","description":"Jouez avec les célébrités. Devenez riche ! Des graphismes éblouissants et de gros gains ! Vous pouvez gagner autant que vous le souhaitez. Jouez aux machines à sous avec les fonctionnalités Wilds, Tours gratuits et Bonus comme à Vegas.\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5E005/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vip-slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40103,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A667P","slug":"fairy-princesses","title":"Fairy Princesses","description":"The Fairy Princesses need to gather flowers and gain magical powers to heal the nature.\nThis won’t be an easy task, as the meadow is full of sleepy bees coming back from work. \nLet the magic guide the fairy!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A667P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-princess/embed?sid=1","plays":40103,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16HG6","slug":"higher-than-the-highest","title":"Higher than the Highest","description":"go as high as possible with the rocket, move with \"a\" and \"d\" or the arrows on the screen.\ndodge the metrorites and grab the clocks for extra time","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16HG6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/higher-than-the-highest/embed?sid=1","plays":40102,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O3T3F","slug":"forest-adventure-match-3","title":"Forest Adventure Match 3","description":"In this exciting game three in a row you will have a pleasant walk through the forest.\nWin on dozens of interesting levels with exciting tasks. A lot of bright elements and a variety of puzzles will not let you get bored!\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O3T3F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/forest-adventure-match-3/embed?sid=1","plays":40101,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56455","slug":"block-tower","title":"Block Tower","description":"A very popular and addictive game release the block by taping anywhere and construct the tower as tall as possible! If you miss three or more Stone blocks you loose! Have Fun and  enjoy the game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56455/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":40100,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6T222","slug":"pink-cuteman-2","title":"Pink Cuteman 2","description":"In the game, which is the 2nd series of the pink cuteman game, the enemies and flying bats will welcome you, be careful, it's snowing and pass the levels covered with cold snow everywhere and finish all the levels. Reach the flag and go to the next level! Be careful, don't fall into the water, be careful of the cliffs, you can fall at any time.  \n\nHow to Play?\nMove to WASD & Mobile Touch Control      \nPause \"P\"  \nDouble Jump Available","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6T222/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pink-cuteman-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40100,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40388","slug":"santa-run","title":"Santa Run","description":"Make Santa run as far as possible and give out presents as he goes.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40388/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40099,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4MNR6","slug":"alexwoman-summer-time","title":"Alexwoman Summer Time","description":"alexwoman she is a strong woman. It is so strong that it manages to survive in the best way possible. Alex woman overcomes all obstacles with her perfect strength and reaches the portal at the end. There is no portal that he cannot become. Obstacles are child's play for him.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4MNR6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alexwoman-summer-time/embed?sid=1","plays":40099,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9PH8K","slug":"chester-jet-pack","title":"Chester Jet Pack","description":"Welcome to Chester Jet Pack, have fun dodging the obstacles and accumulating points by taking coins, what are you waiting for? Go on and play Chester Jet Pack and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9PH8K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chester-jet-pack/embed?sid=1","plays":40099,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9O033","slug":"tower-city","title":"Tower City","description":"Welcome to Tower City, fun jumping on colored blocks climbing the skies and reaching the most distant planets, What are you waiting for? go play Tower City now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9O033/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-city/embed?sid=1","plays":40099,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NA11R","slug":"rail-runner","title":"Rail Runner","description":"Prenez la voie ferrée ! Courez le plus loin possible, évitez les obstacles de la voie ferrée et réalisez tous les succès dans un level design en constante évolution et à la difficulté croissante ! Amassez des pièces et utilisez-les pour améliorer vos capacités de power-up. Mettez vos compétences à l'épreuve et battez votre meilleur score !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NA11R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rail-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40098,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NUS1E","slug":"pinugs-frees-aivin","title":"Pinugs Frees Aivin","description":"Aivin has been kidnapped by aliens, jump on the walls and free him.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NUS1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pinugs-frees-aivin/embed?sid=1","plays":40098,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8C2C","slug":"rescue-the-cd","title":"Rescue The CD","description":"The game was made in 5 days during a game jam.\nyou'll have to rescue the CDs, but be careful, zombies will try to kill you!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8C2C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-the-cd/embed?sid=1","plays":40097,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C6E11","slug":"connect","title":"Connect","description":"A timing based arcade game with a total of 15 levels. \n\nTo beat a level, you will have to reach the box with the red lamp on top of it.\n\nAfter you have beaten the 15 levels.. You can play them again but on challenge mode, good luck!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C6E11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/connect/embed?sid=1","plays":40096,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"515L8","slug":"jungle-run","title":"Jungle Run","description":"Run, jump, avoid walls and warning to the snakes!!\nUse arrows for movement and jump.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/515L8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jungle-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40096,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L1O05","slug":"mini-golf-funny","title":"Mini Golf Funny","description":"Are you ready for mini golf excitement? besides, it's funny. In mini golf funny, you will never lose the fun and your connection to the game, take care of your ball. Drag and drop the ball towards the hole where it should be.\n\nHow to Play?\nDrag and Drop & Mouse Left Clicker","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L1O05/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-golf-funny/embed?sid=1","plays":40096,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"X1060","slug":"matrix-ball","title":"Matrix Ball","description":"The most addictive stack fall game with optimized performance for all devices!\n\nMatrix Ball is a super fun and addictive one touch casual game.\n\nPress and hold on the screen and let the ball go down without touching the obstacles! Hold as long as possible to make combo and break the black blocks. Let the ball fall down from the helix stacks.\n\nMatrix Ball is a 3d arcade game where players smash, bump and bounce through revolving helix platforms to reach the end.\n\nMatrix Ball is a Brand New Stack Ball Game, 3D Ball Arcade game with infinite Levels and infinite fun. Game where players smash, bump and bounce through revolving helix platforms to reach the end.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/X1060/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/matrix-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40095,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1YM2A","slug":"scary-math","title":"Scary Math","description":"$51","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1YM2A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scary-math/embed?sid=1","plays":40095,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TT75T","slug":"attack-in-space","title":"Attack In Space","description":"This is an arcade game, in which you can move a ship and shoot lasers to hit enemy ships! Use left arrow and right arrow to move the spaceship and press space bar for shoot! This is my first videogame!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TT75T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/attack-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":40094,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SB6T0","slug":"defend-military-base","title":"Defend Military Base","description":"Defend Military Base is a HTML5 Skill Game. Tap on the screen to launch the cannonballs and destroy as many tanks as possible before they reach the base! Collect extra balls bonus and make an endless balls chain! Use super bonuses for more destruction!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SB6T0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/defend-military-base/embed?sid=1","plays":40093,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S7175","slug":"space-crash","title":"Space Crash","description":"Captain Rogers is a hero defending the Galaxy. He knows no fear. He knows no remorse. Actually, he doesn't know much in general. \nCaptain Rogers needs to fly through the dangerous sector of the space, while his spaceship's system experienced an error and the laser controls don't work as expected. Will our hero be able survive such harsh conditions? Especially when there's no more \"Astro-bud\" on board.\nThe Captain’s ship is constantly rotating in space. Tap anywhere on the screen to make it go up a little bit. \nYou can’t fly off the screen or crash into an asteroid. \nOh - the ship’s laser gun jammed and are firing all the time (try to destroy some asteroids with the laser shots for points). ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S7175/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-crash/embed?sid=1","plays":40092,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6MH1H","slug":"pixel-cat-mahjong","title":"Pixel Cat Mahjong","description":"Find similar tiles that have a clear route for connection. Clear path for other tiles and solve the pattern within given time.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6MH1H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-cat-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":40092,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RT5AR","slug":"santadays-christmas","title":"SantaDays Christmas","description":"Santa Days : Christmas Finish dozens of courses and collect crowns. Be the winner of the day! Buy the costumes and change your image. Race with 10-40 people, be the winner of the race! Join the world of Fall Days. Race with different costumes on different maps! Make the Difference.\n\nHow to Play?\nMobile Touch Control & WASD + Arrow Keys + ZQSD","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RT5AR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santadays-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40091,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"II5II","slug":"fire-knight-adventure","title":"Fire Knight Adventure","description":"fire knight adventure is a html5 platformer adventure game, journey in 10 level kill the enemy and collect coin to earn score","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/II5II/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fire-knight-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40091,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T3460","slug":"shoot-apples","title":"Shoot Apples","description":"Just shoot to apples...!!\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T3460/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shoot-to-apples/embed?sid=1","plays":40091,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20051","slug":"sprint-club-nitro","title":"Sprint Club Nitro","description":"Devenez un as du volant dans ce jeu d'arcade en 3D à travers 9 niveaux et 3 décors différents. Faites la course avec 20 autres bolides jusqu'à la ligne d'arrivée, et récupérez des boost de nitro pour battre vos adversaires. Dépensez vos gains en achetant des améliorations pour votre véhicule comme une meilleur stabilité, plus de vitesse ou encore des boosts de nitro plus longs!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20051/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sprint-club-nitro/embed?sid=1","plays":40090,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2GY7N","slug":"drag-racing-city","title":"Drag Racing City","description":"Drag Racing City vous fera traverser une série de courses passionnantes et rapides. Battez vos rivaux, obtenez le meilleur rang de drag racer et mettez-vous au défi avec des difficultés personnalisables, le tout avec des voitures réglées et personnalisées pour montrer votre style unique !\n","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2GY7N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drag-racing-city/embed?sid=1","plays":40088,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U3E3U","slug":"sudoku-levels","title":"Sudoku Levels","description":"Sudoku pour débutants et joueurs avancés. Que vous souhaitiez vous détendre ou défier votre esprit, passez le temps de manière agréable ! Faites une pause stimulante ou videz-vous la tête avec les puzzles Sudoku. Emportez votre application préférée avec vous partout où vous allez.\nChoisissez le niveau que vous voulez. Jouez à des niveaux plus faciles pour exercer votre cerveau\n\n*","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U3E3U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sudoku-levels/embed?sid=1","plays":40087,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NH4AA","slug":"color-ball-challenge","title":"Color Ball Challenge","description":"Color Ball Color Switch Challenge Game is free online at Hooguy.com. The Color Switch game is a fun and challenging arcade game. \nColor Ball Color Switch Challenge Game is a fun and addictive game. \nColor Ball Color Switch Challenge Game is a free online game. You can play Color Ball Color Switch Challenge Game in your browser and mobile for free.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NH4AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-ball-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":40086,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RR1SR","slug":"airship-venture","title":"Airship Venture","description":"airship venture is an html5 arcade game, press and hold the screen to fly avoid enemies and get score to win ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RR1SR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/airship-venture/embed?sid=1","plays":40086,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L661A","slug":"bounceball","title":"BounceBall","description":"Make the bubble grow by collecting green marbles","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L661A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bounceball/embed?sid=1","plays":40086,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E9LC2","slug":"bubbles-clicker","title":"Bubbles Clicker","description":"Pop all the bubbles and don't let them fly away","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E9LC2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubbles-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":40085,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4MM63","slug":"memeshooter","title":"Memeshooter","description":"Baloon shooting type of game with memes","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4MM63/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memeshooter/embed?sid=1","plays":40085,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3G01F","slug":"giddy-fruit","title":"Giddy Fruit","description":"Tap To Match The Crazy Fruits As Many As You Can!\n\nMemory Test:\nGiddy Fruit Game new mix of speed, memory and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test it this game!\n\nKey Features:\n- Memory Test!\n- Super cute graphic!\n- Smooth Gameplay!\n- No Load Times!\n\nSo the question is:\nHow long could you follow these crazy Fruits?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3G01F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/giddy-fruit/embed?sid=1","plays":40084,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4T141","slug":"gobo-desert-of-cubes","title":"Gobo Desert of Cubes","description":"Gobo and the Desert of Cubes is a side-scrolling 2D platformer with emphasis on puzzle elements. You need to help Gobo reach the exit door and escape the Desert. You do that by manipulating monsters which in return activate or deactivate boxes on the level, which are used as a platform or an obstacle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4T141/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gobo-desert-of-cubes/embed?sid=1","plays":40084,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D5OAE","slug":"on-the-road","title":"On the road","description":"do cross the dangerous road","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D5OAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/on-the-road/embed?sid=1","plays":40083,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T718T","slug":"hit-it","title":"Hit It","description":"Hit as many goals as you can, score more points than your opponent to win!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T718T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hit-it/embed?sid=1","plays":40082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"005LW","slug":"tasty-jewel","title":"Tasty Jewel","description":"Cette boîte de bonbons contient de précieux joyaux en bonbon ! Associez-les pour fabriquer des joyaux explosifs ! Cela peut vous aider à détruire les blocs qui sont sur votre chemin. Un jeu d'arcade classique de séries de 3 en tour par tour aux nombreux niveaux et modes passionnants vous attend !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/005LW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tasty-jewel/embed?sid=1","plays":40082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40191","slug":"finders-critters","title":"Finders Critters","description":"Faites correspondre 2 blocs ou plus de la même couleur pour aider les petites créatures à atteindre le sol. Planifiez vos actions avec prudence pour ne pas vous retrouver coincé. Utilisez des bombes et des pétards pour éclater encore plus de blocs et amuser les créatures. Jouez encore et encore pour débloquer de nouveaux persos comme l'extra-tesrestre et le bébé requin!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40191/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/finders-critters/embed?sid=1","plays":40082,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"09S3R","slug":"mosaic-puzzle-art","title":"Mosaic Puzzle Art","description":"Tease your imagination and boost creativity with cool and fun mosaic game. Explore lots of puzzles with various images for both skilled and casual players.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/09S3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mosaic-puzzle-art/embed?sid=1","plays":40080,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ALILU","slug":"alien-evolution","title":"Alien: Evolution","description":"Are You Ready To Start Flying Around And Destroying Ultra-Advanced And Futuristic Enemies? If So, Just Jump Into The Game!\nIn This Universe, Each World Has 3 Levels. There Are 2 Worlds, And Your Goal Is To Explore Them All And Discover All Their Secrets. There Are 2 Different Weapons, 2 Movement Mechanics And 2 Different Types Of Enemies. Good Luck Commander!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ALILU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B1RT3","slug":"little-strawberry","title":"Little Strawberry","description":"Help the little strawberry to avoid obstacles and go further into the forest! You must help the little strawberry so that she can travel in the forest! There are many obstacles in her way and you must get over them using your quadruple jump power!!! A single mistake is enough for you to lose the game. So if you want to stay in one piece, pay attention to avoiding obstacles. ... One mistake is enough to lose the game. So if you want to stay whole, try to avoid obstacles.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B1RT3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-strawberry/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2AR65","slug":"quiz-categories","title":"Quiz Categories","description":"It's a classic quiz game where it deals with varied themes like movies, music, biology, are some of the categories of this game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2AR65/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quiz-categories/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14S6P","slug":"super-space-adventure","title":"Super Space Adventure","description":"\"Space Adventures\" est un jeu d'arcade décontracté sur les voyages dans l'espace sur une fusée, qui peut être amélioré au fur et à mesure que le jeu progresse.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14S6P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-space-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RX062","slug":"rexo","title":"Rexo","description":"Rexo is a 2D Platformer where you play as a Cube and your aim is to collect all of the gems in each level to go to the next one while avoiding the spikes, and enemies. As soon as you collect all the gems, the red flag will become green and you can proceed to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty will increase as you proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse Arrow keys to control the movements of the Cube. Press Up arrow key twice to Double Jump. If you are using a mobile, you can use the movement touch buttons on the screen to play the game.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RX062/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rexo/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40320","slug":"stick-freak","title":"Stick Freak","description":"Étirez le bâton pour pouvoir passer de l'autre côté. Veillez à ce que le bâton soit de la bonne longueur – ni trop long, ni trop court – sinon vous allez tomber!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40320/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stick-freak/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0P7CZ","slug":"block-puzzle-chuzzle-classic","title":"Block Puzzle Chuzzle Classic","description":"$52","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0P7CZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-puzzle-chuzzle-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":40079,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NSR36","slug":"candy-monsters","title":"Candy Monsters","description":"Help to a little monsters eat a candy with same color, but be careful, candies with other colors not to their liking. Good luck!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NSR36/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-monsters/embed?sid=1","plays":40078,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NOO5O","slug":"mission-to-moon-online-game","title":"Mission To Moon Online Game","description":"The mission of the game is to reach the Moon, collect a few pieces of space junk, and return back to Earth. Collect new crew members, and earn money for fights with robots. Mission To Moon is an online free game that you can play for free. It's a space flight simulator where you'll be able to explore the moon, fly through the sky and even land on the moon in this fun game.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NOO5O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mission-to-moon-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40078,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26P6I","slug":"jumping","title":"Jumping","description":"Welcome to Jumping, overcome all the blocks without going into the void by managing your jump force, what are you waiting for? Go play Jumping now and fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26P6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumping/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7U941","slug":"shmoup","title":"Shmoup","description":"Endless shoot'em up in space!\nWith controller support\n\nMouse & Keyboard\nArrows/WASD --- Movement (Forward, Backwards, Strafe)\nEscape ------------ Pause\nMouse ------------ Aim\nMouse left  ------- Shoot\n\nController\nD-pad / Left Stick --- Movement (Forward, Backwards, Strafe)\nRight Stick ---------- Aim\nAny Trigger  -------- Shoot\nStart ---------------- Pause","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7U941/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shmoup/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E22A6","slug":"speed-balloons","title":"Speed Balloons","description":"Speed Balloons\n\nThe player will have to hit at least 20 balloons out of 30, each level passed will increase the speed of the balloons","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E22A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speed-balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K576N","slug":"stickman-jetpack","title":"Stickman Jetpack","description":"Stickman. Jetpack is a cool casual game with the famous ragdoll physics. Defy gravity and reach the finish line. Simple at first glance, the game will present you with difficult challenges.\n\nYou are equipped with a jetpack and your goal in this game is to fly successfully to the finish line. But it's not that simple!\nFirstly, the fuel is not infinite. If it ends, you will fall and the game will have to start over.\nSecondly, there will be a lot of obstacles along the way, when you meet them, the jetpack will explode with you!\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\n⭐ More than 10 exciting levels\n⭐ Different game modes and tasks\n⭐ Simple controls and cool ragdoll physics\n\nThink over each trajectory and prove that you are a master of virtuoso flight!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K576N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-jetpack/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9R6S7","slug":"the-shooter-pro","title":"The Shooter PRO","description":"Le Shooter Pro est un jeu de tir de plate-forme familial. Marchez, courez, sautez, faites un double saut, tirez tout en évitant les obstacles et les ennemis. Un coup vous renverra au début du niveau pour réessayer. Atteignez le drapeau, pour une victoire, et essayez un niveau encore plus difficile.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9R6S7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-shooter-pro/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DDU57","slug":"wounded-summer","title":"Wounded Summer","description":"Wounded Summer is a free action / shooter western game with a beautiful realistic graphics.\n\nStory\n\nThe hero of the story is called Tecumseh, who is a Native American. The Tecumseh tribe is attacked and its people are killed while he is hunting. The attackers also took Tecumseh's sister with them. Tecumseh embarks on a perilous journey to bring his sister back and avenge the murderers of his tribe.\n\nGame Features\n\nBeautiful realistic environment\nStrong native American protagonist\nFun and exciting action/shooter gameplay\nEasy to pick up and play\nFor fans of western and action games","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DDU57/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wounded-summer/embed?sid=1","plays":40077,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NYU8O","slug":"funny-tattoo-shop","title":"Funny Tattoo Shop","description":"Choose from the three sets of choices, and you'll be given the piece that you will then tattoo to your chosen model. Do the stencil, make the outline and color it according to your piece. After finishing your artwork, dress up your model that suits the tattoo you have created. Finish the game and unlock all the achievements. Share your screenshots to other players of the game. Have fun tattooing!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NYU8O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-tattoo-shop/embed?sid=1","plays":40075,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SC8SN","slug":"sun-in-space","title":"Sun in Space","description":"hold your finger or mouse in the yellow square and collect as\n many suns as you can without getting hit by other planets","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SC8SN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sun-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":40075,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7A498","slug":"shaman-academy","title":"Shaman Academy","description":"Test your abilities in combat and magic on Shaman Academy.\n\nEach player draws 3 cards on game start, then you can play a different card per turn. The goal is to knock-out your opponent, whatever it takes!\n\nTypes of Cards:\n    Battle Cards - Used to deal damage to your opponent. Can be a Rock, Paper or Scissors type card. When the type Battle Card you played beats your opponent, he will not be able to play his Battle Card.\n    Spell Cards - Used to cast spells for different effects. Some spells costs mana and some will give mana. Spells cards will give you a \"Spell Defend\" for protection from enemy attacks during the turn they are played.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7A498/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shaman-academy/embed?sid=1","plays":40075,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EL406","slug":"color-objects-halloween","title":"Color Objects Halloween","description":"This game is a painting, drawing and coloring tool for kids in Halloween Theme!\nPick your colors and start drawing and painting with your mouse when done.\nKids will enjoy painting using their creative ideas. Have fun using this kids paint app!\n\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Really simple!\n• Over 40 Objects!\n• Really addictive!\n• Really fun!\n• Kids quite!\nHappy Halloween with this great color game for kids have Fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EL406/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-objects-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":40074,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L55L7","slug":"flashball","title":"FlashBall","description":"flash ball that changes directions take it inside","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L55L7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flashball/embed?sid=1","plays":40074,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OO5N6","slug":"donhoop","title":"Donhoop","description":"Solve the puzzle by lining up the colored donuts.\nGrab one of the donuts on the filled sticks.\nMove it to the empty or same color donut.\nContinue in this way to complete the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OO5N6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/donhoop/embed?sid=1","plays":40073,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N568B","slug":"unblock-the-ball","title":"Unblock the Ball","description":"Un jeu de puzzle classique incroyable.Il y a beaucoup de niveaux d'intelligence et de logique qui vous attendent. Combien de niveaux pouvez-vous maîtriser?","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N568B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/unblock-the-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40073,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B64A4","slug":"metalbot","title":"Metalbot","description":"metalbot html5 platformer game, defeat enemies by shooting, get score by picking up gems in each level ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B64A4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/metalbot/embed?sid=1","plays":40073,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3F52V","slug":"cooking-fever","title":"Cooking Fever","description":"La Fièvre de la Cuisine est l'un des jeux de cuisine de restaurant les plus récents et les plus addictifs, mettant en vedette des compétences en gestion du temps ainsi qu'un plaisir de stratégie et de simulation. Montrez vos talents de cuisinier en préparant de délicieux hamburgers et des toasts pour devenir un grand chef !\n\n-150 niveaux difficiles.\n-Graphiques mignons.\n-Animations et effets satisfaisants.\n-2 restaurants différents.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3F52V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cooking-fever/embed?sid=1","plays":40073,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0805Z","slug":"line-puzzle","title":"Line Puzzle","description":"Try to move the lines to match each image fun and relaxing levels","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0805Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40073,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7","slug":"space-miner","title":"Space Miner","description":"Récupérez tous les nuggets et les diamands pour marquer un maximum de points. Mais faites attention à la dynamite!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-miner/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81SES","slug":"balls-ricochet","title":"Balls Ricochet!","description":"\"Balls: Ricochet!\" - game in the arcade-shooter genre. The project pays tribute to the old retro gaming. If you consider yourself a true connoisseur of games, you should play this game and dip into nostalgia. The game will delight you:\n- Authentic gameplay\n- Correct ball physics\n- Nice visuals\nThe addictive, addictive gameplay will immerse you in the pursuit of a better score for a long time. The concept developed in the early 80's still works perfectly. Start playing, and beat your friend's score! \nAlso check out the next installments of Balls, have fun playing!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81SES/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-ricochet/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5BM61","slug":"barbarian-vs-mummy","title":"Barbarian VS Mummy","description":"“Barbarian Vs Mummy” is a super fun and challenging 2D side-scroller game in the same style as blockbuster games like Super Mario, Donkey Kong and Sonic. The game features 06 levels that will challenge you to beat it. The designs are very colorful and beautiful!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5BM61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbarian-vs-mummy/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E6NS5","slug":"basketball-challenge-online-game","title":"Basketball Challenge Online Game","description":"Basketball Challenge is a free online basketball game where you control the ball, and compete against Obstacles. Your goal is to shoot your way through a set of goals while avoiding obstacles in the way.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E6NS5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketball-challenge-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G46CO","slug":"water-color-sort","title":"Water Color Sort","description":"Watery Bottle - Water Color Sort Puzzle Game is a simple, easy and addictive puzzle game. A challenging yet stress free puzzle game to exercise your brain.\n\nSort the colored water in the glass bottles until all colors in the bottle not poured with same colors.\n\nThis game looks very simple, but it is quite challenging. Higher the level, higher the difficulty means you needs think critically for each move.\n\nTest your intelligence by solving this liquid sort water puzzle game 🧠.\n\n\nHow To Play:\n- Tap any water bottle to pour water into another bottle.\n- The way to pour is that you can only pour the water if it is the same color and there’re enough space on the glass bottle.\n- To complete the level, one bottle must have single color only.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G46CO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/water-color-sort-puzzle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"917M6","slug":"escape-minimap","title":"Escape Minimap","description":"Welcome to Escape minimap, have fun through the various levels collecting objects and avoiding monsters, with the addition of a mini map to help you locate everything, what are you waiting for ???? Go play Escape minimap now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/917M6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-minimap/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O6S5O","slug":"tob-vs-kov-2","title":"Tob vs Kov 2","description":"Tob vs Kov 2 is a 2D sci-fi themed platformer where you play as Tob, the robot, and your mission is to collect red balls while avoiding the enemies, flying robots, and saws and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O6S5O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tob-vs-kov-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40072,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G77NN","slug":"surprise-eggs-vending-machine","title":"Surprise Eggs Vending Machine","description":"Surprise Eggs Vending Machine is a really fun game. Each item inside the vending machine has a price; you have a set of coins at your disposal to insert the right sum you can see on the display. If you’re right, the vending machine will release the item, if you’re wrong you’ll receive an error message. Uncover the surprises and collect all the items.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G77NN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/surprise-eggs-vending-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40071,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"39756","slug":"hugi-wugi","title":"Hugi Wugi","description":"hey you need to run, be quick! run run non stop! Hugi wugi is watching you, you have to run, run. You have to find the lucky block before the time runs out or the hugi wugi might catch you. hurry up and reach the lucky block. Reach the lucky block and jump to the next level!       \n\nHow to Play?\n*Use WASD keys to play!       \n*Use mouse cursor to rotate 360 ​​degrees.       \n*Press the \"p\" key to stop the game.       \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/39756/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hugi-wugi/embed?sid=1","plays":40071,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"516F1","slug":"fly","title":"Fly","description":"Fly and collect as many stars as you can to get your own high score","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/516F1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fly/embed?sid=1","plays":40071,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D51KU","slug":"kids-animal-fun","title":"Kids: Animal Fun","description":"Les jolies images de puzzles d'animaux sont de retour ! Laissez vos enfants jouer et développer leurs habiletés cognitives, leur motricité fine, leur patience et leur capacité à se concentrer. Et en plus de ça… Vous n'avez pas à ranger ensuite !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D51KU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-animal-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":40071,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"38464","slug":"leap-and-jump-1","title":"Leap and Jump 1","description":"Welcome to Leap and Jump, have fun overcoming all obstacles and all levels, what are you waiting for ??? Go play Leap and Jump now and the fun will be guaranteed.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/38464/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/leap-and-jump-1/embed?sid=1","plays":40070,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"QO8QU","slug":"squid-pop-it-game","title":"Squid Pop It Game","description":"This is a super classic Pop it game in a Squid Game theme.\nHow to play: click on the pops to smash them and clear all the board.\nBe quick and smash all the pops and feel the relax from the tensions, this game is for all ages and you can play for hours.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/QO8QU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-pop-it-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40070,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3Z13B","slug":"kill-the-zombies-2","title":"Kill the Zombies 2","description":"Welcome to Kill the Zombies 2, have fun in the brand new and second game of the Kill the Zombie series, with an innovative mechanics and the ability to move around the map you will be a policeman in the role of zombie hunters in an abandoned park, you will have the task of killing the more possible and then what are you up to ??? Go play Kill the zombies 2 now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3Z13B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kill-the-zombies-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40068,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1CNOT","slug":"mahjong-sweet-connection","title":"Mahjong Sweet Connection","description":"This online game “Mahjong Sweet Connection” is able to collect in front of the screen both adults and young players. Connect pairs and get stars. Allow yourself to relax. Relax and take your mind off business!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1CNOT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-sweet-connection/embed?sid=1","plays":40068,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G4091","slug":"goblin-flying-machine","title":"Goblin Flying Machine","description":"Your goblin girlfriend has been kidnapped by evil dwarfs. You build a catapult to launch yourself into the sky to get into dwarven zeppelin and save your girl! Highly addictive launcher game with tons of humor!\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G4091/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goblin-flying-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":40068,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83557","slug":"hustler","title":"Hustler","description":"Become the ultimate druglord by travelling around the globe and buying and selling narcotics! Arm yourself because an attack can come at any moment from anyone. The goal is to become as rich as you can.","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83557/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hustler/embed?sid=1","plays":40067,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y73I3","slug":"maze-labyrinth","title":"Maze & Labyrinth","description":"Maze & labyrinth - brainteaser game, the real challenge to your intellect! Сollection of mazes and labyrinths, from simple to very complex. Classic and shade mazes type, the ability to download a maze image. Train your logic and intelligence, think, remember, develop your mind and find a way out of the maze.\n\nHow to Play:\nFind a way out of the maze. Arrow keys or WASD for a PC or on-screen buttons for mobile devices.\nSpace bar or Ctrl for move back.\nLarge mazes can be scaled and moved across the screen.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y73I3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maze-and-labyrinth/embed?sid=1","plays":40065,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HCAY3","slug":"candy-cane-hit","title":"Candy Cane Hit","description":"The ultimate Candy Cane Hit challenge is here!\n\nThrow the candies into the logs to break them. Slash the apples \n\nBe careful to not hit the Candies or the spikes. Time your actions, target carefully and become the candies master!\n\nCan you beat all the bosses?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HCAY3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-cane-hit/embed?sid=1","plays":40065,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14114","slug":"move-the-pin","title":"Move the Pin","description":"Move pins as you can!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14114/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/move-the-pin/embed?sid=1","plays":40065,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ED19F","slug":"base-defense","title":"Base Defense","description":"Build turrets to defend your base!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ED19F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/base-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O4MUU","slug":"color-mixed-up","title":"Color Mixed Up","description":"Color Mixed Up an educational game to play on! Opps all the word got mixed up! all the words got messy, so make the blocks move and arrange them to create and solve the puzzle to find the five hidden words which are hiding to find out.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O4MUU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-mixed-up/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58543","slug":"mathsgs","title":"MathsGs","description":"Let's see how good you are at math","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58543/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mathsgs/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40P4I","slug":"pig-ball-impostor","title":"Pig Ball Impostor","description":"How would you like to join the adventure of the cute ball pig in the forest? help the pig and hunt the impostors. Hunt all the square impostors with the special space suit itself. kill the monsters, collect the star and get the right to pass the next level. Don't forget you have to collect 3 stars. kill monsters and get points. 10 different levels are waiting for you.  \n\nHow To Play?\n*Use WASD Keys to play.            \n*Watch out for the enemies to survive!            \n*You can climb on top of monsters and kill them.            \n*Double jump is active in the game.     \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40P4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pig-ball-impostor/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5P3I5","slug":"puzzle-pin","title":"Puzzle Pin","description":"Use your pins to make the ball fall inside the glass!\n\nCONTROLS:\n- Click/Tap to place a pin. You can drag to draw a line of pins.\n- Click/Tap the Play button to start the simulation.\n- Click/Tap the Undo button to undo the last pin.\n- Click/Tap the Reset button to clear all the pins.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5P3I5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-pin/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UAE5R","slug":"santa-snow-runner","title":"Santa Snow Runner","description":"Santa Snow Runner is a free online game. Run through the snow and deliver the presents. \nSanta Snow Runner is an online HTML5 game. You can play the game on smartphone and tablet (iPhone, iPad, Samsung, Android devices and Windows Phone).Santa Snow Runner Online free game. Play free online games, fun games, puzzle games, action games, sports games, flash games and more \n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UAE5R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-snow-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D5E7A","slug":"beenvaders","title":"Beenvaders","description":"The evil Floretron has sent an army of evil flowers to wipe out the bees. Eliminate as many flowers as you can. Watch out for the evil little pink flowers. Collect the capsules and hearts to increase your lives.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D5E7A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beenvaders/embed?sid=1","plays":40064,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4RS0P","slug":"noob-vs-pro-help-hacker","title":"Noob vs Pro Help Hacker","description":"Noob needs to reach the bed Noob wants to sleep Help Nooba as a pro and reach the bed. Monsters are coming towards you cut them with your sword and overcome them all. hey pro nooba help. Don't be fooled by hacker's games Hacker is shooting be careful don't touch the bullets. use the best sword in the world and reach home.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4RS0P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-pro-help-hacker/embed?sid=1","plays":40062,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CCUA6","slug":"hug-and-kis-city","title":"Hug and Kis City","description":"In the hug and kis series, collect gold today, watch out for zombies, get the key and reach the door. You need to get to the door safe and both of you need to get there safe. Help them in the adventure of hug and kis. help deliver to home and door. collect gold and reach the highest score.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CCUA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hug-and-kis-city/embed?sid=1","plays":40062,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N873","slug":"robo-runner-io","title":"Robo Runner IO","description":"Try to win in a race. Prove that you are better than other 7 players.\nCollect stars to unlock new skins and tracks.\nBecome the fastest robot in the universe!\nHave fun!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N873/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robo-runner-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40061,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y6OCR","slug":"yummy-chocolate-factory","title":"Yummy Chocolate Factory","description":"Hey chocolate lovers! Ready for this yummy and chocolaty making game? In this cooking game, you will be able to prove your skills to make tasty chocolate. There are some tasks included to make this cooking game more interesting. That's going to be totally awesome and really yummy!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y6OCR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-chocolate-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":40061,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DA2DA","slug":"ninja-adventure-2","title":"Ninja Adventure 2","description":"ninja adventure 2 is a html5 platformer game","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DA2DA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-adventure-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8076I","slug":"boxing-quiz","title":"Boxing Quiz","description":"QUIZ BOXING, IT IS A QUIZ GAME WHERE IT BRINGS INTERESTING CHALLENGES TO OUR KNOWLEDGE. PLAY NOW!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8076I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boxing-quiz/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ET66N","slug":"kunumeo-battle-online","title":"Kunumeo Battle Online","description":"Kunumeo Battle Online est un jeu de tir en ligne à l'ancienne. de nombreuses fonctionnalités sont implémentées telles que des bonus à acheter avec des pièces de monnaie en jeu (KC) et un système de sauvegarde/chargement pour enregistrer votre KC. Kunumeo ne peut être joué qu'en ligne, avec des personnes du monde entier, vous devez sélectionner la région avant de jouer","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ET66N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kunumeo-battle-online/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ULI1","slug":"pony-dress-up","title":"Pony Dress Up","description":"Original Hyper Casual Game – basé sur une étude de marché :\n\nDe plus en plus de jeux hyper-casual utilisent le système « crowd », où le but est de collecter de plus en plus de personnes/balles/autres collectibles. C'est un effet satisfaisant et une mécanique de jeu qui conquiert les marchés.\n\nMélanger l'élément tendance \"balles clones\" de Ball Clone avec un gameplay de coureur rend le jeu très amusant et original.\n\nSoyez le premier à en faire un TOP jeu !\n\nLes niveaux sont générés aléatoirement à partir de préfabriqués. (Cela signifie que vous n'avez pas à passer des heures à créer de nouveaux niveaux, il y a déjà des niveaux infinis dans le modèle ;)\n \n\nFaites glisser votre doigt pour déplacer vos balles d'un côté à l'autre et éviter les obstacles.\n\nCollectez de nombreuses balles et atteignez la ligne d'arrivée pour terminer un niveau.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ULI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dress-up-girls/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M0N4N","slug":"sun-and-moon","title":"Sun and Moon","description":"Fight your enemies in a war across many galaxies and constellations. In this game, you need to find the best strategy for each constellation that you are playing. You will have different types of planets with different levels of difficulty which all contribute to making up the time limit that is given on every level. It's not just about fighting but also strategizing as well because only by finding out what works can one win against their opponents and move on to higher levels where they face tougher challenges","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M0N4N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sun-and-moon/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9O1H3","slug":"tomb-of-the-cat-color","title":"Tomb of the Cat Color","description":"a cemetery escape story you are a cat and you are escaping from the cemetery you are painting everywhere. Remember, you don't have to paint everything. You have 10 seconds and quickly collect all the coins and achieve victory. This game with 20 different levels is waiting for you. If you want to escape too, go to the right game!  \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9O1H3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tomb-of-the-cat-color/embed?sid=1","plays":40060,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E4LGA","slug":"candy-egg-blast","title":"Candy Egg Blast","description":"$53","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E4LGA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-crush-eggs-blast-game-eggs-link-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40058,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6CA19","slug":"ufo-attack","title":"UFO Attack","description":"UFO Attack is an online shooting game where you defend against invading aliens! Use your mouse to aim and shoot at the UFOs, and try to stay alive for as long as possible. Can you beat your high score? Play now and find out!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6CA19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ufo-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":40058,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K5MI8","slug":"commander-keen-summer-edition","title":"Commander Keen Summer Edition","description":"Remake of the well-known game \"Commander Keen\". Platform with procedural levels. Play new scenarios and help Keen to save Cloudland. Make the highest score, comparing yourself to other players.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K5MI8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/commander-keen-summer-edition/embed?sid=1","plays":40058,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20053","slug":"mini-putt-garden","title":"Mini Putt Garden","description":"Si vous aimez le minigolf, alors vous adorerez les 18 niveaux de \"Mini-Putt Garden\". Découvrez les 2 environnements \"Morning Garden\" et \"Water park\" et profitez d'un gameplay évolutif au fil du jeu. Jouez à des mini-jeux pour vous sortir de situations difficiles, comme quand votre balle se retrouve coincée dans la boue!","category":"Sport","tags":["classics","sports","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20053/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-putt-garden/embed?sid=1","plays":40058,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TO117","slug":"andys-factory","title":"Andys Factory","description":"$54","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TO117/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/andys-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":40057,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E954R","slug":"double-plane-venture","title":"Double Plane Venture","description":"double plane venture is an html5 arcade game, play 2 planes avoid crashes and get fuel so they don't explode ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E954R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/double-plane-venture/embed?sid=1","plays":40057,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HBA4A","slug":"alphabet-for-child","title":"Alphabet for Child","description":"Alphabet for Child a fun and intuitive game to play! learning is always fun while playing.\nThis special game will help your child to learn alphabets and their words too.\nAn interesting part is clicking on the image to see some random and fun action.\nPlay a lot more educational games with Mapi Games!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HBA4A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alphabet-for-child/embed?sid=1","plays":40057,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6UMM8","slug":"yummy-super-burger","title":"Yummy Super Burger","description":"Everybody likes burgers! Now is the time for you to make your own yummy super burger!\nPrepare the ingredients by following every part on the tasklist untill your burgers are ready to sell. Make yummy burger as fast as you can. Serve to your customers on time.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6UMM8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-super-burger/embed?sid=1","plays":40056,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H1R28","slug":"archer-hero","title":"Archer Hero","description":"Adventure Game, where the archer must cross the monster valley, where he encounters many challenges. Collect all the stars in each stage. Archer Hero is a super fun and challenging 2D side-scroller game. The game features 30 levels that will challenge you to beat it. The designs are very colorful and beautiful!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H1R28/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/archer-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":40056,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BS4BC","slug":"ball-thief-vs-police-2","title":"Ball Thief vs Police 2","description":"Ball Thief vs Police 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as a thief and you have to collect the bags of money while avoiding the police, drones and spikes.        \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. This is the second installment of the original Ball Thief vs Police series. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BS4BC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-thief-vs-police-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40055,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y1O2P","slug":"happy-helloween","title":"Happy Helloween","description":"Halloween is a cool holiday with lots of yummy candies. Do not miss the falling candies. How mutch you can catch?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y1O2P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-helloween/embed?sid=1","plays":40055,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6L6BD","slug":"3dball","title":"3DBall","description":"jump with the ball before the ground disappears","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6L6BD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3dball/embed?sid=1","plays":40054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1D0U","slug":"handgun-simulator-parabellum","title":"Handgun Simulator Parabellum","description":"Handgun Simulator Shooting Range offers realistic and closest experience for semi-automatic and modern weapons shooting on the firing range. Imagine classic gun shooting closest experience with dynamic weapons sounds when you pull of the trigger aim for bull's eye.","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1D0U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/handgun-simulator-parabellum/embed?sid=1","plays":40054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9922O","slug":"motobike","title":"MotoBike","description":"On a cool motorcycle you have to drive an obstacle and a distance through cities and natural steppes. The main thing is that the bike does not roll over, and you get to the finish line.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9922O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motobike/embed?sid=1","plays":40054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40352","slug":"monster-hospital","title":"Monster Hospital","description":"Monstre hôpital est libre interactif pour enfants jeu. Nos jeux pour les enfants sont la combinaison parfaite de divertissement et d'apprentissage! \nLaissez vos enfants, essayez ce jeu pour le plaisir et la connaissance. Le Monster Hospital - Jeu enfants ont 3 mini-jeux pour les enfants à jouer. Vos enfants vont apprendre sur les soins médicaux et profiter de raclage des enfants","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40352/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-hospital/embed?sid=1","plays":40054,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RTL6O","slug":"theory-of-planet-evolution","title":"Theory of Planet Evolution","description":"It is a highly customizable solar system building game, use you imagine to build you dream universe.\n\nThere is no limitation to build the solar, the only limitation is do you have time to customize it.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RTL6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/theory-of-planet-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":40053,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T55O1","slug":"asteroid","title":"Asteroid","description":"Classic is a beautiful spacecraft game that has to destroy all meteorites","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T55O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asteroid/embed?sid=1","plays":40053,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P122L","slug":"zoo-pinball","title":"Zoo Pinball","description":"Voyagez dans le temps et découvrez un ancien flipper ! Écoutez la bille métallique percuter les éléments et voyez votre score s'envoler ! Vivez l'expérience d'un véritable flipper animal à même le navigateur de votre téléphone ! Lancez la bille dans la gueule du puissant lion, du tigre ou de l'hippopotame pour marquer plein de points. \n","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P122L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zoo-pinball/embed?sid=1","plays":40053,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A0P46","slug":"alphabet-soup-for-kids","title":"Alphabet Soup for Kids","description":"Alphabet Soup for Kids is a fun and educational game for all ages.\nLearning with fun gives more attention and interest to kids.\nSo let us learn from this game. In this game we see the soup where the snacks are filled with alphabets, all you have to do is to collect the alphabets in order from A - Z which can be capitals and small letters.\nComplete all letters as soon as possible and complete the game.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A0P46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alphabet-soup-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40052,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ORION","slug":"angela-insta-fashion-stories","title":"Angela Insta Fashion Stories","description":"Welcome to the Angela Insta Fashion Stories. Angela feels about her popularity on social media. She has plans to attract the people on her side. She decided to share posts and stories among the popular hashtags. But she needs some experts like you. Come and join with Angela and make an attractive post. Have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ORION/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angela-insta-fashion-stories/embed?sid=1","plays":40050,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HHE0L","slug":"zombies-vs-halloween","title":"Zombies VS. Halloween","description":"Les zombies envahissent le far west ! Prenez vos armes et protégez les citoyens innocents contre les hordes de morts-vivants. Améliorez vos armes, équipez-vous ou embauchez des compagnions afin de stopper la prolifération des zombies ! Parviendrez-vous à survivre ?\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HHE0L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombies-vs-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":40050,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71SCA","slug":"christmas-pictures","title":"Christmas Pictures","description":"Christmas game for orientation and memory development for children and adults.                \nThis game will help your child to have fun and develop memory.                \nLook carefully and remember New Year's pictures!                \nClick to flip two identical images so that the images remain.                \nThe design of the game is very colorful and bright.                \nWith it you will plunge into the atmosphere of the New Year and Christmas holidays.                \nHave fun, adults and children, strengthening memory!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71SCA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-pictures/embed?sid=1","plays":40049,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KDA1R","slug":"desert-dakar-xtream","title":"Desert Dakar Xtream","description":"desert dakar xtream is car rally game, drive to desert collect coin and get the cash to buy another item","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KDA1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desert-dakar-xtream/embed?sid=1","plays":40049,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13I1B","slug":"mini-billiard","title":"Mini Billiard","description":"The game is a simple reinterpretation of the game of billiards but without rules and technicalities ... your child will be really happy to play it for hours and hours!\n\nJust to understand, you have to get all the billiard balls into the hole as quickly as possible trying to make the fewest mistakes!\n \nThis game is ideal for all children and teenagers who do not want a challenging and technical pool but rather prefer a fun, simple, not boring and colorful pastime with which to spend time.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13I1B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-billiard/embed?sid=1","plays":40049,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IG836","slug":"3d-falling-down","title":"3D Falling Down","description":"Whats it like to free fall at 100mph while trying to avoid random obstacles?\nFind out in our newest 3D Falling Down Game.\nNever ending gameplay that gets harder!\nHave Fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IG836/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-falling-down/embed?sid=1","plays":40048,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TTM46","slug":"match-link-io","title":"Match Link IO","description":"Try to link the similar blocks faster than your opponent to beat him!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TTM46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-link-io/embed?sid=1","plays":40048,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5WN4O","slug":"snowmen-vs-penguin","title":"Snowmen VS Penguin","description":"Snowmen vs Penguin an action-based defense game. The out cute little penguin is in deep trouble and has to defend the eggs from the dangerous snowmen. Help him to move fast and throw the snow balls and avoid them reaching the egg. If they reach the egg, you lose the game.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5WN4O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowmen-vs-penguin/embed?sid=1","plays":40048,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IM181","slug":"cubical-jump","title":"Cubical Jump","description":"Jump!🕹️\nHave fun in this little jumping game!\n\nNormal Mode!✨\nIn this mode, you can unlock characters, and your score will be saved every 50 points. No stress just enjoy jumping.\n\nChallenge Mode!🤺\nWhat did you said? too easy for you? you want more challenge? Don't worry dude! we got you! Here your score won't be saved unless you beat your previous score. Basically a classic game with the best score.\n\nRelax Mode!🌴\nJust make points and have fun, here you can't lose!\n\nLook at that! Combo!!🔥\nTap fast and you will do a combo! wait too much and you have to start again!\n\nUnlock more than 30 characters!🤖👻📺🐔🎇\nExactly 36 characters! everybody is unique and some have even special abilities!\n\nUnlock medals!🥇\n9 different medals to unlock! \n\nLocal Multiplayer🎎\nPlay with your friends! (or with random people why not)","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IM181/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cubical-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76LLG","slug":"block-triangle","title":"Block Triangle","description":"Triangle Block Puzzle Game. Are you ready to solve block puzzle games with rainbow triangles? Arrange shapes made up of triangles to fill up all kinds of designs!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76LLG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-triangle/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K185J","slug":"jumpy-the-legacy-of-a-chicken","title":"Jumpy! The Legacy of a Chicken","description":"A little nervous chicken, which has been affected by hormones, is ready to escape.\n\nUse your special abilities to escape from the slaughterhouse, jump on the walls, avoiding electric sparks.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K185J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumpy-the-legacy-of-a-chicken/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6BN45","slug":"the-dungeon-labyrinth","title":"The Dungeon Labyrinth","description":"Dead Ends, Enemies, Gems, Bombs, EasterEggs and much more... only on The Dungeon Labyrinth","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6BN45/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-dungeon-labyrinth/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4IG83","slug":"jumping-ninja","title":"Jumping Ninja","description":"Control the ninja jumper. Jump from line to line. Beware of enemies and try not to fail. Show your dexterity and get to the very top in the best time.\n\nControl:\n\nUse the \"A\" and \"D\" KEYS to move Left - Right.\n\nAnd the \"Space\" key for jumping. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4IG83/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumping-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E845U","slug":"duck-rescue-boat","title":"Duck Rescue Boat","description":"A shipment of ducks has fallen into the sea. The ducks are drifting surrounded by hungry octopuses. Manage the duck rescue boat, day and night, and collect as many ducks as you can. Watch out for the octopuses, there are a limited number of hits. Collect the life floats to increase the number of hits.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E845U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duck-rescue-boat/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10036","slug":"football-tricks","title":"Football Tricks","description":"Prenez le contrôle d'une équipe de football et devenez le maitre du terrain. Faites des figures incroyables et renforcez votre équipe de champions pour marquer des buts depuis n'importe quelle position!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10036/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-tricks/embed?sid=1","plays":40047,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P016J","slug":"cheese-helix-jump","title":"Cheese Helix Jump","description":"Helix jump est un jeu de défilement sans fin où vous évitez les pièges et collectez des pièces pour débloquer plus de plaisir","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P016J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cheese-jummp/embed?sid=1","plays":40046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8I1G6","slug":"creative-coloring","title":"Creative Coloring","description":"Coloring Creative is a fun coloring game that makes your creation improved. It's addictive and helpful to relax you and keep you creative. You can find various images to get colored, you have two options here to match the color or to freestyle, you can color with any color you want. Have fun exploring the creative artistic insight inside you and have fun. Unlock all achievements and have fun.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8I1G6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/creative-coloring/embed?sid=1","plays":40046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R17RH","slug":"happy-hopper","title":"Happy Hopper","description":"Can you help the Oomee time his jumps and reach the prize?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R17RH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-hopper/embed?sid=1","plays":40046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B6Z89","slug":"puzzlebot","title":"Puzzlebot","description":"Complete 7 different jigsaw puzzles on 3 different difficulty levels.\nPut the pieces of these seven stunning images in the right place, and complete the puzzle as fast as you can. If you need some help, try to touch the icon to find out where to place some of the pieces.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B6Z89/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzlebot/embed?sid=1","plays":40046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"68616","slug":"touch-wheels","title":"Touch Wheels","description":"touch wheels and a fantastic arcade game \nhow to play? simple just plug the wheels!\nwhat will be your record?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/68616/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/touch-wheels/embed?sid=1","plays":40046,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40350","slug":"kids-kitchen","title":"Kids Kitchen","description":"Êtes-vous prêt à ouvrir votre premier restaurant? Prenez votre tablier et toque et nous allons ouvrir votre restaurant. Comme vous le défi étoiles de restaurant à vos clients pour fou manger et découvrir le défi principal de l'alimentation!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40350/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-kitchen/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RO2RB","slug":"acorn-bot","title":"Acorn Bot","description":"Acorn Bot is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the ice cream cones while avoiding enemy bots, spikes, ground saws, and rotating lasers and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RO2RB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/acorn-bot/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12PN1","slug":"penguin-skip","title":"Penguin Skip","description":"Little penguin Spok likes to jump from one ice floe to another. He doesn’t like splashing into the water that much though. Help Penguin Spok in his journey! Tap anywhere on the right side of the screen to jump to the floe on the right and anywhere on the left to jump left. Don’t fall into the water, as Penguin Spok doesn’t like that at all (it’s a bit strange for a penguin, isn’t it?). From time to time there’s going to be some fish on the ice - collect that for extra points. \nAfter each game, depending on your score, you’ll get some pretty cool gifts. Tap on them to unravel and grab some super cool hats and scarfs for the Penguin Spok. There are over 200 combinations of the Spok’s outfits, enjoy finding your most favorite one!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12PN1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-skip/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66ATA","slug":"santa-gravity","title":"Santa Gravity","description":"Santa Gravity is a Christmas racing game where Santa's objective is to collect the greatest number of presents using the world's gravity and avoiding obstacles.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66ATA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-gravity/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R868R","slug":"mr-toro-2","title":"Mr Toro 2","description":"Mr Toro 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect money while avoiding the enemies, spikes, saws and flying robots and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.      \n      \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Mr Toro\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R868R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-toro-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4432T","slug":"sky-combat-squadron-battle","title":"Sky Combat Squadron Battle","description":"This game is made in Unity with C#. \nTry to shoot down the enemy to complete the mission.\nThe game has multi-levels \nTry to get more coins to buy and Upgrade System ( Plane & Skill) ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4432T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"94IGD","slug":"solitaire-grande","title":"Solitaire Grande","description":"Découvrez pourquoi partout dans le monde des millions de personnes jouent au Solitaire tous les jours ! Profitez d'un gameplay relaxant en piochant 1 ou 3 cartes. Déverrouillez des succès difficiles pour gagner des pièces et essayer de magnifiques thèmes. Jouez avec différentes faces et dos de cartes, ainsi que des arrière-plans. Vous ne connaissez pas les règles ? Ne vous inquiétez pas, les instructions pour les débutants, ainsi que des indices et des annulations illimités, sont inclus !\n","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/94IGD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-grande/embed?sid=1","plays":40043,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9N552","slug":"jewels-mine","title":"Jewels Mine","description":"Jewels Mine is a match 3 game. \n\nSwap and match 3 or more gems of the same type and make points and special power ups.\n\nEarn points and compete with your friends and with all other players around the world in the global leaderboards!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9N552/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewels-mine/embed?sid=1","plays":40042,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"441OS","slug":"pop-pop-the-balloons","title":"Pop Pop the Balloons","description":"Hit with your finger the blowing up balloons on the screen!    \n    \nHow To Play:    \nHit the blowing up balloons on the screen, came on don’t let them vanish away! you have just 60 second to pop all points! so focus on all your senses and on your extraordinary a sight!    \n    \nNow get out all your power against the balloons! Came on hurry up! Watch out the colors balloons, white give more points than the others.    \n    \nProduct feature bullets:    \n• Amazing effects    \n• Fantastic gameplay    \n• Endless gameplay    \n• Easy to play    \n• Beautiful graphics","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/441OS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pop-pop-the-balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":40042,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20Z46","slug":"block-puzzle","title":"Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Blockpuzzle, challenge physics until you fall to the floor without leaving the screen, pass all the levels and reach the end, what are you waiting for ??? go now and play Blockpuzzle and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20Z46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40041,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"95595","slug":"funny-spider","title":"Funny Spider","description":"About the game: Get to the top and prove that you are the best.Game controls: To jump up and to the left, tap the left side of the screen, it will jump to the left.To jump to the right and up, tap the right side of the screen.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/95595/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-spider/embed?sid=1","plays":40040,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SGMCT","slug":"maximum-streets-drag-race","title":"Maximum Streets - Drag Race","description":"Are you fast enough for the streets? Prove it by beating every skilled racers in this ultimate drag race.\n\nDrag race through busy highways and obstacles. Try not to destroy your brand new street racing cars!\n\nControls:\nCar accelerates automatically\nA and D - steer\nE - shift up\n","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SGMCT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maximum-streets-drag-race/embed?sid=1","plays":40040,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE47T","slug":"monster-live","title":"Monster Live","description":"$55","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE47T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-live/embed?sid=1","plays":40040,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40446","slug":"kitty-take-care-new-born-baby","title":"Kitty Take Care New Born Baby","description":"The cats love for her little ones is really an adorable view. Here the pet mom cat has given birth to a very cute kitten now she has to take all the necessary care for her kitten. Help the mom cat to take care of the new born kitty to keep the baby healthy and safe. You must follow all the prescribed tasks with the given steps to complete the total care of the kitten. Bath, feed, and dress up the adorable kitten and have fun with this lovable game for kids.","category":"Course","tags":["junior","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40446/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kitty-take-care-new-born-baby/embed?sid=1","plays":40040,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40117","slug":"key-shield","title":"Key & Shield","description":"Bienvenue dans Key & Shield le nouveau jeu d'aventure HTML5 où vous devrez sauver tous vos amis. En effet, un ange un peu tête en l'air vous a permit de sortir de votre cage et vous a donné la \"clé\" et le \"bouclier\", alors profitez-en!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40117/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/key-shield/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M1TRB","slug":"dead-target-shoot-zombies","title":"Dead Target Shoot Zombies","description":"Grab your rifle, your gun or whatever you have to survive the zombie apocalypse. Kill zombies and earn points to upgrade weapons. It is free! Don't miss this opportunity! Hurry up before we all turn into zombies!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M1TRB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dead-target-shoot-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6G741","slug":"lemmings-savior","title":"Lemmings Savior","description":"Lemmings Savior is a highly addictive game where you control a life craft to bounce the crazy lemmings to safety as they jump off the cliff.       \nGrab the craft and try to save all crazy Lemmings that you can!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6G741/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lemmings-savior/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9I2N3","slug":"alien-run","title":"Alien Run","description":"alien run is a html5 endless run game, run and jump avoid obstacles and monsters ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9I2N3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-run/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44M60","slug":"smash-the-ants","title":"Smash the Ants","description":"These ants are everywhere! Hurry up stop them before they go out of the screen! your last line of defense.\nHow many points can You score? Enjoy it!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44M60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smash-the-ants/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4IEAG","slug":"car-garage-tycoon-simulation-game","title":"Car Garage Tycoon - Simulation Game","description":"Hey Guys! Get ready to give different auto service in your own car garage store. Customers will come to your garage to have various activities like car repairing, car wash, car painting, fueling & lubricating, food and etc. Upgrade your garage store and other products to earn big amount of coins. Expand your garage to gain more parking spots, start more service and for more stores. So what are you waiting for? Get this addictive game & start playing it right now.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4IEAG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-garage-tycoon-simulation-game/embed?sid=1","plays":40039,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E5I5","slug":"tiny-zombies-2","title":"Tiny Zombies 2","description":"Tiny Zombies 2 is an exciting zombie-killing game and you have to defend your area without getting infected.\nKill as many zombies and they will become faster on further waves, so boost your reflexes and kill the fast-paced game.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E5I5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-zombies-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40038,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3SO5O","slug":"obstacle","title":"Obstacle","description":"Welcome to Obstacle, have fun tackled all levels of increasing difficulty avoiding obstacles and accumulating points, what are you waiting for? Go play Obstacle now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3SO5O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/obstacle/embed?sid=1","plays":40038,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7AEW8","slug":"the-word-search","title":"The Word Search","description":"Play the best word search game. English crosswords. Word search and word game. If you like puzzle games and fun games, this game is for you. It is one of difficult games and different games.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7AEW8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-word-search/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IP2M6","slug":"mission-impossible-save-christmas","title":"Mission Impossible-Save Christmas","description":"It's time to save christmas! Santa claus has lost all of his present and he doesn't know how to get them back, therefore you're going to use use his prodigious hat to regain them.\n\nControls:\nYou have to hold down the left button to make the hat follow you, you have to collect the green presents to get an higher score, but avoid the red ones, because they're dangerous!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IP2M6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mission-impossible-save-the-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1813W","slug":"pawky","title":"Pawky","description":"The pawky jump platformer game is all about jumping on platforms. The player must be quick and agile enough to avoid obstacles, but also know when they have reached their destination so as not to waste time or energy by revisiting locations already explored moments before!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1813W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pawky/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"10S01","slug":"steve-ball-temple","title":"Steve Ball Temple","description":"Steve with the ball got lost in the temple and he has to pass the monsters and help him survive! steve you have to collect the stars collect the stars and move towards the end of the level you need to collect 3 stars but you can pass the level with 1 star steve.  \n\nHow to Play?\n*Use WASD Keys to play.               \n*Watch out for the enemies to survive!               \n*You can climb on top of monsters and kill them.               \n*Double jump is active in the game.        \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/10S01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-ball-temple/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"79247","slug":"tenpuzzle","title":"TenPuzzle","description":"Welcome to TenPuzzle, have fun choosing from 10 different puzzles by combining all the pieces, solving them and accumulating points to increase your score, what are you waiting for ???? Go play TenPuzzle now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/79247/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tenpuzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7521H","slug":"the-maze","title":"The Maze","description":"This is my first game. I hope you will enjoy it!\nthe game is very simple; you have to reach the red zone to pass the level and start the forthcoming level.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7521H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":40037,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R97S4","slug":"swing-helicopter","title":"Swing Helicopter","description":"It is easy to control but hard to get a high score! Just tap the screen to control the helicopter and try to avoid colliding with miscellaneous obstacles.\nThere are many achievements for you to challenge.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R97S4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swing-helicopter/embed?sid=1","plays":40036,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1N1C7","slug":"mr-wick-one-bullet","title":"Mr Wick One Bullet","description":"Hey John, you need to find your way to defeat criminals.\nEach level is a challenge. Are you ready to accept it? You are Mr.Wick, you can do it!\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1N1C7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-wick-one-bullet/embed?sid=1","plays":40035,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SS1IO","slug":"solitaire-legend","title":"Solitaire Legend","description":"Vous souvenez-vous de l'époque avant internet ? À passer son temps à jouer au même vieux jeu sur l'ordinateur. Le jeu de tri de cartes classique - le Solitaire ! Tout le monde le connaît, et si ce n'est pas le cas, c'est très facile à apprendre. Profitez d'indices et annulations. En gagnant des pièces, vous pouvez débloquer différents skins.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SS1IO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-legend/embed?sid=1","plays":40034,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3LAK2","slug":"dunk-ball","title":"Dunk Ball","description":"You are good at basketball, show your skills in scoring points in the baskets.\n\nJust move the basket to score each ball that passes","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3LAK2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dunk-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40033,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SSAIS","slug":"scorpion-solitaire","title":"Scorpion Solitaire","description":"If you are a big fan of Klondike and Spider solitaires but you are looking for new variations, you'll surely like Scorpion Solitaire. Choose among three different game's difficulty: Easy Medium and Hard and complete the solitaire with the least number of moves.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SSAIS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scorpion-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":40033,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6VT42","slug":"jet-adventure","title":"Jet Adventure","description":"Jet Adventure Online is the perfect game for those who love a challenge. In this game, you must help your jet avoid obstacles and reach the finish line as fast as possible. With great graphics and sound effects, Jet Adventure Online is sure to keep you entertained for hours on end.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6VT42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jet-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40031,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MNH1W","slug":"the-man-from-the-window","title":"The Man from the Window","description":"$56","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MNH1W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-man-from-the-window/embed?sid=1","plays":40031,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61O16","slug":"toto","title":"Totò","description":"Welcome to Totò, have fun in 3 levels of increasing difficulty where you will have to collect coins to increase your best score while avoiding obstacles, what are you waiting for? Go play Totò now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61O16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/toto/embed?sid=1","plays":40031,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40113","slug":"freecell-solitaire","title":"Freecell Solitaire","description":"Retrouvez le célèbre \"Freecell Solitaire\" dans cette version HTML5 fidèle à l'original!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40113/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/freecell-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":40031,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C223X","slug":"space-pixel","title":"Space Pixel","description":"Venture into this space adventure! In this game you will have the opportunity to play numerous game modes continuously updated. Collect gems with which you can buy crates to upgrade ships and level up by accumulating points by playing! Good luck!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C223X/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-pixel/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U5A5S","slug":"super-coconut-basket","title":"Super Coconut Basket","description":"Super Coconut Basketball a fun sports game to play on. Tap and throw the ball, control its angle and power, then shoot towards the hoop.\nThe perfect effect and physic effect will help you see more clearly.\nThe game is an endless arcade game, then shoot towards the hoop to win the levels. as the difficulty could increase, there are four different random movements for the hoop; You have just three shots to complete each level!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U5A5S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-coconut-basket/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51S6U","slug":"supermarket-simulator","title":"Supermarket Simulator","description":"hey, how about you become a market owner? the shelves can be empty, sell and fill the shelves. Do not forget that there are thieves, sometimes they can take the products on the shelf and escape. the floor can get dirty, you need to clean the floor with a brush. Market cleanliness is very important. Don't leave the market dirty. If the products are low in the market, do not forget to go by truck and refresh the products.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51S6U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/supermarket-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RC77N","slug":"cherry-inhere-circle-pong-king","title":"Cherry Inhere-Circle Pong King","description":"$57","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RC77N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cherry-inhere-circle-pong-king/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"222S6","slug":"fire-steve-and-water-alex","title":"Fire Steve and Water Alex","description":"Bad things happen to Alex and Steve this time, and Steve gets his firepower. Alex also gets water power. If steve touches water because of fire, he dies. If Alex touches fire with lava, he dies, so you have to be very careful by collecting all the food on the way, you should collect points and get 3 elements, definitely collect diamonds, gold and emeralds, otherwise the portal will not form.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/222S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fire-steve-and-water-alex/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2I50J","slug":"kingdom-of-ninja-2","title":"Kingdom of Ninja 2","description":"In this game, which is the 2nd series of the kingdom of ninja game, it is to overcome the obstacles and reach the chest that will take you to the next level without being eaten by the monsters. reach the chest and reach the next level. Finish 10 different levels and reach the end of the game.  \n\nHow to Play?\n\"Z\" Jump + \"Arrow key\" Move / Mobile Touch Control","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2I50J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kingdom-of-ninja-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U6T5K","slug":"building-stacking","title":"Building Stacking","description":"Building stacking is a 3d game where you have the challenge of trying to stack as many floors as you can in a building. Click for the floor to stop at the right moment and try to beat your record and have fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6T5K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/building-stacking/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"09RTR","slug":"fighter-tank","title":"Fighter Tank","description":"Fighter tank online games are a lot like war games. They're fast-paced and full of action, and they often require quick decisions. That's why product managers who are looking for a challenge should consider playing fighter tank online games. They're a great way to sharpen your decision-making skills and learn more about strategizing. Players can enter into the fray and battle it out with other players from around the world.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/09RTR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fighter-tank/embed?sid=1","plays":40030,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0612K","slug":"breaking-fall","title":"Breaking Fall","description":"Drop the elevator down and try to reach the finish line. Easy to play Hard to master.\nHow to play:\n- Press to Brake\n- Release to Fall","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0612K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/breaking-fall/embed?sid=1","plays":40029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I2514","slug":"floppy-bird","title":"Floppy Bird","description":"Help little Red Bird to flying through the sky trying to avoid obstacles that can kill the bird and you need to help the bird pass through it!        \n        \nIt's easy to start and hard to finish game; tap on the screen for free falling flapping bird to fly through obstacles!        \n        \nHow to play:        \n-Tap to flap your wings to fly.        \n-Avoid the pipes.        \n        \nFloppy Red Bird is the best bird game to play and entertain your kids for hours!        \n        \nFlap your wings to fly... and have fun with this great game!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I2514/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/floppy-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":40029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18011","slug":"mazy","title":"Mazy","description":"Find your own way through the maze and collect all points to complete it!\n\nThere are a total of 20 mazes for you to find your way through!\n\n- 15 main levels \n- 5 extra levels in the Endless mode","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18011/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mazy/embed?sid=1","plays":40029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T069R","slug":"puzzle-collect-color","title":"Puzzle - Collect color","description":"Guess the secret of the little puzzle. The goal of the game is to collect pieces of the same color in each corner. To move a chip, move the mouse pointer over it and, pressing the left button on it, move the pointer, without releasing the button, to the desired free place. On touch screens, press the chip with your finger and, without removing your finger from the screen, move the chip.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T069R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-collect-color/embed?sid=1","plays":40029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21174","slug":"rombo","title":"Rombo","description":"You are a mercenary who got hired by the President when the renegades kidnapped mayor's daughter. And some ministers. Also his secretary too. Go through various battles and mini bosses that are challenging to be conquered. Upgrade all equipment and find other mercenaries, and work together to destroy the enemy.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21174/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rombo/embed?sid=1","plays":40029,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0J0EE","slug":"jack-o-gunner","title":"Jack'o Gunner","description":"Jack-O Gunner is a casual action and survival game with Halloween theme. Your aim is to kill all the skeletons, upgrade your skills and survive as long as possible.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0J0EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jack-o-gunner/embed?sid=1","plays":40028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SPRHP","slug":"sad-or-happy","title":"Sad or Happy","description":"This online emoji-matching game can help improve your mood by providing a fun and easy way to connect with others. The game is simple - just match the emoji with the corresponding emotion. If you're feeling sad, try matching the sad emoji with a happy one. Or, if you're feeling happy, try matching the happy emoji with a sad one.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SPRHP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sad-or-happy/embed?sid=1","plays":40028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1S0PA","slug":"super-phantom-rabbit","title":"Super Phantom Rabbit","description":"A cool and handsome rabbit who thinks he has superpowers must reach the guards at the end of the episode and join the guardian army in the last episode. He must protect his life and his forest. Beware, there are many cool and powerful monsters!\n\nHow to play?\nWASD and mobile touch control (double jump available)","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1S0PA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-phantom-rabbit/embed?sid=1","plays":40028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O9188","slug":"zooboo","title":"Zooboo","description":"Zooboo is a 2D Adventure game where you play as Zooboo, whose mission is to collect all of the orange fruits while avoiding poisonous fruits(purple), enemies and spikes. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nWASD or arrow keys for movement.   \nPress \"W\" or \"Up arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O9188/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zooboo/embed?sid=1","plays":40028,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7I4R6","slug":"spider","title":"Spider","description":"Spider game, drag the arrows to the right point to open the door to the spider and go to the next level, you have two levels the first with 5 levels at 60 seconds and the second with 5 other levels at 55 seconds, let's see if you can finish the 10 levels totals","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7I4R6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider/embed?sid=1","plays":40027,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NI67O","slug":"inoi-2","title":"Inoi 2","description":"Inoi 2 is a 2D simple platformer where you need to avoid green, yellow and red cactus of different sizes and reach the red flag. You have to collect all of the water containers before reaching the red flag in order to go to the next level.      \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. This is the sequel of the original Inoi game.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow keys\" for player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NI67O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/inoi-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40026,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"148ER","slug":"red-bird","title":"Red Bird","description":"Red Bird is a highly addictive game for all kids and teens! Tap to fly and go from side to side earning 1 point or go for the cherry and get an extra 5 points; but avoid the crowns!\nRed Bird is simple game but addictive gameplay.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/148ER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/red-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":40026,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FA0AO","slug":"platfoban","title":"Platfoban","description":"Platfoban is a Sokoban-style puzzle game with a platforming element! You need to collect all the coins at every level. There are two modes in the game: the platforming mode, in which you can run and jump, and the Sokoban mode, in which you can move blocks, coins, etc. In Sokoban mode, chest monsters wake up, attack, and chase the main character. In platforming mode, chests sleep and can be used as platforms.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FA0AO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/platfoban/embed?sid=1","plays":40026,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20064","slug":"dropme","title":"Dropme","description":"Dans ce jeu inspiré par \"Cut The Rope\", aidez de mignonnes petites creatures à grimper dans le tube! Relevez les challenges proposés et prenez-vous d'affection pour ces adorables bêtes!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20064/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dropme/embed?sid=1","plays":40026,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3R47R","slug":"sport-car-hexagon","title":"Sport Car Hexagon","description":"Are you ready to win in the sport car hexagon game? If you want to be a winner, you must be the last person to fall off the cliff. you have to be first on the road to victory. Be the first and be the most survivor. grab the scores, be the winner\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3R47R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sport-car-hexagon/embed?sid=1","plays":40026,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8H2AL","slug":"the-black","title":"The Black","description":"The Black is a minimalist puzzle game. Your goal is to turn all the tiles balck by clicking / tapping at them, but clicking a tile will also flip the adjacent tiles.\n\nEnjoy the puzzle in 3x3, 4x4, 5x5 and 6x6 grid difficulties.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8H2AL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-black/embed?sid=1","plays":40025,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OR0O3","slug":"rich-or-poor","title":"Rich or Poor","description":"Get to the finish line of the track and try to collect money and more money you collect, the better your outfit will look","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OR0O3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rich-or-poor/embed?sid=1","plays":40022,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5L986","slug":"color-fill","title":"Color Fill","description":"Fill the entire board with one color!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5L986/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-fill/embed?sid=1","plays":40021,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RF81","slug":"finger-rage","title":"Finger Rage","description":"Tap the more you can to make more points and earn money, but try not to make any mistakes or you'll have to start again!!! We've tried to make the challenge as realistic and difficult as possible allowing endless gameplay. Try to earn a lot of money and unlock all hands! How far can you get?\nKey Features:\n• Simple Gameplay!\n• Nine Funny Hands to Unlock! \n• Cool Toon Graphics! \n• One Click to Play!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RF81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/finger-rage/embed?sid=1","plays":40021,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ERPVM","slug":"purple-monster-adventure","title":"Purple Monster Adventure","description":"In this incredible platform game, help the monster to reach the end of the valley, going through obstacles and facing his mushroom enemies.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ERPVM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/purple-monster-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":40020,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E080P","slug":"space-fighter-2099","title":"Space Fighter 2099","description":"Destroy all enemy spaceships!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E080P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-fighter-2099/embed?sid=1","plays":40019,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3ITRI","slug":"spider-solitaire-cards","title":"Spider Solitaire Cards","description":"Obtenez le meilleur score ou faites juste une partie relaxante de Spider Solitaire ! Plongez directement dans l'action, aucun réglage supplémentaire n'est requis. Créez des piles de cartes, du Roi à l'As.\n","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3ITRI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider-solitaire-cards/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83N1C","slug":"tictoc-nightlife-fashion","title":"Tictoc Nightlife Fashion","description":"Are you ready to set your night life on fire?\nDress up the girl in the most gorgeous way by following the hint.\nGet ready to take selfies and try to get more likes. So that you can buy \nnew additional items and explore different styles. Make her into a tictoc star!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83N1C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictoc-nightlife-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9165L","slug":"go-go-gorilla","title":"Go Go Gorilla","description":"Help the Gorilla to collect all the soccer balls on the screen, stay balanced on the white lines but be careful not to fall into the void and lose the game! try to be as fast as possible to complete the levels and then once you have completed a whole Stadium check your best score on the leaderboard; Will you be the fastest of all.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9165L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/go-go-gorilla/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E4LW1","slug":"stickman-war-multiplayer","title":"Stickman War Multiplayer","description":"Stickman War Multiplayer is a multiplayer game set in a paper world. Choose your character, face enemies in a random match, or your friends in a combined match.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E4LW1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-war-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"QQ7CO","slug":"quizcoaster","title":"QuizCoaster","description":"QuizCoaster is an Amusement and Theme Park's based game.\nWith QuizCoaster you can test and improve your knowledge about amusement, water and theme parks od the world.\n \nYou have only 5 minutes to answer as many questions as possible and score as many points as you can!\n \nLeaderboard online!","category":"Aventure","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/QQ7CO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quizcoaster/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B0445","slug":"blast","title":"Blast","description":"Try to land the mine in the safe area with the least number of attempts!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B0445/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blast/embed?sid=1","plays":40018,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7E6R","slug":"cleaner","title":"Cleaner","description":"In this game with 50 levels you will have to tap a slot on the grid so that it and its 4 neighbors (vertically and horizontally) are also changed. You must make the grid clean!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7E6R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cleaner/embed?sid=1","plays":40017,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MD9O0","slug":"emoji-down-the-hill","title":"Emoji Down The Hill","description":"Emoji Down The Hill c'est un jeu en zigzag avec l'unité a plusieurs emoji","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MD9O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/emoji-down-the-hill/embed?sid=1","plays":40017,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OSO71","slug":"color-blocks-1010","title":"Color Blocks 1010","description":"Color Blocks 1010 is an addictive block puzzle game that is great for brain training!\n\nWelcome to an incredibly addictive puzzle game with an original plot of events!\n\nColored Blocks 1010 is a simple logical but difficult puzzle game to complete.\n\nThere are no time limits or tasks in the game.\n\nThe graphics of the game are suitable for all ages, Color Blocks 1010 will be interesting to play for both children and adults!\n\n\nGame Features:\n⭐️ Availability of ready-made various themes.\n⭐️ A game for all ages.\n⭐️ Many auxiliary bonuses for passing the game\n⭐️ Night theme to relax your eyes and play comfortably before going to sleep.\n\n\nTrain, play and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OSO71/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-blocks-1010/embed?sid=1","plays":40017,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"939ID","slug":"letter-tracing-for-kids","title":"Letter Tracing for Kids","description":"Letter Tracing Games for Kids is an educational game for kids designed to teach kids writing ABC letters alphabets.   \n   \nThis app is suitable for kids of all ages including toddler, preschool kids and even kindergarten kids can also use it learn letters, draw number and shapes tracing or writing ABC with animal images!   \n   \nYour kids love this great educational app! when he play he learn the right shape of letter and listen a really funny music!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/939ID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/letter-tracing-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40017,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1L7LU","slug":"2048-number-ball","title":"2048 Number Ball","description":"The Eatable Numbers Ball Game is a fun way to get your child involved and active while they're playing outside. Eatable Numbers Ball Game eat as many numbers from 1 to 9 that appear on your screen when they pop up. You’ll get more points if it's a Lowest number!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1L7LU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-number-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C6O1I","slug":"arkanoid-bricks","title":"Arkanoid Bricks","description":"Pass through challenging 60 levels and challenge your friends in this classic Arkanoid game!\nArkanoid Bricks -In this classic game you need to destroy various bricks with their unique characteristics with the help of a ball, you will also meet various skills that will help you do this, such as lasers, fireball, giant ball, cannon, etc.","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C6O1I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arkanoid-bricks/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54655","slug":"crazy-jumper","title":"Crazy Jumper","description":"Crazy Jumper is the Jump Platformer online jumping game! How far will you jump?   \nPlay Crazy Jumper  online for free - a fun platform game that you can play here.   \nIf you are a great fan of adventurous games, then you have got a treat in store for you. Crazy Jumper is a simple yet entertaining game. Playing it brings out some exhilarating experience. On the face of it, this game seems to be simple and plain but the reality is that in order to win the game (as well as earn some cool points on your way) you need to jump from rock to rock while avoiding various obstacles.   ","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54655/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-jumper/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HALLS","slug":"petits-chevaux-small-horses","title":"Petits Chevaux Small Horses","description":"Le jeu des petits chevaux, à jouer à 1, 2, 3 ou 4 joueurs. C'est trop génial ! \nRetrouvez le jeu de plateau de votre enfance, avec les petits chevaux sur votre mobile ou votre tablette. Ce grand jeu classique, est tout simplement l'un des jeux les plus simples mais aussi l'un des meilleurs jeux de société de tous les temps. \n\nJouez contre l'intelligence artificielle ou contre des amis, et amusez-vous autant que vous le voulez.\n\nQui rentrera tous ses chevaux dans la case centrale le premier ?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HALLS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/petits-chevaux-small-horses/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1116S","slug":"sparrow-flappy","title":"Sparrow Flappy","description":"Sparrow Fly to get this  to pass through circles to get higher score win...","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1116S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sparrow-flappy/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RAYNS","slug":"fantasy-creatures-princess-laboratory","title":"Fantasy Creatures Princess Laboratory","description":"Princesse Eliza adore les animaux et la magie. Un jour, elle a eu l'idée d'utiliser ses pouvoirs magiques pour créer de nouveaux animaux fabuleux. Rendez-vous au laboratoire de la princesse et, en utilisant divers composants naturels et magiques, découvrez de nouvelles espèces de créatures avec Elisa. Pouvez-vous les créer tous?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RAYNS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fantasy-creatures-princess-laboratory/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2SOI0","slug":"neon-invaders","title":"Neon Invaders","description":"“Neon Invaders” is a game inspired by one of the first games ever created, Space Invaders. A shoot-up style game, where the player must defeat enemies before they reach you. With arcade mechanics and easy gameplay, it allows great fun. Defeat all enemies and win each level, advancing to accumulate the most points. The graphics were created in the neon style, they are colorful and beautiful.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2SOI0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-invaders/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56O69","slug":"piano-tile","title":"Piano Tile","description":"The main goal is:\nDon't touch the withe tiles!  \nEnjoy it!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56O69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/piano-tile/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CCS6U","slug":"click-and-color-dinosaurs","title":"Click and Color Dinosaurs","description":"In this great cool game you have over 30 different Dinosaurs to color!     \nThis game is really suitable for everyone; just one click or touch to color the dinosaurs! enjoy it!  \nIt's a baby quiet game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CCS6U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/click-and-color-dinosaurs/embed?sid=1","plays":40015,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7N4IV","slug":"ferrari-track-driving","title":"Ferrari Track Driving","description":"Select different Ferrari cars and test drive them across the track.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7N4IV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ferrari-track-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":40014,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TU424","slug":"super-tank-battle","title":"Super Tank Battle","description":"On Console Tank Battle is very Classical game. \n\nSuper Tank Battle is a modern style Tank Battle Game with new attractive elements and 500 build-in maps, you no longer need to play on Emulator anymore.\n\nThis is the game of modern war, please boom the map, summon your alliance, and strike the Enemy! Clash It!\nPrepare the tank battle, prepare the tank modern city war! \n\nThere are 5 different difficulty levels (from easy to crazy). It should meet different people need.\n\nGame Rule 101:\n- Defence your base, and destroy all enemy tanks\n- If your tank or your base is destroyed, it will be game over. \n\nFeatures:\n- have 500 Maps can be played\n- helper tank (summon alliance), it is like a 2nd player to help you (Computer AI control)\n- special items in game\n- classical tank battle game's style\n- 20 enemy tanks per map","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TU424/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-tank-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":40014,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40290","slug":"monster-nail-doctor","title":"Monster Nail Doctor","description":"Each one of these four creepy creatures has really been neglecting themselves lately. They could definitely use some monstrous manicures. Can you fix up their feet in this game for girls? Help them go from ghoulish to gorgeous!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40290/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-nail-doctor/embed?sid=1","plays":40013,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"V0N00","slug":"alex-and-steve-nether","title":"Alex and Steve Nether","description":"In the 2nd adventure of the beloved couple alex and steven, the portal door suddenly opens to the nether map, which is covered with dangers full of red. You have to help them survive. alex needs you steve , stevin needs you alex you two should go back to your world together. You have to go back to your own world. be careful everywhere is full of tnt.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/V0N00/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alex-and-steve-nether/embed?sid=1","plays":40013,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3B668","slug":"robot-awake","title":"Robot Awake","description":"Wake the robots!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3B668/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-awake/embed?sid=1","plays":40013,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E450E","slug":"outer-planet","title":"Outer Planet","description":"The outer planet has been invaded by aliens! You need to save the planet and fight back. The game is free to play online. Outer planet alien online game is a free browser game where you fight aliens on different planets","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E450E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/outer-planet/embed?sid=1","plays":40012,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"92G55","slug":"brutusgame","title":"BrutusGame","description":"easy game, help the ball reach the goal","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/92G55/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brutusgame/embed?sid=1","plays":40012,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"295BV","slug":"beach-drive","title":"Beach Drive","description":"Driving your favorite car, rush along the tropical beach avoiding obstacles. Collect coins and buy new cars. Remember the pleasant moments of summer vacation!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/295BV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beach-drive/embed?sid=1","plays":40012,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D0409","slug":"roodo","title":"Roodo","description":"Roodo is a sci-fi themed 2D platformer where you have to collect the keys while avoiding the green enemy robots, spikes and ground saws and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level.      \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D0409/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roodo/embed?sid=1","plays":40012,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S9YS6","slug":"jelly-cute-rush","title":"Jelly Cute Rush","description":"jelly cute rush is a match 3 html5 puzzle game, draw lines and match as many jelly as possible to get score ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S9YS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jelly-cute-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":40011,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1B01B","slug":"kuma-bear-2","title":"Kuma Bear 2","description":"Kuma Bear 2 is a 2D platformer where you play as a bear who have to collect all of the chocolate bars while avoiding the enemy dogs and foxes, flying birds, spikes and pins and reach your house in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Kuma Bear\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1B01B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kuma-bear-2/embed?sid=1","plays":40011,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4226S","slug":"sushi-drop","title":"Sushi Drop","description":"Drop the Sushi a fun puzzle game to save the sushi.\nThe Sushi Brothers are completing the ancient right of passage that all little Sushi must complete.\nIf they want to land safely on the plates of happy customers at the hibachi.\nThey must first practice landing safely under the most challenging of circumstances.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4226S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sushi-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":40011,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T77Z1","slug":"tri-puzzle","title":"Tri Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Tri Puzzle. Hey kids! welcome to the new challenges of the puzzle game. Drag the block and drop and correct position. Sounds simple right? This is a new fun and interactive game for kids. Play and have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T77Z1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tri-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40011,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16766","slug":"inquisitive","title":"Inquisitive","description":"inquisitive is an addicting and fun trivia game. Test your knowledge on a huge variety of categories that appear randomly. Remember, the fast you answer the questions the higher your score will be at the end!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16766/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/inquisitive/embed?sid=1","plays":40010,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5NL64","slug":"pingball","title":"PingBall","description":"Ping pong that increases his desire to play, the ball becomes faster and faster, you will have to be fast too to make your record","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5NL64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pingball/embed?sid=1","plays":40010,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40828","slug":"snowboard-king-2022","title":"Snowboard King 2022","description":"Prêt pour les pistes ? Frayez-vous un chemin à travers les montagnes. Évitez les arbres et les rochers et dérapez sur la glace. Étudiez chaque piste et trouvez le chemin le plus court pour descendre la colline. Pouvez-vous échapper à l'avalanche aussi ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40828/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowboard-king-2022/embed?sid=1","plays":40009,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ML82","slug":"merge-to-million","title":"Merge To Million","description":"Merge to Million is a blocks-combining game with an objective to reach one million in number!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ML82/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-to-million/embed?sid=1","plays":40009,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2D529","slug":"diff","title":"DIFF","description":"Quickly tap the single difference in each set of characters, see how far you can get!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2D529/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/diff/embed?sid=1","plays":40008,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40424","slug":"journey-fox","title":"Journey Fox","description":"Help little fox to run through all challenging puzzle levels. Drag objects on the field to create a path and reach all gems of this funny adventure!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40424/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/journey-fox/embed?sid=1","plays":40008,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1K17N","slug":"poker-match-king","title":"Poker Match King","description":"Poker Match King is an online puzzle game that challenges players to match three Poker card symbols. The game is easy to learn but difficult to master, and offers hours of fun and excitement for players of all ages. Poker Match King is an online puzzle game that challenges players to match three of a kind. With multiple levels of difficulty, the game is perfect for players of all ages and experience levels.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1K17N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poker-match-king/embed?sid=1","plays":40008,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"483K6","slug":"a-b-kids","title":"A & B Kids","description":"A & B Kids is the best way for your kids to learn their ABCs! Our educational games are designed specifically for teaching kids the alphabet in a fun and engaging way. A&B Kids is making educational games for kids that help them learn the alphabet. These games are not only entertaining for kids, but they also help them develop essential skills like hand-eye coordination and problem solving.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/483K6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/a-and-b-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40006,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N86A1","slug":"flappy-santa","title":"Flappy Santa","description":"You're Santa is Christmas and you flight in the sky but avoid the pipes!  \nTry to resiste the more you can and sign your best record!  \nEnjoy it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N86A1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-santa/embed?sid=1","plays":40006,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T35CH","slug":"park-the-cars","title":"Park the Cars","description":"Bienvenue dans Park the Cars, plongez-vous dans la conduite de votre véhicule sans le casser, garez la voiture et passez les niveaux. Qu'attendez-vous, allez jouer à Park the Cars maintenant et le plaisir est garanti !!!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T35CH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/park-the-cars/embed?sid=1","plays":40006,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FA715","slug":"space-defense-idle","title":"Space Defense Idle","description":"Votre mission est de garantir la sécurité de tout l'espace, pour cela vous devez détruire le vaisseau ennemi qui tente d'envahir l'orbite terrestre. Tirez avec votre canon autant que nécessaire pour protéger les Terriens!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FA715/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-defense-idle/embed?sid=1","plays":40005,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67591","slug":"the-cave-of-terror","title":"The Cave of Terror","description":"The adventure begins right from the cave of horrors. Could you help the hero run as far as possible, collect coins and kill enemies. Be careful and have fun! ... You want to learn how to play this game so badly, right? You can simply disable the ad blocker to watch this amazing step-by-step video. Description. The adventure begins right from the cave of horrors. Could you help the hero run as far as possible, collect coins and kill enemies. Be careful and have fun!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67591/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-cave-of-terror/embed?sid=1","plays":40005,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1I8RO","slug":"truck-factory-for-kids","title":"Truck Factory for Kids","description":"It is a very colorful game educational game for kids in kindergarten. This game is accessible not only games for boys but also to girls. If you are fond of cars and trucks or anything connected with building games thematic, you can join us in Truck Factory For Kids. I hope you can have fun learning truck games!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1I8RO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/truck-factory-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":40005,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8MH3O","slug":"alien-mahjong","title":"Alien Mahjong","description":" Try to remove all the tiles in those 3 levels by matching at least 2 of the same tiles at once. Use the bomb mode when no matches are left to generate new ones and clean the whole level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8MH3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":40004,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EAPAE","slug":"save-the-apple","title":"Save the Apple","description":"THE GAME\nIn this amazing game you have to save a poor Apple from many enemies that are going to try to destroy it in every way they can, by eating  it or even turning it to dust. Now touch and move the Apple and survive as long as you can. \n\nENHANCEMENTS\n Among many enhancements, you'll find the Iron Ingot that grants your Apple invulnerability for a short amount of time as well as the appearance of an Iron Apple able to defeat some enemies.\n\nWhat are you waiting for? The Apple needs you, start to play and save\n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EAPAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-apple/embed?sid=1","plays":40004,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40219","slug":"sushi-matching","title":"Sushi Matching","description":"Le but du jeu est simple: faites correspondre 3 sushi identiques ou plus de façon à terminer le niveau avant le temps imparti. Utilisez des sabliers bloqueurs de temps ou des bombes pour vous aider dans les niveaux avancés, de plus en plus difficiles!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40219/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sushi-matching/embed?sid=1","plays":40003,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U21D1","slug":"square-3d","title":"Square 3D","description":"Square 3D is a 3D view where you can manoeuvre all kinds of shapes in position to gain points by filling a single 3D plane","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U21D1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":40003,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40225","slug":"doggy-dive","title":"Doggy Dive","description":"Discover a fantastic underwater world in Doggy Dive! Get into the water and dive as deep as you can. Collect air bubbles and coins and avoid dangers like poisonous jellyfish, blowfish and sharks. Prove your skills and reach a high score!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40225/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doggy-dive/embed?sid=1","plays":40003,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TKC03","slug":"cocktail-with-fruit","title":"Cocktail with Fruit","description":"un gioco arcade game che vi fara spendere ore per racogliere abbastanza soldi","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TKC03/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cocktail-with-fruit/embed?sid=1","plays":40002,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58284","slug":"brain-test","title":"Brain Test","description":"Test your intellect and have a lot of fun! Think outside the box, train your brain. Solve exciting puzzles for adults - prove that you are smarter than everyone!\n\nTrust common sense and pay attention to details. Don't try to solve puzzles in the usual way, some puzzles are not as easy as they seem! Enjoy insanely addictive puzzles and puzzles that will make you think outside the box.\n\nYou will use logic to solve some puzzles, while others will test your IQ.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58284/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-test/embed?sid=1","plays":40001,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3ZZ3E","slug":"halloween-puzzle","title":"Halloween Puzzle","description":"Un jeu de puzzle relaxant plein d'images sur le thème d'Halloween. Parcourez les niveaux et employez différentes façons pour terminer le niveau actuel. Ce puzzle sur le thème d'Halloween est fait pour vous.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3ZZ3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":40000,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J29P1","slug":"mahjong-quest-of-japan-clans","title":"Mahjong - Quest of Japan Clans","description":"Do you like mahjong solitaire and other exciting brain games? Then this game will cheer you up, and at the same time lvl up your memory! And a lot of levels, beautiful design and relaxing melody will make solving this puzzle enjoyable. Solving such a title match puzzle, you will be happy to train your brain. Complete all levels and develop your attentiveness and logic to the maximum in Mahjong - Quest of Japan Clans! Find treasure Japan samurai!\n\nFeatures of the game: \nNice music and graphics\n The atmosphere of ancient Japan  the samurai era\nEasy one-finger control \nLots of easy and challenging levels\nLogic quest for your mind\nFree  game training thinking \nTo play offline patience game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J29P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-quest-of-japan-clans/embed?sid=1","plays":40000,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0E6S6","slug":"safe-joe","title":"Safe Joe","description":"Safe joe!how?simple,hit hit hit hit hit and buy the power up !!!!!\n\nHave a fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0E6S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/safe-joe/embed?sid=1","plays":40000,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SREFN","slug":"grand-theft-stunt","title":"Grand Theft Stunt","description":"Reach the finish line on time with your extreme luxury and extremely expensive car. You have to be careful, you can fall down the cliff with your expensive car. You have to drive slowly and carefully. You must reach the finish before the time runs out. reach the finish line and complete all levels 10 different challenging levels. \n\nHow to Play?\nPress WASD keys to move. \nMobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SREFN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-theft-stunt/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I6I90","slug":"do-re-mi-piano-for-kids","title":"Do Re Mi Piano For Kids","description":"Your Do Re Mi is a free and simple piano which is suitable for children and beginners, the easiest way to play piano, guaranteed.    \nTap anywhere on the piano to play the next note in the song.    \n  \nYou've these three tools in one game:  \n- Piano  \n- Flute  \n- Arpa  \n    \nMoreover, the function of listening examination can train your sound hearing; the main features is shown as follows.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I6I90/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/do-re-mi-piano-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N0465","slug":"rainbow-insta-girls","title":"Rainbow Insta Girls","description":"Apprenez à mieux connaître les élèves de l'école arc-en-ciel. Ces filles aiment les vêtements à la mode et les coiffures lumineuses. Cela les aide à devenir des stars d'Instagram. Les amis ont même réussi à attirer les gars dans cette aventure de la mode. Joignez-vous au plaisir et essayez des tenues avec les filles. Un incroyable bain à remous arc-en-ciel et une extravagance colorée vous attendent!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N0465/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-insta-girls/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SDRRS","slug":"block-destroyer","title":"Block Destroyer","description":"Bienvenue dans Block Destroyer, amusez-vous à briser tous les blocs dans les plus brefs délais. Achetez de l'aide dans la boutique et consultez le tutoriel, qu'attendez-vous !!! allez jouer à Block Destroyer maintenant et le plaisir est garanti.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SDRRS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/block-destroyer/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CCC6K","slug":"escalate-dack","title":"Escalate Dack","description":"Help Deck climb as high as possible to escape possible traps, be aware that the walls can have traps too.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CCC6K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escalate-dack/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P6633","slug":"slime-pet","title":"Slime Pet","description":"Take care of the slime!\nClick on it to cheer it up!\nBring the food,drinks and toys for full joyness but careful it might get angry sometimes!\nCompete with others to see whose pet is happier!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P6633/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slime-pet/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P1SSR","slug":"supergolf","title":"SuperGolf","description":"Welcome to SuperGolf, challenge all levels and get to the end by pocketing all the balls, what are you waiting for ??? Go play SuperGolf now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P1SSR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/supergolf/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SE46T","slug":"castel","title":"Castel","description":"Welcome to the castle game, let's see if you can win the 4 levels, have fun","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SE46T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/castel/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C3K10","slug":"balls-vs-bricks","title":"Balls vs Bricks","description":"Visez les balles pour écraser toutes les briques pour vous amuser et vous détendre. Plus les briques sont détruites, plus vous obtiendrez de points.","category":"Sport","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C3K10/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-vs-bricks/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6330S","slug":"7-errors","title":"7 Errors","description":"7 Errors is a game where you have to find the 7 mistakes before time runs out. Can you find all 7? Have fun looking.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6330S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/7-errors/embed?sid=1","plays":39999,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LE63S","slug":"airplane-puzzles","title":"Airplane Puzzles","description":"Airplane puzzle is a fun online puzzle game. Drag the pieces into right position using mouse. Solving puzzles is relaxing, rewarding, and keeps your brain sharp. You need to spend $1000 to be able to purchase one of the following pictures. You have three modes for each picture from which the hardest mode brings more money. You have a total of 10 pictures.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LE63S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/airplane-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":39998,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"07C61","slug":"coloring-book","title":"Coloring Book","description":"Si vous cherchez un moyen de développer les compétences ou la créativité de votre enfant, ce jeu est la meilleure solution pour vous!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/07C61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":39998,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TOP8P","slug":"match-pictures-to-words","title":"Match Pictures to Words","description":"You just need to match the pictures to the correct words.\n\nHow To Play:\nIt’s really simple and intuitive… just use your mouse and click on a picture after drag’ n’ drop the picture over the correct Word!\nIf you do right you see a message of well done if you are wrong you see an error message!\n\nYou have 2 Game Modes:\nEasy:\nYou can play freely without stress because you can go back and forth in the game when you want! It’s really suitable for kids.\nNormal:\nIn this mode you have 3 lives and you must match correctly the pictures over the word or you go in game over! So, pay attention!\n\nThis great word match game is very suitable for kids or who loves word matching games.\n\nKey Features:\n- Two game modes Easy and Normal.\n- Super User Friendly Interface.\n- Awesome kid’s Music theme and Sound effects.\n- Really Simple gameplay.\n\nThis is amazing word matching game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TOP8P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-pictures-to-words/embed?sid=1","plays":39997,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U8YRI","slug":"punch-boxing-for-dummy","title":"Punch Boxing for Dummy","description":"Are you ready to fight?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U8YRI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/punch-boxing-for-dummy/embed?sid=1","plays":39997,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00CRL","slug":"unicorn-puzzle","title":"Unicorn Puzzle","description":"Educational Puzzle Game / “Unicorn Puzzle” is a great game to help children improve their abilities and speed in solving problems. There are 6 beautiful puzzles for kids to play with. Have fun with this amazing puzzle for kids! The designs are very colorful and beautiful! Have fun while building your memory!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00CRL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/unicorn-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":39997,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T5A3","slug":"rainy-night","title":"Rainy Night","description":"Watch out the rain! it isn't what it seems...\nAvoid it and survive the most time you can.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T5A3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainy-night/embed?sid=1","plays":39995,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69F1E","slug":"the-fly","title":"The Fly","description":"Welcome to The Fly, challenge the flies and bees to the last spray, kill all the enemies before the time runs out, otherwise you won't go to the next level. What are you waiting for!!! go play The Fly now and the fun is guaranteed !!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69F1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-fly/embed?sid=1","plays":39995,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC5R2","slug":"color-element","title":"Color Element","description":"Color Element is the fun arcade game in which you have to pass through moving rings and obstacles of different colors. Based on the classic Color Switch game, you may only pass through the parts that are the same color as the ball that you are controlling.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC5R2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-element/embed?sid=1","plays":39993,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NOSO4","slug":"i-can-transform","title":"I Can Transform","description":"I Can Transform is an 2D action-platform.\n\nIn this game you will use your special costume which allows you to transform into mechanical objects (Car, Rocket, Helicopter, Motorcycle, ...) to avoid obstacles, collect Vortex Gems in levels and defeat the Assas (The bad guys who want to destroy the world).","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NOSO4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/i-can-transform/embed?sid=1","plays":39993,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9AS1S","slug":"tribe-escape","title":"Tribe Escape","description":"tribe escape is a arcade pixel game, run and avoid the enemy on stage, collect fruits to earn score","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9AS1S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tribe-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":39992,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W0366","slug":"halloween-remembers","title":"Halloween Remembers","description":"Try to remember the sequence of moving pumpkins. Reproduce it according to your memory.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W0366/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-remembers/embed?sid=1","plays":39991,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44545","slug":"mission","title":"MISSION","description":"Drive your spaceship, Avoid the obstacles and save the lost astronauts!\n\nIf you touch a malus (an astronaut with a red cross) you'll lose 1 point!\n\nCONTROLS:\nUSE YOUR MOUSE TO MOVE YOUR SPACESHIP\n\nUSE SPACE TO SHOOT: YOU HAVE ONLY 5 SHOTS AVAILABLE. GRAB AMMOS FALLING DOWN TO ADD 1 AMMO.\n\nUSE LEFT DOUBLE CLICK TO BECOME IMMORTAL FOR 5 SECONDS. \n\nTO BECOME IMMORTAL AGAIN YOU HAVE TO WAIT 15 SECONDS OF COOLDOWN, SHOWN IN THE BOTTOM-CENTER OF THE SCREEN.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44545/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mission/embed?sid=1","plays":39991,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ER584","slug":"destroy","title":"Destroy","description":"try to be quick to avoid the vavicles that are thrown at you","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ER584/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/destroy/embed?sid=1","plays":39990,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6RS9R","slug":"super-car-racer","title":"Super Car Racer","description":"Super Car Racer is an action-packed racing game about high-speed racing and intense competition. You take on the role of a skilled driver who must navigate a series of challenging tracks while facing off against other top-notch racers. The game features a variety of stunning cars, each with its unique strengths and weaknesses, and a range of customization options to help you tailor your vehicle to your specific preferences. As you progress through the game, you'll unlock new tracks and vehicles, all while honing your driving skills and learning to outmaneuver your opponents. With its fast-paced action, exhilarating gameplay, and stunning graphics, Super Car Racer is the ultimate racing experience for adrenaline junkies and car enthusiasts alike.  \n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6RS9R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-car-racer/embed?sid=1","plays":39990,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9O4C1","slug":"frog-with-recoil","title":"Frog with recoil","description":"use weapon recoil to move your frog and collect appels avoid obstacles","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9O4C1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-with-recoil/embed?sid=1","plays":39989,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4MHMH","slug":"meme-match-3","title":"Meme Match 3","description":"Classic Match 3 game with memes. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4MHMH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meme-match-3/embed?sid=1","plays":39988,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33U73","slug":"cursed-treasure-2","title":"Cursed Treasure 2","description":"The hordes of good heroes come again and they are hungry for gems more than ever because The King himself wants the stones for his private needs. Gather the evil forces, build towers, upgrade, drink soda, cast the mighty spells, do whatever you can but don’t let them touch your gems!\n\nWhy be good when you can be... bad? Cursed Treasure 2 is an addictive tower-defense game that puts the power of darkness at your fingertips. As a creature of ultimate evil, you don't ask for much... just to raze the odd kingdom and have your cache of all-powerful magical gems safely hidden away. Too bad the (ugh) good guys are out to steal them. Using the powers of the orcs, demons, and undead, you'll build unique and powerful towers along paths to destroy any hero that dares get close.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33U73/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cursed-treasure-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39988,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91R3R","slug":"warrior-orc","title":"Warrior Orc","description":"Imagine an orc trying to survive in an 8bit world in a jungle full of monsters and must pass all the levels and reach his own world! must survive without stopping.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Use WASD Keys to play.\n*Watch out for the enemies to survive!\n*You can climb on top of monsters and kill them.\n*Double jump is active in the game.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91R3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/warrior-orc/embed?sid=1","plays":39987,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KTC06","slug":"auto-rickshaw","title":"Auto Rickshaw","description":"Drive and avoid obstacles on the roads of New Delhi.\nCollect coins and unlock special Rickshaws!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KTC06/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/auto-rickshaw/embed?sid=1","plays":39987,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7608E","slug":"next-level-balls","title":"Next Level Balls","description":"hey you player are you up for a fun game? Pass through levels of varying difficulty. To increase your level, you have to eat all the balls of lower level than you. Oh, balls with a high level of attention can eat you. Watch out for obstacles they can steal your levels. Get to the finish line and qualify to the next level. Complete all levels to get 5 different costumes.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7608E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/next-level-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":39986,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5B60","slug":"ball-sort-color","title":"Ball Sort Color","description":"Ball Sort Puzzle is a fun and addictive puzzle game! Try to sort the colored balls in the tubes until all balls with the same color stay in the same tube. A challenging yet relaxing game to exercise your brain!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5B60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-sort-color/embed?sid=1","plays":39985,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8147O","slug":"colorful-shapes","title":"Colorful Shapes","description":"Welcome to Colorful Shapes, immerse yourself in the adventure among the colored shapes, overcome them and accumulate as many points as possible to pass your best score. What are you waiting for, go play Colorful Shapes now and fun will be guaranteed","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8147O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colorful-shapes/embed?sid=1","plays":39985,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U4669","slug":"kunoichi-run","title":"Kunoichi Run","description":"kunoichi run is an html5 arcade game, run and drift avoid obstacles and get ninja scrolls to fly ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U4669/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kunoichi-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39985,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EEOT","slug":"space-route","title":"Space Route","description":"Space Route is a game in which you will have to control a spaceship and dodge meteorites to get to your home planet, and how long this journey will be, you will find out only in the game itself.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EEOT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-route/embed?sid=1","plays":39985,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"48L5S","slug":"spiderblock","title":"Spiderblock","description":"Think of a block and it's a living thing. He can also throw a spider web with a special ability. Thanks to the spider web he throws, he can pass from wall to wall and jump over obstacles. How would you like to join this 10-level adventure?  \n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/48L5S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spiderblock/embed?sid=1","plays":39985,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46NAS","slug":"santa-chase","title":"Santa Chase","description":"Complete missions in snowy and fun levels and build your gift train as long as possible in this new year themed game!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46NAS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-chase/embed?sid=1","plays":39984,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"914EE","slug":"steve-alex-drive","title":"Steve Alex Drive","description":"Steve and Alexs need to reach the finish line. The red and blue players have to reach the finish line. get the red and blue box, get the right to move to the new level, remember, you have to be very careful, you can crash every month. Play the game with 2 of your friends and reach the finish.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/914EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-alex-drive/embed?sid=1","plays":39984,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N292N","slug":"falling-cubes","title":"Falling Cubes","description":"Dodge cubes to survive and collect coins to win new skins (coming soon)","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N292N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-cubes/embed?sid=1","plays":39984,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZRB2C","slug":"circle-zombie","title":"Circle Zombie","description":"Break your personal record in Circle Zombie, an online game where you control a circle and jump on a line. Jump as high as you can to reach the top of the leaderboard.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZRB2C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circle-zombie/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S4HMR","slug":"heart-match-master","title":"Heart Match Master","description":"Heart Match Master is an online game that lets you match different hearts together. The game is free to play, and you can earn points by matching as many hearts as possible. Looking for a fun and free online matching game? Look no further than Heart Match Master! This addicting game is perfect for players of all ages and skills levels. Simply match up the hearts in pairs of two or more to score points. The more pairs you match, the higher your score will be. So what are you waiting for? Give Heart Match Master a try today!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S4HMR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heart-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E58IU","slug":"kitty-jewel-quest","title":"Kitty Jewel Quest","description":"Passez votre temps libre avec un vrai délice pour tous les amoureux des chats ! Faites la course contre la montre pour associer trois adorables chatons ou plus en ligne ou en colonne. Ce jeu vous procurera des heures de plaisir et de détente pour tous les âges.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E58IU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kittty-jewel-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"177RI","slug":"mini-train-io","title":"Mini Train io","description":"Collect nuts and bolts to build up your train's length in this io-style snake game! Play amongst other trains but be sure not to collide with one or else it's game over! Grab the wheel and dodge and weave your way through the chaos while you grow your train to the top of leaderboard!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/177RI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-train-io/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O8H75","slug":"monty-hall","title":"Monty Hall","description":"The Monty Hall problem is a famous probability puzzle named after the host of \"Let's Make a Deal\", Monty Hall. It involves a contestant choosing one of three doors to win a prize. After the initial choice, one door revealing a non-prize is opened. The contestant is then given the option to stick with their choice or switch to the remaining unopened door. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O8H75/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monty-hall/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31CAE","slug":"planet-escape","title":"Planet Escape","description":"Planet Escape Announces Release of its New Casual Vertical-Scrolling Game Planet Escape, a casual vertical-scrolling game, has released its newest title, titled \"Planet Escape\". With its simple and addictive game play, this new game is perfect for anyone who loves casual games. You can pick up runaway minerals from planets using rockets to escape the planet and find new ones to explore. There are also three different difficulty levels to choose from, so you can find the game that's right for you.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31CAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/planet-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1O1OO","slug":"world-map-coloring-for-kids","title":"World Map Coloring For Kids","description":"$58","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1O1OO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-map-coloring-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E082","slug":"2048-level-12","title":"2048 Level 12","description":"2048 game","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E082/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048-level-12/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T80S1","slug":"akochan-quest-2","title":"Akochan Quest 2","description":"Akochan Quest 2 is a 2D Anime themed platformer where you play as a girl, Akochan, who have to collect all of the necklaces while avoiding the zombies, flying heart monsters, rotating blades, spikes and reach the Yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Akochan Quest\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T80S1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/akochan-quest-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"826AR","slug":"alien-war","title":"Alien War","description":"Action shooting Alien War is an online game that will keep you on the edge of your seat! With exciting gameplay and fast-paced action, you won't want to stop playing. Looking for an online game that will keep you on the edge of your seat? Look no further than Alien War, the action-packed shooting game that will have you blasting aliens all day long! With amazing graphics and fast-paced gameplay, this is one game you won't want to miss. So suit up and get ready to take on the aliens today!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/826AR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-war/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16T76","slug":"istint","title":"Istint","description":"Welcome to Instinct, reflex and speed game, try to get on the podium, have fun","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16T76/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/istint/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CFBA8","slug":"pit-bull-avoid-traffic","title":"Pit Bull Avoid Traffic","description":"Help your Pit Bull went to reach his car intact, avoiding the mad traffic, the distance to the player car. Using the control arrows, you will have to direct the movements and actions of your character so that he would avoid all dangers and as far as it can go.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CFBA8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pit-bull-avoid-traffic/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L36S6","slug":"yellow-pipes","title":"Yellow Pipes","description":"Rotate the pipes correctly. FORTY available levels !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L36S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yellow-pipes/embed?sid=1","plays":39983,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1ON5C","slug":"traffic-control","title":"Traffic Control","description":"Il y a une circulation folle ! C'est à vous de conduire les conducteurs impuissants jusqu'à la sortie. Utilisez vos compétences de gestion pour éviter les collisions mortelles sur ces routes dangereuses.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1ON5C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/traffic-control/embed?sid=1","plays":39982,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P6P9A","slug":"philatelic-escape-fauna-album-3","title":"Philatelic Escape - Fauna Album 3","description":"Philatelic Escape - Fauna Album 3 is the 3nd episode of series of games about stamp collector. This time your objective is to get inside the next apartment from the address list and find 10 stamps. Like the previous you need to open the front door and enter the room. Walk across the room, click on the items you see on the screen, collect them and use to solve the puzzles. Open the shelves and look for clues for cracking numeric and letter codes. The keys, postage stamps and other items that you are looking for could be hidden in anywhere, so be sure to check every single corner. Use logical thinking, creativity and your brains to solve all puzzles and find 10 stamps.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P6P9A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/philatelic-escape-fauna-album-3/embed?sid=1","plays":39981,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"638GF","slug":"artic-fishing","title":"Artic Fishing","description":"$59","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/638GF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/artic-fishing/embed?sid=1","plays":39981,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8EFH9","slug":"frog-match-master","title":"Frog Match Master","description":"Frog Match Master is an online matching game that is free to play. The objective of the game is to match as many pairs of frogs as possible in the allotted time. There are different levels of difficulty, and the player can choose to play against other players or against the computer. In this game, you must help the frogs match up all of the correct pairs of objects. With dozens of levels to play, Frog Match Master is sure to keep you entertained for hours. So why not give it a try today?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8EFH9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frog-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"991MR","slug":"air-simulator","title":"Air Simulator","description":"Looking for a fun and challenging online game? Look no further than Air Simulator. In this game, you'll take control of an aircraft and fly through a variety of different landscapes. With beautiful graphics and smooth game play, Air Simulator is sure to keep you entertained for hours on end. So what are you waiting for? Give it a try today!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/991MR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/air-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0NTB1","slug":"break-the-candy","title":"Break the Candy","description":"Break The Candy is an online game where the objective is to, well, break the candy. You can play by yourself or with friends, and there are multiple levels to keep you challenged. The game is designed to be fun and easy to pick up, but with enough depth to keep you coming back for more.\n\n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0NTB1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/break-the-candy/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K566G","slug":"horik-viking","title":"Horik Viking","description":"Horik Viking is a super fun and challenging 2D side-scroller game. The game features 10 levels that will challenge you to beat it. Cross the Nordic valley in search of the stars of Oddin, facing angry dragons!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K566G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horik-viking/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1DS1R","slug":"ichikas-adventure-2","title":"Ichikas Adventure 2","description":"Ichikas Adventure 2 is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as Anime girl called Ichika who have to collect all of the necklaces while avoiding the enemies and their bullets, flying creatures, spikes, and saws and reach the door of your house in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Ichikas Adventure\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1DS1R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ichikas-adventure-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61T61","slug":"jump-to-the-moon","title":"Jump to the Moon","description":"Jump as high as you can!\nCollect coins to get power ups. Collect carrots to replenish your health.\n\nControls on PC:\n- Left and right arrows to move.\n- Space to activate power up.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61T61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-to-the-moon/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61KO4","slug":"klondike-solitaire-panda","title":"Klondike Solitaire Panda","description":"Welcome to the popular solitaire  klondike card game!\n\nEnjoy playing the classic Solitaire and train your brain and  with Panda.\n\nShow off your card skills and creativity in Solitaire Panda with simple and easy gameplay, smooth sounds and awesome design.\n\nYou can Move cards with dragging or single tap, and you can choose from two draw modes, either play Draw 1 games where more chance to win, or challenge your skills and play the Draw 3 mode.\n\nSolitaire Panda Features:\n• Draw 1 Card Mode\n• Draw 3 Cards Mode\n• Unlimited Free Hints\n• Undo Moves\n• Left-handed / Right-handed Solitaire Mode\n• Customizable Card Faces, Backs & Board Background\n• Auto-Complete On/Off","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61KO4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/klondike-solitaire-panda/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1O886","slug":"rocky-the-jetpack-boy","title":"Rocky the Jetpack Boy","description":"rocky the jetpack boy is an html5 adventure game, fly and shoot enemies, get coins for the highest score ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1O886/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocky-the-jetpack-boy/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"50688","slug":"soto-man","title":"Soto Man","description":"Soto Man is a 2D simple platformer where you play as Soto Man, the super hero, who have to collect the stolen red gems while avoiding the enemies, robots, spikes and reach the magic hole which leads you to the next level.    \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50688/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soto-man/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"32L2T","slug":"spatial-match","title":"Spatial Match","description":"Only fast thinking and observation will get you through this game. All you have to do is look at each card and see if the next card matches the one before!\n\nYou have 45 seconds on the clock - how many cards can you get right? Remember every card and see if the next card matches the card before; then remember the card you just looked at and see if the next card matches that one and this goes on till the timer shows 0. Level up and test yourself to see how many cards you can get right! \n","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/32L2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spatial-match/embed?sid=1","plays":39980,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6YT77","slug":"rolling-gravity-sky-ball","title":"Rolling Gravity Sky Ball","description":"Rolling Gravity Sky Ball","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6YT77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rolling-gravity-sky-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39976,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"94U63","slug":"stack-pileup","title":"Stack PileUP","description":"Stack the aliens on each other correctly and prevent them from falling.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/94U63/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stack-pileup/embed?sid=1","plays":39976,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4I6EH","slug":"climb-hero","title":"Climb Hero","description":"Il s'est entraîné pendant des années et il veut montrer à tout le monde que c'est lui le héros de l'escalade. Aidez-le à choisir les bonnes pierres et grimpez ensemble jusqu'au sommet de la montagne. Pouvez-vous y arriver en un seul essai ?\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4I6EH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/climb-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":39975,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N55A7","slug":"cry-mansion","title":"Cry Mansion","description":"Our protagonist is a brave dude, who came to save his girlfriend. That sounds good, but it's not so easy. There are enemies ahead, there may be many zombies ahead, but he fears no one. I'd say let's keep going until we reach the end. But be warned - there are more mysteries to come. You'll have to push boxes, guess codes and even play piano. Oh no! I'd rather meet a zombie than face a piano!\nOur target is not shoot all zombies, but find the exit form night horror and wake up to real world! And one more time - avoid contact with zombie...\n\nFeatures:\n\n- There are many rooms in the mansion.\n- There are many various enemies in the mansion.\n- Story-driven gameplay experience.\n- Find weapon and bullets.\n- Find many clues to open doors and fight with enemies.\n- A sad main story and A lot of dialogues.\n- Read the notes and solve the mystery contained in its page.\n- Easy and functional touch controls.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N55A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cry-mansion/embed?sid=1","plays":39975,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A6SSO","slug":"aeroplane-chess","title":"Aeroplane Chess","description":"For childhood classic games, Ludo / Flying / Aeroplane chess must be the one.\n\nThere is a lot of Ludo chess games, but most of them are unsatisfactory customer needs (including what we have made before), summarized a lot of customer opinion, this game should be able to make you satisfied.\n\nFeatures:\n\n- Customizable game rules, Aeroplane chess has many variation rules, different places are different, we preset two most common rules set, you can play directly. And also has two customizable rules set for you to define your rule.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A6SSO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aeroplane-chess/embed?sid=1","plays":39974,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ANNIH","slug":"mini-zombie-the-invasion","title":"Mini Zombie The Invasion","description":"Shoot with your weapon all Mini Zombies that you see on the screen! Grab your weapon and shoot on the zombie's head to destroy it! The main goal is to resist the more you can and defend your barricade!\nKey Features:\n-Great gameplay over 60fps!\n-Smooth animations!\n-20 Different Tiny Zombies!\n-5 Different Weapons to blast Zombies!\n-Endless gameplay!\n\nHave fun with this great funny endless game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ANNIH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-zombie-the-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":39974,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41RS4","slug":"avoid-the-germs","title":"Avoid the Germs","description":"Avoid the germs and collect the gunk and look out for speedy power ups in this great arcade packed fast paced game for kids!\nProduct feature bullets: \n• very very easy to play\n• nice 2D graphics\n• endless game\n• very fun game for kids and babies\n• cool music sound effects\n• amazing animations\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41RS4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/avoid-the-germs/embed?sid=1","plays":39974,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1A202","slug":"dangerous-landing","title":"Dangerous Landing","description":"Dangerous Landing is a new version of the classic Blitz game, your plane's fuel is running out, the only hope of salvation is to create a landing strip, luckily the buildings below are empty and ready to be destroyed, tap on the screen or press the space key on your keyboard to drop your bombs, more and more buildings will be added to each level, how long can you resist?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1A202/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dangerous-landing/embed?sid=1","plays":39974,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"29C4L","slug":"rival-colors","title":"Rival Colors","description":"is a nice arcade game that aims to refine reflexes and long-term fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/29C4L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rival-colors/embed?sid=1","plays":39974,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"791C7","slug":"cannon","title":"Cannon","description":"Let's see how many policemen kill with your cannon","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/791C7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cannon/embed?sid=1","plays":39973,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N69NT","slug":"mr-santa-run","title":"Mr. Santa Run","description":"mr santa run is a html5 endless run game, run and jump avoid obstacles and get as many stars","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N69NT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-santa-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39973,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4TEAR","slug":"steveman-lava-world","title":"Steveman Lava World","description":"Steveman's 2nd series has to survive in the lava world, let's see if he can do it. don't forget it needs you to survive you have to collect the red eggs collect them and earn points. You have to reach the door, watch out for the thorns, but don't die. There are flying monsters, be careful with them.  \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4TEAR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steveman-lava-world/embed?sid=1","plays":39973,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71BT7","slug":"mincraft-cube-puzzle","title":"Mincraft Cube Puzzle","description":"Minecraft Cube Puzzle is a new game in the setting of Minecraft, in the puzzle genre. You have to guide the cube to the exit, on its way there will be side cubes, which you can move in two planes. The project is different:\n\n- Spatial physics. You need to see the whole picture\n\n- Variety of levels\n\n- Original gameplay, in the setting of mintcraft\n\nManage the dice from maincraft, pass all levels. The complexity gradually increases, in the end are waiting for a truly difficult levels!\n\nPlay, think, develop - all with Minecraft Cube Puzzle!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71BT7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minecraft-cube-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":39973,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41ERX","slug":"geomatrix-space-wars","title":"Geomatrix Space Wars","description":"Fly inside the space and destroy all Alien Ships and a giant Boss that you see in unique super fight shooter to save your world!. During your gameplay collect power up to to upgrade your Ship and use your mega bomb if necessary.\nProduct feature bullets:\n• Endless Gameplay\n• 4 Mega Boss\n• 4 Upgradeable Weapons\n• 2 Fantastic Musics\n• 1 Super mega Bomb\n• 3D Prerendered Graphics\n• Amazing explosion effects\n• Very Easy To Play\nHave fun with this amazing Arcade Shooter Game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41ERX/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geomatrix-space-wars/embed?sid=1","plays":39972,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6B8B1","slug":"gravity-ball","title":"Gravity Ball","description":"gravity ball is a arcade game, touch the ball to bounce and dont get hit a obstacle","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6B8B1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gravity-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39972,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"74338","slug":"sea-maiden","title":"Sea Maiden","description":"Sea Maiden is an underwater online game that challenges players to explore the depths of the ocean. With stunning graphics and a unique gameplay experience, Sea Maiden is a must-play for all gamers.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/74338/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sea-maiden/embed?sid=1","plays":39972,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6APLU","slug":"2-player-red-blue-pirates","title":"2 Player Red Blue Pirates","description":"The cute and yet powerful twin pirate has to survive. red and blue pirates need protection from enemies they need to stay strong. They need to collect 6 bombs and reach the door. collect the bombs and reach the door.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys               \n*Double Jump available               \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6APLU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2-player-red-blue-pirates/embed?sid=1","plays":39971,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40400","slug":"run-canyon","title":"Run Canyon","description":"Drive the quad through the fantastic grand canyon. Play the 30 levels, survive and unlock new vehicles.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","adventure","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40400/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-canyon/embed?sid=1","plays":39970,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OTT5S","slug":"dots-sorting","title":"Dots Sorting","description":"Sort the dots by color - click on the corresponding color - beware of circulars","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OTT5S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dots-sorting/embed?sid=1","plays":39970,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2KCGG","slug":"skateboard-challenge","title":"Skateboard Challenge","description":"\"Skateboard Challenge\" is a very fun extreme Sport Game! Your objective is to collect all the letters that form the word \"S-K-A-T-E\" and also the letters that form the word \"C-O-M-B-O\", as well as reaching a target score contained in all levels. Beat all the levels performing different extreme maneuvers, use the rail to make combinations of maneuvers and multiply your score! Collect coins to unlock characters. A super radical game to play with your friends! Have a good time!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2KCGG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skateboard-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":39970,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C19I3","slug":"real-car-parking-3d","title":"Real Car Parking 3D","description":"Car parking game with realistic graphics. You have to get to the finish line without rubbing the car against the wall, don't worry, the boxes don't damage your car, but they slow you down. You have to be careful not to crash. Manage to park your car in 15 different levels and become the best parking master! Become a car parking master from both mobile and pc.  \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C19I3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/real-car-parking-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":39970,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8L3E6","slug":"power-wall","title":"Power Wall","description":"Essayez de participer à une expérience scientifique en laboratoire. Jouez et surpassez-vous ! Mais ne laissez pas la balle sortir du laboratoire. Activez la paroi électrique à l'écran au bon moment. La vitesse augmente progressivement pour tester votre attention, votre précision et votre rapidité. Avec ces compétences spéciales, ce jeu de perception mêle amusement et défi dans un environnement aux graphismes agréables. Un jeu simple et beau tout public. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8L3E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/power-wall/embed?sid=1","plays":39969,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78S3I","slug":"super-knight-adventure","title":"Super Knight Adventure","description":"super knight adventure is a html5 platformer game explore the jungle earn coins and gems and get keys from enemy bosses to unlock levels ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78S3I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-knight-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":39969,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N65CM","slug":"locoman","title":"Locoman","description":"Locoman is a 2D platformer where you have to collect the silver keys while avoiding the spikes and enemies and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N65CM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/locoman/embed?sid=1","plays":39968,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4E208","slug":"squid-match-game","title":"Squid Match Game","description":"Squid Match Game is a simple cool game that requires finding match card pairs based on a Squid Game theme!\nMemorize all the characters of Squid Game on the cards and match the twos or three pairs as per the target; play the total game and win the game.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4E208/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-match-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39968,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H0E61","slug":"themonster","title":"TheMonster","description":"game where you have to upset the monster that appeared on the screen","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H0E61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/themonster/embed?sid=1","plays":39968,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SA8A6","slug":"gnam-gnam-shark","title":"Gnam Gnam Shark","description":"Pilot the little Blue Shark and eat all the  red fish that you see in the sea, be careful don't touch the red monsters or you'll lose one life! The main goal of the game is to collect as much fish as possible and sign your personal record.      \nOccasionally you will see a red balloon, touch them and earn a bonus.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SA8A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gnam-gnam-shark/embed?sid=1","plays":39968,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3EN61","slug":"chicken-hunter","title":"Chicken Hunter","description":"chicken hunter is an html5 arcade game, shoot as many chickens as possible, don't shoot BIRDS or game over ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3EN61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chicken-hunter/embed?sid=1","plays":39967,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40317","slug":"pick-a-lock","title":"Pick a Lock","description":"Challenge your reflexes and concentration in this exciting lock-popping game! Pop all the locks and be the best!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40317/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pick-a-lock/embed?sid=1","plays":39967,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"944DT","slug":"dr-rocket","title":"Dr. Rocket","description":"3 GAME MODES IN 1 GAME!\nDr.Rocket is a html5 game which includes 3 game modes in it!\n-First mode is a launch game. -Second mode is platform (don’t touch the walls) game. -Third and the final mode is an endless climbing game.\nRANKING SYSTEM\nThe game also includes ranking system.There is 4 rank in the game;\nFirst rank : Astronaut Second rank : Novice Space Pilot Third Rank : Galaxy Pilot Final Rank : Legendary Rocketman","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/944DT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dr-rocket/embed?sid=1","plays":39967,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O6196","slug":"donuts-match","title":"Donuts Match","description":"Here’s something everybody loves - Donuts!\nThis game will test your skills and donuts knowledge. Start by taping on selected donut and move your finger (touching the screen all the time) to the same donuts that are nearby. If you select two or more donuts in this way - they’ll disappear when you stop touching the screen. \nThere’s no rush or timer - you can take all the time you need to select the donuts. \nHow many points would  you be able to score until there’s no more donuts of the same kind to select?","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O6196/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/donuts-match/embed?sid=1","plays":39967,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40445","slug":"hair-do-design-2","title":"Hair Do Design 2","description":"It's your first day of college and you want to change yourself to be the most stylish girl at campus with different hair styles. It's your time to shine: no makeup is complete without some amazing hair styles! Wash it all off to try new creative hair stylish shapes & ideas!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40445/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hair-do-design-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39966,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A2IR4","slug":"handbrake-parking","title":"Handbrake Parking","description":"Handbrake Parking is a fun game of car parking that requires extreme focus and timing.\nThe car runs automatically and you need to park in a very tight parking space at a perfect time! Crash into other cars and its game over.\nIt's a fun endless free game but hard to master.\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A2IR4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/handbrake-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":39966,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SOCL5","slug":"slots-beach","title":"Slots Beach","description":"Happy free spins as a gift! ... The Beach slot machine will give betting participants a real vacation on the seashore, where they can earn big winnings if they collect a combination of identical symbols according to the schedule of one or more lines. As assistants, slot users will use octopuses with prize features and bottles that activate free spins packages. The marine style of the Beach slot machine is further emphasized by the collection of symbols, which includes images of shells and stones with card denominations.","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SOCL5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slots-beach/embed?sid=1","plays":39965,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G756O","slug":"coloring-kids","title":"Coloring Kids","description":"It's a coloring game where your child can have fun using their creativity by coloring the canvases and then saving them as they wish.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G756O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coloring-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39965,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22D9T","slug":"math-nerd","title":"Math Nerd","description":"Train your brain with this cool and exciting math game “MATH NERD” with cool sounds and music to stimulate more brain activity! This game can also be dedicated for children education and school projects! Test your skills with this new math educational game and learn how to calculate very fast!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22D9T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-nerd/embed?sid=1","plays":39965,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"83S03","slug":"kids-farm-fun","title":"Kids: Farm Fun","description":"Laissez votre enfant visiter la ferme avec tous ses adorables habitants ! Une expérience passionnante de résolution de casse-têtes l'attend. Les puzzles présentent les animaux de la ferme dans diverses situations animées qui amuseront votre enfant. Ces casse-têtes le divertiront mais l'éduqueront également. Alors laissez-le résoudre ces puzzles !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/83S03/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-farm-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":39963,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P1N5L","slug":"planetup","title":"PlanetUp","description":"PlanetUp is an amazing journey through space. Fly a planet through the cosmos and avoid dangerous asteroids. Collect upgrades. Unlock all 90 planets! Are you ready for a new adventure? Play now!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P1N5L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/planetup/embed?sid=1","plays":39963,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I1TSE","slug":"valiant-knight-save-the-princess","title":"Valiant Knight Save the Princess","description":"The Valiant Knight is back! Vicious orcs have abducted his beloved wife the princess and now they demand staggeringly high ransom.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I1TSE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/valiant-knight-save-the-princess/embed?sid=1","plays":39962,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IC6GI","slug":"giddy-cake","title":"Giddy Cake","description":"Tap To Match The Crazy Cakes As Many As You Can!  \n  \nMemory Test:  \nGiddy Cake Game new mix of speed, memory and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test it this game!  \n  \nKey Features:  \n- Memory Test!  \n- Super cute graphic!  \n- Smooth Gameplay!  \n- No Load Times!  \n  \nSo the question is:  \nHow long could you follow these crazy Cakes?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IC6GI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/giddy-cake/embed?sid=1","plays":39961,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0O108","slug":"minigolf-clash","title":"Minigolf Clash","description":"Il est temps de jouer au minigolf et de montrer votre créativité. Utilisez les différentes balles de golf à votre avantage et glissez à travers les niveaux avec facilité. Achetez d'autres niveaux grâce aux récompenses et perfectionnez vos talents de golfeur.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0O108/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minigolf-clash/embed?sid=1","plays":39961,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4B8ZZ","slug":"blockzzle","title":"Blockzzle","description":"organiser les briques à l'électricité active toutes les ampoules","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4B8ZZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blockzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":39961,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AU374","slug":"sane-runner","title":"Sane Runner","description":"On Web using Space, left mouse click to Jump and double Jump\n\nOn Mobile using touch or double tap to jump and double jump.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AU374/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sane-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39961,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B3L3G","slug":"vegetables-for-aliens","title":"Vegetables for Aliens","description":"In a contaminated area, vegetables and tubers other than natural ones were born. \nThey are radioactive, harmful to humans, but aliens like them. \nHelp the aliens collect vegetables and tubers. But ... BEWARE of the PUMPKIN.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B3L3G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/vegetables-for-aliens/embed?sid=1","plays":39961,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"53AZO","slug":"zuma-boom","title":"Zuma Boom","description":"A classic Zuma puzzle that can be played either with mouse or touch.\n\nMake a line of 3 or more balls of the same color by shooting at the balls on the level. \n\nDon't let the balls reach the finish. Make chain matches to get bonuses!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/53AZO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zuma-boom/embed?sid=1","plays":39960,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1C3AA","slug":"pig-ball-christmas","title":"Pig Ball Christmas","description":"cute ball animal pig. The pig has to survive in the square animals world pass all the levels and reach the final level. More challenging monsters and longer maps await you at each level. kill monsters and collect your score.   \n\nHow to Play?\n*Use WASD Keys to play.          \n*Watch out for the enemies to survive!          \n*You can climb on top of monsters and kill them.          \n*Double jump is active in the game.   \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1C3AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pig-ball-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":39959,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EAAAB","slug":"steve-vs-alex-jailbreak","title":"Steve vs Alex Jailbreak","description":"In this adventure, Steve and Alex have to escape from prison. He has to escape jailbreak. Help them escape. The creatures are all over the prison. Open the chest and find the key. Its not enough to get the key. Collect all the gold and get into the car to escape the prison.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EAAAB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-vs-alex-jailbreak/embed?sid=1","plays":39959,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"760U0","slug":"yuas-quest-2","title":"Yuas Quest 2","description":"Yuas Quest 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to play as an anime girl who have to collect antidotes of Zombie virus while avoiding the various kinds of zombies, flying zombies and their bullets, saws and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Yuas Quest\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/760U0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yuas-quest-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39959,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"642AG","slug":"tap-tap-challenge","title":"Tap Tap Challenge","description":"Tap Tap Challenge: challenge other players, unlock new balls & WIN!\n\nYou are the ball and you need to go around crazy scenarios searching for gems. You need GEMS to evolve from a simple ball to something new... Follow the path as much as you can, keep calm and collect the gem.\n\nTry to reach the final evolution of your ball.\n\nTap the screen to change the direction or to teleport over lava. If you fall off the edges, you're gone!\n\nIn this hyper-casual zig-zag adventure you can:\n\n• Unlock dozen unique balls\n\n• Explore crazy levels\n\n• Enjoy awesome 3D graphics and sound effects\n\n• Collect precious gems\n\n• Challenge other gamers in 4 players matches\n\n• Enjoy electronic musics (three tracks available, more coming soon)","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/642AG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-tap-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":39959,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4F7E6","slug":"temple-of-oom","title":"Temple of Oom","description":"Help the Oomee get the fruit to his dog by creating a suitable path!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4F7E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/temple-of-oom/embed?sid=1","plays":39958,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1O111","slug":"coffy","title":"Coffy","description":"welcome to Coffy, can you make six coffees?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1O111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coffy/embed?sid=1","plays":39957,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81969","slug":"garden","title":"Garden","description":"Garden is a new colorful game in the popular genre of \"three in a row\". New levels and new adventures are waiting for you. Go through your garden saga.Collect the same game elements from three or more figures in columns or rows. Collect the required number of items on the level","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81969/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/garden/embed?sid=1","plays":39957,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8B4EF","slug":"craft-bros-boy-runner","title":"Craft Bros Boy Runner","description":"100","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8B4EF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/craft-bros-boy-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39957,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z1E1A","slug":"kaboom-maze","title":"Kaboom Maze","description":"is a simple game where a bomb must solve a maze and find the way out, it can also explode to break walls, but be careful, if you explode too much, you lose","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z1E1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kaboom-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":39956,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46E6U","slug":"brutal-defender","title":"Brutal Defender","description":"Prepare for extreme violence and gore and use big arsenal of weapons to shoot all incoming enemy forces.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46E6U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brutal-defender/embed?sid=1","plays":39955,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A68N6","slug":"brazen-ball","title":"Brazen Ball","description":"You play as a robotic ball as you roll your way through challenging obstacles like sawblades, lasers, meteor showers, trap gates, spikes, magnets, water, wind and many more. Your task is to reach the end marker in as little time as possible, collecting as many orbs as you can!","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A68N6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brazen-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39955,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S0A63","slug":"snakes-and-ladders","title":"Snakes and Ladders","description":"Snakes and Ladders is a 2 player ancient Indian roll and move game. 100 squares full of traps and tricks... Ladders will help you reach the top, but watch out for the snakes! The first player to reach the very last square wins.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S0A63/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snakes-and-ladders/embed?sid=1","plays":39955,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C14HC","slug":"angry-checkers","title":"Angry Checkers","description":"Common checkers are boring? Try angry checkers!\nTry to beat enemy checkers out of the board.\n\nGAME MODES\n1. Multiplayer - you play versus another random player via internet.\n2. Single Player - you play versus AI.\n3. Hot Seat - you play versus your friend on the same device.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C14HC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angry-checkers/embed?sid=1","plays":39953,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6GN77","slug":"summer-beach-parking","title":"Summer Beach Parking","description":"Summer day and a great time to enjoy on the beach with friends, but you must first find a parking space! You’ll have to drive a car and park in some very difficult spots! See if you can navigate each parking lot without damaging your ride!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6GN77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/summer-beach-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":39953,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66717","slug":"ronni","title":"Ronni","description":"Ronni is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the coins while avoiding the enemies, spikes and saws and reach the Exit door. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.        \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66717/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ronni/embed?sid=1","plays":39953,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"32383","slug":"pizza-go","title":"PIZZA GO","description":"it's a simple game","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/32383/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pizza-go/embed?sid=1","plays":39953,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z6L2T","slug":"beltz","title":"Beltz","description":"Free Funny Game ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z6L2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beltz/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B51P6","slug":"bubble-pop","title":"Bubble Pop","description":"Bubble pop games are a classic and beloved game genre that is simple, yet highly entertaining. In this game, you will find yourself immersed in a world of colorful bubbles that are just waiting to be popped. Your goal is to pop as many bubbles as you can in order to score points and progress through the levels.\n\nAs you play, you will encounter a variety of different bubbles, each with their own unique properties. Some bubbles will require multiple hits to pop, while others will have special power-ups that can be unlocked by hitting them in a certain way.\n\nAs you progress through the levels, the game will become increasingly challenging, with more bubbles appearing on the screen at once and moving at faster speeds. But don't worry, as you play, you will also have access to power-ups that can help you clear the screen and earn even more points.\n\nWith addictive gameplay and vibrant graphics, this bubble pop game is sure to provide hours of fun and entertainment for players of all ages.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B51P6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-pop/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R59A5","slug":"candle-run","title":"Candle Run","description":"candle Run est un jeux unity","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R59A5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candle-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC866","slug":"coccode","title":"Coccode","description":"the rooster will collect as many eggs as possible","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC866/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coccode/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4CS2K","slug":"color-sudoku","title":"Color Sudoku","description":"Color Sudoku is a variation of the classic Sudoku game where instead of numbers, different colors are used to fill the grid. The game is played on a 9x9 grid, divided into 3x3 sub-grids. Each row, column, and sub-grid must contain all the colors exactly once.\n\nThe objective of the game is the same as the traditional Sudoku game, which is to fill in the empty spaces in the grid with the nine different colors so that each row, column, and sub-grid contains all the colors exactly once.\n\nPlaying Color Sudoku requires logical thinking and deduction skills, as you need to identify which colors can fit into the empty spaces based on the colors already placed in the grid. The game can be played at different levels of difficulty, with easy, medium, and hard puzzles available.\n\nColor Sudoku is a fun and challenging game that can be played alone or with friends. It is a great way to exercise your brain and improve your problem-solving skills while enjoying a colorful and visually appealing game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4CS2K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-sudoku/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3K538","slug":"dizzy-kawaii","title":"Dizzy Kawaii","description":"Dizzy Kawaii a fun and interesting matching game. Tap To Match The Crazy Kawaii As Many As You Can! This Game new mix of speed,\nmemory, and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test in this game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3K538/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dizzy-kawaii/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HIS5F","slug":"fish-master","title":"Fish Master","description":"Master of Fishing - a new project for fans to sit with a fishing rod, and just relax.\nThe game will give you extremely positive emotions, here you will be able to\ncatch the fish you want, but you have to try. The game offers:\n- Meditative gameplay\n- Nice drawn graphics\n- Realistic fishing\nAre you ready to cast your rod and pull in your biggest catch? Then go for it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HIS5F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fish-master/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FHP61","slug":"floppy-fish","title":"Floppy Fish","description":"Avoid obstacles to level up, find fantastic treasures.\nHelp the fish to swim among the obstacles and discover the interesting regions under the oceans and most importantly, survive as long as you can and beat world's best high score!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FHP61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/floppy-fish/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33194","slug":"jeremy-quest","title":"Jeremy Quest","description":"Jeremy Quest is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the red gems while avoiding the monsters, fire and spikes and reach the green flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33194/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jeremy-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8B613","slug":"motobots-1","title":"MotoBots 1","description":"MotoBots 101 originaly from Mars you are a Bot that goes to buy some space coffe from earth . try to get as far as possible in this arcade style infinite runner .","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8B613/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motobots-1/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C775L","slug":"multiplication-table","title":"Multiplication Table","description":"Multiplication table is a game where the player exercises his knowledge in multiplication and still has fun playing. Fun and education in one place.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C775L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/multiplication-table/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ENK86","slug":"paint-strike","title":"Paint Strike","description":"Paint Strike est un jeu de tir 3D addictif à une main avec une infinité de niveaux à compléter ! Faites glisser et déposez pour tirer et peindre toutes les quilles ! Dans chaque niveau, vous disposez d'un nombre limité de balles et devez frapper tous les clients de peinture qui se trouvent sur le plateau.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENK86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paint-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7HPI4","slug":"phone-for-kids","title":"Phone for Kids","description":"This fun educational game will teach your kids and toddlers to learn numbers and songs for hours on end with classic nursery rhymes with adorable images.\nWe value children’s education and your child will love playing with this fun baby toy.\nThey will learn numbers, letters and notes quickly and easily! your children will love learning with the songs and making sound effects!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7HPI4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/phone-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7HO78","slug":"queen-of-the-maze","title":"Queen of the Maze","description":"Players of all ages can enjoy the Queen of Hearts Maze Game, which is straightforward but challenging. It is a good example of a classic maze game, and it is sure to bring back memories for those who played it in the early days of PC gaming.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7HO78/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/queen-of-the-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"79TBF","slug":"robot-fish","title":"Robot Fish","description":"Robot Fish Online is a free online game that allows you to control a robotic fish in an underwater world. The game is played through a web browser and requires no download.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/79TBF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-fish/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8BC64","slug":"super-cowboy-run","title":"Super Cowboy Run","description":"Super Cowboy Run is a platform game in which you need to run a cowboy as far as possible, crossing all obstacles. In Super Cowboy Run game you have obstacles like zombies trying to attack from behind bushes and trees, a wheel coming at you so you need to jump over it, a bird is flying and dropping feather bombs so you need to avoid them to live and monsters keep coming at you so you need to shoot them to survive.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8BC64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-cowboy-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7DD6I","slug":"tiny-red-bird","title":"Tiny Red Bird","description":"Tiny Red Bird is the most simple game to play! Help Tiny Red Bird to fly through the sky trying to avoid obstacles that can kill the bird and you need to help the bird pass through it.\nLet us enjoy this game and achieve high scores and challenge your friends.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7DD6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-red-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4O53N","slug":"yummy-slot-machine","title":"Yummy Slot Machine","description":"Si vous aimez les jeux de machine à sous gratuits, Délice de machine à sous est fait pour vous. Un gameplay classique de bandit-manchot qui associe nourriture savoureuse et gros gains. Ressentez l'excitation suscitée par les machines à sous sans craindre de perdre de l'argent. Jouez à des machines à sous gratuites avec les fonctionnalités Wild, tours gratuits et partie bonus comme à Las Vegas. Emportez votre machine à sous partout avec vous.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4O53N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":39952,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H9ISG","slug":"sky-flight","title":"Sky Flight","description":"Sky Flight est un simulateur d'oiseaux simple et fascinant. Un jeu relaxant et magnifique pour ceux qui veulent se sentir en vol libre.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H9ISG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sky-flight/embed?sid=1","plays":39951,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"34U9O","slug":"colour-bubble-touch","title":"Colour Bubble Touch","description":"Color Bubble Touch is a bubble popping game, touch the screen and pop as many bubbles as possible to get a score. Be careful not to lose it ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/34U9O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colour-bubble-touch/embed?sid=1","plays":39951,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D2202","slug":"find-the-shadow","title":"Find the shadow","description":"Find the shadow is a game where you are challenged to find the right shadow for the image. There are 3 language options in the game. Have fun and see how many shadows you can find.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D2202/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-shadow/embed?sid=1","plays":39951,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"193EU","slug":"bubble-runner","title":"Bubble Runner","description":"Bubble Runner is the new game distributed by GamePix. You're a running bubble man and you need to avoid the obstacles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/193EU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39951,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ROSS3","slug":"color-boxes","title":"Color Boxes","description":"Build a bridge - click on the screen when the block is in the right place to fix it","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ROSS3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-boxes/embed?sid=1","plays":39951,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3TCB1","slug":"guess-top-brick","title":"Guess Top Brick","description":"Watch the action and try to tell which brick was the top one!\nThat's more fun than it sounds :)","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3TCB1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guess-top-brick/embed?sid=1","plays":39950,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51N61","slug":"ski-king","title":"Ski King","description":"Frayez-vous un chemin à travers les montagnes. Évitez les arbres et les rochers et dérapez sur la glace. Étudiez chaque piste et trouvez le chemin le plus court pour descendre la colline. Terminez en réalisant le meilleur temps.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51N61/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ski-king/embed?sid=1","plays":39950,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"236IS","slug":"expression","title":"Expression","description":"Expression, a math based puzzle\nYour goal is to write a mathematical expression with the tiles available on screen, so that the expression matches the result shown after the \"=\" symbol on the bottom line.\n\nYou can use some of the tiles or all of them. If you manage to write a correct expression made up of every available tile, you'll get a skip point, which allows you to skip a level if you find it too difficult.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/236IS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/expression/embed?sid=1","plays":39950,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6DR6Q","slug":"squid-impostor-escape","title":"Squid Impostor Escape","description":"hey you are alone in space and there are astronauts you need to save from monsters. rescue them and launch them into the safe zone of space. don't forget to collect all you need to complete the level and reach the portal! Go through the portal and complete all levels of 15 different difficulties.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6DR6Q/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squid-impostor-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":39950,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4ROND","slug":"redemption-slot-machine","title":"Redemption Slot Machine","description":"Dans l'Ouest sauvage, il y a deux types de joueurs de machine à sous. Ceux qui perdent tout le temps et les vainqueurs. Vous devriez gagner. Dans Redempion slots, vous pouvez faire l'expérience excitante d'un vieux parieur sans avoir à dépenser de l'argent réel ! Et si vous l'osez`, vous pouvez tenter de doubler vos gains. Venez jouer !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure","board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4ROND/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/redemption-slot-machine/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I1DP6","slug":"darts-practice","title":"Darts Practice","description":"How to play\n• Tap to fix the horizontal and vertical lines and you will throw to the intersection\n• You get 3 Chances","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I1DP6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/darts-practice/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"113RC","slug":"ichikas-adventure","title":"Ichikas Adventure","description":"Ichikas Adventure is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as Anime girl called Ichika who have to collect all of the necklaces while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, spikes, and saws and reach the door of your house in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/113RC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ichikas-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"05NUS","slug":"monster-puzzles","title":"Monster Puzzles","description":"Monster Puzzles is a cute puzzle game with all funny and scary monsters. Here is the season of Halloween where you see lots of similar items like pumpkins, hats. eyeballs, skeletons, spiders, and more scary stuff.\nHere in this game select any scary item and try to solve the jigsaw puzzle by matching all the pieces.\nComplete all the items and enjoy the game.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/05NUS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40323","slug":"tower-mania","title":"Tower Mania","description":"Build your towers in a fantastic futuristic world in the simplest one-click manner! Place floating blocks as precisely as you can and discover all the wonderful locations!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40323/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33DHR","slug":"deadly-hunters","title":"Deadly Hunters","description":"Find all the hunters and form a team to kill Jungle beast. Avoid obstacle and form a big team cause beast is not so weak!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33DHR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deadly-hunter/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14N31","slug":"endless-neon","title":"Endless Neon","description":"5 games in 1!\nAll games are endless!\nThere is a total score.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14N31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/endless-neon/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NB2LL","slug":"flying-bird","title":"Flying Bird","description":"Bienvenue sur Flying Bird, volez avec votre oiseau pour surmonter les obstacles et accumuler le plus de points possible","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NB2LL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-bird/embed?sid=1","plays":39949,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"70G4I","slug":"dagger-aim","title":"Dagger Aim","description":"Stick the daggers and avoid the metal plate. Try to hit the apple for bonus points.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/70G4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dagger-aim/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ER17T","slug":"dexitroid","title":"Dexitroid","description":"Dexitroid a fun fast-paced game to play on.\nBoost your reflex and move the bar ahead of traps and achieve high\nscores.\nSurvive as long as you can in the fun-based game and have fun.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ER17T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dexitroid/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A358O","slug":"dino-dash","title":"Dino Dash","description":"Dino Dash Online Arcade Adventure Game is an online game that challenges players to help a baby dinosaur escape from a group of hungry predators. The game features vibrant graphics and simple controls that make it easy for players of all ages to enjoy.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A358O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dino-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S7V18","slug":"akihiko-vs-cannons-2","title":"Akihiko vs Cannons 2","description":"Akihiko vs Cannons 2 is a 2D platformer where you have collect gold bars while avoiding ground enemy cannon bots, flying cannon bots, bullets, ground saws, spikes and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. You have 6 lives to start with. \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Akihiko vs Cannons\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S7V18/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/akihiko-vs-cannons-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P6RER","slug":"flappy-bird-runner","title":"Flappy Bird Runner","description":"Flappy Bird Runner is a fun and exciting arcade game. Play this cute and addictive game today. Flappy Bird Runner is a fun and exciting arcade game that's perfect for anyone who loves to play games.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P6RER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-bird-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8O931","slug":"rexo-2","title":"Rexo 2","description":"Rexo 2 is the Second installment of the original game, Rexo, which is a simple 2D Platformer where you play as the Cube and your aim is to collect all of the coins while avoiding spikes, and enemies. You have to get to the Red flag which will lead you to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nUse Arrow keys to control the movements of the Cube. Press Up arrow key twice to Double Jump. If you are using a mobile, you can use the movement touch buttons on the screen to play the game.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8O931/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rexo-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5775R","slug":"rinos-quest","title":"Rinos Quest","description":"Rinos Quest is a 2D platformer where you need to collect the silver key while avoiding the spike, saws and the spike monster enemies and unlocked the exit door.        \nThere are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as your proceed. \n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5775R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rinos-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O16AB","slug":"streetboard","title":"StreetBoard","description":"hey skateboarder take your skateboard and let's dust the streets. Let's reach the finish line on dangerous roads with our skateboard in the dark of the night, remember that it is very dangerous at night. At night there are snakes, poisonous mushrooms and deadly prickly cacti you have to watch out for.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Use \"wasd\" or \"arrow keys\" to move.    \n*You can jump twice.(double jump)         \n*Mobile touch control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O16AB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/streetboard/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C160T","slug":"pirate-jack","title":"Pirate Jack","description":"cute pirate jack's ship is invaded by pirates and all he wants is to reach his precious chest! Pirate Jack will do his best to reach his chest. watch out you have to survive on this ship full of deadly guns and angry pirates.  \n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD & Mobile Touch Control  \n*Double Jump Available","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C160T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pirate-jack/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"20630","slug":"jewel-blocks","title":"Jewel Blocks","description":"Entraînez votre cerveau avec ce défi d'arcade logique prenant aux formes de blocs classiques ! Jouez sans fin pour battre votre meilleur score et collecter des récompenses ! Facile à apprendre et amusant à maîtriser. Plein de décors disponibles.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/20630/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":39948,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"481O8","slug":"oomee-cake","title":"Oomee Cake","description":"There's a lot of cake to get through... How high can you stack the cake slices?","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/481O8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/oomee-cake/embed?sid=1","plays":39947,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P6434","slug":"punch-ball","title":"Punch ball!","description":"punch ball arcade game ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P6434/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/punch-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39946,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"633E6","slug":"explode-ball","title":"Explode Ball","description":"Explode Ball is fun arcade game.\nWhat you need to do is to aim and strike balls with the same color together and make higher level balls.\n\nKeep merging balls, more shooting chance will be gained, try if you can make the highest level of ball.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/633E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/explode-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39945,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O70RD","slug":"idle-robots","title":"Idle Robots","description":"Have you ever dreamed of programming your own robot from scratch? Build it step by step, choosing the best parts for it? Well, now it's possible more than ever.\n\nThe game \"Idle Robots\" presents a huge selection of technologies. Here you will find such legendary robots as T 800, R2D2, D.O.G, ARM and so on. Create them piece by piece and unlock more and more new robots!\n\nAdvantages of the game:\n-Variety of content\n-This clicker features the most iconic robots for cinema and art time. Start by assembling the upper parts and discover additional body design options.\n- Get gifts, increase your speed, travel through time and try your luck with happy spins.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O70RD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-robots/embed?sid=1","plays":39945,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"36","slug":"pet-drive-in","title":"Pet Drive In","description":"Grâce à Pet Drive In, devenez le meilleur gérant de fast food de la région. Prenez les commandes, faites des hamburgers maison et servez vos clients affamés!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/36/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pet-drive-in/embed?sid=1","plays":39945,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5L560","slug":"dd-dunk-line","title":"DD Dunk Line","description":"DD Dunk Line is a sport arcade game that has an interesting idea. In the game, you should move the ball into the basket with drawing lines!!!!!\n\nPlay and Buy more HTML5 games source code from DoonDookStudio Store: https://doondook.studio/buy-html5-games","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5L560/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dd-dunk-line/embed?sid=1","plays":39944,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00CH7","slug":"catch-the-mole","title":"Catch the Mole","description":"Catch the mole\nIncrease your score if you catch moles, but watch out for pumpkins","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00CH7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-the-mole/embed?sid=1","plays":39944,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"17C73","slug":"trz-cannon","title":"TRZ Cannon","description":"TRZ Cannon is a casual game in which the player must estimate strength and distance to hit cannon shots into baskets to win. The game has more than 100 levels with some small puzzles.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/17C73/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trz-cannon/embed?sid=1","plays":39943,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2N71L","slug":"icedland-adventure","title":"Icedland Adventure","description":"iceland adventure is a html5 platformer game, explore 10 stages defeat enemies and collect coins to get score\n\nhow to play:\nA > throw snowball\nARROW UP > jump\nARROW > move ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2N71L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/icedland-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":39943,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40309","slug":"color-pin","title":"Color Pin","description":"Lancez des balles colorées dans une roue en mouvement. Préparez-vous à des combinaisons de couleurs, des changements de rotation et à d’autres variations de gameplay qui émergent progressivement. Un bon timing et la perception des couleurs sont la clé, donc soyez prudent. Faites bien attention aux couleurs et à ne pas frapper les autres balles!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40309/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-pin/embed?sid=1","plays":39943,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5O106","slug":"brain-workout","title":"Brain Workout","description":"Game in which you need to solve math problems for some time. The further you advance, the more difficult the tasks and the faster the time goes!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5O106/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brain-workout/embed?sid=1","plays":39942,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MCL4G","slug":"ball-falling-match-color","title":"Ball Falling Match Color","description":"$5a","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MCL4G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-falling-match-color/embed?sid=1","plays":39941,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4049S","slug":"christmas","title":"Christmas","description":"Bienvenue à Noël, plongez-vous dans l'aventure, évitez les bombes et collectez des cadeaux pour les apporter au Père Noël, le tout accompagné d'un magnifique paysage, qui met en scène la demi-lune. Qu'est-ce que tu attends????? allez jouer à Noël maintenant et le plaisir sera garanti !!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4049S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":39941,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2636F","slug":"frogie","title":"Frogie","description":"Welcome to Frogie, have fun in this fantastic game crossing all the obstacles and accumulating points, what are you waiting for? go play Frogie now and the fun will be guaranteed !!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2636F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frogie/embed?sid=1","plays":39941,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"70599","slug":"slide-path","title":"Slide Path","description":"Faites glisser les diamants colorés sur les rails, tous se déplacent en même temps, votre objectif sera que tout le monde soit sur leur cible les diamants colorés de leur couleur respective","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/70599/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slide-path/embed?sid=1","plays":39941,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5T1OR","slug":"explorers-memory-match","title":"Explorers Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Explorers Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Explorers Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Explorers Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5T1OR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/explorers-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":39940,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31KH2","slug":"kris-mahjong-animals","title":"Kris Mahjong Animals","description":"In Kris Mahjong Animals, be prepared to test your attention! Cats and Lions and other cute animals decorate the tiles in this game, and all you have to do is to link them together. How many points do you think you can earn before the timer hits zero?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31KH2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kris-mahjong-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":39940,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6D1K7","slug":"ear-doctor-for-kids","title":"Ear Doctor for Kids","description":"Ear doctor is a doctor simulate game! Here we have many awesome medical tools and interesting treating processes, which make you feel like a real and powerful doctor! You can also play mini-games that will put your skills to the test as you help your patients with their ear problems.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6D1K7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ear-doctor-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39938,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AH332","slug":"heart-smash","title":"Heart Smash","description":"This is a game where you have to shoot arrows at hearts in 15 seconds. this game was created by Ludovico Rak (LudowS) in just one day\nusing the Godot game engine the graphics were created by Pixel Frog (Pixel Adventure)","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AH332/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heart-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":39938,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6DZD3","slug":"kids-zoo-fun","title":"Kids: Zoo Fun","description":"Ce jeu de puzzle est adapté à la fois aux enfants et aux parents. Le but du jeu est d'assembler chaque image. Le jeu est accessible en trois difficultés avec une quantité de pièces croissante pour chaque image. Les paramètres et les instructions sont protégés par un simple verrouillage parental.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6DZD3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-zoo-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":39938,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NIIC","slug":"space-ship-hunting","title":"Space Ship Hunting","description":"In this game you will enjoy the shooting in space .","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NIIC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-ship-hunting/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MRP56","slug":"yummy-super-taco","title":"Yummy Super Taco","description":"Do you like eating taco? In this game you have to make your delicious taco!\nStart from scratch and make the dough, tortilla, and cook the beef meat. Fill your taco with some fresh veggies and sauce. Make the tastiest taco in your town and serve to your customers.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MRP56/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-super-taco/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8R6C9","slug":"color-by-numbers","title":"Color by Numbers","description":"Hi! in this fantastic application you can color all the cute and funny characters by associating each color with a number!\n\nThis game is different than the other apps! here you have to color as if you had a pencil; you need to color all the blocks!\n\nSo be careful and try to color by associating each color with a number and try to not go outside the edges of the object!\n\nRemember: try to associate all the colors with the corresponding numbers to have the best possible result!\n\nThe game was created just for the little ones, who will have a lot of fun coloring by following the numbers, so while playing they will also learn the numbers and the colors associated with them!\n\nKey Features:\n• Over 60 items to color!\n• Colorful graphics!\n• Great fun music!\n• Simplified game interface!\n• Funny characters!\n• Baby quite game!\n• Ideal for the whole family!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8R6C9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-by-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T8464","slug":"jetpack-rider","title":"Jetpack Rider","description":"Jetpack rider have to finish the level and not die. On his way there are obstacles, enemies and moving platform! Buy a new character skin by collecting a coints, supportive items can be bought from a shop to finish the level!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T8464/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jetpack-rider/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6A085","slug":"space-scale","title":"Space Scale","description":"Space Scale est un jeu de plateforme musical 2D génial où vous aidez Giba à atteindre son vaisseau spatial sans perdre d’oxygène.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6A085/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-scale/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UTHRN","slug":"ant-squisher","title":"Ant Squisher","description":"Squish the Ants! Features a variety of Ants to squish, with a different speed and point value.\nAvoid the red Ants! they are very very dangerous!, if you touch 3 red Ants your game is finished... Have fun with this amazing and funny Ant game.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UTHRN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ant-squisher/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N76NO","slug":"find-word","title":"Find Word","description":"find the hidden words","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N76NO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-word/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C4E5L","slug":"halloween-circle","title":"Halloween Circle","description":"Come try your hand at our online Halloween game, Circle. See how high of a score you can get by jumping on the line with the circle.\nThe Halloween Circle online game is a fun way to get into the Halloween spirit. In the game, you jump on a line with a circle and try to break the highest record.\n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C4E5L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-circle/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8S48B","slug":"ninja-timba-man","title":"Ninja Timba Man","description":"Your goal is to chop wood and avoid the branches.   \nIt could be an easy task? It's easy to play but hard to master!   \nSo use your martial arts as every lumberjack does and chop the tree as fast the more you can!   \n· One-touch control system!   \n· Simple and addictive gameplay!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8S48B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloons/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"315OR","slug":"space-tower","title":"Space Tower","description":"You have a space tower to build! You have a balloon, and space cubes that fly\npast your platforms, bounce the ball over the cubes, build your tower. A project\nthat will give you a lot of wonderful emotions! In the game you will find:\n- Exciting gameplay.\n- Beautiful graphics\n- Amazing sound design\nReady to build your tower and climb to the top? Good Luck!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/315OR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I5SE6","slug":"speed-racer-online-game","title":"Speed Racer Online Game","description":"$5b","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5SE6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speed-racer-online-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H9OVO","slug":"stervella-in-the-fashion-world","title":"Stervella in the Fashion World","description":"Estelle aime la mode depuis son enfance. Mais une mode audacieuse et insolite! La fille mélange des styles incompatibles et souffle le cerveau avec ses idées. Elle a décidé de percer tout en haut de la scène de la mode et de devenir une célèbre créatrice de mode, et a même pris un pseudonyme pour elle - même-Stervella. Aidons Stervella à éblouir le public avec des tenues et des accessoires incroyables et à devenir la plus grande créatrice de mode de tous les temps!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H9OVO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stervella-in-the-fashion-world/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6957W","slug":"one-plus-two-is-three","title":"One Plus Two is Three","description":"Try your brain skills with this great math game! Play this fun math game with an intense adrenaline booster on your head.\nAs the timer is really quick, be as fast as you can to answer the question and clear the puzzles.\nBut is not easy to get a reply when the time is over! Have fun with this great math app game!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6957W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-plus-two-is-three/embed?sid=1","plays":39937,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0NLNA","slug":"tunnel-race-ball","title":"Tunnel Race Ball","description":"Move the circle and avoid the lines below, get the score by touch the other circle down, simple game to play.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0NLNA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tunnel-race-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39936,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16PIT","slug":"siege-battleplan","title":"Siege Battleplan","description":"Siege Battle Plan is a strategy game that rewards a quick mind and fast fingers. With an interactive game, design and exciting gameplay Siege Battle Plan will keep you immersed in it for hours. You'll need to combine good tactics with fast reflexes if you want to keep up with the challenge that is fallen before you. In love and war, everything is allowed, so use good strategy with perfect timing to belittle your opponent. ","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16PIT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/siege-battleplan/embed?sid=1","plays":39936,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"644O6","slug":"on-the-edge","title":"On the Edge","description":"On the Edge is a puzzle game where you have 40 levels to have fun with, with the objective of filling the containers to the limit set.\nJust click until the amount of water needed to fill, you can’t let it overflow or go below the limit. Have fun in these challenges.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/644O6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/on-the-edge/embed?sid=1","plays":39935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1S2I","slug":"don-t-step-on-the-white-tile-revenge","title":"Don't Step on the White Tile Revenge","description":"White Tiles is an addicting game that tests your reflexes against time and movement! Is it easy! Everybody can handle it, but not everyone can handle it well!\nWhite Tiles includes 2 modes: Classic and Rush The aim of the user is to tap on the Black tiles as fast as possible while keeping away from the white tiles.\nGame Over if you step on any white piano tiles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1S2I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-step-on-the-white-tile-revenge/embed?sid=1","plays":39935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5L1H6","slug":"flappy-change","title":"Flappy Change","description":"flappy change is an html5 arcade game, press and hold the screen to fly, avoid enemies and get coins","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5L1H6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-change/embed?sid=1","plays":39935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"666IO","slug":"pinoblu","title":"PinoBlu","description":"Pino is very hungry, and he needs your help!\n\nHelp Pino eat as many heads as possible and collect coins in a retro pixelated 2D experience! You have three hearts, if a person escapes you lose one heart, avoid credit cards because if you eat one you lose all three hearts. The more people you eat, the harder it will be. With the collected coins you can buy numerous skins to customize Pino and the background to your liking.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/666IO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pinoblu/embed?sid=1","plays":39935,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0C1R2","slug":"acorn-bot-2","title":"Acorn Bot 2","description":"Acorn Bot 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the ice cream cones while avoiding the enemy bots, flying robots, ground saws, spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Acorn Bot\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0C1R2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/acorn-bot-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O6EA0","slug":"halloween-racing","title":"Halloween Racing","description":"Halloween is just around the corner, and what better way to celebrate than by playing some spooky racing games? We've collected the best Halloween-themed racing games for you to play, so get ready for some ghoulish fun!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O6EA0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/halloween-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DEUD4","slug":"deep-sub","title":"Deep Sub","description":"Control a submarine in ocean, avoid trash and collect coins!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DEUD4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deep-sub/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BLG23","slug":"gliding-box","title":"Gliding Box","description":"Slide, jump and enjoy 15 levels with the difficulty of your choice. A classic of our times to enjoy for free.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BLG23/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gliding-box/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9OTD1","slug":"jocker-man-adventure","title":"Jocker Man Adventure","description":"Relax arcade game of adventure Pocker Man. Just jump to collect as much coins as you can. Open new levels, collect boosters and enjoy.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9OTD1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jocker-man-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L8OF1","slug":"platform-swap","title":"Platform Swap","description":"Swap between two Colors to be able to stand on the Ground or Platforms.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L8OF1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/platform-swap/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7F444","slug":"ufo-shooting-game","title":"UFO Shooting Game","description":"This awesome alien game lets you fly a UFO wherever you want! Fly through an amazing world with rivers, ships, mountains and everything in between. Play at any time of the day from morning to night!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7F444/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ufo-shooting-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FPG2P","slug":"flying-pig","title":"Flying Pig","description":"The Flying Pig is an adventure Game! An entertaining skill and action game the whole family can enjoy! catch as many flying food items as you can! But, don't catch the bombs, and mines or all your lives get drained out!\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FPG2P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-pig/embed?sid=1","plays":39934,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0K090","slug":"snack-ball","title":"Snack Ball","description":"This is one of those Color ball Pop games that features a gameplay that is delightful and exciting at the same time, This delightful balls connect game is ideal for those who are looking for a baloney game with a simple one-touch gameplay.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0K090/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snack-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39933,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A9B9S","slug":"fletearth-the-sendbox-game","title":"Fletearth - The Sendbox Game","description":"You are the God of Fletearth, you can create your world! Create seas, deserts, islands, woods, mountains, create peoples, but beware, different peoples will make war!\nCreate fluffy zombies that will hunt down your commoners. Unleash the power of the DRAGONS!\nLet the commoners face the seasons, with rain and snow, day and night. Unleash earthquakes, hurricanes, meteorites, eruptions, black holes and acid rains.\nSave your progress.\nAnd if you are tired of dominating the upper world, build an access to the underworld and set out to explore procedural dungeons, where you have no powers and strange creatures will make your life difficult.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A9B9S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fletearth-the-sendbox-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39932,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40099","slug":"skater-dude","title":"Skater Dude","description":"Attrapez votre skateboard et dévalez les pentes! Dirigez-vous à droite ou à gauche pour éviter les obstacles et les officers de sécurité. Attention car plus vous jouez et plus votre skate accélère, j'espère que vous ne craignez pas la vitesse!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40099/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skater-dude/embed?sid=1","plays":39932,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NN6R","slug":"nitro-rally","title":"Nitro Rally","description":"Nitro Rally is a fun classic 2D arcade racing game similar with the classic racing games of the 80's.\nPlay ten different circuits to race in a car that runs automatically.\nUnlock two or more powerful cards that are hidden and discover other features while playing.\nUse the turbo when you need an extra speed boost and set the best lap time.\nThe game shows colorful and detailed graphics and a nice sound effects you will enjoy.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NN6R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nitro-rally/embed?sid=1","plays":39931,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40091","slug":"let-s-go-fishing","title":"Let's go fishing","description":"L'été est là et c'est bien connu, l'été est le meilleur moment pour aller pêcher! Saisissez votre canne et partez pêcher le plus gros poisson que vous pourrez trouver!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40091/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lets-go-fishing/embed?sid=1","plays":39930,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1AL5I","slug":"jewel-aquarium","title":"Jewel Aquarium","description":"Cet océan regorge de poissons rares et autres créatures marines ! Associez-les pour fabriquer des poissons explosifs ! Cela peut vous aider à détruire les blocs qui sont sur votre chemin. Un jeu d'arcade classique de séries de 3 en tour par tour aux nombreux niveaux et modes passionnants vous attend !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1AL5I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-aquarium/embed?sid=1","plays":39930,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IFC1F","slug":"traffic-io","title":"Traffic.io","description":"In Traffic.io,  you have to prevent crashes. You can stop and start cars by tapping on them. This game is quite challenging after few seconds.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IFC1F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/traffic-io/embed?sid=1","plays":39930,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W3NA5","slug":"mahjong-around-the-world-africa","title":"Mahjong Around The World Africa","description":"Our mahjong journey will start on the African continent. Find all mahjong pairs to clear the game field and set free all 10 African animals. Mind that there is a time limit for each level. You can also use prompts, and swap tiles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W3NA5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-around-the-world-africa/embed?sid=1","plays":39929,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62IDD","slug":"dodge-it","title":"Dodge it!","description":"A new short game made for a game jam.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62IDD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dodge-it/embed?sid=1","plays":39929,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"410AA","slug":"4-in-row-mania","title":"4 in Row Mania","description":"Le jeu de connexion classique et populaire à deux joueurs ! Soyez le premier à connecter quatre pions de votre couleur dans une grille suspendue verticalement.\n\nDéfinissez le niveau de difficulté et jouez contre l'ordinateur ou contre un ami en vous relayant pour déposer vos pions colorées dans la grille, et essayer de battre votre adversaire !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/410AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/4-in-row-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":39928,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TEBGD","slug":"knight-bridge","title":"Knight Bridge","description":"This Knight has a dream of covering the long distance to get the treasure. Would you think that you are capable enough to help him make his dream come true? Take this challenge and show off the world that you are a true adventurer! Be careful while dropping your stick from one side to the other since your wrong decision can make your character fall in the water and you would lose the game immediately!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TEBGD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knight-bridge/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TN6OO","slug":"blasty-shooting","title":"Blasty Shooting","description":"Faites exploser les boules qui tombent. Détruisez chaque balle avant qu'elle n'atteigne le sol, si l'une des balles descend, votre jeu s'en remettra. Améliorez votre joueur pour tirer plus vite et plus fort, ce qui vous aidera à détruire les balles plus rapidement.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TN6OO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blasty-shooting/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8E4CG","slug":"candle-slider-image-challenge","title":"Candle Slider Image Challenge","description":"Welcome to Candle Slider Image Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Candle Slider Image Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Candle Slider Image Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8E4CG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candle-slider-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NU9F8","slug":"funny-rescue-sumo","title":"Funny Rescue Sumo","description":"The sumo looks so messy after his battle. Rescue him immediately. Help him recover from the wounds and don't forget to give him some makeover. ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NU9F8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-rescue-sumo/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6E6E7","slug":"pompas-breaker","title":"Pompas Breaker","description":"Aim at the birds, shoot them with the water hose to make them release feathers and break the bubbles before they scare them away.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6E6E7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pompas-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ET9EO","slug":"some-little-bosses-2","title":"Some Little Bosses 2","description":"Some little bosses 2 is the sequel of Some little bosses, fight against 8 different bosses on mobile or desktop pc and try to defeat them all, won't be easy! ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ET9EO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/some-little-bosses-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M56D6","slug":"jump-dude","title":"Jump Dude","description":"You will have to show all the care and reaction speed to pass the slippery track. If the attempt fails, you will have to repeat the level again. But jumping is an extremely exciting activity that gives a lot of pleasure. Go through level after level, despite the difficulties!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M56D6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-dude/embed?sid=1","plays":39927,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE439","slug":"jewel-halloween","title":"Jewel Halloween","description":"Utilisez votre vivacité et votre logique dans ce nouveau jeu d'halloween. Profitez de l'aventure pleine de citrouilles, de monstres et de squelettes tout en collectant des pièces. Pourrez-vous réussir tous les niveaux sans avoir peur ?\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE439/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":39926,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5AIA4","slug":"build-an-island","title":"Build an Island","description":"Build your island and create your little civilization. How beautiful of an island can you build?","category":"Stratégie","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5AIA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/build-an-island/embed?sid=1","plays":39925,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YE964","slug":"eat-money","title":"Eat Money","description":"Welcome to Eat Money, challenge the enemies, use the secret passages, parkour between the blocks, find 12 coins and finish the game. Suitable for both PC and phone Eat Money will involve you in a fantastic adventure full of fun, what are you up to !! go play Eat Money now.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YE964/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eat-money/embed?sid=1","plays":39925,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UIM70","slug":"somersault-ninja-samurai-ninja-jump","title":"Somersault Ninja-Samurai Ninja Jump","description":"Somersault Ninja: Samurai Ninja Jump is a jump ninja battle survival game. In the middle of night, a group of ninjas came out with naked swords to steal another food but were also attacked themselves in an attempt at protecting their own provisions from being taken by these skilled Thieves! This new outdoor adventure will test your limits as you help one side fight off other rival warriors while trying not fall prey yourself - it can get pretty dangerous around here sometimes!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UIM70/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/somersault-ninja-samurai-ninja-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":39923,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PRA4S","slug":"space-transport","title":"Space Transport","description":"This is a casual game in which spaceships come in four colors: red, yellow, blue and green. You have to change the color of the black hole so that it matches the color of the spacecraft approaching it. if the color does not match, then in this case you will lose. Changing the color is the main task in this game.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PRA4S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-transport/embed?sid=1","plays":39923,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C8GM6","slug":"cooking-mania","title":"Cooking Mania","description":"Réalise tes rêves en tant que chef dans ton propre restaurant. Choisis l'un des cinq restaurants différents avec une difficulté croissante. Améliorez votre équipement pour gérer le nombre croissant de clients qui adorent votre cuisine.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C8GM6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cooking-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":39923,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C6C9N","slug":"cap-boy-run","title":"Cap Boy Run","description":"cap boy run is an html5 game, play as boy run,  jump over obstacles or enemies and get gems to get high score ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C6C9N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cap-boy-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39922,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"955P1","slug":"pancake","title":"Pancake","description":"Use one Click To move Collect pancake and avoid obsticles","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/955P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pancake/embed?sid=1","plays":39922,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6J66G","slug":"mahjong-quest","title":"Mahjong Quest","description":"Découvrez le Mahjong dans ce casse-tête de type Solitaire ! Les règles sont simples, vous devez retirer les pièces correspondantes du plateau jusqu'à ce que vous atteigniez l'objectif. Si vous êtes rapide, vous recevrez des médailles et des outils !\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6J66G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":39921,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NB6BN","slug":"boulder-snow","title":"Boulder Snow","description":"A classic puzzel in Christmas revisitation, with sweets, balls and saplings. Complete the levels by being careful of the various trap falls.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NB6BN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boulder-snow/embed?sid=1","plays":39921,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4DLO2","slug":"jail-drop","title":"Jail Drop","description":"Jail Drop is a 60 levels of fun physics puzzle game! all boxes except the grass must be removed where the prison is standing.\nSimply click or tap on the boxes or blocks to destroy them.\nCarefully use the set blocks in what ever way you can to get the prisoner safely into the grass.\nYou can reset each level if you made a wrong move.\nSolve this fun physics game and enjoy!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4DLO2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jail-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":39921,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E66UC","slug":"super-charlie","title":"Super Charlie","description":"Welcome to Super Charlie, help Charli pass all levels, kill enemies and overcome obstacles. What are you waiting for?? Go play Super Charlie now and the fun is guaranteed !!!!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E66UC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-charlie/embed?sid=1","plays":39921,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4994Q","slug":"one-square","title":"One Square","description":"A simple game where you have to be careful of squares falling from the sky","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4994Q/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/one-square/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BOT6A","slug":"aneye-bot-2","title":"Aneye Bot 2","description":"Aneye Bot 2 is a 2D Sci-Fi themed platformer where you have to collect the ice cream while avoiding the enemy robots, flying bots, spikes and saws and reach the house which leads you to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.       \nThis is the second installment of the original \"Aneye Bot\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.       \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BOT6A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aneye-bot-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19UN3","slug":"ants-quest-2","title":"Ants Quest 2","description":"Ants Quest 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the sugar cubes while avoiding the enemy ants, three-eyed ants, bullets, flying ants, spikes and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.     \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Ants Quest 2\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.     \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19UN3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ants-quest-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42A91","slug":"arkanoid-for-painters","title":"Arkanoid for Painters","description":"Destroy all blocks and enemies.\nInstead of using board just draw obstacles to prevent the ball from falling. \n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42A91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arkanoid-for-painters/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"601RL","slug":"b-baller","title":"B-Baller","description":"B-Baller is an online arcade basketball game that is perfect for anyone who loves the sport. The game is easy to pick up and play, and it is a great way to pass the time. B-Baller is an online arcade basketball game that lets you compete against other players from around the world. With its fast-paced gameplay and easy-to-use controls, B-Baller is perfect for any fan of basketball.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/601RL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/b-baller/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O13BA","slug":"baby-boss-photo-shoot","title":"Baby Boss Photo Shoot","description":"In this cute Baby Boss Photo Shoot game, Boss Baby is thrilled about his photoshoot for upcoming candidacy. He wants to make a show by wearing some cool outfits. Beach baby or skater baby? Casual baby or a pro-style office baby? Hip-hop baby or a mini superhero? Boss is overwhelmed with choice. Help the baby boss choose and try different dress up and makeover outfits to enjoy delivering a stunning appearance.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O13BA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/baby-boss-photo-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T2217","slug":"black-hole-solitaire","title":"Black Hole Solitaire","description":"Black Hole is an addictive solitaire card game with similar rules as Tri Peaks or golf solitaire. Your goal is to move all cards to the black hole by either counting up or counting down in value.","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T2217/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-hole-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PP39L","slug":"brawl-poo","title":"Brawl Poo","description":"hey poo let's go to war? Win the battle in the arenas and buy yourself new clothes, don't forget the clothes can make you look more attractive. let's fight and win. Collect the gold as you earn, get the bonus and get the skin you want! Every victory will carry you forward poo you have to win the battles.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Click and drop to play  \n*Pull it in the opposite direction you want to fly.  \n*Shoot arrows in the direction you shoot!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PP39L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brawl-poo/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19ZY7","slug":"buzzy-bee","title":"Buzzy Bee","description":"Use your finger and flap your wings to fly be careful to try to avoid all dangerous trunks! Have Fun! Fly as long as you can without hitting the trunks and achieve high scores.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19ZY7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buzzy-bee/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NY9RE","slug":"crazy-runner","title":"Crazy Runner","description":"Full description: Crazy runner is an endless game in which you can collect gold stars and overcome obstacles. With a selection of different characters running along a jungle trail where you can find a way to survive, it will be very difficult and requires a quick response.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NY9RE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OMB55","slug":"cube-zombie-shooter","title":"Cube Zombie Shooter","description":"Cube zombie shooter the game you try to survive as long as possible, control player A,S,D,W and shoot with left mouse button\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OMB55/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cube-zombie-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UB613","slug":"deep-blue-turtle","title":"Deep Blue Turtle","description":"Deep Blue Turtle! Guide our turtle hero back and forth, avoiding the jelly fish hazards along the way.\nTap or Click to stay a float, and collect the pearls as you Go!\nHave fun with this great endless game!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UB613/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/deep-blue-turtle/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L16SB","slug":"evasive-balls","title":"Evasive Balls","description":"Touch to change the circle rotation and avoid the pink balls to loss, and also to get score get the yellow balls","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L16SB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evasive-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87881","slug":"evil-invader","title":"Evil Invader","description":"Evil Invader is an exciting online top-down shooter game. In Evil Invader, you will face off against hordes of enemies, using your skills and quick reflexes to survive. With challenging gameplay and a variety of weapons and power-ups to choose from, Evil Invader is a game that will keep you coming back for more!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87881/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evil-invader/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A0163","slug":"falling-stars","title":"Falling Stars","description":"A fun game to train your motor skills and attention.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A0163/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/falling-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AEI13","slug":"fish-jigsaw-tile-mania","title":"Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania","description":"Welcome to Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania! Our Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania picture. With a wide variety of Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Fish Jigsaw Tile Mania Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AEI13/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fish-jigsaw-tile-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6GU3P","slug":"floppy-penguin","title":"Floppy Penguin","description":"Floppy Penguin is a free online game that is perfect for players of all ages. With its simple controls and easy-to-follow gameplay, Floppy Penguin is a great way to pass the time and have some fun. At Floppy Penguin, we pride ourselves on providing high-quality, family-friendly online gaming experiences. Our games are free to play, and we believe that gaming should be accessible to everyone. Whether you're a seasoned gamer or just getting started, we hope you'll give our games a try. Thank you for your interest in Floppy Penguin!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6GU3P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/floppy-penguin/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3TU88","slug":"gift-unlock","title":"Gift Unlock","description":"The game helps to improve your intellectual facilities.\nfun game to pass the time and relax your mind from work or school\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3TU88/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gift-unlock/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EA4GN","slug":"green-ball-po","title":"Green Ball Po","description":"Green Ball Po is a 2D platformer where you need to collect Golden keys in order to unlock the door while avoiding spikes and enemies. There are 8 levels to play and difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow keys\" for player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"up arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EA4GN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/green-ball-po/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE7RA","slug":"heart-breaker","title":"Heart Breaker","description":"Heart Breaker is a free online game that challenges players to break as many hearts as possible. The game is suitable for all ages and offers a great way to relieve stress.\n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE7RA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heart-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T32T0","slug":"letter-match","title":"Letter Match","description":"Match the letters in thier group and play over 100 levels the game gets harder each level. the controls press esc to go to the main menu \nleft click to pick letters and right click to unselect","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T32T0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/letter-match/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O94OG","slug":"long-lines","title":"Long Lines","description":"Try to pilot the snake to collect all dots and finish each level!\nEnjoy this great puzzle games!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O94OG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/long-lines/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C81A6","slug":"magic-land","title":"Magic Land","description":"Magic Land is an endless runner game where you play as a wizard who must run through a magical land, collecting coins and avoiding obstacles. The game is played from a side-scrolling perspective, and you can move your character left and right to avoid obstacles. You can also jump to collect coins that are floating in the air. As you collect coins, your score will increase. The game will end if you collide with an obstacle or fall off the edge of the screen.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C81A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magic-land/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HMM3M","slug":"match-memory","title":"Match Memory","description":"Memory Match is a simple classic board game which can help and challenging your brain memory. and reach highest score as possible while timer is decreased every second.\n\nTap, click or touch tile to flip/open. then open another closed tile.\n\nIf two open tile match, tile will be removed from the screen and score will be increased","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HMM3M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-memory/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5OE2T","slug":"megaslots","title":"Megaslots","description":"Very exciting slot game, with 6 wheels. Win horizontal or diagonal with 3 or more items of the same kind. Get the spinning wheel, and win even more.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5OE2T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/megaslots/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OAEV7","slug":"nekoman-vs-gangster","title":"Nekoman vs Gangster","description":"Nekoman vs Gangster is a 2D platformer where you play as a cat who have to collect all of the silver keys while avoiding the Gangsters, saws and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OAEV7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nekoman-vs-gangster/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RUAE4","slug":"nina-adventures-2","title":"Nina Adventures 2","description":"Nina Adventures 2 is a 2D little platformer where you play as a cute girl who have to collect all of the chocolate ice cream bars while avoiding the monsters, flying creatures and their bullets, ground saws and spikes and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.   \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Nina Adventures\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RUAE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nina-adventures-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZPLAI","slug":"paulie-the-pizza","title":"Paulie the Pizza","description":"Help Paulie the Pizza survive and not get consumed! Jump, run, solve puzzles and beat bosses! Fast-paced platform game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZPLAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paulie-the-pizza/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P358E","slug":"perfect-run","title":"Perfect Run","description":"Paint the floor using the sponge cloth.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P358E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/perfect-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A69O","slug":"pocket-solitaire","title":"Pocket Solitaire","description":"Pocket Solitaire is a classic and addictive online card game that challenges your problem-solving skills and strategic thinking. With simple rules and intuitive gameplay, you can enjoy hours of fun, anytime and anywhere. In this single-player game, your goal is to move all the cards from the tableau to the foundation piles, according to suit and in ascending order. Can you beat the clock and solve the puzzle before running out of moves?","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A69O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pocket-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BNP19","slug":"pro-obunga-vs-noob-and-hacker","title":"Pro Obunga vs Noob and Hacker","description":"You have to escape from the pro obunga monster, if it catches you, it can eat you and cut you to pieces. so step on the gas with your friend and run away from him please never slow down and be very careful. Jump off the ramps and drive cars carefully on bumpy roads. Remember, the beast is right behind you. Collect the hell mines that you need to collect while escaping from the monster.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BNP19/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pro-obunga-vs-noob-and-hacker/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ASN0S","slug":"santa-swing-spike","title":"Santa Swing Spike","description":"Help Santa to jump side to side and try to avoid the spikes!    \nThat's all you need to do but try to resist the more you can!    \nEnjoy!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ASN0S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-swing-spike/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"95N62","slug":"season-pass","title":"Season Pass","description":"Changer de vêtements selon la météo","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/95N62/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/season-pass/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NONH8","slug":"sheon-panda-2","title":"Sheon Panda 2","description":"Sheon Panda 2 is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect all of the bamboo sticks while avoiding enemy panda(red), flying Panda drones, saws, and spikes and reach the Exit cave in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.    \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Sheon Panda\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NONH8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sheon-panda-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1B080","slug":"slip-ball","title":"Slip Ball","description":"Touch and move the ball to avoid enemies, get the score by taking the visiable blocks","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1B080/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slip-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0S516","slug":"smash-all-ants","title":"Smash All Ants","description":"Tap as many ants as you can, protect a chocolate on the bottom of the screen before ants","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0S516/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/smash-all-ants/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NL18K","slug":"snake-blocks","title":"Snake Blocks","description":"Snake Blocks is a 2D puzzle game where you control a snake of blocks. The goal of the game is to reach the end of each level by maneuvering your snake around obstacles and collecting power-ups. The game features a variety of levels, each with its own unique challenges. Some levels require you to navigate tight spaces, while others require you to use power-ups to solve puzzles.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NL18K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snake-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L7S67","slug":"snowfall","title":"Snowfall","description":"The Snowfall Online Jump Action game is a great choice for anyone looking for a fun and challenging way to spend their free time. With its simple controls and easy-to-learn gameplay, the game is perfect for players of all ages and skill levels. Whether you're a seasoned gamer or just starting out, the Snowfall Online Jump Action game is sure to provide you with hours of entertainment.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L7S67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowfall/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0HA8E","slug":"squash-these-ants-2","title":"Squash These Ants 2","description":"Destroy with your fingers all ants that exit on the hole.    \nSquish all the ants that appear on the screen with your fingers, before they leave the screen be very careful don't tap the red ants, they are very dangerous.    \nYou have in this awesome App seven modality to smash all the Ants that you see on the screen.    \nAll you can have a game of ants is in \"Squash these Ants 2\" easy to play hard to stop.    \n    \nKey Features:    \n• Very very easy to play    \n• Nice 3D pre rendered graphics    \n• Amazing 3D realistic animations    \n• Seven different gameplay modality    \n• Endless gameplay modality for kids    \n• Very great game for kids and babies    \n• Cool ambience nature music    \n• In Slasher/Weight modality mega \"combo\" bonus    \n• In Defense very innovative gameplay    \n• Different backgrounds    \n    \nHave fun with this great endless Ant smasher game.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0HA8E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/squash-these-ants-2/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"V2RUV","slug":"superhero-violet-summer-excursion","title":"Superhero Violet Summer Excursion","description":"Superhero Violet Summer Excursion is just kicking in. Violet couldn’t stop thinking about the sea and beach so she decided to take a break and head to the closest beach she knew. But before anything else, she needs to properly prepare her complexion for the long sunbathing sessions she has in mind – care to help her out? Come and join her in getting started with this amazing makeover game for girls and first of all, take good care of her tiered complexion.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/V2RUV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superhero-violet-summer-excursion/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RSIL6","slug":"survival-fairy","title":"Survival Fairy","description":"Survival Fairy jump is a survival game that you can play online. The objective of the game is to survive as long as possible by avoiding obstacles and collecting resources. You can play solo or team up with other players to increase your chances of survival. Survival Fairy is a jump survival game that you can play online. In the game, you control a fairy who must survive in a dangerous world full of traps and enemies. The game is challenging and requires quick reflexes and good decision-making skills.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RSIL6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survival-fairy/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EH8HW","slug":"throw-daggers","title":"Throw Daggers","description":"Throw Daggers was designed to be a fun and challenging game, your objective is to hit as many fruits as possible while throwing daggers towards you, but always be careful with the wind as it is always changing its direction and its strength if you don’t hit anything. you will lose a dagger, you lose by missing the last dagger available, so pay close attention! Challenge your friends to see who can get the highest score!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EH8HW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/throw-daggers/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5H6A5","slug":"tomato-ketchup","title":"Tomato Ketchup","description":"Tomato Ketchup is an online game that is free to play. It is a lot of fun, and it is also a great way to improve your skills. The \"Tomato Ketchup Online Game\" is a free and fun game that can be enjoyed by people of all ages.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5H6A5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tomato-ketchup/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5PINK","slug":"viking-escape","title":"Viking Escape","description":"Viking escape is a game in which you control a Viking flying on a dragon, the Viking must go all the way to the end to get out of a dark forest filled with goblins and other mutants. A Viking can throw different types of weapons, and a dragon can breathe out a fiery flame. Help the Viking survive, get out of the forest and score as many points and ammunition as possible.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5PINK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/viking-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B9WI5","slug":"web-ski-christmas","title":"Web Ski Christmas","description":"Santa Claus has lost all the gifts from the sleigh, now they are scattered around the mountain!Help him to take them all skiing at full speed, but do not forget any!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B9WI5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/web-ski-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T07ME","slug":"winter-gemstone","title":"Winter Gemstone","description":"Winter Gemstone is an online 2D game that challenges players to collect as many gems as possible. The game is set in a winter wonderland and features a variety of obstacles and enemies.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T07ME/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/winter-gemstone/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76Z74","slug":"zigzag-racing","title":"Zigzag Racing","description":"Zigzag Racing Bike is a free online game that challenges players to race against each other in a fast-paced, competitive environment. Zigzag Racing Online is a fast-paced game that will put your driving skills to the test. You'll need to be quick and accurate to win, so practice your reactions and aim before you race!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76Z74/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zigzag-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40100","slug":"snack-time","title":"Snack Time","description":"Waldy le sanglier sauvage doit se préparer pour la venue de l'hiver. Faites bouger les glands vers les zones désignées et traversez les 12 niveaux qui composent cet étonnant jeu de Sokoban!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40100/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snack-time/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"03OJ0","slug":"jump-forward","title":"Jump Forward","description":"jump and don't die ,,, keep the mouse or finger pressed for a longer jump","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/03OJ0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-forward/embed?sid=1","plays":39920,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AM2P6","slug":"paddle-game","title":"Paddle Game","description":"Rotate the board and bounce the ball to the same color side.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AM2P6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/paddle-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39919,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I386R","slug":"anime-vampire-girl-coloring-pages","title":"Anime Vampire Girl Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Vampire Girl Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Vampire Girl Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Vampire Girl Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Vampire Girl Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I386R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-vampire-girl-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":39919,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GMEPA","slug":"patchwork-images","title":"Patchwork Images","description":"Logical game where you need to collect from pieces of geometric shapes different patterns, you do not know how and where the pieces of the puzzle are located, you see only the general silhouette of the pattern, you need to pick up the position and the correct angle of the piece of the puzzle, what would eventually turned out a beautiful picture.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GMEPA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/patchwork-images/embed?sid=1","plays":39919,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64ALR","slug":"fruit-slasher","title":"Fruit Slasher","description":"Fruit Slasher Slicing Master is one of the best 3D slicing games for you with simple gameplay of 3d fruit cut with tribal weapons.\nJust tap your finger on the screen and cut the fruit to score high and make juicy beverages to feel the feelings of a drunk master.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64ALR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-slasher/embed?sid=1","plays":39919,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1992R","slug":"farm-puzzles","title":"Farm Puzzles","description":"Farm Puzzles Jigsaw is a free online game from genre of puzzle and jigsaw really suitable games for kids!         \nYou can select one of the 14 different animals and then try to complete all image!         \nHave fun and enjoy with your little one!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1992R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/farm-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":39918,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56LLD","slug":"doodle-man","title":"Doodle Man","description":"Jump from platform to platform grab on to anything you can find to stay up! another addictive, and deliciously re-playable micro game, works with almost any device","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56LLD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doodle-man/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1GAG6","slug":"fall-germ","title":"Fall Germ","description":"Fall in Love With the Fall Germ While Playing Germ Crazy Game Online","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1GAG6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fall-germ/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RDN7D","slug":"free-printable-mandala-coloring-for-kids","title":"Free Printable Mandala Coloring For Kids","description":"$5c","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RDN7D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/free-printable-mandala-coloring-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6192N","slug":"hungry-rabbit","title":"Hungry Rabbit","description":"Hungry Rabbit Arcade is an online arcade game full of fun and action. In our arcade games, hungry rabbits try to jump higher and run faster in order to catch carrots, because friends don't let friends miss out on their veggies! Play now for free!    \nHungry Rabbit is an online arcade full of games that are fun and action-packed. These games include Hungry Rabbit, Rabbit Jump, and Rabbit Dash. They are fun for all ages and skill levels, but mostly for anyone who likes fast-paced arcade action! Play now for free!    \n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6192N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hungry-rabbit/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MS6EJ","slug":"kaomoji-match-master","title":"Kaomoji Match Master","description":"Kaomoji Match Master is an online game that challenges you to match kaomoji characters in the shortest time possible. Kaomoji Match Master, the online matching game that challenges you to find the perfect emoticon for every situation! With over 1000 different kaomoji to choose from, you're sure to find the right one for every occasion.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MS6EJ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kaomoji-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"75693","slug":"miss-yuuno","title":"Miss Yuuno","description":"Miss Yuuno is a 2D adventure platformer where you play as a girl called Yuuno who have lost memories because of a traumatic incident. You have to collect your lost pieces of memories while avoiding the shadow monsters, spikes, and reach the loop hole in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play with moderate difficulty.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.    \nUse \"W\" or \"Arrow\" key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/75693/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miss-yuuno/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D7NO7","slug":"run-dino-run","title":"Run Dino Run","description":"You play as a dinosaur and you have to run from extinction.The revamped version of Chrome's offline Dino runner. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D7NO7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/run-dino-run/embed?sid=1","plays":39917,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91RN1","slug":"funny-puppy-dressup","title":"Funny Puppy Dressup","description":"It's Puppy dress up time! Lots of stylish items available. Shoes, hats, clothes, pants, and even super cool hairs! Unlock more adorable cute puppy outfits by playing interesting mini games. It's easy and fun to play.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91RN1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-puppy-dressup/embed?sid=1","plays":39915,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40306","slug":"blocky-warrior","title":"Blocky Warrior","description":"Play Blocky Warrior, the brand new puzzle action game for every device. Defeat all the enemies and finish the game!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40306/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blocky-warrior/embed?sid=1","plays":39915,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RTN4R","slug":"crash-monster-teeth","title":"Crash Monster Teeth","description":"An evil monster wants to eat you. \nThe goal of the game is to knock out all the teeth of an evil monster with a hammer. You will have a limited time. But you can get extra time by collecting balls in a row. Use the buttons to rotate and change blocks in the dashboard. Collected coins will help you change any shape.","category":"Sport","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RTN4R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crash-monster-teeth/embed?sid=1","plays":39914,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A180O","slug":"freecell-solitaire-cards","title":"Freecell Solitaire Cards","description":"Obtenez le meilleur score ou faites juste une partie relaxante de Free cell Solitaire ! Plongez directement dans l'action, aucun réglage supplémentaire n'est requis. Cherchez les As parmi les quatre couleurs, placez-les sur les bases dès que possible et créez des piles de cartes par ordre croissant. Vous pouvez placer quatre cartes dans les cases libres pour pouvoir accéder aux cartes des colonnes. Et rappelez-vous, on peut toujours gagner à une partie de Freecell solitaire ! \n","category":"Action","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A180O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/freecell-solitaire-cards/embed?sid=1","plays":39914,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TISM6","slug":"match-fruits","title":"Match Fruits","description":"Match Fruits is a match 3 game with 72 stages (and counting). Swap and match 3 or more fruits of the same type and make points and special fruits before time runs out. Earn points and compete with your friends and with all other players around the world in the global leaderboards.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TISM6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-fruits/embed?sid=1","plays":39913,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TAMR3","slug":"hammer-master-io","title":"Hammer Master io","description":"Smash the players on the battlefield and absorb their power! Join the gang beasts fight and enjoy the crazy action. Become bigger and stronger kicking every buddy in the PvP io arena! Win the round and become the last stickman fighter who lived in this battle royal!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TAMR3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hammer-master-io/embed?sid=1","plays":39912,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4NRYN","slug":"funny-daycare","title":"Funny Daycare","description":"Funny Daycare is a fun loving game to play with various cute animal characters in daycare center. You'll become a babysitter and take care of them. This game provides some creative task like bathe the babies, play with them, prepare delicious meals, and dress up. Let your imagination fly exploring and playing with Funny Daycare!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4NRYN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-daycare/embed?sid=1","plays":39911,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE5R5","slug":"steveman-horror","title":"Steveman Horror","description":"In horror, the last game of the steveman series, monsters are more dangerous, more challenging and stronger. If you want to help steveman, you have to give him strength and help. Help collect purple pumpkins and reach the portal quickly. New levels are waiting for you in the portal, pass the levels and pass the last level. Be careful, monsters can eat you. don't show your fear.  \n\nHow to Play?\nWASD + Mobile Touch Control","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE5R5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steveman-horror/embed?sid=1","plays":39911,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46E69","slug":"here","title":"Here","description":"pass the levels, in the second level don't get hit by the water","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46E69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/here/embed?sid=1","plays":39911,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"08587","slug":"tori","title":"Tori","description":"Tori is a 2D cute little platformer where you play as Tori, who have to collect orange balls while avoiding the enemies, spikes and ground saws and reach the red flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you continue.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.                  \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/08587/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tori/embed?sid=1","plays":39910,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RYLE6","slug":"pixelpool-2-player","title":"Pixelpool - 2 Player","description":"The blue and red men from the pixelpool family must reach the door safely. As the pixelpool, they have to watch out for the obstacles and jump over the obstacles and reach the finish line without dying. Reach the door together with red and blue. get the victory. be the winner.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RYLE6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixelpool-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":39910,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TU7UP","slug":"asylums-picture-piece","title":"Asylums Picture Piece","description":"Welcome to Asylums Picture piece, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Asylums Picture piece, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Asylums Picture piece and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TU7UP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/asylums-picture-piece/embed?sid=1","plays":39909,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8Y6RY","slug":"crazy-truck","title":"Crazy Truck","description":"Hill climbing is a tough challenge, but with the right truck it can be a fun and thrilling experience. \"Crazy Truck Online Hill Climbing Games\" offers a variety of trucks to choose from, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Players must use their skills to navigate the truck up the hill, avoiding obstacles and mastering the terrain. With exciting gameplay and beautiful graphics, \"Crazy Truck Online Hill Climbing Games\" is the perfect game for any truck-lover looking for a challenge.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8Y6RY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-truck/embed?sid=1","plays":39909,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71H96","slug":"i-hde","title":"I hde","description":"try to crush the characters hiding in the bins, then make the bonus level","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71H96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/i-hde/embed?sid=1","plays":39909,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"61ER2","slug":"sweet-world","title":"Sweet World","description":"Hey sweet tooth! Welcome to the world of candies! Get ready for great journey though our magic sugar land! Plenty of exciting but challenging adventures and cool prizes are waiting for you. Hurry up, start playing straightaway!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/61ER2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-world/embed?sid=1","plays":39908,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40430","slug":"micro-tank-battle","title":"Micro Tank Battle","description":"Control your tank and kill enemy tanks to get to the next level! How far can you get?","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40430/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/micro-tank-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":39908,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O9MC7","slug":"domino-block","title":"Domino Block","description":"Combine Dominoes avec le même nombres de points. Joue tous tes dominos avant tes adversaires, avec le moins de mouvements possibles. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O9MC7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/domino-block/embed?sid=1","plays":39908,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M9475","slug":"math-for-kids","title":"Math for Kids","description":"It's never too early to start your child's education.      \nPreschoolers, kindergarteners, toddlers, and older kids are eager to learn their ABCs, counting, addition, and more!      \nThe best way to encourage that is to share smart, well-made educational games with them on a daily basis.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M9475/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39908,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"501MI","slug":"bring-to-rome","title":"Bring to Rome!","description":"Is time to bring to Rome the trophy !\n\nHelp the team to stop them !","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/501MI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bring-to-rome/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4RRSO","slug":"classic-golf-solitaire-card-game","title":"Classic Golf Solitaire Card Game","description":"A classic golf solitaire card game. Try to win as many rounds of golf solitaire as you can by removing all the cards from the grid. Based on the solitaire gameplay, it will help you to keep your brain smart & sharp. Play it right now!\n\nRULES:\n\n1) Cards can be removed if they are one HIGHER or LOWER than the visible card at the bottom right (suits are irrelevant). \n\n2)Aces are both high and low.\n\n3) Jokers are wildcards: any card can be placed on top of them.\n\nEnjoy the game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4RRSO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-golf-solitaire-card-game/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6HUC3","slug":"crypto-crush","title":"Crypto Crush","description":"Crypto crush is a crypto currency themed “Candy Crush” style game with the theme of today’s major crypto currencies.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6HUC3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crypto-crush/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41I46","slug":"furious-racing","title":"Furious Racing","description":"Feel the thrill of a retro race!\nGet into a super fast car and overtake the opponents. \nClick/Tap left and right to change the lanes. ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41I46/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/furious-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"522B9","slug":"the-climbest","title":"The Climbest","description":"Ladies and gentlemen, The Climbest! \nTap 👆 to Jump and then tap again to hang \nReach the 🔝 to get your 🎁 👌\nDon't fall, it's not fun 🔥💀\nIn The Climbest, nothing is ever repeated twice - from the level structure to the background music, everything gets generated procedurally! Enjoy your climb towards the top... if you can make it!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/522B9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-climbest/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1997L","slug":"uglyvilla","title":"UglyVilla","description":"The ugly toys living in uglyvilla need to be put in the box urgently. The ugly toy green and red have to take the key and go to the box. you must help them. Help them and get them to the box. Help the ugly toys get to the box. do not forget to collect the buttons, do not do not collect. toys need buttons.\n\nHow to Play?\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys      \n*Double Jump available      \n*Mobile Touch Control","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1997L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/uglyvilla/embed?sid=1","plays":39906,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R721R","slug":"color-me","title":"Color Me","description":"This is a puzzle game with relaxing music and simple graphics. Color the tiles by clicking on the colored buttons located horizontally and vertically. The resulting drawing must match the pattern indicated at the top of the playing field. Spend time listening to pleasant music and solving various puzzles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R721R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-me/embed?sid=1","plays":39905,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"721OA","slug":"let-s-do-it-santa","title":"Let's do it Santa","description":"You’re Santa and is the night of 24th December, you need to deliver as many gifts as possible!\nThe game is really simple just touch the screen to throw the gift into the chimneys! It’s a really great cool Christmas game for all families!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/721OA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lets-do-it-santa/embed?sid=1","plays":39905,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2T56O","slug":"math-playground","title":"Math Playground","description":"Math Playground is an online educational game that helps kids learn math. It's a great way for kids to practice their math skills and have fun at the same time.\nMath Playground is an online educational game that helps kids learn math. It's a great way for kids to practice their math skills and have fun at the same time. Players can use the game to help them learn basic math concepts, including addition and subtraction, multiplication and division, and geometry. The game has a variety of challenges and activities to keep kids entertained, and it is free to play.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2T56O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-playground/embed?sid=1","plays":39905,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U1620","slug":"jump-up","title":"Jump Up","description":"Touch based Arcade hyper casual jumping game to move up and get high score.\nKeep moving left or right by landing on the platform and bounce up and this addictive jump up game.\n\nHow to Play:\n- Swipe Left/Right\n- Land on the Platform by swiping and jumping up\n- Avoid platform edges \n\nEnjoy this Endless Arcade style Hypercasual Jumping Game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U1620/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-up/embed?sid=1","plays":39905,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SKSIR","slug":"skibidi-in-the-backrooms","title":"Skibidi in the Backrooms","description":"Skibidi in the Backrooms is a game where you have to collect as many video tapes as you can without being spotted by the evil Skibidi wandering around the backrooms. Use the map to find your way, and collect all the tapes as fast as you can!","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SKSIR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-in-the-backrooms/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C1LU9","slug":"multicolor","title":"MultiColor","description":"Welcome to game, multicolor, just be careful is when the object collides with object below, click object below","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C1LU9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/multicolor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U611E","slug":"speedupdown","title":"speedupdown","description":"welcome to the game, click to change direction and be careful not to get caught","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U611E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speedupdown/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"51ROT","slug":"treecolor","title":"TreeColor","description":"Welcome to game tree color, Move the spheres to match the incoming spheres","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/51ROT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/treecolor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R71F4","slug":"francy-friend","title":"Francy Friend","description":"welcome to Francy Friend","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R71F4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/francy-friend/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZCC3R","slug":"francycrazy","title":"FrancyCrazy","description":"Welcom3e to FrancyCrazy Game","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZCC3R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/francycrazy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O8OO3","slug":"pongcolor","title":"PongColor","description":"Welcome to the Ping Color game, a classic of ping pong , but more difficult you have obstacles and colored effects that will make you lose","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O8OO3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pongcolor/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"70CCA","slug":"guess-card","title":"Guess card","description":"welcome to the game where it's easy to win you just have to guess whether the card is high or low","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/70CCA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guess-card/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1A111","slug":"para2","title":"para2","description":"You have to be quick to catch the jumping smiley and move it to the left of the screen","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1A111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/para2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z003M","slug":"3d-maze","title":"3D Maze","description":"welcome to 3d maze, have fun in this fantastic game where you will have to walk through a 3d maze","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z003M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-maze/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I9039","slug":"golf-it","title":"Golf IT","description":"Golf c'est un jeu de golf fait pour tous les amoureux de ce sport, le jeu peut être joué sur : smartphone, tablette et ordinateur. N'oubliez pas de parcourir chaque semaine car de plus en plus de niveaux seront ajoutés ! Qu'est-ce que tu attends? JOUE MAINTENANT!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I9039/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/golf-it/embed?sid=1","plays":36192,"rating":4.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S953S","slug":"super-huggie-bros","title":"Super Huggie Bros","description":"Entrez dans le monde de Super Huggie bros face aux îles mystérieuses, sautez et courez sur les obstacles, et combattez des monstres super maléfiques pour trouver son trésor à la destination finale dans un monde dangereux. Complétez tous les niveaux, collectez des pièces et détruisez chaque bloc pour trouver les clés et ouvrir les portes.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S953S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-huggie-bros/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MOW31","slug":"towmino","title":"Towmino","description":"Everyone is famous game \"Pentamino\" - in a great graphic design.\n\nA game for lovers of timeless puzzle classics.\n\nThe ability to pass levels in several ways.\nSimple game controls and exciting mechanics of finding solutions.\nSolve puzzles and watch as miniature towns and villages are built!\nOver 50+ different levels to play with different shapes!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MOW31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/towmino/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4L2T9","slug":"universe-tile-matching","title":"Universe - tile matching!","description":"Complete unique levels in \"Universe - tile matching\" \nCollect items in groups and earn points! \nGame Features:\n- Lots of levels and a variety of themes!\n- Cloud saves synchronize your progress between your devices!\n- Compete with other players on the leaderboard!\n\nClick on groups of items to complete objectives and pass levels!\nUse mouse to play from computer, and touch screen for mobile devices!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4L2T9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/universe-tile-matching/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ATTRR","slug":"skibidi-toilet-vs-cameraman","title":"Skibidi Toilet vs Cameraman","description":"Kill toilet enemies with your friend. Hunt down all the toilet enemies. Unite with your friend and only kill the monsters that belong to you. The blue cameraman can kill the blue toilet monster, so work together with your friend to kill the toilet monsters of your own color. Toilet monsters are everywhere.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ATTRR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-vs-cameraman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4YR7N","slug":"hungry-warriors","title":"Hungry Warriors","description":"Hungry Warriors is an addictive and challenging street fighting game in which you will have to defeat all the enemies in the streets in order to advance.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4YR7N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hungry-warriors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5TX98","slug":"t-rex-run","title":"T-Rex Run","description":"$5d","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5TX98/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/t-rex-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CR184","slug":"mechdinosaur","title":"MechDinosaur","description":"A hyper-casual game with a variety of dinosaur armors to choose from. Use the dinosaur armor to pass the level to your hearts content.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CR184/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mechdinosaur/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BX49S","slug":"fashion-box-glam-diva","title":"Fashion Box Glam Diva","description":"Bonnie is one of the first influencers to try the life in plastic fashion challenge, and she could use your help to nail the look. She's going to go for a glam diva look, and she needs your help to look stunning. Are you ladies ready for a one-kind dress-up game? Then let's get started with the Fashion Box: Glam Diva dress-up game for girls and see what chic look you can put together for our beautiful fashionista.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BX49S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fashion-box-glam-diva/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ETG99","slug":"gluttonous-giraffe","title":"Gluttonous Giraffe","description":"What level can you play?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ETG99/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gluttonous-giraffe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A3I6C","slug":"grimace-shake-escape-skibidi-and-cameraman","title":"Grimace Shake - Escape Skibidi and Cameraman","description":"You wake up in Doctor Grimace Shake scary hospital and remember nothing.\n\nYou should survive and escape - search for items and avoid Doctor Grimace terrifying guinea pigs - Dop Dop Skibidi Toilet in the sewer and Yes Yes Cameraman on the hospital grounds.\n\nLook for creepy items that are located in the hospital, open drawers, safes and do everything to leave this scary and unpredictable place. Grimace and Skibidi like to hide things in many different places, even in closets and small cupboards.\n\nTry not to make any noise, because otherwise any of the guinea pigs will come and knock you out, from Skibidi Toilet and Cameraman himself to the most important doctor of the whole hospital, Grimas Shake","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A3I6C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-shake-escape-skibidi-and-cameraman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1149","slug":"when-granny-met-grimace-shake","title":"When Granny Met Grimace Shake","description":"Granny must meet Grimace, help his way in this brainy puzzle adventure","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1149/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/when-granny-met-grimace-shake/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LS3L1","slug":"grimace-shake-hidden-skibidi-toilet","title":"Grimace Shake Hidden Skibidi Toilet","description":"Find skibidi toilet between Grimace Shake","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LS3L1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-shake-hidden-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"436T3","slug":"mathematical-crossword","title":"Mathematical Crossword","description":"- Math crosswords are randomly generated.\n- You can choose the difficulty and turn on or off arithmetic symbols as you wish.\n- Arcade mode is a mode in which you need to solve crossword puzzles step by step to gain ranking points. Also in this mode, after each completed crossword puzzle, the difficulty will gradually increase.\n- You can exit arcade mode at any time through the game menu and save your game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/436T3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mathematical/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C27M9","slug":"stickman-in-jail","title":"Stickman in Jail","description":"For the sake of his beloved, Stickman robbed a bank and brought the money home. The police did not have to look for the robber for a long time. Stick was found and sent to jail. His beloved sent an unusual package to prison in order to escape. You will be able to choose different options for escaping. You need to choose the right options, otherwise you will lose. A love story will show you what people are ready for for love and romance. Now it's time to make a jailbreak.\nFind all 28 bad options and one lucky option! Make your fun jailbreak!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C27M9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-in-jail/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0C0MI","slug":"triple-match","title":"Triple Match","description":"Welcome to Match-3 Fantasy 3D! Here, your task is simple yet mind-bending: merge three distinct elements into one. Each level presents a unique mental challenge.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0C0MI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/triple-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FBB99","slug":"alphabet-merge-runner","title":"Alphabet Merge Runner","description":"Evolution Merge games that you like! Monsters from all over the universe are alive! Drag and combine letter monsters in the mutant fighting simulator. Play and explore Alphabet Letras workshop and adventure games! Monsters from other universes have joined the alphabet kitchen to fight in evolution games! Play in 3D as one of your favorite characters from the collection:\n\n✨ Letters of the alphabet from A to Z. Evil A, Amazing A or C. They're all here!\n✨ A sick person. Henry Stickman is here too!\n✨ The head of the siren monster. The legend is the same as Slenderman and Rack! Choose sirenhead and smash the enemies!\n✨ Hagi-Wagi monster. Drag Hagi Wagi onto another to increase his strength.\n✨Scary train Choo Choo Charlie. Team up and fight with other mutant monster letters\n✨Monster red scary impostor with a lizard mouth\n✨Train Choo Choo Charlie. Team up and fight with other Alphabet Lord letters\n✨Blue rainbow friends with a crown on their head","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FBB99/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alphabet-merge-and-fight/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91NE4","slug":"house-design-match-3","title":"House Design Match 3","description":"Renovate a mansion house and solve challenging candy puzzles in this relaxing and romantic free explosive three in a row game!\nComplete levels to renovate all kinds of rooms and houses, including the backyard, balcony and even swimming pools!\nReconstruct the estate, decorate and expand your mansion with unique locations that are connected with history!\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\nA large number of interesting levels: many unique \"three in a row\" levels, rich elements of sweet candies and various interesting props.\n✔️ Innovative gameplay: exchange identical candies, complete different levels, complete tasks and decorate your own house.\nFollow the plot and meet new characters, life in this mansion is boiling. Discover all the secrets that these walls hold!\n✔️ Show off your repair skills and renovate the house with stunning decors!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91NE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/house-design-match-3/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OS56C","slug":"soccer-dash","title":"Soccer Dash","description":"Soccer dash is a soccer game in which you swipe a soccer ball through obstacles and soccer players and hit the ball to score a goal.\n\nYou have drag controls, drag to choose the direction of the kick, and release to hit the ball. During the dragging process, the game goes into a slow motion state, so you can take your time to choose the direction of the kick.\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\n🧠 Developing ingenuity and the right trajectory\n🎯 Unusual football full of traps\n🧩 Slow motion style game\n🤹‍♀️ Fun and creative animation","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OS56C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G7GEC","slug":"bless-magic","title":"Bless Magic","description":"Here is a classic role-playing game implemented in the Adler genre. You do not need to control the character directly, he will fight automatically. You need to pump up your hero, find various armor and items in this RPG game.\n\nThe graphics are made in retro RPG style, where all the art is made in pixel style. In this idle RPG game you are given to choose one of three heroes: a Magician, a vampire and a hunter, but you can play and pump everyone. In this RPG there are many entities for leveling: heroes, magic, armor, gems, forge, etc. \n\nYour hero in this game will fight with various monsters and bosses himself. You can also go to fight in the arena or dungeon.\nFind rare loot and equip your hero.\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\n☆ Classic role-playing game ☆\n☆ Equip your hero ☆\n☆ Various battlefields ☆\n☆ Unique items and Gems ☆\n☆ Buffs and Rating ☆","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G7GEC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bless-magic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S01AH","slug":"bubble-shooter-blast","title":"Bubble Shooter Blast","description":"In the game you can become an experienced bubble shooter. You just need to choose a ball and shoot at the right place to burst the bubbles. You have to go through more than 200 levels, so play this exciting game and start popping bubbles. Collect and shoot 3 or more bubbles to experience a sweet victory! Blow up all the balloons with your quick thinking and tactics. The next level will be harder than the previous one. Are you ready to burst all the balloons in this game?\n\nAre you ready to shoot bubbles?\n\n★ Make rows of 3 or more 3 bubbles to burst them in the right order in this shooting game.\n★ Aim carefully and tap to shoot the right bubble or a couple of bubbles to burst them!\n★ Use multiple bubbles to get the highest score and win 3 stars.\n★ Use boosters and power-ups to burst more bubbles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S01AH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-shooter-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3V69U","slug":"survival-zombie-battle","title":"Survival Zombie Battle","description":"\nZombie Battle Survival is a cool Battle Royale game with casual mechanics in the cartoon world of the zombie apocalypse.\n\nSurvive in the apocalypse city, desert, forest, farm and military base. Use a wide variety of improvised items in the battle with zombies and players! Axes, pitchforks, construction tools, pistols, grenades, chemical weapons, bulletproof vests, flight boots, fast food, first aid kits and much more! Grab whatever you want and try to survive among zombies and other hunters even offline!\n\n💣 Main features of the Zombie Battle Survival: 💣\n\n- Fast and exciting battles! Destroy all the zombies!\n- Simple game controls!\n- A huge and interesting game map! Choose a landing place and don't get caught by zombies!\n- A wide arsenal of guns, axes, pitchforks, grenades and much more!\n- Cool loot items – search and collect them on the battlefield!\n- A huge collection of maps that unlock tons of new weapons, boosters, game modes and enemies!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3V69U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survival-zombie-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D4VR4","slug":"city-driver-destroy-car","title":"City Driver Destroy Car","description":"Save up money, buy cars and destroy them in the trash!\n\nGet ready for a crazy car destruction simulator! The goal of the game is to smash your car as hard as possible! For each scratch you will receive money. They can be spent on new cars and their upgrades.\n\nFeatures:\n- 3D car racing;\n- Accidents, breakdown of cars and their breaking;\n- Unique system of destruction and deformation of the car;\n- A large selection of cars;\n- Realistic handling, like in driving simulators;\n- Jump on cars from skyscrapers and sky jumps","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D4VR4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-driver-destroy-car/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S14CI","slug":"blackriver-mystery-hidden-objects","title":"Blackriver Mystery. Hidden Objects","description":"\"Blackriver Mystery. Hidden Objects\" is a new game in which you have to try on the role of a mystical detective, the one who is destined to restore the town from the ruins and solve its mystery. Here you will find a lot of interesting quests, unique collections, popular mini-games (such as three-in-a-row, wheel of fortune and others).\n\nIt's time to solve the riddle of Black River, detective!\n\nMain features of the game:\n- the need to rebuild the city from the ruins;\n- search for items in the most beautiful locations;\n- an intriguing plot;\n- monsters;\n- fascinating puzzles and mini-games;\n- ominous anomalies;\n- search for items like a real detective;\n\nExplore locations, find the most difficult items following an interesting plot. Play three-in-a-row and use boosters. The fate of the whole city is in your hands!\n\nGood luck, Detective.","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S14CI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blackriver-mystery-hidden-objects/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"56O4B","slug":"stickman-broken-bones-io","title":"Stickman Broken Bones io","description":"Play as a Stickman, run, jump and do damage. The unique physics of ragdoll gives the game a special charm. The more damage you do, the more points and new levels you unlock! The game is designed for fans of the Stickman and Ragdoll genres.\nThe game also has a leaderboard and a shop with a system for pumping stickman and his transport. Thanks to this, you will be able to break your character more spectacularly and interestingly, as well as compete with your friends on points scored.\n\nFeatures of the game:\n- Everyone's favorite ragdoll physics\n- Spectacular limb injury system\n- Lots of levels with lots of traps\n- Character upgrade system\n- Transport store","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/56O4B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-broken-bones-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEEWS","slug":"weighted-seesaw","title":"Weighted Seesaw","description":"Weighted Seesaw is an exhilarating test of skill and adaptability. Progress through levels, immerse yourself in a world of increasing complexity, and conquer the seesaw’s delicate balance against time.\n\nA unique blend of physics-based gameplay and puzzle-solving challenges. Analyze the weights, adjust your approach, and unlock your inner puzzle-solving genius.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEEWS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/weighted-seesaw/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IA31C","slug":"monster-match-mania","title":"Monster Match Mania","description":"Embark on a monstrous adventure in Monster Match Mania!\nMatch 3 monsters of the same color to eliminate them and progress through challenging levels!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IA31C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-match-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OEE10","slug":"move-to-gram","title":"Move to Gram","description":"‘Tangram Challenge’ is an intriguing puzzle game inspired by the timeless art of tangram. Their mission is to solve each level by rotating, dragging, and dropping the tangram pieces into the correct positions to form the secret shape.\n\nWith 24 exciting levels, ‘Tangram Challenge’ offers a progressively challenging experience. Each level presents a new and complex shape, requiring players to think strategically and visualize the perfect arrangement of the tangram pieces.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OEE10/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/move-to-gram/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44AAA","slug":"tangram-swap","title":"Tangram Swap","description":"‘Tangram Swap’ is a captivating puzzle game centered around the ancient Chinese art of tangram. In this game, players are presented with a collection of beautifully crafted tangram pieces, initially shuffled and scattered across the screen. The objective is to strategically click on the pieces to swap their positions, allowing players to gradually assemble the correct shape.\n\nThe player can also rotate the pieces to unlock additional possibilities for fitting them together. By combining swapping and rotating actions, the player must skillfully manipulate the tangram pieces until they perfectly align and complete the target shape.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44AAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tangram-swap/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19119","slug":"picturecipher","title":"PictureCipher","description":"PictureCipher isn’t just a game; it’s a fusion of art, language, and skill. It’s a test of your ability to decipher imagery and language under pressure, all while racing against time. Whether you’re a word enthusiast, a visual thinker, or someone seeking a fresh twist on traditional puzzles, PictureCipher promises an immersive and intellectually stimulating adventure.\n\nDive into the captivating realm of PictureCipher today and experience the thrill of revealing hidden images one word at a time. Sharpen your mind, explore your creativity, and unlock the potential that lies within each pixel. Are you ready to embrace the challenge?","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19119/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/picturecipher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4A449","slug":"staxfall","title":"StaxFall","description":"Embark on a stacking adventure in ‘StaxFall’!\nCombine the thrill of Tetris with the challenge of physics-based stacking. Strategically position Tetris-like pieces atop an immovable base. As each piece falls, precision and quick thinking are key to building a towering masterpiece.\nHow high can you stack before the balance tips? Test your stacking skills in this addictive puzzle game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4A449/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/staxfall/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"411E4","slug":"wallbound-explorer","title":"Wallbound Explorer","description":"Embark on a captivating adventure in 'Wallbound Explorer.' Maneuver through intricate mazes, using walls to guide you. Collect coins strategically while mastering wall-bound movement. Discover and conquer challenging puzzles and become the ultimate explorer in this thrilling maze quest!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/411E4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wallbound-explorer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NLLLI","slug":"bricks-n-balls-pinball","title":"Bricks 'n' Balls Pinball","description":"Bricks 'n' Balls Pinball is an exciting and innovative fusion of classic pinball and the addictive gameplay of Breakout. Players embark on a thrilling adventure where they control a pinball paddler to smash through vibrant brick formations.\nAs the pinball bounces off the paddler, it collides with the colorful bricks. Each level presents new challenges with unique brick layouts, enhancing the pinball's abilities and adding strategic depth.\nWith its intuitive controls and captivating gameplay, \"Bricks 'n' Balls Pinball\" promises fun for casual and avid gamers alike.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NLLLI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bricks-n-balls-pinball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2A423","slug":"gravity-dunk","title":"Gravity Dunk","description":"Gravity Dunk is an exhilarating physics-based basketball game where player control a bouncing basketball on an infinite journey.\nThe challenge lies in avoiding deadly spikes scattered throughout the endless course that could pop the ball and end the game.\nTest your skills, timing, and reflexes in this fast-paced arcade-style adventure and see how many hoops you can score before meeting a thorny demise.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2A423/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gravity-dunk/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0118D","slug":"decipher","title":"Decipher","description":"Welcome to the exciting and challenging world of “Decipher,” a game that will test your ability to decode symbols and form words within an 1:30. Prepare for a unique puzzle experience where your mental agility and powers of observation will be put to the test as you venture through increasingly complex challenges.\n\nThe objective of “Decipher” is simple. The game is divided into two layouts: the first field will display a series of symbols, each associated with a specific letter. In the second field, you’ll find only symbols, with no apparent letters. Your challenge is to use your visual memory and knowledge of letter associations to input the correct letters and form valid words.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0118D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/decipher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"666II","slug":"mc8bit","title":"MC8Bit","description":"Are you ready for an 8-bit gaming adventure? In this 8-bit game, youll need to guide Alex and Steve to the finish line in Minecraft. Leave the house and be cautious of monsters in the spooky forest. Your pickaxe is of no use here, so dont rely on it. Defeat the monsters in the forest. Collect all the obsidian stones. If you dont collect the obsidian stones, the portal wont form. Without the portal, you cant progress to the next level.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/666II/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mc8bit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9N4OT","slug":"kingdom-of-toilets","title":"Kingdom of Toilets","description":"You need to help the toilet robots escape from this underground prison filled with obstacles. You must assist them in escaping. Be careful as there are toxic waters everywhere underground. You must collect all the gold coins, or else the portal wont activate. Collect all the gold coins to activate the portal.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  \n*double jump available  ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9N4OT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kingdom-of-toilets/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1H203","slug":"steve-hardcore","title":"Steve Hardcore","description":"Are you ready for Steves exciting adventure? There are green monsters everywhere, and you need to collect all the obsidian pieces. Gather all the pieces and reach the opened black hole. Go through the black hole and reach the portal in the cave. You must reach the portal safely. Remember, youre in hardcore mode. You have three chances to die. If you die more than three times, all levels will be deleted, and youll start from scratch.\n\n**Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1H203/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-hardcore/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4KRS1","slug":"fishing-clicker","title":"Fishing Clicker","description":"Fishing Clicker is another clicker / Idle game with the peculiarity of being completable!\n\nSee what happens to Mr. D when you click all the way through the ending of the game, and watch the unfortanate epilogue of our main character!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4KRS1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fishing-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6CG65","slug":"grimace-vs-giant-clown-shoes","title":"Grimace vs Giant Clown Shoes","description":"Help grimace escape from the giant clown shoe. Collect the coins with Grimaces image on them to break the platforms and the hamburgers to push the giant shoe away. Watch out for the small shoes! If you get hit, youll slow down.\n\nCONTROLS\n\nTouch or click on the left or right side of the screen.\nCursors left and right on the keyboard","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6CG65/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-vs-giant-clown-shoes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M9M3M","slug":"madness-combat-fangame","title":"Madness Combat Fangame","description":"Madness Combat Fangame is a game inspired by the famous animations and games series Madness Combat!\nFight against hordes of Grunts, kill all the Sheriff Clones with all the weapons you can find and leave the complex before Tricky the Clown comes and get you!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M9M3M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/madness-combat-fangame/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8808B","slug":"skibidi-toilet","title":"Skibidi Toilet","description":"Help Skibidi Toilet to collect all the purple Orbs!\nSquash the Goo's as you roll, climb, bounce, and zoom around devilishly designed levels.\nA challenge awaits anyone hard enough to squash some Goos!\nThis physics-based puzzle game is hours of enjoyment for the whole family!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8808B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OI6ST","slug":"dont-drop-the-skibidi","title":"Dont Drop The Skibidi","description":"Dont let Skibidi and Grimace fall!\nAnd pop all the balloons that you see on the screen!\nTap with your finger or click with your mouse on the screen to popo the balloons and touch/click the Skibidi/Grimace to prevent it from falling down.\nYou need to play and sign a good record to unlock the Grimace!\nEnjoy this supercool game!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OI6ST/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-drop-the-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G6E96","slug":"complete-the-missing-numbers","title":"Complete The Missing Numbers","description":"Drag the numbers to complete the missing wagons and help the train to continue its journey, a game with fun and education.","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G6E96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/complete-the-missing-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7LALT","slug":"what-letter-is-it","title":"What Letter is It?","description":"A fun game to learn and exercise your knowledge with the letters of the alphabet.\n2 game modes for you to play just to learn or teach, and another mode for you to try.\nTo make the most hits in 90 seconds. A perfect game to learn and teach.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7LALT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-letter-is-it/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6K116","slug":"dead-aim-skibidi-toilets-attack","title":"Dead Aim Skibidi Toilets Attack","description":"Dead Aim: Skibidi Toilets Attack is a shooting game where you play as special forces soldier on a city streets invaded by skibidi toilets and your mission is to shoot them all in order to survive and unlock 10 types of weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6K116/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dead-aim-skibidi-toilets-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2A992","slug":"3d-mania","title":"3D-Mania","description":"welcome to 3d mania , Can you catch the marble without being hit by the marble that kills you?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2A992/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/3d-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7198E","slug":"spacefly","title":"spacefly","description":"Welcome to the Spacefly game, in this game you have to catch as many stars as they turn, but you have to be careful of the missiles and other enemies who try in every way to blow you up","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7198E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spacefly/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6M968","slug":"tommy","title":"Tommy","description":"Welcome to Tommy, enjoy this amazing game where you have to jump forward and hide in blocks just like a mole to survive and hope the obstacles, will you be up to the challenge? What are you waiting for? Go play Tommy now and have fun!!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6M968/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tommy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96893","slug":"crafty","title":"crafty","description":"crafty game,,, you crafty ??","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96893/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crafty/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U39FO","slug":"watch-out-for-the-roof","title":"watch out for the roof","description":"Welcome to watch out for the roof have fun in this game by facing difficulties and accumulating your score, what are you waiting for?? go and play watch out for the roof now and the fun will be guaranteed!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U39FO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/watch-out-for-the-roof/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IR092","slug":"little-sailor-chibi-moon-puzzle-quest","title":"Little Sailor Chibi Moon Puzzle quest","description":"Welcome to Little Sailor Chibi Moon Puzzle quest, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Little Sailor Chibi Moon Puzzle quest, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Little Sailor Chibi Moon Puzzle quest and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IR092/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-sailor-chibi-moon-puzzle-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"85S6Z","slug":"anya-jigsaw-puzzle-frenzy","title":"Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy","description":"Welcome to Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy! Our Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy picture. With a wide variety of Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Anya Jigsaw Puzzle Frenzy Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/85S6Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anya-jigsaw-puzzle-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6C6CA","slug":"princess-memory-match","title":"Princess Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Princess Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Princess Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Princess Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6C6CA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W73AJ","slug":"crayon-jigsaw-jam","title":"Crayon Jigsaw Jam","description":"Welcome to Crayon Jigsaw Jam! Our Crayon Jigsaw Jam Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Crayon Jigsaw Jam picture. With a wide variety of Crayon Jigsaw Jam images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Crayon Jigsaw Jam Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W73AJ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crayon-jigsaw-jam/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"68A69","slug":"queen-elizabeth-i-memory-match","title":"Queen Elizabeth I Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Queen Elizabeth I Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Queen Elizabeth I Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Queen Elizabeth I Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/68A69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/queen-elizabeth-i-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"76825","slug":"mites","title":"Mites","description":"Welcome to the mite game, you have to be smart to kill them all, have fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/76825/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mites/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AEI4I","slug":"minigolf-archipelago","title":"Minigolf Archipelago","description":"Bienvenue dans le monde incroyable de « Minigolf Archipelago » ! Préparez-vous à relever des défis passionnants au minigolf sur plusieurs îles. Explorez des îles pittoresques et surmontez les obstacles tout en perfectionnant vos compétences. Profitez de commandes intuitives, de graphismes époustouflants et d'un gameplay engageant. Préparez-vous pour une partie de minigolf amusante avec des défis uniques dans \"Minigolf Archipelago\" ! Êtes-vous prêt à devenir le maître de l’archipel ?","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AEI4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minigolf-archipelago/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7760G","slug":"soccer-ping-io","title":"Soccer Ping .IO","description":"$5e","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7760G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ping-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ST6O9","slug":"save-the-alphabet-lore","title":"Save the Alphabet lore","description":"In the game, you will make a path between letters by clicking on pins and connecting small letters with their corresponding large letters. But be careful, on your way to save the alphabet you will face various obstacles such as the evil letter F, bomb and lava. Become the savior of the alphabet.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ST6O9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-alphabet-lore/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S600Z","slug":"puzzle-of-betty-jones","title":"Puzzle of Betty & Jones","description":"Puzzles of Betty and Jones. Use the touch or arrow keys to move the tile and recompose the image.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S600Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-of-bettyandjones/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"170G5","slug":"grimace-drop","title":"Grimace Drop","description":"Help Grimace to escape from prison!!!\nGrimace Drop is a 60 levels of fun physics puzzle game! all boxes except the grass must be removed where the prison is standing.\nSimply click or tap on the boxes or blocks to destroy them.\nCarefully use the set blocks in what ever way you can to get the Grimace Drop safely into the grass.\n\nSolve this fun physics game and help Grimace to escape from prison!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/170G5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"INIE9","slug":"fishing-simulator-online","title":"Fishing Simulator Online","description":"Bienvenue dans le monde passionnant de Fishing Online, un jeu de pêche en ligne unique en son genre ! Embarquez pour un voyage passionnant à travers des rivières, des lacs et des océans pittoresques, où plus de 250 espèces de poissons vous attendent. Ce ne sont pas seulement des poissons ordinaires qui vous attendent, mais aussi des rencontres passionnantes avec des monstres des profondeurs !\n\nDes tâches passionnantes, des lieux magnifiques et de nombreuses espèces de poissons vous attendent, ainsi que différents équipements de pêche pour améliorer vos compétences et attraper les plus gros poissons !\n\nNe manquez pas l'occasion de devenir un vrai professionnel de la pêche et de vous hisser au sommet du classement. Nos trésors et nos succès vous attendent !\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu :\n- De nombreux types d'équipements de pêche.\n- Plus de 250 espèces de poissons.\n- 15 lieux étonnants.\n- Encyclopédie de toutes les espèces de poissons.\n- Système d'accomplissement.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/INIE9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fishing-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C411C","slug":"checkers-3d-international","title":"Checkers 3D International","description":"Checkers 3D online with many modes.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C411C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/checkers-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GR14U","slug":"boing-bang-adventure-lite","title":"Boing Bang Adventure Lite","description":"Boing Bang Adventure is a 2D arcade game in the style of the classic arcade game \"Pang\"\n\nFight against a horde of bouncing alien and save BoingBang Land from their vicious attack!\nDefeat the enemies using your blast gun, and remember to use all the powerful power-ups you can find on the battlefield.\n\nYou can even stop the time, to shoot without worrying about the enemie's counter attack!\n\nAnd finally, if you think you cannot face a menace that big, you can always ask for the help of a friend and play the game in local co-op!\n\nSo what are you waiting for? Destroy the bouncing alien and save your land!\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GR14U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boing-bang-adventure-lite/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8K225","slug":"sudoku-challenge","title":"Sudoku Challenge","description":"Défi Sudoku : Exercez votre esprit avec le jeu de puzzle classique, Sudoku. Aiguisez votre logique et vos compétences en réflexion critique en remplissant la grille de chiffres. Pouvez-vous résoudre le défi et devenir un maître du Sudoku ?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8K225/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sudoku/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L5OEL","slug":"kotoklan-fluffy-epic-idle","title":"Kotoklan Fluffy Epic Idle","description":"In the \"Kotoklan: Fluffy Epic\" you will have an exciting adventure where you will become a virtual millionaire, thanks to your loyal cats. You need to buy cats, and these cute furry creatures will start bringing you money. Each of your cats is a source of additional profit, and your task is to collect the largest amount of gold.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L5OEL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kotoklan-fluffy-epic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7E49M","slug":"number-puzzle","title":"Number Puzzle","description":"Défi de Fusion de Nombres : Préparez-vous à une expérience stimulante pour l'esprit ! Fusionnez et combinez stratégiquement des nombres pour atteindre l'objectif ultime. Résolvez des casse-tête complexes, débloquez de nouveaux niveaux et mettez à l'épreuve vos compétences en matière de calcul. Pouvez-vous fusionner votre chemin vers le sommet ?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7E49M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/number-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5AA8E","slug":"idle-medieval-village","title":"Idle Medieval Village","description":"Create a medieval community. Build a prosperous village by starting with a little income, increasing it by upgrading existing inhabitants, and hiring new ones.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5AA8E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-medieval-village/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7SY7","slug":"dr-psycho-hospital-escape","title":"Dr. Psycho - Hospital Escape","description":"Dr. Psycho: Hospital Escape is a thrilling horror escape game where you are trapped in a nightmare clinic and need to get out of there. \n\nGather essential items to unlock doors and escape the clutches of the deranged Doctor Psycho and his psychotic patients. Time is ticking, you only have 3 days to break free. Navigate terrifying space and uncover multiple escape routes while avoiding detection. \n\nHide in cleverly hidden places and explore the place carefully avoiding deadly traps. Can you outwit the doctor and secure your asylum escape?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7SY7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dr-psycho-hospital-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8XN9A","slug":"extreme-stunt-car-game","title":"Extreme Stunt Car Game","description":"Get ready for most exciting impossible and challenging Extreme Stunt Car Games.\n\nPlay like a car stunt master while riding on the tricky tracks. Accept the challenge of car stunt games and choose your favorite vehicle to enjoy the driving challenges in car stunt races.\n\nThis Extreme car stunt game having amazing Game play and challenging levels which is not an easy job for any stunt car driver. Now it’s time To perform crazy stunts, tighten your seat belt and enjoy loads of different cars while climb up the massive heights but try not fall down on the city otherwise you will lose.\n\nKey Features of Extreme Stunt Car Game : Car Driving games\nRealistic car physics and driving controls.\nAddictive and fast paced game play.\nRealistic HD graphics.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8XN9A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/extreme-stunt-car-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5594E","slug":"swipe-rush","title":"Swipe Rush","description":"Swipe your way to victory in the addictive endless runner Swipe Rush! Tap and swipe to guide your character as he sprints past sawblades, wrecking balls, and other treacherous obstacles.\nDash through numbered blocks to gain helpful allies and defeat your enemies.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5594E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swipe-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6REM3","slug":"stickman-doodle-epic-rage","title":"Stickman Doodle Epic Rage","description":"Stickman Doodle Epic Rage is fun and addictive beatemup game with realistic physics and hardcore gameplay. With simple controls you can perform amazing stunts and blows to defeat your opponents.\nUnknown enemies emerge in the city! Our Stick hero continues to fight them off with a wide array of deadly weapons as well as helicopters and robots, who can devastate all enemies at once!\nThe followers of Stickman games still have not forgotten the feeling of tight guillotine and ecstatic graphics of Stickman Brawl of Rage. And what would you expect in a recent version of Stickman fight and this revenge? Whether this revenge will end or not?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6REM3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-doodle-epic-rage/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11O25","slug":"nooby-and-obby-2-player","title":"Nooby And Obby 2 Player","description":"Are you ready for the mind-boggling parkour adventure of two inept siblings? Its extremely funny and they are totally unskilled. They are referred to as the newbie brothers. One is nooby, the other is obby, and both are equally unskilled. Help them navigate through the courses. Assist them in completing the courses using their skills without touching the red blocks, and ensure they finish the course.\n\n*Noob Player: Use WASD to move and Space to jump.\n*Noob Baby Player: Use Arrow Keys to move and P to jump.\n*Mobile Control Available ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11O25/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/nooby-and-obby-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E69T2","slug":"gunnercraft","title":"GunnerCraft","description":"Its time to fire your weapon, Steve. Fire your gun and start jumping. You can jump by shooting and go wherever you want. Draw your bow and shoot the arrow. You must collect all the boxes. Collect the boxes and kill all the invisible monsters. You cant see them until you collect the boxes. So, collect the boxes first and then hunt down all the monsters!\n\nClick to shoot! or tap with your finger!    \nWherever you shoot, you move in the opposite direction.    \nmove according to the tab of the gun!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E69T2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gunnercraft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OA121","slug":"duoland","title":"Duoland","description":"Two siblings are on their way to becoming little pirates, and you should join the adventure too. The little pirates are searching for chests and collecting treasures in my name. Each sibling is looking for different gems and chests on the island, so they must sequentially find the chests that belong to them. The first rule of being a pirate is to collect everything on the island, including all the coins. After collecting everything, a hidden pirate ship will suddenly appear in the top right corner of the island. Get on that ship and escape from the island.\n\n*Players use \\\\WASD\\\\ AND \\\\Arrow key\\\\ keys to move.\n *Mobile gameplay, mobile touch control is available.\n*Open all the chests, collect all the diamonds, and gather all the gold! Run to the ship.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OA121/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duoland/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Q69D1","slug":"aqua-dogy","title":"Aqua Dogy","description":"Would you like to join the adventure of the dog siblings having fun at the water park? This adventure is just for you. Slide down the slides with the dogs and collect all the badges. Gather all the badges and head straight to the finish line. Slide down the slide with your friend and reach the finish line together.\n\n*Collect all the badges, activate the Black Hole. \n*Playable on both desktop and mobile. \n*Jump by pressing the W key and the Arrow up key.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Q69D1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aqua-dogy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O8KN9","slug":"only-up-parkour","title":"Only Up Parkour","description":"Only Up! is an exciting arcade game in which you have to overcome obstacles and conquer heights. Inspired by the popular game Your task is to guide the character through a vertical labyrinth full of various obstacles. You must react quickly, jump accurately and climb up dexterously to avoid crashing into obstacles and falling down. As you progress through the various levels, you will encounter increasing difficulty and new challenges such as moving platforms and rotating obstacles.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O8KN9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/only-up-parkour/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B5O31","slug":"flappy-bob","title":"Flappy Bob","description":"This a fun and fast-paced arcade game, where you guide a bird and prevent hitting some spikes. The game is easy to pick up and play.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B5O31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-bob/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L1A69","slug":"flap-a-bird-3d","title":"Flap A Bird 3D","description":"If someone made Flying Bird Which Support RTX then I made Flying Bird which does not support RTX but looks Beautiful and it is in 3D.\n\nThis is a game in which you control a bird who is trying to fly and avoid the pipes if bird hits the pipes then it will die now you have to save the bird from dying just tap on the screen to fly.\n\nOk Bye","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L1A69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flap-a-bird-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1PPY9","slug":"pixel-protect-your-planet","title":"Pixel Protect Your Planet","description":"Protect your planet and defend from invaders and destroy all androids for reach the best score in this arcade game.\n\nMobile:\nTouch left screen for rotate in left\nTouch right screen for rotate in right\n\nDesktop:\nA key = move left \nD key = move right ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1PPY9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-protect-your-planet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CKE28","slug":"grimace-shake-coloring","title":"Grimace Shake Coloring","description":"Ce jeu est un jeu de coloriage intéressant et spécial sur Grimace Shake. Toutes les images incluent des sentiments à son sujet. Les joueurs peuvent utiliser différentes couleurs pour dessiner les images, mais vous pouvez également utiliser le stylo magique pour leur redonner son aspect original. J'espère que vous pourrez vous amuser !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CKE28/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-shake-coloring/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D42K7","slug":"skibidi-drop","title":"Skibidi Drop","description":"Help Skibidi Toilet to escape from prison!!!\nSkibidi Drop is a 60 levels of fun physics puzzle game! all boxes except the grass must be removed where the prison is standing.\nSimply click or tap on the boxes or blocks to destroy them.\nCarefully use the set blocks in what ever way you can to get the Skibidi Toilet safely into the grass.\n\nSolve this fun physics game and help Skibidi to escape from prison!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D42K7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T0CES","slug":"barbies-sketch","title":"Barbies Sketch","description":"Experience the fun and challenges of sketchboarding with Barbie. Here, Barbie is the main character of the game, where she sketches to reach her destination. Stay aware of the new environment and different obstacles, and help Barbie avoid all the obstacles on her way.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T0CES/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbies-sketch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G818E","slug":"flying-grimace","title":"Flying Grimace","description":"Flying Grimace is a fun shooting game for all. To play this game, you need to be great at aiming. The game is set in colorful environments, and your aim is to destroy as many Grimaces as possible. Remember, you have limited bullets. Flying Grimace will surely test your aiming skills and keep you engaged for hours. This game is perfect for fans of arcade shooting games and anyone who loves a good challenge.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G818E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-grimace/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EG2KV","slug":"speakerman-revenge","title":"Speakerman Revenge","description":"Spekerman Revenge is a single-player game where the player controls a Spekerman laser gun to shoot down boxes. The Spekerman can move left and right to avoid the boxes, a box that appears randomly on the screen. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EG2KV/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spekerman-revenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6O667","slug":"skibidi-dungeon-of-doom","title":"Skibidi Dungeon Of Doom","description":"Skibidi Dungeon Of Doom  is an epic adventure through 100 levels of monsters, traps and danger.\nHave you got the brains and fast reflexes to escape all 100 dungeons in this unique action puzzle game.\nBats will chase you, Ghosts will try and trick you, Monsters around every corner, Hazards include Spikes, Guillotines, Poison gas and more...\nHave you got what it takes?\nProduct feature bullets:\n- Skibidi On Board!\n- 100 epic levels!\n- Cute graphic!\n- Cool Skibidi music!\n- Really addictive! \n- Easy to play!\nEnjoy with this great Puzzle Adventure game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6O667/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-dungeon-of-doom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8BIKE","slug":"grimace-and-skibidi-whack-a-mole","title":"Grimace And Skibidi Whack A Mole","description":"This is a fun game for You, your friends and your family!\nYour objective is to hit all the popping Grimaces to get points the more you can!\nDo you like \"Whack A Mole\"? then you will love this game too!\nEnjoy it!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8BIKE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-and-skibidi-whack-a-mole/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0B61R","slug":"grimace-vs-skibidi","title":"Grimace Vs Skibidi","description":"Grimace vs Skibidi is an action-based defense game.\nThe Grimace is in deep trouble and has to defend the shakes from the dangerous Skibidi Aliens.\nHelp him to move fast and throw the snow balls and avoid them reaching the shakes; If they reach the eggs you lose the game!","category":"Sport","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0B61R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-vs-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G4K84","slug":"rolling-skibidi","title":"Rolling Skibidi","description":"An unsuspecting Skibidi drank too much and ended up in a wheel...\nHelp him before its too late!\n\nTake control of your Skibidi and ride the barrel down the mountain.\nWatch out for the boulders, trees and wildlife!\n\nKey Features:\n- Addictive one touch game play that is easy to pick up but difficult to master!\n- Its a Skibidi running on a giant barrel down a mountain! What more do you want!\n- Highly addictive","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G4K84/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rolling-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G0G09","slug":"grimace-commando","title":"Grimace Commando","description":"Defend the world to the Grimace invasion!\nUse your mini machine gun to destroy all Grimace Inavders!\nThis game is a classic endless trend arcade game when you need to resist the more you can and sign the best record!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G0G09/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-commando/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EGEBL","slug":"grimace-ball-juggling","title":"Grimace Ball Juggling","description":"Help Grimace to not let the ball fall!\nHow many times you can juggle these two soccer balls?\nHow to play:\n- Tap left side of screen to kick the left football\n- Tap right side of screen to kick the right football\nWarning: This game create dependence! :-)","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EGEBL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-ball-juggling/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EREE","slug":"grimace-tennis","title":"Grimace Tennis","description":"Like in a great tennis game, Help Grimace to stopping the tennis balls! but requires speed and precision, make one mistake and you’re out! its may be simple to play but it’s a challenge to get high scores! The longer You stay on ground, the faster the tennis balls will come at you and it is your job to return them while also avoiding flying bottles. Youre warned! the Platinum medal is VERY hard to complete! only if youre a true grand slam may catch it!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EREE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-tennis/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"53941","slug":"swing-grimace","title":"Swing Grimace","description":"Help Grimace to jump side to side and try to avoid the spikes!\nThats all you need to do but try to resist the more you can!\nTry to sign you best personal record in the leaderboard!\nHappy Birthday Grimace!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/53941/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swing-grimace/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I51P1","slug":"skibidi-hop","title":"Skibidi Hop","description":"It's just a really simple endless hyper casual game!\nHelp Skibidi and try to avoid the Red triangle when you run; is simple: you just make a jump! but you run in a planet so you need to resist the more you can and sign the best record possible!\nThis game i suitable for every one, enjoy it!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I51P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-hop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3M6V3","slug":"grimace-invasion","title":"Grimace Invasion","description":"The goal is to resist the more you can and after you can sign your personal record in the local leaderboard!\nShoot all the Grimace aliens as fast as you can and survive much time and achieve high scores.\nUse your machine gun weapon to destroy all Grimace!\nThe goal is to resist the more you can and after you can sign your personal record in the local leaderboard.\nHave fun with this great funny endless game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3M6V3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9U9K3","slug":"skibidi-toilet-platform-jump","title":"Skibidi Toilet Platform Jump","description":"Skibidi Toilet: Platform Jump Game is a challenging and fun game where you control a toilet that must jump and avoid obstacles to reach the end of the level. The game features a variety of levels, each with its own unique challenges. Youll need to use your skills and reflexes to navigate the levels and avoid falling off the platforms.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9U9K3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-platform-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7K5E6","slug":"the-elevator-clicker","title":"The Elevator Clicker","description":"Murphy's Law: The Elevator is a particular kind of clicker game where you can actually complete the game and watch the ending.\nHelp Mr D. to take the elevator and go back home from work.\nYou can buy many upgrades to strengthen your finger and press the button faster!\nWill Mr. D. be able to take the elevator? You are the only who can help him!\n\nTouch click or press any key to call the Elevator","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7K5E6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-elevator-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5NG8O","slug":"pandjong","title":"Pandjong","description":"You need to go through all 80 levels to free all 80 pandas.  Use jokers and bonuses to simplify the process. In addition to the usual jokers in the game there are jokers for each suit. If you click on the pandas, you will get some points and a strike bonus.\nYou have to draw cards one at a time from your stockpile. Select the cards that are one higher or one lower in value to your drawn card to remove it from the playing field. To complete a level you need to remove all the cards from the playing field withou","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5NG8O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pandjong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8S07E","slug":"solitaire-seasons","title":"Solitaire Seasons","description":"You need to go through all 40 levels to open all four windows, each of which goes into its own season. Use jokers to simplify the process. In addition to the usual jokers in the game there are jokers for each suit.\nYou have to draw cards one at a time from your stockpile. Select the cards that are one higher or one lower in value to your drawn card to remove it from the playing field. To complete a level you need to remove all the cards from the playing field withou","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8S07E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-seasons/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R1K97","slug":"brick-together","title":"Brick Together","description":"Control the yellow block to push single colored blocks. Blocks of the same color stick to blocks of the same color when adjacent. If you push a block belonging to a group of the same color, the group is destroyed, except for the block you pushed. Only one block of each color should be left on each level.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R1K97/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brick-together/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0API8","slug":"spaces-solitaire","title":"Spaces Solitaire","description":"The full pack of cards is dealt to the card table, into four rows of cards. Each row has a single space. Your task is to rearrange the cards so they form a correctly ascending sequence of cards, one suit in each row. The catch, you can only move cards into the empty spaces if the card to the left of the empty space is of the same suit and of lower face value.\nUse spaces to arrange all cards in suit and in sequence from 2 to King. You can move a card to a space or empty spot if it is the same color and 1 higher in value than the card to the left of the space.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0API8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaces-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L0L41","slug":"wild-west-freecell","title":"Wild West Freecell","description":"On the tableau can you build down on alternating color. You can use the Freecells (top left) to temporarily park a card. Collect the pistol action cards for a bonus action to move any card on a tableau to the first position in a column. You always start with one or more bonusactions you can use immediately.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L0L41/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-west-freecell/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A86I4","slug":"pride-mahjong","title":"Pride Mahjong","description":"You have to find three identical tiles with food to destroy them. The tiles are placed on a special form where 7 tiles can be placed at the same time. The game also has three types of bonuses that can be used to make the game easier.\n\nMatch three of the same tiles. Click on a tile to move it to the collection spots at the bottom. If you have collected three of the same tiles there, they will be removed.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A86I4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pride-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MA2FE","slug":"street-cafe-mahjong","title":"Street Cafe Mahjong","description":"You have to find three identical tiles with food to destroy them. The tiles are placed on a special form where 7 tiles can be placed at the same time. The game also has three types of bonuses that can be used to make the game easier.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MA2FE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/street-cafe-mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E866T","slug":"summer-aesthetics","title":"Summer Aesthetics","description":"Hop on a plane and spend your summer vacation traveling around the world together with your favorite Disney princesses. Discover beautiful sceneries and practice your fashion advisor skills while helping them choose their outfits of the day in the Summer Aesthetics Dress Up Game for girls! Have a blast!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E866T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/summer-aesthetics/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A440","slug":"xmasjong","title":"Xmasjong","description":"Find a couple of identical tiles to remove them from the playing field. If you collect all the tiles underneath, you will find one item that will automatically be placed on or under the Christmas tree.\nMake Mahjong matches  complete all the levels, collect all the toys and dress up the Christmas tree!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A440/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/xmasjong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AMLG7","slug":"grimace-penalty","title":"Grimace Penalty","description":"The Grimace Penalty Goal Game is a fun and challenging game where you have to attempt to score a penalty goal against a Grimace. To score a goal, you need to time your shot carefully and aim for the right spot in the goal. The Grimace will move around, so you need to be quick and accurate if you want to succeed. If you miss three goal, the game will be over. ","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AMLG7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-penalty/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LM11A","slug":"casual-pinball-game","title":"Casual Pinball Game","description":"Casual Pinball Game is a fast-paced and addictively fun game that combines the classic game of pinball with modern game design elements. In this game, players are challenged to score as many points as possible by using a set of flippers to keep a metal ball bouncing around a playing field filled with obstacles and targets.\n\nThe game features simple and intuitive controls that allow players to quickly get into the action, with Left-touch and Right-touch controls used to activate the flippers and launch the ball. The playing field is designed to be visually appealing and filled with vibrant colors, lights, and animations that add to the excitement of the game.\n\nHyper casual pinball is a game that is easy to pick up and play, but difficult to master, providing endless hours of entertainment for players of all ages and skill levels.","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LM11A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/casual-pinball-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"18BUL","slug":"duo-ball-adventure","title":"Duo Ball Adventure","description":"the adventure of two balls that cannot be separated from one another makes the movement of the ball difficult to control. Help the two balls to get to their destination, control the ball and pass all the obstacles","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/18BUL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-ball-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MMAT1","slug":"skivl-tycoon-farm-magnat","title":"Skivl Tycoon Farm Magnat","description":"Bienvenue dans «Skivl Tycoon: Farm Magnat»! Vous avez atterri sur une planète inhabitée où vous devrez construire votre ferme! Engagez des assistants pour réparer rapidement votre vaisseau spatial et explorer d'autres planètes!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MMAT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skivl-tycoon-farm-magnat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"43134","slug":"obstacle-racing","title":"Obstacle Racing","description":"Obstacle Racing is an exciting game that will put your skills to the test! Your mission is to overcome obstacles and earn money as you race endlessly through different themes. With five awesome themes to choose from, each with its own unique look and feel, you'll never get bored. Use the money you earn to unlock themes and expand your racing experience. Can you conquer all the obstacles and become the ultimate champion? Jump, dodge, and race your way to victory in \"Obstacle Racing\"","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/43134/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/obstacle-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NAR00","slug":"poligon-dash-geometry","title":"Poligon Dash - Geometry","description":"poligon scoot is a very simple but challenging game and every level is full of entertainment, you have to pass through the obstacles and get to the finish line.\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NAR00/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poligon-dash-geometry/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E4EG1","slug":"among-spider-at-easter","title":"AMONG SPIDER AT EASTER","description":"Play online or over local WiFi with 4-10 players as you attempt to prep your spaceship for departure, but beware as one will be an impostor bent on killing everyone!\n\nCrewmates can win by completing all tasks or discovering and voting the impostor off the ship.\n\nThe Impostor can use sabotage to cause chaos, making for easier kills and better alibis.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E4EG1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/among-spider-at-easter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"09043","slug":"feed-me","title":"Feed me!","description":"Assemble sandwiches to feed your friends. The better the sandwich, the more coins you'll get!\n\nThe game features:\n— The largest variety of ingridients for the most creative sandwiches!\n— You can get unique gloves skins by completing fascinating quests!\n— A record chart! Compete with other players for the highest sandwich!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/09043/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/feed-me/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KKR1C","slug":"skibidi-toilet-soccer","title":"Skibidi Toilet Soccer","description":"Skibidi is a great goalkeeper in soccer training!\nUse your finger to slide goalkeeper to the kicked penalty.\nAs a super goalkeeper you must protect your goal from as much incoming balls as you can.\nHow to Play:\n- The computer will shoot soccers\n- Just swipe the screen to control Skibidi\n\nEnjoy your soccer game! Become a Skibidi Soccer Goalkeeper Superstar!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KKR1C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-soccer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5LBN7","slug":"flight-pinball-machine-2-evolution","title":"Flight Pinball Machine 2 Evolution","description":"The game consists of 6 levels. The first 5 levels you have to compose the flying objects. At level 6 you can play endlessly.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5LBN7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flight-pinball-machine-2-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OH0EO","slug":"hit-cans-and-bottles","title":"HIT Cans and Bottles","description":"HIT Cans and Bottles. This game consists of: Cans, Cups, Bottles, Pot and Spoons. 17 levels. You have to hit and collect the items to go to the next levels.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OH0EO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hit-cans-and-bottles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4300E","slug":"esther-the-penguin-learn-to-swim","title":"Esther the penguin. Learn to swim.","description":"Esther the penguin. Learn to swim. This game is the second part of Esther's return to Antarctica. \nEsther can't swim and you have to help her learn to swim. You have to avoid icebergs and sea predators.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4300E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/esther-the-penguin-learn-to-swim/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1DPUR","slug":"study-group","title":"Study Group","description":"Welcome to Study group, have fun immersing yourself in two crazy levels in a platformer with enemies to escape the maze, can you escape ??? What are you waiting for??? go now to play Study group and the fun will be guaranteed !!!!!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1DPUR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/study-group/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AR6UE","slug":"super-huggie-adventure","title":"Super Huggie Adventure","description":"Plongez dans le monde d'aventures de Super Huggie en affrontant les îles mystérieuses, sautez et courez par-dessus les obstacles, et combattez les super méchants monstres pour trouver son trésor à la destination finale dans un monde dangereux. Terminez tous les niveaux, collectez des pièces et détruisez chaque bloc pour trouver les clés et ouvrir les portes.\n\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AR6UE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-huggie-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"621N1","slug":"boca-moca-freelancer","title":"Boca Moca Freelancer","description":"Have you ever earned money by working from home? Now is the perfect time. Earn money by working from home, protect your computer from viruses, and add to your income by doing the right coding. But remember, youre a sweet girl and you might get hungry and change your hairstyle. You can also bring in items for your home. Everything is in your hands.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/621N1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boca-moca-freelancer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R66RI","slug":"truck-simulator-skibidi-toilet","title":"Truck Simulator Skibidi Toilet","description":"Before you start your multi-million dollar logistics company, you will first have to complete quick jobs using provided trucks. You will have to earn at least before buying your first truck.\nAs the player completes jobs and levels up, they will unlock skills. Skills can be used to upgrade fuel efficiency and long distance cargoes as well as unlocking hazardous, fragile, and important deliveries.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R66RI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/truck-simulator-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RA10X","slug":"mix-and-kick-monsters","title":"Mix and kick monsters","description":"Ever wanted to create your own monster? Now you have such an opportunity! Mix the body parts of various monsters, and then destroy these monsters with a variety of weapons to create a new monster later!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RA10X/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mix-and-kick-monsters/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19T8D","slug":"pose-to-hide-puzzle","title":"Pose To Hide. Puzzle","description":"The goal of the game is to place people in a certain frame.\nEach character in this game has their own unique set of poses. Try to figure out the correct pose and find the correct place for the character in the frame.\nA fun puzzle game to train mindfulness and have fun.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19T8D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pose-to-hide-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ISMR5","slug":"skibidi-smasher","title":"Skibidi Smasher","description":"Skibidi Toilet Smasher is an exciting alien-killing game where you have to defend your area without getting infected!\nKill as many Skibidi Toilet and they will become faster on further waves, so boost your reflexes and kill the fast-paced game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ISMR5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-smasher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SP8P1","slug":"huggie-and-banzai","title":"Huggie and Banzai","description":"Ne manquez pas le jeu Huggie & Banzai si vous êtes fan des jeux classiques ! Cette édition de la série mettant en vedette le plombier le plus aimé au monde apporte quelque chose de nouveau. Êtes-vous prêt à vivre les aventures de Huggie sous un nouvel angle ?\n\nNe vous inquiétez pas ! Vous ne manquerez aucune des fonctionnalités amusantes qui rendent Huggie si génial. Il y aura toujours plein de plateformes, d'obstacles mobiles, de pièces et d'ennemis menaçants ! Êtes-vous prêt à les affronter ?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SP8P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sponge-piano/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1R678","slug":"bird-sort","title":"Bird Sort","description":"Your main goal is to collect birds of the same color on the tree branch. Once you place all birds of the same color on one branch, they will fly away.\nWith soothing music and peaceful birds singing, you will have a great time. Bird sorting is a great puzzle game to relax and train your mind.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1R678/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bird-sort/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19DD9","slug":"mad-dash","title":"Mad Dash","description":"$5f","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19DD9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mad-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I10D1","slug":"skibidi-laser-kill","title":"Skibidi Laser Kill","description":"Skibidi Laser Kill Game is a fast-paced, action-packed laser shooter arcade game. Players take control of a laser-wielding character and must defend themselves against waves of oncoming enemies. The game features a variety of enemies, each with their own unique attacks. Players must use their skills and reflexes to dodge enemy fire and take them down. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I10D1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-laser-kill/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TTOR0","slug":"tiktok-floral-trends","title":"TikTok Floral Trends","description":"In our next game, you will discover another summer trend that is inspired by the beautiful colors of the summer. The game stars Kiki, an amazing artist, who shares her unicorn-themed makeup look that was inspired by the magical world of the unicorns. It continues with Olivia's passion for red and glitzy accessories, and it ends with you dealing with Regina's makeup look. Play today and have a lot of fun being a makeup artist! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TTOR0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiktok-floral-trends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TAER8","slug":"tripeaks-solitaire-100-levels","title":"Tripeaks Solitaire 100 levels","description":"Play Classic TriPeaks or 100 different Tripeaks levels. Remove all cards from the tableau, you can remove top cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value than the open card on the bottom. Click on the closed stack to get a new open card.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TAER8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tripeaks-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":39887,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8IALS","slug":"pyramid-solitaire-classic","title":"Pyramid Solitaire Classic","description":" Remove all cards from the pyramid by combining two cards to a total value of 13. The numerical cards are worth the face value, the A is 1 point, the J is 11 points, the Q is 12 points and the K is 13 points. The King can be removed as a single card. You can use the cards in the Draw pile to get a new face-up card.\n\nRemove all cards by pairing cards to a value of 13. An A=1, J=11 and Q=12 points. A K=13 points and can be removed as single card.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8IALS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pyramid-solitaire-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54SGS","slug":"agent-t-action-shooter","title":"Agent T Action Shooter","description":"Stylish, deadly and smooth as a billiard ball, Johnny Trigger is a man on a mission in this non-stop platform shooter game where the action never ends. Do you have what it takes to bring down the underground world of the mafia? “Less talk, more bullets” – that’s Johnny’s motto as he runs, jumps, spins, slides and keeps on shooting till every bad guy’s bitten the dust.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54SGS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/agent-t-action-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"STEDI","slug":"granny-kill-skibidi-toilet-behind","title":"Granny Kill Skibidi Toilet Behind","description":"Granny must kill all skibidi toilet from behind!\nDont let them find you!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/STEDI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/granny-kill-skibidi-toilet-behind/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OW311","slug":"grimace-wood-cutter","title":"Grimace Wood Cutter","description":"In this game you need to chop wood and avoid the branches.\nIt could be an easy task? Its easy to play but hard to master!\nSo help Grimace as every lumberjack does and chop the tree as fast the more you can!\n· One-touch control system!\n· Simple and addictive gameplay!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OW311/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-wood-cutter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1944C","slug":"coco-skibidi","title":"Coco Skibidi","description":"Coco Skibidi is a game of rhythm, hand-eye coordination and hair-pulling action!\nWith the fate of two Skibidi Toilet at your finger tips, it's up to you to keep them from getting coconuts!\nKey Features:\n- Great Gameplay.\n- Cute Graphic.\n- Simple Gameplay.\n- One click/touch to play.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1944C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coco-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KTOTL","slug":"skibidi-toilet-basket","title":"Skibidi Toilet Basket","description":"$60","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KTOTL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-basket/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K0636","slug":"skibidi-toilet-stick","title":"Skibidi Toilet Stick","description":"Stretch the stick the more you can to reach and walk on the platforms. Beware! If the stick is not long enough, you will fall down!\nGet yourself in the ninja action!\nHow far can you go? ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K0636/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-stick/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3DOOS","slug":"skibidi-toilet-invasion","title":"Skibidi Toilet Invasion","description":"The goal is to resist the more you can and after you can sign your personal record in the local leaderboard!\nShoot the Skibidi Toilet aliens as fast as you can and survive much time and achieve high scores.\nUse your machine gun weapon to destroy all Skibidi!\nThe goal is to resist the more you can and after you can sign your personal record in the local leaderboard.\nHave fun with this great funny endless game!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3DOOS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2BD5U","slug":"double-guns-2d-hit","title":"Double Guns 2d Hit","description":"Bien sûr! \"Double Gun Game\" est un terme anglais qui pourrait être traduit en français de différentes manières en fonction du contexte. Voici quelques traductions possibles :\n\n\"Double Gun Game\" peut être traduit par \"Jeu de Double Pistolet\" : Cela pourrait faire référence à un type de jeu vidéo ou de jeu de société où les joueurs utilisent deux pistolets (armes à feu) simultanément pour affronter leurs adversaires.\n\n\"Double Gun Game\" peut également être traduit par \"Jeu de Double Fusil\" : Cela pourrait se rapporter à une activité sportive ou de loisirs où les participants utilisent deux fusils pour le tir ou la chasse.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2BD5U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/double-guns-2d-hit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C2A2D","slug":"hiding-banana-cat","title":"Hiding Banana Cat","description":"The goal of the game is to move the glasses on the grid so that the Banana Cat can stay open as long as possible. It will move around the grid randomly, so you will need to react quickly and move the glass so that it does not close.\n\nMove the glasses like in the classic 11-element puzzle where you have to move only one element at a time. But you should take into account that the Banana Cat can move in any direction and at any time, so you need to react quickly and move the glasses.\n\nThe game “Hiding Cat Banana” offers an exciting gameplay that requires a quick reaction and the ability to analyze the situation on the go. Try your hand at this exciting game!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C2A2D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hiding-banana-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3N2II","slug":"line-join","title":"Line Join","description":"remplir tous les cubes avec une seule ligne, peut revenir en arrière pour la correction aussi","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3N2II/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-join/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"195LE","slug":"the-tiles-flow","title":"The Tiles flow","description":"The tiles flow is an endless runner game where tiles keeps flowing from top to bottom and player needs to keep destroying the yellow ones.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/195LE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-tiles-flow/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE10S","slug":"impostor-sort-puzzle-pro","title":"Impostor Sort Puzzle Pro","description":"\"Plongez dans le défi intrigant d'Impostor Sort Puzzle ! Ce jeu hyper décontracté mettra à l'épreuve vos compétences en résolution d'énigmes en démêlant des modèles complexes et en triant le vrai du faux. Plongez-vous dans un monde d'imposteurs rusés et d'énigmes captivantes qui garderont votre esprit vif et diverti. Pouvez-vous déchiffrer les indices, exposer les imposteurs et résoudre chaque énigme ? Jouez maintenant et prouvez vos prouesses de tri dans Impostor Sort Puzzle !\"","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE10S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/impostor-sort-puzzle-pro/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22462","slug":"crazy-pong-2","title":"Crazy Pong 2","description":"Prevent the ball from leaving the round, obtain the best score and purchase new skins in this addictive game.\n\nInstructions:\n-Touch in left for move in left and right in right","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22462/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-pong-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AXCAM","slug":"galactic-pixel-storm","title":"Galactic Pixel Storm","description":"Embark on an exciting cosmic adventure in \"Galactic Pixel Storm\"! Immerse yourself in a world of captivating pixel art graphics and mesmerizing sound effects. Pilot your spacecraft through a realm of pixel art targets, smashing them with rockets in a symphony of explosive brilliance. Your mission is to meticulously obliterate each pixel art piece, shattering them into a mesmerizing dance of one or two pixels. As a player, you'll enjoy the thrill of upgrading your spacecraft, selecting from three unique ship types, and harnessing a variety of game-changing power-ups.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AXCAM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galactic-pixel-storm/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IANX6","slug":"penguin-exit-path","title":"Penguin Exit Path","description":"Penguin Exit Path is a platform penguin game.  The objective of the game is to arrive on the other side of the mountain alive.\nControl the penguin to perform and avoid from all traps in his way.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IANX6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-exit-path/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S4A9A","slug":"survivalpixel-io","title":"SurvivalPixel.io","description":"We need you in a popular survival game. Help the Warrior survive and assist them in battling tougher monsters at each level. Be cautious, as monsters are coming from everywhere and you need to stay alive. Grab your sword, and eliminate all the monsters. The monsters you defeat will grant you health and power. Keep getting stronger and defeat the boss monsters.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S4A9A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survivalpixel-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I4L7F","slug":"freelancersim","title":"FreelancerSim","description":"Have you ever wanted to work from home and earn money? Yes, today we are freelancing and earning money by working from home. We can earn money by typing the required words or by detonating viruses on computers. We can buy things for our home or feed ourselves with the money we earn. If you go hungry and die, everything starts from scratch.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I4L7F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/freelancersim/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VOO0O","slug":"above-shooter","title":"Above Shooter","description":"Kill all the zombies and set new records!\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VOO0O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/above-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RT3O6","slug":"shoot-arrows","title":"Shoot Arrows","description":"shoot arrows is game arcade 2024 ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RT3O6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shoot-arrows/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2SVSU","slug":"summer-festivals-fashion","title":"Summer Festivals Fashion","description":"This summer, festivals are back in trend, and you will have a blast attending 3 famous parties in our dress-up game for girls called Summer Festivals Fashion. Get it started, and have a great time creating jaw-dropping #ootd for these 6 BFFs getting ready to dance, dance, dance while looking in style. Have a blast!\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2SVSU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/summer-festivals-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3HG8","slug":"super-hexbee-merger","title":"Super Hexbee Merger","description":"Hexbee - un jeu de puzzle unique ultra accrocheur !\nLes règles sont très simples : Associer les trois hexagones (vert, bleu et rose) sur la grille pour collecter le plus de points possible !\n\nMode de jeu :\nFaites bouger l'ensemble d'hexagones du bas vers la grille et reliez-le avec d'autres hexagones de la même couleur. Atteignez la cible pour débloquer l'hexagone spécial \"fusion\".\n\nLorsque l'espace disponible sur la grille est complet, la partie est terminée. Adoptez la bonne technique. Placer les hexagones dans la bonne position est la clé pour devenir maître ! N'attendez plus et essayez ! Bonne chance !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3HG8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-hexbee-merger/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23S93","slug":"last-world","title":"Last World","description":"A 2D platform game is a type of video game where the main character navigates through a two-dimensional environment while avoiding obstacles and enemies. In this specific game, the main player is a young boy who is on a mission to escape the spell of witches and skeletons. There are 10 episodes in total, each one presenting new challenges and obstacles for the player to overcome.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23S93/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/last-world/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NO71E","slug":"injection-invasion","title":"Injection Invasion","description":"Ive got a fear of injections! In this game, Injection Invasion, The little boy has a very big fear of injections. He has been running and jumping around to avoid the injection. The game has a very simple concept, but it’s fun to play. Help the little boy avoid the injection. You can use the mouse or the keyboard key arrows to play the game. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NO71E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/injection-invasion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6CTE0","slug":"match-mystery","title":"Match Mystery","description":"Match Mystery is a match-3 puzzle game. It has an endless level of a twist challenging game. It has  stunning graphics, fantastic gameplay and an impressive storyline. Match Mystery is a  hours of fun and brain-teasing game for all ages! ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6CTE0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-mystery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O64SI","slug":"goal-skibidi-goal","title":"Goal Skibidi Goal","description":"Goal Skibidi Goal is a fast-paced, physics-based soccer game where you control a little character with your head. The goal is to score more goals than your opponent by heading the ball into their net. You can jump, duck, and slide to control the ball, and you can also use power-ups to give yourself an edge.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O64SI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goal-skibidi-goal/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A8T7A","slug":"learn-the-alphabet","title":"Learn The Alphabet","description":"A fun game for children to learn letters and words, perfect for those just starting to learn to read or learn English.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A8T7A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/learn-the-alphabet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8IR5N","slug":"write-the-missing-letter","title":"Write The Missing Letter","description":"A fun game where you exercise children’s knowledge with words and letters.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8IR5N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/write-the-missing-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IF8O0","slug":"what-is-my-food","title":"What Is My Food","description":"A fun game in which the player must decide which food is preferred by each animal.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IF8O0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-is-my-food/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"89IA4","slug":"skibidi-toilet-moto-bike-racing-2","title":"Skibidi Toilet Moto Bike Racing 2","description":"Skibidi Toilet Moto Bike Racing 2 with a cool bike racing Skibidi Toilet. \nThis sequel is harder than previous game. Toilet vehicle based game with racing modifications for drag bike lovers. In this game, there are several types of toilet that you can play to ride the reckless Skibidi Toilet.\nDriving a drag toilet racing vehicle is a thrilling experience that is hard to forget. With the Skibidi Toilet Moto Bike Racing game, you will get a large collection of drag toilet racer. Games that you can download for free that have an additional collection of drag bikes make playing the game exciting. ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/89IA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-moto-bike-racing-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SB88I","slug":"minecraft-skibidi-hidden-toilet","title":"Minecraft Skibidi Hidden Toilet","description":"Minecraft Skibidi Hidden Toilet is a wonderful online game with hidden objects. Find out the hidden toilets in the specified images. Each level has 10 hidden keys. There are 10 levels in total. The time is limited so be fast and find all hidden objects before time runs out. Clicking in the wrong place several times reduces the time by an additional 5 seconds. So, if you are ready start the game and have fun! ","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SB88I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/minecraft-skibidi-hidden-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8IN81","slug":"drift-racing-gear-simulator","title":"Drift Racing Gear Simulator","description":"Get ready to drive high performance cars (turbo or naturally aspirated) and make them drift at high speed in tracks designed specifically for drift racing.\nImprove your racing and drifting skills and earn virtual money to tune and customize your car.\nRace to battle the world record of the leaderboard or just for fun in the freeride mode.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8IN81/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drift-racing-gear-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TLYOT","slug":"only-up-skibidi-toilet","title":"Only UP Skibidi Toilet","description":"Going up as far as possible, as sikibidi toilet jump around to be the top","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TLYOT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/only-up-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G22IK","slug":"skibidi-toilet-ball-juggling","title":"Skibidi Toilet Ball Juggling","description":"Help Skibidi Toilet to not let the ball fall!\nHow many times you can juggle these two soccer balls? \nHow to play:\n- Tap left side of screen to kick the left football\n- Tap right side of screen to kick the right football \nWarning: This game create dependence :)","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G22IK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-ball-juggling/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I3II1","slug":"skibidi-run-fast-run","title":"Skibidi Run Fast Run","description":"Skibidi Run Fast Run is a fun adventure game to play on!\nHere is Skibidi Toilet who has been stuck in middle with a whole lot of traps, help him to dodge them.\nThere are really fast-paced obstacles passing by, keep away from them and survive as long as you can.\nThis game will boost your reflexes while the hardest objects moving on him.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I3II1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-run-fast-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1I519","slug":"skibidi-retro-fps","title":"Skibidi Retro FPS","description":"$61","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1I519/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-fps/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"31Z8D","slug":"zombie-world","title":"Zombie World","description":"In a future world, where zombie apocalypse is upon us, and you are the last survivor fighting alone with just one gun. Come on for the victory of mankind,how long can you hold on? Come and challenge yourself now!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/31Z8D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-world/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1L54D","slug":"skibidi-toilet-math-challenge","title":"Skibidi Toilet Math challenge","description":"Skibidi Toilet Math Challenge test you to answer the math quickly before time run out!\nBeware Skibidi Toilet will haunt you if the time run out or you make a mistake!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1L54D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-math-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MEAI1","slug":"geo-metric-run","title":"Geo-Metric Run","description":" Geometric Game is a fast-paced arcade game where players maneuver through a dynamic obstacle course, collecting coins while striving to cover maximum distance. ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MEAI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometric-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PKO64","slug":"shoots-skibidi-dop-dop-yes-yes","title":"Shoots Skibidi Dop Dop Yes Yes","description":"Shoots Skibidi Dop Dop Yes Yes Tap Down is the most addictive shooting game. With its simple yet challenging gameplay, you'll be hooked from the first time you play. Tap down to shoot the enemies as they come at you from all sides. Use your powerups to take down the bosses and progress to the next level. There are endless hours of fun to be had with Shoots Skibidi Dop Dop Yes Yes Tap Down.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PKO64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shoots-skibidi-dop-dop-yes-yes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9SES9","slug":"heads-up-skibidi","title":"Heads Up Skibidi","description":"Heads Up Skibidi is a Head ball game where one player is the skibidi head and poo picker. The skibidi head wears a blindfold and tries to head the ball into the poo picker's mouth. The poo picker tries to dodge the ball and pick up as much poo as possible.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9SES9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heads-up-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TB6ST","slug":"skibidi-toilet-tennis","title":"Skibidi Toilet Tennis","description":"In this great arcade sports game may be simple to play but it’s a challenge to get high scores!\nLike in a great tennis game, Help Skibidi Toilet to stopping the tennis balls! but requires speed and precision, make one mistake and you’re out!\nThe longer You stay on ground, the faster the tennis balls will come at you and it is your job to return them while also avoiding flying bottles.\nYou're warned! the Platinum medal is VERY hard to complete! only if you're a true grand slam may catch it!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TB6ST/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-tennis/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"97E6T","slug":"skibidi-toilet-shooting","title":"Skibidi Toilet Shooting","description":"Skibidi Toilet Shooting is an action packed shooting game set in blocky world where you play as american soldier and your mission is to shoot given amount of skibidi toilets in order to successfully complete each level and unlock new types of weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/97E6T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-shooting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A6DR2","slug":"road-madness","title":"Road Madness","description":"Si vous aimez les voitures de course et les armes à feu, vous allez adorer ce jeu ! Vous pouvez améliorer et débloquer des voitures plus destructrices, plus vous avancez. Profitez d'effets épiques et de bonus tout en chassant les nouveaux boss et obtenez des succès pour cela !\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A6DR2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/road-madness/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0A6R2","slug":"rodha","title":"Rodha","description":"$62","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0A6R2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rodha/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69CKI","slug":"virus-clicker","title":"Virus Clicker","description":"Use new viruses as you click. Unlock all viruses enjoy them all","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69CKI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/virus-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RURRS","slug":"stickman-counter-terror-strike","title":"Stickman Counter Terror Strike","description":"Stickman Counterterror Strike Frappe contre la terreur de Swat Stickman\n\nStickman première personne tireur avec où le Stickman Terror doit tirer sur le Stickman Terror et leur causer un coup fatal.\n\n\n- tu peux jouer sans Internet\n- tireur avec contrôle commode\n- jeu de style \"tireurs à partir de 1 personne\".\n- Stickman 3D et niveaux\n- Tir anti-terroriste avec Stikman\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RURRS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-counter-terror-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7TY1H","slug":"huggy-wuggy-run-from-skibidi-toilet","title":"Huggy Wuggy Run From Skibidi Toilet","description":"Huggy Wuggy and Killy Willy fight Skibidi Toilet in the city.\nGrab all rifle that cameramen has placed around, and avoid skibidi toilet","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7TY1H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/huggy-wuggy-run-from-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TEI6O","slug":"epic-skibidi-toilet-clash","title":"Epic Skibidi Toilet Clash","description":"Epic Skibidi Toilet Clash part 1 is the first story of galactic superhero to fight skibidi toilet in space. This war is so epic and no one can match this skibidi toilet epic war!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TEI6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/epic-skibidi-toilet-clash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OL2II","slug":"noob-goes-to-skibidi-toilet-school","title":"Noob Goes To Skibidi Toilet School","description":"Noob Goes To Skibidi Toilet School  is a fight simulator, where you have to fight all skibidi toilet in your school.\nMost fun to fight with your enemies. You finally find out who is steeper in all the school fights without rules.\nPlease enjoy high school life in Japan.\nAddicting and interactive battle game\nApply your strategy to win the great high school battle\nBe ready to meet furious Skibidi toilet\nFEATURED:\n-8 exciting levels\n-tons of noob skin to change after mission\n-Cool fighting mission each level","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OL2II/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-goes-to-skibidi-toilet-school/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1R9G","slug":"horror-grimace-burn-or-die","title":"Horror Grimace Burn or Die","description":"An epic battle between you and Grimace, burn or be killed!\n\nNo more Grimace Terror. It's time to put him into eternal flame of death.\n\nYou have your guts, you have the will. This is too much! Grimace Must DIE!\n\nLock and load! Revenge is MY NAME!\n\nKill or be killed!\n\nIf you like survival horror game you gonna love this!\n\nYou came to investigate strange happenings at the abandoned Cave.\n\nThere are rumors that Grimace is behind them.\n\nTry getting out alive!\n\nGood Luck!\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1R9G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horror-grimace-burn-or-die/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CESAR","slug":"grimace-shake-draw-and-erase","title":"Grimace Shake Draw and Erase","description":"Help Grimace to collect a recipe for a shake! Draw a path around obstacles or erase them with an eraser. Fascinating puzzles and creative solutions are waiting for you in \"Grimace Shake: Draw and Erase\".","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CESAR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grimace-shake-draw-and-erase/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TI42B","slug":"swing-skibidi-toilet","title":"Swing Skibidi Toilet","description":"Help Skibidi Toilet to jump side to side and try to avoid the spikes! That's all you need to do but try to resist the more you can! try to sign you best personal record in the leaderboard!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TI42B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/swing-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6S2E3","slug":"skibidi-toilet-vs-camer-man","title":"Skibidi Toilet vs Camer Man","description":"Skibidi Toilet vs Camera Man A shooting game is a fun and challenging game that is perfect for players of all ages. It is a great game to play with friends or family, and it is sure to provide hours of entertainment. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6S2E3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-vs-camer-man/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LBK2J","slug":"skibidi-triple-jump","title":"Skibidi Triple Jump","description":"Skibidi Triple Jump Game, a single-touch jumping reaction game, has everything you need to make your next app store hit!\nUse your skills and agility to survive by jumping over obstacles and avoid getting hit.\nJust tap the screen and makeup to three jumps before touching the ground again.\nAvoid the dangerous obstacles or your Skibidi character will explode and the game will be over!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LBK2J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-triple-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L966T","slug":"goal-quest","title":"Goal Quest","description":"Experience the fusion of sports and puzzle-solving in this captivating 2D soccer ball game. Break through cube stone obstacles by simply touching them, clearing your path to the goal. But it’s not just about scoring; you must also collect three stars scattered throughout each level to unlock new challenges. Navigate intricate mazes, utilize physics, and explore visually stunning environments as you strive to become the ultimate soccer ball champion. Are you ready for an adventure filled with excitement, discovery, and a touch of soccer magic?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L966T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goal-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1II8T","slug":"skibidi-toilet-adventure","title":"Skibidi Toilet Adventure","description":"Skibidi Toilet Adventure is a fun and challenging platformer game that is perfect for fans of the Skibidi Toilet meme. Its a great game for players of all ages, and its sure to provide hours of entertainment.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1II8T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MMZT1","slug":"battle-simulator-stickman-zombie","title":"Battle Simulator Stickman Zombie","description":"Simulator Stickman bataille contre les zombies! Battez l'apocalypse!\n\nPuis vint une autre apocalypse zombie dans le monde stickman! (Oui, beaucoup d'entre eux: P)\nDans stickman Simulator: Zombies bataille épique vous persévérez stickman caractère: nous devons sauver le monde de l'invasion de zombies. Le sort du héros vous attend!\n\n• Beaucoup de meurtre et de sang!\n• Entièrement 3D - bâton stickman et le champ de bataille\n• style de jeu Tubs!\n\nMusique:Portrait MetalRenard_This moiré\nSons: freesound.org","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MMZT1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-simulator-zombie-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TONE","slug":"obunga-nextbot-spot-difference","title":"Obunga Nextbot Spot Difference","description":"Find all obunga and other nextbot character, in this different game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TONE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/obunga-nextbot-spot-difference/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TU6C","slug":"you-cannot-beat-this-game-mate","title":"You cannot beat this game mate","description":"You cannot beat this game mate is an ongoing project that i am working on use the arrow keys to move","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TU6C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/you-cannot-beat-this-game-mate/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DTOA1","slug":"modern-paintings-gallery-of-art","title":"Modern Paintings. Gallery of Art","description":"Make the most of your time with a purposeful experience! Immerse yourself in the captivating aura of modern art, treasured by art enthusiasts worldwide. Embark on an extraordinary 3D journey through grand halls adorned with masterpieces created by the greatest contemporary artists such as Takashi Murakami, Cecily Brown, Anish Kapoor, Mikel Barcelo, and numerous others.\n\nTour exhibition is constantly evolving and growing, ensuring there's always something new to discover.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DTOA1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/modern-paintings-gallery-of-art/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H1H97","slug":"the-dungeon","title":"The Dungeon","description":"Dodge the HOT FIREBALLS and collect the GOLD COIN much as you can!!! use different heroes...why? All heroes need gold for his adventure! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H1H97/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-dungeon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TC726","slug":"chaotic-loop","title":"Chaotic Loop","description":"Try to get the gold medal in this platform game, also every level has something different!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TC726/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chaotic-loop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2NZI3","slug":"line-join-puzzle","title":"Line Join Puzzle","description":"In this free-to-play puzzle game, you merely have to draw one line. It is deceptively simple, yet profoundly deep.\nPlay through the extensive stages, sharpening your wits as you have fun.\n\nFEATURES\n• NO WIFI? NO PROBLEM! Enjoy line puzzle anytime, anywhere!\n• NO penalties or time limits; You can enjoy it!\n• TONS OF UNIQUE LEVELS\n- Full of fun and amazing challenges!\n• STUNNING GRAPHICS\n- Soothing sounds and gorgeous visual effects\n• OPTIMIZED ANDROID & GOOGLE PLAY GAMES\n- Designed for tablets & phones.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2NZI3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-join-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PRA6P","slug":"favorite-puzzles","title":"Favorite Puzzles","description":"Découvrez Favorite Puzzles, vos nouveaux puzzles préférés ! Ce jeu de puzzle addictif vous ravira avec une galerie infinie de belles images pour tous les goûts ! Favorite Puzzles sera intéressant pour les enfants et les adultes, dans ce jeu, vous pouvez régler la difficulté et diviser l'image de 6 à 600 éléments ! Pour rendre les puzzles encore plus agréables et plus faciles, vous pouvez toujours obtenir un indice, inclure un exemple et afficher la grille ! Vous aimez la complexité ? Activez ensuite le mode Réaliste et résolvez des puzzles à partir de pièces éparpillées sur le terrain ! Et vous pouvez également créer un puzzle à partir de votre propre image ou photo !\n\nCaractéristiques de jeu:\n\n🧩 Difficulté de 6 à 600 éléments avec et sans rotation\n🧩 48 catégories d'images et recherche de base d'images VIP\n🧩 Créez des puzzles à partir de vos photos\n🧩 Modes de jeu classiques et réalistes\n🧩 Interface personnalisable et couleur de fond\n🧩 Classement et réalisations","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PRA6P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/favorite-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7C6TM","slug":"maze-black-and-withe","title":"Maze Black And Withe","description":"Pass all the 10 levels in this challenge game and your objective is collect all the objects for unlock the next door and avoid all the walls for pass the other levels\n\nInstructions:\n\nCollide for the walls You Lose\n\nMovement Desktop:\nW/Up Arrow = Up\nA/Left Arrow= Left\nD/Right Arrow = Right\nS/Left Arrow = Down\n\nMovement Mobile:\nGamePad for controll the movement\n\nFeatures :\n-10 Levels for unlock\n- Challenge game for avoid all the walls or you lose","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7C6TM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/maze-black-and-withe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5A7CA","slug":"endless-car-race","title":"Endless Car Race","description":"Prove to the world that you are the most skilled driver! \nTry to last as much as you can while driving your car between all kind of obstacles!! \nThe road is going to be full of dirty oil puddles that will hurt your car if you let them; and pay attention to the road limit, you don't wanna find yourself in the grass!\nPlay using the mouse or the touchscreen if you're on your phone :)","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5A7CA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/endless-car-race/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06TR9","slug":"wordscraft","title":"WordsCraft","description":"A mix of word puzzles and resource gathering. Collect resources to gain abilities and level up.\n\n-Swipe words for extra upgrades!\n\n-Find as many words as you can, and manage your resources to maximize your output.\n\n-Blast missiles to destroy crates and get even more upgrades!\n\nCan you craft all the words?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06TR9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wordscraft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"671L9","slug":"doodle-run-3d","title":"Doodle Run 3D","description":"$63","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/671L9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doodle-run-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3DO5L","slug":"color-crowd","title":"Color Crowd","description":"$64","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3DO5L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-crowd/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A0P54","slug":"tap-em-fast","title":"Tap Em Fast","description":"Appuyez sur la boucle au bon moment pour gagner contre vos amis et montrer vos réflexes","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A0P54/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tap-em-fast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96II6","slug":"hill-car-climb-mountain-hill-racing","title":"Hill Car Climb Mountain Hill Racing","description":"$65","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96II6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hill-car-climb-mountain-hill-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E010C","slug":"spaceface","title":"SpaceFace","description":"¡Dispara a los asteroides y naves enemigas para ganar mejoras y derrotar al jefe final!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E010C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaceface/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NT668","slug":"synth-racer","title":"Synth Racer","description":"Race at speed through a synth wave city and collect as many coins as possible for a high score. Don't crash into obstacles otherwise you might crash your car!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NT668/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/synth-racer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O1EE1","slug":"dino-offline-game","title":"Dino Offline Game","description":"Dinosaur Game est un jeu de course sans fin intégré à l'origine dans Google Chrome.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O1EE1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dino-offline-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GS5A1","slug":"ai-soccer-training","title":"AI Soccer Training","description":"Train to become a skilled football goalkeeper or striker, and join an extraordinary team of AI players! Whether you choose to focus on goalkeeper training or sharpen your skills as a striker, you will be part of a team alongside AI partners. Brace yourself as AI players challenge your team's abilities on the field!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GS5A1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ai-soccer-training/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D6DEJ","slug":"crocodile-jigsaw-perfect-slide-puzzle","title":"Crocodile Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Crocodile Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle! Our Crocodile Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Crocodile Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle picture. 