 So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IMMOO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kid-jumping-on-trampoline/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IG3IO","slug":"kaligrafi-photo-image-scramble","title":"Kaligrafi Photo Image Scramble","description":"Welcome to Kaligrafi Photo Image Scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Kaligrafi Photo Image Scramble, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Kaligrafi Photo Image Scramble and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IG3IO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kaligrafi-photo-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ISE0F","slug":"easy-perfect-fit-jigsaw","title":"Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw! Our Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw picture. With a wide variety of Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Easy Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ISE0F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/easy-perfect-fit-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rati