s are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Zombies Slider Image Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0E40O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombies-slider-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P7CIS","slug":"cute-anime-face-girls-coloring-pages","title":"Cute Anime Face Girls Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Cute Anime Face Girls Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Cute Anime Face Girls Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Cute Anime Face Girls Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Cute Anime Face Girls Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P7CIS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-anime-face-girls-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2SS1T","slug":"granny-street-rage-skibidi-toilet","title":"Granny Street Rage Skibidi Toilet","description":"A brave cameramen and granny fight all skibidi toilet in the city!\nSo violent and cool at same time!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2SS1T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/granny-street-rage-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"620IR","slug":"egg-clicker","title":"Egg Clicker","description":"Egg clicker, a clicker game based on eggs. Gain eggs, buy upgrades, unlock achievements and game mechanics and become the master of eggs! How many of them will you collect?","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/620IR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/egg-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HTLCH","slug":"help-the-cat","title":"Help The Cat","description":"An exciting game in which you have to go through many interesting and difficult levels and help the cat. A game for those who like to solve logic problems and intricate puzzles.\nIn the game, you need to remove the necessary flaps with the help of a touch so that the cat can safely reach his favorite toy.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HTLCH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/help-the-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2KIC0","slug":"punch-skibidi-toilets","title":"Punch Skibidi Toilets","description":"Be the champ and knock down as many tree as possible with your Head super Skibidi toilet!\nPlay this adrenaline rush game with lots of intensity.\nBe specific with your timing as you need to punch the tree in the exact time to smash it so you can create a way to run as far as you can.\nAchieve high scores are play lot more running games only with Mapi Games!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2KIC0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/punch-skibidi-toliets/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8606C","slug":"kick-virus","title":"Kick Virus","description":"let's kick virus","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8606C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kick-virus/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OSK1T","slug":"granny-skibidi-toilet-escape-horror","title":"Granny & Skibidi toilet Escape Horror","description":"Night Skibidi Toilet Simulator plays your role for a man named CameraHead\n\nSkibidi Night Toilet Simulator takes place in an old house, you yourself have to get all the clues by visiting all the rooms one by one, observe them for coins.\n\nNight Skibidi Toilet Simulator plays your role for a man named CameraHead. You come to the underworld environment which is placed next to a scary haunted warehouse.\n\nTake them all and escape, but your quest is not easy, because the Skibidi Toilet wants to haunt you.\n\nEnjoy playing Night Skibidi Toilet Simulator horror game.\n\nHave you ever faced Skibidi Toilet, otherwise let's escape Skibidi Toilet chase in nextbots game.\n\nSkibidi Toilet is very angry and trying to chase you, What will you do in escape game? Are you able to make an escape. Let's see if you can escape from the scary chase","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OSK1T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/granny-and-skibidi-toilet-escape-horror/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NERSL","slug":"skibidi-toilet-five-difference","title":"Skibidi Toilet Five Difference","description":"Find all difference for skibidi toilet depicted in the picture within time limit.\nFind the differences between the two pictures! Focus on the different details, improve your powers of observation, and enjoy this free spot the difference game!\nExplore more than 40 different free pictures and have fun while you try to spot the hidden differences between them. Challenge your mind with find the difference games!\nTest your detection and concentration skills to see if you can spot the difference in two seemingly identical images before the timer runs out. Enjoy playing find the difference games!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NERSL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-five-difference/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BO1L4","slug":"ww1-battle-simulator","title":"WW1 Battle Simulator","description":"simulateur de la bataille de la Première Guerre mondiale\nEpic World War I a commencé!\nPour atteindre la victoire, vous aurez besoin de stratégie et de tactique - c'est un simulateur de combat!\n\n.. il n'y a plus de tranchée - il y a des tanks, des mitraillettes et un sniper!\nLa guerre doit être gagnée! Nous n'oublierons pas le premier monde ...\n\nSons: freesound.org\nMusic_Geoplex_Drift","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BO1L4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ww1-battle-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8LEY7","slug":"stickman-neon-motorcycle-racing","title":"Stickman Neon Motorcycle Racing","description":"Moto Racing 3D dans le monde Stickman Neon Warriors\n\nSalut Stickman Biker! La course sur votre moto va bientôt commencer: préparez votre vélo, collectez les bonus et vite jusqu'au bout!\nLe monde des néons est d’autant plus dangereux. En tant que motard, vous devriez éviter les guerriers laser et le trafic pour prouver que vous êtes le meilleur coureur de stickman néon!\n\n\n- Circulation avec tir\n- Motos 3D et stickman néon\n- course libre sur moto néon!\n- Vous pouvez jouer hors ligne (sans internet) !!\n\nMusique: F-777_This_Isnt_Rocket_Science","category":"Course","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8LEY7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-neon-motorcycle-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LTRTT","slug":"counter-terror-battle-simulator","title":"Counter Terror Battle Simulator","description":"Simulateur de combat gratuit terreur contre la terreur\n\nLe commandement des forces spéciales (contre-terrorisme) doit résister aux attaques terroristes. La bataille sera juste épique!\n- Cette fois c'est un simulateur de bataille (Battle) et pas un shooter!\n\nCaractéristiques:\n☑ taktinen peli taistelussimulaattorin tyyliin\n☑ Beaucoup d'armes réelles, y compris Ak47, M16, sniper, MP5K, Uzi, M249\n☑ niveaux nostalgiques donnera / désert\n☑ Guerre épique entre contre-terrorisme et terroriste\n\n   - Votre héritage attend!","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LTRTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-terror-battle-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67GJ6","slug":"playtime-mix-monster","title":"Playtime Mix Monster","description":"Playtime Mix Monster  is probably the first character creator game online to have been added to the Poppy Playtime Games category of our website, which means that is more relaxing and creative than the majority of them, as this category is known for its horror, and we're highly positive that you will enjoy it just as much as we did, which was quite a lot, the main reason for bringing the game over!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67GJ6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ghtsggjvv/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"29784","slug":"enigma-chapter-1-morgue-escape","title":"Enigma Chapter 1 - Morgue Escape","description":"Enigma Chapter 1: The morgue is the first series of our most favorite point and click mysteries to solve.\nUnlock all clue and escape from horrific morgue","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/29784/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/enigma-chapter-1-morgue-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RRC6","slug":"grab-pack-play-time","title":"Grab Pack Play time","description":"Il s'agit d'un jeu de cheminement en 30 étapes où vous devez déplacer soigneusement vos bras pour éviter les monstres et autres obstacles dangereux. Vous avez les bras les plus longs du monde, qui peuvent faire plus de 1 000 fois le tour du Livre Guinness des records. Votre personnage rend Gumby envieux.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RRC6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grab-pack-play-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"APPVE","slug":"evil-space-base-fps","title":"Evil Space Base FPS","description":"Evil Space Base : FPS is a first person action horror game set in a sci fi space base.\n\nthe game is about a space patrol that finds a mysterious base on a remote planet and goes there to inspect. But this space base has a big secret and terrible events have happened in it.\n\nGame Features\n\n    Intense  action horror gameplay\n    Beautiful  and atmospheric sci-fi environment \n    Entertaining and simple story\n    Good graphics  ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/APPVE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evil-space-base-fps/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"616IN","slug":"the-courage-of-an-american-grandfather","title":"The Courage of an American Grandfather","description":"The courage of an American grandfather is a free Beat 'em up game with modern graphic and feel of classic games like streets of rage and final fight.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Classic style Beat 'em up gameplay\n    Good graphics\n    Easy to pickup and play\n    Simple and entertaining story  ","category":"Action","tags":["sports","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/616IN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-courage-of-an-american-grandfather/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C6666","slug":"skibidi-wood-cutter","title":"Skibidi Wood Cutter","description":"In this game you need to chop wood and avoid the branches.\nIt could be an easy task? It's easy to play but hard to master!\nSo help Skibidi Toilet as every lumberjack does and chop the tree as fast the more you can!\n· One-touch control system!\n· Simple and addictive gameplay!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C6666/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-wood-cutter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BN91N","slug":"noob-mineblox-hunt-skibidi-toilet","title":"Noob Mineblox Hunt Skibidi Toilet","description":"Noob Mineblox Hunt Skibidi Toilet is a combination between action and stealth game.\nAs a Noob Mineblox you must survive from hurdles of Skibidi Toilet.\nTake aimlessly all Skibidi Toilet enemies from behind.\nDont let them catch you!\nGame features:\n- Map design each level is unique and has its own strategies to complete\n- The cool feeling of stealth 2.5D action packed game\n- Cool environment and enemy AI","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BN91N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-mineblox-hunt-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I316F","slug":"fnf-skibidi-toilet-dance-party","title":"FNF Skibidi Toilet Dance Party","description":"FNF Skibidi Toilet Dance Party is a rhythm action game.\nFeaturing Cameramen and Skibidi Toilet to perform great dance performance!\nChoose your music and defeat Skibidi Toilet in this exciting battle dance music game.\nUpgrade your special performance to gain more score!\nEnjoy the cool song!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I316F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fnf-skibidi-toilet-dance-party/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KS17D","slug":"skibidi-match-master","title":"Skibidi Match Master","description":"Play trending characters skibidi in this exciting match-3 puzzle game, Skibidi Match Master! Remove tiles from play by making sets of three or more of the same kind. You'll get access to more playable characters and levels as you make your way through the game. Moreover, you may compete with your friends to see who can achieve the highest score.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KS17D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44934","slug":"stickman-epic","title":"Stickman Epic","description":"Choose from three unique characters, fight bosses and upgrade your hero's power!\n\nEquip your hero with 72 different armor options, complete 15 exciting levels and fight 6 different bosses!\nOpen chests and get rewards!\nEarn a rating and be the best among the rest!\n\nBonuses every day! Come and get them!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44934/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-epic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ADOT","slug":"skibidi-toilet-puzzle","title":"Skibidi Toilet Puzzle","description":"$66","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ADOT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M317K","slug":"gummy-blocks-battle","title":"Gummy Blocks Battle","description":"\"Gummy Blocks is an interesting puzzle game with an original plot.\n\nYou will easily learn how to play and win - just drop the cubes to create or destroy full lines on the screen, both vertical and horizontal.\n\nControl of the game is adapted to all available platforms.\n\nGo ahead and try to become the best in the game!\"","category":"Puzzle","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M317K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gummy-blocks-battle/embed?sid=1","plays":39880,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2C26T","slug":"cycle-sprint","title":"Cycle Sprint","description":"\"Customize your cyclist and perfect your bike for a thrilling adventure!\n\nCompete in Italy, France and Spain.\n\nWin all 63 races and earn your spot on the podium of champions!\"","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2C26T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cycle-sprint/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6UYML","slug":"gummy-blocks-evolution","title":"Gummy Blocks Evolution","description":"Drag and drop the blocks onto the board to create rows of gummies and make them disappear. \nOnce you’re all out of room, it’ll be game over!\nIf you want to add adrenaline, try two new modes: “Advanced”, in which you will get fantastic bonuses in case you delete two or more lines of blocks at the same time. Bomb mode is a challenge: try to blow up a dynamite block in 9 moves.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","puzzles","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6UYML/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gummy-blocks-evolution/embed?sid=1","plays":39758,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ACSI1","slug":"skibidi-survival-challenge","title":"Skibidi Survival Challenge","description":"Skibidi Survival Challenge is a fast-paced, endless roadrunner survival game. In this game, you must control a Skibidi dancer as they run down a never-ending road, dodging obstacles and collecting coins. The longer you survive, the more points you earn. But be careful! If you hit an obstacle or fall off the road, it's game over.\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ACSI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-survival-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7OH1W","slug":"blow-fish-2","title":"Blow Fish 2","description":"Use your pearls to clear each level by destroying all sea creatures.\nIf you receive 2 or 3 stars next level will unlock.\nTap and hold finger to aim, release to shoot pearl.\nBuy special features in the shop during game play","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7OH1W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blow-fish-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4U6R6","slug":"bubble-hero","title":"Bubble Hero","description":"Become a hero as you pop your way to success with Bubble Hero.\nShoot bubbles, collect special items, free the mice and move through 80\naddictive levels of excitement with rewards along the way","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4U6R6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H6SL2","slug":"horse-simulator-3d","title":"Horse Simulator 3D","description":"$67","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H6SL2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horse-simulator-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H011S","slug":"princess-makeover-fashion-blog","title":"Princess Makeover Fashion Blog","description":"In this new cute game Princess Makeover Fashion Blog, Princess Anna, and Elsa are decided to create a fashion blog. So they planned to make a photoshoot for their blog.\n\nFace decor with photoshoot can never get more fascinating than this! They planned to try some cute face art with different lip colors. And also they decided to try different hairstyles. Princess confused about choosing a nice variety of butterflies, animals, and superhero face art. They need some expert advice to make a perfect blog.\n\nHelp them with your decorative skill and make some unique face art for each princess. And also help them in the dress-up part. They have cute wardrobe collections. Help them to choose the best one among the collections.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H011S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-makeover-fashion-blog/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CLNC8","slug":"princess-in-colourful-wonderland","title":"Princess In Colourful Wonderland","description":"In Princess in Colourful Wonderland game, Princesses grant wishes, make fairy play and enjoy themselves. Quickly they realize it’s all in their dreams.\n\nPrincesses now want to make their dream a reality. The princesses are planning to wear some cool fairy outfits, bands, and crowns with a cute collection of fairy feathers. They want to make it happen in reality and grant their fairy wishes to each other. Enjoy this fun-filled experience on wonderland with our fairies! So help the princess have maximum fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CLNC8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-in-colourful-wonderland/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CAMN4","slug":"agent-cameraman-skibidi-toilet","title":"Agent Cameraman Skibidi Toilet","description":"Hey agent! Quickly grab your weapon and be ready for the mission. The monsters are coming, and their bosses are here too. Eliminate all the restroom monsters! Agent cameraman, if youre ready for the mission, lets begin. Start from the difficulty level you prefer; some missions are harder than others. The monsters can be very powerful. You also need a better weapon to kill the monsters. Get the best weapon and defeat all the restroom monsters. Many costumes are waiting for you as well. Put on the costume you want and start the adventure yourself.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CAMN4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/agent-cameraman-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NU11D","slug":"skibidi-toilet-jump-challenge","title":"Skibidi Toilet Jump Challenge","description":"Skibidi Jump Challenge is a fun yet challenging game to play. Here, the player has to make a stack of dustbins and jump at the right time to place the skibidi toilet on top of the stack. Focus on the timing; do not let the toilet fall, or the game will be over. \n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NU11D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-jump-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12A69","slug":"hungry-shark-vs-skibidi","title":"Hungry Shark Vs Skibidi","description":"Hungry Shark vs. Skibidi Jump Challenge Game is a fun and addictive game that is sure to keep you entertained for hours on end. With its simple but addictive gameplay, variety of different sharks to choose from, and  Skibidi Jump Challenge event, there is something for everyone to enjoy. ","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12A69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hungry-shark-vs-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7IKI","slug":"skibidi-snake","title":"Skibidi Snake","description":"Skibidi Snake.io is a fast-paced, action-packed snake game that will test your reflexes and strategy skills. In this game, you control a snake that must eat as many Skibidi as possible to grow in size. The longer your snake gets, the more difficult it will be to control, but the more points you will score.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7IKI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-snake-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B1L66","slug":"skibidi-vs-alien","title":"Skibidi Vs Alien","description":"Skibidi Vs. Alien is an endless runner survival game where you play as Skibidi, a young alien who must dance his way through a series of challenging levels in order to defeat the evil aliens who have invaded his planet.\nThe game is simple to play but difficult to master. You control Skibidi by tapping the screen to make him jump and slide. You must avoid obstacles and enemies while collecting power-ups to help you stay alive. The levels get progressively more difficult as you progress, and you will need to use all of your skills to survive.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B1L66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-vs-alien/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E1D30","slug":"skibidi-toilet-basketball","title":"Skibidi Toilet Basketball","description":"Welcome to the exciting world of \"Skibidi Toilet Basketball\"! This is an addictive arcade game that will offer you a unique and addictive gameplay. You have to throw your head towards the toilet, and each blow can be a real challenge, because the head can bounce off the barrier, adding an additional element of strategy and skill.\n\nIn \"Skibidi Toilet Basketball\" you will pump up your skills, overcome difficulties at each level and compete with friends for the best results. With each completed level, the game becomes more exciting and more interesting.\n\nWith high-quality graphics and exciting gameplay, \"Skibidi Toilet Basketball\" promises you an unforgettable experience. Show your dexterity, accuracy and strategic thinking.\n\nAre you ready to accept the challenge and become the best in \"Skibidi Toilet Basketball\"? Start playing right now and show your masterful game in this addictive arcade game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E1D30/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7KOI1","slug":"flappy-skibidi-toilet","title":"Flappy Skibidi Toilet","description":"Help Skibidi Toilet to avoid the pipes obstacles in this flappy bird game and try to survive as long as you can to sign the best possible score! Enjoy it!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7KOI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LB48O","slug":"zomblox-io","title":"Zomblox.io","description":"Multiplayer zombie survival game!\nDefeat waves of zombies on on 3 different maps.\nDestroy loot boxes to get more powerful weapons. Destroy TNT barrels to create an explosion.\n\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LB48O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zomblox-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M8860","slug":"simple-math","title":"Simple Math","description":"Develop logical thinking by solving the simplest arithmetic puzzles. Trains: verbal logic; elementary counting operations; switching and attention distribution","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M8860/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/simple-math/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I0A8N","slug":"tic-tac-toe-online","title":"Tic Tac Toe Online","description":"Tic-tac-toe, also known as noughts and crosses, is a classic paper-and-pencil game played on a square grid typically consisting of three rows and three columns. The objective of the game is to be the first to create a straight line of three of your own marks, either horizontally, vertically, or diagonally.\nTic-tac-toe is a simple yet engaging game that can be played quickly, making it suitable for casual entertainment, as well as a means of introducing basic strategy concepts to players of all ages. Its simplicity and familiar gameplay have made it a popular choice for passing the time and developing critical thinking skills.","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I0A8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tic-tac-toe-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T7NA9","slug":"bunny-needs-carrot","title":"Bunny Needs Carrot","description":"Collect Carrot and go trought the portal to get inside the new level","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T7NA9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bunny-needs-carrot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5F5SS","slug":"fish-rain","title":"Fish Rain","description":"Le jeu de pêche est un simulateur de pêche à part entière et vous donne la possibilité de pêcher dans des lieux réels de la vie et d'attraper les poissons qui y vivent.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5F5SS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fish-rain/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1F85O","slug":"rootbeer-floater","title":"Rootbeer Floater","description":"Rootbeer Floater is a 2D hyper casual game in which you play as scientist T Awesomesauce. T Awesomesauce created the world best rootbeer. Now everything is trying to have a taste. Dodge lip, rootbeer mugs and more. Collect the power barrel to fill up the pow meter for the special attack.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1F85O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rootbeer-floater/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T1T6","slug":"ballblast","title":"BallBlast","description":"Fantastic Ball Blast Game","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T1T6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ballblast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A1ET","slug":"the-adventures-of-merlock-and-doteson-part-1","title":"The Adventures of Merlock and Doteson - Part 1","description":"Jeu de plateforme d'horreur 3D. Dans ce jeu passionnant, vous devez enquêter sur des incidents mystérieux en tant que détective Merlock et son ami et assistant, le Dr Doutson. Vous devrez résoudre des énigmes, combattre des ennemis assoiffés de sang et avancer vers l'objectif à travers la peur et le doute afin de terminer votre mission à la fin et de recevoir des récompenses et de la gratitude.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A1ET/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-adventures-of-merlock-and-doteson-part-one/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3OM17","slug":"wormpocalypse","title":"Wormpocalypse","description":"The game is a hardcore pixel art platformer created in the style of old school games. Protagonist must overcome various difficult levels full of traps and enemies to find out how to survive. During the game, the protagonist will acquire new weapons and improvements.\n\nIn a world struck by an unknown catastrophic event, the era of the post-apocalypse has come. As a result of this cataclysm, dangerous substances were released into the atmosphere, which turned ordinary worms into a mutated form of life. These worms began to suck on people's heads, allowing them to control their carriers.\n\nThe main character of the story is a boy, who survived the disaster. He discovered that worms have intelligence and use people as their puppets to achieve their own goals.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3OM17/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wormpocalypse/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16FL3","slug":"elite-minigolf","title":"Elite MiniGolf","description":"Elite MiniGolf, where precision meets excitement! Test your skills in this challenging and addictive mini golf game. Navigate through meticulously designed courses, featuring unique obstacles and breathtaking landscapes. \nAim, putt, and master the art of controlling your shots to achieve the coveted hole-in-one. With intuitive controls and stunning visuals. \nElite MiniGolf offers an immersive experience for casual players and golf enthusiasts alike. Can you conquer every hole and become a mini golf champion? Tee off now and swing your way to victory in Elite MiniGolf!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16FL3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/elite-minigolf/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25AEI","slug":"avoid-the-spikes","title":"Avoid the Spikes","description":"Jump to fly but be careful with the walls above and below because if you fall or fly too much you could puncture and avoid colliding with the spikes that appear on the left and right or the game will be over\n\nFeatures:\n- Obtain the best score\n- 12 Skins for select\n- 11 Skins for unlock from gems","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25AEI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/avoid-the-spikes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OORI1","slug":"bike-stunt-skibidi-toilet","title":"Bike Stunt skibidi Toilet","description":"Bike Stunt Skibidi Toilet with a cool bike racing Skibidi Toilet. Toilet vehicle based game with racing modifications for drag bike lovers. In this game, there are several types of toilet that you can play to ride the reckless Skibidi Toilet.\nDriving a drag toilet racing vehicle is a thrilling experience that is hard to forget. With the Bike Stunt Skibidi Toilet game, you will get a large collection of drag toilet racer. Games that you can download for free that have an additional collection of drag bikes make playing the game exciting. ","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OORI1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-moto-bike-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16ER3","slug":"circle-defence","title":"Circle Defence","description":"You are the blue Circle and has 100 health points. each Enemy has the capability to decrease your health by 10.  For each kill you will get 2 health points\n\nControls:\n\nuse mouse left button to kill the enemies.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16ER3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/circle-defence/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IH1I9","slug":"skibidi-fight","title":"Skibidi Fight","description":"Hey buddy! Are you up for a showdown with your friend? Guns are drawn, its the perfect time to fire. Shoot right away and claim victory. The toilet guys need to battle it out. There are no obstacles in the arena, all you need to do is make swift moves left and right. Dodge the bullets, fire as fast as you can. Collect the boost boxes to win. The boxes will contain power-ups and weapons. Grab your weapon, aim at your enemy, and win.\n\nUse the WASD keys to move the Blue Player. Press the T key to shoot. Use the Arrow Keys to move the Red Player. Press P to shoot. Mobile devices are also supported for gameplay.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IH1I9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-fight/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OO0O3","slug":"doodle-drop","title":"Doodle Drop","description":"Traversez les niveaux avec le chaton. Utilisez des bonus pour geler et ralentir les plateformes. Maîtrisez les plateformes descendantes et rendez votre chaton heureux !\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OO0O3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doodle-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42L22","slug":"line-98-classic","title":"Line 98 Classic","description":"Do you love playing classic puzzle games like Lines 98, Color Lines, or Ball Lines?\n\n If so, you will enjoy our new game, Line98! It’s a fun and addictive marble game that challenges your logic and strategy skills. You have to clear the board by forming lines of five or more balls of the same color. \n\nThe more balls you pop, the more points you get. But be careful, new balls will appear after every move, so you have to plan ahead. Can you beat the high score and become the master of Line98? Try it now !","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42L22/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/line-98-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01THE","slug":"plane-shooter","title":"Plane Shooter","description":"Prepare for thrilling aerial combat in our action-packed Plane Shooter game! Take control of a powerful fighter plane as you navigate through intense enemy territory, engaging in epic dogfights and dodging enemy fire. Test your skills and reflexes as you shoot down waves of enemies and boss planes in a visually stunning, fast-paced experience.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01THE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/plane-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"INOOT","slug":"a-little-walk-in-the-woods","title":"A Little Walk in the Woods","description":"Il fait beau aujourd'hui et vous décidez de partir en promenade.","category":"Aventure","tags":["classics","adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/INOOT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/a-little-walk-in-the-woods/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91R60","slug":"thirsty-pirate","title":"Thirsty Pirate","description":"The thirsty Captain Fiasco has exaggerated with rum and has fallen victim to the prankster ghost pirates who have stolen and hidden his loved maps in the islets of the South Seas. Help him finding his \"treasures\". In this puzzle game the player has control of the island by rotating it, so that the mission can be completed","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91R60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/thirsty-pirate/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PO1G0","slug":"ragdoll-physics-push","title":"Ragdoll Physics Push","description":"Poussez Ragdoll Physics 3D simulation! contient maintenant Stikman!\n\n\"Push Ragdoll: Physique 3D\" jeu totalement gratuit! En outre, il y a maintenant Stikman!\nPréparez-vous à tuer le temps: cliquez pour lancer Ragdoll à niveau 3D pour récupérer des pièces et des trésors!\nChoisissez l'un des nombreux personnages: normal, Stikman, géant et centaure\nLe jeu contient 3 trésors dans chaque niveau - pouvez-vous les trouver?\nDiffusez vos résultats sur Facebook!\nPhysique réaliste :)\n \nattribution:\nMusique: DJ-M-Power du système de freinage\nUI sons: KillaMaaki\nAtteindre son Kastenfrosch-\nson nenadsimic- Coin\n ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PO1G0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ragdoll-physics-push/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"99IID","slug":"rainbow-friends-vs-skibidi-toilet","title":"Rainbow Friends VS Skibidi Toilet","description":"Rainbow Friends VS Skibidi Toilet is a combination between action and stealth game.\nAs a Rainbow Friend you must survive from hurdles of Skibidi Toilet.\nTake aimlessly all Skibidi Toilet enemies from behind.\nDont let them catch you!\nGame features:\n- Map design each level is unique and has its own strategies to complete\n- The cool feeling of stealth 2.5D action packed game\n- Cool environment and enemy AI","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/99IID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-spy-mario-vs-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AN7I6","slug":"stickman-car-racing","title":"Stickman Car Racing","description":"Juego de carreras gratis con stickman\n\n¡La temporada de carreras en el mundo stickman ha comenzado! ¡Elige tu coche de carreras y corre a correr!\n- Conducción extrema con stickman\n- Cada nivel y coche en 3d\n- Juego 100% fuera de línea (no se requiere multijugador)\n- Coches en 3D y stickman\n- Geniales stickman conductores: ¡carreras increíbles!\n\nMúsica: newgrounds_vibes_8bit__mega_Foxeh ---\nTechno-Rage-FULL_IoChron --- TrAnCeD-Mastery-\n","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AN7I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-car-racing/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O01IT","slug":"skibidi-toilet-in-the-tower","title":"Skibidi Toilet In The Tower","description":"Skibidi Toilet in The Tower takes the Endless runner (i guess endless flyer) genre!\nHelp our friend Skibidi the alien to get as high as he can, avoiding the obstacles such as rolling mines, spikes, TV on the way and collecting as many coins as possible.\nDont hit any enemies or its game over for Skibidi!\nChallenge your friends scores on the local leader boards to see who comes out top in this addictive, challenging and entertaining arcade game.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O01IT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-in-the-tower/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4A90E","slug":"helix-ball","title":"Helix Ball","description":"Helix ball is an endless road that is constantly accelerating and challenging. Collect balls of your own color from the constantly rotating circles and reach a new record.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4A90E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/helix-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ED098","slug":"skibidi-toilet-shooter","title":"Skibidi Toilet Shooter","description":"Skibidi Toilet Shooter is a fast-paced, shooting game where you have to kill the nasty Skibidi toilets. It is your responsibility to stop the Skibidi toilets from taking over the world. Use all your ability to kill those nasty toilets and set the world free. \n\nControl: \nDesktop: Use the arrow key buttons of the keyboard to move. And the space button is for the shoot. You can also use the buttons on the screen to move and shoot. \n\nMobile: There are arrow buttons on the screen; you can use those buttons to move, and there is a shoot button on the bottom left, which you can use when you need to shoot. \n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ED098/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAHRH","slug":"barbie-match-master","title":"Barbie Match Master","description":"Play as your favorite Barbie characters in this exciting match-3 puzzle game, Barbie Match Master! Remove tiles from play by making sets of three or more of the same kind. You'll get access to more playable characters and levels as you make your way through the game. Moreover, you may compete with your friends to see who can achieve the highest score.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAHRH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbie-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PI11S","slug":"floppy-skibidi","title":"Floppy Skibidi","description":"In the tough arcade game Floppy Skibidi, you take control of a flying toilet. Your objective is to avoid striking any pipes as you soar through the air between them. As you advance, the pipes will be closer together, making the game harder and harder. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PI11S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/floppy-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5828H","slug":"feed-the-fox","title":"Feed The Fox","description":"Feed the Fox is a fun game to play. In this game, the main character is a hungry fox who needs to eat to survive. Help the fox eat the little chicks that are coming down but be aware of the tiny bombs that are coming down with the chicks as well. To continue playing the game keep your eyes on the bombs. Use the arrows on the screen or the keyboard arrows to play the game if you are playing on your computer. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5828H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/feed-the-fox/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S2SUE","slug":"skibidi-jump-adventure","title":"Skibidi Jump Adventure","description":"Playing as a small child named Skibidi, you'll engage in nonstop platforming action in the game Skibidi Jump Adventure. Skibidi is a skilled dancer who uses his abilities to jump, slide, and avoid danger as he makes his way through a series of challenging levels. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S2SUE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-jump-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"336A7","slug":"cats-picnic","title":"Cats Picnic","description":"Cats Picnic Link is a Match 3 Puzzle Game. it is an exciting challenging game for gamers of all age. It is cheerful fun game. very easy to learn. By connecting three or more similar Fish items, you can assist the cats in enjoying a picnic. You can quickly empty the board by matching various Fish. Your score increases if you match more items.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/336A7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cats-picnic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6V8OE","slug":"evading-the-police","title":"Evading The Police","description":"Evading The Police is an online game where you help the character avoid the police. The game is set in a city environment and you must use your agility and speed to escape the police. The graphics are good and the gameplay is smooth. This is a great game to play if you are looking for something to do online.\nJump, run, and hide from the police in this exciting online game! See how long you can last while avoiding capture in Evading The Police. Play now for free!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6V8OE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/evading-the-police/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C28GL","slug":"flying-challenge","title":"Flying Challenge","description":"Flying Challenge is a Flappy Bird game . where You can control a bird that is trying to fly and facing many obstacles, including bow, and other objects. Your main target is to control this bird without facing obstacles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C28GL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9OEAI","slug":"infinite-galaxy-shooter","title":"Infinite Galaxy Shooter","description":"The thrilling space shooter game known as Infinite Galaxy Shooter has frantic gameplay and lightning-fast action sequences throughout the game. This game is very easy to play where all you have to do is shoot the enemy and avoid the bullets they are shooting. Complete and stay alive is the player's mission.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9OEAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/infinite-galaxy-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TN4OG","slug":"ping-pong-shooter","title":"Ping Pong Shooter","description":"Ping Pong Shooter is a fun and addictive puzzle game that combines the classic gameplay of Bubble Shooter with the physics-based gameplay of Ping Pong. \nThe game features a variety of different levels, each with its own unique challenges. As you progress through the game, the levels will become more difficult, requiring you to use your skills and strategy to clear them.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TN4OG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ing-pong-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26B6L","slug":"strawberella","title":"Strawberella","description":"This strawberry princess-inspired dress-up game is sure to turn heads as it showcases an amazing fashion design challenge featuring a beautiful pink dress, a makeup artist challenge that will get you glamming up like never before, and an accessory extraordinaire challenge where you get to accessorize your looks beyond imagination. Play today!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26B6L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/strawberella/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8R89B","slug":"fight-bros","title":"Fight Bros","description":"Have you ever thrown a stone with a slingshot before? shoot and beat your friend with slingshot. It is a game that can be played for 2 players. Fight with each other with your friend. You have 3 lives. 3 lifeless dies and loses. fight to win. There are 3 different maps. Superpowers are falling because of the sky. Get the gift box and get your power. Kill your opponent with fish oranges and stars.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8R89B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fight-bros/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I9FN3","slug":"skibidi-toilet-friends","title":"Skibidi Toilet Friends","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of two friends? Achieve victory with teamwork. You should move with your friend. You should support your friend. two toilet men need to reach the door. proceed in order. Reach the door in this fun for two. Watch out for moving obstacles. You must reach the door before you die. neither of you should die.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I9FN3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-friends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NEV3E","slug":"skibidi-vs-noob-cameraman","title":"Skibidi vs Noob & Cameraman","description":"Two friends are running away from the monster. The toilet monster is chasing. Escape the toilet monster. toilet monster can kill you. collect all the gold. Collect the gold to open the portal. Jump over obstacles, go faster than some. run with your friend, dont stop. reach the portal. boiler.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NEV3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-vs-noob-and-cameraman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5P5T5","slug":"escape-the-sewer","title":"Escape The Sewer","description":"Have you ever survived in temple with your friend? so join this adventure with your friend now. survive in the temple! There are puzzles in the temple. The temple is filled with poison. watch out for the poison in the temple. watch out for the dangers in the temple, you can die at any moment. Solve puzzles with your friend. Collaborate with your friend. Progress by teamwork.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5P5T5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-the-temple/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EAAS8","slug":"square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-landscape","title":"Square jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Landscape","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments carrés. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EAAS8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-landscape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BRQA4","slug":"square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-cartoon","title":"Square jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Cartoon","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments carrés. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BRQA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-cartoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ELBSM","slug":"square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-fruits","title":"Square jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Fruits","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments carrés. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ELBSM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-fruits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZZASE","slug":"square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-flowers","title":"Square jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Flowers","description":" Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments carrés. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZZASE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/square-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-flowers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E606L","slug":"battle-simulator-police-prison","title":"Battle Simulator - Police Prison","description":"Simulateur de prison où les forces spéciales et la police peuvent empêcher la fuite\n\nPolice à se battre! La prison est en état de siège! Gangsters - les prisonniers tentent de s'échapper de prison. Un simulateur de guerre dans une prison de police vous fournit des unités de police épiques pour combattre une armée de gangsters condamnés.\n\nTraits:\n• prison tridimensionnelle et modèles de prisonniers (condamnés) de bandits\n• Tactiques policières parfaitement précises.\n• unités de police, y compris pistolet Taser, swat (forces spéciales), police maladroite et cyclistes\n• Bataille épique avec de nombreuses unités, sang et ragdoll\n• sons de freesoundDotOrg et crédit de musique Janze_Fake_tune\n\n---> Aucun prisonnier ne devrait s'échapper! ←","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E606L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/police-prison-battle-simulator/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5OODS","slug":"coloring-book-for-kids","title":"Coloring Book For Kids","description":"Coloring Book For Kids is fun coloring app game for kids and adults!\nIf you like coloring characters then you will love this fun cute cartoon themed coloring book!\nChoose one of the cute images, pick your favorite color and start coloring! Enjoy it!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5OODS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mario-coloring-book-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SKM2U","slug":"skibidi-toilet-and-the-pumpkin","title":"Skibidi Toilet And The Pumpkin","description":"Hey Mr. Pumpkin you need to escape from the Skibidi Toilet!\nTry to resit the more you can and complete all 20 Levels!\nEnjoy this summer season with this great trend game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SKM2U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-and-the-pumpkin/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S3AKY","slug":"skibidi-flappy-poppy","title":"Skibidi Flappy Poppy","description":"Get ready for an exhilarating gaming experience with Skibidi Toilet game series!\nStep into the shoes of the beloved character Skibidi Toilet as you play through a high-stakes game inspired by the super series Flappy Bird in poppy style.\nAre you able to avoid all pipes and try to collect all medals?\nEnjoy this great game!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S3AKY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-flappy-poppy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"48081","slug":"stunt-skibidi","title":"Stunt Skibidi","description":"Are You the next great stunt Skibidi Toilet pilot?\nYou will need to have strong nerves and great precision to finish the game.\nThe difficulty increases as you advance in levels but sometimes you will be forced to repeat a level many times before completing the mission.\nHow to play: \nThe main goal is to collect all stars to finish each levels, so fly inside the hoops without crashing, but be aware to your fuel bar because sometime you need to refill it so collect the fuel barrel.\nAre you ready to fly now?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/48081/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stunt-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6C2N2","slug":"science-perfect-fit-jigsaw","title":"Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw! Our Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw picture. With a wide variety of Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Science Perfect Fit Jigsaw Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6C2N2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/science-perfect-fit-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEZLL","slug":"the-rake-jigsaw-puzzle","title":"The Rake Jigsaw puzzle","description":"Welcome to The Rake Block puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Rake Block puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Rake Block puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEZLL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-rake-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SE1G3","slug":"tiny-eevee-photo-jigsaw","title":"Tiny Eevee Photo Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Tiny Eevee Photo jigsaw, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Tiny Eevee Photo jigsaw, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Tiny Eevee Photo jigsaw and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SE1G3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-eevee-photo-jigsaw/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0FRFO","slug":"flowers-coloring-game-for-adults","title":"Flowers Coloring Game for Adults","description":"$68","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0FRFO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flowers-coloring-game-for-adults/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D928G","slug":"hard-coloring-pages-for-kids","title":"Hard Coloring Pages For Kids","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Hard Coloring Pages Fo0r Kid game! Whether you're a fan of Hard Coloring Pages Fo0r Kid or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Hard Coloring Pages Fo0r Kid images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Hard Coloring Pages Fo0r Kid masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly gam