os-coloring-game","title":"Tattoos Coloring Game","description":"$69","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OM94A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tattoos-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2796A","slug":"lucky-vegas-roulette","title":"Lucky Vegas Roulette","description":"Choisissez votre table préférée et participez à la roulette la plus chanceuse de votre vie ! Prévoyez les machines à sous gagnantes et placez votre mise. Faites tourner la roue et regardez la bille choisir le gagnant. \n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2796A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lucky-vegas-roulette/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"97Y66","slug":"claw-crane-toys","title":"Claw Crane. Toys","description":"Fun and addictive arcade game \"Claw Crane: Toys\". Everyone's favorite toy-catching machine is now in your pocket. Catch toys and earn achievements.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/97Y66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/claw-crane-toys/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K01OD","slug":"monster-attack-tower-defense","title":"Monster Attack Tower Defense","description":"Dans le jeu Monster Attack: Tower Defense, vous devez défendre votre forteresse contre une attaque visqueuse.\n\nDans le jeu Monster Attack Tower Defense, il y a beaucoup de pompages différents. Le jeu propose plus de 50 améliorations pour votre forteresse.\n\nUn jeu du genre inactif. Ou AFK. Dans ce jeu inactif, vous n'avez pas besoin de tirer depuis votre tour, tout est automatisé, il vous suffit d'améliorer votre forteresse.\n\nCaractéristiques du jeu Monster Attack : Tower Defense :\n- Un gameplay fascinant et simple dans le genre de \"défense de tour inactive\"\n- Un grand nombre d'améliorations, grâce auxquelles vous pouvez créer votre propre tour unique et conquérir des monstres sans fin !\n- Achat de nouvelles améliorations qui aideront à détruire les foules de monstres visqueux\n- Un classement où vous pouvez voir combien de temps vous avez résisté aux attaques de monstres","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K01OD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-attack-td/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EI3E8","slug":"jetpack-kiwi-lite","title":"Jetpack Kiwi Lite","description":"Jetpack Kiwi Lite is a classic 2D side scrolling shoot em up game featuring 4 levels, 1 bosses, hordes of enemies spaceships, with multiple characters to choose from; each one with an unique special attack. Complete the game in single player or with a friend in local co-op! \n\nGame Controls:\nWASD - ARROWS = Move\nX = Shoot\nB = Bomb\nM = Mute/unmute audio\nP = Pause\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EI3E8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jetpack-kiwi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8B6RG","slug":"mr-noob-eat-burger","title":"Mr. Noob EAT Burger","description":"This place has a lot of burgers, you need to find and eat them all. But they are guarded by the terrible Mr. Noob! Arm yourself with a torch and a burger detector to find them all, trick Noob and escape his estate.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8B6RG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mr-noob-eat-burger/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"W6EO6","slug":"idle-cat-town-clicker","title":"Idle Cat Town Clicker","description":"Jeu de tapotement au ralenti avec un chat - tapez votre chemin vers la richesse !\n\nTu es un chat! Un chat oisif ! Frayez-vous un chemin vers la richesse pour devenir le millionnaire du magnat des chats !\n\n- construis ta cité des chats !\n- beaucoup de chats !!\n\nProuvez que vous pouvez taper mieux que moi ! la ville des chatons vous attend","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/W6EO6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-cat-town-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N130R","slug":"grandma-recipe-nigiri-sushi","title":"Grandma Recipe Nigiri Sushi","description":"Her friends will be coming over tonight. It's time to serve a delicious food for them and Nigiri Sushi can be a good choice! Ask grandma to get the recipe. Prepare the tools and find the ingredients. Make the rice ball perfectly then decorate the nigiri sushi. Keep following grandma's instruction to finish making nice sushi! Don't forget to dress up with various cute costumes. Making Nigiri Sushi has ever been more fun!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N130R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grandma-recipe-nigiri-sushi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11019","slug":"colorbox-puzzle","title":"ColorBox Puzzle","description":"Colorbox Puzzle is a classic creative block game. It's addictive to play with challenges and various funny patterns in every stage! Drag the block pieces to a suitable place in the given pattern until it is filled correctly. Just drag, drop, and move! With multiple difficulties and many patterns, welcome to the amazing blocks world!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11019/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colorbox-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"32R33","slug":"barbiecore","title":"Barbiecore","description":"Introducing Barbiecore, the ultimate fashion and dress-up game that invites you to explore a delightful new trend! Step into a world where hot pink and bubblegum hues reign supreme, and meet the charming Ellie, a doll who adores everything Barbiecore. Immerse yourself in her world and unleash your creativity as you create adorable casual and sporty chic looks in this captivating free-to-play game designed for girls. Get ready to embrace the vibrant pink palette and dive into the enchanting world of Barbiecore!","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/32R33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/barbiecore/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O39T3","slug":"summer-floral-prints","title":"Summer Floral Prints","description":"Get ready to embrace the summer with our dress-up game, Summer Floral Prints! Explore the playful and feminine fashion trend of floral prints. Create stunning #ootd looks for 5 BFFs as they conquer the bustling boulevard in style. Get ready for endless fun and fashion-forward moments!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O39T3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/summer-floral-prints/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HSPPR","slug":"lol-surprise-preppy-fashion","title":"LOL Surprise Preppy Fashion","description":"Welcome to LOL Surprise Preppy Fashion. LOL Suprise doll plans to try a new stylish fashion. Yes! It’s preppy fashion. Browse and choose the best set of outfits for them. Show your fashion skill and give them a stunning look. Enjoy playing this new collection of games and have fun! ","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HSPPR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lol-surprise-preppy-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LPCB6","slug":"rainbow-girls-space-core-aesthetic","title":"Rainbow Girls Space Core Aesthetic","description":"Welcome to the Rainbow Girls Space Core Aesthetic. Who loves space adventure? Everyone right! Rainbow Girls Skyler, Sunny, Ruby, and Violet are adventurer high school girls planning to try space aesthetic outfits. Browse their wardrobe and pick a cute and suitable outfit for them. Join with the girls and have fun! ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LPCB6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-girls-space-core-aesthetic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33YF7","slug":"my-best-ff-outfits","title":"My Best FF Outfits","description":"Welcome to the My Best FF Outfits. Princesses Anna, Elsa, Snowwhite, and Ariel are more font FF game. They always love to wear the FF costumes and accessories. So they planned to try FF outfits. Join and help the girls to pick a suitable outfit for each one of them. Try to choose unique costumes and hairstyles. Play and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33YF7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-best-ff-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T4RS6","slug":"princess-trendy-t-shirt","title":"Princess Trendy T-shirt","description":"Princess Trendy T-Shirt season is on. Princess Anna and Elsa are planning to challenge each other with different styles. Dresses are available in plenty, the princesses are now in a state of confusion in choosing the best outfits to win over other princesses. They need some expert help. So please help the princess to choose the best t-shirt and give each one a perfect look with fashionable t-shirts.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T4RS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-trendy-t-sh