ks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Mermaids Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RDI8M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mermaids-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YBI34","slug":"100-seconds-labyrinth","title":"100 seconds Labyrinth","description":"Explore the maze in the less time possible","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YBI34/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/labyrinth/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"626A4","slug":"zombie-vs-ai-witch","title":"Zombie vs. AI Witch","description":"Engage in an epic battle between Zombies and AI witches, where the objective is to gather a greater number of delectable balls than your formidable opponent. Experience the thrill of a captivating 3D game with straightforward rules, while taking off against a formidable adversary. This enthralling entertainment is designed to captivate both adults and children like.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/626A4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-vs-ai-witch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9I1DR","slug":"drive-in-the-traffic","title":"Drive in the Traffic","description":"Welcome to Drive in the Traffic!\n\nGet ready to test your reflexes and driving skills as you immerse yourself in a chaotic road scenario. \nCollect the thunders along the way to get extra points. \nTry to accumulate the highest score possible by avoiding collisions. Test your dexterity and become the undisputed champion of Drive in the Traffic!\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9I1DR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drive-in-the-traffic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ROLTH","slug":"bobble-space-shooter","title":"Bobble Space Shooter","description":"bobble space shooter is game classic ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ROLTH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bobble-space-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TC33","slug":"match-away-3d-cube","title":"Match Away 3D Cube","description":"$6a","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TC33/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/match-away-3d-cube/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PCN2N","slug":"kid-halloween-coloring-pages","title":"Kid Halloween Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Kid Halloween Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Kid Halloween Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Kid Halloween Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Kid Halloween Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PCN2N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kid-halloween-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5IES5","slug":"printable-st-patricks-day-coloring-pages","title":"Printable St Patricks Day Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Printable St Patricks Day Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Printable St Patricks Day Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Printable St Patricks Day Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Printable St Patricks Day Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5IES5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/printable-st-patricks-day-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"16690","slug":"durak","title":"Durak","description":"Durak is a traditional Russian card game that is widely recognized and popular in many post-Soviet states. The objective of Durak is to be the first player to get rid of all your cards, making it a shedding type of game.\n\nThe unique aspect of Durak is that there is no single winner, but there is one 'Durak' - the 'fool' who is the last player left with cards. The game is typically played with 2 to 6 players and a deck of 36 cards. A key element of strategy is to go out fast, though players also have to be mindful of the cards they leave behind for their opponents.\n\nAttack, defense, and bluffing are integral parts of the gameplay, making Durak not only a game of chance but also a test of skill, strategy, and cunning. Despite its seemingly simple rules, the game requires tactical thinking and risk-taking.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16690/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/durak/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RID7P","slug":"spider-solitaire-deluxe","title":"Spider Solitaire Deluxe","description":"Spider Solitaire Deluxe game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RID7P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spider-solitaire-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5F9E7","slug":"freecell-solitaire-deluxe","title":"Freecell Solitaire Deluxe","description":"freecell solitaire","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5F9E7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/freecell-solitaire-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14O11","slug":"stickman-swing-hook","title":"Stickman Swing Hook","description":"\"Découvrez Stickman Hook, le nouveau jeu signé LayStudio.\n\nAppuyez pour vous accrocher et faire d'incroyables sauts. Évitez tous les obstacles qui se dressent sur votre route. Pourrez-vous exécuter toutes ces figures acrobatiques d'affilée comme un as de la voltige ?\n\nDans ce jeu, incarnez le bonhomme araignée.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14O11/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stick-man-hook/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IIB42","slug":"sniper-hero-killing-skibidi","title":"Sniper Hero Killing Skibidi","description":"Perfect Sniper 3D est un jeu de tir amusant, addictif et extrêmement décontracté. Visez simplement la cible et tirez sur le Skibidi. Vous pouvez également faire exploser des explosifs pour tuer les Skibids. Apprécier!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IIB42/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sniper-killing-skibidi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"29511","slug":"tetmino","title":"Tetmino","description":"A classic puzzle game that allows you to quickly and effectively hone your logic, observation and reaction speed.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/29511/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tetmino/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C9TA6","slug":"find-my-cat","title":"Find my cat","description":"Don’t worry, your sight is fine, you’re not seeing in black and white! It’s just that my cat got lost and I cannot see him!\nPlay with the most adorable animal on Earth and help me get my cat back! 🙂😻\n\n- HOW TO PLAY -\n• Find my cat among other cats\n• Be quick to find it to go to the next level\n• The faster the more levels complete\n\nRace against time with several levels where the difficulty increases.\nHave fun with this free and addictive observation test.\n\nWill you help me find my cat? 😀🐱","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C9TA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-my-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ARRKD","slug":"skibidi-laboratory","title":"Skibidi Laboratory","description":"The game \"Skibdi Laboratory\" offers exciting adventures where you, as a Skibidi, must overcome obstacles, bypass the cameramen and collect all the crystals on the level.\nYour goal is not only to collect valuable crystals, but also to destroy all enemies to get to the end and conquer the laboratory.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ARRKD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-laboratory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9LO2K","slug":"knock-balls","title":"Knock Balls","description":"Throw balls at structures to make them collapse but be careful not to exceed the allowed limit!\n\nEach saved ball will count double at the next level, take advantage of it to apply you!\n\nOne-tap easy-to-learn controls with stunning visual effects and addictive gameplay mechanics.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9LO2K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knock-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8Y2L0","slug":"tiny-football-cup","title":"Tiny Football Cup","description":"Devenez une légende du football en gagnant tous les tournois et les matchs ! Débloquez tous les championnats et jouez avec 28 équipes différentes. Prouvez à vos amis que vous êtes le meilleur joueur de football.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade","sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8Y2L0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tiny-football-cup/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"191LL","slug":"all-seasons-nail-salon","title":"All Seasons Nail Salon","description":"Welcome to All Seasons Nail Salon. It is manicure madness over here and it’s your time to become the greatest Nail Salon of the year! All you need to do is choose the shape, paint, polish, and also help to pick beautiful accessories and tattoos. Play and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/191LL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/all-seasons-nail-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UM65M","slug":"bff-summer-shine-look","title":"BFF Summer Shine Look","description":"Welcome to BFF Summer Shine Look. Bffs are planning for the weekend summer party at the resort. They are bored of trying old fashion summer costumes. Browse their wardrobe for a new collection of outfits and pick a suitable one for each one. Choose matching accessories and unique hairstyles for them. Help them and make this summer party a more memorable one.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UM65M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-summer-shine-look/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"54S6N","slug":"princess-pastel-fashion","title":"Princess Pastel Fashion","description":"Princess Pastel Fashion is totally on in this season! That’s why these stylish princess Anna and Elsa have decided to design some awesome outfits that feature tons of pastel colors. They have already decorated their wardrobe with a set of cute pastel dresses. Help the princesses to choose the best.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/54S6N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-pastel-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NE8H","slug":"superhero-violet-fashion-shoot","title":"Superhero Violet Fashion Shoot","description":"In this cute game Superhero Violet Fashion Shoot, Violet is an incredible teenage girl who is normally very shy and stays away from her peer group of girls. So violet decides to surprise her best friends, parents, and boyfriend by putting up an exquisite photo shoot.","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NE8H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superhero-violet-fashion-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"181TH","slug":"what-color-is-this","title":"What Color Is This","description":"A fun game that you learn and exercise your knowledge of colors.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/181TH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/what-color-is-this/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O9YW9","slug":"world-history-important-dates","title":"World History Important Dates","description":"Test your knowledge of important dates in world history! You will be offered a quiz that contains more than 100 dates of world history from 3500 BC to 1991 AD.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O9YW9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-history-important-dates/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UOB5M","slug":"save-the-baby-home-rush","title":"Save the Baby Home Rush","description":"“Save the Baby: Home Rush” is an entertaining puzzle game that involves drawing. The main goal is to bring a lost child back home to their mother while avoiding various obstacles. What are you waiting for? Save the child now!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UOB5M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-baby-home-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8Y4T6","slug":"ibiza-pool-party","title":"Ibiza Pool Party","description":"Join Elsa and Ariel in an exciting online makeover game where they have planned some incredible girly-girl summer adventures just for you. Are you ready to go on a fabulous trip to Ibiza? Dive right into the Ibiza Pool Party and enjoy a fantastic time with your beloved Disney princesses. Help them get ready for the highly anticipated pool party of the year and have a blast together!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8Y4T6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ibiza-pool-party/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"698B5","slug":"tetra-blocks","title":"Tetra Blocks","description":"The game mechanics are simple and easy to understand yet challenging to master.\nYour objective is to fit Tetra blocks of different shapes into a line without any gaps. With each completed line, they’ll earn points and move on to the next level. The higher they go, the faster the blocks fall – so they must be quick on their feet!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/698B5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tetra-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1C883","slug":"heist-of-the-century","title":"Heist of the century","description":"Noob found a huge diamond while fighting a black dragon. But rainbow friends felt that it was unfair that it belongs only to him, and decided to kidnap him.\n\nThe game consists of 6 chapters where you have to escape from prison, visit a haunted house and even become a bank robber.\n\nThere is also an arena mode where you have to fight zombies and defeat their king!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1C883/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heist-of-the-century/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SZ3B3","slug":"suburbs-zombie-driving","title":"Suburbs Zombie Driving","description":"Suburbs Zombie Driving is an action packed driving game where you mission is to drive across the suburbs and crush the given amount of zombies on each level in order to win and unlock lots of different cars.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SZ3B3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/suburbs-zombie-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84687","slug":"pretty-tiles","title":"Pretty Tiles","description":"In this HTML5 match puzzle game you should tap on three tiles with the same shapes to destroy them. If you match three labeled tiles in the specified time you’ll get a reward. You have three options that can help you:\n- Undo your move\n- Shuffle Tiles\n- Match a group of tiles","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84687/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pretty-tiles/embed?sid=1","plays":39722,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"74U3E","slug":"sand-sort-puzzle","title":"Sand Sort Puzzle","description":"In this game, you should tap on the glasses to pour the same-colored sand into different glasses and sort them. By filling a glass with one color, a flower will grow on that glass. So this is a challenging game for your brain! Also, you can restart the level whenever you get stuck in the puzzle game. You will collect coins by passing each level and there is a shop where you can buy new glasses with your coins.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/74U3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sand-sort-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87868","slug":"people-onet","title":"People Onet","description":"In this puzzle game, the goal is to remove all tiles by connecting pairs of matching tiles. Connect the same tiles within 3 lines. Spend less time and connect farther tiles to get 3-star to unlock new cities.\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87868/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/people-onet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KDKUK","slug":"duckwak","title":"DuckWAK","description":"Are you ready for the adventure of 2 duck brothers? The adventures are very challenging and extremely scary. duck brothers need to survive. Help them and get them to the finish line. Help the duck brothers with your friend. Get the star and get super power.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KDKUK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duckwak/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"85YRR","slug":"burger-day","title":"Burger Day","description":"On Burger Day, customers order burger sandwiches… but these sandwiches are sometimes too long… Prepare customer orders and complete levels. Be careful not to get angry customers!! And prepare their burgers for them on time Are you ready for a burger day challenge? So start…","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/85YRR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/burger-day/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"BLAA3","slug":"ball-red-legacy","title":"Ball Red Legacy","description":"ball red legacy is game arcade","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BLAA3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-red-legacy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8M1U5","slug":"wuggymissy-change","title":"WuggyMissy Change","description":"Have you ever escaped from a forest with monsters before? yes you need to collect stars in this forest. Help sisters Wuggy and Missy on their adventure in the forest. join the adventure. Protect yourself from dangers in your adventures. How many monsters are everywhere from dangers. be careful monsters can kill you. You have to reach the finish line in order. Remember time is running. If the time in the game runs out, you lose. You can play with 2 friends in turns or you can play alone. dont stop run get the stars and reach the finish line.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8M1U5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wuggymissy-change/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4M68L","slug":"jumper-ball","title":"Jumper Ball","description":"Train your reaction and attentiveness! Get on the platform in a short time!","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4M68L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumper-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L57Z9","slug":"fairy-puzzle","title":"Fairy Puzzle","description":"In the game, you can collect beautiful jigsaw puzzles from large pieces. Many levels with magical pictures for a relaxing holiday.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L57Z9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fairy-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TCE8N","slug":"remembering-selection","title":"Remembering Selection","description":"Simple memory game, where you need to avoid selecting the same animal again.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TCE8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/remembering-selection/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I110E","slug":"pizza-deliver","title":"Pizza Deliver","description":"A game about delivery, where you will have to avoid traffic (pedestrians and buses), pick up goods and return them in order to get money for the base.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I110E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pizza-deliver/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87I96","slug":"boxes-wizard-2","title":"Boxes Wizard 2","description":"Boxes Wizard 2 est la suite palpitante du jeu de plateforme en pixel art en 2D. Jouez en tant que sorcier avec des pouvoirs de téléportation et de poussée de boîtes dans 40 niveaux stimulants remplis de casse-têtes. Échangez de place avec les boîtes pour créer de nouveaux chemins et surmonter les obstacles.\nDes graphismes rétro inspirés et un gameplay immersif font de cette aventure un moment passionnant. Maîtrisez de nouvelles mécaniques, affrontez des défis plus difficiles et sortez victorieux en utilisant vos compétences magiques.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87I96/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boxes-wizard-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7E68O","slug":"somewhere","title":"Somewhere","description":"Navigate through 7 challenging levels filled with obstacles in this unique 1-bit 2D platform game. No enemies, only obstacles! Can you conquer them all?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7E68O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/somewhere/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40109","slug":"mahjong-deluxe","title":"Mahjong Deluxe","description":"Mahjong Deluxe est un jeu de mahjong gratuit basé sur un jeu classique chinois. Le but est d'enlever toutes les tuiles du plateau. Vous pouvez retirer que les paires libres.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board","classics","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40109/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":39152,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LR048","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-smiley","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Smiley","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LR048/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-smiley/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5EZJA","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-letter","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Letter","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5EZJA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CEIO1","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-number","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Number","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l`écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CEIO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-number/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"697OO","slug":"word-nerd","title":"Word Nerd","description":"Form words by tapping the letters. Each level requires a certain number of words to fill the progress bar. Buy special items in the shop to improve your performance. Tap special item to collect and tap letter to place item.\nFill the progress bar, before time is up, to score bonus points.\nForm long words to score combo points. Advance to the next level and unlock special items.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/697OO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/word-nerd/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KR684","slug":"park-the-beetle","title":"Park the Beetle","description":"Hop on the driver’s seat and drive your car to a designated parking spot.\nAvoid objects and other cars at all costs or you will lose.\nA lot of different cars, incredibly realistic graphics, interesting levels, and other cool things are waiting for you in this addicting game.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KR684/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/park-the-beetle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YKIRO","slug":"parking-toy-story","title":"Parking Toy Story","description":"There is the chaos and mess in the children room, the toys are scattered on the floor. Your goal is to rule the toy car and to park it into the appropriate place. Driving around the toys find the right road in the labyrinth. However be in hurry as the time is limited as at any moment the parents can come in and scold the boy for the untidy room. The game has pleasant graphics and excellent gameplay","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YKIRO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parking-toy-story/embed?sid=1","plays":39710,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RK66","slug":"skull-racer","title":"Skull Racer","description":"Skull Racer is fun addictive monster car game. In this game you have to cross all the hurdles to reach your destination.\nCollect much more coins you can. Use arrow keys to play the game.","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RK66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skull-racer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PS001","slug":"super-footpool","title":"Super Footpool","description":"Super Footpool is a billiard-like soccer game. You’ll have to set the angle and power to shoot the ball inside the goal.\nYou’ll better be fast or else the AI will beat you to it!\nYou can win the World Cup!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PS001/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-footpool/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UE2RE","slug":"super-oscar","title":"Super Oscar","description":"Super Oscar is finally back and he isn't alone!\nHe has brought 3 new friends to complete all worlds.\n§ 6 beautiful worlds(more coming soon)\n§ 35 awesome levels(more coming soon)\n§ 50+ different enemies\n§ 4 different characters","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UE2RE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-oscar/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1WGER","slug":"t-rex-running-black-and-white","title":"T-Rex Running Black and White","description":"T-Rex Running is a game of adventure and very entertaining. The T-Rex has to run, but you need to overcome many traps, such as cacti and pterodactyls. See how many obstacles you can avoid like cactus and ducks under flying pterodactyls as your T-Rex runs faster and faster. The goal is to help T-Rex run his way by jumping over cacti, pterodactyls, and more.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1WGER/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/t-rex-running-black-and-white/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6L3AI","slug":"world-in-danger-earth-attack","title":"World in Danger Earth Attack","description":"The world is in danger and under attack! Evil planets invade the Solar System and want to destroy the Earth. But the Earth will attack! And the Earth will not be alone, the moon will be together in this battle.\nHelp to rotate the Planet Earth to shoot the enemy planets and destroy them before they can destroy the Earth. There are many weapons, evolve, increase its speed, and survive to crash all planets!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6L3AI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-in-danger-earth-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ITTT","slug":"tutti-frutti","title":"Tutti Frutti","description":"Tap to place your Fruits before your time is up.\nConnect five fruits vertically, horizontally or diagonally to win.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ITTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tutti-frutti/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KR466","slug":"tricky-trees","title":"Tricky Trees","description":"As the name says, Tricky Trees is an easy-to-learn but hard-to-master Match-3 game in the best tradition of the genre. You not only need to match the right items but also beat the time which can indeed become very tricky but also pretty addictive.\nYour task is to match three or more fruits in a row and collect the number of fruits depending on the goal each level is giving to you! Good Luck and lots of fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KR466/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tricky-trees/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ME4Y2","slug":"sweety-mania","title":"Sweety Mania","description":"Sweety Mania is a super addictive Match-3-Game. Collect all the ingredients listed at the top of the screen by clearing lines of 3 or more of the same ingredients in a row.\nBut be careful: You need to finish the level before the 2-minute timer runs out. Can you beat the clock and become the Sweety Mania champion?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ME4Y2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweety-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NETS6","slug":"snowball-the-cat-christmas-fun","title":"Snowball The Cat Christmas Fun","description":"Welcome to the difficult and distant world of the brave Snowball the Cat. will start your adventure! In this Christmas fun game, Snowball the Cat will start your adventure! Snowball the Cat is lost and needs your help to find his way home in time for dinner. And on the way home, you need to catch all the birds and rats of their world. Find the key and go through the door that leads to a new level!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NETS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowball-the-cat-christmas-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1","slug":"2048","title":"2048","description":"Dans cette version HTML5 du célèbre 2048, utilisez les touches fléchées pour déplacer les tuiles. Lorsque deux tuiles avec le même chiffre se touchent, elles fusionnent. Atteignez le nombre 2048 pour gagner!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048/embed?sid=1","plays":38171,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ITTTN","slug":"turbo-dismounting","title":"Turbo Dismounting","description":"Turbo Dismounting Stickman game","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ITTTN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/turbo-dismounting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CIIPR","slug":"classic-limo-car-parking","title":"Classic Limo Car Parking","description":"Classic Limo Car Parking is an awesome and unique driving game in which you must test your parking and driving skills in a series of car parks! You must hop into your vehicle and race around the parking lots carefully and avoid taking any damage. Follow the markers and head for your designated parking space!\nThe graphics are realistic and the driving controls are easy to pick up. For each different parking challenge you complete, you earn cash. You can use this cash to purchase awesome upgrades for your vehicle and customize it to your liking! Can you complete every challenge and prove your parking skill?\n\nControl :-\nWASD or arrow key To drive car.\nUse spacebar for hand brake","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CIIPR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-limo-car-parking/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7888F","slug":"free-birds","title":"Free Birds","description":"Free birds is a casual puzzle game with two modes: Leveled and endless.\nIn this game, birds are trapped in cages, and you must use a bow and arrows to set them free. Using your aim and arrow power, you must shoot the cage’s rope holding the birds to free them and pass each level. The Leveled mode of the game includes several stages (between 2 and 5), while in the endless mode, the player starts with five lives (hearts), and for each unsuccessful shot, they lose a life. The game will continue as long as the player has a life.  There are also items in the game known as extra arrows that help you progress through the levels.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7888F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/free-birds/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EUE1S","slug":"bubble-up-endless","title":"Bubble Up Endless","description":"Your goal is to destroy balls that are the same color and clear rows. Throughout the game, you’ll come across numerous items known as boosters that will help you progress through the levels. The bomb, rocket, rainbow, and lightning boosters all fall within this category.\nAs you go through the game, the ball arrangement becomes more complicated, and the number and distribution of the same colored balls increase. Enjoy!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EUE1S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-up-endless/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6U8B3","slug":"bubble-up","title":"Bubble Up","description":"Your goal in this game is to destroy balls that are the same color and clear rows. Throughout the game, you’ll come across numerous items known as boosters that will help you progress through the levels. The bomb, rocket, rainbow, and lightning boosters all fall within this category. As you go through the game, the ball arrangement becomes more complicated, and the number and distribution of the same colored balls increase. In some levels, you also need to collect a set amount of gems rather than bursting the balls. Bubble Shooter uses cheerful colors and rhythmic music to make it enjoyable for players of all ages.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6U8B3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6II68","slug":"bottle-flip","title":"Bottle Flip","description":"Bottle Flip is an action-casual game in which players must tap and hold to land the bottle on the platforms in front of them. You must prevent the bottle from hitting the ground, or else you will lose. It has two modes: Endless and levels mode. Check out the shop to unlock levels mode.\n\nThe objective is to collect more points. This game has got an infinite number of levels, and its music is upbeat and exciting. This game also features two visual modes, Grayscale and Pixelate.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6II68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bottle-flip/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I8Y86","slug":"blastify-2","title":"Blastify 2","description":"Blastify 2 is a funny and lovely tap-to-blast puzzle game. It's easy to play, but with plenty of fun and surprise. Just tap on the same color blocks to crush them. There are some targets in each level that you need to collect! There is a nice booster system, which supports you to solve any problem you meet in the game.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I8Y86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blastify-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OIIOS","slug":"klondike-solitaire-paradise","title":"Klondike Solitaire Paradise","description":"Klondike Solitaire","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OIIOS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/klondike-solitaire-paradise/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O7P6O","slug":"mechloop","title":"MechLoop","description":"Youve never played a platform game like this before. Its a game where you have to use your mind completely. use your mind! You have to use your brain. There are different intelligence levels and different intelligence difficulties in each section. Sometimes the roads are easy, sometimes the roads are very difficult. You have to pass many challenges to overcome the obstacles on the roads. Sometimes the button may not work with one touch. Sometimes you have to touch many times. sometimes the wall is just visible but never stops. Everything is up to your brain power.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O7P6O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mechloop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LI1U1","slug":"logic-puzzle","title":"Logic Puzzle","description":"A fun logical puzzle game for kids, great for kids to exercise their logical thinking. Try to make the maximum score of correct answers. Turn on timer mode, and try to solve the puzzles before time runs out.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LI1U1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/logic-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T1NE9","slug":"find-the-letter","title":"Find The Letter","description":"Learn the letters in this fun game. Stimulate players’ attention and learning.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T1NE9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-letter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"K1ARE","slug":"skibidi-head-roll","title":"Skibidi Head Roll","description":"In \"Skibidi: Head Roll\" you will overcome difficulties and various obstacles, strategically planning each move to successfully complete each level.\n\nImmerse yourself in fascinating puzzles that require skill, logical thinking and attention to detail. \n\nGo through a variety of different levels of the exciting game \"Skibidi: Head Roll\" with increasing difficulty. Each level presents unique puzzles that challenge your creative thinking. \n\nDevelop an effective strategy by analyzing the location of obstacles and optimizing your moves to successfully reach the toilet.\n\nAre you ready to become the savior of Scooby Doo and help him get to the toilet? Embark on an exciting journey through puzzles and prove your dexterity and logical thinking in the game \"Skibidi: Head Roll\" now!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/K1ARE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-head-roll/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"882LC","slug":"wordle-classic","title":"Wordle Classic","description":"This is a real yoga for the brain, meditation for the mind and vocabulary development — and all this in an easily accessible game that can be played at any age!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/882LC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wordle-classic/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NWAOW","slug":"world-countries-and-capitals","title":"World Countries and Capitals","description":"Test your knowledge of the names of the capitals of states on our planet. Raise your level of knowledge. It's easy with the \"World Countries and Capitals\" quiz!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NWAOW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-countries-and-capitals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"41911","slug":"fruitmas","title":"Fruitmas","description":"Slice fruit, don’t slice bombs and become a master of slicing fruits. That is all you need to know to get started with Fruitmas!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/41911/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruitmas/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"81EC6","slug":"centipede","title":"Centipede","description":"Centipede is a fixed shooter arcade game. The primary objective is to shoot all the segments of a centipede that winds down the playing field","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/81EC6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/centipede/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"H0CNE","slug":"bowling-challenge","title":"Bowling Challenge","description":"There’s a challenge on each level, and you should knock down all the bowling pins with the ball. Also, you can play the endless mode and make high scores by hitting all the bowling pins and don’t let them pass the line.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H0CNE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bowling-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0L8OE","slug":"soccer-challenge","title":"Soccer Challenge","description":"Soccer Challenge is a point-and-shoot football game. To progress, you must stand behind the ball in a penalty-like mode and beat the goalkeeper. With each stage you pass, the difficulty increases. It seems easy, doesn’t it? We’re confident it’s more challenging than you think! That’s why we named it the Soccer Challenge!","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0L8OE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AE6B8","slug":"dd-basketball-challenge","title":"DD Basketball Challenge","description":"Hit the basket and do the challenges to win the levels. It all depends on your skills! A moving basket may be an obstacle. There is an endless mode for you to play, too. So, you can play it in more fun ways and enjoy the game.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AE6B8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basketballchallenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T2A68","slug":"pro-basket","title":"Pro Basket","description":"Very Addictive and fun Basket game\n§ Tap and drag the angle to aim, release to shoot. Use your points in the shop to buy\n§ special FEATURES and improve your score. Unlock new items with special achievements. Have fun...","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T2A68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pro-basket/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C1O1A","slug":"snowball-the-cat-catch-and-go","title":"Snowball The Cat Catch and Go","description":"Start your adventure in this difficult and distant world of the brave Snowball the Cat! Your task is to help Snowball the Cat as he collects the keys to unlock new worlds. Jump over obstacles and rescue mice and birds.\nThere's no way to stop moving on this planet! Once he starts running, he will not stop. You must catch all the birds and rats of their world; each level is more difficult than the other. Good luck!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C1O1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snowball-the-cat-catch-and-go/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HE166","slug":"scary-halloween-spooky-nights","title":"Scary Halloween Spooky Nights","description":"Scary Halloween: Spooky Nights is a game in a spooky Halloween setting that can be enjoyed all over the year. With fantastic graphics and creepy music, you will never get enough of this game!\nSwitch and swap identical symbols in order to align them and to reach the goal in each level. But be careful, the time is running short, and things can get scary fast","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HE166/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/scary-halloween-spooky-nights/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9T1N8","slug":"santa-christmas-mania","title":"Santa Christmas Mania","description":"Your mission is to helpSanta pack up all the gifts for the children.\nIn each level, Santa will request items to collect. Match 3 or more of each gift to collect the number requested.\nRemember, you need to be quick and get them all before your time runs out! Have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9T1N8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-christmas-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T446U","slug":"roulette","title":"Roulette","description":"The Classic roulette game is here. Choose your bet and spin,\nand see if you can blow the bank and get a real jackpot","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T446U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/roulette/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"89BCS","slug":"sports-jigsaw","title":"Sports Jigsaw","description":"Welcome to Sports Jigsaw Block Blitz! Our Sports Jigsaw Block Blitz Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Sports Jigsaw Block Blitz picture. With a wide variety of Sports Jigsaw Block Blitz images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Sports Jigsaw Block Blitz Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/89BCS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sports-jigsaw-block-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LABAS","slug":"pegasus-jigsaw-scramble","title":"Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble","description":"Welcome to Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble! Our Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble picture. With a wide variety of Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Pegasus Jigsaw Scramble Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LABAS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pegasus-jigsaw-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6MR6L","slug":"motorcycles-photo-image-scramble","title":"Motorcycles Photo Image Scramble","description":"Welcome to Motorcycles Photo Image Scramble, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Motorcycles Photo Image Scramble, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Motorcycles Photo Image Scramble and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6MR6L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motorcycles-photo-image-scramble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C4RO7","slug":"motor-racing-in-space","title":"Motor Racing in Space","description":"Are you ready for an action-packed journey in space? Collect diamonds and power up your engine while staying alive. You can also purchase new and faster engines with the diamonds you collect. Challenging and dangerous paths await you. Will you be able to reach the end of this 30-level motor riding adventure? Then start accelerating!","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C4RO7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/motor-racing-in-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5RA6R","slug":"the-floor-is-lava-run","title":"The Floor is Lava Run","description":"Welcome to the \"The Floor is Lava\" impossible run!\nJump and try to not fall into the lava or you will start from the beginning.\n30 coins = WIN , who is going to try this impossible run?\n\n@ale.tc\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5RA6R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-floor-is-lava-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OD45I","slug":"mirror-wizard","title":"Mirror Wizard","description":"Jump, avoid obstacles, and use your magic to flip sides.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OD45I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mirror-wizard/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I8856","slug":"adorable-girls-valentino-fashion","title":"Adorable Girls Valentino Fashion","description":"Welcome to Adorable Girls Valentino Fashion. Willow, Dee Dee, and Noah are the BFFs. They hear about a new contest, so they planned to try something different. Willow got an idea to try Valentino fashion trends. But they need some fashion tips to win the contest. Help them and have fun! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I8856/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adorable-girls-valentino-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E003","slug":"dungeon-chess","title":"Dungeon Chess","description":"$6b","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E003/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dungeon-chess/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4161I","slug":"zrist-dx","title":"Zrist DX","description":"Dodge endless obstacles while you get used to constantly shifting rules! Earn credits and buy new outfits!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4161I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zrist-dx/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"27868","slug":"black-hole-attack","title":"Black Hole Attack","description":"In the game \"Black Hole Attack\" your task is simple. You have to collect as much weaponry as possible using the Black Hole before time runs out. And stay focused: the more you collect, the more chances you have to fight the boss! Play now! ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/27868/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-hole-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AE1VI","slug":"save-the-earth-with-slaps","title":"Save The Earth With Slaps","description":"Destroy Missiles!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AE1VI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-earth-with-slaps/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8D67E","slug":"doge-man","title":"Doge-Man","description":"Casual game inspired to the classic Pac-Man with the amazing Doge","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8D67E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doge-man/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"26ON1","slug":"master-of-numbers","title":"Master of Numbers","description":"Add up the numbers as you move forward. You are waiting for pleasant visual sensations, calm meditative gameplay, the pleasure of passing. Relax now.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/26ON1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/master-of-numbers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ETI4I","slug":"skibidi-toilet-search","title":"Skibidi Toilet search","description":"Skibidi: Toilet Search is a game about drawing a path for each Skibidi to its final point - the Toilet!\n\nFind the most optimal path and draw it, but make sure that the paths of both Skibidi do not coincide, otherwise they will fight and the level will be lost!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ETI4I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skibidi-toilet-search/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M98MY","slug":"memorybot","title":"Memorybot","description":"Play this classic memory card game with beatifully illustrated cards. Choose how many cards you want to play with and start the game trying to match all the cards as fast as you can. Do your best and make the highest score!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M98MY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/memorybot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y80GN","slug":"guilty-sniper","title":"Guilty Sniper","description":"Guilty Sniper is a game where you have to recognize and eliminate the targets as fast as you can. Do not worry about the causalities but pay attention to your ammunitions! They won't last forever! Try your best and kill all the targets before the time runs out!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y80GN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guilty-sniper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6LO89","slug":"steve-and-alex-skibidi-toilet","title":"Steve and Alex Skibidi Toilet","description":"The skibidi toilet monster is chasing you need to escape urgently hey steve and alex run save yourself. While the monster is chasing you, collect the emeralds you need to collect, then you can buy yourself a costume with them. If the monster catches you, you lose. you should never get caught by the beast.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6LO89/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-and-alex-skibidi-toilet/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SA18S","slug":"rise-of-lava","title":"Rise of Lava","description":"hey lava is rising you need to escape urgently! Get ready with your friend and start running. The lava is constantly rising, so constantly jump to higher ground. dont forget to collect the emeralds you need them emeralds will get you a costume. Go to the high ground with your friend, none of you should die. escape the lava without dying.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SA18S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rise-of-lava/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"291R4","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-bouquet-flowers","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Bouquet flowers","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments sous la forme de segments de cercle. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/291R4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-bouquet-flowers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ML1E0","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-cartoon","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Cartoon","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments sous la forme de segments de cercle. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ML1E0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-cartoon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z8IDN","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-fruits","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Fruits","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments sous la forme de segments de cercle. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z8IDN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-fruits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SZ8WN","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-landscape","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle 2 - Assemble Landscape","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments sous la forme de segments de cercle. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l`écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SZ8WN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-2-assemble-landscape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58EIL","slug":"recoil-arena-1vs1","title":"Recoil Arena 1VS1","description":"youve seen recoil guys kill monsters before. Now they are fighting among themselves. enemies for each other. the guys recoil have joined the arena and the one with the most kills wins. Experience the thrill of killing in different maps to the fullest. Shoot and kill each other by playing with your friend. Whichever of you kills the most wins. may the best win.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58EIL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/recoil-arena-1vs1/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4744H","slug":"bullhead-2","title":"Bullhead 2","description":"Welcome to bullhead 2, have fun in this fantastic game where you have to try to avoid obstacles and accumulate points and bestscores, what are you waiting for?? go play bullhead 2 now and have fun!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4744H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullhead-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J7607","slug":"jump-and-jump","title":"Jump and Jump","description":"run and jump and catch the ball without falling, your high score remains fixed","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J7607/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-and-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7LEF3","slug":"the-flipper","title":"The Flipper","description":"welcome to the game, The Flipper , pinball with a different method than the usual pinball machine, here you have to hit the red ball within the tot .. seconds ,,, and beware of the bombs that pop up from time to time","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7LEF3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-flipper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TAAB5","slug":"escape-laboratory-1","title":"Escape Laboratory 1","description":"Welcome to Escape Laboratory 1, enjoy this fantastic game facing all the difficulties and obstacles to try to escape from the laboratory, what are you waiting for? go play Escape Laboratory 1 now and have fun!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TAAB5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/escape-laboratory-1/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IGE16","slug":"right-and-left","title":"Right and Left","description":"welcome to the game jump left and right , you have to jump left and right while avoiding the missiles, the game records the highest score","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IGE16/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/right-and-left/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2DR1E","slug":"yo-defender","title":"Yo Defender","description":"welcome to yodefende, have fun in this game by shooting enemy ships and accumulating points, what are you waiting for?? go play yodefende and have fun!!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2DR1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yo-defender/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"856I6","slug":"charlie","title":"Charlie","description":"Welcome to Charlie, have fun in this game where you have to overcome obstacles and levels, what are you waiting for go play now and fun will be guaranteed!!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/856I6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/charlie/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RGNTM","slug":"gorilla-tag-drag-and-drop-game","title":"Gorilla Tag Drag And Drop Game","description":"$6c","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RGNTM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gorilla-tag-drag-and-drop-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AM6LE","slug":"little-mermaid","title":"Little Mermaid","description":"Little Mermaid Endless Runner, you play as the Little Mermaid, as she swims through the ocean collecting pearls. You must avoid obstacles such as rocks, jellyfish, and sharks, and collect as many pearls as possible. The longer you swim, the faster the ocean currents become, making it more difficult to avoid obstacles.","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AM6LE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-mermaid/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3OS3T","slug":"skateboard-challenges","title":"Skateboard Challenges","description":"Skateboard Challenges is a fast-paced and challenging game that will test players' skills and reflexes. The game features a variety of levels, each with its own set of challenges. Players must complete these challenges in order to progress to the next level.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3OS3T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skateboard-challenges/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A17CD","slug":"dark-space","title":"Dark Space","description":"dark space is game strategy","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A17CD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dark-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S535T","slug":"battle-space-legacy","title":"Battle Space Legacy","description":"battle space legacy is game strategy 2023","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S535T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battle-space-legacy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J382L","slug":"mahjong-royal","title":"Mahjong Royal","description":"Commencez votre nouveau casse-tête oriental favori. Ce classique du Mahjong vous captivera et vous incitera à jouer. Vous deviendrez un maître en un rien de temps.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J382L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-royal/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O4H3D","slug":"sumikko-gurashi","title":"Sumikko Gurashi","description":"$6d","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O4H3D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sumikko-gurashi-drag-and-drop-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6E6BE","slug":"heroes-head-ball","title":"Heroes Head Ball","description":"Have you ever seen him play football with his head? yes, its a football game where you score goals with your head. are you up for head football? Score a goal in head soccer with your friend and one of you wins. You have to score the most goals to win. You can play with your friend or you can play with artificial intelligence. All you have to do is choose 1 of 10 characters and start the match.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6E6BE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/heroes-head-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"40WY7","slug":"how-many","title":"How Many","description":"A fun educational game for children learning to count, about numbers or even for children to exercise counting and attention.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/40WY7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/how-many/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8HER7","slug":"find-the-number","title":"Find The Number","description":"In this fun game you must find the numbers that the game asks for. Play timer mode and try not to lose. Compare the results of the end game with your friends. Education and fun, in one place.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8HER7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-number/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3D8TK","slug":"desert-attack","title":"Desert Attack","description":"Small arcade game that allow you to become a pilot of A10 and destroy enemies using GAU8. Controls are simple, WASD - move, space - shoot, F - drop a bomb. Have a nice flight! \n\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3D8TK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/desert-attack/embed?sid=1","plays":39573,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EKMD","slug":"word-maker","title":"Word Maker","description":"\"Word Maker\" is a game that will captivate you with its fascination and help you develop your vocabulary. Make words from syllables and go through 500 levels, getting daily bonuses for additional hints. Learn interesting facts about each word and expand your horizons. Start playing right now and immerse yourself in the world of verbal adventures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EKMD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/word-maker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1A7T","slug":"little-panda-match-3","title":"Little Panda Match 3","description":"petit panda est livré avec un autre jeu unique amusant Treasure Hunters correspondant Gems avec bébé chinois panda match 3 thème qui vous emmènera à l’aventure bébé panda voyage. Voyagez à différents niveaux et jouez avec des diamants, des pierres précieuses et des bijoux en associant trois propriétés similaires ou plus. Associez cinq bijoux en un seul mouvement et créez des gemmes magiques qui agissent comme une rangée ou une colonne-breakers pour compléter les niveaux difficiles rapidement.\n\nJewel match 3 diamants classiques ou plus similaires en un seul mouvement pour collecter et remplir la boîte au trésor. Résoudre l’unique\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1A7T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/little-panda-match3/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Y0S8Y","slug":"beehive-yourself","title":"Beehive Yourself","description":"Guide the little Bee with your mouse cursor to the hive, but beware as she may run straight into walls and hurt herself. Try to collect stars for the perfect finish.\n\nControls: Mouse","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Y0S8Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/beehive-yourself/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TR4AT","slug":"robot-band","title":"Robot Band","description":"If you are tired of playing games that are stressful or too hard, then take your time and relax with \"Robot Band\". Listen to this band of robots playing its techno music in Trastevere, the heart of Rome. Move the sliders to change colors, music speed, daytime and so on and touch the robots to make them play.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TR4AT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-band/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NBREF","slug":"robot-band-find-the-differences","title":"Robot Band - Find the differences","description":"Spot all the differences you can find in the pictures of these lively robots playing their instruments and do it fast!\nTry to find all the differences in each picture before the time runs out. Be careful though: Do not touch the screen randomly trying to catch all the differences this way!\nIf you touch the screen 5 times without touching one of the differences is game over!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NBREF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robot-band-find-the-differences/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9A3D8","slug":"bullhead","title":"Bullhead","description":"Welcome to bullhead, have fun in this fantastic game where you have to try to avoid obstacles and accumulate points and bestscores, what are you waiting for?? go play bullhead now and have fun!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9A3D8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bullhead/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ATA1","slug":"catch-the-apple","title":"Catch the Apple","description":"Catch all the apple!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ATA1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-the-apple/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A681A","slug":"base-five","title":"Base Five","description":"In the game \"Base Five\" you have to show your logic and mathematical abilities to form numbers based on base 5.\nYou will be given a 3x4 grid in which you need to fill the cells with randomly generated numbers.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A681A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/base-five/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WRO8R","slug":"princess-goldsword-and-the-land-of-water","title":"Princess Goldsword and the Land of Water","description":"In a world of magic in a far away land, there is an island where Trinks lives a very friendly creature, Princess Goldsword. They have the loyalty of the courageous Princess. It protects from all dangers. But something terrible has happened! The monsters from the waters stole all the treasures of Trinks. And worse, stolen children also! The task is to help Princess Goldsword recover the stolen treasures while facing monsters, traps, and challenges of all sizes.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WRO8R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-goldsword-and-the-land-of-water/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J6P8J","slug":"jumper-jam-2","title":"Jumper Jam 2","description":"Jumper Jam 2 is an endless jumping game. jump on the platforms and create your highest score! Tap or mouse click to jump","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J6P8J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jumper-jam-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P4E37","slug":"panda-jewels","title":"Panda Jewels","description":"Become a master of collecting amazing jewels. Loads of levels and\nexcitement during the game. Hours of fun and addictive game play.\nTap and drag items and match 3 or more items to blast them.\nThe faster you reach the goal, the more points you receive.\nUse the special rewards that appear to blast items away faster.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P4E37/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/panda-jewels/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UY77M","slug":"frogman-vs-maskguy","title":"Frogman vs Maskguy","description":"Frogman and maskguy is a html5 arcade game, compete with your opponent to pick fruit and get the highest score be careful don't hit the falling cubes or score decrease!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UY77M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frogman-and-maskguy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4HIO1","slug":"alien-spaceship-shooter","title":"Alien Spaceship Shooter","description":"Alien spaceship shooter is an html5 spaceshooter game, collect all item to get sore and destroy alien spaceship ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4HIO1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-spaceship-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7577O","slug":"mouse-pop","title":"Mouse Pop","description":"Pop Pop. Tap and swipe bubbles to switch places. Match 3 or more bubbles to blast them away. The faster you reach the target, the more points you receive.\nDuring the game, you will receive special bonus features. Use them wisely, since you don’t have unlimited moves.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7577O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mouse-pop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N5NB7","slug":"arabian-tictactoe","title":"Arabian TicTacToe","description":"arabian tic tac toe is an html5  Noughts and Crosses game, make horizontal, vertically, or diagonal match","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N5NB7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arabian-tictactoe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M5HG1","slug":"mahjong-farm","title":"Mahjong Farm","description":"Amazing and fun Mahjong Farm Style game. Match 2 tiles to clear them from the deck. You can only match tiles that are on top of a stack. Match all the tiles before the time runs out to clear the level. Good Luck...","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M5HG1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong-farm/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I94SS","slug":"classic-yatzy","title":"Classic Yatzy","description":"Roll the dice and collect your scores.\nYou can reroll up to two times and hold any dice you want to keep.\nWhen done, choose your score box to enter your points or place a zero, if you don’t have a match.\nIf the sum of the upper section is 63 or more, you receive 50 bonus points. ","category":"Stratégie","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I94SS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-yatzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7547","slug":"candy-xmas","title":"Candy Xmas","description":"Xmas is coming. Santa need candys for childrens. Help Santa to collect more candys to all childrens but be carefull, snow Yeti keep that candys for them.\nGood luck!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7547/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-xmas/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KR8AA","slug":"kids-coloring-game","title":"Kids Coloring Game","description":"kids coloring game is a html5 coloring game, perfect for kids to play and hone their skills","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KR8AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-coloring-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I6R01","slug":"kids-memory-game","title":"Kids Memory Game","description":"games for young children to strengthen memory\n\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I6R01/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-memory-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAA9A","slug":"blast-mania","title":"Blast Mania","description":"You’ll definitely have a blast with this match 3 puzzle game.\nQuickly link together all of the different elements.\nCan you form some unique connections between each one of the fire, wind, and water icons?","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAA9A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blast-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3NIO7","slug":"shooting-block","title":"Shooting Block","description":"shooting block is an html5 slingshoot game, shoot the block and destroy collect star to earn score","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3NIO7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/shooting-block/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A7ZU5","slug":"dead-zone-adventure","title":"Dead Zone Adventure","description":"Dead Zone Adventure features dark scary asylum where your mission is to search for given amount of crystals in order to successfully complete complete each level and try to avoid deadly zombies encounters in order to survive.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A7ZU5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dead-zone-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87454","slug":"penny","title":"Penny","description":"Welcome to Penny, have fun in this fantastic game where you will have to face gravity and enemies on platforms to accumulate points and coins. What are you waiting for?? go play now and the fun will be guaranteed !!!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87454/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penny/embed?sid=1","plays":39818,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DLO1Y","slug":"indygirl-and-the-golden-skull","title":"Indygirl and the Golden Skull","description":"Welcome to the life of Indygirl where challenges and adventures are fun! The girl who loves to uncover hidden treasures and adventures. She now found the Golden Skull and now ready come and needs your help dig into the cave! Your task is help Indygirl in her journey to collect all the jewels and golds that are hidden in the cave. All the golden pieces and diamonds and jewelries from each level of this game, must be collected. But beware, danger and adventures are in,\nbut not in the same amount in all levels. Focus on getting gold! Run as fast as you can before that gigantic rock will run over you!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DLO1Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/indygirl-and-the-golden-skull/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I1I3N","slug":"i-scream-ice-cream-match3-fun","title":"I scream Ice Cream Match3 Fun","description":"Match as many ice creams as possible to get bigger more effective power ups including the rainbow Popsicle. You will be challenged with a new and much more difficult target as you proceed through the levels.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I1I3N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/i-scream-ice-cream-match3-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AV4EN","slug":"game-on-cat-vs-rats","title":"Game On Cat vs Rats!","description":"Get ready to help and take control of brave cats, and fight against their archenemy, the Rat King! It's causing problems and needs to be stopped; we don't know how a rat could grow this big. These cats are upset about the evil plans of the Rat King! With the use of a slingshot, they plan to reach the evil king and scratch its face! Your objective in this game is to complete each level by launching the cats toward the enemy to kill it.","category":"Action","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AV4EN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/game-on-cat-vs-rats/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4Y42U","slug":"flying-bubbles","title":"Flying Bubbles","description":"Aim and shoot of the red bubble. Destroy all bubbles and collect starts and coins for extra points. Collect special bonus items for excitement. Draw with your finger a line to avoid the red bubble to fly out of the bottom of the screen.\n100 levels of amazing fun. Good luck! ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4Y42U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flying-bubbles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LC79P","slug":"skull-picture-scramble-challenge","title":"Skull Picture Scramble Challenge","description":"Welcome to Skull Picture Scramble Challenge, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Skull Picture Scramble Challenge, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Skull Picture Scramble Challenge and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LC79P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skull-picture-scramble-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RWMT8","slug":"trees-jigsaw-triumph","title":"Trees Jigsaw Triumph","description":"Welcome to Trees Jigsaw Triumph! Our Trees Jigsaw Triumph Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Trees Jigsaw Triumph picture. With a wide variety of Trees Jigsaw Triumph images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Trees Jigsaw Triumph Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RWMT8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/trees-jigsaw-triumph/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IA9RM","slug":"queen-nefertiti-memory-match","title":"Queen Nefertiti Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Queen Nefertiti Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Queen Nefertiti Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Queen Nefertiti Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IA9RM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/queen-nefertiti-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IT45I","slug":"stickman-rope","title":"Stickman Rope","description":"Click to hook and make breathtaking jumps to reach your destination!\nBut make sure to not hit the white platforms, or you will bounce further from your destination.\n\nIn this game you will have to swing from hook to hook to reach the end of the level: will you be able not hit anything?\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IT45I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickrope/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3HH56","slug":"noob-way-home","title":"Noob Way home","description":"Nubik is surrounded by hordes of zombies, how can he deal with them?\nHelp the nbik complete all the levels! Only you and your skill will help the nubik pass all the levels! Difficult tests await you, which not everyone can handle!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3HH56/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-way-home/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58RS6","slug":"rogue-survivors","title":"Rogue Survivors","description":"Embark on a thrilling adventure in Rogue Survive, a captivating game that combines the intensity of roguelike gameplay with the challenge of survival. Vanquish formidable enemies, and push your limits to survive as long as possible. Upgrade your character with unique attributes, unlock powerful abilities, and unlock new characters. Will you conquer the perils that await you in this immersive roguelike experience?","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58RS6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rogue-survivors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8E8OE","slug":"tower-defense-zombies","title":"Tower Defense Zombies","description":"Préparez-vous à affronter des hordes de zombies qui ne pensent qu'à manger des cerveaux ! Utilisez votre cerveau contre eux et construisez vos défenses. Créez des tours de destruction massive de zombies pour affronter divers ennemis.\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8E8OE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-defense-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4LH3T","slug":"puzzle-math","title":"Puzzle Math","description":"Puzzle Math is a fun game where you exercise your knowledge of mathematics and still have fun revealing various puzzles according to the right answers. Education and fun in one place.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4LH3T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-math/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TNR66","slug":"dont-forget","title":"Dont Forget","description":"“Don’t Forget” is a logical thinking game where the player needs to have a good memory to remember the sequence shown and repeat it.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TNR66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dont-forget/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OHOA6","slug":"math-crossword","title":"Math Crossword","description":"A crossword and math game, perfect for learning and exercising your math skills.\nFun and education in one place.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OHOA6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/math-crossword/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3YC91","slug":"find-the-crypto","title":"Find The Crypto","description":"“Find the crypto” is a THEMED game about cryptocurrencies, you don’t earn cryptos by playing it, but it attracts many visitors to your site and downloads with this game, as it is a subject that is on the rise and it is a fun game for those who want to start in the crypto world or just have fun.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3YC91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-crypto/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"371AE","slug":"the-power-of-math","title":"The Power Of Math","description":"Choose your character in this fun game and use the power of math to defeat the monster.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/371AE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-power-of-math/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65C6C","slug":"space-rancher","title":"Space Rancher","description":"Space Rancher is a procedural,arcade game! Enjoy!","category":"Arcade","tags":["classics","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65C6C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-rancher/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"107O2","slug":"puppy-coloring-book","title":"Puppy Coloring Book","description":"Puppy Coloring Book For Kids is a painting, drawing and coloring tool for kids!\nPick your colors and start drawing and painting with your finger when done. Kids will enjoy painting using theirs creative ideas.\nHave fun using this great kids paint app.\nKey Features:\n-Really simple!\n-Really addictive!\n-Really fun!\n-Over 40 objects to color!\n-its a baby quite game!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/107O2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puppy-coloring-book/embed?sid=1","plays":39818,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HDDGE","slug":"sliding-tim-way-to-home","title":"Sliding Tim - Way to home","description":"Adventure game based on completing a difficult path. You play as the hero Tim. \nHe was far from home and he needed help to run back. But the path ahead is not easy, along the way you have to overcome many different obstacles, you will need to go through mud, desert and even red-hot lava. \nIt is important to keep the pace, to slip somewhere, and to slow down in time. At first glance, a simple task can turn into a failure, because with each new step, unpredictable routes await you. ","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HDDGE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sliding-tim-way-to-home/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O65TR","slug":"free-cell-solitaire","title":"Free Cell Solitaire","description":"The object of the game is to build the four HomeCells up in ascending suit sequence from Ace to King. e.g. with cards of identical suit.\nThe card at the end of each tableau column is available for play. You can move it to an empty FreeCell at any time to release the card beneath.","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O65TR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/free-cell-solitaire/embed?sid=1","plays":39779,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P81P1","slug":"flappycat-crazy-steampunk","title":"FlappyCat Crazy Steampunk","description":"The Crazy Steampunk FlappyCat is back again and is on a BIG adventure - this time he needs your help to rocket his way through a crazy steampunk world. In this exciting game of skill, your task is to help FlappyCat fly through the obstacles with his super amazing jetpack. Do you have the necessary flying skills to help this cat navigate the most dangerous flight path in the world?","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P81P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappycat-crazy-steampunk/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1CLPY","slug":"flappycat-crazy-copters","title":"FlappyCat Crazy Copters","description":"FlappyCat wants to fly up into the sky... as far as he can go. But\nunfortunately, Diego, the dastardly dog wants to make things more difficult for him. By making flight a very challenging one he's placed\nsome terrible floating obstacles on the way. Your goal in this game is to guide Flappy the Cat as he flies into the air. Are you ready to take this adventure challenge and try to fly as high as possible?! How high can you go? ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1CLPY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappycat-crazy-copters/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I9Z1S","slug":"flappycat-crazy-christmas","title":"FlappyCat Crazy Christmas","description":"FlappyCat is all dressed up and back for Christmas. Now things have\nbecome more difficult, he has a sleigh and reindeer with him. The goal is to use perfect timing and quick reflexes to guide FlappyCat through the obstacles. Help FlappyCat zoom through the candy canes and earn the highest score!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I9Z1S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappycat-crazy-christmas/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0I8F6","slug":"flamingo-bingo","title":"Flamingo Bingo","description":"Play Flamingo Bingo for hours of fun and entertainment. You can play for free and win coins and tickets to play 2-4 cards at the same time. Purchase special features to help increase your winnings in your group of players. Find and use the keys to complete your collections. Feel lucky? Join the game now!","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0I8F6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flamingo-bingo/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7036A","slug":"farm-dream","title":"Farm Dream","description":"You are not in a dream. You are just playing a fun and cool game called Farm Dream. Hours of fun and very addictive. Enjoy. Tap and drag items and match 3 or more items to blast them. The faster you reach the goal, the more points you receive. Use the special rewards that appear to blast items away faster.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7036A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/farm-dream/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5N6IN","slug":"dressing-up-the-girl","title":"Dressing Up The Girl","description":"Girls want to be trendy, beautiful, and charming. Dressing Up The Girl is the best way to get exactly that! Let the girl find her own style and charm in this beautiful dress up game.Choose your favourite Items from the menu; there is lot of options including hair styles, eye colors, outfits and glasses. Once you have selected your best look, complete it with a dance scene in the disco!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5N6IN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dressing-up-the-girl/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AT4M9","slug":"cute-animals","title":"Cute Animals","description":"Tap and drag items and match 3 or more items to blast them. The faster you reach the goal, the more points you receive. Use the special rewards that appear to blast items away faster. As you move through the various levels you’ll have fun as you hear the satisfying pop of items with all the cute animals you can expect.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AT4M9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":39892,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EKOT8","slug":"crazy-cookies-match-mix","title":"Crazy Cookies Match & Mix","description":"We love Cookies! And this game is full of them, how great! Play your way through each yummy level by matching 3 or more of the same style of lovely cookies which will delight you with colorful effects.\nMatch cookies by three or more to make them disappear and always watch the clock that is ticking fast and faster","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EKOT8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-cookies-match-and-mix/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"64U60","slug":"crazy-christmas-fun","title":"Crazy Christmas Fun","description":"In this holiday Christmas adventure game, many balloons have invaded the North\nPole, and Santa must run to catch the gifts. But Santa changed his sleigh,\nand he is now fast and furious! He and his reindeer need your help! Your\ntask is to fly through the sky dodging obstacles and collecting gifts. Once\nyou reach the Christmas tree you will level up! Have Fun!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/64U60/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-christmas-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"94506","slug":"mini-chaos","title":"Mini Chaos","description":"Destroy the little bots and do your best score in this little arcade game ","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/94506/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mini-chaos/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4K41N","slug":"drunken-crane","title":"Drunken Crane","description":"This game is an action-puzzle game in which you carry a drunk uncle to a bench by the crane.\nUse the buttons on the right side of the screen to play by operating horizontally, down, and releasing.\nYou can enjoy it like a crane game.\nThere are 38 stages, so you can play without getting bored.\nIn addition to the bench, there will also be stages where you can make ridden a uncle on an elephant.\nA stage that uses the recoil of the trampoline will also appear.\nIf you clear all 38 stages with 3 stars, hidden stages will appear, so please challenge it.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4K41N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drunken-crane/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"I78OR","slug":"warrior-kingdom","title":"Warrior Kingdom","description":"Warrior Kingdom is an action RPG for one person. You will guide your character through the game, fighting enemies and completing tasks. The game includes a number of different weapons and armor, as well as spells and abilities. To battle the enemies and save the kingdom, you must employ all of your skills. \n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I78OR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/warrior-kingdom/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7K46D","slug":"kids-online-games","title":"Kids Online Games","description":"Kids online games can be a great way for children to have fun, learn new things, and develop their skills. When choosing online games for kids, it is important to consider the age appropriateness, educational value, and safety of the games. There are many websites that offer kids online games, so parents can easily find games that their children will enjoy.","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7K46D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-online-games/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87T68","slug":"kids-math-online","title":"Kids Math Online","description":"Kids Math Online is a Educational game that offers a variety of free online math games for kids of all ages. The games are designed to be fun and engaging, while also helping kids learn important math concepts.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87T68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kids-math-online/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5ON7","slug":"christmas-pong","title":"Christmas Pong","description":"Christmas Pong is an online ping-pong game that is similar to the classic game. \nLooking for a fun and festive way to celebrate Christmas this year? Why not try your hand at Christmas Pong, the online pong game that everyone is talking about? With exciting gameplay and beautiful Christmas-themed graphics, Christmas Pong is the perfect way to get into the holiday spirit! ","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5ON7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YS1SW","slug":"galaxy-wars","title":"Galaxy Wars","description":"In the 2D space shooter Galaxy Wars Alien Shooter, waves of alien attackers must be fought while controlling a spaceship. The game's levels come in a wide variety, and each one has its own unique challenges. You must use your skills and reflexes to ensure your life and the annihilation of the aliens.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YS1SW/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/galaxy-wars/embed?sid=1","plays":39874,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L993F","slug":"flappy-fish-journey","title":"Flappy Fish Journey","description":"Flappy Fish Journey is a fun and challenging game where you control a small fish as it swims through a series of obstacles. The goal of the game is to reach the end of the level without hitting any obstacles.\nTo control your fish, simply tap the screen to make it flap its fins. The faster you flap, the faster your fish will swim.  The obstacles in Flappy Fish Journey come in all shapes and sizes. There are rocks, seaweed, and even other fish. If you hit any of these obstacles, you will lose a life. Flappy Fish Journey is a great game for players of all ages. It is simple to learn, but challenging to master. If you are looking for a fun and challenging game to play, then Flappy Fish Journey is the perfect game for you.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L993F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-fish-journey/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"516S6","slug":"rocket-odyssey","title":"Rocket Odyssey","description":"Rocket Odyssey is a simple yet addictive game where you control a rocket ship as it flies through a series of obstacles. The goal of the game is to get as far as possible without crashing. The obstacles in the game include pipes, trees, and other objects.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/516S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rocket-odyssey/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D6SWO","slug":"retro-tower-defense","title":"Retro Tower Defense","description":"Retro Tower Defense is a classic tower defense game with a retro twist. In this game, you must use your strategic skills to place towers and defend your base from waves of enemies. The game features a variety of towers to choose from, each with its own unique abilities. You can also upgrade your towers to make them even more powerful. As you progress through the game, you will face increasingly difficult enemies. Will you have what it takes to defend your base and win the game?\nRetro Tower Defense is a fun and challenging tower defense game that is sure to test your strategic skills. If you are a fan of the tower defense genre, then you will definitely want to check out this game.\n\n","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D6SWO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/retro-tower-defense/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IM8SP","slug":"christmas-puzzle","title":"Christmas Puzzle","description":"Christmas Puzzle is an online game that you can play by yourself or with friends. It's a link game, which means that you need to connect at least three of the same Christmas-themed objects in order to score points. The game can be played on a computer or mobile device.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IM8SP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/christmas-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ITN68","slug":"fruit-chop-ninja","title":"Fruit Chop Ninja","description":"How many times can you slice these Fruits? Cut the sweet and delicious fruit.\nAll Blades and Dojos now have a unique effect on gameplay. Throw the knives to slicing the fruits! Just one slice to burst the specified fruits with limited time or blades! Cut various natural products without a moment's delay","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ITN68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"07BEL","slug":"brick-breaker-endless","title":"Brick Breaker Endless","description":"Fun filled Addictive Bricks breaker Game, \"Brick Breaker Endless\" is out with excitement and fun. This Challenging Breaking neon bricks with firing balls will blow out your stress. \n\nBreak as many bricks as possible and achieve high score. \nShoot the Bricks in proper angle to break more bricks and target power-ups to gain better scores.\n\nFeatures:\n- Endless Gameplay\n- Free to play\n- Neon colored tiles\n- Special Power Ups","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/07BEL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brick-breaker-endless/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"78U5J","slug":"colojump","title":"ColoJump","description":"Fun filled, addictive casual game. Tap to make the colored ball to overcome the obstacles and colored circles of each level, the color of your player must match the color of the obstacle to be able to cross it, you must have patience and good timing to achieve it.\n\nDon't try to jump on wrong color.\n\nHow to play ?\n\n* Tap and tap so the ball can pass the obstacles\n* You can only pass through the same color as your player\n* Patience and good timing are the keys to victory","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/78U5J/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/colojump/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"66Z0K","slug":"zikzak","title":"ZikZak","description":"Have fun with ball rolling on zig zag path in this ZikZak game.\nStay on the line and enjoy your exciting ride on zigzag path.\nAddictive, attractive exciting endless ball rolling game.\nWith ZigZak Curves, check how far and how fast you can go?\n\nSimple Game touch based fun filled game.\nEnjoy this exciting Ball runner game on this hyper casual Zikzak game.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/66Z0K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zikzak/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"67281","slug":"co-omets","title":"Co-omets","description":"Co-omets, ça veut dire quoi? Des comètes en Co-op à 4 bien sûr!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/67281/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/co-omets/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U4016","slug":"candy-rush-clicker","title":"Candy Rush Clicker","description":"candy rush\nAn idle game, where you have to collect candies\nhave fun","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U4016/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MBM15","slug":"merge-battler","title":"Merge Battler","description":"Merge Battler est un jeu de stratégie en temps réel cool et adapté à tous.\n\nLe but principal du jeu est de vaincre tous les ennemis en combinant vos guerriers ou vos mages. Combattez de multiples vagues d'ennemis dont la force augmentera à chaque niveau, ce ne sera donc pas facile.\n\nRéagissez et réfléchissez rapidement. Utilisez votre stratégie et vos tactiques pour gagner la bataille et passer au niveau suivant.\n\nCombattez le boss final en combinant toutes vos créatures ! À chaque étape de ce défi, des adversaires de plus en plus forts vous attendent ! Appliquez votre stratégie en temps réel et gagnez chaque bataille !\n\nDébloquez de nouvelles troupes plus puissantes en les combinant !\n\nSeul 1% des joueurs pourront débloquer tous les types de troupes et réussir tous les défis ⏩ Êtes-vous prêt ?","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MBM15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/merge-battler/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EC316","slug":"box-challenge","title":"Box Challenge","description":"Solve engaging puzzles and master the Box Challenge! Train your brain with this addictive game. The ultimate puzzle game that will put your problem-solving skills to the test! Prepare to embark on a captivating journey filled with challenging puzzles and addictive gameplay. \nIn the Box Challenge, your goal is simple yet intriguing: move the colored boxes to their designated target positions. Sounds easy, right? Think again! As you progress through the levels, the puzzles become increasingly complex, requiring strategic thinking and careful planning. Get ready to stretch your mental muscles and overcome each brain-teasing obstacle in your path.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EC316/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/box-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2TD8O","slug":"defuse-the-bombs","title":"Defuse the Bombs","description":"Welcome to the thrilling world of “Defuse the bombs”!\n\nGet ready for an addictive experience where your strategy and agility will be put to the test. In this puzzle game, your mission is to align colors on the 7×7 grid by sliding rows or columns to create perfect combinations.\n\nBut beware! Bombs are scattered throughout the board, and you need to defuse them before they reach ZERO. Starting with numbers at 50, each player move decreases their value by 1.\n\nThe challenge is to keep the countdown away from zero while scoring. Be quick, smart, and meticulous to destroy the bombs and achieve the highest score possible!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2TD8O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/defuse-the-bombs/embed?sid=1","plays":39811,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A6RM6","slug":"mathgrid-master","title":"MathGrid Master","description":"MathGrid Master is a challenging and enjoyable math game that will test your numerical skills and logical reasoning.\n\n• In a 9x9 grid, you must fill the horizontal, vertical, and diagonal tracks with correctly positioned numbers and appropriate mathematical operations.\n\n• Drag the numbers to the correct positions and solve the calculations to complete the grid.\n\n• But be careful, you have a limit of three hearts. If you make three mistakes, it's game over!\n\n• Challenge yourself with different levels of difficulty and become the true master of calculations!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A6RM6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mathgrid-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9B5J1","slug":"ninja-blocks","title":"Ninja Blocks","description":"Eliminate all the enemies to save the princess pixel!\nAngry Bird Mechanics.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9B5J1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-blocks/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6OPPK","slug":"stickman-rope-heroes","title":"Stickman Rope Heroes","description":"Have you ever seen a stickman throwing a web before? yes he is throwing net and trying to reach the finish line to fulfill his mission. Net and jump at all marked locations. Help him as a stickman superhero and network together. Reach the finish line without falling off the cliff in different difficulty levels.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6OPPK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-rope-heroes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LD77H","slug":"head-volley","title":"Head Volley","description":"Have you ever played head volleyball before? Now is the time to play head volleyball. You must win the volleyball match by fighting with your friend or by fighting with artificial intelligence. You should join this volleyball fun too. Play with different costumes and win this match. Its up to you to win the match. You can play for two players or single player.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LD77H/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/head-volley/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A9YR3","slug":"green-and-yellow-run","title":"Green and Yellow Run","description":"Are you ready for the adventure in the world full of adventures of green and yellow chubby men? You have to help them in this adventure they can only run they just run non stop. Its only up to you to stop them while theyre running and make them jump. Be careful, monsters are everywhere, they can eat you. But dont worry, you have to crush the monster to kill it. jump and crush. If you do not get the gold and the chest, the door will not open, but do not forget.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A9YR3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/green-and-yellow-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R00SN","slug":"monster-rash","title":"Monster Rash","description":"Different monsters in one have to survive in the retro planet world. monsters suddenly turned into cubes and they need to reach the end of the level by jumping from obstacles in their cube state. Jump over obstacles and collect stars. You have to collect the stars because you have to have 20 different monster costumes. In some sections, you can get on a rocket and fly on a rocket. If you get on the rocket, whatever costume youre wearing will return to its original state.","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R00SN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monster-rash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PY11Y","slug":"happy-candy","title":"Happy Candy","description":"Have you ever seen a candy-eating monster before? These monsters love candies. their favorite things are candies. collect candies and get gold. Be careful, even if you are a monster, thorns can kill you. moving spines can kill you. collect gold coins and own lots of happy monsters. they are all very happy and sweet monsters.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PY11Y/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-candy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1A7E","slug":"4-games-for-2-player","title":"4 Games For 2 Player","description":"Are you having fun with four different games for two that you can play with your friend? 4 different entertainment in one. Difference awaits you and your friend in every game. Compete with your friend, fight and win. more fun and more adventure in every game. You can compete with your friend in the first game. The last one to touch the obstacles wins. Remember, you have to survive. The top scorer in the second game wins, remember you have to beat your friend. score and win In the third game, you have to be very careful to survive the battle of tanks and make the right shot at the right time. blast your friend and win. In the fourth, take the best shot and beat your friend.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1A7E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/4-games-for-2-player/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7H7OO","slug":"killer-brothers-shoot","title":"Killer Brothers Shoot","description":"Have you ever seen a man with such a bouncing and bouncing gun before? Every time you shoot you will bounce like a ball, you have to be very careful. lock on target and shoot there is monster you need to kill. Take turns killing monsters with your friend and move on to the next level. Its up to you to kill the monsters. Anyone can kill their own monster. You have to shoot to jump or to move but be careful.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7H7OO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/killer-brothers-shoot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N8328","slug":"war-of-tanks-3d","title":"War of Tanks 3D","description":"Prepare for an adrenaline-fueled battle! Enlist now in epic, explosive open world tank battles, where honor is at stake. Collaborate with your teammates to devise the ultimate strategy and face off against commanders from across the globe. The destiny of your alliance rests in your hands. Join the fight today!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N8328/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/war-of-tanks-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AIEKR","slug":"kara-s-cafeteria","title":"Kara's Cafeteria","description":"Help Kara beautify, expand, and provide the best customer service in the city that everyone will surely love! Guide the customers to their tables, take their orders and bring it to the chef to prepare, and serve their delicious meals. The happier the customers, the more energy you collect to boost up your speed. Don't forget to customize your shop to attract more customers! Enjoy this classic cooking game with a twist!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AIEKR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kara-s-cafeteria/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O1341","slug":"zoocraft","title":"Zoocraft","description":"Zoocraft is an addictive game that will let you create your very own zoo! A world inhabited by various kinds of animals. In this game you have to tame animals, improve your skills, build aviaries and travel to different corners of the earth! Take an unforgettable journey from the village meadow to the hot desert and cold Antarctica!","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O1341/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zoocraft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VFR6E","slug":"bff-candy-fever","title":"Bff Candy Fever","description":"Princesses are now in BFF Candy fever mood. Princess Ariel, Merida, and Cinderella are BFFs forever. They want to enjoy a cute collection of tasty candy costumes. Watch the Princesses travel to a Candy wonderland and experience a variety of candy makeovers and candy cream hair.  Decorate each princess with cute candy styles and help them to enjoy this candy saga. \n\n","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VFR6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-candy-fever/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6I6S2","slug":"princess-stripes-vs-dots","title":"Princess Stripes Vs Dots","description":"Princess Stripes vs Dots Competition is about to begin and make things more exciting. The two little princesses of Cutedressup simply adore the modern world and fashion. They are trendsetters and best friends. But sometimes their taste in fashion is not the same. They need some experts to advise them to choose stripes or dots which one is best.\n\nNow they could use your expert helping hand to learn how to properly accessorize their new additions. Care to help them out? Come and join the little trendsetters getting started with this brand new cute dress up game for girls called Princess Stripes Vs Dots and see what playful, summery looks you can put together for them.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6I6S2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-stripes-vs-dots/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KC5U5","slug":"duck-shooting","title":"Duck Shooting","description":"Duck Shooting is an exciting and adventurous shooting game based on the amusement parks. When you enter the colorful shooting range to shoot there is floating a duck with a crown, and there is a pouty red and offended bird. But there are ducks with a cross! Your task is to hit the ducks and monsters. But be careful to hit the wrong duck because when you do it means that you cannot shoot at them because the points are reduced!\nGoodluck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KC5U5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duck-shooting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6AL66","slug":"eight-ball","title":"Eight Ball","description":"Fun and addictive Eight ball game.\nPocket all your own balls (you will be playing the solid balls, while the other player will be playing the stripes) and then pocket the black ball as the last ball.\nUse your finger to tap and control the angle. Release and tap again to shoot.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6AL66/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/eight-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E998A","slug":"chocolate-dream","title":"Chocolate Dream","description":"Melted Chocolate Mmmmmmm. Tap and swipe chocolate to switch places.\nMatch 3 or more chocolates to blast them away. The faster you reach the target,\nthe more points you receive. During the game you will receive special bonus\nfeatures. Use them wisely, since you don’t have unlimited moves. Relaxing and\naddictive game play swapping chocolate in 54 levels of excitement with cool\nrewards a long the way. Happy popping…","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E998A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chocolate-dream/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"96B15","slug":"bubble-hit","title":"Bubble Hit","description":"Amazing, fun and addictive physics game. Cool graphics and cute bubbles,\nmake this a blast to play. 28 levels of fun game play.\nTap where you want to throw the stone. Destroy bubbles and collect coins for\nextra points. Avoid the black bubbles.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/96B15/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-hit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"74738","slug":"checkers","title":"Checkers","description":"Move your piece one step diagonally forward, to an adjacent unoccupied square.\nCapture opponent’s piece by jumping over it. If a piece reaches the other end,\nit is crowned and can move in both directions. If possible, you must jump one or\nmore consecutive steps, by jumping between and capture several pieces.\nYou win when you have captured all your opponent’s pieces.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/74738/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/checkers/embed?sid=1","plays":39095,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6H8S6","slug":"candy-smash","title":"Candy Smash","description":"Pop Pop candy. Tap and swipe candy to switch places. Match 3 or more candies\nto blast them away. The faster you reach the target, the more points you receive.\nDuring the game you will receive special bonus features. Use them wisely, since\nyou don’t have unlimited moves.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6H8S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-smash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"73S8N","slug":"candy-sling-shot","title":"Candy Sling Shot","description":"Tap, drag and aim to shoot down candy of all kinds.\nCollect stars to increase your chance to go to the next level.\nCollect bonus items to destroy more candy and get more points.\nBe careful, not all items are friendly, and will take your life.","category":"Action","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/73S8N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-sling-shot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13YPR","slug":"candy-drop","title":"Candy Drop","description":"Tap to place your candy before your time is up.\nConnect five candy’s vertically, horizontally or diagonally to win.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13YPR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-drop/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2UBT8","slug":"black-jack-unlimited","title":"Black Jack Unlimited","description":"Beat the dealer, and show your skills in the exiting Black Jack game.","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2UBT8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/black-jack-unlimited/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9TSB8","slug":"battle-of-the-battles","title":"Battle of the Battles","description":"For thousands of years Battle of the Battles happens, and it is most exciting battle\nof all time! This year the team the Braves have only one representative, Marin.\nCan you help Marin overcome the Renegades? With each level, hide Marin in a\nbox and try to guess in which box the Renegades are hiding their players. You\nneed to guess that right so their player must start all over again, first player to\nmake it to the last box wins the match. Goodluck!","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9TSB8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/battle-of-the-battles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"42884","slug":"meal-mayhem","title":"Meal Mayhem","description":"Get ready to cook up a storm, serve customers' orders, and unlock new stores in the addictive and delightful game Meal Mayhem!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/42884/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/meal-mayhem/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D6G2D","slug":"speedy-golf-3d","title":"Speedy Golf 3D","description":"Shoot Incredible Golf Scores!\n- fast 3D graphics\n- easy one button three tap play control\n- caddy does the math for you\n- play an 18 hole par 72 course in a few minutes","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D6G2D/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/speedy-golf-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AB96G","slug":"balls-game","title":"Balls Game","description":"Welcome to Balls Games, have fun in this fantastic game where you will have to use your cunning to try to find the right combination to try to accumulate points and increase your bestscore, what are you waiting for??? Go play Balls Games now and have fun!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AB96G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balls-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"443A6","slug":"alone","title":"Alone","description":"A story mode Horror ( 3D First Person Game ) where you need to solve  puzzles, explorer the house and leave the house as fast as possible.\n\nStory : You where live alone at home when you are sleeping you feel that something is here and you're trying to leave the house.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/443A6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alone/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IDEEN","slug":"stone-miner-idle","title":"Stone Miner Idle","description":"Smash Miner  Idle Game is an idle game where players collect and sell resources from mines. Players start as the owner of a mining business and begin the mining process to collect resources from their mines. Initially, players can only collect resources from their mines using a simple pickaxe. However, as players progress, they can purchase different mining tools to collect more resources.\n\nThe goal of the game is to reach the highest level possible by collecting and selling the most valuable resources. Players earn money by collecting resources from their mines and can use this money to purchase more advanced mining equipment. Additionally, players can sell resources from their mines to obtain more valuable products.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IDEEN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stone-miner-idle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"88EAA","slug":"jetpack-panda-bao","title":"JetPack Panda Bao","description":"JetPack Panda Bao is a side-scrolling, runner game in which you are traveling through the sky to reach the boss in a jetpack. You are trying to avoid kill enemies and avoid obstacles. Collected coins can be used for upgrades in a shop","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/88EAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jetpack-panda-bao/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"01918","slug":"find-the-cat","title":"Find The Cat","description":"Find The Cat is a Hidden Object game where you have to find different cats in aleatory maps! Collect all the cute cats through a calm and relaxing gameplay!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01918/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-cat/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44L34","slug":"toid-blaster","title":"Toid Blaster","description":"$6e","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44L34/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/toid-blaster/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L691R","slug":"slinger","title":"Slinger","description":"A Wild West 3D Shooting Game\n\nAs sheriff you have been assigned to protect a train gold shipment.\nUnfortunately many bad guys want to steal that gold.\nBeing an honorable sheriff, your objective is to only disarm the bad guys and destroy the TNT cache.\n\nGood luck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade","classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L691R/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slinger/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6N0W4","slug":"kick-score-now","title":"Kick&Score Now","description":"Kick the ball to the soccer goal and become an amazing soccer player.\nBut be careful, if you don't aim correctly, the opposing goalkeeper will take your shot.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6N0W4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kickandscore-now/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9NT5N","slug":"geometry-gunner","title":"Geometry Gunner","description":"Geometry gunner is an exciting video game where the player must escape from enemy squares by shooting them down.\n\nTo play the game, you'll need to use both your mouse and WASD keys. Use your mouse to aim at the enemy squares and WASD keys to move your character around the screen.\n\nThe goal of the game is to avoid getting hit by the enemy squares while shooting them down before they can reach you. You'll need to be quick and strategic to make it through each level.\n\nWith each level, the enemy squares become faster, smarter and more difficult to beat.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9NT5N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/geometry-gunner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A58CN","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-pattern","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Pattern","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A58CN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-pattern/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"98N3E","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-kitten","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect Kitten","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/98N3E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-kitten/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13UFL","slug":"round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-butterfly","title":"Round jigsaw Puzzle - Collect the Butterfly","description":"Le but du jeu est de collecter une image découpée en fragments triangulaires. Pour déplacer un fragment, faites le premier clic de souris sur le fragment que vous souhaitez déplacer. Le deuxième clic doit être fait sur le fragment où vous voulez déplacer le premier fragment. Après cela, les fragments seront échangés. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez sur l'écran de jeu avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13UFL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/round-jigsaw-puzzle-collect-the-butterfly/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"94848","slug":"kill-a-ghost","title":"Kill a Ghost","description":"«Kill a ghost» is a simple shooter with frightening music and a tenacious ghost. Don't let this ghost get close to you!\nYour task is not to let the ghost get close to you. You'll have magic bullets. But it's not always easy to get into a cast. It can think!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/94848/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kill-a-ghost/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MX72E","slug":"taxi-take-me-home","title":"Taxi - Take me home","description":"Taxi Simulator - help people get home! Become a taxi driver - drive passengers and earn money!\n\nLearn the stories of your passengers who want to get home as soon as possible. Discover new corners of the cozy town, following the marks on the map. Practice safe driving and parking, keep an eye on the condition of your car, and of course, eat a burrito at the gas station! \n\nDo not forget to fill up and repair your car in time. Try to remain profitable, and do not forget that in the case of unsafe driving, you will pay compensation to passengers.\n","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MX72E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/taxi-take-me-home/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NALLL","slug":"tall-and-rush","title":"Tall and Rush","description":"Tall and Rush is an addictive hypercasual HTML5 game where you embark on a mission to become taller and defeat a formidable robot. Jump higher, collect power-ups, and unleash your kicking skills to overcome the robotic adversary. How tall can you grow and how many rounds can you conquer?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NALLL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tall-and-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":39895,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T4E3L","slug":"belt-master","title":"Belt Master","description":"In Belt Master, drag elastic belts to protect objects from falling off a truck. Test your skill and aim for the highest level. Can you become the ultimate Belt Master?","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T4E3L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/belt-master/embed?sid=1","plays":39734,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"39E53","slug":"jump-or-die","title":"Jump or Die","description":"Jump or Die is a hypercasual online game inspired by Squid Game's final challenge. Dodge obstacles, time your jumps, and aim for the highest score. Can you survive?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/39E53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jump-or-die/embed?sid=1","plays":39779,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"90804","slug":"pvpz-io","title":"PvPz.io","description":"PvPz.io is an online multiplayer extraction game where you engage in thrilling PvP battles against other players. Step into a realm of strategic action, accessible directly from your web browser, and experience the thrill of a full loot top-down shooter.\n\nCollect hundreds of distinctive weapons and items, each with their own unique attributes and abilities. Explore the world of Zendaria, overcome formidable challenges, and prove your skills as you strive to survive and successfully extract with all the valuable treasures you've acquired. If you fail to extract you lose everything you've looted on that run!\n\nBecome a force to be reckoned with in this multiplayer gaming experience.\n\nFight, Loot, Extract!\n","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/90804/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pvpz-io/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CWW8W","slug":"space-warrior","title":"Space Warrior","description":"Space Warrior is a side-scrolling, runner game in which you are traveling through the space to reach the boss of each level. You are trying to kill enemies and avoid electric obstacles. Collected coins can be used for upgrades in a shop","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CWW8W/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/space-warrior/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PE834","slug":"glass-puzle","title":"Glass Puzle","description":"Glass Puzzles is an interesting geometric puzzle. Collect the picture in pieces, the shape of which is never repeated and go through a huge number of unique levels. By connecting the puzzle pieces you will see the picture hidden under it!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PE834/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/glass-puzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NL3LO","slug":"casino-slot","title":"Casino Slot","description":"A traditional Casino Style Slot game with free spins and wild cards.","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NL3LO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/casino-slot/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"23512","slug":"spaceships","title":"SpaceShips","description":"SpaceShips is an exciting game where your goal is to skillfully dodge enemy spaceships and accumulate the highest score possible","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/23512/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spaceships/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L74AM","slug":"mummy-land","title":"Mummy Land","description":"Mummy Land is a free online platformer game where you play as a mummy trying to escape from a pyramid. Collect treasure and power-ups as you try to reach the exit. Can you make it out alive? Play now and find out!\nLooking for an online game that's fun and challenging? Look no further than Mummy Land! In this platformer game, you'll guide your mummy through a series of levels, avoiding traps and solving puzzles. With multiple difficulty levels, there's a challenge for everyone. So put on your adventurer's hat and get ready for some mummy-land fun!\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L74AM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mummy-land/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"65L5U","slug":"ice-ball-run","title":"Ice Ball Run","description":"Ice Ball Run is an online platformer game that challenges players to navigate through a series of levels by controlling a ball made of ice. The game features a variety of level designs and obstacles, and players must use their skills to overcome these challenges. Ice Ball Run is an addictive and challenging game that will keep players engaged for hours.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/65L5U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ice-ball-run/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5G3HH","slug":"ghost-runaway","title":"Ghost Runaway","description":"The Ghost Runaway platformer game series is known for its fast-paced gameplay and challenging level design. Players must use their quick reflexes and platforming skills to navigate through treacherous environments, avoid enemy attacks, and reach the end of each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5G3HH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ghost-runaway/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5G83E","slug":"king-of-majesty","title":"King of Majesty","description":"The King of Majesty Online Platformer Game is a game that requires quick thinking and decisions. As a product manager, you are responsible for making decisions about the game's features and content. You will need to be able to evaluate your options and make decisions quickly.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5G83E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-of-majesty/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C58AA","slug":"fireball-vs-ice-cream","title":"Fireball Vs Ice Cream","description":"Enjoy a new and exciting online game – Fireball Vs Ice Cream! This game is perfect for those who want to have fun and challenge themselves. Test your skills by jumping and escaping from the fireballs. Can you make it to the end? Play now and find out!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C58AA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fireball-vs-ice-cream/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6AL0L","slug":"football-panda","title":"Football Panda","description":"The Football Panda Platformer online game is a great way to pass the time. It is a fast paced game that requires quick reflexes and good hand-eye coordination. The object of the game is to score as many goals as possible in a set time period. There are different levels to the game, each with its own challenges. The graphics are good and the gameplay is smooth. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6AL0L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/football-panda/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"421U1","slug":"rainbow-ball-rush","title":"Rainbow Ball Rush","description":"Introducing \"Rainbow Ball Rush\" - a thrilling game where your objective is to navigate a ball through an array of colorful platforms and obstacles.\n\nAs you progress through each level, the game gets increasingly challenging, with new obstacles and tricky platforms appearing at every turn. Your goal is to keep the ball moving forward without falling off the edge or colliding with any obstacles.\n\nThe platforms come in a variety of colors and shapes, adding to the visual appeal of the game. Some platforms are stationary, while others move back and forth, making it harder to time your jumps.\n\nIn addition to the platforms, you'll encounter a range of obstacles designed to trip you up. These can include spinning blades, swinging pendulums, and even fiery pits that will instantly destroy your ball on contact.\n\nTo succeed in Ball Rush, you'll need quick reflexes and precise timing. The game provides a real challenge, but with practice, you'll master the ball's movements and become a true champion.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/421U1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rainbowball-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1366T","slug":"start-game","title":"Start Game","description":"welcome to start game, the game of the ball that gets faster and closer, be careful not to drop it, we'll save your points","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1366T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/start-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O35RR","slug":"superhero-memory-match","title":"Superhero Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Superhero Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Superhero Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Superhero Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O35RR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/superhero-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LWGF1","slug":"giraffe-jigsaw-image-challenge","title":"Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge","description":"Welcome to Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge! Our Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge picture. With a wide variety of Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Giraffe Jigsaw Image Challenge Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LWGF1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/giraffe-jigsaw-image-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E5GI2","slug":"the-nun-sliding-game","title":"The Nun Sliding game","description":"Welcome to The Nun Sliding game, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Nun Sliding game, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Nun Sliding game and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E5GI2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-nun-sliding-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7II91","slug":"guns-block-puzzle-blitz","title":"Guns Block Puzzle Blitz","description":"Welcome to Guns Block Puzzle Blitz, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Guns Block Puzzle Blitz, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Guns Block Puzzle Blitz and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7II91/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/guns-block-puzzle-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PLWPP","slug":"snail-jigsaw-perfect-slide-puzzle","title":"Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle! Our Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Snail Jigsaw Perfect Slide Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PLWPP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snail-jigsaw-perfect-slide-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MN882","slug":"huggy-wuggy-in-minecraft","title":"Huggy Wuggy in Minecraft","description":"Huggy Wuggy in Minecraft features blocky graphics and Huggy Wuggy as the main character in minecraft world. Your mission is to kill given amount of mobs in order to progress to the next levels.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MN882/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/huggy-wuggy-in-minecraft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"87996","slug":"whaito","title":"Whaito","description":"Whaito is a 2D cute little platformer where you have to collect all of the red cubes while avoiding the spikes, man eater monsters, enemies and reach the white flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87996/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/whaito/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TB129","slug":"skeleton-lab","title":"Skeleton Lab","description":"Collect coins without getting in the way of skeletons, be careful because the processor speed is too high. After collecting the last coin, you will receive protection with which you can defeat all the skeletons!\n\nThe game is waiting for you:\n- Pleasant music\n- 20 challenging levels\n- Addictive gameplay","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TB129/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/skeleton-lab/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00O5G","slug":"t-rex-running-color","title":"T-Rex Running Color","description":"T-Rex Running is a game of adventure and very entertaining. The T-Rex has to run, but you need to overcome many traps, such as cacti and pterodactyls. See how many obstacles you can avoid like cactus and ducks under flying pterodactyls as your T-Rex runs faster and faster. The goal is to help T-Rex run his way by jumping over cacti, pterodactyls, and more. ","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00O5G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/t-rex-running-color/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZLY18","slug":"crazy-color-balls","title":"Crazy Color Balls","description":"Crazy Color Balls is an amazing and exciting game very similar to what is in fashion. Rush your way through and around obstacles of all shapes and sizes in this colorful game! Control the color ball and try to avoid hitting any objects that are not the same color as the ball. The speed of the game starts slow and picks up fast as the game progresses. Have fun!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZLY18/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-color-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OB847","slug":"color-blast","title":"Color Blast","description":"Tap and blast 3 or more same color blocks. Clear one level and get 2 stars to\nunlock the next. When you do good you will receive special reward items to help\nimprove your score.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OB847/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-blast/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N6A6E","slug":"classic-tank-wars-extreme-hd","title":"Classic Tank Wars Extreme HD","description":"Classic Tank Wars Extreme HD brings back the good old Arcade days to your mobile\ndevice! Attack and destroy enemy armored vehicles in 120 exciting levels to achieve the\nmain goal victory! But do not forget to defend your base in the heat of the fights; its\ndestruction leads to the failure of your entire mission. There are also dangerous minibosses and other challenges. Can you master them and become the hero in this classic\narcade game? Good luck!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N6A6E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/classic-tank-wars-extreme-hd/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8BOBB","slug":"bubble-wooble","title":"Bubble Wooble","description":"Bubbles... Bubbles with monsters. Red ones, green ones, blue ones... They all\nhave a home they need to go to. Help them get there by popping their bubble\ncage and get them to their homes.\n Endless skill based game\n Weekly, daily and all-time top 100 leaderboards\n Ridiculously simple to pick up, ridiculously hard to top the leaderboard","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8BOBB/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-wooble/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U1BUP","slug":"bubble-jumper","title":"Bubble Jumper","description":"Bubble Jumper is an extremely fun game. This is one of those games you get\naddicted to, so if you want to have fun, play this game and help the bubbles\nreach the other side, by shooting bubbles from below. It also has awesome\nbonus features like extra life, coins, stars, enemies, 2 and 3 bubble shots, bubble\nsplit, and much more!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U1BUP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-jumper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LII64","slug":"penguin-splash","title":"Penguin Splash","description":"Penguin Splash is a fun and challenging online match 3 game. Link three or more penguins of the same color to make them splash and score points. Use special power-ups to clear the board and advance to the next level. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LII64/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-splash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"119H7","slug":"world-cup-flag-match","title":"World Cup Flag Match","description":"The World CupFlag Match is an online game that tests your knowledge of flags from around the world. Match three flags in a row to score points and advance to the next level.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/119H7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-cup-flag-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00PO8","slug":"hoops-fruits","title":"Hoops & Fruits","description":"Get ready for a slam dunk of fun with Hoops & Fruits, the ultimate basketball puzzle game! Score points by shooting hoops and solving challenging puzzles, all while enjoying a fruity twist. With over 100 levels to play, you'll never run out of excitement as you work your way through increasingly difficult challenges. Master the game by perfecting your aim and using power-ups to clear tricky obstacles. Whether you're a basketball fanatic or just looking for a fun and addictive puzzle game, Hoops & Fruits is the perfect choice. ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00PO8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hoops-and-fruits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"39866","slug":"draw-dash","title":"Draw Dash","description":"Draw your way to the hoop and slam dunk! Play the best basketball game! Get ready to experience the ultimate basketball challenge with Draw Dash Basketball! This exciting game lets you take control of the ball and dribble your way to the hoop with your finger. Use your creativity and draw your own path to victory, avoiding obstacles and defeating opponents as you make your way to the basket. ","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/39866/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/draw-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84646","slug":"tower-defense-kingdoms","title":"Tower Defense Kingdoms","description":"Tower Defense Kingdoms is an exciting and challenging game that puts you in control of defending your kingdom against waves of enemies. Build and upgrade your towers strategically to fend off hordes of invaders and prevent them from reaching your castle. With dozens of levels and various enemies, each with their unique strengths and weaknesses, Tower Defense Kingdoms will keep you engaged and entertained for hours on end. Unlock new towers and upgrade your existing ones to increase your chances of success. So get ready to defend your kingdom and embark on an epic journey in Tower Defense Kingdoms!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84646/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tower-defense-kingdoms/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CCCCT","slug":"egg-collector","title":"Egg Collector","description":"Get ready to run, jump, and collect eggs with Egg Collector - the online runner game that will keep you on your toes! Play now and see how many eggs you can collect in this exciting, fast-paced adventure. Are you looking for a new online game to play? Look no further than Egg Collector! This exciting runner game challenges you to collect as many eggs as possible while dodging obstacles and enemies. With its colorful graphics, fast-paced gameplay, and endless levels to explore, Egg Collector is t","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CCCCT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/egg-collector/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RL586","slug":"butterfly-dash","title":"Butterfly Dash","description":"Fly, dodge, and collect nectar in this thrilling butterfly adventure game.  Get ready to soar through the sky and embark on a thrilling butterfly adventure! In Butterfly Dash Adventure, you'll take control of a beautiful butterfly as you fly through a stunning world filled with obstacles, enemies, and plenty of sweet nectar to collect. With simple but addictive gameplay, you'll need quick reflexes and expert timing to dodge obstacles and collect as much nectar as possible.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RL586/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/butterfly-dash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5R4N4","slug":"jet-jumper-adventure","title":"Jet Jumper Adventure","description":"Fly through the skies and collect coins in this thrilling Jet Jumper game.\nTake to the skies in this thrilling adventure game, Jet Jumper. Fly through obstacles and collect coins to earn points and unlock new levels. With smooth and easy-to-use controls, you'll be soaring through the clouds in no time. Challenge yourself and your friends to see who can get the highest score.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5R4N4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jet-jumper-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0IN67","slug":"mike-and-mia-beach-day","title":"Mike And Mia Beach Day","description":"What's more fun than a day at the beach? It's time for a fun-filled day with tons of beach activities with Mike and Mia! Dress up in stylish beach clothing, play volleyball, catch fishes, go surfing and ride the waves. Make the best beach picnic ever with Mike and Mia!","category":"Sport","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0IN67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mike-and-mia-beach-day/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3A1R5","slug":"grandma-recipe-apple-pie","title":"Grandma Recipe Apple Pie","description":"Annie miss her grandma's apple pie. So she has to ask her grandma to get an Apple Pie recipe. Can you help her to make a delicious Apple Pie? Of course you can, because it will be so much fun! Prepare the tools and find the ingredients. Cook the apple pie perfectly and decorate with some delicious toppings. Dress up with cute clothes, take a picture, and put some emojis.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3A1R5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grandma-recipe-apple-pie/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"YR8GH","slug":"doc-honeyberry-puppy-surgery","title":"Doc HoneyBerry Puppy Surgery","description":"This cute little puppy got several injuries after having an accident. Let's rescue it with Doc Honneyberry! Clean up the puppy, cure the injuries, heal the broken bones, dress up, and more! Make this cute puppy heal and recover, so it will be able to enjoy running and playing again.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/YR8GH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doc-honeyberry-puppy-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E0T8E","slug":"mike-and-mia-the-firefighter","title":"Mike And Mia The FIrefighter","description":"Do you see a fire and smell the smoke? Help Mike and Mia to jump on their wagon and drive to emergency mission! Dress them up with some cute firefighter outfits and decorate the wagon. Rescue all cats and extinguish the flames. Be the firefighter hero with Mike and Mia!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E0T8E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mike-and-mia-the-firefighter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CAA2C","slug":"yummy-ice-cream-factory","title":"Yummy Ice Cream Factory","description":"What makes your summer more vibing? Yes, Ice cream! Create your own ice cream cones. Yummy! Go through every step of the making of ice cream with unique and deliciouse recipes. Pick your favorite flavours, choose from different cones, and finish it with a combination of toppings. Don't forget to pick out the perfect outfits for the girls. Have fun with Yummy Ice Cream Factory!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CAA2C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-ice-cream-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OASS1","slug":"mike-and-mia-1st-day-at-school","title":"Mike And Mia 1st Day At School","description":"Mike and Mia are very excited for their first day of school. Help them to clean their room and make a delicious snack box. Get dressed up with various cute clothes. Enjoy the first day at school with fun and loving playful activities!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OASS1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mike-and-mia-1st-day-at-school/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G8847","slug":"funny-angela-haircut","title":"Funny Angela Haircut","description":"Give Angela the best hairstyle ever! Enjoy tons of professional tools like curling irons, blow dryers, scissors, magic hair growing spray, and so much more! Dye her hair in any variety of colors. Complete the makeover with stylish outfit, mix and match cute clothes and dress up Angela to become more fashionable!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G8847/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-angela-haircut/embed?sid=1","plays":39811,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MKIG5","slug":"gempicker","title":"Gempicker","description":"Gempicker est un jeu de puzzle et d'adresse amusant qui vous met au défi de choisir les bonnes gemmes sur deux tableaux dans le bon ordre. Attention, c'est plus difficile qu'il n'y parait. Mais très satisfaisant quand on le fait bien! La bonne nouvelle est qu'il existe généralement certaines symétries entre les planches qui peuvent vous donner un indice et faciliter un peu le processus de résolution des défis.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MKIG5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gempicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3TAR7","slug":"patric-s-pursuit","title":"Patric's Pursuit","description":"Patric's Pursuit is a simple Platformer game featuring Patric, who is trying to get away from Paul Ice. Collect the Harry-O's to get points, and try to get to 101! This dumb game will keep you entertained for hours. More updates to come if y'all like it!","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3TAR7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/patric-s-pursuit/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"84277","slug":"jamir","title":"Jamir","description":"Jamir est un jeu de tir tactique de science-fiction rapide et gratuit. Maîtrisez vos capacités et vos objets pour détruire les créatures et les ennemis. Améliorez votre personnage, vos armes, vos capacités et vos objets pour devenir le plus puissant du monde.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/84277/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jamir/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OE3OL","slug":"iconic-celebrity-look","title":"Iconic Celebrity Look","description":"Welcome to the Iconic celebrity Look. These princesses sure have their favorite celebs and they just want to dress up like them. In this game, you will discover the most iconic celebrity outfits! You will have the chance to dress up these princesses as your favorite celebs. Play them and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OE3OL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/iconic-celebrity-look/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LLIRO","slug":"my-trendy-plaid-outfits","title":"My Trendy Plaid Outfits","description":"Welcome to the My Trendy Plaid Outfits. Plaid is back on the top list when it comes to fashion trends! And who else should know more about Plaid outfit if not Princess Ariel, Moana and Jasmine? This game is all about wearing the Plaid outfit the right way! There are many great ways to wear the timeless Plaid print, but you need to know how to match it with the rest of the outfit to avoid a fashion disaster. Are you ready to explore different outfits with us? ","category":"Aventure","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LLIRO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-trendy-plaid-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"46NSI","slug":"insta-girls-fruity-fashion","title":"Insta Girls Fruity Fashion","description":"Welcome to the Insta Girls Fruity Fashion. Dee Dee arranges a party at her home. Yes! It’s a fruity fashion Party. She invites her friends Willow and Noah to the party. Help them to browse their wardrobe to pick the best outfit. Come and Join the girls and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/46NSI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/insta-girls-fruity-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D838S","slug":"popular-80-s-fashion-trends","title":"Popular 80's Fashion Trends","description":"Welcome to the Popular 80’s Fashion Trends. Rainbow high school girls are in love with the 80’s style. And they are going to dress up accordingly. Who else loves it? Have you ever created an 80’s style outfit? Here is your chance to create four different ones, one for each girl. The wardrobe is stacked with tones of clothes waiting for you, so have fun dressing them up! ","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D838S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/popular-80-s-fashion-trends/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"06808","slug":"princess-love-pinky-outfits","title":"Princess Love Pinky Outfits","description":"Welcome to Princess Love Pinky Outfits. Princess Anna, Elsa, Moana, Jasmine, Snow White, and Ariel met after a long time. They are Planned to throw a weekend party with their beloved theme called Pinky Outfits. Browse the wardrobe for each princess and pick cute pinky outfits. Join with girls and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/06808/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-love-pinky-outfits/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ES462","slug":"horses-speed","title":"Horses Speed","description":"Welcome to the Horses speed game, it is the traditional horse race, if you win you also have the Speed bonus available which will help you in the speed of your selected horse","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ES462/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horses-speed/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LP49X","slug":"parmesan-partisan-deluxe","title":"Parmesan Partisan Deluxe","description":"You are the last defense, you are a lonely cheesy partisan who has to protect his people from the menace of the Mice People, who wants to conquer an eat all the cheese they can find! You are the last hope of your people: defend them using all your weapons, kill as many rats as you can, and free your nation from the rodents conquerors!\n\n- 10 different levels\n- 5 angry mice with different weapons\n- 9 different weapons to choose from\n- 1 Final Boss\n\nGame Controls: \nWASD and ARROWS to Move\nRight Mouse Button to Dodge\nLeft Button to Shoot","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LP49X/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/parmesan-partisan-deluxe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IAB8I","slug":"counter-craft-3-zombies","title":"Counter Craft 3 Zombies","description":"Counter Craft 3 Zombies features fun and action packed zombie shooting in minecraft world. Use three types of weapons to shoot given amount of zombies and watch out for enemy soldiers and explosives in order to survive and successfully complete each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IAB8I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-craft-3-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7C7YG","slug":"crazy-goat-hunter","title":"Crazy Goat Hunter","description":"You are crazy goat hunter and your mission is to find and shoot all goats in the forest.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7C7YG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-goat-hunter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O77B7","slug":"slender-zombie-time","title":"Slender Zombie Time","description":"You are lost alone in cold zombie infested forest and your mission is to find and kill the slender man.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O77B7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/slender-zombie-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IRMSY","slug":"siren-memory-match","title":"Siren Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Siren Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Siren Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Siren Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IRMSY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/siren-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"PALLE","slug":"axolotl-jigsaw-picture-puzzle","title":"Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle! Our Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Axolotl Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/PALLE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/axolotl-jigsaw-picture-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1YUME","slug":"pegasus-memory-match","title":"Pegasus Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Pegasus Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Pegasus Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Pegasus Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1YUME/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pegasus-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1I1E8","slug":"idle-destroyer","title":"Idle Destroyer","description":"Idle Destroyer est un jeu d’inactivité classique où vous utilisez plusieurs destroyers avec différentes vitesses et forces, ainsi que des capacités spéciales supplémentaires pour détruire des millions de blocs! Vous trouverez 6 types de destroyers, des dizaines d’améliorations, un système de bonus et de prestige, ainsi qu’un système de réalisations aimé par beaucoup.","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1I1E8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/idle-destroyer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8AB8A","slug":"big-space-adventure","title":"Big Space Adventure","description":"Big Space Adventure is the same classic game of other match 3 games. \nYou will need to match 3 identical objects to swap, at times you will be stuck \nbut you just need to use power ups to get it all clear. \nAlways remember your clock is ticking so make sure you do it as fast as you \ncan. Goodluck!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8AB8A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-space-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T6IC9","slug":"santa-s-christmas-mania","title":"Santa's Christmas Mania","description":"Your mission is to help Santa pack up all the gifts for the children.\nIn each level, Santa will request items to collect. Match 3 or more of each gift to \ncollect the number requested.\nRemember, you need to be quick and get them all before your time runs out! Have \nfun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T6IC9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-s-christmas-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"91GAR","slug":"real-estate-giant","title":"Real Estate Giant","description":"To be a Real Estate Giant you must buy and sell the property as many \nas you can. So, you want a building? You've gotta work for it! Buy Low! Sell High! \nBut remember to take a look on price of buildings and sell them to \nmake many profits. Your goal is to keep making money in the property market. But work fast!","category":"Stratégie","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/91GAR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/real-estate-giant/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"814R0","slug":"hidden-object-search","title":"Hidden Object Search","description":"Are you a fan of solving puzzles and finding hidden objects? \nIf you are and you love being a detective, then Hidden Object Search Game \nis just for you! This is a simple yet fun hidden objects game. Look for various \nitems, animals, and persons hidden in the image within a minute.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/814R0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-object-search/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"45NCD","slug":"hidden-object-search-2-more-fun","title":"Hidden Object Search 2 - More Fun","description":"Play the classical Hidden Object Search 2 game. Finding hidden objects can \nbe a great deal of fun with those who have a keen eye for detail. \nDo you have the necessary skills to complete all missions and to unlock a \nhidden bonus level? Click on an object when you find it. Goodluck!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/45NCD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hidden-object-search-2-more-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1NMFA","slug":"urban-traffic-commander","title":"Urban Traffic Commander","description":"I don't know about you, but I find it hard to stay focused when there's a lot of \ntraffic. This is your chance to be in control! Take command of the traffic in the \nstreets and redirect cars on their way. As you get through each level, get better at \nkeeping them moving. Be careful though, those pedestrians can be tricky!","category":"Course","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1NMFA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/urban-traffic-commander/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R5R6I","slug":"santa-girl-running","title":"Santa Girl Running","description":"Go Santa Girl, run! The daughter of Santa Claus has a task, and it is to collect \nall present gifts in North Pole that are scattered. But be careful, there are lot of \nenemies, challenges, and obstacles along the way. Your goals are to collect gifts \non your way but avoid all the deadly obstacles to the finish line. You will collect \nthe sleigh power up to blast through walls. Go to your goal right now and run, \nremember to collect sleigh bonuses, and make sure that you will do all the best \nof your abilities and jumping skills, to make this adventure even more exciting!","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R5R6I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/santa-girl-running/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"566ZF","slug":"frozen-winter-mania","title":"Frozen Winter Mania","description":"Brrrr, there's a chill in the air! Frozen Winter Mania is a game for Match 3 \ngames lovers. Match 3 or more of the identical shape to clear the frozen \ngems. \nWork fast to clear board before time runs out. If you get stuck, use the \npowerups to help you clear the screen. Have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/566ZF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/frozen-winter-mania/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A68A9","slug":"doc-darling-santa-surgery","title":"Doc Darling Santa Surgery","description":"Christmas is coming but Santa had an accident on his way! He needs your help to fix Santa's sleight and find his deer. Also bring him to Doc Darling to take care of all injuries and prepare for an emergency surgery. Complete all treatments and dress him up till he gets ready to deliver the gifts for Christmas night!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A68A9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doc-darling-santa-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ASA93","slug":"doc-darling-bone-surgery","title":"Doc Darling Bone Surgery","description":"Oh no, the girl just fell off her scooter and she needs Doc Darling to take care of her injuries. Play as a doctor who cures the injuries and fix all of the broken bones to get the girl back on her feet. Complete all of the stages to unlock dress up mode and give her a cute makeover.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ASA93/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doc-darling-bone-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"366MY","slug":"yummy-candy-factory","title":"Yummy Candy Factory","description":"Purple, red, green, and yellow! The candy comes in many different colors and flavours. And now you have a whole candy factory to make candies in your style! You have a few steps to make your awesome candies. Choose flavours such as strawberry, grapes, apple, and pineapple. Mix and boil the ingredients. Shape all of the candies and decorate them! Let's learn how to make yummy candies together!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/366MY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-candy-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"14C6S","slug":"tictoc-catwalk-fashion","title":"Tictoc Catwalk Fashion","description":"Have you ever dream to be a model stylist? This cutie girl needs your help to realize her dream of modeling! Follow the hint and choose the right outfit to make her stand out on the catwalk. Take the picture to get many likes on every reel. So you can earn money to buy new items. Make her look more stylish and fashionable on the catwalk.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/14C6S/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictoc-catwalk-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9788T","slug":"tictoc-paris-fashion","title":"Tictoc Paris Fashion","description":"This beautiful girl is taking a trip to Paris. She needs your help to make her into a tictoc star by making her fashionable in Paris. Follow the hint to choose the right make up, clothes, hairstyles, and accessories for her. Make her look stylish on every reel. Get many likes and earn money to buy new items.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9788T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictoc-paris-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"62M27","slug":"funny-zoo-emergency","title":"Funny Zoo Emergency","description":"Be the best veterinarian by taking care of these baby animals.\nHelp them to cure their sickness and solve every animal's problems.\nTreat injured animals, clean all the dirts, dress them up with unlimited outfit\ncombination, and make them perfect again.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/62M27/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-zoo-emergency/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58UIS","slug":"tictoc-kpop-summer","title":"Tictoc KPOP Summer","description":"Help this cute girl to become tictoc kpop star by helping her to choose the right make up and clothes by following the hint. Make her look stylish on every reel. You can buy new items by getting many likes after posting the photo.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58UIS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictoc-kpop-summer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"29NMC","slug":"funny-cooking-camp","title":"Funny Cooking Camp","description":"The great outdoors is calling! But the mice are starting to get hungry. Help them to built the clay oven and collect the items for the grill. Bake delicious pizza and grill the BBQ satays. Enjoy this funny camping game!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/29NMC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-cooking-camp/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"444S5","slug":"blast-out-battle-royale","title":"Blast Out Battle Royale","description":"Search for weapons on vast area, use your vehicle to travel across the land and try to shoot all enemies in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/444S5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blast-out-battle-royale/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M52MC","slug":"zombie-vacation","title":"Zombie Vacation","description":"You are special forces soldier, your plane crashed and you got unexpected vacation on a tropical island crowded with zombies, your mission is to use your modern sub-machine gun to shoot thousands of zombies and try to survive each wave of zombies in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M52MC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-vacation/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EBL6L","slug":"brutal-battle-royale","title":"Brutal Battle Royale","description":"Search for weapons on the map and try to shoot all enemies in order to win in battle royale.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EBL6L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brutal-battle-royale/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RGA77","slug":"super-sergeant","title":"Super Sergeant","description":"You are super sergeant and your mission is to destroy all enemy forces using different types of weapons and find the exit on each level.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RGA77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-sergeant/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44D44","slug":"grand-city-driving","title":"Grand City Driving","description":"Select different super-cars and test drive them across the grand city.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44D44/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-city-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEOE7","slug":"dead-zone-sniper","title":"Dead Zone Sniper","description":"Use your sniper rifle to shoot all hazmat soldiers in the contaminated area, try to survive before the time runs out in order to progress to the next levels.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEOE7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dead-zone-sniper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4GNCC","slug":"mafia-city-driving","title":"Mafia City Driving","description":"Select different super cars and try to accomplish various missions across the mafia city.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4GNCC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mafia-city-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R92EE","slug":"cute-anime-animals-coloring-pages","title":"Cute Anime Animals Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Cute Anime Animals Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Cute Anime Animals Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Cute Anime Animals Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Cute Anime Animals Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R92EE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-anime-animals-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RRTLL","slug":"robert-the-doll-picture-slide-puzzle-frenzy","title":"Robert the Doll Picture Slide Puzzle Frenzy","description":"Welcome to Robert the Doll Picture Slide Puzzle Frenzy, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Robert the Doll Picture Slide Puzzle Frenzy, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Robert the Doll Picture Slide Puzzle Frenzy and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RRTLL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/robert-the-doll-picture-slide-puzzle-frenzy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TMPN5","slug":"miniature-charmander-picture-block-quest","title":"Miniature Charmander Picture Block Quest","description":"Welcome to Miniature Charmander Picture Block Quest, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Miniature Charmander Picture Block Quest, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Miniature Charmander Picture Block Quest and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TMPN5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miniature-charmander-picture-block-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4AISI","slug":"gymnastics-jigsaw-jam","title":"Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam","description":"Welcome to Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam! Our Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam picture. With a wide variety of Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Gymnastics Jigsaw Jam Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4AISI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gymnastics-jigsaw-jam/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LTR6T","slug":"letter-h-alphabet-lore-jigsaw-victory","title":"Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory","description":"Welcome to Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory! Our Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory picture. With a wide variety of Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Letter H Alphabet Lore Jigsaw Victory Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Sport","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LTR6T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/letter-h-alphabet-lore-jigsaw-victory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8EEOO","slug":"horror-movies-coloring-pages","title":"Horror Movies Coloring Pages","description":"$6f","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8EEOO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/horror-movies-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":39805,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O3NAI","slug":"coloring-pages-for-kid-that-are-8-animals","title":"Coloring Pages For Kid That Are 8 Animals","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Coloring Pages For Kid That Are 8 Animals game! Whether you're a fan of Coloring Pages For Kid That Are 8 Animals or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Coloring Pages For Kid That Are 8 Animals images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Coloring Pages For Kid That Are 8 Animals masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O3NAI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/coloring-pages-for-kid-that-are-8-animals/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"79ANM","slug":"naga-memory-match","title":"Naga Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Naga Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Naga Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Naga Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/79ANM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/naga-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZS3HE","slug":"the-slender-man-slide-puzzle","title":"The Slender Man Slide puzzle","description":"Welcome to The Slender Man Slide puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Slender Man Slide puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Slender Man Slide puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZS3HE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-slender-man-slide-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MHII6","slug":"chibi-anime-coloring-pages","title":"Chibi Anime Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Chibi Anime Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Chibi Anime Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Chibi Anime Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Chibi Anime Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MHII6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/chibi-anime-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"71UN3","slug":"funny-puppy-care","title":"Funny Puppy Care","description":"Are you a puppy lover? Meet cute little puppy who needs you to take good care of him. let's rescue this puppy from dirty tar. Give him a shower to wash off the dirt. Cure the puppy's wound and fix the broken leg. Play mini games and dress up the puppy with various clothes and cute accessories.\nEnjoy this fabulous pet care game!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/71UN3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-puppy-care/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T66N6","slug":"funny-kitty-care","title":"Funny Kitty Care","description":"Meow! Let's take care of an adorable stray kitty! You play as the rescuer who save a cute little kitty. Clean its dirty fur and treat the wounds until the kitty is completely healthy. Try dressing your kitty with various cute clothes and accessories. Enjoy Funny Kitty Care!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T66N6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-kitty-care/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"N4C4E","slug":"funny-heroes-emergency","title":"Funny Heroes Emergency","description":"The heroes look so messy after their fight to save the world. Help them to recover by taking care all of their injuries one by one. Makeover their looks till they are ready to get back into fighting action. Save your favorite heroes!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N4C4E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-heroes-emergency/embed?sid=1","plays":39843,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T3OA5","slug":"tom-and-angela-insta-fashion","title":"Tom and Angela Insta Fashion","description":"Help Tom & Angela to become Instagram famous. Buy and choose clothes, hairstyles, or accessories by following their moods. Make them look stunning on every occasion, take beautiful pictures to post on Instagram and receive lots of likes. Get their insta-ready outfits and have fun!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T3OA5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tom-and-angela-insta-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RN5AC","slug":"tictoc-summer-fashion","title":"Tictoc Summer Fashion","description":"This cute girl needs your help to make her into tictoc star. Buy and choose the right make up and clothes by following the hint. Make her look stylish on every reel to get many likes and money to buy new items.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RN5AC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tictoc-summer-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":39863,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S1HEA","slug":"car-crash-test","title":"Car Crash Test","description":"Car Crash est un jeu passionnant avec une physique réaliste et d'excellents graphismes en trois dimensions, dans lequel vous devez tester la résistance de la voiture en la cassant de différentes manières!\n\n• Voitures accidentées\n• Obtenez des pièces pour cela\n• Acheter des voitures et des cartes\n• Crash cars à nouveau!\nLes machines sont contrôlées par des touches WASD standard ou des flèches sur le clavier.\n\n• C-changer la vue de la caméra\n- Dans la première vue standard, vous pouvez faire pivoter la caméra avec la souris.\n\n• Espace-frein à main\n• Décalage à gauche-Nitro (pour la publicité)\n\nIl y a des boutons sur l'écran de jeu:\n• Réinitialisation du niveau (touche R)\n• Menu principal (touche H)\n• Dilatation du temps (touche T)\n- Il est plus pratique d'effectuer ces actions à partir du clavier, mais vous pouvez également cliquer sur les boutons avec la souris.\n- Pour rendre la souris visible - appuyez sur la touche Échap ou TAB.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S1HEA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/car-crash-test/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE389","slug":"just-bubbles","title":"Just Bubbles","description":"Bubble Shooter pour toute la famille \"Juste des balles \" ne vous laissera pas vous ennuyer.\n\nSpécificité:\n- Beaucoup de chansons Lo-Fi comme musique de fond.\n- Différents types d'arrière-plans et de balles.\n- Support PC et Smartphone-jouez où vous voulez.\n\nLe jeu dispose de 2 modes de jeu:\n- Infini. Ce mode ne vous oblige pas à vous fatiguer. Faites éclater les boules pour le plaisir. La largeur dynamique du champ permet d'ajuster la complexité. Aide à se détendre après une dure journée de travail.\n- Pour un temps. Pour les joueurs sophistiqués. Ici, vous devez tenir le plus longtemps possible, gagner des points et établir des Records. Pour chaque éclatement - 20 points, pour chaque chute - 50 points.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE389/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/just-bubbles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"88108","slug":"zombie-colosseum","title":"Zombie Colosseum","description":"Vous êtes un soldat captif qui a combattu dans une guerre interplanétaire qui a pris fin il y a longtemps. Maintenant, vous êtes utilisé comme un gladiateur dans l'arène pour le plaisir du public. Et vous affrontez d'innombrables hordes de zombies avides de votre perte.\n\nArena aime les forts. En devenant un guerrier plus expérimenté, Vous serez pompé et recevrez une récompense sous la forme d'une boîte d'armes et/ou d'un espace dans un entrepôt. L'essentiel est que pour chaque arme de la boîte, il y ait assez d'espace dans l'entrepôt, sinon l'arme durera jusqu'à des temps meilleurs.\n\nArena aime les gourmands. Pour le meilleur des meilleurs propriétaires de l'arène préparé 7 modèles d'armes, qui sera un excellent outil dans la lutte contre l'ennemi.\n\nArena aime bien. Essayez d'obtenir ces créatures à la peau verte dans la tête pour augmenter les dégâts.\n\nEt rappelez-vous-Zombie Arena ne pardonne pas les erreurs...","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/88108/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aaawwe/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RI4PS","slug":"dino-island-rampage","title":"Dino Island Rampage","description":"You are dinosaur hunter and your mission is to shoot all incoming dinosaurs and try to survive in order to unlock new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RI4PS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dino-island-rampage/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NSN7N","slug":"survival-monk","title":"Survival Monk","description":"Survival Monk - Jumping Monkey Adventure is a Collect banana and survive in this online jumping monkey arcade game. Are you ready to join the Survival Monk in his epic adventure? In this online jumping monkey arcade game, your mission is to collect as many bananas as possible while avoiding obstacles. With intuitive controls and addictive gameplay, Survival Monk is the perfect game to play anytime, anywhere. \n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NSN7N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/survival-monk/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"60EIS","slug":"save-the-pumpkin","title":"Save the Pumpkin","description":"Save the Pumpkin is a fun Halloween adventure game in which you must save the pumpkin from spooky creatures.\nAre you ready for a Halloween adventure? In Save Pumpkin, you will embark on a spooky journey to rescue the pumpkin from evil creatures. Use your quick reflexes to dodge obstacles and defeat enemies in this exciting game. Save the Pumpkin is perfect for all ages and offers endless hours of fun. So, join the adventure today and become a pumpkin hero! Download now and experience the thrill of this fantastic game.\n","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/60EIS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-pumpkin/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"856HM","slug":"traditional-mahjong","title":"Traditional Mahjong","description":"Play the real Mahjong puzzle game. Match up traditional Mahjong tiles until all of tiles are gone in this authentic Chinese style board game. Unlock new levels and zoom into the field, speeding through levels in a bid to become the real Mahjong Ace!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/856HM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mahjong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C71H9","slug":"special-hero","title":"Special Hero","description":"Get your weapons filled with slug & get ready for the ultimate soldier action\n\nUse various weapons filled with slug and power ups to fight your way through a multiple enemies, metal tanks, copters and put an end to the evil army leader!!!\n\nVery awesome challenging action game with amazing graphics and smooth gameplay will make you play this game for hours.\nThis action game will take you through series of classic levels, various enemies and boss battles with amazing experiance of side scrolling platformer games.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C71H9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/special-hero/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"831H2","slug":"ninja-head-ball","title":"Ninja Head Ball","description":"Play as a ninja and score goals with your head in this exciting head Ball game!\nNinja Head Ball is a thrilling soccer game that puts your ninja skills to the test! Play as a ninja and compete in matches against other players from around the world. Use your head to score goals and defeat your opponents.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/831H2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-head-bal/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"63AOE","slug":"balloon-match-master","title":"Balloon Match Master","description":"Balloon Match Master is the perfect game for anyone who loves colorful, fun, and addictive gameplay. With easy-to-learn controls and challenging levels, this game will keep you entertained for hours on end.\nIn Balloon Match Master, your goal is to pop as many balloons as you can in each level. You'll need to match balloons of the same color to make them pop, and you'll need to do it quickly to earn a high score. As you progress through the levels, you'll encounter new challenges and obstacles that will test your skills and keep you on your toes.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/63AOE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-match-master/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZB7N3","slug":"brazil-vs-argentina-challenge","title":"Brazil vs Argentina Challenge","description":"Brazil vs Argentina Challenge Online Head The Ball Games is an exciting online game that allows you to experience the thrill of football in a fun and engaging way. The game is all about heading the ball and scoring as many goals as possible to win the match.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZB7N3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brazil-vs-argentina-challenge/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LIOLD","slug":"diamond-compiler","title":"Diamond Compiler","description":"So, I'm curious: What's your go-to online game when you need a good time and a good challenge? To see how the Diamond Compiler can help you, try it out! Collecting as many diamonds as you can in this game is how you win. There's no stopping the enjoyment, so you can kill time and exercise your brain with this excellent pastime. For this reason, I strongly suggest you give it a shot right this second.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LIOLD/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/diamond-compiler/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"88C4C","slug":"candy-by-colors","title":"Candy by Colors","description":"Can you never get enough sweets? What's your opinion of playing games online? If so, you'll find that Candy by Colors is a lot of fun. This tasty and entertaining game is totally free, and it's great fun to play against your pals and see who can get the highest score. So, why do you linger? Get your game on right now!\n","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/88C4C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-by-colors/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U91C9","slug":"candy-bounce","title":"Candy Bounce","description":"Get ready for a sweet adventure on the basketball court with Candy Bounce Basketball! This addictive game is perfect for players of all ages who love basketball and candy.\nCollect points and unlock new levels as you progress through the game. Challenge your friends to see who can get the highest score!\nCandy Bounce Basketball features colorful graphics, fun sound effects, and exciting gameplay. Whether you're a casual player or a serious gamer, this game will keep you entertained for hours.\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U91C9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-bounce/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E8E3O","slug":"backrooms-abandoned-reality","title":"Backrooms Abandoned Reality","description":"\"Backrooms: Abandoned Reality\" is a thrilling video game where you find yourself trapped in a maze of interconnected backrooms, with a menacing monster as your only enemy. Your mission is to collect valuable data from three different computers scattered throughout the maze and upload it to the main computer to unlock the elevator that leads to freedom. With a randomly generated map, every playthrough is unique, and your survival depends on your ability to outsmart the monster and collect the data before it's too late. Can you escape the backrooms and evade the monster's grasp in this abandoned reality? Play now to find out!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E8E3O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/backrooms-abandoned-reality/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3UAG8","slug":"happy-devil-and-unhappy-angel","title":"Happy Devil and UnHappy Angel","description":"A demon and an angel are needed to survive in hell! hey you and a friend, how about one of you become a devil and the other an angel? The devil and the angel need to get out of hell, help them and get them out of hell. Hell creatures are everywhere. You must be very careful. Monsters and obstacles are too full. Both of you need to reach the orange, be quick, collect the gold, get the key and reach the portal.\n","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3UAG8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/happy-devil-and-unhappy-angel/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8T3WF","slug":"flapflat-twins","title":"FlapFlat Twins","description":"The twin brothers need to collect the diamonds and activate the door. You have to help the twin brothers sister and brother need to get the diamonds. they have special abilities, they can jump from wall to wall. they jump very well. The best ability of the brothers is to jump. Collect the diamonds in order and reach the paper. The only way out of the temple is to collect the diamonds. You have to watch out for obstacles to survive. thorns can cut you. You must be very careful.\n","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8T3WF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flapflat-twins/embed?sid=1","plays":39843,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5CLKE","slug":"stickman-party-electric","title":"Stickman Party Electric","description":"In 2 groups, either as a team of 2 or 4 people, kill all the monsters and help them pass through the portal and move on to the next level. There are too many enemies, you have to kill them all. Be careful, they are everywhere. dont touch the thorns or dodge the flying monsters. you can go through the portal and teleport to the next location.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5CLKE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-party-electric/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"30151","slug":"duo-bad-brothers","title":"Duo Bad Brothers","description":"Youve never seen a couple like this before. zombie brothers are extremely funny and extreme adventurers. These two brothers are embarking on a super adventure. They need to escape from the lab. you need to help them. You have to help them escape. Extremely dangerous plans are swirling in the lab. You learned the plans and now you have to escape. The strong one can open the doors, but the small holes cant go through those holes I know someone who can. little brother can go through all the little holes. Collect all 3 stars and reach the door together. You must collect all the necessary stars to open the door.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/30151/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/duo-bad-brothers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ARDA","slug":"blue-and-red-ball","title":"Blue and Red Ball","description":"two ball brothers need to survive help them they are in a very dangerous forest only you can save them. To save them, they need to find the key safely and while searching for the key, you must escape from the enemies coming from the side. Play with your friend and the two brothers make the ball reach the door.","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ARDA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blue-and-red-ball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LL656","slug":"princess-lovely-fashion","title":"Princess Lovely Fashion","description":"This time, you are the fashion maker! Apply makeup and choose a beautiful outfit, and hairstyle to make them look stunning. Don't forget to take a photo with various effects. Play the best fashion game with Princess Lovely Fashion!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LL656/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/princess-lovely-fashion/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IR62F","slug":"funny-kitty-haircut","title":"Funny Kitty Haircut","description":"Have you ever dreamed of becoming the best hair dresser in your own hair salon? Help the kitties in this new haircut game! Run the best kitty's salon and take care of your virtual kitties. Wash, color, and brush their hair, then create beautiful hairstyles. Don't forget to dress up and accessorize them to become more fashionable!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IR62F/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-kitty-haircut/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7N072","slug":"funny-puppy-emergency","title":"Funny Puppy Emergency","description":"Hello every dogs lover! Ever wanted to be the animal vet doctor?\nTry this game by helping the puppies to heal their sickness. So go fast and solve their problems. Don't forget to dress them up after giving your best treatment!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7N072/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/funny-puppy-emergency/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4C1AY","slug":"yummy-pancake-factory","title":"Yummy Pancake Factory","description":"Yummy tummy! Nothing better than a sweet, tasty pancake for your breakfast. Mix your pancake and pour it in the pan. Once your pancake are fluffy and golden brown, top it with various yummy toppings. Make each pancake perfect! ","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4C1AY/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-pancake-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OURKI","slug":"doc-honeyberry-kitty-surgery","title":"Doc HoneyBerry Kitty Surgery","description":"Play as Doc Honneyberry to help this cute little kitty from the trash. Take care of the injuries and heal the broken bones. After recovery, dress up the kitty with many styles and colors of clothes, pants, shoes, hats, and try different pattern skins. Give the kitty a cute makeover! ","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OURKI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/doc-honeyberry-kitty-surgery/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R4668","slug":"bff-art-class","title":"BFF Art Class","description":"The girls are going to get ready for their school today. But one of them is not in the good mood and she looks so messy. She's really in a hurry and needs your help to pick the best outfits and give her nice makeover. Boost her mood with your fashion ideas and make her more stylish!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R4668/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bff-art-class/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OO42A","slug":"summer-fashion-makeover","title":"Summer Fashion Makeover","description":"Lily has been neglected her look for a long time in pandemic time. When the summer come and things get better, she wants to go to the beach again. But look at her! What a scary look she has now! Let's help makeover her to be pretty and neat again!","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OO42A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/summer-fashion-makeover/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U6M1A","slug":"yummy-donut-factory","title":"Yummy Donut Factory","description":"Let's be a donut chef! Mix all ingredients by following the receipt to make the dough. Create different shapes and bake the donuts. Decorate and throw on some sweet goodies, such as candies, sprinkles, frosting, and many more. You'll be the best donut baker ever!","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6M1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/yummy-donut-factory/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"03848","slug":"dv7-adventurer","title":"DV7 Adventurer","description":"Welcome to the DV7 game you have to go back and forth without getting hit by the discs, your records remain saved, have fun","category":"Aventure","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/03848/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dv7/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"G6NNA","slug":"angry-penguins","title":"Angry Penguins","description":"Angry Penguins is an online shooting game that pits you against other players in a fight to the death. The game is fast-paced and requires quick reflexes and sharp shooting skills. ","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/G6NNA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/angry-penguins/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7E776","slug":"gun-master-3d","title":"Gun Master 3D","description":"Use big arsenal of weapons to shoot hordes of enemies and try to survive in order to unlock new guns.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7E776/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gun-master-3d/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"644S6","slug":"super-suv-driving","title":"Super SUV Driving","description":"Select different newest super suvs and drive them across the big city.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/644S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-suv-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"4HTMM","slug":"ghost-team-shooter","title":"Ghost Team Shooter","description":"You are ghost team soldier and your mission is to eliminate mercenaries training camp inside ancient ruins, use your arsenal of powerful weapons to shoot all incoming enemy forces and try to survive all waves of enemies in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4HTMM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ghost-team-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7I4S6","slug":"special-strike","title":"Special Strike","description":"Use different types of weapons to shoot enemy players on different maps, try to get the highest score by the end of each round in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7I4S6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/special-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O986V","slug":"city-of-vice-driving","title":"City of Vice Driving","description":"City of Vice features next gen graphics and different super cars to drive across the city roads.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O986V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/city-of-vice-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"070SI","slug":"special-strike-operations","title":"Special Strike Operations","description":"You are special forces soldier and your mission is to shoot incoming enemy forces and try to survive each wave of enemies in order to unlock more powerful weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/070SI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/special-strike-operations/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"12OSE","slug":"sugar-skull-coloring-pages","title":"Sugar Skull Coloring Pages","description":"$70","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/12OSE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sugar-skull-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ECPWK","slug":"wolf-tile-block-puzzle","title":"Wolf Tile Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Wolf Tile Block Puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Wolf Tile Block Puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Wolf Tile Block Puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ECPWK/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wolf-tile-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"KA72U","slug":"the-black-eyed-tile-block-puzzle","title":"The Black-Eyed Tile Block Puzzle","description":"Welcome to The Black-Eyed Tile Block Puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn The Black-Eyed Tile Block Puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to The Black-Eyed Tile Block Puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KA72U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/the-black-eyed-tile-block-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ZUAT9","slug":"carnival-jigsaw-picture-puzzle","title":"Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle! Our Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game is a fun and engaging way to test your visual acuity and problem-solving skills. Simply slide the images around until you find the perfect match, and watch as the puzzle pieces come together to form a beautiful Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle picture. With a wide variety of Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle images to choose from, you're sure to find something you love. So why wait? Come on in and start playing our Carnival Jigsaw Picture Puzzle Puzzle Slider game today!\n\n","category":"Course","tags":["board"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ZUAT9/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/carnival-jigsaw-picture-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"COCMM","slug":"mermaid-memory-match","title":"Mermaid Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Mermaid Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Mermaid Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Mermaid Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/COCMM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mermaid-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1TTTA","slug":"lion-tamer-memory-match","title":"Lion tamer Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Lion tamer Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Lion tamer Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Lion tamer Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1TTTA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lion-tamer-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7TT1A","slug":"knight-memory-match","title":"Knight Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Knight Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Knight Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Knight Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7TT1A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knight-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M1R95","slug":"hydra-memory-match","title":"Hydra Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Hydra Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Hydra Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Hydra Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/M1R95/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hydra-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S6RL8","slug":"blin-stars","title":"Blin Stars","description":"blin stars is arcade game","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S6RL8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/blin-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"13883","slug":"save-egg","title":"Save Egg","description":"Do you like platform games and eggs? Then you'll love this game where you'll have to jump from one platform to another, collecting colored balloons to keep the balance of a giant egg that keeps floating. But be careful, it's not all balloons. There are also stars that give you extra points and bats that take them away. How long will you last without breaking the egg or falling? Choose your character and find out in this fun and challenging game!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/13883/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/save-egg/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OT84A","slug":"gravytx-the-gravytoid","title":"GravytX The Gravytoid","description":"Incarnez GravytX un extraterrestre qui a la capacité de contrôler des objets à distance et de manipuler la gravité. Parcourez l'univers pour sauver les peuples qui sont sous la domination des Vodouas (Des êtres malveillants qui veulent conquérir l'univers) et apportez la paix sur leurs Planètes.\n\n• Voici quelques surprises qui vous attendent lors de vos voyages:\n- Plusieurs Planètes à découvrir\n- Des niveaux diversifiés et amusants\n- Des mécaniques de Gameplay unique à chaque Planète\n- Des puzzles amusants à résoudre\n- Plusieurs Boss et Mini-boss à défier!\n- Et plein d'autres choses à découvrir (Nous n'allons pas tout vous dévoiler quand même!)\n\n• Notez que le jeu support les Gamepads!\n\nPréparez vous à vivre des aventures qui dépassent l'entendement humain!","category":"Course","tags":["adventure","arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OT84A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gravytx-the-gravytoid/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"44498","slug":"pixel-peak","title":"Pixel Peak","description":"$71","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/44498/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixel-peak/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"33657","slug":"candy-time","title":"Candy Time","description":"Get ready for a sweet adventure in this colorful match-3 puzzle game! Swipe and match candies to progress through levels and unlock exciting new challenges. With endless fun and delicious rewards, this game will keep you entertained for hours on end. Join the fun and start crushing those candies today!”","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/33657/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/candy-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"U7BU0","slug":"rusher-box","title":"Rusher Box","description":"rusher box is a html5 endless run game, tap the screen to jump and avoid obstacles get stars to get scores, and buy other characters","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U7BU0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rusher-box/embed?sid=1","plays":39438,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7EEEC","slug":"bacteria","title":"Bacteria","description":"Bacteria is a html5 puzzle game, touch to explode small creatures and scatter bullets horizontally or vertically to destroy others.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7EEEC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bacteria/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S9GTC","slug":"cute-puppies-photo-frenzy-sliding-game","title":"Cute Puppies Photo Frenzy Sliding Game","description":"Welcome to Cute Puppies Photo Frenzy Sliding Game, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Cute Puppies Photo Frenzy Sliding Game, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Cute Puppies Photo Frenzy Sliding Game and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S9GTC/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-puppies-photo-frenzy-sliding-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8ENAA","slug":"ninja-escape","title":"Ninja Escape","description":"ninja escape is an html5 arcade game, run and collect coin to score avoid obstacle and ghost","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8ENAA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ninja-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TIG1E","slug":"anime-fox-girl-cute-coloring-pages","title":"Anime Fox Girl Cute Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Fox Girl Cute Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Fox Girl Cute Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Fox Girl Cute Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Fox Girl Cute Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TIG1E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-fox-girl-cute-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0OI6N","slug":"antonio-brown-coloring-pages","title":"Antonio Brown Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Antonio Brown Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Antonio Brown Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Antonio Brown Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Antonio Brown Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0OI6N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/antonio-brown-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E77LI","slug":"demons-slider-block-blitz","title":"Demons Slider Block Blitz","description":"Welcome to Demons Slider Block Blitz, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Demons Slider Block Blitz, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Demons Slider Block Blitz and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E77LI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/demons-slider-block-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8NMAL","slug":"human-cannonball-memory-match","title":"Human Cannonball Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Human cannonball Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Human cannonball Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Human cannonball Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8NMAL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/human-cannonball-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8AK5V","slug":"king-david-memory-match","title":"King David Memory Match","description":"Welcome to King David Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn King David Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to King David Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8AK5V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-david-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"F324I","slug":"big-farming-fun","title":"Big Farming Fun","description":"By playing Big Farming Fun make your way in each level by matching 3 of the same shapes as many as possible to clear the screen before your time runs out. If you get stuck, you can use different powerups to help you clear the screen. Have fun!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/F324I/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/big-farming-fun/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"C0CA0","slug":"create-a-pizza","title":"Create-A-Pizza","description":"Welcome to Create-A-Pizza!\nCreate marvellous pizza's with a variety of realistic looking toppings.","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/C0CA0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/create-a-pizza/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ECMG6","slug":"magicraft-the-story-of-escape","title":"Magicraft The Story of Escape","description":"In this game you have to avoid dangerous traps and solve mysterious puzzles to get to the exit of the castle. At every step you will have to use your skills and reaction not to get trapped or collide with the enemy.\n\nThe game reminds classical platformers and will be interesting both for adults and children. It offers you a great way to have fun and spend time enjoying the funny and attractive gameplay. You can enjoy beautiful pixel graphics, great music and sound effects that will plunge you into an exciting platformer world.\n\nSo, if you are ready for an adventure, join the game and pass all 30 levels to become a real hero!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ECMG6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/magicraft-the-story-of-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LTNE1","slug":"call-to-action-multiplayer","title":"Call to Action Multiplayer","description":"Call to Action Multiplayer features next-gen graphics and big arsenal of modern weapons to shoot rival players on different highly detailed maps.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LTNE1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/call-to-action-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GV841","slug":"military-vehicles-driving","title":"Military Vehicles Driving","description":"Select different military vehicles and test your driving skills across vast desert area.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GV841/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/military-vehicles-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T13ES","slug":"critical-strike-zero","title":"Critical Strike Zero","description":"Critical Strike Zero features next-gen graphics and big arsenal of modern weapons to shoot rival players on different highly detailed maps.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T13ES/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/critical-strike-zero/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S6UNI","slug":"insane-track-supercars","title":"Insane Track Supercars","description":"Select different super cars and drive them across the insane track.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S6UNI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/insane-track-supercars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SK17L","slug":"color-snake","title":"Color Snake","description":"Exciting, Challenge, fun filled connection of color dots and make the snake moving to get high scores.\nShow your magic to achieve high scores in connecting the endless color game.\n\nHow to Play\n- Tap to turn \n- Turn towards the colored dot\n- Match each colored dot to make the snake moving\n- Avoid Edges and keep moving\n- Beat Every Challenge and get a High Score in Endless","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SK17L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/color-snake/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"Z3373","slug":"mazes","title":"Mazes","description":"Classic Fun filled Brain Puzzle game for perfect time breaker.\n You will be trapped in the maze and with your smart brain with fast observation you will have to find the right path to escape the maze.\n\nGreat Experience for exciting levels for all the ages.\n\nplaying this casual puzzle, maze, labyrinth game when you feel mentally fatigued or need to sharpen your mind.\n\nGuide the dot through different routes in this free maze adventure.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z3373/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/mazes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O5SNF","slug":"differences-detective","title":"Differences Detective","description":"Ultimate time passing for all the ages with different levels to sharpen their focussing skills.\nSpot all the differences you see with different Art aspects and shapes.\n\nThis is a classic game of finding differences. The game contains a lot of beautiful illustrations pictures with different designs of Homes, landscapes, outdoor etc.\n\nCan you find the difference between the two pictures?","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5SNF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spotthedifference/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"LCC67","slug":"2048colourballs","title":"2048ColourBalls","description":"Match the Same numbered Color balls to grow big till you reach 2048 in this Amazing number merge block drop puzzle game.\n\nUltimate Web game with unlimited Fun and Engagement.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/LCC67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/2048colourballs/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WO558","slug":"flow-free","title":"Flow Free","description":"Simple and Challenging Brain Puzzle game. Match the Color Dots to make the flow free without any intersections.\nGoal is to connect the same color dots with out intersecting other color flow.\nPair Up and match all the colors in the Grid to close the puzzle and move on.\n\nHappy Time pass!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WO558/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flow-free/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"817N8","slug":"tangram-puzzles","title":"Tangram Puzzles","description":"Exciting, addictive and challenging Puzzle game to understand the Shapes and patterns with this random shape arrangement in Two dimensional environment to provide you classic brain teasing game.\n\nThe tangram is a dissection puzzle consisting of seven flat polygons, called tans, which are put together to form shapes.\n\nThe objective is to replicate a pattern and generally found in a puzzle using all seven pieces without overlap. Alternatively the tans can be used to create original minimalist designs that are either appreciated for their inherent aesthetic merits or as the basis for challenging others to replicate its outline.\n\nDifferent Levels for different skills:\n- Beginner\n- Easy\n- Medium\n- Hard\n- Expert","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/817N8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tangram-puzzles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E2EOI","slug":"zombie-village","title":"Zombie Village","description":"Après l'Apocalypse zombie, Vous avez le seul point d'appui - un village abandonné. Mais Vous avez encore à se battre pour la survie, comme les hordes de créatures ne dorment pas.\n\nSpécificité:\n- En devenant un défenseur plus expérimenté, Vous serez pompé et recevrez une récompense sous la forme d'une boîte d'armes et/ou d'une place dans un entrepôt. L'essentiel est que pour chaque arme de la boîte, il y ait assez d'espace dans l'entrepôt, sinon l'arme durera jusqu'à des temps meilleurs.\n- Disponible pour l'utilisation de 7 modèles d'armes qui seront un excellent outil dans la lutte contre l'ennemi.\n- Essayez de frapper les zombies dans la tête pour augmenter les dégâts infligés.\n- Et rappelez-vous-les zombies veulent toujours manger.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E2EOI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-village/embed?sid=1","plays":39763,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3CA3L","slug":"case-clicker","title":"Case Clicker","description":"\"Case Clicker - сase opening simulator\" is a cases and clicker simulator with various functions.\nWaiting for you:\nCase opening - over 80 cases and collections containing over 800 skins that you can get!\nUpgrade system - over 300 upgrades, increase your income, open new cases, increase your chances for better skins.\nMissions - complete missions and get money and experience.\nInventory - build your own collection of the most expensive and rare skins and knives.\nContracts - exchange 10 skins for 1 better quality skin.\nRanking system - get to the highest rank.\nLots of minigames - play and win the most expensive skins.\n\nBest Features:\n★ Opening Cases.\n★ Opening Collections\n★ Clicker\n★ Contracts\n★ Roulette\n★ Crash\n★ Tower\n★ Ranks\n★ Experience System\n★ Inventory\n★ Enhancements\n★ StatTrak\n★ Player stats\n★ Item quality","category":"Stratégie","tags":["arcade","strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3CA3L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/case-clicker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6L911","slug":"100-balls","title":"100 Balls","description":"Reflex testing skill game with screen tapping for collecting the different colored balls. Each ball you get through the cup rewards you with a different amount of points, depending on the color of the cup. \n\n100 Balls collecting game is an utterly addictive game where the goal is to get the highest score possible!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6L911/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/100-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E80E1","slug":"tim-the-traveler","title":"Tim the Traveler","description":"Help Tim escape to all planets","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E80E1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/timthetraveler/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RO964","slug":"flappy-dragons","title":"Flappy Dragons","description":"Fly high and dodge obstacles in this addictive dragon adventure.\nAre you ready to soar through the skies with Flappy Dragons? In this addictive adventure game, you'll take on the role of a brave dragon and navigate through challenging levels, avoiding obstacles and collecting coins along the way. With intuitive controls and beautiful graphics, Flappy Dragons are sure to keep you entertained for hours on end.\nAs you progress through the game, you'll encounter a variety of obstacles that will test your reflexes and timing. From towering trees to rocky outcroppings, you'll need to be quick and agile to dodge them all. But don't worry - with a little practice, you'll soon be flying like a pro.\nIn addition to the main game, Flappy Dragons also feature a range of special challenges and achievements to keep you coming back for more. So why not join the millions of players already enjoying this exciting dragon adventure? Download Flappy Dragons today and start flying high!\n","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RO964/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/flappy-dragons/embed?sid=1","plays":39016,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J843P","slug":"penguin-jump","title":"Penguin Jump","description":"Penguin Jump - Endless Fun way through endless ice platforms with Penguin Jump!\nAre you ready to take on the challenge of endless fun? Then Penguin Jump is the game for you! With easy-to-learn controls and addictive gameplay, Penguin Jump is perfect for players of all ages. But beware, as the platforms get higher, the jumps get harder. Don't let our little penguin fall into the icy waters below! With stunning graphics and fun sound effects, Penguin Jump is sure to keep you entertained for hours.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J843P/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-jump/embed?sid=1","plays":39836,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"T0NA4","slug":"turtle-ninja","title":"Turtle Ninja","description":"Turtle Ninja: Epic Adventure on an epic adventure to save their city from the evil forces!\nGet ready for an action-packed adventure with Turtle Ninja! The city is under attack by evil forces and its up to the brave and agile Turtle Ninja to save the day. In this epic game, youll join forces with the Turtle Ninja to battle through challenging levels and defeat the enemies that threaten the safety of the city.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/T0NA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/turtle-ninja/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"58PNM","slug":"super-ninja-plumber","title":"Super Ninja Plumber","description":"“Ninja Plumber” is an action-adventure game with a super cute retro style! You play a plumber who transforms into a Ninja to save the mushroom world. Beat the levels and defeat the stone boss to complete your mission! A game with a retro soundtrack that goes very well with the pixel art graphics. Have a good fun!","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/58PNM/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-ninja-plumber/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"HLHFA","slug":"find-the-flag","title":"Find the Flag","description":"Find the flag is a game where you learn and have fun at the same time, learn about different flags from countries around the world and even try to make the highest score possible, the best combination of fun and education.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior","puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HLHFA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/find-the-flag/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC0M3","slug":"recycling-time","title":"Recycling Time","description":"Learn to recycle in this fun game. Play fun mode to learn, or play competitive mode and try to recycle as many items as possible.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC0M3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/recycling-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SZ0Z1","slug":"zombie-squash","title":"Zombie Squash","description":"Welcome to the world of Zombie Squash - a thrilling, action-packed game that will put your skills to the ultimate test! The zombies have invaded your town, and it's up to you to squash them before they take over completely.\n\nBut beware, these zombies aren't your ordinary, slow-moving creatures - they're fast, cunning, and incredibly dangerous. Armed only with your trusty mallet, you must squash as many zombies as you can before they overwhelm you.\n\nWith stunning graphics, heart-pumping sound effects, and challenging gameplay, Zombie Squash will keep you on the edge of your seat from start to finish. Do you have what it takes to survive the zombie apocalypse? Play Zombie Squash now","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SZ0Z1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-squash/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1EYR8","slug":"berry-snakes","title":"Berry Snakes","description":"Enter a world of vibrant colors and fast-paced action in this multiplayer online game. Take control of your snake avatar and navigate through a map filled with multi-colored pellets. Grow your snake by consuming these pellets and outsmart your opponents to become the longest snake in the server. But be careful - one wrong move could mean the end of your journey. Are you ready to rise to the top and become the ultimate champion?","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1EYR8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/berry-snakes/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7H866","slug":"air-fighter","title":"Air Fighter","description":"Take to the skies and engage in thrilling aerial combat in our new air fighter game! Pilot advanced fighter jets and engage in intense dogfights against enemy aircraft. With realistic physics and stunning graphics, you’ll feel like you’re really in the cockpit. Do you have what it takes to become an ace pilot? Play now and find out!","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7H866/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/air-shooter/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R021T","slug":"adventure-quest","title":"Adventure Quest","description":"Embarquez pour un voyage épique dans Adventure Quest! Explorez des mondes vastes, combattez des ennemis féroces et découvrez des trésors cachés. Avec des contrôles intuitifs et des graphismes époustouflants, ce jeu de plateforme vous tiendra en haleine. Êtes-vous prêt pour l’aventure de votre vie?","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R021T/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adventure-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DG686","slug":"medieval-pong","title":"Medieval Pong","description":"Classic game of Pong in a medieval outfit","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DG686/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/medieval-pong/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D76O1","slug":"dollwar-2","title":"DollWar 2","description":"$72","category":"Action","tags":["strategy"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D76O1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/dollwar-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"25O5G","slug":"arrow-legacy","title":"Arrow Legacy","description":"ARROW LEGACY IS ARCADE GAME","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/25O5G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/arrow-legacy/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E131","slug":"house-above","title":"House Above","description":"Welcome to the house over game, you have to throw the houses on top of the other houses without letting them fall","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E131/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/house-above/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SU05E","slug":"super-up","title":"Super Up","description":"Have fun in this fantastic game where you will have to overcome obstacles to accumulate points, what are you waiting for?? go play Super up now and the fun will be guaranteed","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SU05E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-up/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S72E1","slug":"cubo-speed","title":"Cubo Speed","description":"Welcome to speed cube game, you have to merge cubes quickly to match them, when the cube has the same number","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S72E1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cubo-speed/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3FSSS","slug":"fallings-balls","title":"Fallings Balls","description":"Welcome to Fallings Balls, have fun in this game where you have to collect as many balls as possible to increase your Bestscore, what are you waiting for?? Go play Falling Balls now and have fun!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3FSSS/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fallings-balls/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"9MM8M","slug":"small-time","title":"Small Time","description":"Welcome to the little game, avoid enemies to win, have fun, you have a limited time","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/9MM8M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/small-time/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OEE7M","slug":"super-sergeant-zombies","title":"Super Sergeant Zombies","description":"Shoot all zombies on your way and try to find an exit on each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OEE7M/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/super-sergeant-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"DRG53","slug":"martian-driving","title":"Martian Driving","description":"Drive across vast martian surface and try to smash all hostile creatures on your way.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DRG53/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/martian-driving/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"511SI","slug":"critical-strike-global-ops","title":"Critical Strike Global Ops","description":"Critical Strike Global Ops features next-gen graphics and big arsenal of modern weapons to shoot rival players on different highly detailed maps.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/511SI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/critical-strike-global-ops/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"L6E12","slug":"brutal-zombies","title":"Brutal Zombies","description":"Shoot hordes of zombies and try to survive to unlock new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/L6E12/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/brutal-zombies/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OE1T1","slug":"future-soldier-multiplayer","title":"Future Soldier Multiplayer","description":"Future Soldier Multiplayer features next-gen graphics and big arsenal of modern weapons to shoot rival players on different highly detailed maps.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OE1T1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/future-soldier-multiplayer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1T5SA","slug":"homeless-battle-royale","title":"Homeless Battle Royale","description":"Find loot and kill all gopniks in the city in order to win russian battle royale.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1T5SA/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-battle-royale/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"116T7","slug":"full-life-deathmatch","title":"Full-Life Deathmatch","description":"Full-Life Deathmatch is a 3D multiplayer game which features intense deathmatch battles with five highly detailed maps and three types of weapons to shoot rival players, try to get the highest amount of frags in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/116T7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/full-life-deathmatch/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"77P5U","slug":"two-cups","title":"Two Cups","description":"Your girlfriend, Cupgirl, has been smashed by a gigantic nasty cat who loves to break cups along with other stuff...\nThe Cupgirl pieces are lost in countryside and it is up to you to fight back the nasty cat, collect all cup fragments, put your girlfriend back togheter, and live happily ever after with her.","category":"Action","tags":["classics"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/77P5U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/two-cups/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"5B96B","slug":"bapbap","title":"BAPBAP","description":"$73","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/5B96B/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bapbap/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RNRU","slug":"cube-dash-runner","title":"Cube Dash Runner","description":"This is an endless isometric runner game, with 7 characters to choose from settings and its have beautiful color backgrounds and relax music ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RNRU/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cube-dash-runner/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3OF26","slug":"my-dreamy-flora-fashion-look","title":"My Dreamy Flora Fashion Look","description":"Welcome to My Dreamy Flora Fashion Look. Girls! You know that spring is on its way when you see the trees starting to bud and bloom, and the bulbs you planted last fall start to sprout out of the ground. Join with Ellie and their friends to celebrate the most beautiful and colorful season. ","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3OF26/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/my-dreamy-flora-fashion-look/embed?sid=1","plays":39191,"rating":4.6,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"50ANR","slug":"crazy-boat-adventure","title":"Crazy Boat Adventure","description":"Welcome to Crazy Boat Adventure. Jump in your supercharged boat and take a wild ride through twisting canals and rivers. Skill, stunts, and speed will be your best allies as you grab massive air off huge waves, kick out death-defying tricks, and boost your jet ski to victory across a dynamic, power ups, upgrades and shoots","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50ANR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-boat-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AL52N","slug":"wild-animal-care-and-salon","title":"Wild Animal Care And Salon","description":"“Wild Animal Care And Salon” is an interactive simulation game where players take on the role of caretaker and stylist for a variety of wild animals. Players will be responsible for giving treatment, feeding, grooming, and playing with the animals to keep them healthy and happy. As they progress through the game, players will unlock new animals to care for, each with their own unique needs and personalities.","category":"Course","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AL52N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wild-animal-care-and-salon/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"21OTT","slug":"spring-haute-couture-season-1","title":"Spring Haute Couture Season 1","description":"Welcome to Spring Haute Couture Season 1. These celebrities get more excited to be a part of Spring Haute Couture. Join and browse their wardrobe to pick the perfect outfits and costumes. Don’t forget to pick a unique hairstyle. Are you ready to try the perfect one for the girls? Play and have fun!","category":"Action","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/21OTT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/spring-haute-couture-season-1/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"00S2Z","slug":"puzzle-swap","title":"Puzzle Swap","description":"Play this puzzle with 30 pictures of various places in the world.\nTo move the pieces just touch to select them then touch on other to swap","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00S2Z/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzle-swap/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SDZID","slug":"boxes-wizard","title":"Boxes Wizard","description":"Boxes Wizard est un plateformer 2D en pixel art dans lequel vous jouez en tant que magicien armé d'un bâton en bois. Avec le pouvoir de téléporter et de pousser des boîtes, vous naviguerez à travers des niveaux de plus en plus difficiles remplis de casse-têtes et d'obstacles.\n\nÉchangez de place avec les boîtes pour créer de nouveaux chemins et résoudre les casse-têtes. Chaque niveau est soigneusement conçu. Avec des graphismes inspirés des jeux rétro, \"Boxes Wizard\" offre une aventure stimulante et immersive.\n\nAu fur et à mesure que vous progressez, vous devrez affronter des défis de plus en plus difficiles. Utilisez vos pouvoirs magiques et vos compétences pour tous les surmonter et émerger victorieux!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SDZID/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boxes-wizard/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE2S2","slug":"reverse-rush","title":"Reverse Rush","description":"Reverse Rush is a 2D arcade game where you dodge cars to reach the highest score in Reverse Rush!","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE2S2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/reverse-rush/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1RL99","slug":"poppy-retro-basketball","title":"Poppy Retro Basketball","description":"Poppy Basketball a fun sport game to play on.\nThis is the game just to throw as many balls as you can and achieve high score.\nAim the ball exactly in the basket and archive goal.","category":"Sport","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1RL99/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-retro-basketball/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"J024E","slug":"objects-math-game","title":"Objects Math Game","description":"Youre good at maths?\nwell then try to answer all the questions about the tiles where an image of different Objects is hidden underneath!\nhow to play:\ndrag all the left numbered blocks onto the corresponding right tiles covering the picture.\nHave fun and try to unlock all pictures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/J024E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/objects-math-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6EHA3","slug":"kawaii-math-game","title":"Kawaii Math Game","description":"You're good at maths? well then try to answer all the questions about the tiles where an image of Kawaii cute animals is hidden underneath! How to play: drag all the left numbered blocks onto the corresponding right tiles covering the picture.\nHave fun and try to unlock all pictures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6EHA3/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/kawaii-math-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"MY382","slug":"poppy-math-game","title":"Poppy Math Game","description":"Youre good at maths?\nWell then try to answer all the questions about the tiles where an image of poppy is hidden underneath!\nhow to play:\ndrag all the left numbered blocks onto the corresponding right tiles covering the picture.\nHave fun and try to unlock all pictures!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/MY382/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/poppy-math-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11141","slug":"basket-goal","title":"Basket Goal","description":"Basket Goal is a puzzle game with simple mechanics but varied levels. Move the balls and the basket across the playing field to make a goal. Collect coins, unlock new balls. Lots of interesting and challenging levels","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11141/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/basket-goal/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"848M6","slug":"zombie-defence-team","title":"Zombie Defence Team","description":"Zombie Defence Team features cool graphics and four big levels crowded with zombies, play as special forces soldier and use your big arsenal of modern weapons to shoot all undead on your way.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/848M6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-defence-team/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RF686","slug":"counter-craft","title":"Counter Craft","description":"Counter Craft features multiplayer battle on different minecraft themed maps and lots of various types of weapons to buy and shoot all rival players in order to win.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RF686/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/counter-craft/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"19B6V","slug":"biozombie-of-evil","title":"Biozombie of Evil","description":"Biozombie of Evil features crazy zombie shooting in misty town, you play as special forces officer and your mission is to shoot given amount of zombies on each level and successfully survive each day in order to unlock new weapons.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/19B6V/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/biozombie-of-evil/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ELILF","slug":"tangram-puzzle-guess-the-silhouette-of-a-little-man","title":"Tangram puzzle guess the silhouette of a little man","description":"Le but du jeu est de deviner et de collectionner la silhouette d`un homme, qui est cryptée dans les formes géométriques du tangram. Si la silhouette est correctement assemblée, un message apparaîtra et vous passerez au niveau suivant. Pour déplacer une forme, déplacez le pointeur de la souris dessus et, en appuyant sur le bouton gauche dessus, déplacez le pointeur, sans relâcher le bouton, vers l`emplacement souhaité. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez et maintenez la forme avec votre doigt et déplacez-la.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ELILF/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tangram-puzzle-guess-the-silhouette-of-a-little-man/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ESOCP","slug":"protect-the-cheese","title":"Protect the Cheese","description":"Le but du jeu est d`attraper le plus de souris possible tout en protégeant un morceau de fromage.  Pour attraper un petit voleur, cliquez dessus avec le pointeur de la souris. Sur les appareils à écran tactile, appuyez sur la souris avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ESOCP/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/protect-the-cheese/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OH95G","slug":"zombie-shooter-shooting-game","title":"Zombie Shooter-Shooting Game","description":"Winning a surviving battle in an after apocalyptic situation is a skill and let's use that skill to kill the zombies in \" Zombie shooters \" Zombies are living dead, and they became extinct from their human life because of the war between humans. The Breakout of war happens because of the misdeed of humankind, and that destruction's outcome affects others. Zombies or living dead are the victims of those wars outbroke. Zombies are dead but also considered as living things as they can walk around. And This happens in a world when humans are on the way to their extinction and zombies; in other words, the living dead have started to come into life without being alive again. That's when the surviving or left alone humans have to create a battle with the living dead. The zombies are coming into life again without being alive because they want revenge.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OH95G/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/zombie-shooter-shooting-game/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"99522","slug":"rescue-rangers","title":"Rescue Rangers","description":"The Rescue Rangers find themselves trapped in a strange desert temple. They must work together and solve puzzles to escape! ","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/99522/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/rescue-rangers/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O6680","slug":"jewel-royal-saga","title":"Jewel Royal Saga","description":"Asseyez-vous et écoutez le son des bijoux et des pierres précieuses qui tintent lorsque vous les associez. Améliorez vos compétences en matière de résolution de puzzles tout en vous relaxant pendant votre temps libre.\n","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O6680/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jewel-royal-saga/embed?sid=1","plays":39766,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"FF82N","slug":"fruit-king","title":"Fruit King","description":"In the Fruit King game, you need to create fruits around a circle and put them together to score points.\nCollect as many combinations of fruits as possible and become the first in the world leaderboard!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/FF82N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-king/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WUW47","slug":"toilet-rush-draw-to-pee","title":"Toilet Rush Draw To Pee","description":"$74","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WUW47/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/toilet-rush-draw-to-pee/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EE929","slug":"bike-descent","title":"Bike Descent","description":"In this game you will have an unforgettable bike ride straight down the hill. Hold on to your bike with your hands and feet, because the road will be long.\n\nIn the game you will find:\n- Endless descent down\n- Complex physics of controlling the great\n- Competition for the first place in the leaderboard","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE929/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/bike-descent/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OEFIH","slug":"monkeys-fighting","title":"Monkeys Fighting","description":"hyper casual game created by unity its name is monkeys fightings","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OEFIH/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/monkeys-fighting/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"WN0LE","slug":"sweet-halloween","title":"Sweet Halloween","description":"$75","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/WN0LE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sweet-halloween/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"111S0","slug":"twisted-roads","title":"Twisted Roads","description":"hyper casual game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/111S0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/twisted-roads/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"11170","slug":"pressme","title":"Pressme","description":"hyper casual game","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/11170/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pressme/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"R3W0O","slug":"wording","title":"Wording","description":"This is a simple word spelling game where players tap on the letters in the correct order to spell words.\nHow to Play\n Tap on a letter tile which is the first letter of a word.\n Keep the mouse pressed in while scrolling to the next letter in the word.\n Repeat the process until you have spelled out the word.\n Repeat the above process until all words have been spelled.\n In the lower right corner, there is a lightbulb that can be clicked on to provide hints.\n In the lower-left corner, there is a star that shows what progress you have made in finding 15 additional secret words which are not part of the main game levels.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R3W0O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/wording/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3T89U","slug":"buto-square-2","title":"Buto Square 2","description":"Buto Square 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the special red hats while avoiding the square enemies, spikes, ground saws, flying square enemies and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Buto Square\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3T89U/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/buto-square-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8864A","slug":"jezaa","title":"Jezaa","description":"Jezaa is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as an anime girl who have to collect purple cubes while avoiding the monsters, flying creatures, their bullets, ground saws, lava, and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play with increasing difficulty.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for player's movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8864A/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jezaa/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7K1K2","slug":"inuko-2","title":"Inuko 2","description":"Inuko 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect all of the orange ice cream while avoiding the enemies, flying creatures, spikes, saws and giant blades and reach the purple flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Inuko\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7K1K2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/inuko-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"UR665","slug":"adou-adventure","title":"Adou Adventure","description":"Adou Adventure is a 2D Platformer where you have to collect the jewels while avoiding the enemies, rotating blades and spikes and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/UR665/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/adou-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22444","slug":"quevi","title":"Quevi","description":"Quevi is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect all of the metal balls while avoiding the enemy robots, flying robots and their bullets, rotating lasers, giant blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels with increasing difficulty.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement. \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Sport","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22444/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/quevi/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SCUTE","slug":"cute-hamsters-picture-piece","title":"Cute Hamsters Picture piece","description":"Welcome to Cute Hamsters Picture piece, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Cute Hamsters Picture piece, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Cute Hamsters Picture piece and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SCUTE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cute-hamsters-picture-piece/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"CC111","slug":"anime-coloring-books","title":"Anime Coloring Books","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Coloring Books game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Coloring Books or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Coloring Books images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Coloring Books masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/CC111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-coloring-books/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69166","slug":"hippocampus-memory-match","title":"Hippocampus Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Hippocampus Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Hippocampus Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Hippocampus Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69166/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/hippocampus-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"A1AR2","slug":"king-arthur-of-memory-match","title":"King Arthur of Memory Match","description":"Welcome to King Arthur of Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn King Arthur of Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to King Arthur of Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/A1AR2/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/king-arthur-of-memory-match/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"M64EA","slug":"hula-hooper-memory-match","title":"Hula hooper Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Hula hooper