nleash your creativity and make unique Anime Coloring Pages For Kids masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/KOKPG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-coloring-pages-for-kids/embed?sid=1","plays":39811,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AL7OG","slug":"anime-wolf-girl-coloring-pages","title":"Anime Wolf Girl Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Wolf Girl Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Wolf Girl Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Wolf Girl Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Wolf Girl Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AL7OG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-wolf-girl-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2UR14","slug":"stickman-brothers-nether-parkour","title":"Stickman Brothers Nether Parkour","description":"4 stickman brothers survival battle. 4 must survive in front of him. You have to help them in the nether world full of obstacles. Help them by playing with your friends. Hurry up and join this adventure. everywhere is full of danger. Be careful and never, ever fall down. 4 must reach the portal in front of him. There are tasks to be done in each section and they must be fulfilled.","category":"Action","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2UR14/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-brothers-nether-parkour/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"D9S0E","slug":"besties-on-wednesday","title":"Besties on Wednesday","description":"Une jeune meilleure amie va à l'école pour apprendre la magie et se faire de nouveaux amis. Elle a son propre style. La fille préfère les couleurs noires dans les vêtements et un look gothique. Sa colocataire aime les couleurs vives dans ses vêtements. Il ne sera pas facile pour de nouvelles connaissances de trouver un langage commun. Cependant, cette fille brillante n'est pas aussi simple qu'il y paraît à première vue. Elle a ses secrets. Essayez de choisir pour chaque élève une image qui lui convient parfaitement. Et un jour, ces meilleures amies seront meilleures amies.","category":"Arcade","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/D9S0E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/besties-on-wednesday/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"3268O","slug":"noob-baby-vs-pro-baby","title":"Noob Baby vs Pro Baby","description":"In this adventure, a surprise awaits at the end of the episode, as in every adventure, in the forest full of dangers. You have to be very careful to reach that surprise. Complete the levels with your friend without falling down, without tripping over thorns, without being eaten by monsters. Kill all monsters with pro player's sword that sword is very powerful. Don't look at the noob being stupid, he's actually very smart and can open unopenable chests.\n","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/3268O/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/noob-baby-vs-pro-baby/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"VCVE4","slug":"steve-vs-alex-rocketman","title":"Steve vs Alex Rocketman","description":"There are 2 astronauts who need to survive in the world of skyblock, one of them is steve and alex. Help two fellow astronauts and make them reach the portal or they may lose. There are dangerous tnt rocks and rotating sharp tnts everywhere in the world of skyblock, they can kill you if you leave the safe zone, you will die, be very careful. Collect 3 gold bars with your friend and one of you will reach the portal.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/VCVE4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/steve-vs-alex-rocketman/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TPAA4","slug":"pixcade-twins","title":"Pixcade Twins","description":"Have you dived into the world of Pixcade before? come on, what are you waiting for? You and your friend must survive in the pixcade world. You must collect all the gold and kill the monsters. Everything is in your hands, be the ruler of this world with your friend. Be careful, slime monsters can kill you and cause you to start the level again.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TPAA4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/pixcade-twins/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2919E","slug":"alien-bubbles","title":"Alien Bubbles","description":"Alien bubbles is widely inspired by classic games like puzzle bubble. Shoot the arrows at the right moment and hit the aliens of the same color of your arrow. Use the special arrows to deal more damage, but use them wisely, because the number of the special arrows is limited!\nBeat all the levels and save the world!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2919E/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/alien-bubbles/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"IE9OL","slug":"gelatino","title":"Gelatino","description":"Gelatino needs your help! He needs to collect as much ice as he can! \nThe hot summer sun will melt him if he doesn't pay attention!\nBut the road isn't safe: it is full of evil hot suns that will melt Gelatino in no time!\nDestroy them will make you earn more points, but the price to pay to make a highscore could be to high..","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/IE9OL/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gelatino/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"TC066","slug":"crazy-platform","title":"Crazy Platform","description":"Welcome to Crazy Platform, have fun in 3 levels of this fantastic platform where you will have to face monsters and various difficulties, what are you waiting for?? go play Crazy Platform now and have fun!!","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TC066/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crazy-platform/embed?sid=1","plays":39811,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8V168","slug":"voltier-2","title":"Voltier 2","description":"Voltier 2 is a 2D platformer where you have to collect power boxes while avoiding the enemies, bullets, spikes, water, rotating blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level.  There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed. \n    \nThis is the second installment of the \"Voltier\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the players movement.\nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8V168/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/voltier-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8AA9L","slug":"ball-stars","title":"Ball Stars","description":"ball stars is game arcade","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8AA9L/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/ball-stars/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"8AS68","slug":"small","title":"Small","description":"Welcome to small game, avoid enemies to win, have fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8AS68/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/small/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1P16K","slug":"stickman-huggy-escape","title":"Stickman Huggy Escape","description":"Have you ever played a game full of adventures like this before? yes, join this adventure too. Help stickman huggy brothers and escape from prison. They need to escape, help them and escape. The cops are looking for them everywhere. Watch out, cameras are everywhere. Collect the keys and open the doors to open a lot of different doors. complete the sections.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1P16K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/stickman-huggy-escape/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"EEE98","slug":"cyberpuke","title":"Cyberpuke","description":"Cyberpuke features cool graphics and big arsenal of weapons, you are special agent and your mission is to shoot all cyber cops and successfully reach the extraction point on each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EEE98/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/cyberpuke/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AZ6UI","slug":"puzzles-fantastic-creatures","title":"Puzzles - Fantastic Creatures","description":"Découvrez le monde unique des images neurologiques dans le jeu \"Puzzles - créatures fantastiques\". Collectionnez 30 belles images créées par un réseau neuronal.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AZ6UI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/puzzles-fantastic-creatures/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"15TG8","slug":"gravity-error","title":"Gravity Error","description":"\"science has gone too far, its final product being the \"End of the world\". Our hero can do nothing but fight until he has no fight in him left.\"","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/15TG8/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/gravity-error/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"22E43","slug":"grand-city-car-thief","title":"Grand City Car Thief","description":"You are car thief in Grand City and your mission is to steal cars across the city and drive them to your garage.","category":"Course","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/22E43/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-city-car-thief/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"P8635","slug":"goal-penalties","title":"Goal Penalties","description":"Welcome to Goal Penalties, you have to play this fantastic game trying to score the goalkeeper and accumulate points and increase the best score, what are you waiting for?? go play Goal Penalties now and have fun!!!","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/P8635/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/goal-penalties/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"7187C","slug":"catch-an-ant","title":"Catch an Ant","description":"Le but du jeu est d`attraper le plus de fourmis possible. Pour attraper une fourmi, cliquez dessus avec le pointeur de la souris. Sur les appareils à écran tactile, appuyez sur la fourmi avec votre doigt.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7187C/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/catch-an-ant/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OIAL6","slug":"balloon-slicer","title":"Balloon Slicer","description":"Balloon Slicer is a casual puzzle game where you need to aim and throw your saw at the balloons. Slice and pop them all to get more stars and rewards. Find keys to open secret chests and find more skins or extra rewards. Jump off the walls and slash everything! There are 50 challenging levels, enjoy!","category":"Sport","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OIAL6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/balloon-slicer/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"OASM7","slug":"grand-zombie-swarm","title":"Grand Zombie Swarm","description":"Grand Zombie Swarm features open world zombie shooting, you are special forces soldier and your mission is to use different types of weapons to shoot hordes of zombies and try to survive each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OASM7/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/grand-zombie-swarm/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NN0P1","slug":"fantasy-sniper","title":"Fantasy Sniper","description":"Use your sniper rifle to find and shoot all fantasy creatures on each level.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NN0P1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fantasy-sniper/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"NE9TI","slug":"russian-strike","title":"Russian Strike","description":"Russian Strike features intense multiplayer combat on different maps with russian environment, select various powerful weapons to shoot all rival players and try to get the highest score in order to win each round.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/NE9TI/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/russian-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6W6E1","slug":"lone-wolf-strike","title":"Lone Wolf Strike","description":"Lone Wolf Strike features modern graphics and intense combat with lots of enemies, your mission is to use different types of weapons and try to shoot all incoming enemy forces before the time runs out.","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6W6E1/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/lone-wolf-strike/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"2R340","slug":"aroka-2","title":"Aroka 2","description":"Aroka 2 is a 2D anime themed platformer where you play as a cute anime girl who have to collect all of the bottles containing medicine while avoiding the enemy monsters, super fast monsters, flying creatures, rotating blades, spikes, fire and reach the yellow flag in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.  \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Aroka\"series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2R340/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/aroka-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"69R31","slug":"t-rally","title":"T-Rally","description":"Drive different rally cars and try to smash all terrorists on track in order to win and unlock new vehicles.","category":"Course","tags":["sports"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/69R31/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/t-rally/embed?sid=1","plays":39840,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1NKR6","slug":"snake-survival","title":"Snake Survival","description":"snake survival is arcade game","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1NKR6/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/snake-survival/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"S49WO","slug":"miles-tails-prower","title":"Miles Tails Prower","description":"Get ready to join Miles Tails Prower on an exciting adventure through Sonic's world in this fun and challenging drag and drop puzzle game! In Tails' Adventure, you'll need to use your problem-solving skills to help Tails navigate through different levels by dragging and dropping objects in the right places.\n\nAs a platformer game, Tails will need to jump, run, and dodge obstacles to reach the end of each level. But to do that, he'll need your help to move boxes, unlock doors, and even build bridges with the objects you drag and drop.\n\nWith each level, the puzzles get more challenging, and you'll need to use your creativity and quick thinking to find the right solutions. But don't worry, Tails will be there to guide you every step of the way.\n\nIf you're a fan of puzzle games, platformers, or the Sonic the Hedgehog franchise, Tails' Adventure is the perfect game for you. Join Tails on this epic adventure and show off your puzzle-solving skills today!","category":"Aventure","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S49WO/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/miles-tails-prower/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"1E9N5","slug":"banana-monkey","title":"Banana Monkey","description":"Welcome to the banana monkey game, you have to overcome the obstacles go and get the banana and take it to the base, good luck and have fun","category":"Arcade","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1E9N5/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/banana-monkey/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"822OT","slug":"fyer-bot-2","title":"Fyer Bot 2","description":"Fyer Bot 2 is a 2D Sci-fi themed platformer where you have to collect fire cubes while avoiding the enemy Fyer bots, flying bots, bullets, turrets and their bullets, spikes, giant blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.  \n\nThis is the second installment of the original \"Fyer Bot\" series.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.      \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/822OT/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/fyer-bot-2/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"6ES74","slug":"curses-slide-puzzle","title":"Curses Slide Puzzle","description":"Welcome to Curses Slide puzzle, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Curses Slide puzzle, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Curses Slide puzzle and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6ES74/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/curses-slide-puzzle/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E7LRG","slug":"crystals-sliding-image-adventure","title":"Crystals Sliding Image Adventure","description":"Welcome to Crystals Sliding Image Adventure, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Crystals Sliding Image Adventure, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Crystals Sliding Image Adventure and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E7LRG/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/crystals-sliding-image-adventure/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"ELCBE","slug":"creepy-doll-photo-block-blitz","title":"Creepy Doll Photo Block Blitz","description":"Welcome to creepy doll Photo Block Blitz, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn creepy doll Photo Block Blitz, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to creepy doll Photo Block Blitz and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ELCBE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/creepy-doll-photo-block-blitz/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GEN9N","slug":"anime-chibi-coloring-pages","title":"Anime Chibi Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Chibi Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Chibi Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Chibi Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Chibi Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GEN9N/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-chibi-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0TR67","slug":"anime-cat-girl-coloring-pages","title":"Anime Cat Girl Coloring Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Cat Girl Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Cat Girl Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Cat Girl Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Cat Girl Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0TR67/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-cat-girl-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":39843,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RM21A","slug":"harpy-memory-match","title":"Harpy Memory Match","description":"Welcome to Harpy Memory Match, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Harpy Memory Match, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Harpy Memory Match and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RM21A/