ng Pages","description":"Discover the joy of coloring with our free Anime Boys Coloring Pages game! Whether you're a fan of Anime Boys Coloring Pages or just love to create art, our game has something for everyone. With a wide variety of Anime Boys Coloring Pages images to choose from, as well as different coloring tools and effects, you can unleash your creativity and make unique Anime Boys Coloring Pages masterpieces. Suitable for both kids and adults, our user-friendly game is perfect for anyone looking to de-stress and have fun. So why wait? Click play now and let your imagination run wild!","category":"Puzzle","tags":["junior"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/6P6IR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/anime-boys-coloring-pages/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"RI68K","slug":"creatures-picture-block-quest","title":"Creatures Picture Block Quest","description":"Welcome to Creatures Picture Block Quest, a classic puzzle game where players must slide tiles to reassemble a picture. Move the blocks by touching or clicking on them to solve the puzzle.\n\nIn Creatures Picture Block Quest, players are challenged to solve the puzzle by sliding tiles to reassemble a picture. The objective of the game is to move the blocks by touching or clicking on them until the picture is complete. Welcome to Creatures Picture Block Quest and enjoy solving the puzzle.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/RI68K/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/creatures-picture-block-quest/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"AAA77","slug":"sphere-assassin","title":"Sphere Assassin","description":"$76","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AAA77/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/sphere-assassin/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"B4BB4","slug":"boing-bang","title":"Boing Bang","description":"Boing Bang is a classic arcade game inspired by games like Pang! Complete all the levels trying to achieve the best score ever!\nTo win you have to destroy all the bouncing balls in the level, without getting hit! ","category":"Sport","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B4BB4/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/boing-bang/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"GNZAZ","slug":"tangram-puzzle-guess-the-number","title":"Tangram Puzzle Guess the Number","description":"Le but du jeu est de deviner et de collecter la silhouette du nombre de 1 à 7, qui est cryptée dans les formes géométriques du tangram. Si la silhouette est correctement assemblée, un message apparaîtra et vous passerez au niveau suivant. Pour déplacer une forme, déplacez le pointeur de la souris dessus et, en appuyant sur le bouton gauche dessus, déplacez le pointeur, sans relâcher le bouton, vers l`emplacement souhaité. Sur les écrans tactiles, appuyez et maintenez la forme avec votre doigt et déplacez-la.","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/GNZAZ/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/tangram-puzzle-guess-the-number/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"0PCCN","slug":"penguin-ice-breaker","title":"Penguin Ice Breaker","description":"Penguin Ice Breaker is a puzzle game. In this game, you need to break the Iceberg and finish the level But keep in mind that icebergs have a count just not that count, and jump that number of times to break the icebergs. Looks easy but it's difficult to play.  Enjoy and have fun","category":"Puzzle","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/0PCCN/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/penguin-ice-breaker/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"SDPAE","slug":"drive-space","title":"Drive Space","description":"Space Velocity is an endless space-themed game where players control a spacecraft traveling through the vast expanse of the universe. The game offers an immersive experience with stunning graphics, captivating sound effects, and a variety of challenging obstacles to overcome.","category":"Course","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/SDPAE/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/drive-space/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"O1111","slug":"voltier","title":"Voltier","description":"Voltier is a 2D platformer where you have to collect stolen power boxes while avoiding the enemies, spikes, water bodies, rotating blades and reach the Exit door in order to go to the next level. There are 8 levels to play and the difficulty increases as you proceed.\n\nControls:\nUse \"WASD\" or \"Arrow\" keys for the player's movement.   \nUse \"W\" or \"Up\" arrow key twice for double jump.","category":"Aventure","tags":["adventure"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O1111/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/voltier/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},{"id":"E93DR","slug":"world-of-war-hunters","title":"World of War Hunters","description":"World of War Hunters is a 2D platformer in which player has to navigate through  a series of enemy installations by firing at them. These installations are in the form of howitzers, drones and mines. They are various guns to choose from, each having a specific range but ammo does deplete as you shoot. More ammo and lives are available for picking as the game proceeds. ","category":"Action","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E93DR/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/world-of-war-hunters/embed?sid=1","plays":5000,"rating":3.5,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"},